NK078(tshu)001:1: // m+aa y+aa u ba di sha pa n+pa s+saya&a&a&a kra
NK078(tshu)001:2: ma s+ya bri t+ti b+h+aa shi tam ma ha ra
NK078(tshu)001:3: t+na s+ya dza lam ke ta ka na ma bi
NK078(tshu)001:6: sgyu 'phrul man ngag lam gyi rim pa'i 'grel bshad
NK078(tshu)001:7: rin po che'i chu dwangs zhes bya ba bzhugs so
NK078(tshu)001:8: // bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:9: bdag don dgongs pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:10: gzhan don gzugs sku gdul bya'i ngor snang zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:11: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dbyer med rdo rje'i sku //
NK078(tshu)001:12: rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gtso bo nyid la 'dud //
NK078(tshu)001:13: 'phags mchog kun gyi gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin cing //
NK078(tshu)001:14: zab don dbyer med rang snang mngon byas pas //
NK078(tshu)001:15: mkhyen brtse nus ldan 'gro ba'i mgon dang gnyen //
NK078(tshu)001:16: 'dren pa mtshungs med drin chen rnams la 'dud //
NK078(tshu)001:17: sgyu 'phrul man ngag gzhi las 'bras bu'i don //
NK078(tshu)001:18: 'grel bshad bdag gis brtsam par mi 'os kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:19: don byas bshes gnyen rnams kyis bskul phyir du //
NK078(tshu)001:20: bla mas gsungs bzhin rin chen chu dwangs bri //
NK078(tshu)001:21: rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK078(tshu)001:22: ba'i man ngag lam gyi rim pa 'di nyid bshad
NK078(tshu)001:23: pa'i dbang du byas na gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:24: 'chad nyan ji ltar bya ba'i tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:25: gang 'chad par byed pa dam chos kyi rnam bzhag dang /
NK078(tshu)001:26: 'chad nyan mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan no //
NK078(tshu)001:28: gang la nyan pa'i bshes gnyen gyi rang bzhin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:29: gang gis nyan pa gang zag gi rang bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:33: de ltar bshad pa'i phan yon no //
NK078(tshu)001:35: mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:36: thos pa chung la nga rgyal che ba'i slob dpon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:37: thugs rje chung la gdug rtsub che ba'i slob dpon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:38: gdams pa chung la 'dod pa che ba'i slob dpon dang gsum spangs te /
NK078(tshu)001:40: log par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK078(tshu)001:41: log lta'i spyi brtol khro gtums che //
NK078(tshu)001:42: sdig spyod don dang mi ldan yang //
NK078(tshu)001:43: bdag 'di nges pa kho na zhes //
NK078(tshu)001:44: bab tshol snyan brgyud bslu byed bslad //
NK078(tshu)001:46: gnyis pa bzang po'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:47: thos pa dang gdams ngag tu ldan pa'i bla ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:48: rtogs pa dang nyams myong du ldan pa'i bla ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:49: thugs rje dang byin rlabs su ldan pa'i bla ma ste gsum bstan no //
NK078(tshu)001:50: khyad par gsang sngags kyi slob dpon ni /
NK078(tshu)001:51: chos kun mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas lugs rtogs shing goms pas spyod pa dang 'brel la /
NK078(tshu)001:52: brgyud pa'i zam ma chad pa /
NK078(tshu)001:53: dbang bzhi'i chu bo ma nub pa /
NK078(tshu)001:54: byin rlabs nyams rtogs kyi mdangs ma yal ba /
NK078(tshu)001:55: snyan brgyud gdams ngag gi gnad ma 'chug pa /
NK078(tshu)001:56: snying rje phan sems kyis slob ma 'dzin pa'i gnyer dang ldan pa /
NK078(tshu)001:57: gsang sngags kyi rgyud gzhung phrin las chog khrigs tha dag la mkhas pa dang ldan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:58: 'di nyid kyi le'u bdun pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:59: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:60: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK078(tshu)001:64: bla med snying pos smin pa'i rkyen //
NK078(tshu)001:65: blo gros chen po dri ba'i yul //
NK078(tshu)001:66: lam ston sa mkhan bshes gnyen mgon //
NK078(tshu)001:67: mun sel sgron ma rin po che //
NK078(tshu)001:68: mthong mig dbang po yod pa rnams //
NK078(tshu)001:69: chu bo rab med sgrol ba'i gru //
NK078(tshu)001:70: 'jigs pa'i rdzong chen brten pa'i mkhar //
NK078(tshu)001:71: 'khor ba gcong 'byin sman pa'i mchog /mtsho gling rin chen len byed pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:72: ded dpon dam pa'i bla ma la //
NK078(tshu)001:73: sngon du nges par shes par bya //
NK078(tshu)001:75: gnyis pa 'chang tshul la gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:77: shes lo dang mkhas lo'i sgo nas mi 'chad /
NK078(tshu)001:78: khe grags dang bsnyen bkur gyi sgo nas mi 'chad /
NK078(tshu)001:79: rgyas 'debs dang zil gnon gyi sgo nas mi bshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:80: gnyis pa don gnyer la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:81: mkhas pa'i shes rab dang ldan pas gdul bya'i the tshom gcod cing yid ches pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:82: brtse ba'i thugs rje dang ldan pas gdul bya rjes su bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:83: sbyor ba'i bzod pa dang ldan pas ngal dub med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:85: bshad bya la mkhas pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:86: spyir shes bya rab 'byed la mkhas na legs mod kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:87: 'on kyang rang gi rgyud gzhung las blangs la mkhas
NK078(tshu)001:88: shing don khong du chud cing the tshom chod pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:89: // gnyis pa 'chad byed la mkhas pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:92: ji ltar bshad kyang 'thad pa gsum pos ngag 'brel cing rang gis brjod bde /
NK078(tshu)001:94: gnyis ka'i rna bar snyan cing yid chags pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:95: gsum pa kun spyod la mkhas pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:96: tshul 'chos ma yin par rang gi sgom gsum chos
NK078(tshu)001:97: dang mthun pa'i sgo nas gdul bya dwangs ba 'dren
NK078(tshu)001:98: cing dad pa'i gnas su gyur pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:99: gzhan gyi kun spyod la mkhas pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:100: gdul bya dbang po rno rtul dang rjes su mthun pa'i chos bstan pa la mkhas shing bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:101: gzhan yang sems can gyi don bya ba'i phyir bshad kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:102: rang gi che ba 'dod pa'i phyir ma yin /
NK078(tshu)001:103: snying rje chen pos bstan gyi /
NK078(tshu)001:106: 'khor ba rgyun gcod pa'i phyir bstan gyi /
NK078(tshu)001:107: nyon mongs pa spel ba'i phyir ma yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:108: gsum pa gsang sngags kyi don rtogs nas gzhan la bshad pa'i phan yon ni /
NK078(tshu)001:110: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:111: yon tan spyi gtsug dpag med nyid du 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:112: de yang ji lta bu zhe na //
NK078(tshu)001:114: drang srong rnal 'byor ka yas ni //
NK078(tshu)001:115: drang srong rnal 'byor mang sde la //
NK078(tshu)001:116: theg chen gsang ba'i basngagasa pa brjod //
NK078(tshu)001:117: de rnams nges par bkod pa las //
NK078(tshu)001:118: mang pos rigs chen 'dzin pa thob //
NK078(tshu)001:119: gang der basngagasa pas brjod byed pas //
NK078(tshu)001:120: gsang bdag chos kyi rgyal por 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:121: des na theg chen gsang ba 'di //
NK078(tshu)001:122: kun nas basngagasa pas brjod par gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:123: des ni nga yi dgongs pa thob //
NK078(tshu)001:125: gnyis pa gang gis nyan pa gang zag gi rang bzhin la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:131: shes rab chung la nyon mongs pa che ba'i slob ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:132: dad pa chung la ser sna che ba'i slob ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:133: brtson 'grus chung la 'dod pa che ba'i slob ma de gsum spangs te ye shes gting rdzogs las /
NK078(tshu)001:134: yang dag don gyi lta ba gsang ba 'di //
NK078(tshu)001:135: gdams ngag phyin ci log dang lta ba dman //
NK078(tshu)001:138: nor 'phong kha ral la sogs snod min la /
NK078(tshu)001:139: 'di bstan gnyis ka bsregs phyir rab tu gsang /
NK078(tshu)001:141: gnyis pa bzang po'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:142: dad pa dang shes rab tu ldan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:143: mos gus dang gtong phod dang ldan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:144: ngang rgyud brtson 'grus su ldan pa'i slob ma bsten pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:145: klong gsal nyi ma'i rgyud las /
NK078(tshu)001:146: dad ldan snying rje gtong phod che //
NK078(tshu)001:147: rgyud dul sdig 'dzem dbang po rno //
NK078(tshu)001:148: gsang thub nyams len brtul zhugs spyod //
NK078(tshu)001:149: skyo shas sdug sran snying rus che //
NK078(tshu)001:150: de ni gsangs sngags gsang ba'i snod //
NK078(tshu)001:152: gnyis pa nyan pa'i tshul la gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:155: nga rgyal dang ni ma dad dang //
NK078(tshu)001:156: don du gnyer ba med nyid dang //
NK078(tshu)001:157: phyi rol rnam g.yeng yid bsdu ba //
NK078(tshu)001:158: skyo ba nyan pa'i dri ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:160: gzhan yang khe dang grags pa'i sgo nas mi nyan /
NK078(tshu)001:161: ngo bsrung dang tshul 'chos kyi sgo nas mi nyan /
NK078(tshu)001:162: rang dang gzhan khyad lta'i sgo nas mi nyan no //
NK078(tshu)001:164: gzhi dad pa brtan por btud /
NK078(tshu)001:169: snying gi bum par bsog /don gyi sbrang rtsi myong dgos par gsungs te /
NK078(tshu)001:170: sdong po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK078(tshu)001:171: bdag nyid la nad pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:172: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sman pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:173: chos la sman gyi 'du shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:174: nan tan rjes su bsgrub pa la nad 'tsho ba'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:175: gzhan yang 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho las
NK078(tshu)001:176: bsgral bar 'dod pa la dam pa'i chos min pa
NK078(tshu)001:177: cis kyang mi phan pas de'i phyir nyan /
NK078(tshu)001:178: chos de ston pa'i bla ma de ni yang dag
NK078(tshu)001:179: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dngos dang 'dra ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:181: de'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i chos de ni shi gso'i
NK078(tshu)001:182: sman bas kyang gces pa de'i phyir kyang nyan no
NK078(tshu)001:183: // gsum pa de ltar nyan pa'i phan yon ni /
NK078(tshu)001:184: byams pa seng ge'i sgras zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK078(tshu)001:185: bstan 'chos bstan pa'i dus bstan phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:188: nyan phyir klog pa smos ci dgos //
NK078(tshu)001:190: khyad par gsang sngags thos pa'i phan yon ni /
NK078(tshu)001:192: dper na gyi ling sgrog bkrol ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:193: rnam grol thos bsam sgo mo yis //
NK078(tshu)001:194: shes rgyud kun grol thogs med 'gro //
NK078(tshu)001:196: gnyis pa gang 'chad par byed pa dam chos kyi rnam bzhag la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:197: gang zag 'jug ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:198: de nyid kyi don ma nor bar shes par bya ba'i phyir bshad pa'i thabs bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:199: bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs dang gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:200: dang po chos ngos bzung ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:202: de la theg pa che chung gnyis las chen po /
NK078(tshu)001:203: theg chen la mdo sngags gnyis las sngags /
NK078(tshu)001:204: sngags la phyi nang gnyis las nang pa /
NK078(tshu)001:205: de la ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum las ma h+aa /
NK078(tshu)001:206: de la pha rgyud ma rgyud gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum las 'dir gnyis med kyi rgyud /
NK078(tshu)001:207: de la rgyud dang man ngag gnyis las 'dir man ngag /man ngag la /
NK078(tshu)001:208: rgyud kyi don mngon par rtogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:209: bslab cing nyams su blang ba'i man ngag gnyis las 'dir tha ma /
NK078(tshu)001:210: de la gtso bo dang cha rkyen gnyis las 'di
NK078(tshu)001:211: ni lam gyi ngo bo ting nge 'dzin gtso che
NK078(tshu)001:213: gnyis pa bshad pa'i thabs ni /
NK078(tshu)001:214: 'di nyid rgyud la brten pa'i man ngag yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:215: rtsis mgo lngas 'chad par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:217: thos chung gsar bu yid chos bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:218: man ngag spyi don rtsis mgo klad nas gzhom //
NK078(tshu)001:222: dgongs pa khrol ba'i slob dpon dang //
NK078(tshu)001:223: mtshan lnga ldan pa'i dam chos dang //
NK078(tshu)001:224: theg pa sde snod 'byung ba'i khung //
NK078(tshu)001:225: nye bar tshig gi btus gnas dang //
NK078(tshu)001:226: don du 'gyur ba'i dgos pa rnams //
NK078(tshu)001:227: bstan bcos kun gyi rtsis mgo yin //
NK078(tshu)001:228: zhes gsungs pa'i don lnga las /
NK078(tshu)001:229: dang po khung btsun zhing yid ches par bya ba'i phyir slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:230: rtsom pa po tshad rab 'bring tha ma gsum dang
NK078(tshu)001:231: ldan pa'i mkhas pa grub pa thob pa'i slob dpon
NK078(tshu)001:232: chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa yin te
NK078(tshu)001:234: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa rab //
NK078(tshu)001:235: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro yi //
NK078(tshu)001:236: lung chen thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK078(tshu)001:237: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK078(tshu)001:238: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:240: gnyis pa bka' dang mi 'gal zhing rgyud gang nas btus pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:242: stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud dag las //
NK078(tshu)001:244: thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud las btus so //
NK078(tshu)001:245: gsum pa theg pa'i rang gzhung tshugs par bya ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:246: phyir phyogs gar gtogs pa ni ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK078(tshu)001:248: bzhi pa bstan pa la mtshan nges shing don gyi
NK078(tshu)001:249: mdo tsam zhig rtogs par bya ba'i phyir mtshan ni
NK078(tshu)001:250: / spyir mtshan gyi 'dogs lugs la lnga las /
NK078(tshu)001:253: lam rnam par bkod pa zhes pas /
NK078(tshu)001:254: don rang gi ngo bo la mtshan btags pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:255: lnga pa brtsam pa la don yod par bya ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:256: phyir gang zag gang gi don du mdzad pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:258: dam pa'i rigs can dra ma dang //
NK078(tshu)001:259: de rjes ma 'ongs skal ldan phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:261: slob dpon nyid kyi dngos 'khor dang ma 'ongs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:262: gang zag las 'phro skal ba dang ldan pa rnams
NK078(tshu)001:264: gsum pa bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:265: man ngag rtsom pa la 'jug pa'i yan lag klad kyi don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:266: chos kun khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir gzhung gi don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:267: man ngag brtsam pa mthar phyin pa mjug gi don no //
NK078(tshu)001:270: dang po bar chad bsal zhing tshogs rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir phyag bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:272: mos zhes pa bshad pa'i gzhir bzhag nas /
NK078(tshu)001:273: de'i khyad par gyi chos la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:279: dang po gang la mos na /
NK078(tshu)001:280: sam kri ta'i skad la sh+ri /
NK078(tshu)001:282: de la dpe dang don gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:283: dpe ni 'jig rten na mi nor phun sum tshogs pa la dpal zer ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:284: don la legs pa'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa la 'jug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:285: de la thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa gnyis so //
NK078(tshu)001:286: dang po ni theg 'og gis drangs pa'i 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:287: thob pa ni rtogs pa bdag gi dpal yin la
NK078(tshu)001:288: / des gdul bya'i don mdzad pa ni thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:289: gnyis pa de la khyad par gya dapala la gsuma las /
NK078(tshu)001:290: dang po rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dapala ni /
NK078(tshu)001:291: gzhi rang byung gi ye shes la 'bras bu che
NK078(tshu)001:292: yon sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am nyi
NK078(tshu)001:293: shu rtsa lnga lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:294: yungs dkar la mar nag lhun gyis grub pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:295: gnyis pa rtogs pa bdag gi dapala ni /
NK078(tshu)001:296: don de nyid rtogs shing goms pas 'bras bu sku
NK078(tshu)001:297: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor mngon du gyur pa
NK078(tshu)001:298: ste / nyi ma nam mkha'i mthongs su shar ba lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:299: gsum pa thugs rje chen po zhar las byung ba'i dapala ni /
NK078(tshu)001:300: de ltar bdag don du 'bras bu thob tsam na /
NK078(tshu)001:301: gzhan gdul bya thams cad la mdzad pa phrin las ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:303: dro 'jam rtsol med kyis gzhan gyi mun pa dang 'khyag pa shugs kyis zhu ba bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:304: de ltar dpal gsuma po ngo bo nyid kyisa ldana pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:306: rang bzhin mngon byas ma lus re ba skong //
NK078(tshu)001:308: rin po che rdo rje pha lam gyis gzi mchong
NK078(tshu)001:309: gi dngos po thams cad phar la 'joms shing tshur
NK078(tshu)001:310: gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa lta bu don rang
NK078(tshu)001:312: lta ba ngan pa dang gzhi dang lam gyi nyes
NK078(tshu)001:313: pa thams cad 'joms shing tshur la gang gis nod
NK078(tshu)001:314: pas mi tshugs pa ni phrin las gzhan 'joms pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:315: rdo rje ste / rgyas pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:316: 'joms shing cis kyang mi tshugs pas //
NK078(tshu)001:317: rang byung chen po lha yi lha //
NK078(tshu)001:318: de ltar rtogs pa'i rig pa la //
NK078(tshu)001:319: badz+ra zhes su btags pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:321: nyes skyon dang bral ba des na /
NK078(tshu)001:322: thugs rang byung gi ye shesa kyi rang snang la
NK078(tshu)001:323: 'dus ma byas kyi gzugs sku ni ngo bo 'dus
NK078(tshu)001:324: ma byas pa'i rdo rje ste /
NK078(tshu)001:326: rgyu rkyen bral ba'i skad cig ma //
NK078(tshu)001:327: rang byung nyid du byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:329: de nyid las 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan rnams
NK078(tshu)001:330: gzhan nas ma batsala bar sku gsung thugs yon phrin
NK078(tshu)001:331: las lnga'am nyer lnga rdzogas pa ni yon tan rtsol
NK078(tshu)001:332: ba med pa'i rdo rje ste /
NK078(tshu)001:334: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan las //
NK078(tshu)001:335: rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyi shu lnga //
NK078(tshu)001:337: de nyid rgyu rkyen dang bral te gnyen po gang
NK078(tshu)001:338: gis mi shigas pa ni mtshan nyid skye 'jig dang
NK078(tshu)001:341: rdo rje zhes ni bya ba las //
NK078(tshu)001:342: snying po'i rang bzhin de la ni //
NK078(tshu)001:343: skye 'jig med pa'i mtshan nyid de //
NK078(tshu)001:344: rdo rje zhes ni brjod pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:346: de yang rtogs bya mnyam pa'i dbyingsa de nyid dang rtogs byed rig pa'i ye shesa /
NK078(tshu)001:347: gnyis 'adu ba dang 'brala ba meda pa ni rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje ste /
NK078(tshu)001:349: chos rnams ma lus gnyis med pas //
NK078(tshu)001:350: rang rig byang chub sems nyid de //
NK078(tshu)001:351: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:352: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:354: de ltar rgyu mtshan lnga yis rdo rje grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:355: don de nyid snang stong gnyis su meda pa'i phyir sems zhes bya /
NK078(tshu)001:356: byed pa po med par ngang ngam shugs kyis rang gsal ba'i phyir sems /
NK078(tshu)001:357: yod med rtag chad la sogs gzhan du mi g.yo ba'i phyir na sems /
NK078(tshu)001:358: yul yul can du mi semsa pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:359: de dag mthar thug rgyal ba'i dgongs pa yin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:360: phyir lam ba dang theg 'og gi sems las khyad
NK078(tshu)001:361: par du gyur pas semsa chena po zhes bya ste
NK078(tshu)001:363: rang rig kun gsal bdag phyir rnam rtog bral //
NK078(tshu)001:365: rgyal ba rnams kyi sku gsungs thugs kyi mdzad pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:366: phrin las zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhis bdud bzhi bcom
NK078(tshu)001:367: pa ste / nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes lngar
NK078(tshu)001:368: gnas kyang de ngo bo ma shes pas nyon mongs
NK078(tshu)001:370: nyon mongs pa ye shes su gsal tsam na nyon
NK078(tshu)001:371: mongs pa'i bdud rang bzhin gyis bcom pa ni zhi
NK078(tshu)001:373: phung po lnga rigs lngar ngo ma shes pas phung po'i bdud byung la /
NK078(tshu)001:374: de nyid rigs lngar gsal bar rtogs pas phung po'i bdud bcom pa ni rgyas pa'i phrin las so //
NK078(tshu)001:375: sems nyid skye 'chi gnyis med las gnyis su bzung bas 'chi bdag gi bdud byung la /
NK078(tshu)001:376: skye shi gnyis med du mngon du byas tsam na
NK078(tshu)001:377: 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom pa ni dbang gi phrin
NK078(tshu)001:378: las so // don lha rtogs gnyis med las gnyis su bzung bas lha'i bu'i bdud byung la /
NK078(tshu)001:379: lha rtogs gnyis med mngon du byas tsam na lha'i
NK078(tshu)001:380: bu'i bdud bcom pa ni drag po'i 'phrin las yin
NK078(tshu)001:382: bdud sde tshar gcod ces bya'i dam tshig ni /
NK078(tshu)001:383: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:384: skye 'chi med pa'i g.yung drung gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:385: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor ste //
NK078(tshu)001:387: de ltar bdud bzhi bcom zhing tshur la gnod pas mi tshugs pas dapa'a bo zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:388: lha'i lha zhes pa yul lha la sogs pa phan gnod byed pa'i lha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:389: lha mgon la sogs pa btags pa ming gi lha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:390: khams gsum gyi lha nyer bdun la sogs pa skye bas thob pa'i lha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:391: theg pa 'og ma'i sa lam sbyong ba mthar phyin
NK078(tshu)001:392: nas rang sa'i 'bras bu thob pa ni rnam par
NK078(tshu)001:394: de rnams las khyad par du gyur pa'i lha ni
NK078(tshu)001:395: rdo rje sems dpa' ste de la phyag 'tshal ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:396: // gnyis pa gang gis mos na /
NK078(tshu)001:397: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba rang nyid kyis 'tshal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:398: gsum pa tshul ji ltar mos na /
NK078(tshu)001:399: phyag 'tshal byed kyi mkhan po sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dgongs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:400: 'tshal bya'i yul rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs gnyis su med par mjal ba ni mos pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:402: ji ltar chu la chu blugs sam //
NK078(tshu)001:403: ji ltar mar la mar bzhag bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:404: rang gis ngang gi ye shes gang //
NK078(tshu)001:407: ni lta ba rtogs pa'i phyag go //
NK078(tshu)001:408: sgom pa goms pa'i phyag ni /
NK078(tshu)001:410: gang zhig rtog nas 'jug pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:413: spyod pa ya rab kyi phyag ni /
NK078(tshu)001:415: lus kyi phyag 'tshal yan lag sa la gtug /ngag gi phyag 'tshal bstod de ngag sang sang //
NK078(tshu)001:416: yid kyi phyag 'tshal dga' dang yid bring bring //
NK078(tshu)001:417: sgo gsum dang ba'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:419: bzhi pa dgos ched ci'i phyir mos na gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:421: rjes 'jug gis yi ge ris su bkod pa'i dgos ched do //
NK078(tshu)001:423: ston pa la dbang mi za zhing rtogs nas brtsam du gnang ba'i brdar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:424: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la khung mi dbyung zhing chos kyi gru tshul mi nyams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:426: sgrib gnyis byang bas bar chad kyi rkyen gegs nye bar zhi ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:427: brtsam pa mthar byung ba'i dgos ched yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:429: bdag nyid ya rab tu shes pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK078(tshu)001:430: nyan bshad mthar phyin pa'i dgos ched yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:432: phyag 'tshal ba'i yul rgyal ba rigs lnga la khyad par yod dam med /
NK078(tshu)001:433: yod na sangs rgyas bzang ngan can du 'gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:434: med na rdo rje sems dpa' la sgos su phyag 'tshal ba 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:435: lan ni sangs rgyas rig lnga'i dgongs pa la mtho dman dang bzang ngan med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:436: gdul bya'i mos pa'i dbang gis 'dir thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skabs su 'chad pa'i skyes bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:437: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' yin pa'i phyir na phyag 'tshal ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:439: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:440: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK078(tshu)001:442: dkyil 'khor gtso bo skyes bu mchog /ces pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:443: rdo rje sems dpas bka' bshad pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:445: mi bskyod rgyal po mdun na gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:447: slob dpon nyid kyi thugs dam gyi gtso bo yin
NK078(tshu)001:448: pa'i phyir na rdo rje sems dpa' kho na la
NK078(tshu)001:451: dam pa'i lha phyir phyag 'tshal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:453: gnyis pa lo rgyus la brten te bshad par dam bca' ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:455: khung btsun zhing yid ches par bya ba'i phyir lo rgyus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:456: brtsam pa mi 'gyur bar bya ba'i phyin bshad par de bca' ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:459: spyir gsang bdag gis dam pa'i rigs can lnga la gsang sngags gsungs pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:461: chos rgyud dri ma med pa 'di dang po ji ltar byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:463: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag gsum //
NK078(tshu)001:464: dgongs rig rna bar brgyud pa ste //
NK078(tshu)001:465: gang la thug gi bar du'o //
NK078(tshu)001:466: zhes gsungs pas rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:467: rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos rgyal tshab rigs lnga la brgyud /
NK078(tshu)001:468: rigs lngas lhan cig pa'i 'khor rigs gsum mgon po la brgyud pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:469: rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:470: mi ma yin la brgyud pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:471: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la brgyud pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:472: dang po thub pa'i dbang po 'das nas lo nyi
NK078(tshu)001:473: shu rtsa brgyad kyi bar du 'jam dpal gzhon nu
NK078(tshu)001:474: mdzes pa'i sku dang ldan pa des lha rnams kyi
NK078(tshu)001:475: lus dang bsam pa dang mthun pa'i chos bstan te
NK078(tshu)001:476: / lha grags ldan phyogs skyong la bshad /
NK078(tshu)001:478: des skye dgu'i bdag po tshangs pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:479: des tshangs pa kun grol la /
NK078(tshu)001:480: des tshangs pa gtsug phud 'dzin la /
NK078(tshu)001:481: des dbang po brgya byin la /
NK078(tshu)001:482: des lha'i rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la /
NK078(tshu)001:483: de ltar gyur pa'i lha rnams kyang byang chub sems
NK078(tshu)001:484: dpa'i rig 'dzin cing rgyal ba rnams kyi gdung 'tshob
NK078(tshu)001:485: par gyur to // spyan ras gzigs bdud rtsi sman
NK078(tshu)001:486: gyi sku dang ldan pa des klu dug can rnams
NK078(tshu)001:487: kyi lus dang bsam pa mthun par /
NK078(tshu)001:488: klu rgyal g+h+rir+na nag po la bshad /
NK078(tshu)001:489: des klu mo kha 'dul ma la /
NK078(tshu)001:490: des klu yid 'ong dga' ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:492: des klu'i tshom bu 'bum sde la /
NK078(tshu)001:493: de ltar klu rnams gong bzhin gyur to //
NK078(tshu)001:494: phyag na rdo rje 'jigs tshul bsdigs pa'i sku dang ldan pa des /
NK078(tshu)001:495: gnod sbyin rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par /
NK078(tshu)001:496: gnod sbyin grags ldan mchog skyong la bshad /
NK078(tshu)001:497: des gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la /
NK078(tshu)001:498: des gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje la /
NK078(tshu)001:499: des gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong la /
NK078(tshu)001:500: des gnod sbyin tshom bu 'bum sde la /
NK078(tshu)001:501: de ltar gnod sbyin rnams kyang gong ltar gyur to /
NK078(tshu)001:502: 2 /mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la gsang ba'i bdag pos chos bshad tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:503: gshegs zhes pas gzhir byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:504: de'i khyad par la lnga las /
NK078(tshu)001:505: gang gshegs na ston pa gasnga ba'i badga po ste /
NK078(tshu)001:506: de yang gnod sbyin rnams gsang tshig dang bcas nas
NK078(tshu)001:507: skye shi de rnams 'dul ba'i ded dpon du gyur
NK078(tshu)001:508: pas gnod sbyin gsang ba'i bdag po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:509: dam pa'i mdzod gsum thob par dka' ba /
NK078(tshu)001:510: ma lus pa thob pas lam rgyud lnga 'phags par snang bas gsang ba'i bdag po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:511: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs thob par dka' ba /
NK078(tshu)001:512: ma lus pa thob pas thugs rgyud ye shes su snang bas gsang ba'i bdag po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:513: gsang sngags bstan brtag dka' ba rnams 'chad pa'i skyes bur dbang thob pas /
NK078(tshu)001:514: sdud pa po gsang ba'i bdag po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:515: de rnams don gyi ngo bo gcig kyang 'dir sdud pa po gsang ba'i bdag po ste /
NK078(tshu)001:517: 'khor gyi nang nas skal ldan mchog /
NK078(tshu)001:518: 'dul ba'i dus bab gsang ba'i bdag /phyag rgya rdo rjes bsdu ba mdzad //
NK078(tshu)001:521: dpag med rgyal bas dbang bskur bas //
NK078(tshu)001:522: gsang ba'i bdag po sngags kyi mdzod //
NK078(tshu)001:523: ces gsungs pas ston pa de mngona sum du gshegs so //
NK078(tshu)001:525: drag shul can ri bo chos 'dzin gyi sgrub gnas ma la ya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:527: mi yi gnas kyi 'jig rten khams /
NK078(tshu)001:528: gling bzhi pa las 'dzam gling gi /
NK078(tshu)001:529: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i ri /
NK078(tshu)001:530: gnod sbyin 'du ba'i sa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:531: chos 'dzin rigs kyi sgrub gnas su /
NK078(tshu)001:533: rgyud bde mchog rdo rje'i lcags 'grel las /
NK078(tshu)001:534: za hor yul gyi nye 'khor na //
NK078(tshu)001:535: mthu stobs zhabs bcag ma la ya //
NK078(tshu)001:536: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i rtse dag la //
NK078(tshu)001:538: yang de nyid kyi le'u lnga pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:539: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK078(tshu)001:540: dgon pa chen po'i gnas 'di ni //
NK078(tshu)001:541: ye shes snying po can rnams kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:542: theg chen gsang sngags 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:543: thog ma tha ma'i dus med par //
NK078(tshu)001:544: dam pa rnams kyis basngagasa pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:546: gshegsa nas bstan pa ci gsungs na /
NK078(tshu)001:547: lung dang rgyud kyi chos rnams so //
NK078(tshu)001:548: 'khor gang gi don du gshegs na /
NK078(tshu)001:549: lha brgya byin te blo gros mtha' yas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:552: gnoda sbyin skar mda' gdong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:554: srina po lang ka mgrin bcu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:556: mi lasa li tsa byi dri ma med par grags pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:558: de ltar dam pa'i rigs can lnga ni /
NK078(tshu)001:559: gang zag zag med kyi bden pa rtogs dam chos
NK078(tshu)001:560: kyi skal ba dang ldan pa'i rig pa 'dzin pa
NK078(tshu)001:561: 'dus pa rnams kyi don la gshegs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:563: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dabnga pa mya ngan las 'das
NK078(tshu)001:564: khar gsang sngags ji ltar 'byung ba'i lung bstan pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:565: dus te / mdo'i zhe gsum pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:566: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK078(tshu)001:567: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK078(tshu)001:568: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:569: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK078(tshu)001:570: 'jam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams su //
NK078(tshu)001:571: mi las skal ldan rigs can de //
NK078(tshu)001:572: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK078(tshu)001:573: sngon gyi ltas rnams snang bar 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:574: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rtser //
NK078(tshu)001:575: grogs kyi sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK078(tshu)001:576: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs la //
NK078(tshu)001:577: lag na rdo rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:579: sangs rgyas 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dus su /
NK078(tshu)001:580: dam pa'i rigs can lnga ma la ya'i rtser lhags nas /
NK078(tshu)001:581: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la gdung tshig nyi shu rtsa gsum gyis gsol ba btab pas /
NK078(tshu)001:582: sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsan nas thams cad lcang lo
NK078(tshu)001:583: can du 'dus te gsang bdag la bka' bsgo ba
NK078(tshu)001:584: mdzad de / kye gsang ba'i bdag po lags /
NK078(tshu)001:585: sngon gyi go cha yal lam ci //
NK078(tshu)001:586: 'jig rten sdug bsngal mi shes sam //
NK078(tshu)001:587: snying rjes sa las langs nas ni //
NK078(tshu)001:588: 'jig rten gdung ba bsal bar rigs //
NK078(tshu)001:590: thog ma tha ma med pa nas //
NK078(tshu)001:591: bskul ba'i dus ni nam byung bar //
NK078(tshu)001:592: bdag kyang de bzhin cho 'phrul snang //
NK078(tshu)001:593: zhes zhal gyi bzhes nas dam pa'i rigs can lnga la rgyud dang lung gi chos rnams gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:594: khyad par rgyal po dzahl gsang sngags babs shing grub pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:597: za hor gyi yul a parta murta'i rgyal po u
NK078(tshu)001:598: ta dz+ny+aa na zhes bya ba'i rgyal bu dzahzhesa bya
NK078(tshu)001:599: ba gsang sngags kyi rigsa can de la /
NK078(tshu)001:600: ma la yar gsang bdag gis dam pa'i rigs can
NK078(tshu)001:601: lnga la gsang sngags gsungs pa'i byin rlabs rgyal bu
NK078(tshu)001:602: dzahl rmi ltas su shara ba ni 'di lta ste
NK078(tshu)001:603: / ri de'i shar lhor ngos kyi log la kri
NK078(tshu)001:604: yam a su ra ta zhes bya ba'i brag phug
NK078(tshu)001:605: thog so rim gsum dang ldan pa la sogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:606: yon tan du ma dang ldan pa'i gnas su rgyal
NK078(tshu)001:607: bu dzas gsang sngags phyi rgyud la /
NK078(tshu)001:608: bsgrub pa mdzad cing bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK078(tshu)001:609: rmi ltas bdun las dang po ni /
NK078(tshu)001:610: phyag na rdo rje mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon te /
NK078(tshu)001:611: sku'i gnas nas 'od zer spros pas /
NK078(tshu)001:612: gdul bya rnams kyi rtog sgrib sbyangs /
NK078(tshu)001:613: gsung gi gnas nas bstan pa dang theg pa'i sgra bsgrags pas /
NK078(tshu)001:614: gdul bya rnams kyis go bar gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:615: thugs kyi gnas nas rdo rje 'od 'bar ba byung nas rgyal po'i thugs kar thim /
NK078(tshu)001:616: spyi bo'i gtsug nas nyi ma byung bas rgyal po'i spyi gtsug tu thim pa rmi ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:618: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:620: rmi ltas de ni bag chags sgrib pa thams cad byang ba'i ltas so //
NK078(tshu)001:622: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad nyi
NK078(tshu)001:623: ma dang zla ba la bcibs nas phyag na gser
NK078(tshu)001:624: gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa bsnams nas
NK078(tshu)001:625: sems can thams cad la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK078(tshu)001:626: ba rmis te / de nyid las /
NK078(tshu)001:627: chos kyi bsgro ba mdzad pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:629: de ni chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas so //
NK078(tshu)001:631: nam mkha' la sprin gser gyi mdog can chags /
NK078(tshu)001:633: cho 'phrul gyi 'brug sgra dam pa chos kyi sgra 'ur tir tir sgrog pa rmis te /
NK078(tshu)001:635: chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:637: de ni thugs rjes 'gro ba la chos kyi char chen po 'beb pa'i ltas so //
NK078(tshu)001:639: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun bab ste sa phyogs thams cad chag chag gdab /
NK078(tshu)001:640: gdul bya thams cad kyi rtog sgrib sbyangs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:641: kun kyang rdo rje rnal 'byor zhes gsang sngags kyi sgra di ri ri grags pa rmis te /
NK078(tshu)001:643: bdud rtsi'i char du bab pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:645: de ni 'gro ba kun gyis gsang sngags kyi don rtogs pa'i ltas so //
NK078(tshu)001:647: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas rin po che'i sgrom gyi
NK078(tshu)001:648: nang nas rin po che mthing gi shog bu la
NK078(tshu)001:649: gser gyis rgya rang mnan du bris pa'i po ti
NK078(tshu)001:650: dang glegs bam skar mda' sa la babs pa tsam
NK078(tshu)001:653: rin chen char du babs pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:655: de ni glegs bam babs pa'am chos kyi rgyal por dbang skur pa'i ltas so //
NK078(tshu)001:657: po ti glegs bam de rnams la /
NK078(tshu)001:658: rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis la las ni mchod pa 'bul /
NK078(tshu)001:659: la las ni bskor ba byed /
NK078(tshu)001:660: la las ni bstod pa byed pa'i sgra sgrogs pa rmis te /
NK078(tshu)001:661: de yang p+au rtsa chen po byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:663: de ni gsang sngags kyi che ba bton pa'i ltas so //
NK078(tshu)001:665: nam mkha'i mthong nas gzugs su ma grub pa'i lung bstan pa'i sgra /
NK078(tshu)001:666: las dang skal bar rab ldan nas //
NK078(tshu)001:667: bsod nams chen po'i dra ma khyod //
NK078(tshu)001:668: sprul pas ji ltar lung bstan zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:669: rgyal ba 'byung bar lung bstan pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:670: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /skal ldan khyod la sgrogs par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:672: de yang sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:674: ltas de ni gsang ba dam pa rgya cher sgrog pa'i ltas pa'i ltas so //
NK078(tshu)001:675: der rgyal po mnal sad de mkhar gyi yang thogs su sku 'chags su byon pas /
NK078(tshu)001:676: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje'i sku rin po che
NK078(tshu)001:677: smug po las grub pa gru gang ba gcig bzhugs
NK078(tshu)001:678: kyin gda' / de la phyag gsum 'tshal /
NK078(tshu)001:680: zhabs spyi bo'i gtsug tu blangs te /
NK078(tshu)001:681: e ma ngo mtshar mchog gi sku //
NK078(tshu)001:682: 'dren pa mchog gi dpal lags gang //
NK078(tshu)001:683: mos pa'i yid kyi lha mchog khyod //
NK078(tshu)001:684: sngon tshe gong nas bsgrubs pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:685: las kyi 'brel ba'i lha mchog khyod //
NK078(tshu)001:686: bskal pa brgyar yang mi gtong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:687: gsungs te yid dam gyi lhar bzung nas zla ba bdun du bsgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK078(tshu)001:689: rnams mngon sum du bab cing /
NK078(tshu)001:690: de yang gsung gi byin rlabs dpe char snang ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:692: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i phrin las gnyis 'brela ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:693: stobsa kyis snang ba'i glegs bam rnams la mangna sum
NK078(tshu)001:694: du shes rab kyis brtag pasa /
NK078(tshu)001:695: de'i nang nas rdo rje sems dpa' thugsa kyi bsgrub pa'i le'u mdun du mngona sum du rtogsa te /
NK078(tshu)001:696: thugs kyi sgrub pa de nyid kyi sgo nas zla
NK078(tshu)001:697: ba bdun du bsgrub pas rdo rje sems dpa' de
NK078(tshu)001:699: mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon te /
NK078(tshu)001:700: zhal bstan nas rigs kyi bu dngos grub ci 'dod gsungs pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:701: glegs bam 'di dag rtogs par 'tshal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:703: rigs kyi bu rang gi phung po sbyongs shig ma
NK078(tshu)001:704: 'ongs pa'i dus na gsang ba'i bdag pos lung bstan
NK078(tshu)001:705: par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs nas mi snang bar gshegs
NK078(tshu)001:706: so // yang zla ba bdun du gsang bdag bsgrub pas 'grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:707: gsang bdag dngos su byon te rdo rje lan gsum bsor nas /
NK078(tshu)001:709: spong len brtul zhugs spyod pa'i dbang //
NK078(tshu)001:710: dge bas bskur na sdig pa med ces gsungs pas
NK078(tshu)001:711: don gyi dbang thob nas zag med kyi rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:712: grub bo // tshig gi bstan pa li tsa byi la zhus shig par lung bstan to //
NK078(tshu)001:713: sngar lung bstan te smona pa'i lha phyag na rdo
NK078(tshu)001:714: rje yanga zla ba bdun gyi rjes de ru zhal
NK078(tshu)001:716: sngar rgyal bas lung bstan pa'i dngos grub dam pa dus /
NK078(tshu)001:718: de ltar dona dama rtogs pa'i bcud kyi dam pa de nas rig pa'i ye shes nyid rgyas te /
NK078(tshu)001:719: glegs bam thams cad shes par 'dod pa'i bsam pa'ang dus de ru 'grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:720: bstan pa tha dag gi don ji bzhin khong du chud par gyur to //
NK078(tshu)001:721: gsum pa rim par tshogs bsgrub cing /
NK078(tshu)001:724: rgyal po glegs bam kyi don rtogs shing grub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:725: rjes thog de nas 'dzam bu'i gling ni gang la
NK078(tshu)001:726: 'bras bu mngar po dag yod pa'i shing 'dzam bu
NK078(tshu)001:728: de'i phyir 'dzam bu'i gling zhes bya bar grags so //
NK078(tshu)001:729: yang dbyig gnyen gyi mdzod 'grel las /
NK078(tshu)001:730: de'i 'bras bu'i dbang gis 'dzam gling zhes bya ba grags so //
NK078(tshu)001:731: rgya gar gyi yul dbus su byang chub sems dpa'
NK078(tshu)001:732: srid pa tha ma pas rdo rje lta bus ting
NK078(tshu)001:733: nge 'dzin bsgoms pa'i gadna steng zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:735: de'i dbus su gser gyi sa gzhi la //
NK078(tshu)001:736: gang du byang chub sems dpa' bzhugs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:737: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin bskyed par mdzad pas rdo rje'i gdan mngon par grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:738: de'i lus sems sa phyogs gzhan gyis bzod par mi nus so //
NK078(tshu)001:740: de ltar rdo rje gdan steng gi shara gyi phyogas su za hor gyi yul yod la /
NK078(tshu)001:741: de'i byang shar na ma la ya yod la /
NK078(tshu)001:742: de'i shar lho mtshamsa kyi ngos la a su ra'i brag phug yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:743: gnas de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi zhabs kyis bcags
NK078(tshu)001:744: shing rig 'dzin rnams kyis grub pa'i pho branga gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:745: las khyad par du gyur pas dam pa de'i sgo
NK078(tshu)001:746: zla gam la ngo mtshar gyi ri mo rang byung
NK078(tshu)001:747: ba phug rin chen zur brgyad dam /
NK078(tshu)001:748: sna bdun la nyi zla'i ri mo rang byung ba
NK078(tshu)001:749: nang du bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:750: ngo mtshar can mang po rang byung ba /
NK078(tshu)001:751: sngar grub pa thob pa'i gnas mchog dam pa gsang sngags bsgrub pa'i khang bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:753: rtse na rtsal gyi rgyal po gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:754: ngos na brag dkar khyi'u tshugs pa //
NK078(tshu)001:755: seng ge gnam du mchong 'dras brgyan //
NK078(tshu)001:756: rtsi sman tsa ra tshang bar 'khrungs //
NK078(tshu)001:757: 'du ba'i nad kyis yang mi tshug /spyi bor ka lan ta ka yi //
NK078(tshu)001:758: mi gnyis gcig pur gnas pa'i sgra //
NK078(tshu)001:759: mdzod ldan de yis tshangs bcas shing //
NK078(tshu)001:760: skal ldan rnams kyi bgrod par sla //
NK078(tshu)001:761: skal med rnams kyis yang mi thar //
NK078(tshu)001:763: gnas de ru sgrub pa po ni /
NK078(tshu)001:764: dge slong ku ku ra tsa sa sgrub dpon byas pas 'khor tshom bu 'bum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:765: rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu tis tshom bu khri dang /
NK078(tshu)001:766: sing ha ra tsas tshom bu stong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:767: u pa ra dzasa tshom bu brgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:768: sras mo go mas tshom bu lnga bcu dang bcas
NK078(tshu)001:769: pa la sogsa pa'i khong ro lang bde ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:770: / h'u ka ra la sogs sdud do //
NK078(tshu)001:771: 'o na zhi khro'i tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:772: lha grangs dang mi grangs sprad nas bsgrub pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:773: 'gal zhe na / dang por rang don du zhi
NK078(tshu)001:774: khro'i tshom bu gang yin gyi lha grangs mi grangs
NK078(tshu)001:775: sprad nas bsgrub pas zag med rig 'dzin gyi sar
NK078(tshu)001:777: phyis gzhan gyi don du sgrub dpon yang yang byas
NK078(tshu)001:778: pa'i byin rlabs des 'khor tshom bu 'bum dang khri
NK078(tshu)001:779: la sogs pa rnams kyang tshe gcig la sangs rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:782: tshul ji ltar du bsgrub na /
NK078(tshu)001:783: sgyur 'phrul dra ba ste lha yab yum zung du
NK078(tshu)001:784: 'brel ba'i zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor du dbang mchog bco
NK078(tshu)001:785: brgyad la sogs pa rnams rdzogs par thob nas /
NK078(tshu)001:786: thos bsam gyis zag bcas kyi lta sgom mthar phyin
NK078(tshu)001:787: nas sbyor lam du zhi khro'i tshom bu tshogs dkyil
NK078(tshu)001:788: 'khor gcig gsum lnga pa gang rung mngon sum du
NK078(tshu)001:789: basgrubs te / de ltar bsgrubs pas gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu zag med kyi rig 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:790: mthar thug gi 'bras bu drug pa rdo rje 'chang
NK078(tshu)001:791: chen po sangs rgyas kyi sar mngon sum du tshe
NK078(tshu)001:792: gcig lus gcig la gshegsa nas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:793: gnyis pa brtsam pa mi 'gyur bar bya ba'i phyir bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:795: 'di la yang dgos pa'i don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:797: tshig gi don dang gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:799: dam bca' nyams na skyes bu dam par mi 'gyur ba /
NK078(tshu)001:800: des na brtsams pa myur du rdzogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:801: mgo 'og tu lus tshud pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:805: gzhan don brtsam pa can rnams srog phyir yang //
NK078(tshu)001:806: rang gi nus pa lhod par mi bya ste //
NK078(tshu)001:807: skyes bu dam pas khur lci khur ba dag /nyams nga'i lam du nam yang 'dor mi bya //
NK078(tshu)001:809: gnyis pa bsdus pa'i don la bdun te /
NK078(tshu)001:816: dgos ched ci'i phyir bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:817: gsum pa tshig gi don ni /
NK078(tshu)001:819: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang po 'das nas gsang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:820: bdag pos dam pa'i rigs can lnga la bshad pas
NK078(tshu)001:822: de nas ku ku ra tsa la sogs pas tshom
NK078(tshu)001:823: bu tshogs bsgrub ste rig 'dzin thob pas bar du
NK078(tshu)001:824: grogs bzang de'i don nyams su blangs nas 'khor ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:825: sdug bsngal / dgrol bas tha mar skyabs che la sogs pa'i rgyu mtshan gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:826: yon tan mtha' yas 'dug pa de lta bu'i phyir bdag lta bu la /
NK078(tshu)001:827: spang rtogs kyi yon tan mthar phyin pa med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:828: sangsa rgyas gsang ba'i matshana thob pa ngas bstan par bya'o zhes khengs bskyung ba'i tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:829: gang gis don du bstan na /
NK078(tshu)001:831: shes bya dam pa dngos po'i gnas lugs gnyis med spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:833: de'i don phyin ci ma log par go rtogs nus pa'i shes rab ste gdul bya'i snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:835: ci lta ba bzhin nar son pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:836: de rjogs pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK078(tshu)001:840: dam pa gsang sngags kyi rigsa can te /
NK078(tshu)001:841: de'i nang nas dra ma ni rnal 'byor chen po nyid kyi rigs can te /
NK078(tshu)001:842: slob dpon nyid kyis dngos 'khor rgya gar na sgeg pa'i rdo rje la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:843: bod la bran ka mu ti dang /
NK078(tshu)001:844: sbas many+dzu sh+ri la sogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:845: dngos 'khor de dag gi rjesa su 'jug pa'i ma
NK078(tshu)001:846: 'ongsa pa'i gang zag gsang sngags kyi las 'phro skal
NK078(tshu)001:847: ba dang ldan pa gsang ba sgyu 'phrul la mos
NK078(tshu)001:848: pa rnams kyi don gyi phyir bstan par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:849: gang nas btus te bstan na /
NK078(tshu)001:850: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud chen po dag lasa btus de bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:854: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK078(tshu)001:855: bsnyen nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:857: sngar 'das pa'i rgyal ba dang da ltar gyi sangs
NK078(tshu)001:858: rgyas rnams kyis gshegsa shul du gyur cing 'byung dang
NK078(tshu)001:859: ma 'ongs thams cad kun 'di yis lhun gyis grub
NK078(tshu)001:861: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor kun gyi lam du gyur pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:862: lam de yang theg pa 'og ma'i lam las khyad par gsum gyis 'phags pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:865: bskal pa grangs med gsum du bsgrub mi dgos te /
NK078(tshu)001:866: tshe gcig gis 'bras bu thob pa'i nye ba'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:867: spyod pa'i sgo yangs shing ngang gis rtsol ba dang bral bas bde ba'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:868: 'og ma'i lam 'di'i sngon du song bas rdzogs pa'i phyir mchog ces bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:870: lam gyi nang nas nye lam bde rdzogs pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:871: thabs kyi nang nas ma nor dam pa ni //
NK078(tshu)001:873: 'di zhes pa nye bar mngon sum du mtshon pa'i tshig ste /
NK078(tshu)001:874: gsang sngags kyi snying po gzhi lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa'i chos 'dir bstan par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:875: tshul ji ltar du bstan na /
NK078(tshu)001:876: 'dir nyams su len bde bar bya ba'i don du /
NK078(tshu)001:877: rgyud sde dag nas 'thor ba phyogs gcig tu bsdus
NK078(tshu)001:878: la 'khrugs pa go rim du bsdeb cing mang ba
NK078(tshu)001:879: nyung ngur bsdus nas zab pa'i don rgyas par bkrol
NK078(tshu)001:880: te bstan pa'o // dus gang gi tshe bstan na /
NK078(tshu)001:887: nyon mongs pa rnams tha ma'i phyir snyigs ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:889: de'i tshe nyon mongs pa rgyud drag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:890: gnyen pos spang spyod la sogs dus kyis mi thul
NK078(tshu)001:891: ba'i tshe gsang sngags kyi lam gyi khyad par can
NK078(tshu)001:894: dgos ched ci'i phyir bstan na /
NK078(tshu)001:895: snyigs ma lnga yi dus der gsang sngags kyi nye
NK078(tshu)001:896: lam nyon mongs pa dbang du byed pa'i thabs kyisa
NK078(tshu)001:897: gdul bya 'dul ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir bstan
NK078(tshu)001:898: par bya'o / 7 /gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:899: brgyud pa'i man ngag med na rang nyams kyis mi
NK078(tshu)001:900: rtogs pas rgyud pa'i man ngag dang ldan pa'i bla
NK078(tshu)001:901: ma bsten dgos par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:902: man ngag mi nyams par bya ba'i phyir snod brtag cing sbyin mi sbyin gyi dmigs bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:903: snod ldan la sbyin pa'i man ngag rang gi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:906: des na rang nyams kyis ming rtogs pas gzhan sel gyi dpe don bstan pa dang drang /
NK078(tshu)001:907: spyan bazanga zhes pa long ba la bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:909: u lu tri sha ka /bod skad du /
NK078(tshu)001:911: rkang pa zha ba 'du shes chung ba gsum gyi sgra 'jug go //
NK078(tshu)001:912: de gar yang 'gro ba'i nus mthu med pa'a miga bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:913: lam mkhan long khrid dang bral ba'i dbang gis 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:914: nyamsa med de lam stor bas goms pas bgroda cing
NK078(tshu)001:915: rang gi 'dod pa'i gnas su phyin par mi nus
NK078(tshu)001:916: pa bzhina du / don rag chod tsam gyis blo
NK078(tshu)001:917: tsing po shes rab gsum gyis rgyud ma sbyangs shing
NK078(tshu)001:919: bla ma'i man ngag la ma brten par rang bzo'i
NK078(tshu)001:920: nyams kyisa rang bzhin gasnga ba'i snying po'i don rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:921: shing 'bras bu mthar phyin par mi 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:922: dper na bul shanga ste thang shing smug po la
NK078(tshu)001:923: gnas skabs kyi me tog dang mthar thug gi 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:924: bu shing thog gnyis ka mi 'byung ba bzhin du
NK078(tshu)001:925: / rang nyams kyis bsgrod pas gnas skabs kyi 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:926: bu dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu gnyis ka 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:928: gnyis pa brgyud pa'i man ngag dang ldan pa'i bla
NK078(tshu)001:929: ma bsten dgos pa'i don gnyer de la gnyis te
NK078(tshu)001:931: dang po bla ma bkur ba'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:933: rang nyams kyis mi rtogs pa'i skyon 'dug pa de
NK078(tshu)001:934: bas na bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la bsnyen
NK078(tshu)001:935: bkur dam pa la lung rnams nas byung ba bzhina
NK078(tshu)001:937: de la bskur tshul lung la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:939: bla ma sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK078(tshu)001:940: zhes bla ma sangs rgyas dang mnyam par bltas te bkur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:941: bla ma lnga bcu pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:942: bla ma dang ni rdo rje 'dzin //
NK078(tshu)001:943: tha dad par ni mi blta'o //
NK078(tshu)001:944: zhes bla ma dang sangs rgyas tha dad med par blta ste bkur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:946: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas bas //
NK078(tshu)001:947: bla ma gnyan par shes par bya //
NK078(tshu)001:949: sangs rgyas bas bla ma gnyan pa ste lhag par bltas te bskur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:950: slob dpon gyis slob bu'i snod brtag par bya ba'i phyir du spyo ba byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:951: mtshang 'bru ba dang zhe gcod pa'i tshig rtsub ci
NK078(tshu)001:952: byung yang bzod par byas te ci'i phyir bzod zhe
NK078(tshu)001:953: na / chos kyi phyir 'jig rten mthong ba'i tshe
NK078(tshu)001:954: 'di'i sdug bsngal gyis lus sems la gdung ba ci
NK078(tshu)001:955: byung yang khur du mi blta ste bla mas man
NK078(tshu)001:956: ngag nang nas sdug bsngal de kun yul gyi don
NK078(tshu)001:957: srid du bde ba 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:958: na / bzod par bya'o // gnyis pa bkur ba'i yon tan la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:960: dang po bla ma bkur ba'i yon tan gyis gdams ngag gnang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:963: bla ma bsten cing khur na /
NK078(tshu)001:964: bla ma rdo rje rgyal po des /
NK078(tshu)001:965: nga la chos zab mo 'di lta bu yod do zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:966: bla ma'i dgongs nyamsa kyi man ngag sbyin pa'i bka'i gannga ba thob par 'gyur ta /
NK078(tshu)001:967: gnang ba thob pa de'i tshe rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK078(tshu)001:968: chen po gsang ba snying po'i le'u dgu pa'i gzhung
NK078(tshu)001:969: gi nang nas ji bzhin bshad pa'i yon 'bul te
NK078(tshu)001:971: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK078(tshu)001:972: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK078(tshu)001:973: zhes gsungs pa bzhin phul nas zhus na /
NK078(tshu)001:974: bla ma de'i thugsa kyi man ngag nyid khu zab
NK078(tshu)001:975: mo rnams slob bu de la mnyes bzhin du ster
NK078(tshu)001:976: bar 'gyur ro // gnyis pa gdams ngag /gnang ba'i yon tan gyis sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:978: man ngag thob pa'i gang zag de yis dper na bzhona pa bazanga po /
NK078(tshu)001:979: rta dang glang po che ste chos gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:982: brtan pa'i yon tan can gnyis zhon nas 'gro ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:983: mi de rang gar 'dod pa'i gnas su myur du
NK078(tshu)001:984: phyin par byed pa bzhina du /
NK078(tshu)001:985: don gasnga ba' man ngag rdzu 'phrul rta dang 'dra
NK078(tshu)001:986: ba stobsa glang po che dang 'dra ba'i chos gsum
NK078(tshu)001:987: dang ldan te / gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:988: tshe gcig gis 'bras bu thob pas 'gyogs cing myur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:989: nyon mongs pa lam du byed pas bde ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:990: gol sa'i dbang du mi 'gyur bas brtan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:991: de lta bu'i man ngag la brten nas bzhon pa
NK078(tshu)001:992: bzang po zhon nas 'gro ba'i gang zag 'bras bu'i
NK078(tshu)001:993: sar phyin par byed pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:994: de yang lam bgrod nas 'bras bu thob tshul la
NK078(tshu)001:995: mtshan nyid gsum ste 'di nyid kyi le'u gnyis pa
NK078(tshu)001:996: ltar / rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba mthong ba /
NK078(tshu)001:997: gsum pa nas bdun pa'i bar ltar rkyen 'juga pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:998: mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis tshogs lam dang sbyor
NK078(tshu)001:999: lam bgrod nas / le'u brgyad pa ltar 'bras bu mathara phyina pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1000: gang zag tha dad kyi dbang gis rig 'dzin bzhi bgroda nas /
NK078(tshu)001:1001: le'u dgu pa ltar mthar thug gi 'bras bu thams
NK078(tshu)001:1002: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes snying po'i gansa su phyin
NK078(tshu)001:1003: par byed pa'o // gnyis pa snod brtag pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1005: dang po snod brtag pa dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1007: gong ltar 'bras bu thob pa'i yon tan yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:1008: de bas na rdo rje slob dpon gyis gzhan slob
NK078(tshu)001:1009: ma 'dzin pa'i grangs gnyer gcig gam bzhi dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:1010: pa ste / gcig ni slob bu mi chos kyi
NK078(tshu)001:1011: bya ba spang du bcug nas lha chos kyi lam
NK078(tshu)001:1012: pa ste / la 'dzud pa'o // bzhi ni phyi'i bar chad phyir bzlog pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1013: nang gi nyon mongs lam du bslangs ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1014: bde ba dang sdug bsngal ro snyom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1015: shes rab dang phan sems kyis slob bu rjes su 'dzin pa'i sgo nas snod brtag pa dgos te /
NK078(tshu)001:1016: slob bu snod dang ldan mi ldan rgyang nas brtag pa ni rigs bzang ngan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1017: shes rab che chung dang dad pa che chung gi
NK078(tshu)001:1018: lo rgyus rnams zhib par dris te brtag par bya
NK078(tshu)001:1019: ba dang / drung du brtag pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1022: dam pa'i chos kyi snod du rung ngam mi rung zhib par brtags par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1024: rngam glog ltar byis pa gtsang ma'i semsa la pra phab nas brtag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1025: mkha'a 'gro ma la gtor ma byin pas de yis
NK078(tshu)001:1026: gasnga sngagas ston rung mi rung gi ltas rmi lam
NK078(tshu)001:1027: du ston cig ces brtag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1028: sngar bzhin spyo ba sna tshogs byas pa'i sgo nas brtag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1029: de ltar brtag thabs lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1030: gzhan yang thabs sna tshogs kyi sgo nas slob bu
NK078(tshu)001:1031: de snod du rung mi rung ca nasa kyang brtagsa
NK078(tshu)001:1033: gnyis pa snod ldan la man ngag sbyin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1035: de ltar slob bu'i snod brtags pas bzang ba'i mtshan nyid dang ldan na /
NK078(tshu)001:1036: phyir mi ldog pa'i rigs nges pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1038: dang po gsang sngags kyi don la mi skrag pa ni rang bzhin gyi rigs nges pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1039: dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas dbang zhu zhing dam tshig
NK078(tshu)001:1040: bslab bya la nan tan du byed pa ni bslab
NK078(tshu)001:1042: lta ba rtogs pa ni don mthong ba'i rigs nges pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1043: de ltar gsang sngags kyi theg pa 'di las gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:1044: du blo mi ldog cing brtan par bya ba'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:1045: dbang skur de dam 'bog par byas nas snod /
NK078(tshu)001:1046: brtas shing rgyud smin pa yis /
NK078(tshu)001:1047: sang kri ta'i skad du shi sha /bod skad du slob bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1048: snod dang ldan pa gang yin pa de'i lag tu man ngag zab mo rnams gtad par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1049: gsum pa snod ngan la mi sbyin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1052: dang po snod ngan la man ngag mi sbyin cing 'tshams par don bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1054: de ltar snod brtags pas ngan pa'i skyon gyis mtshan ltas mthong ba'am mngona sum du shes par /
NK078(tshu)001:1055: snod ngan de'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1056: tshe 'di'i 'doda pa phra mo bsgrub pa'i rgyur chos byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1057: zas nor rnyed pa'i kheng dang 'jig rten gyi snyan
NK078(tshu)001:1058: gragsa la sogs pa che ba thob pa'i rgyu ru
NK078(tshu)001:1059: chos byed cing rang 'dod che ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1060: gzhan yang snod ngan pa'i skyon bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1061: man ngag gi bcud chen po brjed nas mi thub
NK078(tshu)001:1062: par 'adzaga pa ni snod zhabs rdol lta bu'i skyon
NK078(tshu)001:1063: dang / rang gi shes long med par gzhan la
NK078(tshu)001:1064: ston pas gsang mi thub pa ni 'bo ba ste
NK078(tshu)001:1066: gsang sngags zab mo bstan kyang mi go ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1067: mi chagsa pa ste kha sbub kyi skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1068: grub mtha' mi gcig pa'i gzhung gzhan dang 'dres pa ni ma rung bar byed pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1069: dug can lta bu'i skyon dang bzhi'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1070: yang gzhi dad pa med pa kha sbub /
NK078(tshu)001:1071: grogs brtson 'grus med pa zhabs rdol /
NK078(tshu)001:1072: brtse gdung gi dam tshig med pa gzhog ral /
NK078(tshu)001:1073: don dpyod byed kyi shes rab med pa dug can gyi skyon dang bzhi'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1074: yang bde gshegs rngod phu ba'i zhal nas /
NK078(tshu)001:1075: snod kha sbub ni brag phug kha byang bltas su nyi ma mi 'char ba lta bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1076: 'ga' zhig la chos bstan kyang mi go //
NK078(tshu)001:1079: chos la go ba bag tsam skyes kyang rang gis
NK078(tshu)001:1080: de la mchog tu bzung drag nas phyis skyed mi
NK078(tshu)001:1081: thon pa'o // zhabs rdol ni go ba'i man ngag snod min la ston cing gsang mi thub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1082: dug can ni nyon mongs pa shas che bas tshul
NK078(tshu)001:1083: 'chos dang chags sdang 'dres pa'am bye brag ma phyed
NK078(tshu)001:1084: par bsres ma rnams yin gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:1085: yang slob dpon sh+r+ai seng has /
NK078(tshu)001:1086: chu shing lta bu'i slob ma ni //
NK078(tshu)001:1087: gting nas dad 'dun mos bral bas //
NK078(tshu)001:1088: rkyen gyis dbang med 'jug tshul can //
NK078(tshu)001:1089: snying po med pa kha sbub yin //
NK078(tshu)001:1090: me tog dkar po lta bu ni //
NK078(tshu)001:1091: dad ldan nan tan rtsol bral bas //
NK078(tshu)001:1092: yal 'gyur rtsa ba rin chen rdol //
NK078(tshu)001:1093: tsan dan lta bu dad brtson can //
NK078(tshu)001:1094: brtse gdung bral ba gzhog ral yin //
NK078(tshu)001:1095: ga bur lta bur ma nges pas //
NK078(tshu)001:1097: bye brag ma byed dug can yin //
NK078(tshu)001:1099: zang zinga dngos po zas nor rnams kyi mtha' ngan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1100: rje sgro phug pa'i gsungs las /
NK078(tshu)001:1101: bya ba byas pa khrab hral /
NK078(tshu)001:1102: zag pa zad pa zangs rgog /khur bor ba rta
NK078(tshu)001:1103: rgan la sogs pa rnams bla ma dang dkon mchog
NK078(tshu)001:1105: dbus te gang gces pa rnams rang gis 'ching nas mi gtong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1106: gang zag sems kyi g.yo sgyu can ni dngos la ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:1107: dga' che la ltag pa sprad pa dang lkog tu bskur ba btab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1108: bla ma'i drung du tshul 'chos pa ltar byed cing
NK078(tshu)001:1109: lkog nas rang dga' ste chos min gyi spyod pa
NK078(tshu)001:1110: byed pa dang / kha snying so sor phye bas ngag la rigs nges te tshig bzang po brjod /
NK078(tshu)001:1111: bsam pa la mi nges te ngan pa bsam pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1112: bud med yin na sems 'dod chags kyi dbang du
NK078(tshu)001:1113: song ste 'dod pa la gnyen po dang ngo tsha
NK078(tshu)001:1114: med pas phyal ba pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1115: skyes pa dang mun pa'i khrod dang mi med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:1116: lkog tu gang 'phrad par 'doda chags spyod pa la
NK078(tshu)001:1117: snyegsa pa ste / skyon de ni skyes pa la yang yod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:1118: de lta bu'i gang zag pho mo gang yin kyang
NK078(tshu)001:1119: tan+t+ra ste rgyud sde rnams kyis snod ldan du ma
NK078(tshu)001:1120: basngagasa pa yin la de dag dang yun bskal par
NK078(tshu)001:1121: lus par grib ma bzhina du 'khor bar 'gyur yang
NK078(tshu)001:1122: thugsa kyi bde ba ste man ngag zab mo'i don
NK078(tshu)001:1123: ni de la spro bar mi bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1124: 'o na sems bskyed dang 'gal lam zhe na ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:1125: kho rang gi blo dang 'tshamsa par drang don du lha'i sku /
NK078(tshu)001:1126: bsgom thabs tsam bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1127: gcan 'phrang dang 'dra ba'i dge sdig gi skyon yon
NK078(tshu)001:1128: la sogs thun mong gi dam tshig bsrung thabs tsam
NK078(tshu)001:1129: sbyin no // gnyis pa byin pa'i nyes dmigs so //
NK078(tshu)001:1131: blo dang 'tshams par don byed pa de lta bu
NK078(tshu)001:1132: min par snod ngan de la zab mo'i chos bshad
NK078(tshu)001:1133: na dper na be'u gnyis ske sbrel nas ril btang
NK078(tshu)001:1134: na cig g.yang du lhung ba'i zhor la gcig de
NK078(tshu)001:1135: yang g.yang du lhung bar 'gyur ba bzhin du dpon
NK078(tshu)001:1136: slob gnyis ka ngan song du ltung bar 'gyur ro
NK078(tshu)001:1137: // de ltar ltung ba'i slob dpon ngan pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1138: zas nor la sogs pa 'doda pa che ba'i khe grags kyi sems kyis blo phrag dog ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1140: lha chos gtso bo mi byed par mi chos kyi
NK078(tshu)001:1141: gcam phyar che bar gyur pas snod kyi skyon ma
NK078(tshu)001:1142: brtagsa par snod ngan la man ngag zab mo'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:1144: rgya gar yul na bsil ba tshal gyi dur khrod dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1145: sing ga la'i yul na sku la rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1146: kha che'i yul na he chen bdal ba'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1147: ma la ya na gnas gsang chen rol pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1148: bal po'i yul na lhun grub brtsegs pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1149: u rgyan yul na pad+ma brtsegs pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1150: za hor yul na lang ka brtsegs pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1151: li yi yul na 'jig rten brtsegs pa'i dur khroda
NK078(tshu)001:1152: kyi gling brgyad kyi mkha' 'gro ma srin mo ging
NK078(tshu)001:1155: 'dzin byed ma dang be ta ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1159: bsnyo byed ma rnams dur khrod du 'du ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:1160: legs nyes kyi stongs 'dzin pa'i mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:1161: ngan pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi dpon slob gyi steng du 'dus par gyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:1162: de dag gis sha za ba dang khrag 'thung nas
NK078(tshu)001:1163: srog la bka' chad 'bebsa shinga tshe 'dir tshe thung
NK078(tshu)001:1164: bar byed la phyi ma ngan song du ltung bar
NK078(tshu)001:1165: 'gyur ba'i skyon chen po yod pa de'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:1166: snod kyi skyon yon brtags nas snod dang mi ldan
NK078(tshu)001:1167: pa la gdams ngag zab mo mi sbyin pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:1169: gsum pa snod ldan la sbyin pa'i man ngag rang gi ngo bo /
NK078(tshu)001:1172: dang po lus mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1174: gong du bstan pa de ltar snod kyi skyon yon brtag pas bzang po ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1175: gsang sngags kyi las 'phro skal ba dang ldan pa
NK078(tshu)001:1176: rnams la bstan pa'i phyir du lus rnam bzhag mdor
NK078(tshu)001:1178: brjod bya don gyi rnam grangs su phye na bcu gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:1179: rjod byed tshig gi gzhung rab byed le'u dgu /
NK078(tshu)001:1180: de dag bsdus na gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du ston par byed pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:1182: bden gsum dbyer med kyi rang bzhin bcos slad dang bral ba'i rang byung gi ye shes ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1183: lam dang 'bras bu thams cad kyi dngos gzhi ye nas rang la gnas pa ni gzhi'i don te /
NK078(tshu)001:1184: de ston par byed pa'i le'u dang po dang gnyis pa lam la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1185: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1186: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1187: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:1189: dngos gzhi'i don de ltar so sor rtogs pa'i shes
NK078(tshu)001:1190: rab kyis gtan la phab cing phyin ci ma log
NK078(tshu)001:1191: par mthong ba ni rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta
NK078(tshu)001:1192: ba ste le'u gnyis pas rgyas par ston to //
NK078(tshu)001:1194: sgom bya lta ba'i don de ltar bsgam byed kyi
NK078(tshu)001:1195: blo 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin la rim dang cig
NK078(tshu)001:1196: char gnyis las / dang po cig char ba ni
NK078(tshu)001:1197: le'u gsum pa'i stod kyis ston la gnyis pa rim
NK078(tshu)001:1198: gyis pa ni rnal 'byor bzhi zhes pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1199: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor ni le'u gsum pa'i smad kyis ston /
NK078(tshu)001:1200: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor ni le'u bzhi pas ston /
NK078(tshu)001:1201: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor ni le'u lnga pas ston /
NK078(tshu)001:1202: spros pa'i rnal 'byor ni drug pas ston /
NK078(tshu)001:1203: de bzhin ni tshogs lam mo //
NK078(tshu)001:1204: lam zag bcas med kyi bar gang gis chad pa med par tshom bu tshogs sgrub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1206: de ni le'u bdun pas ston /
NK078(tshu)001:1207: de lnga ni skyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:1208: gsum pa 'bras bu la mthong lam /
NK078(tshu)001:1209: bsgom lam mthar lam gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:1210: dang po la blo chung ba ni lus lha mi'i
NK078(tshu)001:1211: rnam pa la yid yi dam lha'i skur smin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:1212: rig 'dzin dang / blo che ba ni don lus
NK078(tshu)001:1213: snang sems gsum la rtag tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:1214: rig 'dzin dang / rig 'dzin no // gnyis pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1215: ye shes sgyur ma'i skur phyag rgya chen po longs sku'i cha byad can no //
NK078(tshu)001:1217: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i cha lugs can no //
NK078(tshu)001:1218: de gsum ni zag med kyi lam ste le'u brgyad pas ston te /
NK078(tshu)001:1219: gsum pa ni lam des gzhi don ci lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:1220: bzhin mngon du byas pa ni mthar thug gi 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:1221: bu ste le'u dgu pas ston to //
NK078(tshu)001:1222: de ltar rnam grangs bcu gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1223: dgu dang gsum po rnams kyis go rim rim pa ltar brjod par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1224: de ltar gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyi go don la /
NK078(tshu)001:1225: kun khyab lung 1rig 2pa man 3ngag gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:1228: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor las //
NK078(tshu)001:1229: thos bsam bsgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:1230: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK078(tshu)001:1233: gzhi dang lam dang ngo bo yi //
NK078(tshu)001:1234: nges pa rnam pa gsum du bzhag /ces gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:1237: gzhi nyid ngo bo'i gnas lugs dang //
NK078(tshu)001:1238: don du gnyer ba'i lam nyid dang //
NK078(tshu)001:1239: mngon gyur 'bras bu'i lus bzhag go //
NK078(tshu)001:1242: nye ston chos kyi seng ge na re /
NK078(tshu)001:1244: 'jug par byed pa lam smin pa mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1249: grub pa bgrod dang 'jug pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1256: ye nas gnas shing 'byung khung du gyur pas gzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1258: rang bzhin ye shes rang gnas dang //
NK078(tshu)001:1260: 'jug cing bgrod par byed pas lam ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1261: der mthong der 'jug nas lhun grub lam zhes pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1262: smon cing mthar phyin pas 'bras bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1264: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid bshad /
NK078(tshu)001:1267: lam gyis gtan la dbab byar gnas pa gzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:1268: gzhi shes shing 'bras bu 'grub par byed pa lam /
NK078(tshu)001:1269: grub pa mthar phyin pa 'bras bur bzhed la /
NK078(tshu)001:1270: yang lam 'bras kyi gzhir gyur pa gcig gzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:1271: gzhi 'bras kyi lam du gyur pa gcig lam /
NK078(tshu)001:1272: gzhi lam gnyis kyi 'bras bur gyur pa gcig 'bras bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1274: bla ma lce ston bsgrub pa 'bum gyis gsung gis
NK078(tshu)001:1275: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi gdags gzhir gnas bas na gzhi
NK078(tshu)001:1277: gzhi ni gdags gzhir gyur pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:1279: gzhi shes shing 'bras bu 'grub par byed pa la lam ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1280: de yang de dag shes pa dang 'grub par byed pa la btags pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1282: nyes pa gnyis zad nas skyed du byar med pa ni mthar thug gi 'bras bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1283: gzhi dang lam gyi nyes pa gnyis zad pa gang yin pa de ni 'bras bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1285: de ltar gzhi lam 'bras gsum gcig gam tha dad /
NK078(tshu)001:1286: gcig na gzhi lam 'bras gsum du phye ba dang 'gal /
NK078(tshu)001:1287: tha dad na de gsum la 'brel ba med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:1288: don ngo bo gcig yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:1289: byed las kyis ldog pa tha dad de /
NK078(tshu)001:1290: gzhi ni ye nas gnas kyang mngon du ma gyur pa'i cha'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1291: lam ni de nyid rtogs shing nyams su len pa'i cha'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1292: 'bras bu ni mthar phyin cing mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1293: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1295: gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1296: lam rang gnas rtogs shing goms par bya ba'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1297: 'bras bu rang gnas mngon du gyur pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1298: le'u dang po gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1300: dang po nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1302: gong du bshad pa de la dang po gzhi ye
NK078(tshu)001:1303: shes rang la gnas pa de nyid yan lag rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:1305: gzhi don de nyid skal ldan de yis rgyas par shes par bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1306: gnyis pa gzhung rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1307: rang bzhin ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1308: de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1309: 'khrul yang lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med par rang la gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1311: rang lugs gzhi chos kun sems nyid rang snang la 'khor 'das gnyis su med par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1312: gzhan lugs gzhi 'khor 'das tha dad du 'dod pa la skyon brjod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1315: dang po gzhi 'khor 'das lhun grub yin par khas blang pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1317: de yang phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:1318: 'das kyi chos nyid kyi rang bzhin gyi chos nyid
NK078(tshu)001:1319: 'di kho na ye nas de bzhin gshegs pa sangs
NK078(tshu)001:1320: rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i sku dang ye shes su
NK078(tshu)001:1321: lhun gyis grub pa'i ngo bo nyid du gnas pa
NK078(tshu)001:1322: zhes dam bca' / gnyis pa de nyid kyi gtan tshigs rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1324: de'i rgyu mtshan 'khor ba semsa yin pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:1325: de sgrub byed la gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:1328: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK078(tshu)001:1329: de ni lung gi tshad ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:1333: thams cad ngo bo sems yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:1334: gser gyi dpe bzhin gnyis su med /
NK078(tshu)001:1341: sems la snang ba sems yin phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:1342: sems las ma gtogs chos gzhan med //
NK078(tshu)001:1344: nye ston gyis snang ba sems yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:1345: rang rig pa nyid thams cad du snang ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:1347: rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags pa ni rang bzhin gyis snang ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1349: de bas na thams cad sems nyid rig pa rang
NK078(tshu)001:1350: gi ngo bo la rags pa gang zag gi bdag
NK078(tshu)001:1351: dang phra ba chos kyi bdag gnyis grub pa meda
NK078(tshu)001:1352: pas so // bdag med yin na de'i phyir de bzhin gshegsa pa'ang bsam yas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1353: 'o na gzhi mya ngan las 'das pa'i mthar lhung ngo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:1354: 'khora ba'i snod bcud kyi rang bzhina rang rgyud can du mi dmigsa te /
NK078(tshu)001:1355: de nyid rig pa rang snang gi ye shes kyi
NK078(tshu)001:1356: snang ba yin pa'i phyir de las gzhan du mya
NK078(tshu)001:1357: ngan las 'das pa zhes bya ba gcig log na
NK078(tshu)001:1358: yod pa ma yin te 'khor 'das dbyer med pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:1360: 'khor ba ka dag rin chen gling //
NK078(tshu)001:1361: mya ngan 'das zlas brjod med pa //
NK078(tshu)001:1364: skyon brjod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:1366: dang po 'khor 'das rang bzhin tha dad pa'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1368: 'khor 'das dbyer med yin pa de ltar 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:1369: gnyis kyi rigsa tha dad dang rgyud tha dad du
NK078(tshu)001:1370: grub pa med pas gnas lugs byang ba stong pa
NK078(tshu)001:1371: chub pa snang ba mchoga dbyer med chos sku chen
NK078(tshu)001:1372: po dag ga ngo bo nyid yin pa de la
NK078(tshu)001:1373: / 'khor 'das so sa'i rang bzhina gyi snang stong tha dad du nges pa yin no zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:1374: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'i thabs
NK078(tshu)001:1375: lam thos bsam bsgom gsum gyis 'khor ba myang 'das
NK078(tshu)001:1377: gnyis pa ngo bo tha dad pa'i skyon dpe dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1379: phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa yanga dag pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:1380: sa la gshegsa pa'i 'das pa dang log par rtogsa
NK078(tshu)001:1382: mtshan nyid pa ltar ye nas 'khor 'das gnyis kyi
NK078(tshu)001:1383: ngo bo'i bde sdug tha dad nyid du gnas par
NK078(tshu)001:1385: 'khor ba de la lam gyis bcos shing myang 'das su bsgyur du med de /
NK078(tshu)001:1386: dper na nor bu mching bu la phyag dang mchod
NK078(tshu)001:1387: pa byas kyang nor bu rin chen gyis yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:1388: mi 'byung ba bzhina du tha dad na /
NK078(tshu)001:1389: 'khor ba las 'das pa 'byung bar mi rigs te tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:1390: gnyis pa de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1392: 'khor 'das tha dad na skyon yod pa /
NK078(tshu)001:1393: de bas na dbyer med yin pa de lta'ang 'khrul
NK078(tshu)001:1394: tshul 'og nas 'byung ba 'di bzhin du 'khrul bas
NK078(tshu)001:1406: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas ngo ma shes /
NK078(tshu)001:1407: kun tu brtag pa'i ma rig pas log par rtog
NK078(tshu)001:1408: pa'i gzung 'dzin zhagsa pa dang 'dra bas 'khor bar
NK078(tshu)001:1409: 'ching ba'i rgyus 'khor ba'i ngo bo bskyed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1411: dge mi dge mi g.yo ba'i las gsum dang nyon
NK078(tshu)001:1412: mongsa pa dug lnga ste brgyad kyi rkyen gyis 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:1415: phyi'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis ni rgyu dang 'brel ba drug /
NK078(tshu)001:1416: 'bras bu dang 'brel ba drug gi tshul du 'khor /
NK078(tshu)001:1417: nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1429: de ltar bcu gnyis lus can rnams la dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1430: lus med rnams la bag chags kyi tshul du 'khor te 'khor tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:1434: khams gsum gyi gansa su yang yang bskyar bas 'khor ba zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1437: nang bcud kyi sems can gyis 'doda pa tha dad par snang ba'i 'gro ba rnams so //
NK078(tshu)001:1439: bde ba 'dod pa'i zhen pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1440: sdug bsngal gyis dogs pa'i gdung bas nyam thag cing 'phags pa'i lam dang bral ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1442: 'khor ba rtsom pa'i dus thog ma med pa nas
NK078(tshu)001:1443: dus bzhi kun tu yang dag pa'i don las nyamsa
NK078(tshu)001:1444: pa'o // de yang thog ma tha ma med pa nas /
NK078(tshu)001:1445: yang dag don ma rtogs pas nyams /
NK078(tshu)001:1448: de ltar 'khor bar 'khrul dus ranga bzhin semsa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:1449: sku dang ye shes las gzhan du 'gyur zhing nyamsa
NK078(tshu)001:1450: pa med par la bzla ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1451: 'di'i skabs su 'khrul gzhi yod med kyi brtag pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:1452: gzhan lugs dgag pa dang rang lugs bsgrub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1456: gnyis med phyogs gcig las 'khrul bar 'dod pa dgag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1458: gzhi la 'khrul gzhi ma rig pa rang rgyud can du yod pa las 'khrul lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:1460: thugs thig las sgros 'dog dbang bsgyur gang zag rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:1461: sems nyid dmigs su med pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:1462: dngos po rang rgyud gzhir smra ba'i /
NK078(tshu)001:1463: de yi rgyud rtag par lhung /
NK078(tshu)001:1465: gzhi'i ngo bo 'khrul gzhi ma rig pa rang rgyud du gnas par thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1466: gzhi 'khor ba'i mtha' lhung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1467: lam thos bsam sgom gsum gyis mi sel bar thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1468: gzhi 'khor 'das tha dad du thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1469: theg dman nyan rang gi grub mthar gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1470: mu stegs rtag par lhung bar la sogs pa'i skyon du ma yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:1471: ye nas 'khrul gzhi rang rgyud du 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:1472: gnyis pa ni 'khrul gzhi rang snang med pa las
NK078(tshu)001:1473: 'khrul lo zhe na mi rigs te thugs thig las
NK078(tshu)001:1474: / bskul ba po ni lhun grub la //
NK078(tshu)001:1475: de dang mi mthun so sor rtog /de la de ni mi srid bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:1476: gzhi la ye nas med ces smra //
NK078(tshu)001:1477: zhen blo'i ngos la med do zhes //
NK078(tshu)001:1478: bskur ba gang yin chad lta ba //
NK078(tshu)001:1479: de dang de gnyis tha dad cing //
NK078(tshu)001:1482: gzhi la ma rig pa rang snang du med par thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1483: gzhi stong pa'i mthar lhung bas dbu ma dang khyad med du thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1484: snang stong snga phyi can du thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1485: mu stegs chad lta ltung ba la sogs pa'i skyon
NK078(tshu)001:1486: du ma yod de gzhi rang snang med par 'dod
NK078(tshu)001:1487: pa'i phyir ro // gsum pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1488: btags pa'i snang stong gnyis med phyogs gcig las 'khrul lo zhe na mi rigs te /
NK078(tshu)001:1490: la la ldog pa'i gnyis med las //
NK078(tshu)001:1491: snang smra'ang lhan cig med pa'i ngang //
NK078(tshu)001:1492: brten pa mi dgos gzhir mi btub //
NK078(tshu)001:1493: rgyu rkyen spang bas rig pa min //
NK078(tshu)001:1495: gzhi dag pa'i snang ba phyog gcig tu thal ba'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1496: gzhi snang la 'khor ba'i chos rang snang du med par thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1497: gzhi 'khor 'das dbyer med ma yin par thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1498: snga phyi rgyud dang khyad med du thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1499: mu rtug khas mi len bzhin du gol ba la sogs pa'i skyon du ma yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:1500: gzhi gnyis med phyogs gcig 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:1502: gzhi snang ye shes sgron ma'i ngo bo 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:1503: dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi don ngo ma shes
NK078(tshu)001:1504: pa la 'khrul snang byung bar 'dod de /
NK078(tshu)001:1506: don nyid yod med rig med las //
NK078(tshu)001:1507: de yi rgyu rkyen rang bzhin las //
NK078(tshu)001:1508: sman gyis phan gnod ci bzhin du //
NK078(tshu)001:1509: thams cad ma lus rgyu gcig las //
NK078(tshu)001:1510: mi mthun khyad par so sor snang //
NK078(tshu)001:1512: drug gis 'gro ba thams cad kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:1513: sems nyid nor bu rin po che //
NK078(tshu)001:1514: ci ltar bsam par snang ba las //
NK078(tshu)001:1515: 'khrul gzhis yod med sgro skur bral //
NK078(tshu)001:1517: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rgya mtshor gzugs brnyan ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:1518: rig rtsal 'gags med du rang snang bas 'khrul gzhi yod ces tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK078(tshu)001:1519: de'i dus su thams cad rig pa bdag nyid chen
NK078(tshu)001:1520: po gcig go ngo bor ma g.yos pa yin te
NK078(tshu)001:1521: / 'khor 'das bzang ngan snga phyi tha dad kyi
NK078(tshu)001:1522: rang bzhin phyogs gcig tu ma grub pas 'khrul gzhi
NK078(tshu)001:1523: med ces tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK078(tshu)001:1524: de ltar yod med gnyis la tshig yi ge'i ris
NK078(tshu)001:1525: su snga phyi yod kyang dus la snga phyi med
NK078(tshu)001:1526: / ngo bo la bzang ngan med /
NK078(tshu)001:1527: don la tha dad med par rig pa bdag nyid
NK078(tshu)001:1528: chen po la 'khor 'das phyogs med lhun gyis grub
NK078(tshu)001:1529: cing dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:1530: yang 'khor ba la thog mtha' yod med la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:1534: khams gsum spyi btsan du thog mtha' med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1535: gang zag sgos btsan du thog ma med pa la tha ma yod par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1537: spyir thog ma med par bstan pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1538: dang po dus 'di tsam nas gnas lugs la /
NK078(tshu)001:1539: 'khor ba zhes bya ba mi shes pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1541: thog ma med nas sems yan btang //
NK078(tshu)001:1542: phyin ci log la 'chol nyog spyod //
NK078(tshu)001:1543: gzung 'dzin don la shin tu chags //
NK078(tshu)001:1546: gnyis pa bye brag tu mtha' ma med par rig chad du gyur tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1547: sems can phal mo che chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:1549: byang sems skye dka' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1550: snang log spyi nas 'drangs kyang mi drangs ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1551: sems can grangs tshad las 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:1552: de yang dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:1553: bskal pa bye ba bsam yas su //
NK078(tshu)001:1554: nga yi chos 'di gnas gyur la //
NK078(tshu)001:1555: nyin re bzhin du dus gsum du //
NK078(tshu)001:1556: khams gsum sems can ji snyed pa //
NK078(tshu)001:1557: sangs rgyas sa la dgod byas kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:1558: sems can khams la bri ba med //
NK078(tshu)001:1561: sems can grangs dang tshad 'das pas //
NK078(tshu)001:1564: gnyis pa gang zag sgos btsan la thog ma med pa tha ma yod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1565: gang zag sgos btsan chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:1566: lam nyams su blangs ba la mtha' ma yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:1567: bde gshegs snying po'i khams dang rang chas cha yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1568: rigs sad de dad mos rgyud la skyes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1569: thabs dang gang zag gis lam nyams su blangs pas mthar sangs rgyas te /
NK078(tshu)001:1570: rang gi 'khor ba dong nas sprugs pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:1571: rgyal ba don grub bzhin no //
