NK078(tshu)001:1574: thog mtha' med kyang rtogs na yod //
NK078(tshu)001:1577: thos bsam bsgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:1578: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK078(tshu)001:1580: gnyis pa rtsod pa spong ba la gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:1581: dang po sgos skyon spyi la brgal ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1582: sems can spyi phal mo che chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:1583: 'khor ba la tha ma byung bar thal /
NK078(tshu)001:1584: sgos btsan la mtha' yod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:1585: snon pa med la 'grib pa yod pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:1586: lan la dpe don gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:1588: don ni sems can gcig sangs rgyas /
NK078(tshu)001:1589: gnyis sangs rgyas te 'grib pa yod la bsnan pa med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:1590: sems can la grangs tshad med pas dong mi sprug na ci to ste khyab pa ma grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:1592: 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:1593: khyung chen gcig shar du phur nas btang na shar gyi nam mkha'i mtha' rnyed par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:1594: khyung 'dabs rtsal che bas 'bros pa'i 'dod pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:1597: nam mkha'i khams kyi rang bzhin pha mtha' yas //
NK078(tshu)001:1598: sems can khams kyi rang bzhin de yang pha mtha' yas //
NK078(tshu)001:1600: gnyis pa spyi skyon sgos la brgal ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1601: gang zag sgos btsan chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:1602: nyams su blang bas kyang grol thar mi 'byung bar thal /
NK078(tshu)001:1603: khyab byed spyi la mtha' med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:1604: lan la dpe don gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:1606: spyi la med kyang nyams su blang ba la grol
NK078(tshu)001:1607: thar 'byung na ci to ste khyab pa ma grub
NK078(tshu)001:1609: de ltar na bu ga'i nam mkha' chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:1611: khyab byed 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' la mtha' med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:1613: gsum pa 'khrul yang lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med de rang la gnas pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:1615: dang po dpe dang sbyar te mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1617: 'khrul tshul de ltar 'khrul na yang dper na rgyal
NK078(tshu)001:1618: po'i phru gus rang ngo ma shes pas 'bangs su
NK078(tshu)001:1619: 'khyamsa kyang / rgyal po'i rigs dang sha khrag la
NK078(tshu)001:1620: 'gyur ba med pa de bzhin du 'khrul kyang sangs
NK078(tshu)001:1621: rgyas kyi rigsa las gzhan du 'gyur ba med pas
NK078(tshu)001:1622: shul te lam dang bsgrub bya'i don de 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:1623: rang la gnas te gzhan na yod pa min pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:1624: 'khyamsa kyang / phyir / dper na lha 'phrul dag'i
NK078(tshu)001:1625: longs spyod rang la 'phrul nas longs spyod pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:1626: de bzhin du lam dang 'bras bu gnyis gzhan las
NK078(tshu)001:1627: 'byung ba min te rang la gnas pa'i 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:1629: de yang don dam kun rdzob dbyer med rnam pa
NK078(tshu)001:1630: gsum gyi gnas tshul gyi lus rnam par bzhag pa
NK078(tshu)001:1632: gnyis pa don rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1633: kun rdzob lus dngos po'i gnas lugs la lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med de /
NK078(tshu)001:1635: don dam sems dngos po'i gnas lugs la lam dang
NK078(tshu)001:1636: 'bras bu gzhan na med de rang la gnas pa
NK078(tshu)001:1637: dang dbyer med kyi gnas lugs la lam dang 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:1638: bu gzhan na med de rang la gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1640: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyi don rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1643: yi ge rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1644: gleng gzhi dang rgyud don rang la gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1647: dang po brjod bya don gyi yi ge rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1649: snying gar ye shes snying po'i thig le bam gyi
NK078(tshu)001:1650: dbyibs can la rigs lnga'i sa bon yig 'abru lnga
NK078(tshu)001:1651: sde +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa lngar gnas pa de'i bde ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:1653: rigs lnga'i sku ci yang ma 'gags par snang ba'i phyir thabas chen po zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1655: 'gro ba rigs drug po kun la rang bazhin ngam ngam shugs kyis gansa pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1657: tsit+ta khams lnga'i shi ra la //
NK078(tshu)001:1658: rdo rje rgyal ba rin chen chos //
NK078(tshu)001:1659: shes rab rigs ldan bcud kyi gzugs //
NK078(tshu)001:1660: nges par 'dzin pa gsang ba'i sngags //
NK078(tshu)001:1662: gnyis pa brjod byed tshig gi yi ge rang la gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1664: lus gnas rtsa'i dkyil 'khor spyi bo bde chen /
NK078(tshu)001:1667: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo dang bzhi rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1668: rtsa 'khor de dag gi g.yas na rol ma /
NK078(tshu)001:1670: dbus na kun 'dar ma gsum gyis 'khor lo bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:1671: la srog shing gi tshul du rim par gnas so
NK078(tshu)001:1672: // de ltar 'khor lo bzhi'i rtsa'i gnas na yi ge ji ltar gnas na /
NK078(tshu)001:1673: de yang spyi bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo na
NK078(tshu)001:1674: rtsa 'dabs sum cu so gnyis gdugs phub pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:1675: du gnas pa'i dbus na thig le ham yig mgo
NK078(tshu)001:1676: thur du bstan pa yod la /
NK078(tshu)001:1677: rtsa 'dabs la ka li sgra yig so gnyis gnas so //
NK078(tshu)001:1678: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab
NK078(tshu)001:1679: bcu drug bum pa dra bar bcug pa'i tshul du
NK078(tshu)001:1680: gnas pa'i dbus su am dmar po gnas la /
NK078(tshu)001:1681: rtsa 'dabs la a li dbyangs yig bcu drug gnas so //
NK078(tshu)001:1682: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dabs pad+ma
NK078(tshu)001:1683: 'dab brgyad ltar gnas pa'i dbus na h+aum gnas la
NK078(tshu)001:1684: / rtsa 'dabs brgyad pa sde tshan brgyad kyi thog ma'i yi ge brgyad gnas so //
NK078(tshu)001:1686: rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi gru gu bting ba
NK078(tshu)001:1687: ltar gnas pa'i dbus na a thung shad kyi rnam
NK078(tshu)001:1688: pa dang / rtsa 'dabs la sgra yig so gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:1689: dang dbyangs yig bcu drug g.yas bskor dang g.yon bskor
NK078(tshu)001:1692: rang snang sku yi 'khor lo la //
NK078(tshu)001:1693: rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor rnams //
NK078(tshu)001:1694: g.yas dang g.yon du dbye ba yis //
NK078(tshu)001:1695: sde tshan brgyad dang phye ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:1697: gnyis pa gleng gzhi rgyud don rang la gnas pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:1699: dang po thabs lam gyi gleng gzhi rang la gnas pa nges tshig dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1702: dang po 'og sgo'i gleng gzhi ni e ni gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1703: yum gyi mkha' chos 'byung gru gsum pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1704: ba ni ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1705: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje'i rtse'i thig le bam
NK078(tshu)001:1706: gyi dbyibs su yod pa des bde ba gsal bar
NK078(tshu)001:1707: byed pa'o // ma ni 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1708: ma nu na yid kyi rnam par shes pa la sogs pa rtog tshogs thams cad do //
NK078(tshu)001:1709: ya ni bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1710: lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba don dam byang chub kyi sems de nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:1711: de ltar gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa de yum gyi mkha' gsang la ldan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1712: de dag kyang thal ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:1713: 'dir zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1714: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyings can gnas /
NK078(tshu)001:1715: skad ces gsal byed las ming can /
NK078(tshu)001:1716: bam dbyibs thig le bcas ston pa /
NK078(tshu)001:1717: ma ta ma nu sdom byed yin /
NK078(tshu)001:1718: las can rnam shes de dag la /
NK078(tshu)001:1719: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod /
NK078(tshu)001:1720: sa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud /
NK078(tshu)001:1721: ya ni theg chen 'di yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:1722: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus /
NK078(tshu)001:1723: na ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1725: gnyis pa steng sgo'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1726: gsang ba'i rlung gis sgrom bu snying ga chos kyi
NK078(tshu)001:1727: 'khor lo rtsa 'dabs brgyad kyi dbyibs can ni gnas
NK078(tshu)001:1729: de na yod pa'i ye shes snying po srog mi
NK078(tshu)001:1730: shigs pa'i thig le bam dbyibs can ni ston pa
NK078(tshu)001:1731: / rtsa bzhi la gnas pa'i rnam shes bzhi ni 'khor /
NK078(tshu)001:1732: don dam 'od gsal gyi ye shes ni bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1736: 'og gzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:1737: mi shig thig le bam dbyibs can //
NK078(tshu)001:1738: rang la bde ba gsal byed can //
NK078(tshu)001:1739: ma nu rnam shes yid sogs bzhi //
NK078(tshu)001:1740: ye shes myong ba sdud par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:1741: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pas //
NK078(tshu)001:1742: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK078(tshu)001:1743: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK078(tshu)001:1744: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:1746: de ltar gleng gzhi rang gnas gnyis po de yi
NK078(tshu)001:1747: lam pa'i snang ngo la tan+t+ra ste rgyud kyi don
NK078(tshu)001:1748: bde stong gi ye shes mngon sum 'byin para byed
NK078(tshu)001:1749: pas na gleng gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1750: gnyis pa rgyud don yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po rang la gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1752: grol lam rang la gnas pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:1753: thabs lam rang la gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1756: dang po gtso bo rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1758: gleng gzhi de yis ston par byed pa'i rgyud don
NK078(tshu)001:1759: lam gyi gtso bo ting nge 'dzin ni snying ga
NK078(tshu)001:1760: chos kyi 'khor lo'i gnas de na g.yas chos nyid
NK078(tshu)001:1762: mdun ya shes kyi rtsa kun ting dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1763: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1764: gnyis kyi rgyab las nyid la dngos po rang rgyud kyi rtsa phyag rgya spros pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1765: de yang rtsa bzhi na ma rtogs sems can gyi
NK078(tshu)001:1766: dus su rlung sems rgyu bas rnam shes bzhi dang
NK078(tshu)001:1767: / rtogs pa'i dus su tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi'i lam gyi rim pa ranga bzhin gyis gnas so //
NK078(tshu)001:1768: gnyis pa cha rkyen rang la gnas pa la bdun te /
NK078(tshu)001:1769: phrin las rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1770: bsnyen sgrub bzhi rang la dkyir 'khor rang la dbang
NK078(tshu)001:1771: rang la mchod pa rang la dam tshig rang spyod
NK078(tshu)001:1772: pa rang la gnas par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1774: las bzhi gnas tshul dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1775: sbyin sreg rang la gnas tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:1777: las bzhi nang ltar gnas tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1778: gsang ba ltar gnas tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:1781: dang po bye brag snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo la las bzhi gnas tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1783: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i theg le'i snod ni
NK078(tshu)001:1784: rtsa bzhi ste rtsa de rnams kyi 'od kha dog
NK078(tshu)001:1786: de dag phrin las bzhir gnas te /
NK078(tshu)001:1787: de yang g.yas chos nyid kyi rtsa kha dog dkar
NK078(tshu)001:1788: po dbyibs zlum por gnas pa ni zhi ba'i phrin
NK078(tshu)001:1789: las / mdun ye shes kyi rtsa dog ser por dbyibs gru bzhir gnas pa rgyas pa'i phrin las /
NK078(tshu)001:1790: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa kha dog dmar po dbyibs zla gam du gnas pa dbang gi phrin las /
NK078(tshu)001:1791: rgyab rang rgyud kyi rtsa dmar nag dbyibs gru gsum du gnas pa drag po'i phrin las so //
NK078(tshu)001:1792: gnyis pa spyir rtsa 'khor lo bzhi la las bzhi gnas tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:1794: spyi bo la sogs gnas bzhi'i 'byung ba bzhi la phrin las bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1795: de'ang spyi bo sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi ser po rgyas pa'i gnas /
NK078(tshu)001:1796: mgrin par rlung gi dkyil 'khor zla gam dud ka dbang /
NK078(tshu)001:1797: snying ga me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum dmar nag drag po /
NK078(tshu)001:1798: lte ba chu'i dkyil 'khor zlum po dkar po zhi ba'i gnas so //
NK078(tshu)001:1802: sgrom mdo bzhi na yod pa'i 'byung ba chu sa
NK078(tshu)001:1803: me rlung bzhi yang phrin las bzhi'i ngo bo yin
NK078(tshu)001:1804: te / chu zhi ba'i phrin las /
NK078(tshu)001:1806: me dbang rlung drag po'i phrin las yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:1807: gnyis pa gsang ba ltar gnas tshul lo /
NK078(tshu)001:1809: yum gyi gasnga ba'i mkha' la phrin las bazha rang bzhin gyis ye nas ldan par gnas te /
NK078(tshu)001:1810: de yang phyi 'khyams gru gsum drag po /
NK078(tshu)001:1811: bar khyams gru bzhi rgyas pa /
NK078(tshu)001:1812: skye gnas la zla gam dbang /
NK078(tshu)001:1813: dbyings phyug gi sna rtser rtsa sna tshogs 'dus pa zlum po zhi ba'i phrin las gnas so //
NK078(tshu)001:1814: gnyis pa sbyin sreg rang la gnas tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:1815: drang de yang sum dor ram las me /
NK078(tshu)001:1816: sgrom mdor yam las rlung des bskyed pa las me 'bar /
NK078(tshu)001:1817: g.yas kyi rtsa ro ma ni dgang gzar /
NK078(tshu)001:1818: g.yon gyi rkyang ma ni blug gzar /
NK078(tshu)001:1819: dbus kyi kun rtar ma ni me lha /
NK078(tshu)001:1820: ye shes snying po ni bsreg lha /
NK078(tshu)001:1821: nyon mongs pa la sogs pa'i rnam par rtog pa'i tshogs ni bsreg rdzas te /
NK078(tshu)001:1822: de ltar sbyin bsreg yang rang bzhin gyis ye nas rang la ldan par gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1823: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhi rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1825: de yang g.yas chos nyid kyi rtsa thig les gang
NK078(tshu)001:1826: ba de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo ste bsnyen pa
NK078(tshu)001:1827: / mdun ye shes kyi rtsa thig les gang ba
NK078(tshu)001:1828: kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ste
NK078(tshu)001:1829: / nye bsnyen / g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa thig
NK078(tshu)001:1830: les gang ba ni phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:1831: 'dzin gyi ngo bo ste bsgrub pa /
NK078(tshu)001:1832: rgyab rang rgyud kyi rtsa thig les gang ba spros
NK078(tshu)001:1833: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ste bsgrub pa
NK078(tshu)001:1834: chen po'o // de la bsnyen pa rdzogs tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1835: rtsa gnas thig les gang ba bsnyen pa /
NK078(tshu)001:1836: de yang rang bzhin gyis bde ba 'byung ba nye bsnyen /
NK078(tshu)001:1837: de ltar ngos zin nas nyams su blangs pa bsgrub pa /
NK078(tshu)001:1838: bde ba rgyas te mngon sum du gyur nas nyams su myong ba ni sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1839: de ltar bsnyen sgrub bzhi yang rang bzhin gyis ye nas rang la ldan par gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1840: gsum pa dkyil 'khor rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1842: rtsa ba'i rtsa bzhi de la phye na chos nyid /
NK078(tshu)001:1843: yon tan gyi rtsa la gsum gsum ste drug /ye
NK078(tshu)001:1844: shes dang rang rgyud kyi rtsa la ma phyes pas
NK078(tshu)001:1845: gnyis te yan lag brgyad do //
NK078(tshu)001:1846: sha ra na rtsa man+dala ni dkyil 'khor te /
NK078(tshu)001:1847: ye shes snying po dkyil te dbus na gnas shing
NK078(tshu)001:1848: rtsa brgyad po 'khor du gnas pa'i phyir dal yang
NK078(tshu)001:1849: rang bzhin gyis ye nas rang la ldan par gnas
NK078(tshu)001:1850: pa'o // bzhi pa dbang rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1851: drang gansa pa rtsa dang brten pa thig la las phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1852: nang nus pa'i dbang lnga dang gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1853: dbang bco brgyad rnams rang bzhin gyis ye nas rang la ldan par gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1855: dang po phan pa'i dbang bcus mtshungs ldan rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:1856: rang gi rgyud la ye nas gnas pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1857: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye nas ye shes lngar /
NK078(tshu)001:1858: ye nas rang la gnas pas dbu rgyan no //
NK078(tshu)001:1859: ro rkyang g.yas g.yon 'phyo ba cod pan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1860: kun d+har nang na thig le sum cu rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:1861: phreng ba bsgrig 'dra'i tshul du gnas pa phreng ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1862: rtsa yi dra bas lus kun khyab pa go cha'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1863: thabs shes gsang ba'i dbang po rgyal mtshan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1864: rtog tshogs lhar gnas phyag rgya yin pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1865: bde chen rtsa 'dab sum cu rtsa gnyis gdugs /
NK078(tshu)001:1866: rtsa gnas thig les gang ba bum par bshad /
NK078(tshu)001:1867: 'dod yon ma spangs sems su spyod pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:1868: lce la ro 'bab ma nus yod pa bza' btung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1869: khams lnga'i bcud lnga yig 'bru lngar gnas pa /
NK078(tshu)001:1870: snying po lnga ste rang la gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1871: gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang lnga gnas pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1872: rna ba'i 'dom rtsar reg shes thig le'i sgra /
NK078(tshu)001:1873: nyan par nus pa'i nyan dbang rang la gnas /
NK078(tshu)001:1874: snying la dran rig sna tshogs 'gyu gnas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:1875: reg shes thig les gnas pa bsgom pa'i dbang /
NK078(tshu)001:1876: lag gnyis 'dam rtsar bya byed nus pa yi /
NK078(tshu)001:1877: reg shes thig le sa gnas pa phrin las te /
NK078(tshu)001:1878: lce yis thig les brjod bya'i sgra tshig rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:1879: gsal bar bstan nus 'chad pa'i dbang yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:1880: yan lag lnga la las rnams byed nus pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:1881: reg shes thig les gnas pa rdo rje rgyal /
NK078(tshu)001:1882: rab 'byams bka' yi dbang nyid ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1883: gsum pa zab mo'i dbang gsum ldan pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1884: don dam skye ba med pa gsang ba'i dbang /
NK078(tshu)001:1885: kun rdzob sgyu ma shes rab ye shes te /
NK078(tshu)001:1886: zung 'jug bden pa dbyer med bde chen dbang /
NK078(tshu)001:1887: de ltar phyi nang gsang gsum dbang mchog gis mtshungs ldan de dag rang la mi gnas na /
NK078(tshu)001:1888: dbang rnams bskur yang thob par mi 'gyur bas /
NK078(tshu)001:1889: de phyir dbang gi mtshungs ldan rang la gnas zhes pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1890: lnga pa mchod pa rang la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1892: nang gi lha mo la gsang bar bzhag pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1893: bskyed sngags la sbyor sngags zhugs pas sam bde ba
NK078(tshu)001:1894: bskyed pa'i sbyor ba zhugs pas gsang ba'i lha mo
NK078(tshu)001:1895: te / de yang gsang ba' lha mo bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1896: rtsa gnas na thig le'i chos kyis sgeg pa l+aa s+ya ma /
NK078(tshu)001:1897: thig le rgyun mi chad pa m+aa l+ya ma /
NK078(tshu)001:1898: ha dang si'i sgra sgrogs pa ni girti ma /
NK078(tshu)001:1899: bde bas mnyes par byed pa ni ra ti ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1900: nang ga lha mo bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:1901: bde bas tshims par byed pa d+hu pe ma /
NK078(tshu)001:1902: bde ba 'thor bar byed pa push+pe ma /
NK078(tshu)001:1903: bde ba gsal bar byed pa +aa lo ke ma /
NK078(tshu)001:1904: bde bar 'byams par byed pa g+han+d+hee ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1905: 'doda yon gyi lha mo lnga ni yab yum phan
NK078(tshu)001:1906: tshun nyi zla'i thig les sgeg cing mdzes pa gzugs
NK078(tshu)001:1907: kyi lha mo / bskyod pa ha dang si'i sgra sgrags pa ni sgra'i lha mo /
NK078(tshu)001:1908: bde bas tshim par byed pa'i dri'i lha mo //
NK078(tshu)001:1909: bde ba myong ba ro'i lha mo /
NK078(tshu)001:1910: gsang ba'i rnam shes dang yul dang dbang po reg pa ni reg bya'i lha mo'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1912: long ka'i rtsa na dri chen /
NK078(tshu)001:1913: lte ba'i tsa na sha chen /
NK078(tshu)001:1916: kun d+harma na byang sems te /
NK078(tshu)001:1917: dam rdzas lnga po de dag kyang rang bzhin gyis
NK078(tshu)001:1918: ye nas ldan pa ni mchod pa rang la gnas
NK078(tshu)001:1919: pa ste / phyi rol na yod pa ma yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:1921: drug pa dam tshig la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1923: gong du bstan pa de dag rang la rang chas
NK078(tshu)001:1924: su gnas pa las mi 'ad'a basa na dam tshig
NK078(tshu)001:1925: /lus ngag yid gsum la ranga bzhina gyis ye nas
NK078(tshu)001:1926: ldan par gansa pa'i phyira sa ma ya ste dam
NK078(tshu)001:1927: tshig ces bya'o // bdun pa spyod pa rang la gnas par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1929: rang bzhin gyi sgo nas lus ngag yid gsum gyi 'du byed kyi spyod pa ni gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:1930: phyi ltar na lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod pas dngos su spyod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1931: nang ltar na rtsa kha dog dbyibs su yod pa ni lus /
NK078(tshu)001:1932: rtsa'i nang du thig le yi ge'i dbyibs su yod
NK078(tshu)001:1933: pa ni ngag /de la gnas pa'i tshogs brgyad kyi
NK078(tshu)001:1934: rtogs pa bde ba'i rang bzhin du yod pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:1935: yid do // gsang ba'i lugs ltar na /
NK078(tshu)001:1936: gsang ba'i yul pad+ma lus gsang ba'i dbang po ngag gsang ba'i rnam shes yid do //
NK078(tshu)001:1937: yang na phyi lus kyi spyod pa nang ngag gi spyod pa /
NK078(tshu)001:1938: gsang ba yid kyi spyod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1939: de ltar phyi nang gsang gsum du lus ngag yid
NK078(tshu)001:1940: gsum gyi 'adu byed kyis spyod pa thams cad rgyal
NK078(tshu)001:1941: ba'i mdzad pa dang spyod pa nyid du rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:1942: ngang gis ye nas rang la ldan par gnas pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:1943: // gnyis pa thabs lam rang la gnas pa'o /
NK078(tshu)001:1945: bde ba la zhen cing chags pa rang kha mas khams gsum 'khor ba 'grub pa'i rgyu yin kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:1946: cig shos te bde ba'i thabs bde ba lta ba'i rtsis kyis zin na /
NK078(tshu)001:1947: ranga bzhin nam dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ya
NK078(tshu)001:1948: shes de lam pa'i blo la 'grub par byed pa'a
NK078(tshu)001:1949: // gnyis pa 'bras bu rang la gnas pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:1951: dang po lung rig gi sgo nas rtog tshogs 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:1952: bu lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo nyid yin par
NK078(tshu)001:1955: lnga phung gi ye shes la skye 'jig med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:1957: rigs lnga'i rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir rda rje /
NK078(tshu)001:1958: phung po'i mtshan nyid ni du ma 'dus pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:1959: de ltar phung po lnga'i yan lag rtog pa'i ri
NK078(tshu)001:1960: bo brgyad cu dang bcas pa kun yang dag par
NK078(tshu)001:1961: rdzogsa pa'i sangsa rgyas sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:1962: rigs lngar gsal ba la grags zhes so //
NK078(tshu)001:1963: sogsa sgras skye mched khams rnams so //
NK078(tshu)001:1964: dngosa po kun la chagsa pa'i rten 'byung ba lnga
NK078(tshu)001:1965: dang nang gi rten tshul bzung ba phung po gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:1966: kya byed las khams dang skye mched rnams kyi ngo
NK078(tshu)001:1967: ba lha dang lha mo' rang bzhin du gnas pas
NK078(tshu)001:1970: rang bzhin phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK078(tshu)001:1971: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad kun //
NK078(tshu)001:1972: rigs lnga bde gshegs yab yum gyi //
NK078(tshu)001:1973: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:1975: gnyis pa dpe'i sgo nas gtan tshigs rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1977: 'di la 'bru yi 'dug sa bsgyur don gyis go
NK078(tshu)001:1978: rim sdeb na rgyu rkyen rten 'brel 'dus nas snang
NK078(tshu)001:1979: la rang bzhin med pa sgyu ma'i dpes mtshon pa
NK078(tshu)001:1980: / yul du rnam pa du ma spungs pas na phung po lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1981: byed pa po med pa las rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pas na khams bco brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1982: yul dang dbang po 'dus nas rnam shes skye ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:1983: sgo 'byed pas na skye mched bcu gnyis rnams rgyu
NK078(tshu)001:1984: rkyen gyis rang rgyud par grub pa med pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:1985: / log rtog sgyu ma ste gzhi rig rtsal 'gags med kyi snang bar gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1986: snang la gzung du med pa chu zla yi dpes mtshon pa gang gi phung khams skye mched rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:1988: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:1990: sku phyag rgya chen po dang bzhi po rdzogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:1991: lha'i dkyil 'khor so sor ma 'dres la yongs su
NK078(tshu)001:1992: rdzogs par gsal la rtog pa med pa ni phyag
NK078(tshu)001:1994: gzhi snang ye shes sgron me'i ngo bor gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:1995: de ltar 'khor 'das 'gro 'ong med pa la cir
NK078(tshu)001:1996: yang snang ba sprul pa lta bu'i dpes mtshon pa
NK078(tshu)001:1997: bzhina du / de ltar gzhi gnas lugs kyi ngo
NK078(tshu)001:1998: bor 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rig rtsal 'gags
NK078(tshu)001:1999: med du ye shes rang snang du gcig gi ngo
NK078(tshu)001:2000: bo gcig la go mi 'gags pas /
NK078(tshu)001:2001: cir yang shar bas sna tshogs su 'gyur zhing cir yang rang snang bas lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2002: de la lhag pa kun rdzob kyi nges tshig ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2003: gang lhag na sngags kyi kun rdzob de lhag /gang las lhag na /
NK078(tshu)001:2004: theg 'og gi kun rdzob las lhag /tshul ji ltar du lhag na /
NK078(tshu)001:2005: kun rdzob kyi ngo bo sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du 'dod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:2006: 'khrul pa rang kha mar 'dod pa las lhag /byin rlabs cho 'phrul cir yang snang bas /
NK078(tshu)001:2007: snang ba rang ka ma las lhag /yon tan mtshan nyid 'dus ma byas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:2008: 'dus byas skye 'jig can las lhag /gzhi rang byung
NK078(tshu)001:2009: ye shes kyi ngo bor 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK078(tshu)001:2010: cad rang bzhin med pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:2011: 'gags med cir yang snang bas kun rdzob de nyid
NK078(tshu)001:2012: ye shes kyi snang bar nges pas ngo bo 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:2013: ba med par bden pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2015: phyi nang snod bcud bsdus pa'i chos //
NK078(tshu)001:2016: gzugs su snang ba sku yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:2017: chu zla lta bu bzung du med //
NK078(tshu)001:2020: sems dngos po'i gnas lugs la lam dang 'bras bu'i chos gnas tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2022: dang po lam dang 'bras bu la sogs 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:2023: kyi chos kun rigs rgyud tha dad med par sems
NK078(tshu)001:2024: yin par khas blang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2026: grangs kyi bar ma don dam gyi bden pa la
NK078(tshu)001:2027: mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam gyi chos dang ye
NK078(tshu)001:2028: shes kyis bsdus pa'i 'bras bu' chos rnams lhun gyis
NK078(tshu)001:2029: grub pa'o // de ltar lhun gyis grub pa'i lam
NK078(tshu)001:2030: dang 'bras bu ganga gis kyang rigsa tha dad du
NK078(tshu)001:2031: grub pa'o // rtags pa'am / theg zug tu yod pa min par zhes dam bca' /
NK078(tshu)001:2034: 'o na 'khor ba sems ma yin nam snyam na yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:2035: lam dang 'bras bu'i sems yin pa de bzhin du
NK078(tshu)001:2036: 'khor ba'i chosa kun kyang lam 'bras sems yin pa
NK078(tshu)001:2038: gnyis pa de nyid kyi gtan tshigs rgyas par bshad pa de la drug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2040: dang po sems nyid 'dus ma byas la yul sems
NK078(tshu)001:2041: dbyer med dang dkor bdun lhun gyis grub tshul dang
NK078(tshu)001:2043: de la 'khor ba'i chos su snang ba gzugsa kyi sgo nas dbyibs dang kha dog gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2044: pho mo ma ning gi mtshan ma gsum po yoda pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2045: mtshan ma med pa sgo nga lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2046: khams gsum gyi gansa mtho dman dang rigsa nang tshan
NK078(tshu)001:2047: mi 'dra ba'i sda cha yod pa min te med
NK078(tshu)001:2049: de rnams yongs su rdzogsa te /
NK078(tshu)001:2050: de ltar yul semsa gnyis su 'dzin pa'i yul dang
NK078(tshu)001:2051: bral bzhin du gsal stong gnyis med de nyid dang
NK078(tshu)001:2053: bsgrub bya'i dona gyi mchog tu gyur pa sku gsung
NK078(tshu)001:2054: thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste ye shes lnga
NK078(tshu)001:2055: ni 'bras bu gsang sngags zung 'jug gi don dam
NK078(tshu)001:2056: dang / de nyid sgrib g.yogs med par gsal bas ya shes don dam dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2057: rtogs bya mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyingsa ni rang bzhin don dam ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2058: de ltar bye brag tu phye na bdun dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2059: bsdu na gsum gyi phyir lhag pa don dam yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:2060: gnyis pa de la dkor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2062: dper na gsal ba'i cha nas dapaga bsam gyi shing dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2063: rtog pa med pa'i cha nas yid bzhin gyi nor
NK078(tshu)001:2064: bu rin po che las dgos 'dod lhun grub tu
NK078(tshu)001:2065: 'byung ba ltar / don dam de nyid la dkor
NK078(tshu)001:2066: bdun gyi chos kun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun
NK078(tshu)001:2068: gsum pa de nyid rnams kun mchog ldan gyi chos sku yin par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2070: snod 'jig pa la bcud 'jig pa brten pa'i phyir brtan pa phyi snod kyi 'jig rten /
NK078(tshu)001:2071: g.yo ba nang bcud kyi sems can te 'khor ba'i chos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2072: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos la sogsa pa thams cad snang ba'i dus nyid nas /
NK078(tshu)001:2073: ngo bo rang rgyud can du grub par med pa
NK078(tshu)001:2074: de nyid rnam kun mchog ldan gyi chosa sku chen
NK078(tshu)001:2075: po yin pa de sus kyang ma bcos par rang
NK078(tshu)001:2076: bzhin ngang ngam shugs kyis de ltar du lhun gyis
NK078(tshu)001:2078: bzhi pa de nyid lam dang 'bras bu'i ngo bo yin par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2080: lhag pa'i chos sku de las gzhan pa'i 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:2081: bzang po gcig gud nas thob par bya ba med
NK078(tshu)001:2082: cing / 'khor ba'i chos kun kyang don dam chos skur smin zana yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:2083: lam gyis bsgrod pa'i rtsol ba med de /
NK078(tshu)001:2084: 'bras bu lhag pa'i chos sku de ka nyid bsgrub bya lam gyi ngo bo nyid yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:2085: 'o na gzhi lam 'bras gsum du ji ltar dbye zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:2086: de nyid la 'jug cing bsgrod pa'i cha nas lam /
NK078(tshu)001:2087: de nyid gnas pa'i cha nas gzhi de mngon du
NK078(tshu)001:2088: 'byin pa'i cha nas 'bras bu dang gsum du mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:2089: tshul ma 'dres par phye ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:2090: lnga pa gzhi don des chos kun la khyab cing rgyu yin par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2092: phyogsa bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi
NK078(tshu)001:2093: chos lhag ma lus pa thamsa cad la sems nyid
NK078(tshu)001:2094: rgyu rkyen las ma bskyed pas rang byung gi ye
NK078(tshu)001:2095: shes chen po des dus dang gnas skabs kun tu
NK078(tshu)001:2097: khyab byed rang byung gi ye shes de nyid dngos
NK078(tshu)001:2098: po phyogs gcig tu grub pa med par phyogs med
NK078(tshu)001:2099: du ye shes de nyid 'khor 'das kyi chos kun
NK078(tshu)001:2100: gyi ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu ru mi 'da' ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:2102: gong gi dpe gnyis po dpe lta bu sems nyid de'i ngang du rang snang bas nges pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2103: drug pa gnas lugs de bzhin nyid rgyu rkyen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2106: gzhi don de nyid ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK078(tshu)001:2107: de thams cad kyi 'byung gzhir gyur pas dbyingsa sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:2108: g.yogs med par gsal ba'i ye shes te /
NK078(tshu)001:2109: de nyid ma 'gags par gzhi gnas thabs /
NK078(tshu)001:2111: 'bras bu thob thabsa kyi don la mi 'da' bas
NK078(tshu)001:2112: phyag rgya kun gyi ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu ru
NK078(tshu)001:2114: de la bskyed bya bskyed byed kyi rgyu gnyis rkyen
NK078(tshu)001:2115: bzhi la sogs pa'i ming grangsa med pa'i ngo bo
NK078(tshu)001:2117: de yang spyir rgyu 'bras la dbye ba mang ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2118: bskyed bya bskyed byed kyi rgyu 'bras ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2119: rgyu la 'bras bu'i ngo bo ma grub la /
NK078(tshu)001:2120: de bskyed pa'i nus pa tsam gnas pa te /
NK078(tshu)001:2121: me dang du ba lta bu'am /
NK078(tshu)001:2122: pha ma dang bu tsha lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2123: rnam par bzhag 'jog gi rgyu 'bras ni gtan tshigs blo yul du gyur pa la brten nas /
NK078(tshu)001:2124: grub mtha' blo yul du ma gyur pa bsgrub pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2125: byas pa'i rtags kyis mi rtag pa bsgrub pa shing
NK078(tshu)001:2126: leb gnyis rtse sprad pas gnyis ka mi 'gyel ba
NK078(tshu)001:2127: lta bu'am / res rgyu res 'bras bu ste nas lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2128: gsal bya gsal byed kyi rgyu 'bras ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2129: gnyen pos spang bya spang ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2130: sgron me dang mun khung gi rdzas lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2131: 'dir ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu 'bras sam /
NK078(tshu)001:2132: yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyu 'bras ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2133: lhag pa don dam la lam dang 'bras bu'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:2134: thams cad ngo bo nyid du gnas shing yongsa su
NK078(tshu)001:2135: rdzogsa pa yid bzhin nor bu'i dbyibs kha dog ltar
NK078(tshu)001:2138: kun rdzob mi mnyam don dam mnyam //
NK078(tshu)001:2139: de skad smra ba'i dmus long dag /khre 'bru thu bas sa gzhi che //
NK078(tshu)001:2140: ma mthong tshul dang mtshungs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2142: lhag pa don dam gyi nges tshig ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2143: gang lhag na gsang sngags kyi don dam gyi bden
NK078(tshu)001:2144: pa de lhag /gang las lhag na theg 'og gi
NK078(tshu)001:2145: don dam las lhag /tshul ji ltar lhag na /
NK078(tshu)001:2146: ngo bo zung 'jug gi ye shes su 'dod pas
NK078(tshu)001:2147: dngos po stong rkyang las lhag byin rlabs snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:2149: stong pa la snang bas rgyas theb pa de rgya
NK078(tshu)001:2150: chad phyogs lhung can las lhag mtshan nyid mtha' bral
NK078(tshu)001:2151: snang rig phyogs med du 'char ba de /
NK078(tshu)001:2152: snang rig gang yang mi 'char ba las lhag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2153: de ltar shes bya'i don kun gyi mchog tu gyur
NK078(tshu)001:2154: zhing shes rab dam pa'i yul yin pas don dam
NK078(tshu)001:2155: pa / des mi bslu bar nges pas bden pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2156: gsum pa dbyer med kyi bden pa rang la gnas pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2158: dang po bden gnyis tha dad kyi zhen pa dgrol
NK078(tshu)001:2159: ba'i phyir bden pa dbyer med du khas blang ba
NK078(tshu)001:2161: grangs kyi gsum pa lus snang sems gsum dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:2162: kyi don ni kun rdzob don dam snang stong tha
NK078(tshu)001:2163: dad kyi dngosa por zhen pa dgrol ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:2164: rnam par byang ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sku ye shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2165: kun nas nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i chos phung po khams skye mched la sogs pa rnams chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:2166: gtan tshigs gzhi rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngo
NK078(tshu)001:2167: bor ye gdod ma nas 'khor 'das gnyis kyi rigsa
NK078(tshu)001:2168: tha dad dang rgyud tha dad du brtag cing rang
NK078(tshu)001:2169: rgyud grub pa min par zhes dam bca' 'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2170: gnyis pa de nyid kyi don gtan tshigs rgyas par bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2172: dang po tshogs drug gi yul dang dbyer med par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2174: kun rdzob tu dbang po drug so so'i yul mig gis gzugsa sdug mi sdug sgra snyan mi snyan /
NK078(tshu)001:2178: yid kyi yul 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi chos sam /
NK078(tshu)001:2179: lam dang 'bras bu'i chos kyi bye brag 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:2180: kyi tha snyad ming 'dog tshad sna tshogs su brtag
NK078(tshu)001:2181: pa kun / dper na 'ja' tshon sna lnga ma
NK078(tshu)001:2182: 'dres par snang yang nam mkha' stong pa'i ngang du
NK078(tshu)001:2183: pa kun / gcig pa ltar / gzhi snang gi
NK078(tshu)001:2184: ye shes la 'khor 'das tshogs drug gi bye brag
NK078(tshu)001:2185: ma 'dres par snang dus rang byung ye shes la
NK078(tshu)001:2186: pa kun / gcig pa ltar / / yongs su rdzogs par gcig pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2187: gnyis pa de bas 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas dbyer med par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2189: 'das pa'i don dam 'dus ma byasa pa nyid 'khor ba kun rdzob 'dus byas pa ltar snang yang /
NK078(tshu)001:2190: 'khor ba'i kun rdzob 'dus byas ltar snang ba'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:2191: nyid na'ang don dam 'dus ma byas dang dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:2192: pa'i phyir rdo rje nyid ces bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2193: gsum pa ye nas dbyer med yin kyang bden pa gnyis med du brjod pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2195: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med kyi don de rgyal
NK078(tshu)001:2196: ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sgom pos
NK078(tshu)001:2197: ma mdzad / 'gro ba sems can gyi shes pa
NK078(tshu)001:2198: sgrim pos ma bcos par rang bzhin ngang ngam shugs
NK078(tshu)001:2199: kyis bden pa dbyer med du ye nas gnas pa
NK078(tshu)001:2200: ma mdzad / ste / brgal lan las /
NK078(tshu)001:2201: gnyis med lhun grub bde chen sangs rgyas te //
NK078(tshu)001:2202: sngar 'das sangs rgyas sgom pos 'di ma mdzad //
NK078(tshu)001:2203: slad kyi sems can sgrin pos 'di ma bsgyur //
NK078(tshu)001:2204: ma mdzad ma sgyur byang chub snying po'i don //
NK078(tshu)001:2206: 'o na ye nas dbyer med yin na bshad pa'i dgos ched ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2207: de ltar gnyis med min par tha dad du 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:2208: pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:2209: dbyer med bstan pa las ma gtogs pa'i bden gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:2210: tshig gi tha snyad tsam min pa don gyi ngo
NK078(tshu)001:2211: bo la bden pa gnyis tha dad par 'dod pa
NK078(tshu)001:2212: ni bsam pa'i blo dang brjod pa'i tshig las 'das
NK078(tshu)001:2213: pa'o // bzhi pa yul shes rgyu 'bras phyi nang
NK078(tshu)001:2214: gnyis med ye shes rang snang du bstan pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:2216: phyi yul dang nang shes pa gnyis su snang ba de yang /
NK078(tshu)001:2217: rgyu rkyen med pas rang byung sgrib g.yog gsal ba'i ye shes su snang bar zud do //
NK078(tshu)001:2218: rgyu dang 'brasa bu gnyis su snang yang don gyi
NK078(tshu)001:2219: ngo bo la rgyu 'bras gnyis su med par rang
NK078(tshu)001:2220: byung ye shes su dbyer med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2221: phyi snod ngang nang bcud gnyis su gsal ba'ang rang
NK078(tshu)001:2222: byung ye shes de nyid kyi nganga du rdzogs pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:2223: // lnga pa de nyid lam dang 'bras bu'i ngo bo nyid yin par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2225: gong du bstan pa de ltar gnyis su med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:2226: sems nyid rig pa rang byung gi ye shes ye
NK078(tshu)001:2227: gdong ma nas rang la rang chas su gnas pa
NK078(tshu)001:2228: de / 'jug cing bsgrod pa'i lam dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2229: smin cing grub pa'i 'bras bu kun gyi dngos gzhi yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:2230: gzhi dang lam gnyis thabsa thabs byung du 'brel la /
NK078(tshu)001:2231: gzhi dang 'bras bu gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid chen
NK078(tshu)001:2232: por 'brel ba yod pa'i phyir des na 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:2233: mngona du byed pa yang gzhan na med de gzhi
NK078(tshu)001:2234: rang las byung bar zad do //
NK078(tshu)001:2235: de yang lhag pa dbyer med kyi bden pa'i nges tshig ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2236: gang lhag na sngags kyi dbyer med chen po'i nges
NK078(tshu)001:2237: tshig de lhag /gang las lhag na theg 'og gi
NK078(tshu)001:2238: stong thog gi dbyer me las lhag /tshul ji ltar
NK078(tshu)001:2239: du lhag na / ngo bo 'khor 'das dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:2240: de 'og ma'i gcig las gnyis med pa'i gnyis med
NK078(tshu)001:2241: du lhag na / dam / gnyis ka dbye ru
NK078(tshu)001:2242: med pa'i dbyer med las lhag /byin rlabs dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:2243: lhun grub te gcig las gcig ldog pa las lhag
NK078(tshu)001:2244: /mtshan nyid mtha' bral chen po ste 'khor 'das kyi
NK078(tshu)001:2245: bden gnyis tha dad du 'dod pa las lhag go
NK078(tshu)001:2246: du lhag na / dam / // 'dir ka dag
NK078(tshu)001:2247: lhun grub kyi go don bsdus pa tsam zhig ngos
NK078(tshu)001:2248: du lhag na / dam / // bzung na /
NK078(tshu)001:2249: rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i ngo bo la 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:2250: 'das kyi phyogs zhen spyi bye brag gi rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:2251: phyogs gcig tu ma grub pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:2252: ka dag skyon med dam chen po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2253: dper na nam mkha' bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:2254: de las ma g.yos bzhin du 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK078(tshu)001:2255: thams cad rin po che'i gling bzhin du rig rtsal
NK078(tshu)001:2256: 'gags med du 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad sku
NK078(tshu)001:2257: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:2258: phyir na / lhun grub skyon med dam lhun grub chen po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2259: byed las dgos ched kyi cha nas tha dad ltar snang na'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:2260: don la ka dag lhun grub rgya mtshor gzugs brnyan
NK078(tshu)001:2261: ltar ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid
NK078(tshu)001:2263: nyi ma'i dkyil na rmun med ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:2264: ye shes rang snang ma gtogs par //
NK078(tshu)001:2265: nyon mongs 'khor ba ngang gis med //
NK078(tshu)001:2267: rgyas pa ni gzhan du shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:2268: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2272: dbyer med kyi ye shes rnams ranga la /
NK078(tshu)001:2273: lhun grub tu gnas pa de gsal bar ston par
NK078(tshu)001:2274: byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams 'tshams dang ris
NK078(tshu)001:2275: su gcod cing 'tshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis
NK078(tshu)001:2277: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las yas bgrang dang po'i don du gada'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2278: spyi don gnyis pa lam rang gnas rtogs shing goms par byed pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2279: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2280: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2281: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu zag med kyi rig 'dzin bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2282: de la dang po le'u gnyis pa lta ba bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2283: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2288: de yang gzhi rang byung gi ye shes la don
NK078(tshu)001:2289: dam kun rdzob dbyer med ye nas ma btsal bar
NK078(tshu)001:2290: lhun grub tu gnas pa'i ngang la lta ba rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:2291: pa 'jal ba'i tshul du phyag 'tshal nas zhes pas
NK078(tshu)001:2293: lam kun gyi sngon du lta ba 'gro bas dang po zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2295: lta ba rtogs pa lam gyi thog ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:2298: dman la rgya gsum goms pa'i sa //
NK078(tshu)001:2299: brten nas brtag dpyad klung zhugs mthong //
NK078(tshu)001:2300: zhes sgom pa sngon du bshad pa dang 'gal lam zhe na mi 'gal te /
NK078(tshu)001:2301: blo chung drang don gyi dbang du bsgoms thabs la
NK078(tshu)001:2302: brten nas mthar lta ba rtogs dgos pa yin la
NK078(tshu)001:2303: 'dir blo che bas nges lam thos bsam la brten
NK078(tshu)001:2304: nas lta ba rtogs pa sngon du 'gro bas bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:2305: pa yin pas 'gal ba med do //
NK078(tshu)001:2307: ma rtogs sgoms pa long ba 'dra //
NK078(tshu)001:2309: kun bzang che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud las kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:2310: sgoms pa bas kyang rtogs pa gces /
NK078(tshu)001:2313: yan lag 'di dag thams cad kun //
NK078(tshu)001:2314: thub pas shes rab don du gsungs //
NK078(tshu)001:2315: de yi phyir na sdug bsngal dag /zhi bar 'dod pas shes rab bskyed //
NK078(tshu)001:2317: de'ang rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni lam
NK078(tshu)001:2318: gyi mchog ste nye ba bde ba rdzogs pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:2319: pas / de'i don bashada par bya ba la thos bsam sgom gsum byed dgos pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:2321: dang po thos pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:2322: phyi nang chos la sgro 'dogs chod //
NK078(tshu)001:2323: bar du bsam pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:2324: de don rgyud la goms par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:2325: tha ma bsgom pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:2326: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i nyon mongs zhi //
NK078(tshu)001:2328: thos bsam sgom gsum gyis snga phyi'i go rim nges so //
NK078(tshu)001:2329: gnyis pa le'u'i gzhung la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2331: dang po lus mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2333: las 'phro skal bar ldan pa gang dag gzhi bden
NK078(tshu)001:2334: gsum dbyer med kyi ye shes rang la gnas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:2335: don de mthong bar 'dod pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:2336: don bcu bzhi sgo nas bstan kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:2337: rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis don bcu gcig gis ston te /
NK078(tshu)001:2343: rnam grangsa dang ngo bo dangsa gnyis thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2354: skyon dang lnga ni dgos ched do //
NK078(tshu)001:2358: spyod pa dang bzhi ni rtogs thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:2360: tshad dang gnyis ni ngo bo'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2361: gong gis don de dag yan lag rgyas par bshad cing spros pa'i rtsa bar /
NK078(tshu)001:2362: lus mdor bstan du bzhag go //
NK078(tshu)001:2363: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la bcu gcig ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2365: lta ba rtogs pa'i dus snod dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2366: lta ba rtogs par byed pa'i rgyu rkyen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2367: lta ba rtogs par byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2368: lta ba'i ngo bo rnams grangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2375: dang po dgos ched la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2377: dang po gzhan sel lta ba med na lam mi
NK078(tshu)001:2378: rnyed pas lta ba rtogs dgos par bstan pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:2380: chos nyid mtha' bral lhun grub bsam gyisa mi khyab
NK078(tshu)001:2381: pa'i lta ba'i don ma mthong bar sgom pa bsam
NK078(tshu)001:2382: med tsam gyis rang bzhin gzhi'i dkyil 'khora gyi don
NK078(tshu)001:2384: de ni chos nyid kyi don mi shes pas blun po /
NK078(tshu)001:2385: yang dag pa'i snang ba med par mun pa the
NK078(tshu)001:2386: tshom gyi blo ma nges pas sprul pa'i blo can
NK078(tshu)001:2387: des shes rab kyi spyan med pas langa ba'i sems
NK078(tshu)001:2388: can te / mi snang ba'i grong khyer chen por 'khor zhing 'gro bar byed pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2390: ma rtogs bsgom pa long ba 'dra //
NK078(tshu)001:2392: lta ba med pa'i bsgom pa de //
NK078(tshu)001:2393: lo bas sa mtha' bskor ba 'dra //
NK078(tshu)001:2395: gnyis pa don gnyer thos bsam gyi lta ba rtogs dgos par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2397: lta ba ma rtogs bar bsgoms kyang skyon 'dug pa
NK078(tshu)001:2398: de bas na ma rig pa linga tog dang 'dra
NK078(tshu)001:2399: bas shes rab kyi mig ldong pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2400: yang dag pa'i don ma mthong ba'i slob bu des
NK078(tshu)001:2401: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i slob dpon ni mig
NK078(tshu)001:2402: nang bsal ba'i thur ma mkhan dang 'dra ba de
NK078(tshu)001:2403: sgo gsum gyis mnyes par byas nas dbang thob pa
NK078(tshu)001:2405: de yang dang por gzhung thos pa'i shes rab kyis spyan 'bras phye ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2406: shes bya rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor lta ba'i don mthong bar bya dgos so //
NK078(tshu)001:2407: gnyis pa dus snod thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2409: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2411: gong du bshad pa'i snod dang ldan pa'i gdul bya
NK078(tshu)001:2412: de yanga sngar thun mong gi theg pa la sbyangs
NK078(tshu)001:2413: ba'i rang bzhin gyi rnon po snod du gyur pa
NK078(tshu)001:2414: lta ba rtogs pa'i dus nye ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2415: sngar thun mong lam stegs kyi theg pa la sbyangs
NK078(tshu)001:2416: pa'i rnon po snod du gyur pa lta ba rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:2417: pa'i dus ringa ba'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:2418: sbyangs pa'i rnon po rim gyis pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2419: rang bzhin gyi rnon po cig char ba ste de
NK078(tshu)001:2420: gnyis po re re la yang rim dang cig char
NK078(tshu)001:2421: gnyis gnyis te bzhi cha yis phye bas rnal 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:2422: chen po ma h+aa yo ga'i theg par 'jug par
NK078(tshu)001:2423: byed do // de yang dus ni nye ring /
NK078(tshu)001:2424: snod ni blo'i go 'byed yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:2425: de gnyis thun mong du 'gro tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2426: rang bzhin gyi snod du 'gyur na dus nye /
NK078(tshu)001:2427: sbyongs pa'i snod du gyur na dus ring ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:2428: de dag gi go don la /
NK078(tshu)001:2429: rang bzhin gyi snod du gyur pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2430: skye ba snga ma phan chad thun mong gi theg pa la ma sbyang bar /
NK078(tshu)001:2431: tshe 'di'i stod la rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po bzhi gang rung cig la sbyongs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:2432: tshe smad la ma h+aa la 'jug pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:2433: ma sbyangs par dang po nas ma h+aa la 'jug pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2434: rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2435: sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2436: skye ba snga ma phan chad thun mong gi theg
NK078(tshu)001:2437: pa la sbyangs shing tshe 'dir ma h+aa la 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:2438: pa'am tshe 'di'i stod la nges 'byung gi theg pa
NK078(tshu)001:2440: phyi rgyud sde gsum dor te tshe smad ma h+aa la 'jug pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2441: sbyangs pa'i dbang po rnon po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2442: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2443: dus ring ba sbyongs ba'i snod du gyur pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2444: dus nyer ba rang bzhin gyi snod du gyur pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2447: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2449: dus sam yun bskal pa chen po mang nyung gi tshad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2450: sprul sku'i zhing khams stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i rdul phra rab kyi grangs de snyed du /
NK078(tshu)001:2451: theg pa sna tshogs la shes rab gsum gyi blo
NK078(tshu)001:2452: shin tu sbyangs pa las rab tu gnas par gyur
NK078(tshu)001:2453: pa yis / dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid shes pa ni shes raba kyi mig go //
NK078(tshu)001:2454: de dang ldan pas ma h+aa'i theg mchog 'dir 'jug pa phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:2455: sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa dus ring ba la'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:2456: theg pa tha dag la sbyangs pa'i rim gyis 'jug pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2457: dus mtha'i sgo nas gnas skabs kyis cig char 'jug pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2458: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2459: rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2460: rim gyis pa'i cig char pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2463: dang po sbyangs pa sngon du 'gro bar lung gis gsal bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2465: mdor bstan gyis snga ma dus ring ba'i rim gyis
NK078(tshu)001:2466: pa la'nga tan+t+ra ste rgyud gsang snying gi gzhung nyid
NK078(tshu)001:2467: las theg 'og gi sa dang lam rnams gang 'og
NK078(tshu)001:2468: gi khyad par ma 'dres par rim par bkoda pa
NK078(tshu)001:2469: yang mthar thug rang bzhin gasnga ba'i snying por 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:2471: khyad par bkod pa gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:2472: lha mi nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa'i
NK078(tshu)001:2473: theg pa bzhi yi rang rang gi gzhung bzhin ma
NK078(tshu)001:2474: nor bar bsgrubs pas gang las nges par 'byung na
NK078(tshu)001:2477: byang sems kyis mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung bar byed la /
NK078(tshu)001:2479: gsang sngags kyi theg pa gcig tu nges par 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:2480: bas theg pa de dag gi 'bras bur gnas zhes
NK078(tshu)001:2481: bya'o // de ltar lam stegs kyi theg pa gsang
NK078(tshu)001:2482: sngags kyi theg pa'i sngon du sbyangs pa rdzogs par
NK078(tshu)001:2483: byas pa'i mthar gsang sngags kyi theg mchog ma h+aa
NK078(tshu)001:2484: yo ga la sbyor bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2485: gnyis pa de'i don man ngag gis 'jug tshul bstan pa 'di la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2487: dang po 'jug pa'i gzhi so so'i skye bo'i sa nas sems brgyad skye tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2489: lung nas sbyangs dgongs par bshad pa de yi phyir rigs ma nges pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2491: rtogs skal med la mos skal tsam yod pa yin gsungs te /
NK078(tshu)001:2493: gang du yang rigs ma nges par bshad pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2496: ngan shos ni 'jug pa log lta gcig tu 'jug pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:2497: log rta gang du 'jug ma nges pas rigs ma nges pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2499: yang na nges med 'di zhes bstan du med /
NK078(tshu)001:2502: theg pa kun gyi sgo dang mthun par 'jug cing /
NK078(tshu)001:2503: sbyangs pa'i rigs ma nges pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2504: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po'i sgo dang mthun
NK078(tshu)001:2505: par 'jug pa'i rigs ma nges pa shin tu bzang
NK078(tshu)001:2509: yang na mthun byas kun la 'jal bar 'jug /ces pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2510: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:2511: ma nges spyi yi dbye ba ste //
NK078(tshu)001:2513: 'dir theg pa kun gyi sgo dang mthun par 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:2514: cing spyangs pa'i rigsa mchog des gzhi nas sems bskyed
NK078(tshu)001:2515: lugs ni / shes pa drug las /
NK078(tshu)001:2516: las rgyu 'bras la sogs pa gang yang mi shes
NK078(tshu)001:2517: pa'i mun pa'i shes pa nas phal pa'i sems skye
NK078(tshu)001:2519: ranga bzhin bde gshegs snying po'i khams dang cha rang
NK078(tshu)001:2520: la gnas pa'i rgyu yis bsnyung bar gnas pa la
NK078(tshu)001:2523: gsang ba'i bdag po gzhan yang byis pa so so'i skye bo phyug dang mtshungs pa rnams la /
NK078(tshu)001:2524: brgya lam na res 'ga' zhig chos kyi 'du shes 'byung ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2525: bsnyung bar gnas pa la smyung ba gnas pa zhes bya /
NK078(tshu)001:2526: des de tsam cig sems pa la bya ste mgu
NK078(tshu)001:2527: bar bskyed nas phyi phyir zhing de nyid la goms
NK078(tshu)001:2528: par byed de / gsang ba'i bdag po /
NK078(tshu)001:2529: de ni dge ba'i las skye ba'i sa bon lta bu ste sems dang po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2530: rgyu de nyid kyi mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i nyi ma de dang de dag la /
NK078(tshu)001:2531: pha ma dang bu mo dang mdza' bshes dang nye du de dag la sbyin par byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:2532: de ni myu gu lta bu ste gnyis pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2533: gzhan yang sbyin pa de nyid mi shes pa dag la sbyin par byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:2534: 'di ni sdong bu lta bu ste gsum pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2535: gzhan yang sbyin pa de nyid kyi snod du rung ba yongs su tshol zhing sbyin par byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:2536: 'di ni lo ma lta bu ste bzhi pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2537: gzhan yang sbyin pa de nyid bla ma'am rol mo
NK078(tshu)001:2538: pa dag la dga' bzhin du sbyin par byed de
NK078(tshu)001:2539: 'di ni me tog lta bu ste lnga pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2540: gzhan yang sbyin pa de nyid yid dga' ba dag la sbyin par byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:2541: 'di ni 'bras bu lta bu ste drug pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2543: gzhan yang mthong ris su skye bar byed pa'i phyir tshul khrims bsrung ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2544: 'di ni gsos su gyur pa lta bu ste bdun pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2546: gzhan yang sems de lta bu nyid kyis 'khor bar
NK078(tshu)001:2547: rgyu ba na dge ba'i bshes gnyen la la zhig
NK078(tshu)001:2549: lha 'di dag ni lha chen te //
NK078(tshu)001:2550: thams cad la ni bde ba ster //
NK078(tshu)001:2551: de la khyed kyis gus mchod de //
NK078(tshu)001:2553: de dag kyang ni 'di lta ste //
NK078(tshu)001:2554: dbang phyug dang ni tshangs pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:2555: de bzhin khyab 'jug bde byed dang //
NK078(tshu)001:2556: drag po skems byed de bzhin du //
NK078(tshu)001:2557: nyi ma zla ba chu lha nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:2558: lus ngan nor sbyin brgya byin nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:2559: mig mi bzang dang sna tshogs 'byung //
NK078(tshu)001:2560: gshin rje dus mtshams mya ngan 'da' //
NK078(tshu)001:2561: 'jig rten gtso zhes bya ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:2562: me dang rnam par 'dud pa'i bu //
NK078(tshu)001:2563: de bzhin lha mo dka' thub bzlog /pad+ma dang ni 'jog po klu //
NK078(tshu)001:2564: nor ldan dang ni dus zhes bya //
NK078(tshu)001:2565: kar ko da ta pad+ma che //
NK078(tshu)001:2566: rig ldan dang ni ldeng ka ma //
NK078(tshu)001:2567: rtag tu mtha' yas thog ma'i lha //
NK078(tshu)001:2568: de bzhin lha dang drang srong mchod //
NK078(tshu)001:2569: rig byed rig byed skyes bu yin //
NK078(tshu)001:2570: mkhas pas mchod par gyis shig ces //
NK078(tshu)001:2571: de la de 'dra'i tshig thos nas //
NK078(tshu)001:2572: yid ni yang dag dga' gyur te //
NK078(tshu)001:2573: de tshe rab tu gus ldan pas //
NK078(tshu)001:2574: de dag la ni nan tan byed //
NK078(tshu)001:2575: gsang ba'i bdag po 'di ni byis pa so so'i
NK078(tshu)001:2576: skye bo 'khor ba na kun tu 'khyams pa rnams
NK078(tshu)001:2577: kyi dbugs 'byin pa'i mchog yin te 'di ni stobs
NK078(tshu)001:2579: sems brgyad par rgyal ba rnams kyis bshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:2581: de ni 'jig rten gyi bde legs thob pa'i ched du lha mchod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2582: de la dang po ni dad pa'i sems /
NK078(tshu)001:2583: bar gyi lnga ni sbyin pa'i sems /
NK078(tshu)001:2584: tha ma gnyis ni tshul khrims kyi sems so //
NK078(tshu)001:2585: de ltar 'jig rten phala pa'i semsa brgyad mthar phyin
NK078(tshu)001:2586: cing gnas pa'i tshe nges 'byung bzhi'i dang po la
NK078(tshu)001:2588: gnyis pa 'jug pa'i rgyu rkyen spyir ngos bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2590: spyi'i khams bde gshegs snying po'i rang bzhin gyis gnas
NK078(tshu)001:2591: pa khyad med kyang bye brag theg pa rang rang
NK078(tshu)001:2592: gi khams dwangs mi dwangs su gnas pa ni mtshungsa
NK078(tshu)001:2594: bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK078(tshu)001:2595: skyobs pa'i 'gro ba'i mgon po las lung gnyis thos
NK078(tshu)001:2596: te gang zhe na gong ma'i yon tan bshad cing
NK078(tshu)001:2597: mthong ba dang / 'og ma'i skyon bshad cing mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2598: de yi stobs kyis 'khor ba la skyo zhing rmongs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2599: yon tan la brod cing dwangs pa'i sems skye ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2601: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ru gsungsa pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:2602: rkyen bzhi ni gang gi bla ma de bdag po'i rkyen /
NK078(tshu)001:2603: gsang sngags la sogs pa theg pa ni dmigsa pa'i rkyen /
NK078(tshu)001:2604: skyon yon mthong ba'i slob bu de rgyu'i rkyen /
NK078(tshu)001:2605: de gsum 'dzams pa'i skad cig la sems 'phel ba
NK078(tshu)001:2606: ste g.yo sems dang 'brel ba ni de ma thag
NK078(tshu)001:2607: pa'i rkyen no // gsum pa 'jug pa'i tshul de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2609: dang po rgyu rkyen tshogs nas lhag mi'i theg pa la 'jug tshul dpe dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2611: de ltar rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi dang drug lhan cig tu 'tshogs pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:2612: r+ts+wa las me mched pa bzhin du sems cher 'phel zhing g.yos te /
NK078(tshu)001:2613: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi'i thog ma lha mi'i
NK078(tshu)001:2614: theg pa la sems skyes nas 'jug tshul te dang
NK078(tshu)001:2616: gnyis pa de nas rgyu rkyen gyis theg pa la rim par 'jug tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2618: lha mi'i theg pa de nas nyan rang byang sems
NK078(tshu)001:2619: kri yog gi theg pa rnams la rim gyis bsgrod
NK078(tshu)001:2620: par bya ste / tshul ji ltar du bgrod na
NK078(tshu)001:2621: rgyu gnyis nas bzung rkyen bzhi'i stobs kyis theg pa
NK078(tshu)001:2622: 'og ma nas gong du 'aphara ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:2623: gsum pa yo ga nas ma h+aa la 'jug tshul de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2627: de yang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud yo ga'i theg pa
NK078(tshu)001:2628: la gnas pa la ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa
NK078(tshu)001:2630: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la yo ga man chad kyi skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2631: ma h+aa yo ga'i yon tan gyi lung gnyis thos
NK078(tshu)001:2632: pas gong du bstan pa de ci ltar ba bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:2633: du rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa
NK078(tshu)001:2634: yin te / gnyis pa sems skye ba'i rim pa de la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2636: dang po g.yo ba'i sems dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2638: bla na med pa mchog gi theg pa ma h+aa
NK078(tshu)001:2639: yo ga la 'jug snyam du g.yo ba'i sems skye
NK078(tshu)001:2641: gnyis pa smon pa'i sems dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2644: gzhi de'i go phye nas gsang sngags ma h+aa yo
NK078(tshu)001:2645: ga'i don ci nas kyang khung du chud na ci
NK078(tshu)001:2646: ma rung snyam du smon pa byed pa ni smon
NK078(tshu)001:2647: sems so // gsum pa 'jug pa'i sems dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2649: las dang bya bas lhag pa'i don mtshan pa'i gzug
NK078(tshu)001:2650: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du chos bco brgyad kyis 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:2651: para byed pa ste 'jug sems so //
NK078(tshu)001:2652: bzhi pa gnas pa'i sems de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2654: dang po 'jug chos kyi dam tshig 'bog nas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2656: bla med mchog gi theg pa ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK078(tshu)001:2657: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig kyang skabs
NK078(tshu)001:2658: de ru 'bog cing sbyin par byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:2659: dge bsnyen nan chags kyi rigsa nges par /
NK078(tshu)001:2660: gyur pa'i slob bu la phana pa'i dbang bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2661: bdag don byed nus pa la nyan pa dang bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:2662: pa'i dbang gnyis kyi byin rlabsa tsam slob bu'i rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:2664: gnyis pa lta ba rtogs thabs kyi thos bsam nyams su len pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2666: de nas shes rab ranga gi spyan mchoga lta ba 'byed pa'i thabs thos bsam la brtson nas /
NK078(tshu)001:2667: lta ba rtog pa'i rgyu thos bsam gnyis po'i rang bzhin dkyil 'khor mthonga bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:2668: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i gzhung las thos pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:2669: shes rab dang bsam pa'i shes rab dam pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:2670: du lena par byed pa ni gnas pa'i sems so
NK078(tshu)001:2671: // gnyis pa rim gyis pa'i cig car ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2673: de yang cig char ba'i dbye ba ni drug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2674: dus mtha'i cig char ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2675: rang bzhin gyi gzhi gnas kyi gnas skabs kyi bya rdzogs kyi man ngag gi cig char ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2676: snga ma ni nges 'byung gi theg pa la sbyangs
NK078(tshu)001:2677: nas kri yog sde gsum bor te ma h+aa la
NK078(tshu)001:2679: gnyis pa ni rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po rtogs grol dus mnyam pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2680: gsum pa ni sngar theg pa gang la'ang ma sbyangs
NK078(tshu)001:2681: par so so'i skye bo nas theg pa mchog la
NK078(tshu)001:2682: 'jug go // bzhi pa ni thod rgal bas gnas
NK078(tshu)001:2683: skabs su lam bor la cig char du bgrod do
NK078(tshu)001:2684: 'jug go // // lnga pa ni lam mthar phyin
NK078(tshu)001:2685: te sangs rgyas kyi sa la skad cig gis 'agro'o
NK078(tshu)001:2686: 'jug go // // // drug pa ni snyan rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:2687: zhal gyi man ngag gis rang snang mngon sum du
NK078(tshu)001:2688: 'jug go // // // ngo sprad pa'o // 'dir snga ma bshad de /
NK078(tshu)001:2689: de la zhug ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drang /
NK078(tshu)001:2690: de'i khyad par gyi chos la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2691: gang zhugs na rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa la dgar nas /
NK078(tshu)001:2692: kha cig da lta yan chad thun mong theg pa
NK078(tshu)001:2693: la sbyangs pa'i dus kyi mtha' 'di'i tshe smad du
NK078(tshu)001:2694: ma h+aa la cig char du zhugs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2695: dus nam zhugs na bskal pa sprul sku'i zhing gi rdul snyed dang mnyam pa'i sngon du song basa /
NK078(tshu)001:2696: theg pa gang la sbyangs nas zhugs na thun mong
NK078(tshu)001:2697: nges 'byung gi theg pa dus de nyid du sbyangs
NK078(tshu)001:2698: pa'i mtha' ma gang la zhugs na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK078(tshu)001:2699: ba'i don ma h+aa la zhugs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:2700: tshul ji ltar du zhugs na sngar sbyangs nas tshe
NK078(tshu)001:2701: 'di'i stod la nges par 'byung ba'i theg pa bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:2702: la rima gyis sbyangsa la phyi rgyud sde gsum bor
NK078(tshu)001:2703: nas cig chara du ma h+aa'i drod skyes nas 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:2704: pa'o // gnyis pa dus nye ba rang bzhin gyi snod du gyur pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2706: dang po dbang rnon theg chen du 'jug pa'i 'thad
NK078(tshu)001:2707: pa ngos bzung ba'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:2709: sbyangs pa las gzhan pa'i la la rang bzhin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:2710: shes rab kyis dbang po rnon po dag /rgyu 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:2711: kyi theg pa che chung gnyis gang rung la 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:2712: pa yin te / sngar lam stegs kyi thegs pa
NK078(tshu)001:2713: la blo ma sbyang bar theg chen la 'jug nus
NK078(tshu)001:2714: pa yin te de'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2715: rang bzhin chos nyid kyis grub pa khams dwangs mi dwangs sna tshogs yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2716: chos can rang gi ngo bos grub pa mos pa sna tshogs yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2717: chos tsam rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa dbang po rno rtul sna tshogs yod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:2718: 'dir chos nyid rang bzhin gyis grub pa khams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2719: chos can rang gi ngo bos grub pa theg chen la mos /
NK078(tshu)001:2720: chos tsam rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa dbang
NK078(tshu)001:2721: po rnon po dang gsum yod pa'i phyir rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:2723: de yang blo 'phang mtho ba nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2724: mi 'gyur ba brtan pa ri bo lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2725: shes bya kun la myur ba glog lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2726: shes bya'i gteng 'byin pas rno ba ral gri lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2727: thams cad shes pas rgya che bas gzhi lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2728: dgags sgrub dang bral bar go bas yang pa bar snang lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2729: ming 'dogs dang bral bar go bas rgya mtsho ltar
NK078(tshu)001:2730: zaba pa dang bdun ldan yod pa de theg chen
NK078(tshu)001:2731: la 'jug pa'i rgyu'i gang zag de nyid kyang bdag
NK078(tshu)001:2732: rkyen dge ba'i bshes bnyen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2733: rgyu'i rkyen slob bu mtshan nyid bdun ldan de'nga blo che chung byung bas /
NK078(tshu)001:2734: rim pas phye bas cig char ba'i rim gyis pa rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po rnams la /
NK078(tshu)001:2735: ma nges par 'jug pa dang cig char ba'i cig
NK078(tshu)001:2736: char ba dang po nas ma h+aa 'di nyid du
NK078(tshu)001:2737: 'jug pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2738: cig char ba'i rim gyis pa theg chen gang mos su 'jug pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2739: cig char ba'i cig char ba gdod ma nas ma h+aa la 'jug pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2742: dang po 'brel pa dang ldan pas theg chen dang mjal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2744: cig char ba'i rim gyis pa rgyu'i theg pa la zhugs pa de dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2745: 'bras bu'i theg pa la zhugs pa de'ang 'brel ba bzhi dang ldan tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2746: rang gi semsa nyid khams dngas ba ni bstan pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:2747: dngosa gzhi yin cing de 'chang byed kyi dge ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:2749: nyid khams dang ngo bo'i bdag nyid gcig par 'brel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2750: gong gi don de dang ldan pa shes bya yin
NK078(tshu)001:2751: la rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po ni shes
NK078(tshu)001:2752: byed de shes bya shes byed kyis 'brel ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2753: rang bzhin bdun ldan ni snod bcud du snang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:2754: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po'i lung gnyis snod
NK078(tshu)001:2756: bla ma 'gro ba'i mgon po dang gang zag dbang
NK078(tshu)001:2757: rnon gnyis ni gang zag de la thugs rje 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:2759: bla ma la thugs rje skye bar byed pa'i thabs yod pas las smon thugs rjes 'brel ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2760: 'brel ba bzhi dang ldan pa de'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:2761: theg pa mchog gi lung dbu ma dang 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:2762: gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa rnams dang mjal bar
NK078(tshu)001:2763: byed pa'i phyir 'brel ba bzhi dang ldan pas mjal
NK078(tshu)001:2764: zhes smos pa'o // gnyis pa rgyu rkyen dang ldan pas 'jug pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2767: sngags phyi rgyud gang rung du ma nges par 'jug pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2769: gang gi rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi ste drug dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:2770: pasa rgyu'i theg pa chen po dang sngags phyi pa
NK078(tshu)001:2771: la ma nges par 'jug pa'i tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2772: rang gi shes rab kyi dabnga po rno rtul gyi
NK078(tshu)001:2773: rim pa ji bzhin du rang rgyu 'bras kyi theg
NK078(tshu)001:2774: pa gang la mos mi mos kyi bye brag gam
NK078(tshu)001:2775: / bshes gnyen gang 'phrad kyi rkyen gyis rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:2776: bya ba'i theg pa'am gnyis ka ste spyod pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:2777: rnal 'byor gyi thega pa dang gang mos la sbyor bar byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:2779: theg pa gang la yang 'jug par ma nges te /
NK078(tshu)001:2781: gnyis pa de nas ma h+aa la 'jug tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:2783: rgyu 'bras kyi theg chen gang rung zhig la zhugs
NK078(tshu)001:2784: pa de nas gong du bstan pa de bzhin du
NK078(tshu)001:2785: rgyu rkyen drug gi sgo nas 'dir ma h+aa la
NK078(tshu)001:2786: 'jug pa'ang / sngon rim gyis pa'i skabs bzhina du ma h+aa la g.yo ba'i sems dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2788: 'jug pa'i sems kyis ma h+aa la sbyor nas /
NK078(tshu)001:2789: ma h+aa'i don la shes rab rnam gsum gyi gnas pa'i sems dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2790: don de nyid mthar phyin par byed pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2791: cig char ba'i cig char ba la stos pa'i ringa pa'i dus nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:2792: gnyis pa cig char ba'i cig char ba la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2794: dang po rigs ma nges pa'i sa nas 'brel pa
NK078(tshu)001:2795: rgyu rkyen dang ldan pas ma h+aa la sems skye
NK078(tshu)001:2797: gong du bstan pa'i rigs ma nges pa bzang shos
NK078(tshu)001:2798: kyi sa las dang po nyid nas gong ltar 'brel
NK078(tshu)001:2799: ba bzhi rgyu rkyen drug dang ldan pas sems nyid
NK078(tshu)001:2800: bden pa dbyer med bcos bslad dang bral ba'i don
NK078(tshu)001:2801: rnal ma la / de ji lta ba bzhin rtogs pa'i blo 'byor bas na rnal 'byor de /
NK078(tshu)001:2802: theg 'og las mchog tu gyur pa /
NK078(tshu)001:2803: ma h+aa la sbyor ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2804: dper na mun pa la nyi ma'i zera shar ba'i tshul lam /
NK078(tshu)001:2805: rtsa la me mched pa ltar du g.yo ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2808: mthar phyin pa'ang sngon gong du bstan pa bzhin yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:2809: gnyis pa snod kyi yon tan dang ldan pas thos pa don du gnyer ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2811: 'o na 'jug tshul khyad med dam zhe na ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:2812: mtshan nyid bdun dang ldan pa la khyad med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:2813: 'ang gi sgras tat+t+ra ste rgyud gsang ba'i snying po'i gzhung /
NK078(tshu)001:2815: nganga chu bo chen po'i gzhung ltar ring ba ste cis kyang mi 'khrugs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2816: tshul shes pa ste dge slong gsar bu'i spyod pa lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2817: ranga bzhin bzang ba ste gser btso ma lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2819: blo ri bo lta bur mi 'gyur bar brtan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2820: lus dang longs spyod phangs pa med par chos phyin btang nus pa la sogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2821: snod kyi skyon bzhi las logs pa'i yona tan du ma dang ldan pas /
NK078(tshu)001:2822: shes rab gsum gyi bslab pa la gnas pa'i chos nyid rang byung gi dkyil 'khora chen po ru /
NK078(tshu)001:2823: 'jug pa bzhi ni gzhung thos pas 'jug pa mig phye ba dang 'dra /
NK078(tshu)001:2824: don rtogs pas 'jug pa dkyil 'khor mthong ba dang 'dra /
NK078(tshu)001:2827: 'bras bu thob pas 'dug pa dang dbang thob pa
NK078(tshu)001:2828: dang 'dra ba'i yana lag bzhi'i nang nas mchog tu
NK078(tshu)001:2829: gyur pa dang po gzhung thos pa'i shes rab kyis
NK078(tshu)001:2830: don ched du gnyer bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2831: gsum pa rgyu rkyen drug tshogs nas sam lhan cig
NK078(tshu)001:2832: byed pa'i rgyu ma dgos par rang bzhin ngang gis
NK078(tshu)001:2835: snod dang ldan pa'i ganga zag rang bzhin gyis rim
NK078(tshu)001:2836: dang cig char de gnyis kyi thos pa'i shes rab
NK078(tshu)001:2837: kyis lta ba tshol ba'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:2838: gang ltar rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi dang drug gi sgo
NK078(tshu)001:2839: nas don la mi skrag pa'i bzod pa thob ste
NK078(tshu)001:2840: / re smon sems kyis nyan btson la sbyor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2841: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu la rag ma lus par rang bzhin ngang gis bzod pa thob pasa /
NK078(tshu)001:2842: lta ba rtogs su re zhing 'bras bu thob par
NK078(tshu)001:2843: smon pa'i semsa kyis gzhung nyan pa'i brtson 'grus la
NK078(tshu)001:2844: sbyar ro // gong du bshad pa'i rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2845: sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon gnyis kyi sgrub byed ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2847: dbang po rno rtul gnyis po 'di rgyu 'bras kyi gzhung las bshad kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:2848: phal cher sbyang rnon las rang rno khas len pa nyung bas /
NK078(tshu)001:2849: 'dir ni rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po sgrub byed cig dgod na gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:2850: dang po sngon byung lo rgyus kyi rang bzhin gyi rnon po 'thad par sgrub pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2852: ru yang dag bden pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2854: chos skyong bya ba gsum gyis gdul bya'i dbang po la bsgro ba mdzad pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:2855: ru yang dag bden pa na re /
NK078(tshu)001:2856: rang bzhin gyi rno ba gtso che ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2857: de la 'thad pa mthun pa'i dpe zhig kyang yod /
NK078(tshu)001:2858: rang rno min par sbyang rno kho na yin na gnod byed kyi skyon /
NK078(tshu)001:2862: ba glang gi lci ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2863: ut+pala rang gi sa bon las ud pa la skye ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2864: de dag la de skye ba'i nus pa rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:2865: gyis yod pas skye ba yin gyi sbyangs pas ma
NK078(tshu)001:2868: bag chags rang bzhin gyis med de sbyangs ba kho na yin na /
NK078(tshu)001:2869: zag med kyi mthong lam gtan nas mi skye bar thal /
NK078(tshu)001:2870: sbyang ba'i lugs kyis bag chags 'jog dgos pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:2871: zag bcas kyi skabs su zag med kyi mthong lam
NK078(tshu)001:2872: skye ma myong bas bag chags med pa'i phyir ro
NK078(tshu)001:2873: // 'dod na bag chags ma bzhag par mthong lam skye bas bsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:2874: mchog gi sde pa na re /
NK078(tshu)001:2875: sbyang bas rno ba kho na gtso che yi /
NK078(tshu)001:2876: rang bzhin gyis rno ba mi 'thad de /
NK078(tshu)001:2877: dang po la 'thad pa'i dpe zhig kyang yod la /
NK078(tshu)001:2878: gnyis pa gnod byed kyi skyon yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:2879: dang po ni dper na zhing la 'bru dngos su
NK078(tshu)001:2880: grub pa med kyang sa bon dang chu lud kyi
NK078(tshu)001:2881: rkyen gyis 'bru sna tshogs skye ba bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:2883: rang bzhin gyi rno rtul la sogs pa'i bag chags
NK078(tshu)001:2884: yod na de tshod du ngas sbyin pa ma btang
NK078(tshu)001:2886: tshul khrims ma bsrung bas lha mi'i go 'phang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2887: bzod pa ma bsgoms pa'i gzugs byad bzang po yod
NK078(tshu)001:2888: bya bas ci 'gog /rgyu la ma 'bad pa'i dge
NK078(tshu)001:2890: sbyangs pa la ma ltos par rang bzhin gyis rno ba'ang 'ong ba med ces zer ro //
NK078(tshu)001:2891: ru chos skyong na re khyed gnyis ka la mthun
NK078(tshu)001:2892: pa'i dpe re'ang 'dug /gnod byed kyi skyon re yang
NK078(tshu)001:2893: 'dug pas gnyis ka ltar shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2894: zer nas gnyis ka ltar 'dod do //
NK078(tshu)001:2895: de yang bag chags rang bzhin gyis kyang gnas /
NK078(tshu)001:2896: bsags nas kyang 'jog pas gnyis ka ltar yin pas gong gi /
NK078(tshu)001:2897: skyon gnyis ka las grol bar 'dod do //
NK078(tshu)001:2899: de rnams las rang bzhin gyis rno bar blang bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2900: zhes rang rno gtso che bar bshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:2901: gnyis pa sgrub byed la gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:2904: sems can rnams kyi shes pa'i rgyud la rno rtul rang bzhin gyis med pa ni ma yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:2907: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhing khams na 'khod pa'i sems
NK078(tshu)001:2908: can chen po de dag ni sems kyi rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:2909: sna tshogs pa'i phyir blo shin tu zab ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:2910: / mi zab pa dang yangs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2917: bul ba sha stag pas gsang sngags ngo bo nyid
NK078(tshu)001:2918: kyi gtam rim gyis pa dang cig car thos nas
NK078(tshu)001:2919: de ngag gang la yang mi skrag mi dngang gi
NK078(tshu)001:2921: rangs sar 'gyur ba'i phyir sna tshogs su snang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:2924: lha mi sems can dbang po mi mthun te /
NK078(tshu)001:2925: la la sbyongs pa'i dbang po 'a phro can dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2926: la la ye nas dbang po gcig chod yod /
NK078(tshu)001:2928: ye shes rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK078(tshu)001:2929: rigs drug dbang po gcig chod dam /
NK078(tshu)001:2930: kha cig sbyangs pa'i 'phro can no //
NK078(tshu)001:2933: sems can dang po'i las can la /
NK078(tshu)001:2934: cig char bar ni bstan par bya de nas sbyangs pa'i 'phro can la /
NK078(tshu)001:2935: rim gyis pa ni bstan par bya /
NK078(tshu)001:2938: kha cig thog ma nas de rig /kha cig sbyangs pa las gyur pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2941: rang bzhin las kyis phye ba yis //
NK078(tshu)001:2943: gsum pa rig pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2944: rang rno sgrub byed kyi rigs pa dgod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2945: med na skyon du 'gyur bas rigs pas yod par bsgrub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2946: gzhan gyis rtsod pa spangs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2948: gong ma rnams kyi gsung gi mdo sngags thun mong gi rigs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2949: khyad par sngags kyi rigs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2952: gang zag gi shes rgyud chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:2953: la la rang bzhin gyis dbang po rno ba yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:2954: bag chags mtha' yas rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:2956: gtan tshigs ma grub ce na 'o na khyed kyis bag chags phyogs gcig par khas len nam /
NK078(tshu)001:2957: len na nga gang du skye ba'i bag chags 'dug /lha skye ba'i bag chags 'dug ce na /
NK078(tshu)001:2958: de tshod du ngas mir skye ba'i bag chags yod bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2959: da yod de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:2961: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge ba bcu spang ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:2962: 'dir yang dge bcu shas 'ga' spyod cing mi dge bshas 'ga' spang ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:2963: gnyis ka'i khyab pa ni lung man ngag gis 'grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:2964: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spang byed pa //
NK078(tshu)001:2966: yang dge bcu dag la gtsor len cing /
NK078(tshu)001:2967: zhes pa la sogs pas 'grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:2968: bag chags mtha' yas yod kyang rang bzhin gyi med na ci sto /
NK078(tshu)001:2969: bag chags bsags pa'i stobs las byung ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:2970: gang zag gi shes rgyud chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:2971: kun la bag chags sna tshogs rang bzhin gyis yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:2972: kun bzhi dang bag chags snga phyi tha dad med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:2974: gtan tshigs ma grub zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:2975: 'o na kun gzhi dang bag chags gang snga /
NK078(tshu)001:2976: kun gzhi snga na skyon gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:2977: kun gzhi'i nges tshig med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:2978: 'khor ba la thog ma yod par 'gyur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:2980: bag chags bsag pa kho nar 'dod na /
NK078(tshu)001:2981: kun gzhi dang bag chags snga phyi can du 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:2982: bas bag chags med pa'i kun gzhi gter stong lta
NK078(tshu)001:2983: bu de la kun gzhi'i nges tshig med do //
NK078(tshu)001:2984: gzhan yang sems dang bag chags gcig min tha dad ma yin brtag par rab tu dka' /
NK078(tshu)001:2985: zhes pa la sogs pa dang 'gal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:2986: gnyis 'khor ba la thog ma yod par 'gyur ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:2987: dang po kun gzhi stong pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:2988: phyis bag chags gzhan nas 'ong na /
NK078(tshu)001:2989: de ka 'khor ba'i thog mar 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:2990: kun gzhi la med par phyis 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:2992: bag chags snga na bag chags gang la gsogs te bsags gzhi kun gzhi med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:2993: de bas na mdo sde las /
NK078(tshu)001:2994: lhan cig skyes pa'i bag chags dang //
NK078(tshu)001:2996: glo bur du bsags pa'i bag chags ma yin par
NK078(tshu)001:2997: chos nyid kyis grub pa'i bag chags bya ba zhig
NK078(tshu)001:2998: rang bzhin gyi gnas dgos so //
NK078(tshu)001:2999: de med na sangs rgyas pa'i bag chags kyang med pas bde gshegs snying por yang mi 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3000: bag chags mtha' yas rang bzhin gyis gnas kyang rang
NK078(tshu)001:3001: rno med na ci sto te khyab pa ma grub
NK078(tshu)001:3002: zhe na / bag chags dang mtha' yas yod na
NK078(tshu)001:3003: rang rno yang yod de mtha' yas kyi khong du
NK078(tshu)001:3004: rang rno yang 'du ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3005: yang gtan tshigs khyab pa lung gis grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3006: sems 'di las rnam shes mtha' yas gnas 'gyur bag chags mtha' med nges pa med /
NK078(tshu)001:3007: bag chags rtas shing sang par byed pa'i rkyen yang nam pa sna tshogs te /
NK078(tshu)001:3009: gnyis pa sngags khyad par can gyi rigs pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3010: gang zag gi shes rgyud chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:3011: la la rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:3012: sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:3013: dper na lcags rig 'ga' zhig bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3014: gtan tshigs ma grub zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3016: khyod sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs phyogs gcig par
NK078(tshu)001:3017: khas len na nga'i sems kyi rang bzhin gang du
NK078(tshu)001:3018: nges / 'dod chags dang bcas par nges so zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3019: de tshod du ngas zhe sdang dang bcas par nges bya yi /
NK078(tshu)001:3021: 'dir yang ci'i phyir lhag pa zhen cing chags pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3022: kun nas mnar sems pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3023: sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs kyang rang rno med na ci stong zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3024: sna tshogs pa'i khongs su rang rno yang 'du ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3025: mi 'du na sna tshogs ma yin par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3026: 'dod na sems kyang rang bzhin sna tshogs pa'i phyir zhes pas bsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3027: gsum pa g.yal gyi bzhed ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3028: gang zag gyi shes rgyud chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:3029: la la rang bzhin gyis dbang po rno ba yang yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:3030: gdod ma nas theg pa chen po la 'jug nus pa'i gang zag yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3031: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun dang ldan pa'i gang zag yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3032: gtan tshigs ma grub ce na /
NK078(tshu)001:3034: la la dbang po rno ba dag ces pa lngas rim pa bzhin du gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3035: bye brag tu gnyis pa ma sbyang bar grub pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3036: gang zag gi shes rgyud chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:3037: la la rang bzhin rno ba dag yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:3038: chos can rang gi rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i phyir gser gyi ser po bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3039: chos nyid rang gi ngo bos grub pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:3040: lcags ze'u smug po bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3041: rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:3043: des na de dag rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed pa med
