NK078(tshu)001:3044: par rang bzhin gyis grub pa bzhin du blo rigs
NK078(tshu)001:3045: 'ga' zhig grub pa rang gi rang rno grub pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:3046: // rtags de'i khyab pa dpe steng du grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:3047: 'di nyid la sbyangs rno dang rnam thar ma 'dres
NK078(tshu)001:3048: pa gsum yod de skye ba snga gong du sbyongs
NK078(tshu)001:3050: 'di la theg chung la 'jug mi srid pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3051: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun dang ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3052: de yang ma sbyangs grub pa gsum phyir gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:3054: theg pa chen po gnyis 'jug ste //
NK078(tshu)001:3056: mtho brtan myur rno rgya che yang //
NK078(tshu)001:3057: zab yod rgyu yi gang zag de //
NK078(tshu)001:3058: zhes pa rim pa bzhin du gsal te /
NK078(tshu)001:3059: sbyangs rno la zur za ba'i tshig yin skad /
NK078(tshu)001:3060: gnyis pa med na skyon du 'gyur bas rigs pas bsgrub pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3061: gong gi gzhung rnams dang 'gal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3062: gzhan yang 'jig rten gzhag pa na snod me bdun
NK078(tshu)001:3063: chu gcig gis 'jig pa'i dus su bcud kyi sems
NK078(tshu)001:3064: can rnams la bsam gtan gyi ting nge 'dzin skye
NK078(tshu)001:3065: nas khams gong mar skye ba dang 'gal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3067: rang bzhin gyis ma grub par sbyangs pas rno ba kho na yin na /
NK078(tshu)001:3068: 'jig rten phal pa'i sems brgyad gtan nas mi skye bar thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3069: sbyangs pa mnyam po la rgyud tha dad la rno rtul mi 'byung bar thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3070: rgyud la yang rno rtul gnyis mi 'byung bar thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3071: 'khor ba la thog ma yod par thal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3073: rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po med na 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:3074: rten phal pa'i sems brgyad gtan nas mi skye bar
NK078(tshu)001:3075: thal / gzhi la rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3078: sems brgyad kyi skye tshul gsungs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3080: rang bzhin rgyu yis bsnyung bar gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:3081: phal pa'i sems brgyad mthar gnas tshe //
NK078(tshu)001:3082: zhes rang bzhin ngang gis skye bar bshad pas gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3083: rang rno med kyang phal pa'i sems brgyad skye na ci ste zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3085: sems brgyad rang bzhin gyis skye'am /
NK078(tshu)001:3086: sbyangs pa'i stobs la ltos nas skye /
NK078(tshu)001:3087: dang po ltar na sems brgyad rang bzhin gyis skye
NK078(tshu)001:3088: bar grub pas rang rno yang grub par mtshungs so
NK078(tshu)001:3090: rang bzhin rgyu yi bsnyung bar gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:3092: yang rgyu sems brgyad snga ma snga mas skye'o zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3095: 'dod na sbyangs pa cig 'dug ste rno ba med do gsungs te /
NK078(tshu)001:3096: nang gi sngon ma gang las byung brtag go //
NK078(tshu)001:3098: gang zag las dang po gnyis sbyang ba mnyam po la blo rno rtul mi 'ong bar thal /
NK078(tshu)001:3099: rang bzhin gyis rno rtul med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3100: 'dod na bsal te 'di nyid las snga ma'ang //
NK078(tshu)001:3102: kha gcig dus mtha' cig char ba //
NK078(tshu)001:3103: ces pas sbyangs pa mnyam po la yang rno rtul yod par bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3105: tshogs lam man chad sbyang pa khyad med par mnyam pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:3106: sbyor lam du rang gi 'dod chags kyi gnyen po mi sdug pa bsgom du bcug pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:3107: gcig gis rten 'brel lug bzlog gi sgo nas 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:3108: ba'i rgyu ma rig par shes nas rang rgyal du
NK078(tshu)001:3109: 'gyur la / gcig gis rus pa la brten pa
NK078(tshu)001:3110: dka' las ma shes te nyan thos su lus pas
NK078(tshu)001:3112: de skye ba snga ma'i sbyongs pa la khyad par yod dam ci cha zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3113: des mi phan de ci cha yod rig pa min
NK078(tshu)001:3114: pa'i phyir sbyangs pa la khyad par med dam yang
NK078(tshu)001:3115: ci cha yod khyab brtags ma nges /
NK078(tshu)001:3118: gang zag gcig gi shes rgyud la rno rtul gnyis su mi 'char bar thal /
NK078(tshu)001:3119: rang bzhin rno ba ma grub pa'i phyir gtan tshigs khas blang gis grub /
NK078(tshu)001:3120: khyab pa dngos po la gnas so //
NK078(tshu)001:3121: 'dod na rang gi shes rgyud la sbyangs pa khyad
NK078(tshu)001:3122: med kyang khams kyi rkyen gyis res rno res rtul
NK078(tshu)001:3125: 'khor ba la thog ma yod par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:3126: 'khor ba'i bag chags rang bzhin gyis med de gsar skyes yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3127: gtan tshigs khas blang gis grub la /
NK078(tshu)001:3128: khyab pa dngos po la gnas te /
NK078(tshu)001:3129: glo bur du bsags pa la thog mtha' dang bcas pas khyab pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3130: gsum pa gzhan gyi rtsod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3133: gzhi bzang ngan du thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3134: lam la ma 'bad pa'i rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3135: mtshams med la sogs ma spyad pa'i dmyal ba yod par thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3136: mu stegs bdag lta ba'i grub mtha' bden par thal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3138: gzhi chos nyid bzang ngan can du thal /
NK078(tshu)001:3139: rno rtul gnyis kyi gzhi chos nyid yin pa de gnyis la bzang ngan du 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3141: rkyen la ma ltos pa'i rgyud dag pa dang dmyal ba yod par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:3142: rgyu rkyen la ma ltos pa'i rno rtul 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3144: mu stegs pa'i skye bu shes rig gi bdag ther
NK078(tshu)001:3145: zug gi dngos po 'dod pa de yang bden par
NK078(tshu)001:3146: thal lo // rang bzhin gyi rno rtul yod pa dang mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3148: dang po'i skyon med de rkyen gyis rno rtul bzang
NK078(tshu)001:3149: ngan tha dad ltar du snang yang gzhi ma sems
NK078(tshu)001:3150: nyid dbang btsan par byas nas sems nyid du dbyer
NK078(tshu)001:3152: dper na sku dang zom zangs kyi rkyen gyis bzang
NK078(tshu)001:3153: ngan tha dad ltar snang yang gzhi ma gser du
NK078(tshu)001:3154: bzang ngan mnyam pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3155: de yang ngo bo thams cad sems yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:3156: gser gyi dpe dang gnyis su med //
NK078(tshu)001:3158: de med na rang rno grub pa med pas 'gal lo gsungs te mi 'gal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3159: yang na gzhi bzang ngan can du snang ba thal zer ram /
NK078(tshu)001:3160: grub par thal zer dang po 'dod thog /gnyis pa gtan tshigs med do //
NK078(tshu)001:3161: yod de bzang ngan can du snang ba'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3162: snang yang bzang ngan grub pa med na ci sto khyab pa med do //
NK078(tshu)001:3164: snang tshul cir yang snang ba la //
NK078(tshu)001:3165: yin tshul nges pa med pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:3167: de bas na de skad zer ba ni 'khrul snang
NK078(tshu)001:3168: gi zhen blo tshad mar byas nas gshis la skyon
NK078(tshu)001:3170: de gnyis las khyad che ba'i 'khor 'das dang ma
NK078(tshu)001:3171: rig ye shes kyang bzang ngan med par ro gcig
NK078(tshu)001:3172: par bshad pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud gzhung zab mo'i
NK078(tshu)001:3173: don la rtog shig /gnyis pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3174: rgyud dag pa dang dmyal bar snang ba de lam dang las kyi rkyen la ltos sam mi ltos /
NK078(tshu)001:3175: ltos na de gnyis yod pa 'dod thog ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3176: rgyud gzhung tha dag nas rtogs ma rtogs kyi 'khor 'das byung bar bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3177: mi ltos na rgyu mtshan mi mtshugs te /
NK078(tshu)001:3178: 'di ni rang bzhin gyi rno rtul grub kyang rno rtul tu snang ba rkyen la ltos pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:3179: dper na ze'u smug po bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3181: lam ma sgyangs pa'i rgyud dag ni 'gal la /
NK078(tshu)001:3182: rang bzhin gyi rno ba ni mi 'gal bar bsgrubs zin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3183: lcags rdo la sogs pa la yang rno rtul du ma ye nas grub pas bsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3184: 'di med na ye ji bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas kyang mi 'thad do gsungs /
NK078(tshu)001:3186: rtag pa 'gyur med du 'dod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3187: 'dir bzhi las grub pa tsam du 'dod kyi rtags par mi 'dod pas mi mtshungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3188: dper na me la tsha ba rang bzhin gyis grub kyang mi rtag gi /
NK078(tshu)001:3189: lcags la rno rtul rang bzhin gyis grub kyang mi rtag pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3190: gsum pa de gang la ldan dpyad pa la bzhi las /
NK078(tshu)001:3191: dang po rno rtul gzhi dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs la yod dam /
NK078(tshu)001:3193: gnas lugs la yod na lung dang 'gal ba'i skyon 'byung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3195: byang chub snying po nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:3198: sems can rnams kyis sems rgyud la //
NK078(tshu)001:3199: gzhi nas rno rtul yod dam med //
NK078(tshu)001:3200: sems can rnams kyi sems kyi rgyud //
NK078(tshu)001:3201: bde gshegs snying po gcig pas na //
NK078(tshu)001:3202: sbyor rno che chung khyad par las //
NK078(tshu)001:3203: gzhi nas rang rgyud rno rtul med //
NK078(tshu)001:3204: gal lte rang rgyud rno rtul na //
NK078(tshu)001:3205: de bzhin nyid du gcig mi rung //
NK078(tshu)001:3210: gzhi la rno rtul gnyis 'dug pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3211: lha rje gtsang pa na re /
NK078(tshu)001:3212: 'khrul pa brtag bzhi la rno rtul gnyis 'byung la /
NK078(tshu)001:3213: gnas lugs la rno rtul gnyis med do zhe'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3215: gnas lugs la med par brtag gzhi la 'byung na /
NK078(tshu)001:3216: rgyu med kyi 'bras bur 'byung bar 'gyur bas /
NK078(tshu)001:3217: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi la'ang rgyu gcig tsam zhig yod zhe'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3219: don dam la stong par yod /
NK078(tshu)001:3220: kun rdzob la snang bar yod dbyer med la rno rtul gnyis dbyer med yod ce'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3221: gnyis pa rnon po rtul po gang zag gcig gi
NK078(tshu)001:3222: shes pa'i rgyud la 'tshogs su brtul bam mi btub
NK078(tshu)001:3223: / mi btub na chos thams cad gnyis med du lhun gyis grub pa min par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:3225: 'dod na yod med rtag chad bya brtsol la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:3226: pa kun nas lhun gyis grub par ye nas gnas
NK078(tshu)001:3228: btub na rnon po yin phan chad rtul po min
NK078(tshu)001:3229: la rtul po yin phan chad rnon po min pas
NK078(tshu)001:3231: rno rtul gnyis po de ngo bo la ltos nas 'tshogs su mi btub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3232: rnon po yin phan chad rtul po min la rtul
NK078(tshu)001:3233: po yin phan chad rnon po min pa'i phyir ro
NK078(tshu)001:3234: // rkyen la ltos nas 'tshogs su brtub ste rnon
NK078(tshu)001:3235: po rang yang khams ma bde ba'i rkyen gyis rtul
NK078(tshu)001:3237: gsum pa rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3238: sbyangs pa'i dbang po rnon po gang zag cig gi
NK078(tshu)001:3239: shes pa'i rgyud la 'tshogs su btub bam mi btub
NK078(tshu)001:3240: / mi btub na chos nyid gnyis med du lhun gyis grub pa ma yin par 'gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:3241: btub na rang bzhin yin phan chad sbyangs pa min /
NK078(tshu)001:3242: sbyangs pa yin phan chad rang bzhin min pas 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3243: de gnyis dus gcig la ltos nas 'tshogs su mi btub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3244: rang bzhin yin na sbyangs pa min la /
NK078(tshu)001:3245: sbyangs pa yin na rang bzhin min pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3246: tha dad la ltos nas 'tshogs su btub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3247: rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po rang yang sbyangs shing je rnon du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3248: bzhi ba rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po de
NK078(tshu)001:3249: 'gro ba lha mi lta bu zhig la ldan nam
NK078(tshu)001:3250: mi ldan / mi ldan na 'gro ba gzhan ba
NK078(tshu)001:3251: glang lta bu la ldan par thal 'dod na rmongs
NK078(tshu)001:3253: ldan na sbyangs rnon du thal /
NK078(tshu)001:3254: dge bcu la sbyongs bar bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3255: 'dod na rang rnon 'dod pa bud do //
NK078(tshu)001:3257: rang bzhin gyi bag chags kyis lha mir skye ba'i dbang po mchog la ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3259: gang du bshad pa de rnams kyi don hril gyis dril nas nges par go bya'i don ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3261: gzhi don rang byung gi ye shes bden gsum dbyer med kyi rang bzhin la /
NK078(tshu)001:3262: gzhi snang ye shes sgron ma rig rtsal 'gags med
NK078(tshu)001:3263: kyi snang ba'i dbang du 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK078(tshu)001:3265: gcig du ma'i mtha' dang bral ba snang la rang bzhin med pa rgya mtsho'i gzugs brnyan ltar du /
NK078(tshu)001:3266: khams dang dbang po rno rtul la sogs pa'i bye
NK078(tshu)001:3267: brag thams cad rang rgyud can du bzang ngan tha
NK078(tshu)001:3268: dad gang yang grub pa med par /
NK078(tshu)001:3269: byang chub sems kyi ngo bor lhun gyis grub cing mnyam pa nyid du gnas pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3271: ma 'dres pa la so sor snang //
NK078(tshu)001:3272: yongs su rdzogs pas stong bdag med //
NK078(tshu)001:3275: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK078(tshu)001:3276: de ni lung gi tshad mar bzhag /ces gsung bas /
NK078(tshu)001:3277: de nyid kyi don ma shes pa'i 'dzin stangs phrag rags 'thug srab kyi khyad par las /
NK078(tshu)001:3278: khams dang dbang po rno rtul gyi bye brag sna
NK078(tshu)001:3279: tshogs bar snang ste g.yul thang las rang bzhin gcig
NK078(tshu)001:3281: rdzas sna rnams pa gcig la yang //
NK078(tshu)001:3282: log mthong drug dang yang dag dgu //
NK078(tshu)001:3283: cir yang 'char ba'i ngo bo nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:3285: zhib tu dgongs gzhi dgos ched kyi go don rnams bla ma'i zhal las shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:3286: gsum pa rgyu rkyen thun mong du bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3288: dang po thos bsam lta ba shes pa'i rgyu ru bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3290: snod ldan gang dag thos pa'i sgo nas gzhang mnyam pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3291: yid kyi bsam pa'i shes rab kyis tshi ga don gnyis ka la dpyod pa'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:3292: de ltar gzhung mnyan cing rna ba'i thos pa'i shes rab kyis tshig blo la 'dzin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3293: zin pa'i tshig gis don la yid kyis bsam pa
NK078(tshu)001:3294: dang bsam pa'i shes rab kyis tshe gcig na'ang don
NK078(tshu)001:3295: che long gi rnam pa la rtoog pa ste rtsing
NK078(tshu)001:3296: ba dang / don la zhib tu dpyod pa ste zhib pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3297: de ltar rtog dpyod gnyis po'di dag rgyu shes pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:3298: mtshan nyid lta ba gtan la phab cing rtogs pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:3299: // gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3301: rgyud lung man ngag gi don grol par byed pa'i mkhan po ste bla ma dam pa /
NK078(tshu)001:3303: bla ma dam pa'i man ngag bcas nas ngo sprod
NK078(tshu)001:3304: pa de ni lta ba rtogs pa dang lhan cig
NK078(tshu)001:3305: tu byed pa'i rkyen du 'dod do //
NK078(tshu)001:3306: gsum pa mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3308: de ltar man ngag zab mos ngo srod du btub pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3309: slob bu'i sems kyi rang bzhina la mtho brtan myur
NK078(tshu)001:3310: rno rgya che yangs pa zab pa'i mtshan nyid bdun
NK078(tshu)001:3311: dang ye gdod ma nas mtshungs par ldan pa de
NK078(tshu)001:3312: ni / lta ba shes pa'i rgyud las dgar bas
NK078(tshu)001:3313: gcig shos te mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ru nges pa
NK078(tshu)001:3314: ni / yin no // bzhi pa lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3316: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3318: de ltar rgyu rkyen dang ldan pa'i shes rab kyis spyan gyis lta ba 'tshol ba'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:3319: lta ba gtan la phab pa'i gtan tshigas rnams kyis
NK078(tshu)001:3320: gzhal bya gzhig cing rmal bar byas te gtan la
NK078(tshu)001:3321: dbabs pa dang / don nor ba'i lta ba ngan
NK078(tshu)001:3322: pa rnams rang rang gi so sor rtog pa'i shes
NK078(tshu)001:3323: rab kyis theg 'og phyogs re'i lta ngan gyi dmigsa
NK078(tshu)001:3324: ngos bzung zhing bsal nas gol sgrib kyi gdar sha
NK078(tshu)001:3325: bcad de gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3326: gnas lugs ma nor pa'i don ma h+aa yo ga
NK078(tshu)001:3327: 'di nyid kyi grub mtha' dmigas kyis phye nas dang
NK078(tshu)001:3328: du blang zhing gtan la dbab par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3329: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum ste
NK078(tshu)001:3330: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste rtogs par bya
NK078(tshu)001:3331: ba dang / gol sgrib kyi gdar sha bcad de don gyi dmigs bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3332: don ma nor bar dmigs nas grub mtha' blang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3335: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3337: gtan tshigs kyis brtag cing gzhal bar bya ba'i gzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3338: gzhal byed gtan tshigsa kyis gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3339: nges gtan la phebs pa'i grub pa'i don lta ba de grub mtha'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3340: de ltar rnam pa gsum po de gong gi mdor
NK078(tshu)001:3341: bstan la gsum yod pa'i snga ma gtan tshigs rnams
NK078(tshu)001:3342: kyis rmal bar bya ba'i yan lag rgyas par bshad
NK078(tshu)001:3343: pa 'byung ba'i gzhi ru lus mdor bstan du bzhag
NK078(tshu)001:3344: pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3346: dang po sngon byung dngos lnga'i gzhal bya gtan tshigs
NK078(tshu)001:3347: grub mtha' de kho na nyid 'jal byed dang bcas
NK078(tshu)001:3349: gzhi don phyin ci ma log par yang dag par
NK078(tshu)001:3350: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sgrib pa sangs shing ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:3351: rgyas pa'i rang byung gi ston pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:3352: chos sku longs sku sprul sku mngon byang rdo rje'i
NK078(tshu)001:3353: sku dang lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i drug pa spyi'i
NK078(tshu)001:3354: gzugs can des 'dul ba'i 'khor lhun grub rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:3355: mthar phyin pa rnams la bstan pa drug pa'i don
NK078(tshu)001:3356: gyi gsungs dang / dgongs pa brda'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3359: rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung dang lnga po lhun
NK078(tshu)001:3360: grub tu brda' sprad nas bstan pa'i dus su gzhal
NK078(tshu)001:3361: bya sems nyid gsung lnga lhun grub de kho na
NK078(tshu)001:3362: nyid kyi don gtan tshigs kyis gsung lnga lhun grub
NK078(tshu)001:3363: kyi don de nyid gtan la 'bebsa shing brda 'phrod
NK078(tshu)001:3364: de / gtan la 'beb pa'i grub mtha' yang gsung
NK078(tshu)001:3365: lnga lhun grub de nyid dang 'jal bar byed cing
NK078(tshu)001:3366: de / rdzogs pa'o // des na gsang sngags bla med kyi lugs la /
NK078(tshu)001:3367: sangs rgyas dngos ni rigs lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba spyi'i gzugs can des /
NK078(tshu)001:3368: 'khor dngos ni lhan cig pa'i 'khor mthar lam pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3369: theg 'og gyi rgyal ba rgya mtsho la /
NK078(tshu)001:3370: gsung dngos ni bstan pa gsung lnga lhun grub tu brda' sprod cing sangs rgyas pa'i dus la bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3372: sku yis phye ba'i 'khor rnams la //
NK078(tshu)001:3373: so sor bstan pa'i dus snang yang //
NK078(tshu)001:3374: lhan cig pa la dus gcig snang //
NK078(tshu)001:3376: gsung lnga'i tshul gyis dus gcig snang //
NK078(tshu)001:3379: thun mongs mthar byas pa'i tshe //
NK078(tshu)001:3380: yang dag sku gsung thugs bco lngas //
NK078(tshu)001:3381: byin rlabs 'tshams par mos snang bas //
NK078(tshu)001:3383: tha ma'i tshe na gsung lnga yis //
NK078(tshu)001:3384: dngos ston sngon byung lam zhes bya //
NK078(tshu)001:3386: de dang mthun par spar khab le'u drug pa las de bzhin du gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3387: gnyis pa dngos lnga de nyid rjes su 'jug tshul tshig gi gazhi'am khung byas tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3389: bden mthong chen po sangs rgyas kyi sa de nyid kyi don dngos lnga yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:3390: dngos lnga de nyid phyogs re'i tshul dang mthun par rtogs tshul gyi gtan tshigas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3391: dngos dang tshul gyi don tshig gis brjod pas ngo
NK078(tshu)001:3392: sprod pa ni tshig gis gtan tshigs rnams dngos lnga'i
NK078(tshu)001:3393: gtan tshigs kyis mtshon nas rjes su 'jug tshul tshig
NK078(tshu)001:3394: gi gtan tshigs kyi 'byung ba'i gazhi'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3395: gsum pa dngos lnga de nyid rjes su 'jug tshul
NK078(tshu)001:3396: tshig gi sgo nas gtan la phab dgos par gdams
NK078(tshu)001:3398: mthar lam lhan cig pa'i 'khor de la sngon byung
NK078(tshu)001:3399: gi bstan pa gsung lnga lhun grub kyis don gzhal
NK078(tshu)001:3400: bya gtan tshigs grub mtha'i don rnams dngos kyi sku
NK078(tshu)001:3402: gsung lnga lhun grub de yis don dngos su brda
NK078(tshu)001:3403: sprod pa'i rgyal ba dgongs brgyud sngon byung du sangs
NK078(tshu)001:3404: rgyas pa / de'i rjes su mthun par 'jug pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:3405: tshul sgo tshig gi sgo nas dngos lnga'i don gtan
NK078(tshu)001:3406: la phab nas bstan pa la'ang dper na gser yin
NK078(tshu)001:3408: g.ya' yod med brdar ba'i sa gser la gser du rtogs pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:3409: dngosa lnga'i don de nyid rjes su 'jug tshul tshig
NK078(tshu)001:3410: gi sgo nas legsa par brtags te gtan la dbab
NK078(tshu)001:3411: par bya'o // bzhi pa tshul tshig gi sgo nas gtan la phab tshul dngos de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3412: gzhal bya dang gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3413: des gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3414: dang po gzhal bya brtag bzhi bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3415: gzhal bya brtan gzhi ngos bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3416: de la rtsod pa'i skyon spyang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3419: dang po brtag pa'i gzhi ma bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3421: sngon byung dngos lnga'i don de yang rjes 'jug tshul
NK078(tshu)001:3422: tshig gis gtan tshigs rnams kyis yongas su brtag cing
NK078(tshu)001:3423: dpyad par bya ba'i gzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3424: de la lus la mig gi dbang po la sogs pa'i dbang po drug gi rten la /
NK078(tshu)001:3425: gzugs la sogs pa'i yul drug tu mig gis gzugs
NK078(tshu)001:3426: snang la sogs pa'i rnam shes drug dang bco brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:3428: de ltar yul dang dbang po rnam shes rnams sems
NK078(tshu)001:3429: nyid rang snang ma gtogs pa de rnams rang rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:3430: can du grub nas yoda pa ni ma yina te
NK078(tshu)001:3431: zhes dam bca' gtan tshigs ci phyir na rnal ma
NK078(tshu)001:3432: don gyi kun gzhi'i rnam para 'gags pa med par
NK078(tshu)001:3433: rang 'char ba'i shes pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:3434: de nyid phyi nang yul dang shes pa'i dngosa po
NK078(tshu)001:3435: sna tshagas su ma 'gags par rang snang ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:3436: pa'i phyir rang snang de nyid ngo ma shes pa
NK078(tshu)001:3437: las 'khor ba ngan zhen gyi snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3438: mya ngan las 'das pa'i dngos po bzang zhen gyi
NK078(tshu)001:3439: snang ba dang gnyis la gtan tshigs kyis brtag cing
NK078(tshu)001:3440: dpyod par bya'o // de yang 'khor ba ni snod
NK078(tshu)001:3441: 'byung ba yul dang bcas pa phyi'i snang ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:3442: dpyod par bya'o // / phung khams skye mched dang bcas pa nang gi snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3443: 'das pa ni thog pa mtho dman sna tshogs su snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3444: de yang 'das pa la zhen pas brtag pa spyi'i mtshan nyid la gzhal lam /
NK078(tshu)001:3445: 'das par snang ba rang gi mtshan nyid la gzhal /
NK078(tshu)001:3446: dang po la gzhal te zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3447: rang gi sems la 'das par 'dzin pa'i zhen blo la gzhal lam snyam na /
NK078(tshu)001:3448: 'das par 'dzin pa'i zhen pa ni blos bkod pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:3449: zhen pa 'khor ba'i chos yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:3450: de gzhal bas 'das par gzhal bar mi rigs te /
NK078(tshu)001:3452: blo la mya ngan 'das zhen pa //
NK078(tshu)001:3453: de nyid 'das par rung ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:3455: gnyis pa rang gi mtshan nyid la gzhal na /
NK078(tshu)001:3456: don de las dang po ba'i blo'i spyod yul du
NK078(tshu)001:3457: ma gyur cig /shin tu lkog tu gyur ba ste
NK078(tshu)001:3458: / rmig gi rnam par shes pas sgra thos mi myong la /
NK078(tshu)001:3459: gal te myong na 'das par gzhal ba ha cang thal drag par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:3462: 'das pa'i spyod yul ma gyur phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:3463: brtag pa'i yul du ci ltar rigs //
NK078(tshu)001:3464: gal te 'das pa'i snang ba la //
NK078(tshu)001:3465: gzhal na dang po lkog tu 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:3467: gnyis pa 'khor ba la gzhal na'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:3468: 'khor bar snang ba rang gi mtshan nyid la gzhal lam /
NK078(tshu)001:3469: zhen pas brtag pa spyi'i mtshan nyid la gzhal /
NK078(tshu)001:3470: dang po ltar na de'i ngo bo rig pa rang snang yin pas so skye'i yul ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:3471: gal lte brtags na grub mtha' yin pa'i phyir gzhal bar mi rigs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3473: snang ba rang gi mtshan nyid ni //
NK078(tshu)001:3474: gzhal bya min te rig snang phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:3475: gzhal bar rigs min skye bo yis //
NK078(tshu)001:3476: yul min grub pa'i mtha' ltar snang //
NK078(tshu)001:3478: gnyis pa spyi'i mtshan nyid la gzhal na /
NK078(tshu)001:3483: yul can blo 'khrul ba grub pa dus mnyam ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3484: 'das pa'i phyir gzhal bar mi rung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3486: brtag pa gang la dpyod zhe na //
NK078(tshu)001:3487: brtag dpyad gzhi ru rigs ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:3489: gnyis pa shes pa la gzhal na /
NK078(tshu)001:3490: shes pa skad cig rkyang 'gros yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:3491: skad cig snga ma de ni 'das pas gzhal du mi btub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3492: khyim bya shi bas skad 'byin mi nus pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3493: phyi ma ni ma skyes pa'i phyir gzhal bar mi rung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3494: sang phod kyi ston thog gis da lo'i sa bon mi'agruba pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3496: 'on te rang la nang du yang //
NK078(tshu)001:3497: lta ste dpyod gzhi de nyid zhi //
NK078(tshu)001:3498: log rtog spros pas skad cig las //
NK078(tshu)001:3500: de la brten pas brtags mi rigs //
NK078(tshu)001:3502: da ltar gyi skad cig ni rang bzhin gcig tu mi gnas te /
NK078(tshu)001:3503: mi brtan pas yid so sor rtog pa'i shes rab tu gnas gyur tsam na /
NK078(tshu)001:3504: zhen pa 'gags pas yul med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3505: dper na glog 'gyur ba'i gzhi la mun pa med pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3507: da ltar skad cig mi brtan pa //
NK078(tshu)001:3508: so sor rtog pa gnas gyur na //
NK078(tshu)001:3509: zhen 'gag rang la brtag mi rigs //
NK078(tshu)001:3511: 'o na gang la gzhal zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3512: lam pa'i blo la 'khor ba ngan pa'i dngos por snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3513: 'das pa bzang por zhen pa'i snang ba gnyis la brtag cing gzhal bar bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3514: dper na rgyal bu 'bangs su 'khyams pa'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:3516: yin tshul rgyal bur rtogs pa bzhin yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:3518: nges par bzhag pa'i gzhal bya ni //
NK078(tshu)001:3520: rang gi mtshan nyid mi 'dod de //
NK078(tshu)001:3521: de ltar nang nas zhen pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:3522: phyir rol med las yod ltar snang //
NK078(tshu)001:3523: zhen dang lta ba gnyis la brten //
NK078(tshu)001:3525: gnyis pa de las gzhan nas brtag dpyad byed lugs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3527: brtag lugs la snod 'jig pa la bcud 'jig pa
NK078(tshu)001:3528: brtan pas 'jig rten 'di na ci yod pa'i dngos
NK078(tshu)001:3529: po ka ba la sogs ming tha dad pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:3530: / dngos po dngos med kyi matshana mar 'adzana pa'i yul tha dad rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3531: de ma yin la der 'dzin gyi log rtog dug
NK078(tshu)001:3532: lnga la sogs pa sa so' rang gi mtshan nyid
NK078(tshu)001:3533: zhe sdang sems 'khrug pa la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3534: spyi'i mtshan nyid mi rtag /sdug bsngal /
NK078(tshu)001:3536: bdag med la sogs pa rang spyi'i mtshan nyid rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:3537: shes bya la ci ltar gansa pa ltar brtag cing dpyad par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3538: gsum pa brtag dpyad byas pas don rig tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3540: 'khor ba dang 'das pa'i dngos po gnyis su zhen
NK078(tshu)001:3541: pa'i dngos po dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:3542: su gtogs pa thams cad kun da ltar gyi shes
NK078(tshu)001:3543: pa skad cig ma gcig la gong gi de kun
NK078(tshu)001:3544: rdzogsa pa'i phyir / de yang rgyas pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:3545: ma bcos lhun gyis skad cig ma //
NK078(tshu)001:3546: de yis ma zin gang yang med //
NK078(tshu)001:3547: ces pa 'das pa'i chos kun rdzogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3549: log rtog rgyan gyi skad cig ma //
NK078(tshu)001:3550: de yis ma byas gang yang med //
NK078(tshu)001:3551: ces pa 'khor ba'i chos kun rdzogs te /
NK078(tshu)001:3552: skad cig de nyid kyi dngos po'i gnas lugs kun
NK078(tshu)001:3553: rang snang du mthonga bas yanga dag pa'i don phyin
NK078(tshu)001:3554: ci ma log par rig pa bzhin du shes bya
NK078(tshu)001:3555: srid tshad kyi chos kun kyang gong gi da ltar
NK078(tshu)001:3556: du shesa shing chung bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3559: skad cig gcig la kun rdzogs phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:3560: de shes grol bas rnam kun mkhyen //
NK078(tshu)001:3561: de ltar gzung 'dzin ma grub phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:3565: gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid shes na chos thams cad kyi mdo dang rgyas pa shes par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3567: gnyis pa rtsod pa'i skyon spang tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3569: dang po the tshom gyi dogs pa gzugs ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3571: gzhal tshul de ltar du gzhal na /
NK078(tshu)001:3572: zhen yul kun brtagsa yul du byed pa'i zhen byed
NK078(tshu)001:3573: kyi yid kun brtag kyi shes pa de ni shes
NK078(tshu)001:3574: rab gsum gyi bar ma bsam byung gi so sor
NK078(tshu)001:3575: rtog pa'i shes rab tu gnas 'gyur ba'i skabs su
NK078(tshu)001:3576: phyi'i yul rnams yod pa ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:3577: dper na lus med na grib ma mi 'byung ba
NK078(tshu)001:3578: bzhina du gzhal bya yul med pasa 'jig rten 'di
NK078(tshu)001:3579: na ci yod pa rnams gzhal du mi btub bo
NK078(tshu)001:3580: // 'o na zhon byed kyi yid ranga nyid la gzhal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3581: sems skad cig ma rang gis rang la gzhal du mi btub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3582: dper na mdzub mo rang gi rtse la rang gis mi reg pa bzhin du ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3584: ji ltar ral gri rang gi so //
NK078(tshu)001:3585: ji ltar mdzub mo rang gi rtse //
NK078(tshu)001:3586: mi chod pa dang mi reg pa //
NK078(tshu)001:3587: de bzhin sems kyi sems mi mthong //
NK078(tshu)001:3589: yul dang yul can gnyis ka la gzhal du mi rung ba'i dogsa pa skyes pa'i skyon zug na /
NK078(tshu)001:3590: gnyis pa dogs pa bsal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3592: gzhal bya zhen snang rags pa thos bsam gyis dag kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:3593: zhen snang phra ba'i gnyen po lta ba rang mtshan du rtogs pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:3594: sgom byung gi shes rab rgyud la skyes pa med
NK078(tshu)001:3595: pas zhen pa dag pa min cing zhen snang phra
NK078(tshu)001:3596: ba de nyid / shes rab gsum gyi bar ma
NK078(tshu)001:3597: bsam byung so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis gzhal
NK078(tshu)001:3598: ba'i yul du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:3599: des na gzhal bya'i yul yod ces bya ba'i nges tshiga gam sgra don 'grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:3600: de la nye ston na re /
NK078(tshu)001:3601: bsam byung gi rtog dpyod byed pa'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:3602: bsam bya'i yul la sems byed kyis gzhal /
NK078(tshu)001:3603: re zhig par gnas su 'gyur yang /
NK078(tshu)001:3604: gtan du ba gnas su ma gyur pas de la gzhal gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3606: bsam byung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3610: dus gcig gam mi gcig /mi gcig na bsal bya dang sel byed du mi 'thad de /
NK078(tshu)001:3611: phyi nang gi snang mun dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3612: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes kyis sems can gyi sdug bsngal dang mi shes pa mi sel ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3615: nam gung gi mun pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3616: gcig na yul de grub na bsal bya 'khrul ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3617: ma grub na de la dpyod pa'i sel byed bsam byung 'khrul bar 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3618: ngo bo gcig na ral gri rang gis rang mi
NK078(tshu)001:3619: chod pa ltar sel byed du mi 'gyur la dus
NK078(tshu)001:3620: gcig na / rtog pa gnyis cig char 'jug par 'gyur bas so //
NK078(tshu)001:3622: zhen yul gcig la zhen snang tha dad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3623: blo'i rgyun gcig la 'dzin stangs kyi rtog pa bye ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3624: dus 'phrad nas sel ba med kyang blo rgyun gcig la /
NK078(tshu)001:3626: phyis bsam byung las byung ba'i lta ba nges par
NK078(tshu)001:3627: sgro 'dog gi rgyun skye bar mi nus pa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:3628: la kun brtags kyi zhen pa bsal zhing tha snyad
NK078(tshu)001:3630: lce ston bsgrub pa 'bum gyis gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3633: gzhal byed gtan tshigs kyis gzhal tsam na /
NK078(tshu)001:3634: skad cig ma'i snga logs zhen snang du yod pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:3635: phyi log so sor rtogs par gnas gyur nas gzhal zhing dpyod gsungs /
NK078(tshu)001:3637: dgongs pa dgod spang du bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3638: gtan la mi phebs pa'i dogs pa dgong cing spang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3639: dgos ched med pa'i dog pa dgod cing spang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3640: gzhal gyis mi lang ba'i dog pa dgod ci spang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3641: gzhal bya'i yul med pa'i dog pa dgod cing spang ba dang bzhi las /
NK078(tshu)001:3643: lung gra chad la nyal ba zur la bslang ba 'chad pa po'i gnyer yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:3644: len dkyus nas 'dug na brgal ba khung nas 'byung bar bshad /
NK078(tshu)001:3645: brgal ba dkyus nas 'dug na len khong nas phyung la bshad de /
NK078(tshu)001:3646: dper na rgya gar ba'i mi gcig bod du 'ong na /
NK078(tshu)001:3648: cha bram blangs pas mi phan pa rtogs pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:3649: chos nyid kyi don rtogs par 'dod pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:3650: 'khor 'das kyi zhen snang gtan la phabs pas mi phan par rtogs pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:3651: len dkyus kyi 'khor 'das kyis gzhal byar bstan pas gdab ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3653: grang ba chu yi bdag nyid dag /drod kyi rkyen dang bral ba yi //
NK078(tshu)001:3654: cha bram rdo rdzogs lta bur snang //
NK078(tshu)001:3655: de bzhin kun gzhi rnam shes kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:3656: rnam pa 'gyur nas gzugs su snang //
NK078(tshu)001:3658: chu de grang reg dang 'phrad pas cha bram snang ba de /
NK078(tshu)001:3659: tsha reg dang 'phrad pas chur 'gro ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:3660: kun gzhi'i bag chags kyis 'khor 'das su snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:3661: de gtan la phab pas kun gzhi'i chos nyid rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:3663: chu bram blang ba bas chur len pa sla ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:3664: gtan la phebs kyang chos nyid gtan la phebs pa sla bas /
NK078(tshu)001:3665: zhen snang pheb pa rang dgos med du dogs pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:3667: rang spyi gzhal byar bstan pas lan gdab ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3668: chab bram chur song bas de chu min du dog pa sel ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:3669: log rtog chos nyid ma yin pa'i rtog pa sel lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3670: gsum pa chab bram thams cad bzhu bas mi lang ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:3671: dgos pa 'dug kyang gzhal gyis mi lang ba ltar dgos pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:3673: skad cig mar gzhal byar bstan pas gdab ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3674: cha bram khu tshur tsam zhig bzhu bas /
NK078(tshu)001:3675: kun de ltar rtogs pa ltar ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3677: gzhal du lang yang gzhal bya'i yul med pas mi brtub par dogs pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:3678: brgal len gnyis ka dkyus su byung ste sngar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:3679: gnyis pa gtan tshigs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3680: dngos dang tshul mthun du rtogs pa tshul gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3681: dngos dang tshul gyi don tshig tu ngo sprod pa tshig gi gtan tshigs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3682: dang po brtag pa'i sgo nas tshul mthun du rtogs lugs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3686: gong du bshad pa de ltar dngos lnga'i don de
NK078(tshu)001:3687: nyid tshul drug gi sgo nas gtan la phab cing
NK078(tshu)001:3689: de yang 'khor 'das kyi dngos po de de la /
NK078(tshu)001:3690: 'khor 'das kyi chos de de' rang bzhina nam rang
NK078(tshu)001:3691: spyi'i mtshan nyid ji ltar gnas pa brtag par bya
NK078(tshu)001:3692: ba la brten nas tshul mthun du rtogs lugs ni
NK078(tshu)001:3693: 'di lta ste / gnyis pa tshul mthun rtogs tshul dngos de la drug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3695: dang po ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i gsung gi tshul rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3697: chos nyid kyi don rtogs pa dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK078(tshu)001:3698: 'byor pa bla mchog rnams ni 'khor gyi tshul yin
NK078(tshu)001:3699: la / phyi nang gi dngosa po sna tshogsa su
NK078(tshu)001:3700: snang ba 'di sems nyid rang snang bas gsang sngags
NK078(tshu)001:3701: kyi ngo bo de ston pa'i tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3702: de ltar gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de ni sgrog
NK078(tshu)001:3703: skur dang bral bas nges pa'i lung yin pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:3704: / dngos po mthong thos thams cad kyi chos tshul la ston pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:3706: tshig tu ma brjod kyang brjod pa dang 'dra bar
NK078(tshu)001:3707: chos nyid kyi don brda sprod par byed pas na
NK078(tshu)001:3708: go tshul lo // de dag ni ngo bo nyid
NK078(tshu)001:3709: kyi sku' bshad pa dang tshul mthun pa' phyir ma
NK078(tshu)001:3710: 'ongsa pa'i gang zag blo che ba rnams kyi don
NK078(tshu)001:3711: du chos nyid gtan la pheb pa'i gtan tshigs su
NK078(tshu)001:3712: go tshul lo // nges pa'o // gnyis pa chos sku'i gsung gi tshul skye med don gyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3715: chos sku'i tshul ni sa la gansa pa'i /
NK078(tshu)001:3716: byang chub sems dpa' de dang 'dra ba'i shes rab
NK078(tshu)001:3717: kyi mig dang ldan pa ni 'khor gyi tshul lo
NK078(tshu)001:3718: // ranga bzhin ngang ngam shugs kyis chos nyid skye
NK078(tshu)001:3719: ba med pa'i don rang gi rgyud la lhun gyis
NK078(tshu)001:3720: grub pa ni ston pa'i tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3721: so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis ma brtsal bar
NK078(tshu)001:3722: rang bzhin ngang gis skye med kyi don la snang
NK078(tshu)001:3723: zhing go bar byed pa yang chos kyi 'khor lo
NK078(tshu)001:3724: bskor tshul lo // skye med kyi don tshig tu
NK078(tshu)001:3725: brjod pa med pa de nyid brjod pa dang 'dra
NK078(tshu)001:3726: bar skye med go bar byed pa ni go tshul
NK078(tshu)001:3727: bskor tshul lo // lo // gsum pa longs skus gsung gi tshul dgongs pa brda'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3729: blo dang ldan pa'i lam pa ganga daga ni 'khor gyi tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3730: kha dog dang dbyibs la sogs pa'i gzugsa kyis brta
NK078(tshu)001:3731: dang rnal 'byor pa dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:3732: brda don gyis chos ston pa ni ston pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:3733: lo // mig gis gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3734: rna bas sgra thos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3735: dri ro reg bya la sogsa pa thams cad kyis kyang rang bzhin tshul gyi brda sprod de /
NK078(tshu)001:3736: dkar po nyes skyon dang bral ba la sogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3737: dapa'a bo bla mas dbang dang gdams ngag gnang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:3738: dus su phyag brkyang bskum la sogs pa lus ngag
NK078(tshu)001:3739: gi brda sna tshogs byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3740: bla ma'i dagngas pa mnyam par bzhag pa'i brda yis ngo sprod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3741: slob bu ranga gis ting nge 'dzina bsgom pa'i stobs
NK078(tshu)001:3742: kyis go barda sprod par byed pa ni chos 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:3744: bzhi pa mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i gsung gi tshul rig pa byin rlabs kyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3746: dpera na sa 'oga na gasra yod pa'i rlang ba
NK078(tshu)001:3747: bar snang la rang bzhin gyis 'od 'ong ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:3748: / me longa nyi ma la bzhag pa'i tshe dang
NK078(tshu)001:3749: rang bzhin gyis 'byung ba bzhin du 'khor 'das kyi
NK078(tshu)001:3750: chos kun kyang rang rig pa'i ye shes rang snang
NK078(tshu)001:3751: ba'i phyir rang bzhin ngang gis /
NK078(tshu)001:3752: rig pa'i drod 'byung ba ni ston pa dang 'khor ro //
NK078(tshu)001:3753: ched du ma btsal bar rang bzhin nganga gis brjod
NK078(tshu)001:3754: pa dang 'dra bar don snang ste brda sprod pa
NK078(tshu)001:3755: ni chos 'khor dang go tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3756: lnga pa rdo rje'i sku'i gsung gi tshul grags stong dbyer med kyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3758: 'khor 'das kyi chos kyi sgra skad kun kyang grags
NK078(tshu)001:3759: stong dbyer med brag ca'i sgra bzhin du gnas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:3760: phyir / sgra skad thams cad grags stong dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:3761: du rang bzhin gyis gnas pa de ka rdo rje'i
NK078(tshu)001:3762: sku'i gsungs dang tshul mthun pa ni ston pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:3763: phyir / 'khor ro // gdul bya blo rab 'ga'
NK078(tshu)001:3764: zhig gis sgra thos pa tsam nyid kyi dus de
NK078(tshu)001:3765: nyid du tshig don so sor ma brtag par sems
NK078(tshu)001:3766: nyid dbyer med kyi don go brda mjal bar byed
NK078(tshu)001:3767: pa ni chos 'khor dang go tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3768: drug pa sprul sku'i gsung gi tshul brjod pa tshig gi gtan tshigs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3770: sprul sku'i tshig gi gsungs dbyangs ni 'jig rten gyi
NK078(tshu)001:3771: mes po tshangs pa'i ngag gis 'gro ba so so'i
NK078(tshu)001:3772: skad du don brda sprod pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:3773: sprul sku'ang de lta bu'i gsungs kyis mos par spyod
NK078(tshu)001:3774: pa'i sa pa tshogs sbyor ba la tshig gi sgo
NK078(tshu)001:3775: nas dgrol ba bzhin du rjes 'jug tu bla mas
NK078(tshu)001:3776: tshig tu ngo sprod brjod pa yis /
NK078(tshu)001:3777: don brda sprod nas yongs su dgrol bar byed pa
NK078(tshu)001:3778: ni ston 'khor chos gsum lhun gyis grub tshul lo
NK078(tshu)001:3779: // 'o na gsang ba'i sku'i tshul ma byung zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3780: shes rab kyi dbang po yang rab kyis thos bsam
NK078(tshu)001:3781: gyi thog nas lta ba cig char du rtogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:3782: yin pas / rtogs thabs la thabs lam bsgom cing spyod mi dgos par bshad pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:3783: gsum pa tshig gi gtan tshigs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3785: dang po tshig gis mtshon pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3787: spyir gang zag las dang po ba'i shes rgyud la blo'i bye brag tha dad yod pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:3788: blo che na thos bsam la brten nas tshul drug
NK078(tshu)001:3789: gang mosa kyi sgo nas grol ba yoda pa gong
NK078(tshu)001:3790: du bstan mod kyang blo chung ba rnams des mi
NK078(tshu)001:3791: grol bar tshig gi gtan tshigs bstan pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:3794: sgom pa'i shes rab gsum gyis gnas lugs kyi don
NK078(tshu)001:3795: la blo mnyam par sbyor ba'i thabs kyis 'bras bus
NK078(tshu)001:3796: rang byung gi ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor mngon sum
NK078(tshu)001:3797: du gsal bas 'khor 'das kyi chos kun la ngam
NK078(tshu)001:3798: zhing ngo mtshar ba'i 'bras bu 'grub par byed pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:3799: phyir / don dam chos nyid cir yang mi dmigsa
NK078(tshu)001:3800: pa'i ngang las kun rdzob tu tshig dang yi ger
NK078(tshu)001:3801: blos dmigsa pa'i cho 'phrul brjod pa tshig gi sgo
NK078(tshu)001:3802: nas don chos nyid mtshon cing go nus par bya'
NK078(tshu)001:3803: //gnyis pa dngos dang tshul gyi rjes su tshig gis
NK078(tshu)001:3806: sku lnga lhun grub las gsung lnga dngos su thos
NK078(tshu)001:3807: pa dngos lnga dang de dang tshul mthun du rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:3809: dngos tshul gnyis po de'i rjes su mthun par gdul
NK078(tshu)001:3810: bya blo chung ba rnams tshig lnga'i gtan tshigsa kyis
NK078(tshu)001:3811: mtshon cing gtan la dbab par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3812: gsum pa tshig gi gtan tshigs dngos de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3813: rgyal ba sku bdun gyi dgongs pa tshig tu ngo sprod nas gtan la dbab tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3814: de rnams kyi don mdor bsdus nas go tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:3817: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3819: yul sems ngo ba nyid ranga snang du ston pa ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i gsung gi tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3820: skye med rang snang du ston pa chos sku'i tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3821: ldem dgongs sam brda yis chos nyid mtshon pa longs sku'i tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3822: gang zag dag lam la dkri zhing drang ba'i thabs
NK078(tshu)001:3823: su brgyud tshig tu ston pa sprul sku'i tshig dang
NK078(tshu)001:3824: / 'dod pa rang rkyen du ston pa gsang ba sku'i tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3825: chos thams cad dbyer med ston pa rdo rje'i sku'i tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3826: chos thams cad rang rig mngon gsal du ston pa
NK078(tshu)001:3827: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i tshig gis don mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:3828: pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la bdun te /
NK078(tshu)001:3830: dang po ngo bo nyid kyi gsung mtshon pa rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyi tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3832: 'khor 'das phyi nang gi chos thamsa cad sems nyid
NK078(tshu)001:3833: gsang sngagsa kyi ngo ba nyid rang mtshon pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:3834: / de yang yod med la sogs pa'i mtha'a dang
NK078(tshu)001:3835: de la ltos pa'i dbus kyang grub pa meda de
NK078(tshu)001:3836: / / gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid du
NK078(tshu)001:3837: snang stong dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du
NK078(tshu)001:3838: gnas pa la dbyer med kyi ye shes yin kyang
NK078(tshu)001:3839: / / / ye shes lnga ru dbye ba ni
NK078(tshu)001:3840: rtog tshogs ye shes su rtogsa par 'dod pa'i don
NK078(tshu)001:3841: / / / bya ba'i phyir / gnyis med kyi
NK078(tshu)001:3842: ye shes nyid phyogsa bzhi dang dbus su gnas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:3843: sgo nas ye shes lngar rtogs par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3844: de bzhin du kha dog la sogs pa'i chos kun
NK078(tshu)001:3845: la sems nyid ye shes rang snang gi ngo bos
NK078(tshu)001:3846: chos ston pas de ltar sbyor bar shes par gyis
NK078(tshu)001:3848: gnyis pa chos sku'i gsung mtshon pa skye med don gyi tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3850: sprul pa'i gsung ltar yi ge 'dus pa'i ming dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3851: de 'dus pa'i tshig dang de las brjod pa'i sgra'i
NK078(tshu)001:3852: tha snyad spangsa pa'i phyir tshig tu brjod pa med
NK078(tshu)001:3853: pa'i skye med kyi ngang du gnas pa ni mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:3854: bya'i don no // de mtshon byed tshig gi gsung
NK078(tshu)001:3855: nyid rang bzhin phyogs gcig tu grub pa med par
NK078(tshu)001:3856: mtshon pa'i chos rnams ma lus pa thamsa cad ye
NK078(tshu)001:3857: gdod ma nas skye med du dag pas /
NK078(tshu)001:3858: chos thamsa cad rnam par mi rtog pa'i thugs stong
NK078(tshu)001:3859: pa nyid kyi ye shes su gyur zin pas na
NK078(tshu)001:3860: / brjod pa'i sgra dang mtshon pa'i tshig la don ji lta ba bzhin gnas pa min no //
NK078(tshu)001:3861: gsum pa mngon byang gi sku'i gsung mtshon pa rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3863: brtag bya mya ngan las 'das pa dang ma 'das
NK078(tshu)001:3864: pa 'khor ba'i chos ltar snang ba thams cad kun
NK078(tshu)001:3865: / brtag byed yang dag par mngon sum du rtogs pa'i shes pas rab tu brtagsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:3867: dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad don dam spyod yul dang bral bas /
NK078(tshu)001:3868: ranga bzhin phyogs gcig tu grub pa meda pa ni chos dbyings ye shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:3869: de la phyogs med du me long la gzugs brnyan
NK078(tshu)001:3870: shar ba ltar cir yang snang ba ni me long
NK078(tshu)001:3872: de ltar snang bdo ba'i dus de nyid na mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:3873: pa nyid kyi dbyings nyid yin te mnyam nyid ye
NK078(tshu)001:3874: shes so // mtshon byed kyi tshig gis gnyis med
NK078(tshu)001:3875: kyi don de ltar rtogs par byed pa'i ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:3876: ni dus gsum 'khor 'das kyi chos kun la ye
NK078(tshu)001:3877: shes des dbang bsgyur bas na rang dabnga can ni
NK078(tshu)001:3878: bya ba lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:3879: 'khor 'das kyi chos thamsa cad tshig gi sgras mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:3880: nas gsal ba ltar don ma 'dres par so sor
NK078(tshu)001:3881: rtog par gnas pa ni sor rtogs ye shes so
NK078(tshu)001:3882: // de ltar ye shes su gnas pa 'di ni
NK078(tshu)001:3883: rang byung gi ye shes lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:3885: bzhi pa rdo rje'i gsung mtshon pa grags stong dbyer med kyi tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3887: 'khor 'das snang grags kyi chos rnams kyi nang tshan blos bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3888: snang ba sna tshogs sems nyid du gcig pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:3889: mtha' dang dbus gnyis su med pa'i 'gro 'ong med
NK078(tshu)001:3890: par 'khor 'das kun la thams cad du khyab la
NK078(tshu)001:3891: / de ltar khyab pa'i dus na'ang khyab bya dang khyab byed gnyis tha dad med de /
NK078(tshu)001:3892: dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje'i skus gsung ni mtshon bya don gyi ngo bo'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3893: 'byung ba dang skye 'gro'i sgra skad mi mthun pa sna tshogsa grag pa yanga /
NK078(tshu)001:3894: sgra nyid ngo bo snang stong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3895: don dam par dngosa pora grub pa meda pa lasa
NK078(tshu)001:3896: kun rdzob tu dngosa pa'i sgra sna tshogs su ma
NK078(tshu)001:3898: dpe ji ltar zhe na pi wa de nyid skyes bu'i lag tu thogsa nas brdungs na /
NK078(tshu)001:3899: sgra skad kyi rnam pa ni mi mthun pa'i bye brag sna tshogsa par 'byung bar 'gyur yang /
NK078(tshu)001:3900: sgra de rgyud dang khog pa las byung ba'i dngos
NK078(tshu)001:3901: po grub pa med da grags stong gnyis med de
NK078(tshu)001:3903: lnga pa longs sku'i gsung mtshon pa ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3905: 'di ni dngos don dpe ru blang pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:3906: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub semsa dpa' dang smin pa rgya mtsho'i 'khor rnams la /
NK078(tshu)001:3907: sku gong ma de bzhin du 'dir longs sku yang
NK078(tshu)001:3908: gsung mchog /sprul sku ltar tshig tu mi smra ste
NK078(tshu)001:3909: / 'o na des chos ji ltar ston zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3910: sku'i sgo nas chos rnams 'khor gyi blo la 'ajala bar ston te /
NK078(tshu)001:3911: dper na me long gi nang du gzugs brnyan shar bas /
NK078(tshu)001:3912: byad kyi dri ma rig pa bzhina du ston pa
NK078(tshu)001:3913: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la bltas pas 'khor rang
NK078(tshu)001:3914: la shes sgrib snang ba de rig go //
NK078(tshu)001:3915: drug pa sprul sku'i gsung mtshon pa bkri drang brgyud pa'i tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3917: de yang gdul bya dag lam la bkri shing drang
NK078(tshu)001:3918: ba'i don du don gzhan la dgongs nas tsheg gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:3921: rnam par dkar ba'i chosa rnams lhag ma ma lus pa thamsa cada kun /
NK078(tshu)001:3922: ston pa sprul sku'i gsung mos pa spyod pa'i gdul
NK078(tshu)001:3923: bya la btags pa'i minga dang brjod pa'i tshaga tu
NK078(tshu)001:3924: brtag nas bkri drang brgyud pa'i tshig ston pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3925: chos ji snyed pa manga po'i dona sgra dang tshig tu brjod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:3926: grags stong dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung la tha dad
NK078(tshu)001:3927: du spros pa rdul tsam yang meda pa ni mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:3928: bya'i don no // mtshon par byed pa'i tshig spros
NK078(tshu)001:3929: pa med pa de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos par
NK078(tshu)001:3930: gsung sna tshogs su snang la /
NK078(tshu)001:3931: gdul bya kun gyi blo la chos nyid kyi don
NK078(tshu)001:3932: brda 'ajala zhing gsal bar byed pas ye shes kyi
NK078(tshu)001:3933: gsung yin la gsung dus sgra dang ming tshig kun
NK078(tshu)001:3935: sgra smras kyang nyes pa med pa'i dpe ni sgra
NK078(tshu)001:3936: thams cad mtha'i skyon gyis ma gos pa pad+ma 'dam
NK078(tshu)001:3937: skyon gyis chagsa shing gos pa med pa lta bu'o
NK078(tshu)001:3938: // bdun pa gsang ba'i sku'i gsung mtshon pa 'dod pa rang rkyen gyi tshig go //
NK078(tshu)001:3940: de yang 'dod pa rang rkyen gyi tshig ni 'dod
NK078(tshu)001:3941: chags can bde ba nyid lam du ston pa'i tshig
NK078(tshu)001:3942: la bya'o // de ni yab yum gyi dbang po
NK078(tshu)001:3943: bol la ka ko la rnam pa gnyis phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:3944: bzhis bsrubs pa yis yum gyi mkha' la yab yum
NK078(tshu)001:3945: gyi thig le nyi zla byang sems gnyis dus gcig
NK078(tshu)001:3946: tu 'dzom pa'i dus la bde stong gi ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:3947: la bya'o // shar ba ni / dper na mi
NK078(tshu)001:3948: 'jigsa pa'i seng ges gcan gzan gzhan rnams zil gyis
NK078(tshu)001:3949: gnon pa'i tshul du chags rtog zil gyis manna cing
NK078(tshu)001:3950: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi bde ba mthong
NK078(tshu)001:3951: bar byed pa'i rgyu mtshan de'i phyir dngos po lhan
NK078(tshu)001:3952: cig skyes pa'i ye shes la gtan tshigsa su 'jog
NK078(tshu)001:3954: rtog pa zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3955: don mthong bar byed pa'i lasa la gtan tshigs su brjod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3956: de ltar sku lnga'am bdun gyi tshig tu gsung ba mi 'thad de /
NK078(tshu)001:3957: sprul sku min pas tshig tu ma gsung pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:3958: sku bdun pos dngos su ma gsungs kyang tshig bdun
NK078(tshu)001:3959: po 'di sku bdun kun gyi dgongs pa'i don mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:3960: pa dang chos mthun pas sku bdun gyi tshig tu
NK078(tshu)001:3962: sku bdun gyis dngos su gsungs pa'i tshig tu mi 'dod do ce'o /
NK078(tshu)001:3963: 'on kyang sku bdun gyis tshig tu ma gsungs kyang
NK078(tshu)001:3964: sprul skus sku drug gi gsungs tshig tu gsungs pas
NK078(tshu)001:3965: / sdud pa pos yi ger bkod pa ni tshig gi gsung yin no gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3966: gnyis pa mdor bsdus nas go tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3968: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3970: de ltar phye na tshig bdun yod mod kyang bsdu na 'og nas 'byung ba'i go tshul gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:3971: sku bzhi dang rjes su mthun par mi dpyod pas go ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3972: sprul sku gcig dang rjes su mthun par dpyod pa'i go ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3973: rnam pa gnyis kyi tshul gyis don la dpyod par byed pa'nga /
NK078(tshu)001:3974: shes rab kyi dbang po che chung gnyis dang mthun par sbyar ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:3976: gnas lugs 'khor 'das dbyer med la rang bzhin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:3977: dbang po rnon pos gnyis med du gtan la phab
NK078(tshu)001:3978: pa dang / gzhal bya 'khor 'das gnyis la sbyongs
NK078(tshu)001:3979: pa'i rnon pos so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis
NK078(tshu)001:3982: tshig gis don gcig ston tsam na car phog tu ston pa dpyad du med pa'i go ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3983: brgyud nas ston pa dpyad du yod pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3984: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa /
NK078(tshu)001:3986: sku bzhi dang rjes su mthun par dpyad du med ba'i go ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3987: sprul sku dang rjes su mthun par dpyad pas go ba'i gtan tshigs so //
NK078(tshu)001:3989: dpyad du med pa'i go ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3990: rtogs dpyod kyi gtan la mi pheb par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:3991: ma dpyad par go ba'i dpe don dang go ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:3992: don gyi ngo bo la bcing grol dang bral bar
NK078(tshu)001:3993: bstan pa dang / de so sor rtogs pa'i shes
NK078(tshu)001:3994: rab kyi go ba mchog yin par bstan pa nges
NK078(tshu)001:3998: dang po gzhal bya chos kun snying po byang chub yin pas dpyad du med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4000: mdor bstan la gnyis yod pas de la snga ma dpyad du med pas go bar bya ba'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:4001: 'gro drug gi semsa can ma lus pa thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:4002: kun ye gdong ma nas byang chub snying po'i ngo
NK078(tshu)001:4004: de'i phyir chos nyid la dpyad par bya ba'i yul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4005: dpyod par byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:4006: gnyis pa dpyad du med pa'i go ba'i rgyu mtshan khung dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4008: sku bzhi'i gsung ltar skabs 'dir tshig dang yi ges kyang mi mtshon te /
NK078(tshu)001:4009: ci'i phyir zhe na yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK078(tshu)001:4010: rgyas kyis kyang chos nyid 'di kho na'o zhes tshig
NK078(tshu)001:4011: dang yi ges bstan par dka' ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4013: rgyal ba sku bzhi'i sras po 'khor bzhi la bstan
NK078(tshu)001:4014: pa tshig tu cang mi gsung pa dang tshig tu
NK078(tshu)001:4015: ma gsung pa nyid kyang don rgya cher brda mjal
NK078(tshu)001:4016: nas bshad kyang / ston pas tshig tu 'chad pa dang 'khor gyi nyan pa gnyis ka med do //
NK078(tshu)001:4017: gnyis pa rtog dpyod kyis gtan la mi phebs par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4019: yin min gyi dpyod pa zhugsa na rang las gzhan du rtog pa'i gzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:4020: de ltar rtog pa zhugsa na yul du dmigsa pa'i rten yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4021: yul du dmigsa pa zhugsa na bdag tu 'dzin pa'i gzungs dus 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:4022: de ltar gzung 'dzina gyi mdud pas zin pa'i phyir na 'khor ba las grol bar mi 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:4023: mi grol ba'i skyon yod do 'o na gong du bsam pa'i tshe na rtog dpyod pa /
NK078(tshu)001:4024: gnyis po 'di dag shes pa'i rgyu /
NK078(tshu)001:4025: zhes rtog dpyod lta ba'i rgyur bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4026: 'dir skyon du brjod pa gnyis 'gal lam zhe na ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4027: 'dir ni shes bya'i gshis kyi dbang btsan du blo
NK078(tshu)001:4028: yang rab mchog tu gyur pa 'ga' zhig gis don
NK078(tshu)001:4029: lhangs kyi go ba'i go ba'i ngos nas bzhag pa
NK078(tshu)001:4030: yin la / gong ma ni blo chung ba las
NK078(tshu)001:4031: dang po pas thos bsam gyi lta ba la tshol
NK078(tshu)001:4033: rtog dpyod la phra rags sam /
NK078(tshu)001:4034: yun ring thung yod pas skyon med do gsung /
NK078(tshu)001:4035: gsum pa ma dpyad par go ba'i dpe don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4037: rtog dpyod gnyis kyis mi grol ba de bas na
NK078(tshu)001:4038: dper na gser blta ba la gser rang ston dgos
NK078(tshu)001:4039: pa bzhina du / chos kun rig pa bdag nyid
NK078(tshu)001:4040: chen po rang yin pa'i phyir de ltar dpyad par
NK078(tshu)001:4041: bya ba'i yul dang dpyod par byed pa'i shes pa
NK078(tshu)001:4043: tshig la rtog pa ste rtsing ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4044: don la dpyod pa ste zhib pas 'di ltar yin
NK078(tshu)001:4045: snyams pa'i dmigs 'dzin gyi sgo nas lta ba mi
NK078(tshu)001:4046: tshol bar / rgyal ba sku bdun gyi dgongs pa
NK078(tshu)001:4047: de tshig tu brjod pa nyid kyi rgyal ba ste
NK078(tshu)001:4048: sku bdun de nyid kyi don mathanga zhig go dgos
NK078(tshu)001:4049: tshol bar / so // bzhi pa go ba'i don
NK078(tshu)001:4050: gyi ngo bo bcing grol dang bral bar bstan pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:4052: 'ching byed kyi mkhan po dgra lta bu sus kyang ma bcingas shing /
NK078(tshu)001:4053: bcing bar byed pa'i dngos po zhags pa lta bu med de /
NK078(tshu)001:4054: bcing bar bya ba'i yul dgra btson lta bu'ang yod pa ma yina te /
NK078(tshu)001:4055: de ltar bcingsa pa ltar snang ba'i dus na bdag 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4056: sems can dang sdug bsngal gyi dngos po rnams sems
NK078(tshu)001:4057: nyid rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi gshis la ma grub
NK078(tshu)001:4058: pas bcing pa med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4059: rnam para grol ba po yang med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:4060: 'khor ba spangs nas 'das pa'i sar rgyud grol yanga
NK078(tshu)001:4061: mi 'doda pas bcingsa pa dang ngang gis bral ba
NK078(tshu)001:4062: yin no // de yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK078(tshu)001:4063: bcing bya bcing byed bcing ba pos //
NK078(tshu)001:4064: bdag 'dzin sems can sdug bsdal dngos //
NK078(tshu)001:4065: thams cad sems kyi ngo bo'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:4066: bdag 'dzin zhes bya'i ming yang med //
NK078(tshu)001:4067: des na gnyis po med pas na //
NK078(tshu)001:4068: grol bar mi 'dod bcing dang bral //
NK078(tshu)001:4070: lnga pa de so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis
NK078(tshu)001:4071: go ba mchog yin pa'i nges tshig dang bcas pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:4073: so sora rtog pa'i shes rab kyis 'khor 'das kyi
NK078(tshu)001:4074: dngos po gang la yang gzhal bya'i yul du byas
NK078(tshu)001:4075: nas rtog dpyod byas pa med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:4076: 'khor 'das la sogs pa'i so sor snang ba'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:4077: kun gyi de kho nyid phyin ci ma log par
NK078(tshu)001:4078: rtogsa pa'i phyir / so sora rtog pa'i shes rab
NK078(tshu)001:4079: kyi nang nas mchog gam phul du phyin pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:4080: rtogsa pa'i phyir / te / so sor rtogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:4081: shes rab kyi phyir ming btagsa pa med pa'i so
NK078(tshu)001:4082: sor snang ba kun rtog pas /
NK078(tshu)001:4083: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab mtshon pa'i bla dwags gams /
NK078(tshu)001:4084: dpyad du med par go ba'i gtan tshigs su brjod pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4085: 'dir dpyad du med pa'i gtan tshig rtsod spong la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:4086: lha rje chen po'i bzhed dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4092: skye bo rnams 'bad med du grol bar thal ba'i rtsod spang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4093: so sor rtog pa'i nges tshig nyams pa'i rtsod spang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:4095: ma dpyad kyang go na skye bo tha mal pas chos nyid go bar 'gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:4096: ma dpyad kyang go ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:4098: tha ma ni so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyi nges tshig mi 'grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4099: de ni brtag cing dpyad nas go ba la zer ba yin pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:4100: 'dir ma dpyad par go bas so zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4103: sus kyang ma bcings bcing med de //
NK078(tshu)001:4104: zhes tshig bzhis gnas lugs kyi don de bcing grol dang bral ba yin pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:4105: so skye ba rnams kyis de'i don mi go zhing 'khrul ba'i bag chags dang bcas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:4106: skye bos chos nyid mi mthong la /
NK078(tshu)001:4107: 'dir bcing grol gnyis med kyi don go zhing 'khrul
NK078(tshu)001:4108: ba'i bag chags dang gral bas ma dpyad par go
NK078(tshu)001:4109: ba ni skal ldan rang rno yin kyang gtan tshigs
NK078(tshu)001:4110: kyi rkyen dang 'phrad pas grol bar 'dod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4111: tha ma'i skyon kyang mi 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4112: so sor gang la rtogs med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:4113: zhes pa lngas 'khor 'das sam rang spyi lta bu
NK078(tshu)001:4114: gang la yang so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis
NK078(tshu)001:4115: yul du byas nas rtog cing dpyod pa med de
NK078(tshu)001:4116: / ma brtag par 'khor 'das dang rang spyi la
NK078(tshu)001:4117: sogs par so sor snang ba'i chos kun gyi de
NK078(tshu)001:4118: kho na nyid rtogs shing khong du chud pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:4119: / / dpyad du yod pa'i so sor rtog /pa las mchog tu gyur pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4120: dngos po la brtags shing dpyad pa med par rtog pa'i bla dwags yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4121: gnyis pa ru g.yal gyi bzhed pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4122: sngar dpyad ma dpyad kyi rtsod spong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4123: rkyen la ltos mi ltos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4124: gzhal bya dang ldan mi ldan gyi rtsod spong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:4126: dpyad du med pa de sngar dpyad nas dpyad du med pa yin nam /
NK078(tshu)001:4127: sngar ma dpyad kyang dpyad du med pa yin /
NK078(tshu)001:4128: dang po ltar na rang bzhin gyi rnon po'i gtan
NK078(tshu)001:4129: tshigs ma yin par thal te sngar dpyad zin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:4130: phyir ro // ma dpyad kyang dpyad du med pa yin na gtan tshigs su mi 'thad de /
NK078(tshu)001:4131: gzhal bya gtan la pheb pa'i las dang byed pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:4133: sngar ma dpyad kyang skye ba 'di nyid la dpyad pas gtan tshigs su 'thad do //
NK078(tshu)001:4134: 'di nyid la dpyod na dpyad du yod pa'i go ba dang khyad med du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4135: dpyod pa tsam du khyad med kyang gzhal bya dang
NK078(tshu)001:4136: gtan tshigs la khyad med par bstan zin pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:4137: / skye ba snga ma phan chad la dpyad mi srid pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4138: 'di la yang theg chung gi don la mi dpyod pa'i phyir khyad par du ma yong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:4139: mdor na dpyad du med bya ba de dpyad pa
NK078(tshu)001:4140: tshegs chung ba la brtags kyis ye med min te
NK078(tshu)001:4141: / lha mo sked med ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4142: bu mo lto med ma lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4144: rang bzhin gyis rnon po de sngar theg pa la sbyangs nas rno ba yin nam /
NK078(tshu)001:4145: ma sbyangs bar rno ba yin /
NK078(tshu)001:4146: dang po ltar na sbyangs pa'i rnon por thal /
NK078(tshu)001:4148: rno ba nyid mi 'thad gsungs te /
NK078(tshu)001:4149: dbang po gnyis dang gtan tshigs 'di lha sbyin dang
NK078(tshu)001:4150: sta re lta bus gnas lugs kyi shing gcod pa
NK078(tshu)001:4151: lta bu ste / thun mong ma yin kyang rang
NK078(tshu)001:4152: bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po ni rang bzhin gzhi
NK078(tshu)001:4154: dpyad du med pa ni ye med min te dpyod yun thung ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:4155: gnyis med du 'bebs pa la brjod pas mgo bsgre mi mtshungs so gsung /
NK078(tshu)001:4157: dpyod pa med pa'i gtan tshigs 'di tshig dang yi ge'i rkyen la ltos sam mi ltos /
NK078(tshu)001:4159: tshig dang yi ges mi mtshon te /
NK078(tshu)001:4162: de brjod nyid kyis de nyid mthong /
NK078(tshu)001:4164: gzhan yang don gtan la mi pheb par thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4165: der ma zad de don de yang /
NK078(tshu)001:4166: tha snyad la brten dgos par bshad pas 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4167: brjod pa tsam mam mtshon pa tsam gyis rkyen la ltos /
NK078(tshu)001:4169: 'o na skyon snga ma 'ong zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4170: de don sems kyi ngo bo ji lta ba bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:4171: du sus kyang tshig dang yi ge la sogs pas
NK078(tshu)001:4172: mtshon du med pas de skad ces brjod du zad
NK078(tshu)001:4173: kyis / ming tsam 'di zhes bstan par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4174: rdo rje sems dpas mtshon du med /
NK078(tshu)001:4176: ye nas tshig dngos tshig lam chad /
NK078(tshu)001:4177: sems nyid de kun rang bzhin la /
NK078(tshu)001:4178: de dag sgra brjod bsnyad ci yod /
NK078(tshu)001:4179: brtan brtag dka' bar rgyal bas gsungs /
NK078(tshu)001:4180: zhes so 'on kyang gdul bya la brjod du med pa'i tshig gis mtshon dgos te /
NK078(tshu)001:4181: tshig dang yi ges mi mtshon te /
NK078(tshu)001:4182: zhes brjod pa de ka nyid tshig dang yi ger song ba yin pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:4183: dper na ming med kyi ming gis zhen pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:4184: kyang de nyid kas ming mtshon nus pa bzhin no
NK078(tshu)001:4186: skye med mtshon med 'gags med de //
NK078(tshu)001:4188: sgro skur bral ba'i brjod med de rig byed ces pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4190: mtshon du med pa'i don de yang //
NK078(tshu)001:4191: ma mtshon go bar mi 'gyur bas //
NK078(tshu)001:4192: mtshon du med pa'i don tshig gis //
NK078(tshu)001:4193: mtshon te mtshon med go bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:4196: de la ci bzhin de dbab pa //
NK078(tshu)001:4197: ji bzhin brjod pa'i tshig rnams kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:4198: dkar pos dkar po mtshon pa bzhin bsam brjod 'das pas de nyid mtshon /
NK078(tshu)001:4201: dpyad du med pa'i gtan tshigs 'di gzhal bya dang ldan nam mi ldan /
NK078(tshu)001:4202: dang po ltar na dpyad du yod pa dang khyad med du thal /
NK078(tshu)001:4205: med pa ma gzhal ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:4208: bla ma gong ma'i gsungs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4210: dang po ni gzhal bya dang ldan kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:4211: gzhal tshul la go ba myur bul gyi khyad yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:4212: dper na bsam yas lta bu la blta ba'i tshe
NK078(tshu)001:4213: zha bo dang mgyogs pa 2 tshig la khyad med
NK078(tshu)001:4214: de bgrod tshul myur bur la khyad yod pa bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:4217: gzhal bya dang ldan yang gtan tshigs gnyis po 'di gzhal bya tha dad de /
NK078(tshu)001:4218: dpyad du med pa'i gzhal bya ni gnas lugs de kho na nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:4219: dpyad du yod pa'i gzhal bya ni 'khor 'das gnyis so //
NK078(tshu)001:4220: gzhal tshul la yang rim gyis gzhal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4221: gcig chod du gzhal ba'i khyad yod do gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:4222: gnyis pa dpyad pas go ba'i gtan tshigs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4224: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4226: dpyad du med pa song nas kha gcig phyi ma
NK078(tshu)001:4227: ste dpyad du yod pas gtan tshigs kyis rgyud grol
NK078(tshu)001:4228: bar byed pa'ang / brtag bya gong du gzhal bya'i
NK078(tshu)001:4229: skabsa su brjod zin pa'i 'khor 'das kyi dngos po
NK078(tshu)001:4230: blo'i spyod yul du gyur pa rnams la rtog dpyod
NK078(tshu)001:4231: rang gi so sora rtogsa pa'i shes rab kyis rgyu
NK078(tshu)001:4232: bar byed pa'ang / byas / 'og gi lung man ngag gis gtan tshigas rnams kyis rkyen byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:4233: gtan la dbab pa la dona dang mthun pa'i gtan
NK078(tshu)001:4234: tshigs kyis sgra ji bzhin par gtan la dbab pa
NK078(tshu)001:4235: dang / don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs sgra ji
NK078(tshu)001:4236: bzhin ma yin pa'i gtan la dbab pa gnyis yin
NK078(tshu)001:4237: dang / no // 'di la nye stong chos kyi seng ge na re /
NK078(tshu)001:4238: sgra don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4239: sgra don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs gnyis yin gsungs /
NK078(tshu)001:4242: bsgrub byed kyi gtan tshigs mthun pa'i gtan gnyis la bzhed do //
NK078(tshu)001:4243: 'o na sgra don mi mthun pa gcig gis gtan la 'bebs so //
NK078(tshu)001:4245: pheb ste mtshan nyid lugs kyi 'gal ba'i gtan tshigs /
NK078(tshu)001:4247: ma grub pa'i gtan tshigs gsum skyon du che yang /
NK078(tshu)001:4248: gsang sngags kyi lugs kyis 'gal bas kyang gtan la pheb ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4250: stong ste ci'i phyir snang bar 'dug pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4251: snang ste ci'i phyir stong par 'dug pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4253: ci ste bcu drug gi gtan tshigs /
NK078(tshu)001:4254: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la bkod pa lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4255: ma nges pas kyang pheb ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4261: ma grub pas kyang pheb ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4263: mchog tu gsang ba'i chos nyid 'di //
NK078(tshu)001:4264: rna dbang gzhan las thos mi 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:4265: de bzhin lce yi dbang pos kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:4266: de la brjod du rdul tsam med //
NK078(tshu)001:4268: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:4269: tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4270: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK078(tshu)001:4273: dang po dpe nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4275: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma don dang mi mthun pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:4276: gtan tshigs kyi dpe yang don mtshon par byed pa
NK078(tshu)001:4277: ltar / de yang dpe ni me chos can me yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:4279: mi mthun pa'i dpe chu rlang bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4280: chu rlang nas sgrub bya me log pas rtags du ba yang ldog pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4281: de ka mi mthun pa'i dape'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4282: de dag go byed du ji ltar 'gro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4283: rtags du ba gar yod pa na bsgrub bya me yod par shugs la bstan te rtogs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:4285: yang dpe go byed du 'gro bas mi mthun pa'i dpes don mtshon pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4286: gnyis pa don rgyas pa de la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4288: dang po gnas lugs mtshon pa'i yul las 'das par bstan par dka' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4290: phyi nang 'khor 'das kyi chos kun snang stong rtag
NK078(tshu)001:4291: chad la sogs pa'i mtha' thams cad las 'das pa
NK078(tshu)001:4292: la / snang stong rtag chad la sogs pa'i mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:4293: rnams gang yang dbu ma bkag cing dor ba med
NK078(tshu)001:4294: la / pas na / dpe 'di ltar don 'di'o zhes phyogs gcig tu bstan du med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4295: de rang gi ngo bo tshig tu bstan pa dang blos brtag par dka' ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4296: don de yang chos nyid phyogs gcig tu grub na
NK078(tshu)001:4297: phyogs thams cad du 'char du mi btub pa las
NK078(tshu)001:4298: / cir yang ma grub pas cir yang 'char ba kho na ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4299: phyogs gcig pa thams cad dang bral bas /
NK078(tshu)001:4300: de'i dbyings las phyogs thams cad du ma 'gags par shar ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4302: 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' la dbyibs kha dog thams cad dang bral bas /
NK078(tshu)001:4303: rkyen gyis gzha' tshon sprin rlang pa la sogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:4304: dbyibs dang kha dog gang yang 'char ba bzhin no
NK078(tshu)001:4305: // de'i phyir snang rung gang yang ma spangs la /
NK078(tshu)001:4306: rang rgyud pa ngang gis bral ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4307: gnyis pa ji ltar mtshon pa'i dgos ched /
NK078(tshu)001:4309: 'on kyang zhes pa mi mthun pa mthun par ston pa'i tshig ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4313: stong pa la sogs phyogs dang ris su 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4319: nga yi bka' ni dgongs pa can //
NK078(tshu)001:4320: yod mtha' dgrol phyir med ces bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:4321: med mtha' dgrol phyir yod ces bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:4322: gnyis ka dgrol phyir gnyis med ston //
NK078(tshu)001:4323: gnyis med dgrol phyir rang grol bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:4325: de ltar don dang mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:4326: gtan la dbab pa 'di la gsum du'ang rung ste
NK078(tshu)001:4327: / dang po don mtha' bral la gtan tshigs kyi mtha' mi spangs ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4328: zhen pa'i snang ba chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:4329: yin tshul nas phyogs gcig pa'i mtha' las /
NK078(tshu)001:4331: mtha' gang yang mi dor ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4332: dper na nam mkha' bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4333: gnyis pa don ci yang ma yin pa la gtan tshigs ci yang ma yin par bstan pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4334: dngos por snang tsam chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:4335: yin tshul nas ci yang ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4336: snang tshul cir yang snang ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4337: dper na ga bur bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4338: gsum pa don mtha' gang yang mi spang ba la gtan tshigs mtha' bral du bstan pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4339: dngos por snang tsam chos can yin tshul nas mtha'i phyogs gang du'ang ma lhung ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4340: snang tshul nas mtha' gang yang ma spangs pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4341: dper na 'byung ba chen po nam mkha'i dbyings su 'ja' tshon la sogs pa snang ba bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4342: 'di dag tshig gi mi mthun pa ltar snang yang /
NK078(tshu)001:4343: don mthun pas don car phog tu tshig tu go ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4344: gsum pa gtan tshigs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:4346: dang po kun yin gang ma yin gyi gtan tshigs lhun grub tu bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4349: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:4350: kyi chos nyid ji ltar ming btagsa pa ltar grub
NK078(tshu)001:4351: yid kyis bsam pa bzhin du snang zhing rang rig
NK078(tshu)001:4352: pa'i rtsal du cir yang 'gyur bas 'khor 'das phyi
NK078(tshu)001:4353: nang gi dngos po kun gyi ngo bora ston cing
NK078(tshu)001:4354: / don sems nyid de dpes mtshon cing phyogs med
NK078(tshu)001:4355: kun tu rang snang bas cira yanga yina pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:4356: / / dper na semas kyi chosa nyid la snang
NK078(tshu)001:4357: stong phyogs gcig ci yanga ma grub pas ma yina
NK078(tshu)001:4358: / / na zhes bya'o // gtan tshigs de'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:4359: na phyogs gcig gang yang ma yin phyogs med du
NK078(tshu)001:4360: kun yin pas na ci yang yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4361: des na sems nyid phyogs bral mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:4362: ngang du 'khor 'das kyis chos kun lhun gyis grub
NK078(tshu)001:4363: pa'o // gnyis pa ma spang mi ldan gyi gtan tshigs mtha' bral du bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4365: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes ni snang stong
NK078(tshu)001:4366: la sogs pa'i mtha' kun gyi phyogs dang ris su
NK078(tshu)001:4367: rgya ma chad pa'i phyir snang stong phyogs re'i mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:4369: phyogs med du rang snang bas mtha' kun gyi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ma bral ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4370: des na snang stong la sogs pa'i mtha' gang yang
NK078(tshu)001:4371: ma spangsa pas na phyogs gcig gang yang mi ldan
NK078(tshu)001:4372: pas so // mtha' kun sems nyid du rang snang
NK078(tshu)001:4373: bas ma bral ba'i phyir de bas na phyogs re'i
NK078(tshu)001:4374: mtha' thams cad dang bral zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4375: bzhi pa gtan tshigs kyis gtan la 'beb tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:4377: de ltar sems kyi chos nyid ngo bo ngos bzung
NK078(tshu)001:4378: ba'i sgo nas gtan la phebs pas na gtan tshigs
NK078(tshu)001:4380: de yang mtha' gang yang ma spang ba la gang gi phyogs su ma lhung bas mi ldan te /
NK078(tshu)001:4384: yod med la sogs pa spros pa'i mtha' gang yang ma spang bas ma bral ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4385: bral ba na snang ba'i mtha' dang bral te /
NK078(tshu)001:4386: ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4387: stong pa'i mtha' dang bral te /
NK078(tshu)001:4389: gcig gi mtha' dang bral te /
NK078(tshu)001:4390: ma 'gags sna tshogs du mar snang ba'i phyir du ma'i mtha' dang bral te /
NK078(tshu)001:4391: rig pa byang chub kyi sems nyid chos nyid nyag gcig gi ngo bo las ma g.yos pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4392: rtag pa'i mtha' dang bral te /
NK078(tshu)001:4393: cir yang 'gyur ba'i phyir chad pa'i mtha' dang bral te /
NK078(tshu)001:4394: mi 'gyur zhig gnyen po med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4396: gang yang g.yo ba med pa'i phyir 'ong ba'i mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:4397: dang bral te gang yang song ba med pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:4398: ro // gtan la dbab pa'i don rang gi ngo
NK078(tshu)001:4399: bo 'di kho na'o zhes phyogs gcig par bstan par
NK078(tshu)001:4400: ro // daka'o // gnyis pa tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4402: dang po spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4404: tshig don mi mthun pa las dgar bas cig shes
NK078(tshu)001:4405: su gyur pa tshig don mthun par bstan pa'i gtan
NK078(tshu)001:4406: tshigs la yanga / bye brag tu phye na gtan tshigs bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:4407: mdor bsdus pas gtan tshigs kun la khyab pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:4408: lung man ngag rig pa tshad ma gsum yin te
NK078(tshu)001:4410: lung dang man ngag rig pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:4411: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal ba //
NK078(tshu)001:4412: gzhal byed de yang tshad mar gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:4414: gzhi 'bras bdag nyid gcig pa'i don mngon sum du gyur pa'i gsung ni lung tshad ma yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:4415: de nyid kyi don phyin ci ma log par rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:4416: shing nyams su len pa de bla ma dam pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:4417: zhal nas tshigs su phyung ba rnams ni man ngag
NK078(tshu)001:4418: tshad ma'o // don de gnyis la sgro 'dogs chod
NK078(tshu)001:4419: pa ni rig pa tshad ma yin te de la
NK078(tshu)001:4423: dbang po'i mngon sum dang yid kyi dang rang rig dang rnal 'byor mngon sum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:4424: de yang chos nyid rtog byed ni rig pa tshad ma yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:4425: lung man ngag gnyis ni de'i rkyen yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4426: de ltar chos nyid rtogs par byed pa la de gsum 'tshogs dgos pas kun khyab ces bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4427: tshad ma gsum po de dag dang ldan pa tshig
NK078(tshu)001:4428: don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs kyi rnam grangs su brjod
NK078(tshu)001:4429: pa bsam yas pa yod na'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:4430: 'dir de dag gi cha gcig tsam tshigs su brjod
NK078(tshu)001:4431: pa 'og nas 'byung ba'i tshul 'di lta bu ste
NK078(tshu)001:4433: gtan tshigs rgyas par lus bzhag na /
NK078(tshu)001:4434: tshad ma bka' gzhung gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4435: sgra mthun don dpag gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4436: gzhal bya bdag nyid che sogs blta /
NK078(tshu)001:4438: gnyis pa bye brag so sor bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:4439: tshang ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4440: sgra mthun don dpag gi gtan tshigs so //
NK078(tshu)001:4443: dang po dag pa bzhi dang gsum gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4445: 'khor 'das bden gnyis rgyu 'bras kyi chos rnams rang bzhin yongsa kyi rnam par dag pa'i don ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4449: rgyu rnams rab tu dag pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:4450: 'bras bu yongs su dag gyur te //
NK078(tshu)001:4451: don dam dmigs med rang bzhin dag /kun rdzob sgyu mar ye nas dag /ces gsungs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:4452: rgyu 'byung ba lnga sems su dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4453: 'bras bu dam rdzas lnga rigs lngar dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4454: don dam dmigs med du dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4455: kun rdzob sgyu mar dag pa'i tshul gyis don rtogsa shing mngon du byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:4456: de yang rgyu 'byung ba lnga sems su dag pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4458: rgyu yi mtshan nyid dag pa ni //
NK078(tshu)001:4459: phyi rol chen po rnam lnga ste //
NK078(tshu)001:4460: sems nyid gzung 'dzin gnyis snang ba'i //
NK078(tshu)001:4461: gzung ba'i yul nyid 'byung ba che //
NK078(tshu)001:4462: rgyu nyid rang gi sems yin pas //
NK078(tshu)001:4463: 'byung ba chen po rgyu nas dag /ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:4464: gnyis pa 'bras bu dam rdzas lnga rigs lngar dag pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4466: 'bras bu yongs su dag pa ni //
NK078(tshu)001:4467: sems can kun gyi nus pa ste //
NK078(tshu)001:4468: rdo rje byang chub sems yin la //
NK078(tshu)001:4470: dri chen dri chu gur gum chu //
NK078(tshu)001:4471: so so'i lus la gnas pa dag /ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:4472: gsum pa don dam dmigs med du dag pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4474: don dam dmigs med dag pa ni //
NK078(tshu)001:4475: phyi nang chos rnams thams cad kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:4476: rang gi ngo bo ma yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:4477: skye 'gags med par ye nas dag /ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:4478: bzhi pa kun rdzob sgyu mar dag pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4480: kun rdzob sgyu mar dag pa ni //
NK078(tshu)001:4481: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin thams cad snang //
NK078(tshu)001:4482: chu zla'i tshul du mi dmigs nas //
NK078(tshu)001:4483: mi dmigs pa nyid sna tshogs snang //
NK078(tshu)001:4484: de bzhin bde gshegs ye nas mnyam //
NK078(tshu)001:4488: chen por yum lngar dag pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:4489: phung por sems phyir rigs lngar dag /tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag pas //
NK078(tshu)001:4490: snod bcud kun gyi kun brtag bral //
NK078(tshu)001:4492: snod 'byung ba lnga yum lngar dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4493: bcud phung po lnga rigs lngar dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4494: sems kyi rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyis bsdus pa
NK078(tshu)001:4495: rnams ye shes lngar dag pa la dag pa lta
NK078(tshu)001:4496: ba rtogsa shing gtan la phab pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4498: snod dang bcud dang rgyud rnams kun //
