NK078(tshu)001:4499: dag pas dag pa gsum yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:4500: yum gyi dbyings dang yab kyi mkha' //ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin du //
NK078(tshu)001:4501: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:4502: dag pa gsum du rgyal bas gsungs //
NK078(tshu)001:4504: 'o na dag pa gsum gyis chog pa la bzhi ci la dgos zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4505: gdul bya rmongs pa rnams gsum dag par 'dzin pa
NK078(tshu)001:4506: la bzhi ma dag par 'dzin pa'i zhen pa bzlog
NK078(tshu)001:4507: pa'i phyir brjod kyi ngo bo gcig go //
NK078(tshu)001:4509: gsum dang bzhi brjod dgos ched ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4510: rmongs pa gsum gyis dag ma dag /
NK078(tshu)001:4511: 'dzin pa'i lta ngan bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:4512: rnam grangs brjod kyis ngo bo gcig ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:4513: yang de ltar na gsum bzhi dag gis lnga ma
NK078(tshu)001:4514: dag pa'i zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir lnga dag pa
NK078(tshu)001:4515: yang dgos so zhe na mi dgos te /
NK078(tshu)001:4516: dag pa gsum gyi snod bcud rgyud gsum gyi 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:4517: ba dag kyang 'das pa ma dag pa las bzhis
NK078(tshu)001:4518: 'khor 'das gnyis ka dag tsam na dag par bya
NK078(tshu)001:4519: ba'i rgyu gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:4520: yang dag pa gsum gyis ye shes ka dag tu
NK078(tshu)001:4521: gtan la phab nas 'khor ba'i ngan zhen bcad la
NK078(tshu)001:4522: dag pa bzhis dbyings ka dag gtan la phab nas
NK078(tshu)001:4524: de las lhag pa'i dag pa gzhan mi dgos so /
NK078(tshu)001:4525: gnyis pa mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4527: thun mong gi mnyam gnyis ni mdo sde pa dang sgo bstun pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4528: don dam skye med du mnyam pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4529: kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4530: theg 'og gi bden gnyis de las lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4531: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes su mnyam pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4532: don dam dkor bdun du mnyam pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4533: de ltar lhag pa'i bden gnyis kyisa don dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:4534: kyi rang bzhin la gzhal bya 'khor 'das kyi dngos
NK078(tshu)001:4535: po thams cad 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi
NK078(tshu)001:4536: dkyila 'khora du spyod yul yongs su dag pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:4537: kun tu bzang po ste ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i
NK078(tshu)001:4540: don dam du ni dkor bdun dang //
NK078(tshu)001:4541: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK078(tshu)001:4544: mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs la bden gnyis kyi tshig mthun par 'byung bas /
NK078(tshu)001:4545: sgra mthun don dpag tu thal zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4547: tshad ma'i bka' las dag mnyam grangs //
NK078(tshu)001:4549: theg 'og gi bden gnyis grub mthar mi 'dod la /
NK078(tshu)001:4550: 'dir bden gnyis dbyer med grub mtha' sgrub byed kyi gtan tshigs su 'dod do //
NK078(tshu)001:4551: yang dag pa dang mnyam pa la khyad ci yod zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4552: de gnyis ngo bo gcig la dgos ched ma 'dres te /
NK078(tshu)001:4553: bdag gzhan ma dag pa'i 'dzin zhen dgrol ba'i phyir dag pa'i gtan tshig bstan la /
NK078(tshu)001:4554: bzang ngan che chung gi 'dzin zhen grol ba'i phyir mnyam pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK078(tshu)001:4555: tshul gyis dag mnyam so sor bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:4557: gsum pa rtog pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4559: 'di la rim gyis pa ltar du bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4560: cig char ba ltar du bshad pa gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:4562: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams su zhen pa gzhal bya /
NK078(tshu)001:4563: rgyu gciga par gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4564: don dam skye med du rtogs pa grub mtha' ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4565: des dngos po mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4567: kun dngos rig pa ci snang phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:4568: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu ru gcig /ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:4569: skye med du zhen pa gzhal bya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4570: gsung gi yi ge +aahsku'i yi ge o /
NK078(tshu)001:4571: thugs kyi yi ge la ste yig 'bru'i tshul du gtan la phab pa gtan tshigs /
NK078(tshu)001:4572: kun rdzob lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs mi
NK078(tshu)001:4573: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor rtogs pa grub mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:4574: ste / des stong pa phyang chad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4577: 'bru gsum sgra dbyibs kyis mtshon nas //
NK078(tshu)001:4578: sku gsung thugs kyi 'bras bur rtogs //
NK078(tshu)001:4580: rtogs pa snga ma gnyis su zhen pa gzhal bya /
NK078(tshu)001:4581: byin gyis rlabs kyis gtan la dbab pa gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4582: bden pa dbyer med du rtogs pa grub mtha' ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4583: des bden gnyis tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4585: lhag pa'i don dam kun rdzob gnyis //
NK078(tshu)001:4586: rtogs pa lta ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:4587: ba ra na se'i ras tshos ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:4588: rtogs pa'i byin rlabs zung 'jug pa //
NK078(tshu)001:4589: byin rlabs phyir na sgra 'jug ste //
NK078(tshu)001:4591: dbyer med du rtogs pa la zhen pa gzhal bya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4592: mngon sum par gtan la phab pa gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4593: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar rtogs pa grub mtha' ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4594: de ltar bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod yul du byed pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4596: de ltar tshul gsum brjod pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:4597: mthong ba gang yin shes rab spyan //
NK078(tshu)001:4598: de yang mngon sum zhen pa ste //
NK078(tshu)001:4599: sgra tshig rten bral zhen tsam min //
NK078(tshu)001:4600: yul min rang rig bden dbyer med //
NK078(tshu)001:4601: blos gting go ba mngon sum yul //
NK078(tshu)001:4602: ming tshig sgra la mi brtan par //
NK078(tshu)001:4603: blo yi gting du go bar byos //
NK078(tshu)001:4605: gnyis pa cig car du bshad na /
NK078(tshu)001:4606: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad rgyu ma rig pa la gcig /
NK078(tshu)001:4607: 'das pa'i chos thams cad sku ye shes su rgyu
NK078(tshu)001:4608: gcig /de gnyis ka don dam kun rdzob bden pa
NK078(tshu)001:4609: gnyis ka rang byung ye shes su rgyu gcig pa
NK078(tshu)001:4611: gnyis med don gcig yin par bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:4614: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med dang //
NK078(tshu)001:4615: chos nyid dbyings su tshul gcig pas //
NK078(tshu)001:4616: ma lus rang snang chos thams cad //
NK078(tshu)001:4617: ma lus byang chub sems su rtogs //
NK078(tshu)001:4619: rgyu gcig pa de nyid kyi rang snang la /
NK078(tshu)001:4620: don ma skyes mi 'gags dbyer med ngang /
NK078(tshu)001:4621: rtags sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor de ltar don
NK078(tshu)001:4622: rtags dbyer med cing lhun gyis grub pa'i don yi
NK078(tshu)001:4623: ge 'bru gsum gyi tshul du mtshon pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4625: sku gsung thugs su snang ba yi ma lus gsung gi rgyan du rtogs /
NK078(tshu)001:4626: thams cad gsung gi yi ge ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4627: thabs dang ldan par rgyas gdab bo //
NK078(tshu)001:4629: de ltar rgyu gcig yig 'bru gnyis kyi ngang du
NK078(tshu)001:4630: phung po rnam shes 'byung ba'i chos thams cad sku
NK078(tshu)001:4631: dang ye shes su byin rlabs pa'i don dang dbyer
NK078(tshu)001:4632: med du rtogs pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4634: de gnyis dbyer med byin rlabs las //
NK078(tshu)001:4635: de nyid de yi byin rlabs te //
NK078(tshu)001:4636: gnyis med tshul gyis rang snang ba //
NK078(tshu)001:4637: byin rlabs ngo mtshar bsam mi khyab //
NK078(tshu)001:4639: de nyid blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba rang rig pas mngona sum du rtogs pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4641: rang snang rang byung chos 'di dag /gnyis med rang rig ma skyes par //
NK078(tshu)001:4642: gsal bar mngon sum the tshom med //
NK078(tshu)001:4643: rtogs pa kun gyi mchod tu bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:4645: 'o na mngon sum gyi skabs su gtan tshigs dang grub mtha' dmigs 'dres so zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4647: me chu'i dpe bzhin du zhor sel zhor 'grub yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4648: bden pa dbyer med kyi don la sgro 'dogs bcad par byed pa'i cha nas gtan tshigs /
NK078(tshu)001:4649: sgro 'dogs chod pa ste de blo 'das su shar ba'i cha nas grub mtha' ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4651: des na don dang gtan tshigs kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:4652: ngo bo gcig la thabs kyis phye //
NK078(tshu)001:4653: dper na me dang tsha phyir ram //
NK078(tshu)001:4654: chu dang rlan phyir ji bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4656: de ltar gong du bshad pa'i gtan tshigs rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi yis /
NK078(tshu)001:4657: grub mtha' gzhal bya phyi nang gi chos thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:4658: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal bar rdzogsa shing
NK078(tshu)001:4659: rig pa la rang dbang bsgyur bas na rgyal po
NK078(tshu)001:4660: ste / phyi rgyud man chad las khyad par du
NK078(tshu)001:4661: gyur pas na 'di bas che ba'i grub mtha' gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:4662: ste / med pa'o // 'o na gcig char ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:4663: rtogs pa bzhi'i skabs la gang zag gcig gis rgyu
NK078(tshu)001:4664: gcig pa'i skabs su bden gsum sgro 'dog chod na
NK078(tshu)001:4665: ste / med pa'o // / phyi ma gsum dgos
NK078(tshu)001:4666: sam mi dgos dgos na bden gsum min pa'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:4670: phyi ma gsum don med du thal zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:4671: dang po rgyu gcig dus su /
NK078(tshu)001:4672: de'i ngo bo la byed las dgos ched kyi cha
NK078(tshu)001:4673: nas rtog pa bzhi ma 'dres par phye ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:4674: te / tshig yi ge la snga phyi yod kyang
NK078(tshu)001:4675: don dbyer med kyi ngo bo la yongs su rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:4676: te / pa nges na / ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas 'gal ba med do //
NK078(tshu)001:4677: bzhi pa dag pa gsum khyad par du bshad pa'i bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4679: chos kun rig pa rang byung gi ye shes nyid la nyid kyis dbang bsgyur /
NK078(tshu)001:4680: rang byung gi ye shes nyid la nyid longs spyod pa'i phyir bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs te /
NK078(tshu)001:4681: bdag gi myong ba'i phung po lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4682: gzhan 'byung ba yul ltar du snang ba lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4683: rtog pa'i rgyun ngar 'dzin pa'i rnam par shes pa
NK078(tshu)001:4684: tshogs brgyad po rnams phung po lnga rigs kyi yab
NK078(tshu)001:4685: lnga dang / 'byung ba lnga rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4686: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rnam par dag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4687: gnyis med lhun grub du gsal zhing rang rig pas mngon sum du rtogs pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4688: bla na med pa'i gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa'i mchog ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4689: de ltar bdag gzhan gnyis snang bkag pa'i bdag gcig pu par 'gyur bas /
NK078(tshu)001:4690: phyi rol pa dang khyad med du 'gyur ro zhe
NK078(tshu)001:4691: na mi 'gyur te bdag gzhan tha dad gnyis 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:4692: gyi lta ba bzlog pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4693: bdag gzhan phyi nang thams cad rig pa bdag nyid
NK078(tshu)001:4694: chen po'i ngang du rdzogs pa zhes dgos ched kyi
NK078(tshu)001:4695: sgo nas brjod par zad kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:4696: don du na bdag nyid chen po tsam du yang
NK078(tshu)001:4697: 'dzin pa med pas mu stegs rtags lta dang khyad
NK078(tshu)001:4700: thams cad rig phyir bdag brjod kyi //
NK078(tshu)001:4701: snang bkag rnam pa'i gcig ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:4702: gang zag mos dang brtag pa'ang dag /rang rgyud spyod
NK078(tshu)001:4703: yul 'brel ba'i bdag /rgyu 'bras yul lta bzlog phyir
NK078(tshu)001:4704: la // bdag nyid chen po 'di 'drar med //
NK078(tshu)001:4707: bdag la gzhan pa mi snang zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:4711: nga la nga zhes bstan pas nga ma grub //
NK078(tshu)001:4712: nga nyid dngos su mi snang phyogs dang bral //
NK078(tshu)001:4715: bsgrub bya lhun rdzogs zla med pas //
NK078(tshu)001:4716: nga zhes ming du snyag par zad //
NK078(tshu)001:4718: dngos kyis bstan par nus pa min //
NK078(tshu)001:4720: lnga pa rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med kyi gtan tshigs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4722: dang po rang bzhin snang stong dbyer med du bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4724: mya ngan las 'das pa dang ma 'adsa pa 'khor ba'i chos ma lus pa thamsa cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:4725: don dam gsum mngon du byed pa'i yang daga pa'i shes pas rab tu brtagsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:4726: don dam par spyod yul dang bral bas rang bzhin med pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:4727: kun rdzob tu yul med rang gsal bar cir yang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:4728: de ltar kun rdzob tu ji ltar snang ba'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:4729: nyid na don dam mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyingsa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:4730: las g.yos pa med pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4731: gnyis pa 'khor 'das ngo bo gnyis med du bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4733: de bzhin gshegsa pa'i sku ye shes sgyu ma lta
NK078(tshu)001:4734: bura dag pa'i ngo la snang ba mya ngan las
NK078(tshu)001:4735: 'das pa dang / de ma yin la der 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:4736: pa'i log rtog sgyu ma lta bu ma dag pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:4737: ngo la snang ba 'khor ba'i sems can gnyis ka
NK078(tshu)001:4738: sems nyid kyi ngo bor brten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed
NK078(tshu)001:4739: pa'i rtsa ba med pa'i phyir te /
NK078(tshu)001:4740: rang bzhina gyis stong pa la mya ngan las 'das
NK078(tshu)001:4741: pa'i rigsa dang 'khor ba'i rgyud tha dad du brtag
NK078(tshu)001:4743: gsum pa rang bzhin chos sku lhun grub tu bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4745: don dam 'khor 'das so so'i rigsa tha dad dang
NK078(tshu)001:4746: kha dog dang dbyibsa tha dad phyogs gcig cir yang
NK078(tshu)001:4748: kun rdzob tu 'khor ba'i phyi nang snod bcud dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4749: 'das pa'i theg pa mtho dman thamsa cad du ma 'gags par snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4750: de ltar kun rdzob tu ma 'gags par snang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:4751: dus nyid na don dam par ngo bo grub pa
NK078(tshu)001:4752: med pa de nyid la chos kyi sku zhes bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:4753: // des na chos sku bden pa dbyer med de la phyogs gcig pa'i mtha' las grol ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4754: phyogs med du cir yang 'gyur zhing ye shes rang
NK078(tshu)001:4755: snang du cir yang 'grub pa ste phyogs med du
NK078(tshu)001:4757: 'o na gong du dag mnyam gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4758: 'dir rang bzhin dbyer med gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4759: gsum ka la bden pa dbyer med bshad pa 'dug pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4761: de gsum ngo bo gcig la dgos ched dam mtshon tshul ma 'dres te /
NK078(tshu)001:4762: dag ma dag gi zhen pa dgrol ba'i ngos nas dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4763: bdag gzhan bzang ngan gyi zhen pa dgrol ba'i phyir mnyam pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4764: tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i ngos
NK078(tshu)001:4765: nas rang bzhin dbyer med kyi gtan tshigs bstan pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:4767: gzhan bral rig snang bzang ngan med //
NK078(tshu)001:4768: brtag pa'i dri bral ma 'dres gsal //
NK078(tshu)001:4769: don tshul so sor mtshon tshig phye //
NK078(tshu)001:4770: dngos gcig tshul sgras tha dad kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:4771: don du smra bsam bral bar gcig /ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:4772: gnyis pa sgra mthun don dpag la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4774: dang po rang spyi'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4776: dang po rang spyi'i go don ni mtshan gzhi du
NK078(tshu)001:4777: ma la mtshan nyid gcig gis khyab pa spyi'i mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:4778: nyid dang / mtshan gzhi chos can du ma la
NK078(tshu)001:4779: mtshan nyid mi 'dra ba re re so sor nges
NK078(tshu)001:4780: pa rang gi mtshan nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:4781: de la nyon mongsa pa rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4782: spyir bstan pa'i mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:4785: dang po ni thun mong gi rang spyi'i yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4786: de yang spyi'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4787: mi rtag sdug bsngal stong pa bdag med de /
NK078(tshu)001:4789: spyi yi mtshan nyid brjod pa ni //
NK078(tshu)001:4790: mi rtag sdug bsngal stong bdag med //
NK078(tshu)001:4793: zhe sdang ni kun nas mnar sems shing 'khrugs pa /
NK078(tshu)001:4794: 'dod chags ni yul so sor ma 'dres la zhen cing chags pa /
NK078(tshu)001:4795: gti mug ni kun nas rmongs pa nga rgyal ni bdag lta la brten cing sems khengs pa /
NK078(tshu)001:4796: phrag dog ni blo'i 'phrag tu gzhan gyi yon tan mi shong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4798: rgyas par gsung na'ang bsdus pa mdo las /
NK078(tshu)001:4799: zhe sdang ma 'dres mnar sems pa //
NK078(tshu)001:4801: gti mug ma 'dres kun tu rmongs //
NK078(tshu)001:4802: nga rgyal ma 'dres ri bo che //
NK078(tshu)001:4803: phrag dog ma 'dres kun tu 'khrug /ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:4804: gnyis pa ma nor ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4805: khyad par rang spyi yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:4806: de la spyi'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4807: rang byung gi ye shes rnam kun mchog ldan gyi yongs rdzogs yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:4808: de la rang gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4809: dug lnga rang rig ye shes lngar ma 'dres par gsal ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4812: rtsa ba chags sdang lnga nyid de //
NK078(tshu)001:4813: gzhi rtsa ma bcos skad cig ma //
NK078(tshu)001:4814: de nyid rang spyir gang yin pa //
NK078(tshu)001:4815: rtogs pas spyi dang rang mtshan shes //
NK078(tshu)001:4817: la la rang rig thabs chen du //
NK078(tshu)001:4818: ma 'gags snang bas rang mtshan te //
NK078(tshu)001:4820: de ltar mtshan nyid gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:4821: khyad par spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid ma nor
NK078(tshu)001:4822: bar don rtogsa na nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par
NK078(tshu)001:4823: byang ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam du 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:4824: ba'o // nyon mongs pa lam du 'gyur ba de'i phyir khyad par rang spyi'i gtan tshigsa te /
NK078(tshu)001:4825: snyigs ma'i gdul bya rnams la shin tu gces so zhes gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4826: des na thun mong gi rang dang spyi gnyis tha dad du 'byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4827: 'dir rang spyi dbyer med du ston cing ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas don dpag pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4828: rtse lde gnyis kyis ming gcig pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4829: de ltar na bden gnyis lam du byed par 'dug pas /
NK078(tshu)001:4830: nyon mongs lam du byed pa med pas dbu ma
NK078(tshu)001:4831: dang khyad med du 'gyur ro zhe na mi 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:4833: nyon mongs rang gi mtshan nyid stong nyid du sbyongs shing spyi'i mtshan nyid ltar bar 'dod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4834: bsgom pas kyang rang mtshan spang zhing spyi'i mtshan nyid bsgom par 'dod pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4836: kha cig rang gi mtshan nyid du //
NK078(tshu)001:4837: zhen pa snang ba lta bu la //
NK078(tshu)001:4838: sa sra chu sher la sogs dang //
NK078(tshu)001:4839: nyon mongs rang gi mtshan nyid lnga //
NK078(tshu)001:4840: snying rje skyob pa gdung ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:4841: byams pa mi mjed phan 'dog sogs //
NK078(tshu)001:4842: mya ngan 'das lam gyur pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:4843: rang gi mtshan nyid so sor 'dod //
NK078(tshu)001:4844: zhen pa de nyid mi rtag bsngal //
NK078(tshu)001:4845: stong bdag med pas spyi ru 'dod //
NK078(tshu)001:4848: spang bya log pa'i dug lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4849: gnyen po yang dag pa'i dug lnga ste ye shes lnga ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4850: spang gnyen ro gcig pa'i tshul du skad cig la shar grol du rtogs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4852: nyi ma'i dkyil na mun med ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:4853: ye shes rang snang ma gtogs par //
NK078(tshu)001:4854: nyon mongs 'khor ba ngang gis med //
NK078(tshu)001:4856: nyon mongs lam du byed tshul rgyas par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4857: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu dgu pa'i gzhung 'grel du lta bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4858: gnyis pa mtha' bral gyi gtan tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4860: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid la yod med rtag chad la sogs pa'i mtha' ste ngan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4861: dbus te bzang po zhig med cing gcig dang du mar bral bas /
NK078(tshu)001:4862: gcig dang du mar gang du'ang grub pa min te
NK078(tshu)001:4863: 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid bden
NK078(tshu)001:4864: pa dbyer med pa'i tshul de lam pas rtogsa na
NK078(tshu)001:4865: rnam par bya ba'i lam du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:4867: dbus ma spangs la bral bas mtha' bral gyi gtan tshigs de'nga shin tu gces par gdams pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4868: sngar rang spyir bstan pa de bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4869: de'ang theg 'og gi stong pa'i ngo bo la mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:4870: bzhi'am brgyad ma grub pas mtha' bral du 'dod la
NK078(tshu)001:4871: / 'dir mu bzhi mtha' brgyad ma spangs pa'i mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:4872: bral chen po ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su 'dod de
NK078(tshu)001:4874: lhag gsum dang ni bzhi bral lugs khyad par can gyi de nyid mthong /
NK078(tshu)001:4877: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK078(tshu)001:4878: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:4880: de ltar tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs dang khyad med du thal /
NK078(tshu)001:4881: mtha' ma spangs la bral ba'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:4883: 'dir tshig don mthun pa'i ngos nas mtha' bral yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:4884: gong du tshig don mi mthun pa'i ngos nas mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:4885: bral yin pa sngar 'bru mnan gyi skabs su bshad
NK078(tshu)001:4886: pa bzhin no // gsum pa rnam par dbye ba'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4888: 'bru'i gzugs kyi 'byung gnas yin pas 'byung ba rags cing dbang che bas chena pa /
NK078(tshu)001:4889: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' dang lnga rnams la /
NK078(tshu)001:4890: rang rgyud par 'dzin pa'i rang bzhin grub pa med
NK078(tshu)001:4891: par gtan tshigs kyis gzhiga par bya'i dgos ched yod
NK078(tshu)001:4892: pa'i phyir / sa la sogs pa gciga la'ang sems
NK078(tshu)001:4893: can las snang dbang gis rigs mthun mi mthun gyi
NK078(tshu)001:4894: khyad par gyi snang ngo la /
NK078(tshu)001:4895: 'byung ba lnga re re la'ang 'byung ba lnga lngara
NK078(tshu)001:4896: snang ba'i dbang gis 'byung ba nyi shu rtsa lngar
NK078(tshu)001:4897: dbye bar bya zhing snang du rung bas /
NK078(tshu)001:4898: des na sems can gyi las snang phyogs gcig ma
NK078(tshu)001:4899: grub pas yi ge mu gyis mtshon nas mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:4900: nyid kyi dbyings dang gnyis su med par thim par
NK078(tshu)001:4901: bya / mum gyis mtshon pa'i dbyings de nyid ngag
NK078(tshu)001:4902: gis smra ba dang brjod pa'i mtha' las 'das pa
NK078(tshu)001:4903: bya / dang / yid kyis bsam dpyod kyi mtha' las 'das pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4905: rnam par dbye ba'ang phung po dang //
NK078(tshu)001:4906: 'byung ba la sogs dngos kun la //
NK078(tshu)001:4907: gdos snang re re'ang bye brag gis //
NK078(tshu)001:4908: gtses pas ril por zhen grol nas //
NK078(tshu)001:4909: gcig kyang kun dngos de red med //
NK078(tshu)001:4910: rang rig lhun grub bdag nyid dbyings //
NK078(tshu)001:4913: rdzogs chen mu tig phreng ba'i rgyud las /
NK078(tshu)001:4914: nam mkha' la ni khyab stong pas //
NK078(tshu)001:4915: nam mkha' nyid ni dngos por grol //
NK078(tshu)001:4916: rlung ni gzugs yul mi snang ba'i //
NK078(tshu)001:4917: dngos po sdud pa'i las su grol //
NK078(tshu)001:4918: me ni smin byed byin za bas //
NK078(tshu)001:4919: bskyed cing dngas snyigs 'byed pa grol //
NK078(tshu)001:4920: sa ni spyod byed 'degs pas ni //
NK078(tshu)001:4921: dngos med mtha' bral stong par grol //
NK078(tshu)001:4922: chu ni sdud byed brlan pas na //
NK078(tshu)001:4923: sreg byed smin pa'i las su grol //
NK078(tshu)001:4924: nam mkha'i rlung ni dngos po la //
NK078(tshu)001:4925: nam mkha'i mes ni sdud par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:4926: nam mkha'i chus ni sreg byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4927: nam mkha'i sas ni go skabs 'byed //
NK078(tshu)001:4928: nam mkha'i nam mkha' snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4929: rlung gi rlung ni brtan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4930: rlung gi nam mkha' me dang che //
NK078(tshu)001:4931: rlung gi chu ni myur mgyogs che //
NK078(tshu)001:4932: rlung gi me ni phan sdud che //
NK078(tshu)001:4933: rlung gi sa ni gzugs brnyan gsal //
NK078(tshu)001:4934: chu yi chu ni sgra snyan yin //
NK078(tshu)001:4935: chu yi nam mkha' thog pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:4936: chu yi rlung ni chad med rgyun //
NK078(tshu)001:4937: chu yis me ni sdus par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:4938: chu yis sa ni khyab par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:4939: me yis me ni skyed par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:4940: me yis nam mkha' dngos por bsreg /me yis rlung ni 'bar bar byed //
NK078(tshu)001:4941: me yis chu ni brlag par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:4943: sa yis sas ni 'gro ba khyab //
NK078(tshu)001:4944: sa yi nam mkha' thog pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:4945: sa yi rlung ni gang stong byed //
NK078(tshu)001:4946: sa yis chus ni dngos po skyed //
NK078(tshu)001:4947: sa yis mes ni skom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4948: nges pa med pa'i 'byung ba yin //
NK078(tshu)001:4949: nges par snang bas sems nyid grol //
NK078(tshu)001:4951: sgra mthun la don dpag tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:4952: theg 'og gis sems can gyis las snang 'byung ba
NK078(tshu)001:4953: lnga phye nas de nyid ma grub par stong par
NK078(tshu)001:4954: 'dod la / 'dir las snang 'byung lnga phyogs rer ma grub bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:4955: dngas ma ye shes kyi 'byung ba lngar gcig du
NK078(tshu)001:4956: mar phyogs med du snang ba dang stong pa dbyer
NK078(tshu)001:4958: brgal len kyang don de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4959: bzhi pa mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4963: dper na nam mkha' la dbyibs kha dog mtha' dbus
NK078(tshu)001:4964: phyogs ris sogs gang gis ngos bzunga du meda de
NK078(tshu)001:4965: / de dag thams cad dang bral ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:4966: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thamsa cad kyang de dang 'dra ste /
NK078(tshu)001:4967: don phyogs gcig pa gang du yang gzung du med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4968: sa'i ngo bo sra zhing brtan pas thams cad skyed pa'i las byed pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:4969: don sems kyi chos nyid rang snang du bskyed cing thams cad kyi rten byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:4970: chu bo phan tshun drang du btub pas mnyen zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:4971: byed las dri ma 'khrul ba ltar /ka sems nyid
NK078(tshu)001:4972: ngos bzung med pa cir yang 'char bar shes par
NK078(tshu)001:4973: bya ba dang / me 'od gsal zhing byed las bud shing bsrega pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:4974: sems nyid gsal zhing nyon mongs rnam rtog gi mtshan ma bsreg par shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:4975: kha sems nyid cir yang bsgyur du btub pas mnyen
NK078(tshu)001:4976: zhing de'i don rtogs na nyon mongs dang gzugs 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:4978: rlung gi ngo bo kha dog dbyibs kyi ngos bzung
NK078(tshu)001:4979: du med pa las yangs shing g.yo ba ltar /ga
NK078(tshu)001:4981: nam mkha' bzung du med pa ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:4982: snang srid thams cad de dang 'dra //
NK078(tshu)001:4983: chos rnams thams cad sems nyid de //
NK078(tshu)001:4984: sems ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:4985: ji ltar sa gzhi chen mo la //
NK078(tshu)001:4986: sems kyi zin dang ma zin pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:4988: thams cad kun gyi gnas brten te //
NK078(tshu)001:4989: sangs rgyas byang sems kun kyang gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:4990: theg pa mtho dman thams cad snang //
NK078(tshu)001:4991: thams cad theg chen dbyings su 'dus //
NK078(tshu)001:4992: mes ni thams cad kun bsreg ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:4993: rtog tshogs ye shes ngang du bsreg /chu yis sdud cing 'khrul ba ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:4994: de bzhin de ltar rig par gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:4995: chos rnams ye nas rlung dang 'dra //
NK078(tshu)001:4996: de la bzung du med pa ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:4997: kun la de ltar 'byor bar gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:4999: 'byung ba lnga'i dpe don sems nyid mtshon pa de
NK078(tshu)001:5000: bzhin du phung po la'ang gnyis te ngo bos mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:5001: pa dang / mtshan nyid kyis mtshon pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5003: gzugs kyis snang stong dbyer med mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5004: tshor bas myong stong mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5005: 'du shes kyis mtshan mar 'dzin stong dbyer med dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5006: 'du byed kyis dran rtog dran stong dbyer med mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5007: rnam shes kyis rig stong dbyer med du mtshon te /
NK078(tshu)001:5009: de bzhin gzugs dang tshor ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:5010: mtshan 'du shes 'dzin 'du byed rnam lnga yis //
NK078(tshu)001:5011: mtshan nyid rang rig nyid snang phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5012: snang stong gzugs dbyer med tshor stong grags //
NK078(tshu)001:5013: mtshan 'du shes 'dzin yod med bya dbyer med byed med //
NK078(tshu)001:5014: dran rnam shes stong dbyer med rang snang phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5015: phung po bzhi po ye shes su //
NK078(tshu)001:5016: gcig pas rnam shes rang byung che //
NK078(tshu)001:5019: gzugs kyi phung po 'jig pa ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:5020: don kyang phyogs ris thams cad chos nyid phyogs med du 'jig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5021: tshor ba nyams su myong ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:5022: chos nyid kyang myong ba med pa'i myong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5024: chos nyid mtshan ma med pa'i mtshan mar 'dzin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5025: 'du byed sems mngon par 'du byed pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:5026: sems kyi chos nyid mngon du byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5027: rnam par shes pas ni rnam par rig pa ltar chos nyid ngang gis rang rig pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5028: sems dbang po lnga dang 'dra ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5029: mig gi dbang pos rang rig rang snang gi gzugs 'dzin mthong bar byed pa mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5030: rna dbang gis rang rig rang snang gi sgra thos par byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5031: sna dbang gis rang rig rang snang gi dri tshor bar byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5032: lce dbang gis rang rig rang snang gi ro myong bar byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5033: lus dbang gis rang rig rang snang gi reg par byed pa mtshon pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5035: gzugs snang snang stong rang rig ye shes dbyer med gzugs //
NK078(tshu)001:5036: sgra brjod grags stong dbyer med rig pa rang snang sgra //
NK078(tshu)001:5037: dri zhim chos kyi dri yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:5038: ro bro de bzhin nyid kyi ro //
NK078(tshu)001:5039: reg bya rang byung ye shes reg /log rtog yul lnga ming tsam du //
NK078(tshu)001:5040: snang la rang rgyud med pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5041: rang rig rang snang spyod yul med /
NK078(tshu)001:5042: kun la de don la ltar 'byor bar gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:5045: gzugs snang stong dbyer med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:5046: sems nyid chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin dbyer med par mtshon te /
NK078(tshu)001:5048: ma bcos ye nas de ltar gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:5049: thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:5050: snang ba nyid na 'ja' tshon bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:5051: rang bzhin med par kun tu snang //
NK078(tshu)001:5052: de nyid chos sku yin par bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:5054: sgra ni dngos po med la sna tshogs su grags shing ngo bo stong pa mtshon nas /
NK078(tshu)001:5055: chos thams cad snang grags gnyis su med par shes par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5057: sgra rnams ci snyed brjod pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:5058: dngos po med la dngos po'i sgra //
NK078(tshu)001:5059: brjod dang sgra yi dngos po min //
NK078(tshu)001:5060: chos rnams sgra ltar shes par gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:5062: dri ni dngos po med la snar bsung pa mtshon nas /
NK078(tshu)001:5063: chos thams cad skye med du dri tha dad du 'phro bar shes par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5065: bsnam bya'i dri yi dngos po yang //
NK078(tshu)001:5066: yod pa ma yin kun tu bsung //
NK078(tshu)001:5067: chos rnams thams cad dri dang ldan //
NK078(tshu)001:5068: dngos med sna tshogs dri dang ldan //
NK078(tshu)001:5070: the tshom med pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:5071: chos kun de ltar shes par gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:5073: ro ni yul dang dbang po 'tshogs pas dngos po med bzhin myong ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:5074: chos rnams skye med kyi ror shes par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5076: yul dang dbang shes dngos med par //
NK078(tshu)001:5077: 'tshog pa'i ro yis dngos grub ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:5078: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK078(tshu)001:5079: gzhi rtsa med las thams cad 'byung //
NK078(tshu)001:5081: reg bya ni phung po bzhi rnam shes kyis dbang bsgyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:5082: reg bya sna tshogs myong ba ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:5084: sna tshogs su snang la rang bzhin med par shes par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5086: phung bzhi shes pas dbang bsgyur nas //
NK078(tshu)001:5087: reg bya sna tshogs myong ba ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:5088: chos kun rig pas dbang bsgyur nas //
NK078(tshu)001:5089: sna tshogs snang la dngos po med //
NK078(tshu)001:5091: sems nyon mongs pa lnga dang 'dra ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5092: 'dod chags yul dang bral mi phod pa chags pas mtshon nas /
NK078(tshu)001:5093: shes byed rig pa'i ye shes shes bya chos kyi
NK078(tshu)001:5094: dbyings dang 'du 'bral med par yang dag pa'i 'dod
NK078(tshu)001:5095: chags su rtogs dgos par mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5096: zhe sdang yul la mnar sems pa ltar sems nyid
NK078(tshu)001:5097: skye med rtogs pa mtshan ma sna tshogs la sdang
NK078(tshu)001:5098: ba'am / gang la'ang rtog pa med par yang dag pa'i zhe sdang du rtogs dgos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5099: gti mug rmongs pas bye brag mi phyed pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:5100: chos nyid bden pa dbyer med mtha' dbus tha dad med par yang dag pa'i gti mug dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5101: nga rgyal gyis khengs shing 'gying ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:5102: ye shes kyis gang zhing rgyas pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:5103: chos nyid kyis mngon par mtho ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:5104: nyon mongs pa zil gyis mnon pas yang dag pa'i nga rgyal dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5105: phrag dog gis gzhan gyi yon tan blo la mi shong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5106: de dag par mtshon nas lta spyod dman pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:5107: gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa rang rgyud pa chos nyid
NK078(tshu)001:5108: phyogs med kyi dgongs par mi tshud par yang dag
NK078(tshu)001:5109: pa'i phrag dog tu mtshon par shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5111: yang na thabs chen theg pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5112: dngos pos dngos po bcom par rtogs //
NK078(tshu)001:5113: nyon mongs dug lngas dug lnga grol //
NK078(tshu)001:5114: dug lnga rgyu rkyen ngo bos dag /rang byung ye shes rang snang phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5115: de ltar sus dran nyid kyis grol //
NK078(tshu)001:5117: sems kha dog lngas mtshon nas sems nyid ye shes lnga'i ngo bor shes par bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5118: rang gi ngo bos mtshon pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5120: dkar pos me long lta bu'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5121: ser pos mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5122: dmar pos so sor rtog pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5123: ljang gus bya ba grub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5124: mthing gas stong pa nyid kyi ye shes mtshon par shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5126: ma mthong rmongs pa thams cad la //
NK078(tshu)001:5127: ye shes mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5128: dkar dang ser dang dmar ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:5129: ljang gu la sogs nag por bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:5132: dkar po'i sems nyid nyes skyon dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5133: dmar por chags pa med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5134: ser pos yon tan rgyas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5135: ljang gus don kun rdzogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5136: nag pos mi 'gyur ba mtshon pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5138: byang chub sems nyid dag pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5139: shin tu mdog ni dkar ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:5140: de rtogs bya phyir dkar po'i mdog /chags dang chags par bya ba med //
NK078(tshu)001:5141: chags med rtogs phyir dmar po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5142: zad 'phel med pa rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5143: mdog ni gser gyi mdog tu bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:5144: phrin las kun rtogs bya ba'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5145: ljang gu'i mdog tu bstan pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5146: bsgyur du med pa rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5147: kha dog nag por bstan pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5148: de bzhin kun la shes par bya //
NK078(tshu)001:5150: la sogsa pa' sogs khung du phyogs dang dbyibs bsdus te /
NK078(tshu)001:5152: phyogs dbus ye shes lngar mtshon tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5153: rang gis ngo bos mtshon tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:5155: phyogs dbus kyi chos thams cad gsal la mi rtog pa me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5156: bzang ngan med pas mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5157: ma 'dres par so sor rtog pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5158: bya rtsol med pas bya ba grub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5159: phyogs dbus thams cad yod med kyi mtha' dang bral bas chos dbyings ye shes su mtshon pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5161: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:5162: dbyer med ngang du gnas pa la //
NK078(tshu)001:5163: ye shes rtogs pa'i don bya'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5164: phyogs dang dbus su gnas par byos //
NK078(tshu)001:5167: shar phyogs kyi nyon mongs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5168: ma rig mun pa bsal nas ye shes shar ba mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5169: nub phyogs kyis nyon mongs pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:5171: bcas pa gnyis med kyi dbyings su nub par mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5172: byang gis bdag 'dzin dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa byang bar mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5173: lho phyogs kyis gong gi yon tan de rnams rdzogs par mtshon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5174: dbus phyogs kyis chos thams cad de bzhin nyid du
NK078(tshu)001:5175: 'dus shing de nyid mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas par
NK078(tshu)001:5176: mtshon pa ste / rgyas pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:5177: de ltar ma lus thams cad la //
NK078(tshu)001:5178: thugs rje shar dang sgrib pa nus //
NK078(tshu)001:5179: rnam rtog mtshan nyid byang gyur pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:5180: de nyid yon tan rdzogs par rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:5183: nyon mongs bsal bas ye shes gsal //
NK078(tshu)001:5184: de phyir shar gyi mtshon pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5185: nyon mongs ma rig rgyu 'bras nub //
NK078(tshu)001:5186: rang byung ye shes bdag nyid dang //
NK078(tshu)001:5187: sdug bsngal gdod nas rang dag pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5188: don rtogs bya phyir byed du brjod //
NK078(tshu)001:5189: de ltar rang rig shar nub byang //
NK078(tshu)001:5190: yon tan rdzogs pa mtshon phyir lho //
NK078(tshu)001:5191: de ltar chos kun ma lus kun //
NK078(tshu)001:5192: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings su 'dus //
NK078(tshu)001:5195: chos nyid spros pa dang bral bar mtshon pa zlum po /
NK078(tshu)001:5196: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa mtshon byed gru bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:5197: mtha' rnams dbang du sdus pas na zla gam /
NK078(tshu)001:5198: sku gsungs thugs su rang snang ba mtshon pas na gru gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5200: zlum zhing rnam par ma 'phros pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5201: byang chub sems ni zlum po yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5202: nam mkha'i mtha' ltar kun la khyab //
NK078(tshu)001:5203: byang chub sems ni gru bzhi yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5204: chos rnams ma lus dbang du 'dus //
NK078(tshu)001:5205: byang chub sems ni zla gam yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5206: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5207: byang chub sems ni zur gsum yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5209: de bzhin du snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:5210: chos so cog gi chos nyid thams cad rang snang
NK078(tshu)001:5211: du mtshon par shes par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5212: de bzhin kun la shes par byos //
NK078(tshu)001:5214: gnyis pa dpe rtogs pa'i 'thad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5216: dpe de rnams kyang bsgrub bya'i don dang sgrub byed
NK078(tshu)001:5217: kyis gtan tshigs gnyis po ngo bo gcig kyang mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:5219: gtan tshigs de'i phyir mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs de
NK078(tshu)001:5220: yi chos nyid kyi don phyogs re mtshon cing rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:5221: par byed pa'o // de ni theg pa 'og ma bas dpe don tha dad du 'dod la /
NK078(tshu)001:5222: 'dir dpe don dbyer med du 'dod pas dpag go //
NK078(tshu)001:5223: de yang brgal len la spyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5228: dpe'i gtan tshigs la khyad par med par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:5229: gnyis ka snang srid mthong thos kyis mtshon pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5232: tshig tu brjod pa la ma brten par chos nyid kyi rang brda mjal ba yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:5233: 'di ni dpe bshad pa la brten nas /
NK078(tshu)001:5234: dpes mtshon cing don gtan la phab pa yin pas mi mtshungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:5235: gnyis pa bye brag la brgal len gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:5237: nam mkha' bzung du med pa ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:5240: zhes nam mkha' dang rlung gnyis la ngos bzung med par mtshon par bshad pas bldab pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:5241: khyad med du thal zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5244: mtshon bya don la khyad par med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:5245: mtshon byed kyi dpe la khyad par byung ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5246: nam mkha' ngos bzung med pa ni chos thams cad la khyab pas spyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5247: rlung gi ngos bzung med pa ni bye brag go //
NK078(tshu)001:5249: nam mkha' ni thogs par byed pa'i reg bya tsam dang bral bas ngos bzung med pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:5250: rlung gis thog par byed pa'i reg bya dang ma bral bas ngos bzung med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5251: gsum pa gang nas gtan la phab kyang don gtan la pheb pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5253: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5254: sgra mthun don dpag gis gtan tshigas brjod pa rnams
NK078(tshu)001:5255: bsgrub bya grub mtha'i ngo bo gang yin par shes
NK078(tshu)001:5256: par byed pa'i don gtan la pheb par byed pa
NK078(tshu)001:5257: la dag mnyam la sogs nges tshig gi sgo nas
NK078(tshu)001:5259: bdag nyid chen po la sogs ngo bo'i sgo nas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5260: rang spyi'i matshana nyid kyi sgo nas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5261: la sogsa pa'i khongs su rang bzhin dbyer med kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5262: de ltar gtan tshigs gi sgo gang nas gtan la
NK078(tshu)001:5263: 'bebsa kyang grub mtha' mnyam pa nyid kyi don rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:5264: par rtogs shing khong du chud par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5265: gsum pa mjug bsdus te bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5267: dang po lta ba shes pa'i dam tshig dang ldan dgos par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5269: lta ba'i ngo bo mthong ba'i dus su phyogs 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:5270: gyi zhen pa thamsa cad so sor rtogs pa'i shes
NK078(tshu)001:5271: rab kyis 'jigsa par byed pa ste phyogs med rang
NK078(tshu)001:5272: snang gi don las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig dang
NK078(tshu)001:5273: / rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba gtan la
NK078(tshu)001:5274: phab pa'i dus su rtogs thabs rnams las mi 'da'
NK078(tshu)001:5275: ba'i dam tshig dang ldan par byos /
NK078(tshu)001:5276: gnyis pa don tshig dang bral bar gor bar gyis shig par gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5278: spyir mtshon bya'i chos lhag ma ma lusa pa thamsa
NK078(tshu)001:5279: cad kyi don go bar 'byung ba'ang gang zhe na
NK078(tshu)001:5280: / mtshon byed lung man ngag gi tshig gis don
NK078(tshu)001:5281: mtshon par nus pa las don de gzhan du gud
NK078(tshu)001:5283: 'o na tshig don gcig gam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5284: tshig gi sgra de nyid kyang dngos don gyi dngos po'i ngo bo min te /
NK078(tshu)001:5285: tshig blo'i spyod yul du gyur cing don blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:5286: 'o na sgra don tha dad dam zhe na thog
NK078(tshu)001:5287: ma'i dbang btsan du mtshon bya'i don de nyid mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:5288: byed tshig gi sgras mtshon dgos pa de las gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:5289: don gud gcig na med do //
NK078(tshu)001:5290: gnas skabs dbang btsan du mtshon pa'i tshig la brten nas don gtan la phab pa'i tshe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5293: brjod pa'i sgra tsam la mi brten par /
NK078(tshu)001:5294: rang gi blo'i gting du don mnyam pa nyid ji
NK078(tshu)001:5295: lta ba bzhin yid ches par go zhing rtogs para
NK078(tshu)001:5297: gsum pa grub mtha' dang bzhi pa gol sgrib thun mong du ston pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5299: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5302: bzhi pa gol sgrib thun mong du ston pa'i lus
NK078(tshu)001:5303: rnam bzhag gi dona brjod par bya ba ni 'di
NK078(tshu)001:5304: lta ste / gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5306: dang po rtogs pa'i grub mtha' dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5308: gasnga sngags kyi theg pa ni gzhan las mchog tu
NK078(tshu)001:5309: gyur cing bla na med pa ma hi'i grub mtha'i
NK078(tshu)001:5310: don ni / 'khor 'das phyogs ris mtshan ma bzang
NK078(tshu)001:5311: ngan kun tu blo gros mi rtog par dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:5312: mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du shes bya'i chos thamsa
NK078(tshu)001:5313: cad ro gcig par shes nas /
NK078(tshu)001:5314: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun kyang mnyam pa nyid yin par rtogs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:5315: 'jig rten las 'adsa pa'i lta ba'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5316: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba'i skyon te /
NK078(tshu)001:5317: so so'i lta ba mi mthun pa tha dad par brjod cing lta bar mi bya zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:5318: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba la sogs 'og ma'i skyon
NK078(tshu)001:5319: dagga cing 'das pa'i lta ba la sogs gong ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:5320: yon tan dang du blang bar bya ba'nga med do
NK078(tshu)001:5321: // chos nyid mnyam pa nyid du rtogs par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5322: gnyis pa nor ba'i shes rab kyi dmigs bsal ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5326: spyir ni gnas lugs de ma yin pa la der
NK078(tshu)001:5327: 'dzin pa'i log rtog gi snang ba mi mthun pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:5329: ye 'am gdod ma nyid nas gzhi'i gnas lugs la
NK078(tshu)001:5330: rang rgyud can du grub nas yod pa ma yin
NK078(tshu)001:5331: te / 'o na 'khrul pa ci la byung zer na /
NK078(tshu)001:5332: 'gro ba so so'i gzung 'dzina gyi rnam par rtog pa'i bag chagsa kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:5334: nang 'dzina pa'i sems rnam rtog mang la 'brel ba
NK078(tshu)001:5335: dra ba dang 'dra bas don la sgrib par gyur
NK078(tshu)001:5336: te / sems nyid la phyogs ris ci yang grub
NK078(tshu)001:5337: pa med pa las kun rdzob tu log rtog 'khrul
NK078(tshu)001:5338: ba'i ngo bo la cir yang snang ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5339: byang ba stong pa chub pa snang ba bde gshegs
NK078(tshu)001:5340: snying po'i gzhi don las rang ngo ma shes nas
NK078(tshu)001:5342: gnyis pa gol ba'i ngo bo dngos la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5343: 'jig rten pa'i lta bar gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5346: so so'i skye bar gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5347: mu stegs pa'i lta bar gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5351: dang po 'khrul pa sgrub byed 'thad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5354: bdena par grub pa min te zhes dam bca' /
NK078(tshu)001:5355: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i gzung 'dzin ma grol ba'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5356: nyon mongs pa rang rgyud pas bcingas pa'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5357: skye rga na 'chi bzhi'i dus kyi dgras 'ajamas pa'i phyir dang mi bden cing bslu ba'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5358: mi rtag cing 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5359: 'aphagas pa'i lam thabs shes rab dang bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5360: des thar lam bstan dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5361: thar dka' ba brtson rara tshud pa'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5362: sdug bsngal myong yang gnyen pos mi 'jil te dag dka' ba dang gtan tshig dgus phyir 'khrul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:5363: gnyis pa'am rgyud lngar gol ba spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5365: rgyu mtshan dgus 'khrul ba de bas na 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:5366: kyi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi don phyogs
NK078(tshu)001:5368: nyon mongs pa dug lnga rang rgyud par 'chol nyog
NK078(tshu)001:5369: tu spyod pas 'gro ba lam rgyud lngar 'khor ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:5370: // gsum pa khams gsum lha mir gol ba bye brag tu bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5372: dang po 'dod khams su lha mir gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5375: ma byin len dang srog gcod g.yem //
NK078(tshu)001:5376: tshig gi ngag 'khyal phra ma rdzun //
NK078(tshu)001:5377: brnab sems gnod sems log par lta //
NK078(tshu)001:5378: dge bcu'i bar du gcod pa ste //
NK078(tshu)001:5379: yang dag don gyi dgra zhes bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:5380: ces gsungs pas de dag spangs te dge ba bcu po dag la gtso bor /
NK078(tshu)001:5381: ltas ngan dang du len cing /
NK078(tshu)001:5382: dge bas mtho ris dang mi dge bas ngan song
NK078(tshu)001:5383: du 'gro bas dge sdig rgyu 'bras mi mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:5384: de bas na / mi dge spang zhing dge bcu
NK078(tshu)001:5385: bsgrub pas 'dod khams kyi lha dang mi'i skye gansa
NK078(tshu)001:5386: de bas na / su skye ste / mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:5387: nyid kyi don ma rtogsa pas 'doda khamsa su 'khora
NK078(tshu)001:5388: de bas na / su skye ste / ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5389: de ltar dge bcu'i 'bras bu la lha mi bas
NK078(tshu)001:5390: de bas na / su skye ste / ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5391: mi thob na / glang chen rab 'bog gi rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:5392: de bas na / su skye ste / ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5393: mi thob na / las / srog gcod skyon spang
NK078(tshu)001:5395: khro chen h'u k+aa ra la sogs khro bcu thob par bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5397: bdag med rtogs pa lta ba'i rtsis kyis zin ma
NK078(tshu)001:5398: zin gyis khyad par yin pas mi 'gal gsungs so
NK078(tshu)001:5399: // gnyis pa gzugs khams gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5401: 'khor 'das dbyer med mnyam pa chen po'i don nyid ma rtogsa shing /
NK078(tshu)001:5402: dge bcu'i steng du byams snying rje dga' ba btang
NK078(tshu)001:5403: snyom ste tshad med pa bzhi dang bsam gtan dang
NK078(tshu)001:5404: po la mnyam gzhag dga' bde bsgom thabs la rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:5406: gnyis pa la dga' bde chu lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5407: gsum pa la dbugs 'byung rngub rlung lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5408: bzhi pa la skyon brgyad dang bral ba'i gsal thob gi zhi gnas dwangs cha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5409: de ltar rim pa bzhin du rang rang gi ting
NK078(tshu)001:5410: nge 'dzin la so sora bsgom pas bdag tu 'dzina
NK078(tshu)001:5412: rang rang gi gzugsa gsal thog gi ting nge 'dzin nyams myong rnams kun la /
NK078(tshu)001:5413: nga'am badga tu rtog cing 'dzin pa dang bcas pa
NK078(tshu)001:5414: 'di ni tshangsa gansa la sogs pa bsam gtan bzhi'i
NK078(tshu)001:5415: skye ba'i gnas ris bcu bdun du rim par skye
NK078(tshu)001:5416: ba ste / de la bsam gtan dang po la tshangs ris tshangs pa mdun na 'don /
NK078(tshu)001:5418: gnyis pa na 'od chung tshad med 'od 'od gsal ba dang gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:5419: gsum pa na dge chung tshad med dge dge rgyas dang gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:5420: bzhi pa na so so'i skye bo'i gnas gsum //
NK078(tshu)001:5432: gsum pa gzugs med du gol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5434: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid dang gzugsa med 'khor ba'i chos yin par ma rtogsa nas /
NK078(tshu)001:5437: 'du byed rnam par shes pa ste minga bazha'i phung po la bdag med par ma shes te /
NK078(tshu)001:5438: chos thams cad nam mkha' lta bu yin snyam pas nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched /
NK078(tshu)001:5441: yod min med min gyi skye mched kyi bsam gtan nyid stong pa bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5442: rig thog gi snyoms 'jug gi ting nge 'dzin la
NK078(tshu)001:5443: blo gnas par gyur pa de dag /mtho srid pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:5444: rtse mo ste kun gzhi rtog med kyi bsgom pas
NK078(tshu)001:5445: skye mched mu bzhi'i sa ru skye ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5446: gnyis pa mu stegs lta bar gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5448: mu stegs rtag lta ba ni chub pa snang ba'i phyogs su gol te /
NK078(tshu)001:5450: rang bzhin rtag par 'dod pa grags can pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5451: rig pa rtag par 'dod pa tshangs pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5452: byed pa po rtag par 'dod pa dbang phyug dang
NK078(tshu)001:5453: khyab 'jug /rdul phran rtag par 'dod pa bye brag
NK078(tshu)001:5454: pa'o // chad lta ba ni byang ba stong pa'i phyogs su gol ba yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:5456: tshe snga phyi med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5458: ma mthong ba'i 'gro ba med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5459: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas med par 'dod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5460: de ltar rtag chad gnyis kar gang zag gang gi blo zhena pa de dag ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5461: chos nyid kyi dona bcud kyi snying po gzhi don
NK078(tshu)001:5462: byang chub nyid las gol bar sangs rgyas kyis gsungsa
NK078(tshu)001:5463: so // gsum pa zhor la la bzla ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5465: khams gsum gyi sa ni 'dod khams sa gcig /gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan bzhis bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:5466: gzugs med skye mched mu bzhis bzhi dang dgu po
NK078(tshu)001:5467: de'i zhen pa dag pa'i gnyis med kyi ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:5468: ni / sa dgu'i snang ba ma spang bar gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:5469: su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngang du gsal ba'am
NK078(tshu)001:5471: gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg par gol ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5472: rgyu'i theg par gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5476: dang po nyan thos kyi theg par gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5478: bden bzhi gnyis su med pa'i don ma rtogsa pa'i nyan thos ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5479: 'khor 'das kyi chos thamsa cad la 'khor ba'i 'bras bu sdug bsngal dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5482: rgyu lam gyi bden pa dang bzhi'i dngosa po grub par yod par blta shing /
NK078(tshu)001:5483: 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spang bar byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5484: 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras mi spanga bar dang du len par byed par 'gyur bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:5485: de lta bu 'di ni bden bzhi nyan cing thos pa'i don gzhan la sgrog par byed pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:5486: thos sgrogs nyan thos kyi theg pa'i sa pa zhes bya bar gol ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:5487: de yang shes bya bden pa bzhi gtan la 'beb
NK078(tshu)001:5488: par byed pa la shes byed skad cig bcu drug
NK078(tshu)001:5489: ste / dang po sdug bsngal gyis bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5495: rkyen gyis skye zhing rang dbang med /
NK078(tshu)001:5496: mi rtag /gsum mam brgyad kyis gnod par sdug bsngal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:5497: bdag gi lta ba'i mi mthun phyogs stong pa /
NK078(tshu)001:5498: lnga phung bdag tu bltar med stong pa nyid /
NK078(tshu)001:5500: gnyis pa kun 'byung gi bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5501: rgyu kun 'byung rkyen gyi rnam pa rab tu skye ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5503: de rgyu las nyon phung po'i sa bon ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:5504: de las rgyu drug khams gsum 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5505: bag chags brtas shing rnam par smin byed rkyen //
NK078(tshu)001:5506: rgyu rkyen 'brel nas khams gsum rab tu skyes //
NK078(tshu)001:5513: rgyu rkyen bral bas phung khams 'jig phyir 'gog /sdug bsngal med pas gsum mi 'byung zhib gnas /
NK078(tshu)001:5514: phyis kyang khams gsum sdug bsngal bral gya nom /
NK078(tshu)001:5515: bde bar phyin te skyon las nges par 'byung //
NK078(tshu)001:5517: bzhi pa lam gyi bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5523: 'phags pa'i sar zhugs mya ngan 'das 'phro lam //
NK078(tshu)001:5524: 'khrul ba'i gnyen po tshad mar gyur phyir rigs //
NK078(tshu)001:5525: phyin ci log spang yang dag thob phyir sgrub //
NK078(tshu)001:5526: 'khor bar mi skye 'das la nges par 'byin //
NK078(tshu)001:5528: gnyis pa rang sangs rgyas kyi theg par gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5530: las gsum dang nyon mongas pa lngas rten 'brel gyi chos thamsa cad la /
NK078(tshu)001:5531: gsang sngags ltar mnyam pa chen po'i dona nyid du ngo mi shes shing /
NK078(tshu)001:5532: nang rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5557: de ltar phyi nang gi rten 'brel lugs 'byung ldog gnyis yod par 'dzin cing /
NK078(tshu)001:5558: de yang lugs 'byung dgags bya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5559: lugs ldog bsgrub byar byed na /
NK078(tshu)001:5560: de lta bu'i gang zag 'di ni rang sangsa rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:5561: kyi theg pa'i sa zhes bya bar gol ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:5562: no // gsum pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg par gol ba de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5564: dang po byang chub sems dpa' rang gi 'dod gzhung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5566: bden gnyis dbyer med mnyam pa'i don nyid blta bas mi shes shing /
NK078(tshu)001:5567: de yang kun rdzob kyi bden pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:5568: so so'i skye bo'i snang ba log pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5569: 'phags pa'i rjes thob sgyu mar snang ba yang dag pa'i kun rdzob dang gnyis so //
NK078(tshu)001:5571: dbang por snang zhing don byed nus pa yang dag pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5572: snang zhing don byed mi nus pa log pa'i kun rdzob bo //
NK078(tshu)001:5573: don dam pa'i bden pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5574: blo rigs shes kyis don dam btags pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5575: 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag gi ye shes kyi yul du gyur pa mtshan nyid pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5576: de ltar bden pa gnyis tha dad du 'byed par byed pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5577: de yang don dam la phra ba chos kyi bdag dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5578: rag pa gang zag gi bdag dang gnyis ka med par 'dod pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:5579: de lta bu'i gang zag 'di ni byang chub sems
NK078(tshu)001:5580: dpa'i sa pa zhes bya bar gol ba yin no
NK078(tshu)001:5581: // gnyis pa de las gsang sngags thabs kyi theg
NK078(tshu)001:5582: pa khyad par du dpag pa de la gnyis te
NK078(tshu)001:5583: // / bden gnyis kyi khyad par dpags tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5584: lta spyod dbyer med kyi dpag tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:5587: dang po byang sems kyi kun rdzob kyi 'dod gzhung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5589: theg dman nyan rang las 'phags pa'i bla na med
NK078(tshu)001:5590: pa'i theg pa chen po'i nang nas byang chub sems
NK078(tshu)001:5591: dpa' ni / chos nyid don dam skye med stong
NK078(tshu)001:5592: pa'i ngang du ni yod med la sogs pa'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:5593: thams cad dbye ru med pas dbyer med de kun
NK078(tshu)001:5594: rdzob rgyu tsam du snang ba thamsa cad la /
NK078(tshu)001:5595: dngos por snang zhing don byed nus pa yang dag pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5596: snang yang don byed mi nus pa ste ma dag pa log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis kar 'dzin no //
NK078(tshu)001:5597: gnyis pa gsang sngags kyi bden gnyis kyi 'dod gzhung gi dpag tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:5599: nyon mongs pa la spyad pa ltar snang yang lta
NK078(tshu)001:5600: sgom gyi stobs kyis mi 'ching ba'i gsang sngags thabsa
NK078(tshu)001:5601: mkhas kyi theg pa rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa
NK078(tshu)001:5603: rnam par byang ba mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5604: kun nas nyon mongs zhing sdug bsngal 'khor ba'i chos daga /
NK078(tshu)001:5605: don dam par dkor bdun du dbyer med yin pa lta ci smos /
NK078(tshu)001:5606: phung khams skye mched kun rdzob kyi chos rnams rig
NK078(tshu)001:5607: pa ye shes sgyu ma nyid du yang sku dang
NK078(tshu)001:5608: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du 'dod pas dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:5609: pa yin te / de ltar na byang sems dang
NK078(tshu)001:5610: ma h+aa yo ga gnyis lta ba mtho da man
NK078(tshu)001:5611: gyi khyad par ni da tsam mo //
NK078(tshu)001:5612: de'i phyir gsang sngags thabs kyi theg pa khyad par du dpag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5613: gnyis pa lta spyod dbyer med kyis dpags tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5615: dang po mdor bstan pa dang drang /
NK078(tshu)001:5616: nang pa thabsa kyi theg pa gsang sngags kyi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5617: de dang ya mi bral ba'i spyod pa gnyis gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas chen po ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5618: bla na med pa'i theg pa byang sems kyi lta spyod las khyad par du 'phagsa pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:5619: ji ltar 'phags zhe na 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5620: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5622: dang po lta ba chos kun dbyer med mngon sum du rtogs pa'i khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5624: byang sems dbu ma'i don dam stong pa phyogs gcig pa yin pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:5625: 'dir ma h+aa yo ga'i don dam rnam kun mchog
NK078(tshu)001:5626: ldan gyi stong pa chen po'i ngang du ni 'phags
NK078(tshu)001:5628: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga dbyings ye
NK078(tshu)001:5629: shes gnyis te bdun lhun gyis grub pas 'phags pa
NK078(tshu)001:5630: yin no // byang sems dbu ma'i kun rdzob ni
NK078(tshu)001:5631: dag ma dag dang 'khrul ma 'khrul du 'dzin la
NK078(tshu)001:5632: yin no // / 'dir ma h+aa'i kun rdzob tsam
NK078(tshu)001:5633: du ni phung khams skye mched thams cad sku dang
NK078(tshu)001:5634: ye shes kyi ngang du bzang ngan med par mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:5635: zhing rdzogsa par 'dod pas dpags so //
NK078(tshu)001:5636: chos thams cad bden pa dbyer med yang dag pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:5637: don rtogs pa'i skyes bu mchog gam dam par gyur
NK078(tshu)001:5638: pa yis / de ltar don dam kun rdzob de
NK078(tshu)001:5639: gnyis tshig la tha dad kyang don la dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:5640: par phyir ci ma log par yang dag pa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:5641: du blos gting phyin par rab tu rtogsa pas /
NK078(tshu)001:5642: byang sems kyi bden gnyis tha dad du 'dod pa las dpags pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5643: gnyis pa spyod pa mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos shing cir yang ston pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5645: de ltar bden pa dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:5646: ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du spyod pa'i bye brag
NK078(tshu)001:5647: mi 'gag pa'i thabs kyis don las mi 'da' ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:5648: phyag rgya / spyod pa spang blang dgag sgrub can
NK078(tshu)001:5649: las khyad par du gyur pas chen por ston pas
NK078(tshu)001:5650: phyag rgya / dpags so // gsum pa lta spyod
NK078(tshu)001:5651: gnyis med rnam dag chen por bstan pa la gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:5652: phyag rgya / dpags so // te / bgrang /
NK078(tshu)001:5653: dang po ngo bo thabs shes gnyis med rnam dag tu bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5655: spyod pa thabsa dang lta ba shes rab gnyis su
NK078(tshu)001:5656: med cing rnam par dag pas byang sems kyi lta
NK078(tshu)001:5657: spyod tha dad las dpags so //
NK078(tshu)001:5658: gnyis pa de nyid gnyis med rnam dag chen por la bzla ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5660: kun rdzob tu phung po 'byung ba rnam shes thamsa cad rnam par dag ces bya ba de yang /
NK078(tshu)001:5661: theg 'og ltar kun rdzob kyi dngosa po spang 'geg
NK078(tshu)001:5662: sbyangs pa'i thabs kyis bsal nas dag pa ma yin
NK078(tshu)001:5663: te / 'o na ji ltar zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5664: kun rdzob snang ba rdo ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5665: spyod pa rdo ba'i dus nyid na sku dang ye shes su rnam par dag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5666: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir na kun rdzob kyi snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:5667: rdzun pa kho na yang mi blta ba ste snang
NK078(tshu)001:5668: ba mi spang ba'i phyir dpags pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5669: gnyis pa sngags phyi par gol ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5671: dang po kri yar gol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5673: 'khor 'das gnyis med mnyam pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i don ma shes pas /
NK078(tshu)001:5674: dona dam du skye 'gag gcig dang du ma'i mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:5675: bzhi'i dri ma dag pa chos nyid tsam de nyid
NK078(tshu)001:5678: sor rtog /bya grub ye shesa bzhira shar ba'i yon
NK078(tshu)001:5679: tan la kun rdzob rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK078(tshu)001:5680: snang yang / nyams su blangs dus lha ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:5681: sems dpa' la dngos grub re ba'i tshul gyis mdun
NK078(tshu)001:5683: bden gnyis res sgom byed cing khrus dang gtsang sbra'i
NK078(tshu)001:5684: bya ba las kyi sgo nas 'bras bu grub par
NK078(tshu)001:5685: 'dod pa kri ya'i sa ste der gol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5686: gnyis pa yo gar gol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5688: 'khor 'das dbyer med lhun grub mnyam pa chen po'i don ma mthonga zhing ma rtogs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:5689: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun don dam sems nyid rang
NK078(tshu)001:5690: bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i ngang du rnam par dag
NK078(tshu)001:5691: ste / de rtog pa'i ye shes kyi byin rlabsa
NK078(tshu)001:5692: kun rdzob tu rigs lnga la sogs pa'i rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:5693: dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor lha so bdun la sogs par
NK078(tshu)001:5695: lha rtog gam dkar gsum la sogs dam rdzas la
NK078(tshu)001:5696: blanga dor byed cing dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gtso
NK078(tshu)001:5699: gsum pa don ma nor bar dmigs nas grub mtha' blangs pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5701: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5703: gong du bstan pa de ltar gzhal bya 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:5704: kyi dngosa po gtan tshig gis brtag cing rnal 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:5705: pa'i shes rab kyis mig phyes te bsal nas /
NK078(tshu)001:5706: rang gzhung ma nor ba'i don gyi grub mtha'a dmigs nas blangs bar bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5707: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5708: gsang sngags bla med kyi grub mtha' gnyams pa nyid ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5709: lta ba yod med phyogs rer 'dzin pas mnyam pa nyid las gol tshul dpe dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5710: yod med sgra tsam du brtag tu rung yang /
NK078(tshu)001:5711: don la yod med kyi mtha' las grol tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5712: de skyes bu mchog gi spyod yul yin pas rtogs par gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5715: dang po lta ba rtogs pa'i ngo bo la 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:5716: 'das kyi lta ba thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:5719: gong du bstan pa'i 'das pa'i theg pa mthona po gsang sngags pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5720: dman pa theg dman thamsa cad kyi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5722: mu stegs rtag chad gnyis te 'jiga rten pa'i lta ba ma lus pa thamsa cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:5723: don rang byung gi yeshes chen po rtogs pa'i ngo bor rab tu brtag na /
NK078(tshu)001:5724: don dam par lta ba dang theg pa de dag
NK078(tshu)001:5725: rang bzhin cir yang grub pa med pa las kun
NK078(tshu)001:5726: rdzob tu lta ba dang theg pa de dag cir
NK078(tshu)001:5728: de ltar lta ba dang theg pa'i rim pa ji ltar snang yang /
NK078(tshu)001:5729: de dag gi rang bzhin chos nyid mnyam pa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:5730: kyis dbyingsa las nyams shing g.yos pa med pas na
NK078(tshu)001:5731: snang stong mnyam pa nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:5732: gnyis pa mnyam dus lta ba phyogs 'dzin gyi rtog pa med tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5734: 'o na chos nyid mnyam pa nyid bya ba'i don nyid rang ji lta bu zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5735: mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin phyogs gcig tu gang du yang ngos bzung du med de /
NK078(tshu)001:5736: phyogs med du chos kun tu 'char ba yin la
NK078(tshu)001:5737: mnyam pa de'i ngo bo snang stong phyogs rer 'di
NK078(tshu)001:5739: de la manyama pa dang mi mnyam pa nyid du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa gang yang med do //
NK078(tshu)001:5740: gsum pa de bzhin don byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid yin par bstan pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5742: dang po byang chub sems la 'gro 'ong med cing rang rig pa yin par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5744: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi don byang chub kyi
NK078(tshu)001:5745: sems yin no zhes tshig tu brjod pa'i don ni
NK078(tshu)001:5747: dang po gang nas kyang ma 'ongsa pas skye ba med pa /
NK078(tshu)001:5748: tha ma gara yang mi 'gro bas 'gags pa med pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:5749: da ltar gang na'ang mi gnas te yul yul can
NK078(tshu)001:5750: gyi rtogsa pa gang yang med pas rang rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:5752: dus gsum gyi sangsa rgyas dang khams gsum gyi semsa
NK078(tshu)001:5753: can thams cad rang rig pa byang chub kyi semsa
NK078(tshu)001:5754: la gansa pa'o // gnyis pa de dmigs su med tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5756: byang chub semsa rnams thamsa cad kyis don ni snang
NK078(tshu)001:5757: stong la sogs pa phyogs re ba ngos bzung dang
NK078(tshu)001:5758: bral bas nyi ma'i snying po ltar shin tu blos
NK078(tshu)001:5759: brtag par daka'a zhing rgya mtsho ltar gting zab pas
NK078(tshu)001:5760: / dngos po'i chos su ma dmigsa pas byang /
NK078(tshu)001:5761: dngos med kyi chos su mi dmigsa pas chub /
NK078(tshu)001:5762: tha dad kyi chos su dmigsa bu med pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:5763: gsum pa dbyer med byang chub sems ni chos thams cad kyi ngo bo yin par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5765: semsa nyid de ni don ci lta bu zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5766: byang chub de nyid ni semsa nyid rang snang ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:5767: des na semsa dang byang chub gnyis su med cing dbyera med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:5768: khams gsum 'khor ba'i semsa can lhag gam ma lus pa thamsa cad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5769: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams thamsa cad sems chos nyid byang chub sems 'ba' zhig yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:5770: gnyis pa lta ba yod med phyogs rer 'dzin pas
NK078(tshu)001:5771: mnyam pa nyid las gol tshul dpe dang bcas pa
NK078(tshu)001:5773: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid yin
NK078(tshu)001:5774: pa la 'khor 'das kyi lta ba phyogs re'i dngos
NK078(tshu)001:5775: por yod pa las btsal na mnyam pa nyid la
NK078(tshu)001:5778: dge sdig gi las dngos po yod par 'dzin nas 'dod khams pas sgro btags /
NK078(tshu)001:5779: mi g.yo ba'i las yod par 'dzin nas sgom pas khams gong ma gnyis kyis sgro btags /
NK078(tshu)001:5780: rtag chad yod par 'dzin nas mu stegs pas sgro btags /
NK078(tshu)001:5781: bden bzhi'i dngos por yod par 'dzin nas nyan thos kyis sgro btags /
NK078(tshu)001:5782: rten 'brel rgyu 'bras lug 'byung ldog yod par 'dzin nas rang rgyal gyis sgro btags /
NK078(tshu)001:5783: bden pa gnyis tha dad du 'dod nas byang sems kyis sgro btags /
NK078(tshu)001:5784: don dam chos nyid dang kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor res bsgom byed nas kri yas sgro btags /
NK078(tshu)001:5785: chos kun rnam par dag pa'i ye shes kyi byin
NK078(tshu)001:5786: rlabs las rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du sprul
NK078(tshu)001:5787: par 'dod na yo ga'i sgro btagsa pa dang brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:5789: phyogs med du 'khor 'das kyi lta ba thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:5790: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du gcig kyang rang gi
NK078(tshu)001:5791: lta ba las gzhan pa'i phyogs thams cad med pa
NK078(tshu)001:5792: las batsala na mnyam pa nyid la skur pa btab
NK078(tshu)001:5793: pa yin te / gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5794: dug lnga rang gzhan gi lta ba mi mnyam pa'i rgyud lnga'i sems can gyis bskur ba btab /
NK078(tshu)001:5795: dge sdig dang gzhan gyi lta ba mi mnyams pas
NK078(tshu)001:5796: 'dod khams kyis tshad med dang bsam gata na dang
NK078(tshu)001:5797: mi mnyam pas gzugs khams kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:5798: skye mched bzhi dang mi mnyam pas gzugs med kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:5799: rtag chad dang mi mnyam pas mu stegs kyis bden
NK078(tshu)001:5800: bzhi dang mi mnyam pas nyan thos kyis rten 'brel
NK078(tshu)001:5802: rang rgyal gyis bden gnyis dang mi mnyam pas byang
NK078(tshu)001:5803: sems kyi gnyis med mnyam par ma shes pas kri
NK078(tshu)001:5804: yas lhun grub mnyam par ma shes par yo gas
NK078(tshu)001:5805: skur pa btab pa dang bcu'i gnas su ltung ngo
NK078(tshu)001:5806: // de ltar yod pa dang med pa gnyis las btsal bar byas na /
NK078(tshu)001:5807: sgro skur kyi grangs de snyed kyi skyon gyis mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:5808: pa nyid kyi don mi rtogs nas lung ma bstan
NK078(tshu)001:5810: yod med gnyis las btsal na skyon yod pa de'i
NK078(tshu)001:5811: phyir dper na nam mkha' yod ces bya ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:5812: med ces bya bar gang zag blun po rnams ni
NK078(tshu)001:5814: yang na sgro skur lung ma bstan gyi skyon gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:5817: sems nyid de yul du grub pa med pa las
NK078(tshu)001:5818: dngos po rang ga mar sgro 'dog pa skye bo
NK078(tshu)001:5819: dang gcig /sems nyid stong pa la ril por sgro
NK078(tshu)001:5820: 'dog pa mu stegs rtag pa dang gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:5821: sems gzung 'dzin dang bral ba la rdul dang skad
NK078(tshu)001:5822: cig gi rdzas rig tu sgro 'dog pa nyan thos
NK078(tshu)001:5823: pa dang gsum / skad cig gcig gi rten 'brel
NK078(tshu)001:5824: gyi rdzas su sgro 'dog pa rang rgyal dang bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:5825: pa dang gsum / / rang rig ye shes skad cig mar sgro 'dog pa sems tsam dang lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:5826: kun rdzob sgyu ma'am ma skyes stong par sgro 'dog
NK078(tshu)001:5827: pa dbu ma dang drug rnam dag gi yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:5828: rigs su rje 'bangs su sgro 'dog pa kri ya
NK078(tshu)001:5829: dang bdun / ma skyes de bzhin nyid dam byin
NK078(tshu)001:5830: rlabs sgro 'dog pa yo ga da nga brgyad do
NK078(tshu)001:5831: dang bdun / // gnyis pa skur btab bcu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5832: ma nor ba'i don la bskur ba skye bo dang
NK078(tshu)001:5833: gcig /bdag med pa la bskur ba mu stegs bdag
NK078(tshu)001:5835: nges par bskur ba nyan thos dang gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:5836: phyi nang ma spyod yul med pa la bskur ba rang rgyal dang bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:5837: mtshan nyid la bskur ba sems tsam pa dang lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:5838: rang bzhin la bskur ba rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu
NK078(tshu)001:5839: ma dang drug /ngo bo nyid la bskur ba mdo
NK078(tshu)001:5840: sde spyod pa'i dbu ma ba dang bdun /
NK078(tshu)001:5841: blang dor med pa la bskur ba dbu ma gzhung phyi mo ba dang brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:5842: bdag nyid chen po la bskur ba kri ya dang dgu /
NK078(tshu)001:5843: lhun gyis grub pa la bskur ba yo ga dang bcu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5844: de yang man ngag rim pa'i phreng ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:5846: so so'i skye bo bskur ba can //
NK078(tshu)001:5847: dngos po yang dag 'dzin byed pa //
NK078(tshu)001:5848: ma nor don la bskur ba yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5849: srid pa'i 'khor lo bcu gnyis rgyud grangs //
NK078(tshu)001:5851: bdag med don la skur byed cing //
NK078(tshu)001:5852: bden pa gnyis la bskur byed pa //
NK078(tshu)001:5853: rtag chad lta bas grol 'dod pa //
NK078(tshu)001:5854: drug gis lta ba bdun gyis bslus //
NK078(tshu)001:5856: byang chub sems la bskur ba ni //
NK078(tshu)001:5857: sde pa bco brgyad nor lta bas //
NK078(tshu)001:5858: yul sems phye ste spang drags pa //
NK078(tshu)001:5859: thar pa chen po'i gegs su che //
NK078(tshu)001:5861: rang byung ye shes ma rtogs pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5862: nang yod phyi rol stong byed cing //
NK078(tshu)001:5863: bden pa gnyis la bskur byed pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5865: rgyu 'bras gnyis med bskur ba btab //
NK078(tshu)001:5867: gang dag dam pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:5868: skad cig 'dod pas de kun rdzob //
NK078(tshu)001:5869: 'dod pas mtshan nyid bskur pa btab /
NK078(tshu)001:5871: rang bzhin sangs rgyas ma mthong bas //
NK078(tshu)001:5872: 'khrul snang kun rdzob dam par brtag /gang 'dod rang bzhin bskur 'debs pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5873: spyan bzang lam du btsud dang mtshungs //
NK078(tshu)001:5875: skye med ye shes mthong ba med //
NK078(tshu)001:5876: kun rdzob rdzun pa tsam lta bas //
NK078(tshu)001:5877: rdzun phyir snang ba yod ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5878: dam pa spros bral de mi 'dod //
NK078(tshu)001:5879: ye nas ngo bo nyid la bskur //
NK078(tshu)001:5881: bsod nams rgyu la rag lus phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5882: ci yang rtog med sems nyid las //
NK078(tshu)001:5883: de phyir bsod nams byin rlabs rnams //
NK078(tshu)001:5884: mi snang de bzhin nyid la bskur //
NK078(tshu)001:5885: blang dor med pa bskur 'debs pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5886: de don nam yang mthong ba min //
NK078(tshu)001:5888: kun gzhi ye shes ma rtogs te //
NK078(tshu)001:5889: ye shes gzhi mthong spros bral bas //
NK078(tshu)001:5890: mthong na bya rtsol yod ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5891: bdag nyid chen po dag la bskur //
NK078(tshu)001:5893: lnga po mngon par byang chub pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5894: snang stong res slob grogs blta'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5896: lhun gyis grub pa'i don la bskur //
NK078(tshu)001:5897: gang gi de ltar gnas bzhin du //
NK078(tshu)001:5898: de mi 'dod pas phyogs khyer nas //
NK078(tshu)001:5900: bskur pa'i bskur pa mtha' mar ltung //
NK078(tshu)001:5902: gsum pa lung ma bstan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:5903: mun pa'i shes pa lung du ma bstan pa so so'i skye bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5904: log sred lung du ma bstan pa rtag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5905: chad pa lung du ma bstan pa chad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5906: rdzas rigs kyis lung du ma bstan pa nyon mongs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5907: yul stong gi lung du ma bstan pa rang rgyal dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5908: skad cig gi lung du ma bstan pa sems tsam pa dad /
NK078(tshu)001:5909: rnal 'byor lung du ma bstan pa dbu ma spyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5910: rnal 'byor lung du ma bstan pa bye brag rnal 'byor spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5911: bya ba'i lung du ma bstan pa kri ya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5912: brgyud pa'i lung du ma bstan pa yo ga'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5914: dngos po sgro 'dog yang dag bskur byed pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5915: skye bos sgro skur gdod nas bral //
NK078(tshu)001:5916: de phyir lung du ma bstan pa //
NK078(tshu)001:5917: dang po'i cha shas 'di la med //
NK078(tshu)001:5919: rtag pa'i sgro skur med pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5920: lung du ma bstan gnyis pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5921: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid mthong nas //
NK078(tshu)001:5922: skye 'jig bral phyir chad pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:5923: lung du ma bstan gang yang med //
NK078(tshu)001:5924: yul sems gnyis su mi lta bas //
NK078(tshu)001:5925: rdzas rigs lung du ma bstan med //
NK078(tshu)001:5926: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5927: yul stong lung du ma bstan min //
NK078(tshu)001:5928: rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas te //
NK078(tshu)001:5929: ye shes rgyu mtshan bral ba'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5930: skad cig lung du ma bstan med //
NK078(tshu)001:5931: kun rdzob don dam gnyis med pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5932: rnam par lung du ma bstan med //
NK078(tshu)001:5933: sems kyi chos nyid ma shes pas //
NK078(tshu)001:5934: snang stong lung du ma bstan med //
NK078(tshu)001:5935: bdag nyid chen po rtogs pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5936: bya ba'i lung du ma bstan med //
NK078(tshu)001:5937: snang stong dus gcig rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:5938: brgyud pa'i lung du ma bstan med //
NK078(tshu)001:5940: 'o na don ma gyur pa grub mtha'i skabs su
NK078(tshu)001:5941: sgro skur lung ma bstan gyi skyon gsum byung ba
NK078(tshu)001:5942: 'di nor bsal du 'dug pas skabs 'chol ba'i skyon
NK078(tshu)001:5943: dang gcig 'di btsal thabs su byas na snga ma
NK078(tshu)001:5944: rtogs thabs gtan tshig rnams dang bldab skyon du 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:5945: ba dang gnyis / gtan tshig dang gol sgrib gdar
NK078(tshu)001:5946: sha bcad pa gnyis don med pa'i skyon dang gsum
NK078(tshu)001:5947: ba dang gnyis / du 'gyur ro // zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5951: gol sa bcad pas rang gzhung shugs la rtogs par 'gyur ba'i dgos ched do //
NK078(tshu)001:5952: gnyis pa ni bldab skyon med de /
NK078(tshu)001:5954: gsum pa ni snga ma gnyis la don yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:5955: snga ma gnyis la brten nas mtha' gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:5956: chod par 'gyur ba'i dgos ched yod do //
NK078(tshu)001:5957: gsum pa yod med sgra tsam brtag tu rung yang
NK078(tshu)001:5958: don la don yod med las grol tshul la gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:5962: de yang gang zag nam mkha'i mtshan nyid la mkhas
NK078(tshu)001:5963: pa rnams kyis nam mkha'i rang bzhin yod med la
NK078(tshu)001:5964: sogs pa'i mtha' las grol ba yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:5965: kun gyi go skabs 'byed pas med par kho na yang mi 'dzin la /
NK078(tshu)001:5966: kha dog dbyibs su ma grub pas yod pa kho nar yang mi 'dzin te /
NK078(tshu)001:5967: yod med gnyis kyi mtha' kun dang bral ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5968: gnyis pa don de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5972: de bzhin du semsa nyid rig rtsal 'gag med du
NK078(tshu)001:5973: cir yang snang bas yod pa kun gyi ngo bo
NK078(tshu)001:5974: / snang dus rang rgyud can du ma grub pas med pa kun gyi ngo bo yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:5975: yod med gnyis tha dad med de gnyis su med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:5976: snang stong phyogs re'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i phyir du
NK078(tshu)001:5977: yod med la sogs pa sgra tsam du brjod du
NK078(tshu)001:5978: rung mod kyis / don semsa nyid kyi ngo bo
NK078(tshu)001:5979: la snang stong phyogs re ba 'di kho na'o zhes
NK078(tshu)001:5980: rung mod kyis / rgyal bas kyang / gzhan la
NK078(tshu)001:5981: bstan cing rang gis brtag par dka' ba de la
NK078(tshu)001:5982: rung mod kyis / rgyal bas kyang / / yod
NK078(tshu)001:5983: ces bya ba dang med ces bya ba la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:5984: pa brjod pa ci byar yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:5985: tha dad med cing yod med mnyam pa nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:5986: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:5988: dang po dgos chen gyi sgo nas de kho na nyid kyi ming gi rnam grangs bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5990: 'o na sems nyid ces tshig tu mtshon pa la dgos pa med dam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:5991: semsa nyid ye gdod ma nyid nas phyogs zhen dang bral bas sangsa la /
NK078(tshu)001:5992: ye shes phyogs med du rgyas pa'i phyir sangs rgyas su gnas pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:5993: de ltar mina par 'dzin pa'i lta ba ngan pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:5994: zhen pa bzlog pa'i dgos ched yong ba'i phyir sangs
NK078(tshu)001:5995: rgyas zhes bla dwags tsam du brjod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5996: gnyis 'dzin gyi zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir gnyis med dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5997: bzang ngan dang tha dad kyi zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5998: sems can gyi zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir sangsa rgyas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:5999: gzhan du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir badga nyid chen po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6000: rtsol sgrub kyi zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6001: mu mthar 'dzin pa bzlog phyir mu mtha' med pa chos kyi dbyingsa su dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6002: kun nas nyon mongs pa 'dzin pa bzlog phyir byang chub dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6003: chos can du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa bzlog phyir chos nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6004: dngos 'dzin bzlog phyir stong pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6005: yid yul du 'dzin pa bzlog phyir bsam pa las 'adsa pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6006: bcos pa'i 'dzin pa bzlog phyir ma bcos de bzhina nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6007: rgyu rkyen du 'dzin pa bzlog phyir skye 'agga med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6008: phyogs re'i mtha' 'dzin bzlog phyir mtha' bral dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6009: 'khor ba'i 'dzin pa bzlog phyir mya ngan las 'adsa pa dang /
