NK078(tshu)001:6010: 'khrul rtog gis bcing bar 'dzin pa bzlog phyir rang grol ba la sogsa su /
NK078(tshu)001:6011: don sems nyid phyogs med las rgyu mtshan phyogs re
NK078(tshu)001:6012: nas gang yang mi 'gag par gdul bya'i ngo la
NK078(tshu)001:6013: bla dwagsa tsam du brjod pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:6014: gnyis pa don tshig la mi gnas par la bzla ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6016: gshis ye gdong ma nas tshig gi dngos po sa
NK078(tshu)001:6017: mtshon pa'i don dam tshig la mi gnas pas tshig
NK078(tshu)001:6019: ci'i phyir zhe na semsa nyid de ni gong gi
NK078(tshu)001:6020: tha snyad bla dwags su du btags pa kun gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6022: tha snyad de dag sgra ru brjod cing tshig tu bsnyad du ci yod de med la /
NK078(tshu)001:6023: don phyogs gcig 'di kho na'o zhes gzhan la bstan
NK078(tshu)001:6024: cing rang gis blos brtagsa daka'a ba rgyal bas gsungsa
NK078(tshu)001:6025: so // bzhi pa de skyes bu mchog gi spyod yul yin pas rtogs gcig par gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6027: 'o na sems nyid de de sus kyang rtogs par mi 'gyur ram zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:6028: rdzogs pa'i sangs la gzung 'dzin gyi skyon gyis ma gos pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:6029: ma chagas pa ste dper na me tog pad+ma 'dam nas skyes kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:6031: 'dra ba'i thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes can rgyal ba kun gyi spyod yul 'ba' zhig yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6032: gdul bya lam pa man chad la kun dang spyod
NK078(tshu)001:6033: yul thun monga du gyur pa don de ma yina
NK078(tshu)001:6034: pa'i phyir / de ni bden mthong chen po'i 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:6035: bu'i sa pa mngon sum du byas pa da bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:6036: gshegs pa kho ni'i spyod yul du gyur pa'a //
NK078(tshu)001:6037: te zhes pa lhag ma can gyi tshig ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6038: 'o na gzhan lam pa sus kyang mi rtogs sam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:6040: gsang sngags kyi rigs dang ldan pa'i skyes bu shes
NK078(tshu)001:6041: rab can gyi blo mchog rtsal dang ldan pa rang
NK078(tshu)001:6043: spyang po'i dbang po rnon po rab tu gyur pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6044: zag med kyi rig 'dzin dang zag bcas kyi gang
NK078(tshu)001:6046: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir skal ldan blo rtsal can lam pa ba rnams kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6047: brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6048: lnga pa ngo bo dang rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6050: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6052: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba'i ngo bo dngos
NK078(tshu)001:6053: dang ming grangs dang don gyi rnam grangsa dang don
NK078(tshu)001:6054: gyi rnam grangsa bstan pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:6055: lta ba'i ngo bo ngos bzung ba'i rim pas rnam grangs rnam par phye ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:6056: gnyis pa rgyas bshad de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6057: lta ba ngo bo'i rnam grangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6061: dang po ngo bo dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6063: mdor bstan gyis snga ma lta ba'i ngo bo rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:6064: nus pa kha cig rang rig pa'i mngon sum la
NK078(tshu)001:6065: rnam shes tshogs drug gam tshogs brgyad nyid ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:6067: gyur tshul ni shes rab kyi rnam shes drug dbang
NK078(tshu)001:6068: po drug yul drug dbyer med kyi tshul du gnas
NK078(tshu)001:6069: su gyur par brjod pa lta ba'i ngo bor brjod
NK078(tshu)001:6070: pa'i don ni ngesa par ma nor bar rang rig
NK078(tshu)001:6071: pas mngon sum du mthonga ba de yang /
NK078(tshu)001:6072: tshogs drug ye shes lnga ru gasla ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:6073: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi ngo bo 'ong ye shes lnga de nyid yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6074: de yang ma 'dres par rkyang bka' du ngo sprad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6075: yongs rdzogs lhun grub tu ngo sprad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6077: rnal ma don gyi kun gzhi chos dbyings ye shes su rtogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6078: sbyor ba 'dun pa'i kun gzhi me long ye shes su dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6079: nyon yid mnyam pa yid kyi ye shes su dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6080: yid so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6081: sgo lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su rtogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6083: rnam shes tshogs brgyad rang bzhin med pa blo 'das su rtogs pa chos dbyings ye shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6084: de nyid kyi ngo bo la tshogs brgyad yul dang
NK078(tshu)001:6085: bcas pa gsal la 'dzin pa med pa me long
NK078(tshu)001:6087: de ltar gsal stong snga phyi tha dad che chung bzang ngan med pa mnyam nyid ye shesa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6088: de'i ngang du ma 'dres pa cir yang rang snang ba'i so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6089: de nyid la bdag gzhan gyi bya btsal med par
NK078(tshu)001:6090: lhun gyis grub pa ni bya ba grub pa'i ye
NK078(tshu)001:6093: de nyid ye shes lnga rdzogs te //
NK078(tshu)001:6094: stong pa'i ye shes dngos po med //
NK078(tshu)001:6095: me long ye shes rtog pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:6096: mnyam nyid ye shes che chung med //
NK078(tshu)001:6097: so sor rtog pa ma 'dres gsal //
NK078(tshu)001:6098: bya ba nan tan mthar phyin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6100: gnyis pa rnam grangs de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6101: tshogs drug lta ba'i ngo bo'i rnam grangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6102: tshogs brgyad lta ba'i ngo bo'i rnam grangs dngos po /
NK078(tshu)001:6105: dang po sgo lnga yul med rang gsal gyi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6111: lus kyi dbang po ste lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6112: dmigsa bya gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6113: dmigs byed mig gi rnam par shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6117: lus kyi rnam par shes pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6118: de ltar lnga gsum bco lnga pa rnams rang rig
NK078(tshu)001:6119: tu dbyer med par rtogs pa'i phyir rang snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:6120: yin te / gtan tshig de bas na sgo lnga
NK078(tshu)001:6121: yul dang yul can med par rang rig par gsal
NK078(tshu)001:6122: yin te / bar rtogs pa'o // gnyis pa yid
NK078(tshu)001:6123: kyi shes pa dbyings rigs dbyer med kyi lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:6124: yin te / bar rtogs pa'o // dang / drang /
NK078(tshu)001:6125: shes bya chos kyi dbyingsa dang shes byed rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:6126: yid byed pa po gnyis rang byung ye shes kyi
NK078(tshu)001:6127: ngang du gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i don /
NK078(tshu)001:6128: de nyid bcos bslad dang bral bas de bzhin nyid
NK078(tshu)001:6129: du dbyer med pas na rdo rje'i rigsa zhes bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:6130: // gsum pa yid kyi dbang po gzung 'dzin gnyis med rang snang gi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6132: phyi gzunga ba'i yul gyis gsal cha la nang yid
NK078(tshu)001:6133: kyi dbang po shugs 'dzin gyi yul yul can dang
NK078(tshu)001:6134: bral ba'i rang gi mtshan nyid rang gi rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:6135: de nyid dmigs bya dmig byed med pa'i tshul du
NK078(tshu)001:6137: bzhi pa yid kyi yul chos kun lhun grub phyi
NK078(tshu)001:6138: nang rnam dag mnyam nyid chen po'i lta ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:6140: kun gzhi'i sems nyid ni phyogs ris med pas yangs
NK078(tshu)001:6141: shing kun la khyab pas rgya che 'khor 'das lhun
NK078(tshu)001:6142: grub tu gnas pa de ni thams cad kyi 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:6144: yid kyi yul 'dus byas kyi phyi snod kyi 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:6145: rten nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad ye nas
NK078(tshu)001:6146: chos nyid 'dus ma byas kyi ngo bor rnam par
NK078(tshu)001:6148: de ltar 'dus ma byas su dag pa'i don rang
NK078(tshu)001:6149: rig pa'i mngon sum du rtogs pa de nyid kyang
NK078(tshu)001:6150: 'dus byas dang dbyer med pas snang stong mnyam pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6152: de rtogs pa'i don 'di ni dbyings ye shes dbyer med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:6153: rdo rja bzang ngan med pas na mnyam pa nyid du yina no //
NK078(tshu)001:6154: lnga pa bsdu na shes yul gnyis med kyi lta ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6156: nang rnam par shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6157: des longs spyod pa'i phyi'i yul gyi bye brag rnams
NK078(tshu)001:6158: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bor gnyis su
NK078(tshu)001:6160: yul shes kyis bsdus pa'i chos lhag ma ma lus
NK078(tshu)001:6161: pa thamsa cad byang chub sems su ro gcig pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6162: ngang du rdzogs par rtogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6163: gnyis pa tshogs brgyad lta ba'i ngo bo'i rnam grangs la brgyad de /
NK078(tshu)001:6165: dang po don gzugs dang gsal stong dbyer med ye
NK078(tshu)001:6166: shes rang snang du bstan pa spyan gyi lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:6168: chos kun ma 'dres la rang snang du yongsa su
NK078(tshu)001:6169: rdzogsa par gsal stong gnyis med ni don shes bya
NK078(tshu)001:6170: yul gzugsa kyi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6171: blta bar bya ba'i yul dang lta ba shes pa dang gnyis su byar med par /
NK078(tshu)001:6172: phyogsa bcusa rgyal ba'i zhing khamsa thamsa cad gnyis med rang snang du mthong bas /
NK078(tshu)001:6173: yul yul can ganga du yang ma mthong ba ni shes rab spyan gyi lta ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6174: yul yul can du mthong ba'i mchoga go //
NK078(tshu)001:6175: gnyis pa don sgra dang grags stong dbyer med snyan gyi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6177: chos nyid khyab brdala chen por yul med rang gsal
NK078(tshu)001:6178: ba rang bzhin go ba'i don ni shes bya'i yul
NK078(tshu)001:6180: de yang thos par bya ba dang thos par byed
NK078(tshu)001:6181: pa gnyis med par rang snang du thos pas thos
NK078(tshu)001:6182: pa'i phul du byung ba ste shes rab snyan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6183: lta ba'o // gsum pa don dri dang tshor stong dbyer med shangs kyi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6185: gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma med pas dwangsa basa shes
NK078(tshu)001:6186: rab kyi dbang po tshim par byed pa'i chos nyid
NK078(tshu)001:6187: kyi don ni shes bya'i dri'i lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6188: de yang snomsa bya snoms byed med par gnyis med
NK078(tshu)001:6189: rang snang du tshor ba'i shes rab shangsa kyi lta
NK078(tshu)001:6190: ba'o // bzhi pa don ro dang myong stong dbyer med lce'i lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6192: chos nyid kyi don bcud gnyis med kyi ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:6193: nyamsa su myong ba'i don ni shes bya'i yul ro'i
NK078(tshu)001:6194: lta ba dang / de nyid myong bar bya ba' yul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6195: myang bar byed pa'i sems gnyis su med par myong ba ni shes rab ljags kyi lta ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6196: lnga pa don reg bya dang reg stong dbyer med lus kyi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6198: de tsam na yang dag pa'i chos nyid kyi don
NK078(tshu)001:6199: la reg pa'i don ni shes bya'i yul la reg
NK078(tshu)001:6200: pa'i lta ba dang de nyid reg pa kun gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6202: reg bya reg byed dang bral ba shes rab lus kyi lta ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6203: drug pa yid phyogs med ye shes rang snang du lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6205: yul chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi khamsa sna tshogsa pa kun mkhyen pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:6206: yid rang rig ye shes su rang dbang bsgyur bas
NK078(tshu)001:6207: rgyal por rang snang ba ni shes rab yid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:6208: lta ba'o // bdun pa nyon yid bdag med rang gsal du dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6210: thams cad rang snang yin pa de bas na bdag
NK078(tshu)001:6211: tu 'dzin pa'i nyon nyid kyang rig pa rang gsal
NK078(tshu)001:6212: bas na / bdag 'dzin dang bcas dus bdag dang
NK078(tshu)001:6213: bral ba'i nyon yid bdag med par rtogs pa'i lta
NK078(tshu)001:6214: bas na / ba'o // brgyad pa kun gzhi ye shes rang gsal thams cad mkhyen pa'i lta ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6216: phyi rol gyi don yul dang nang sems can thams
NK078(tshu)001:6217: cad kyi kun gzhi rtog med kyi ngang du gsal
NK078(tshu)001:6218: bas kun gzhi rang byung gi ye shes thamsa cad
NK078(tshu)001:6220: 'o na grub mtha' dang lta ba'i ngo bo la khyad yod dam med /
NK078(tshu)001:6221: med na so sor bshad pa dang 'gal zhing bldab skyon gyur la /
NK078(tshu)001:6222: yod na gang yin zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:6223: de gnyis la khyab che chung gi khyad yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:6224: grub mtha' ni khyab che ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6225: rang gi grub pa'i don mtha' bral spyi'i tshul du mthong ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:6226: gzhan gyi phyogs re'i gnod pa dang bral ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:6228: tshogs drug gam tshogs brgyad rang snang du rtogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:6229: kho na la 'jug pas khyab chung pa yin no
NK078(tshu)001:6230: // de yang rtogs bya don gyi ngo bo ni byang sems mtha' bral /
NK078(tshu)001:6231: rtags byed blo'i ngo bo ni sgro 'dog chod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6232: shes rab rtogs pa rang gi ngo bo ni de
NK078(tshu)001:6233: ma yin la der 'dzin gyi sgro 'dog chod pas
NK078(tshu)001:6234: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6235: de ltar gsum gyi ngo bo thams cad 'dus pa la 'jug pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:6236: gnyis pa rim pa'i don grangs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6238: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6240: grang du ngo bo'i rnam grangs song nas yang lta ba'i rnam grangs dngos ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6241: lam gyi lta ba mtho dman gyi rim pa'i don gyi rnam grangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6242: rgyud don ming gi rnam grangsa rnams brjod pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6243: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6244: don lam gyi lta grangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6245: rgyud don ming gi lta grangs so //
NK078(tshu)001:6248: dang po lta ba gtan tshig gis gtan la pheb pa'i 'phel rim gyi lta grangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6250: don dam rang bzhin med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6251: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i ye shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6252: de gnyis med du mthonga zhing rtogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6253: spyod yul dang bral bar rang rig pa'i mngon sum du byas pa dang bzhi'i rim pas /
NK078(tshu)001:6255: yig 'bru'i tshul dang byin rlabs dang mngon sum du
NK078(tshu)001:6256: rtogsa pa ste rtogs pa bzhi'i go rim dang sbyor
NK078(tshu)001:6257: bar bya'o // de ting stong chen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6260: spros pa rnam pa bzhi ste tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6264: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi dang rim par sbyar bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6268: bsgrub pa chen po bzhi dang sbyor zhing tshogs lam gyi grangsa re re'ang dbye na /
NK078(tshu)001:6273: mthar phyin pa'i nyams kyis rim gyis par 'phar ba rnams dang sbyor bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6275: lam gyi lta grangs de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6277: dang po lam gyi lta grangs ngos bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6279: chos nyid bden pa dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la mi skrag pa'i bzod pa thob pa /
NK078(tshu)001:6280: chos nyid bden pa dbyer med kyi don /
NK078(tshu)001:6281: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du sgro 'dog dang bral bar byas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:6282: yid ches nges pa'i gdengs rnyed pa'i shes rab ste
NK078(tshu)001:6283: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang snang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:6284: rnam pa kun ma spangs par ldan pa rnam pa
NK078(tshu)001:6285: mchog ldan gyi stong pa chen por gyur ba de
NK078(tshu)001:6286: mthong zhing go ba'i ngang la gnas de ting stong
NK078(tshu)001:6287: pa chen po'i lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6288: yul yul can gnyis su med par rang rig pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6289: snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:6290: sgyu ma'i ngo bor shar ba 'di kun snang gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6291: ting nge 'dzin snying rje chen po'i lta ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:6292: / 'di la brtsegs sdeb gcig bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6293: 'bras bu yi dam gyi lha'i sku gcig snang stong
NK078(tshu)001:6294: gnyis med du gsal ba phyag rgya gcig pa'i lta
NK078(tshu)001:6295: ba dang / rtog tshogs thamsa cad lha du ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:6296: dkyil 'khor du gsal bar rtogs pa phyag rgya spros
NK078(tshu)001:6298: sbyor lam bar chad med pa'i lam du yo byad
NK078(tshu)001:6299: lnga snang la rang bzhin med par spyad pas bsod
NK078(tshu)001:6300: nams dang ye shes kyi tshogsa chen gnyis rdzogs par
NK078(tshu)001:6301: mthong ba sbyor lam tshogs sgrub pa'i lta ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:6302: / don la lus snang sems gsum zung 'jug mngon
NK078(tshu)001:6303: sum du byas shing rtagsa la tshe la rang dbang
NK078(tshu)001:6304: bsgyur ba mthong lam tshe dbang gi lta ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:6305: / / dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid kyi don las
NK078(tshu)001:6306: mi g.yo ba sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i lta
NK078(tshu)001:6307: / / ba dang / yab yum gyi dka' ba sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6308: yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug la ye shes lnga'i
NK078(tshu)001:6309: rtsal du kun mkhyen pa lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6311: gnyis pa de nyid shes rab gsum las byung bar bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6313: lta ba'i rnam grangs de rnams rgyu gang las byung
NK078(tshu)001:6314: zhe na dang po gzhung zab mo thos pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:6315: / tshig des mtshon pa'i don la bsam byung so
NK078(tshu)001:6316: sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis rtog /dpyod byas pa
NK078(tshu)001:6317: / dang / de nas bsgom pa'i shes rab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6318: de yang tshigs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6319: sbyor lam rim par bsgom pa'i rgyud las mthong lam de las sgom lam /
NK078(tshu)001:6320: de las mthar lam gyi lta ba skyes pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6321: de lta bas na thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab
NK078(tshu)001:6322: gsuma gyi rgyu las lta ba skyes pa'i phyir shes
NK078(tshu)001:6323: rab gsum la brtson pas 'bod gcig par gdams pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:6324: // gnyis pa rgyud don ming gi lta grangs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6326: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6328: yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po rgyud don
NK078(tshu)001:6329: dgu po lta ba'i gzungsa kyis zin pa'i ngos nas
NK078(tshu)001:6330: lha grangs dgur bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6331: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la dgu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6333: dang po mi 'da' ba dam tshig gi lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6335: rgyud gzhung rnams las rtsa ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6336: yan lag gi dama tshiga ces bya ba bshad pa
NK078(tshu)001:6337: de la'ang gud dam log na yod pa ma yin
NK078(tshu)001:6338: te / khyad par du lam pa ranga ga chos
NK078(tshu)001:6339: nyid lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang las mi 'da' ba
NK078(tshu)001:6340: de ka dama tshiga yina te /
NK078(tshu)001:6341: de yang sgo gsum gyis bsgrub cing bsrung ba las mi 'da' bas sdom pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6342: de la yan lag gis dam tshig dang du blang ba lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6343: mi spang ba lnga ste rnam pa bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6344: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi sdom pa gsum dang bcu gsum mam /
NK078(tshu)001:6345: yang na rtsa ba'i dam tshig la byang chub sems dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6346: slob dpon mched gsung gi thugs kyi dam tshig dang lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:6347: yan lag gi dam tshig la spyad pa lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:6351: shes par bya ba snga ste sum cu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6352: thun mong spyi'i dam tshig yo ga man chad kyi bsrung bya mtha' yas pa rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:6353: chos nyid thig le chen po mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:6354: lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang du bsrung bya thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:6356: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa ji ltar spyad kyang dam tshig sdom pa las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6357: gnyis pa blang dor med pa spyod pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6359: lam pa kun gyi sgo gsum gyi bya bar gyur
NK078(tshu)001:6360: pa'i spyod pa bdag gzhan rnam pa gnyis po'i bye
NK078(tshu)001:6361: brag ji snyed pa yang chos nyid thig le chena
NK078(tshu)001:6362: pa dbyer med pa'i ngang du nges bar rtogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:6363: / spyod bya spyod byed phyogs gcig pa ci la'ang
NK078(tshu)001:6364: blo mi gnas par bdag gzhan gyi don kun la
NK078(tshu)001:6366: de ka'i dus na spyod par byed pa'i mkhan po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6367: spyad par bya ba'i yul gnyis med par thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:6368: rig pa rang snang du mthong ba ni spyod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6369: lta ba'o // gsum pa rol ba phrin las kyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6371: phrin las bya ba'i yul dang byed pa'i mkhan po
NK078(tshu)001:6372: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis su las rnams kun
NK078(tshu)001:6373: la thog pa med par spyod cing /
NK078(tshu)001:6374: zhi rgyas dbang drag rnams pa bzhi'i las dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6375: gcig pu gcig la kun lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga yanga /
NK078(tshu)001:6376: sems nyid spros bral thig le gnyis su med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6377: ngang du gsal bar rtogs pa ni phrin las kyi
NK078(tshu)001:6378: lta ba'o // bzhi pa gnas su stobs pa mchod pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6380: mchod pa'i yo byad steng 'og dang log gi rgyan rin po che dar zab la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6381: phyi nang gsang ba'i longsa spyod 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:6382: lnga'i dngos po ma lus pa kun gzhan na med
NK078(tshu)001:6383: de / rang rig pa byang chub kyi semsa chena
NK078(tshu)001:6384: po cho 'phrul chen po lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang
NK078(tshu)001:6385: de / du 'dus pas / mchod pa gzhan du
NK078(tshu)001:6386: phul ba med par phul bas gnas su stobs pas
NK078(tshu)001:6387: de / du 'dus pas / / dus gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6388: rgyal ba thamsa cad mnyes pa ste mchod pa'i lta
NK078(tshu)001:6389: de / du 'dus pas / / ba'o // lnga pa bkod pa dkyil 'khor gyi ngang /
NK078(tshu)001:6391: rten gzhal yas khang dang brten pa lha zhi ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:6392: dkyil 'khor dang 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogas kyi
NK078(tshu)001:6393: pho nya nang du 'adu ba dang phyi rol du
NK078(tshu)001:6395: log na snang ba ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6396: rang rig byang chub semsa kyi cho 'phrul chen po yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:6397: gtan tshig de ltar bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:6404: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang rnam pa bdun po thams
NK078(tshu)001:6405: cad kyang riga pa rang snang lta ba rtogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6406: ngang du 'du zhing gsal ba ni dkyil 'khor gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6407: lta ba'o // drug pa rim pa dbang gi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6409: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chosa rnamas ma lus pa thamsa cad kun gyi rang bzhina nam /
NK078(tshu)001:6410: ngang gis sems nyid rig pa bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:6411: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang la /
NK078(tshu)001:6414: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum log nas ma btsal
NK078(tshu)001:6415: bar rang rig pa'i sems nyid la lhun gyis grub
NK078(tshu)001:6416: cing rdzogsa te / de ltar phan nus zab gsum
NK078(tshu)001:6417: gyi dbang bco brgyad kyang rang rig byang chub sems
NK078(tshu)001:6418: kyi cho 'phrul du rang snang bar rtogs pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:6420: bdun pa don du gnyen ba sgrub pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6422: dngos grub kyi 'bras bu rang la yod pa la ngo mtshar zhing ngoms pas e ma ho /
NK078(tshu)001:6423: rgyu rkyen gnyis kyis ma bsgrub par rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pas grub pa chen po ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6424: grub pa chen po gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:6425: rang byung gi ye shes chen po yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6426: de bas na lam pas dona du gnyer bar bya
NK078(tshu)001:6427: ba'i bsgrub pa'i rnam grangas thun mong dang mchog gi
NK078(tshu)001:6428: dngos grub ma lus pa kun kyang rang rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:6429: byang chub kyi semsa chen pa lta ba rtogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6430: ngang du 'du zhing gsal ba ni bsgrub pa'i lta
NK078(tshu)001:6431: ba'o // brgyad pa nyams su len pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6433: ting nge 'dzina gyi ngang la gnas pa ltar ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:6434: bye braga mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:6435: kun gzhan ma min te rang rig pa nyid lhar
NK078(tshu)001:6436: snang ba'i phyir / mtshan bcas rnams chu yi chu bur lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6437: mtshan med ni nam mkha' lta bu mtshan ma'i mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:6438: dang bral ba'i rang bzhin du rtogs pas rang rig
NK078(tshu)001:6439: pa'i ye shes nyid du 'du zhing gsal ba las
NK078(tshu)001:6440: gzhan du btsal zhing bsgom pa mina no //
NK078(tshu)001:6441: de ni ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6442: dgu pa bcing grol med pa sngags dang phyag rgya'i lta ba bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6444: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i bskyed pa rkyen gyi /
NK078(tshu)001:6445: bzlas pa las rim gyi sngagsa gsum brjod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6449: las kyi phyag rgya bzhi'ang rang gi sems nyiid rang snang yin pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:6450: sngags grags stong brag ca lta bu dang phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:6451: snang stong chu zla dang 'dra bar snang la ma
NK078(tshu)001:6452: grub par lta bas shesa pa'i dus na /
NK078(tshu)001:6453: phyag rgya bcing grol dang sngags brjod pa'i las nyid
NK078(tshu)001:6454: gang ltar snang yang mya ngan las 'das pa te
NK078(tshu)001:6455: / de bas na phyag rgya bsgom bya bsgom byed dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6456: sngags bzla bya bzla byed gnyis su med par mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:6457: pa nyid kyi don lta ba rtogsa pa'i ngang du
NK078(tshu)001:6459: sngags dang phyag rgya'i lta ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6460: gsum pa lta ba kun 'dir shes dgos par gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6462: de ltar lam gyi lta ba dang rgyud kyi lta
NK078(tshu)001:6463: ba zhes lam dang rgyud don gyi gtso bora lta
NK078(tshu)001:6464: ba brjod med kyang nges pa'i don du na shes
NK078(tshu)001:6465: rab kyis chos kun ngo bo mnyam pa nyid du
NK078(tshu)001:6466: rtogs par byed pa ni lta ba zhes bya ste
NK078(tshu)001:6467: / de ni dper na tshong pa'i deda dpon gyis
NK078(tshu)001:6468: rgya mtshor nor bu rin chen len pa'i thabs la
NK078(tshu)001:6469: mkhas dgos pa'i dpe ji bzhina du /
NK078(tshu)001:6470: gdod ma rgyu shes pa lta ba nas tha ma
NK078(tshu)001:6471: 'bras bu thob pa'i bar gyi skyon yon gyi bye
NK078(tshu)001:6472: brag thams cad lta ba'i skabs 'dir phyin ci ma
NK078(tshu)001:6473: log par shes dgos pas 'dir shes par gdams pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:6474: // drug pa spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6478: thos bsam gyis so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyi
NK078(tshu)001:6479: lta ba rtogsa pa'i thabs la don du gnyer zhing
NK078(tshu)001:6480: blo chub nas rtogs pa'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:6481: bdag don dang gzhan gyi don phyir du sgo gsum
NK078(tshu)001:6482: gyis spyad par bya ba spyod pa'i bye brag rnams
NK078(tshu)001:6484: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6485: bdag don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6489: dang po thos bsam la brten nas rgyud don bcu la spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6491: rgyu shes pa lta ba rtogs thabs la 'jug pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6492: gzhi'i skabs su las bdag gzhan don kun kyang spyod
NK078(tshu)001:6493: la / de yang 'dir thos bsam gnyis kyi sgo nas bslab pa'i mtha' bcu'am /
NK078(tshu)001:6494: yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po bcu la
NK078(tshu)001:6495: spyod cing don ched du gnyer bar byed pas so
NK078(tshu)001:6496: // gnyis pa lta ba rtogs tshab che chung gis
NK078(tshu)001:6497: dbye bas spyod pa la khyad par yod tshul dang
NK078(tshu)001:6499: rgyu shes pa lta ba'i spyod pa 'di la yang /
NK078(tshu)001:6500: gzhan don dbang bsgyur gyi spyod pa'i khyad yod tshul gyi dpe ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6501: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po tsam la 'dra yang /
NK078(tshu)001:6502: 'dul zhing gis khamsa la rgya che chung yod pa bzhin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6503: thabs kyi spyod pas nyon mongs pa thad gcos nus mi nus kyi dpe ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6504: stobsa chen glang po che tsam du 'dra yang /
NK078(tshu)001:6505: rtsal che chung dang sgyid drag zhan yod pa lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6506: bdag don ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod pa la stobs che chung yod pa'i dpe ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6507: dper na lung pa'i rgya che chung gi phye bas
NK078(tshu)001:6508: nam mkha'i zhing gi yul che chung yod pa ji
NK078(tshu)001:6509: lta bar / gzhi shes pa lta ba'i spyod par gcig kyang gzhan don la rgya che chung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6510: nyon mongs pa thad gcod nus mi nus dang bdag
NK078(tshu)001:6511: don ting nge 'dzin stobs che chung gi stobsa kyis
NK078(tshu)001:6512: spyod pa la khyad par yod par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:6513: gsum pa lta ba rtogs pa ngo bo'i spyod thabs bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6515: chos thams cad ye gdong ma nas chos nyid mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:6516: pa nyid kyi dbyingsa su ra gciga pas de la'ang
NK078(tshu)001:6517: bdag tu 'dzin pa gang zag gi nga bdag dang
NK078(tshu)001:6518: / chos kyi badga rang rgyud par ma rtogsa par spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6519: dam rdzas la sogs chos thams cad ye nas rang
NK078(tshu)001:6520: bzhina gyis rnam par dag pa yin pa la dkar
NK078(tshu)001:6521: gsum la sogs gtsang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6522: dam rdzas lnga la sogs pa sme ba mi gtsang
NK078(tshu)001:6523: ba'i blo gnyis su 'dzin par ma byed par gdams
NK078(tshu)001:6525: semsa can thams cad bde gshegsa snying por gcig pa yin pasa na /
NK078(tshu)001:6526: gang ltar spyad kyang bag chags kyi rkyen gyis dri
NK078(tshu)001:6527: ma ngan pa'i rdul gyis ga la 'ag ste mi
NK078(tshu)001:6528: gos pas de sus spyod ce na /
NK078(tshu)001:6529: gang zag shes rab mchog gis tshul de ltar rtogsa
NK078(tshu)001:6530: shing spyod bya'i yul gyi chos ma lus pa kun
NK078(tshu)001:6531: sems su 'dus la sems mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyingsa
NK078(tshu)001:6532: su shes par byos shig par gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6533: bzhi pa spyod pa'i dam tshig dang slob rim bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6535: shes par byos shig par gdams pa de bas na
NK078(tshu)001:6536: rgyu shes par bya ba'i lta ba rtogs thabs dang
NK078(tshu)001:6537: / lta ba'i ngo bo rnams las mi 'da' bas dam tshig dang sdom pa'i ngo bor byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:6538: dgos pa bdag dang gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir du lta ba gtso bor byed kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6539: de yang lam gyi dang po rgyu shes pa lta
NK078(tshu)001:6540: ba la 'jug pa'i dus su sdom pa gsum po
NK078(tshu)001:6541: kun kyang slob cing spyod par byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6542: gnyis pa gzhan don gyi spyod pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6544: dang po shes rab chen po'i spyod pas rtogs pas rang grol nas thugs rjes gzhan dgrol tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6546: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don shes pa'i shes rab chen po'i lta ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:6547: sbyin bsreg gis gang la zhen pa med par sbyin cing /
NK078(tshu)001:6548: bsreg rdzas ni srid pa gsum gyi rtog pa bsreg pa'i me ni lta ba rtogs pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6549: bsreg tshul ni yid kyi rtog pa rang byung gi ye shes rang gsal bas me ru 'bar la /
NK078(tshu)001:6550: ram ni me yi sa bon te /
NK078(tshu)001:6551: rtog pa ye shes kyi mes bdag bsgral nas /
NK078(tshu)001:6552: de nas thugs rjes 'gro drug gi rtogs pa kun
NK078(tshu)001:6553: kyang chos nyid mi dmigs pa'i ngang du bsregs pa
NK078(tshu)001:6555: gnyis pa bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6557: gdoda ma nas rgyu shes pa lta ba nas bzung
NK078(tshu)001:6558: ste mthar 'bras bu ma thob bar du lam don
NK078(tshu)001:6559: gnyer gyi thos bsam gyi spros pa gcod cinga /
NK078(tshu)001:6560: 'bras bu grub para byed pa'i lam bgrod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6561: lam du 'jug pa'i dus der yang /
NK078(tshu)001:6562: bdag don dang gazhana don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6563: chos kyi don te don gsum gyi phyir byang chub
NK078(tshu)001:6564: bsgrub par dam bca' zhing sems bskyed pa de bas
NK078(tshu)001:6565: na rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyi lam bsgrod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6567: gdul bya gzhan gyi don shugs kyis rdzogsa pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:6568: gsum pa de theg chung la mi 'tshams pas khyad par gyi spyod pa yin tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:6570: de bas na byis sba nyan rang rang don byed pa dang 'di gnyis mi mtshungsa te /
NK078(tshu)001:6571: theg chen kun gyi lam skabsa las bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs par shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6572: bdun pa phan yon la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6574: dang po lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan 'khor bar
NK078(tshu)001:6575: mi ltung zhing yon tan tshad las 'das pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:6577: lam pa gang zhig gis yon tan gong du bstan pa 'di 'drara thos bsam la brten nas /
NK078(tshu)001:6578: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du mthong zhing rtogsa pa de ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6579: dngosa grub rnam gnyis las mchog gi dngos grub kyi bcud 'dus pa'i snying po yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6580: dper na chu srin gyi gre bar dngos po gang
NK078(tshu)001:6581: tshud pa phyir mi gtong ba'i phyag rgya ci bzhina
NK078(tshu)001:6582: du dang po chos nyid lta ba'i don rtogs na
NK078(tshu)001:6583: / mthar 'bras bu ma thob kyi bar du lta
NK078(tshu)001:6584: ba de dang ma bral na 'khor bar mi gtong
NK078(tshu)001:6585: / ba dang / gzhan yang dbang po'i spyod yul
NK078(tshu)001:6586: kun tu ye shes su 'char bas yon tan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6587: tshad blos dapaga tu meda do //
NK078(tshu)001:6588: gnyis pa ci ltar spyad kyang rnam smin med cing tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6590: lta ba zin na kun nas nyon mongsa pa 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:6591: ba'i chos la spyod pa'ang rtogs pas grol bar 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:6592: bas thun mong gi lam rgyu'i theg pa che chung
NK078(tshu)001:6593: gnyis sam / yang na sngags phyi pa dang mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:6594: nyid gnyis la spyod pa'ang grol ba de bzhina yin
NK078(tshu)001:6595: gnyis sam / pas na / rgyu dge sdig gi
NK078(tshu)001:6596: 'bras bu rnam smin la mtho ris kyi bde ba
NK078(tshu)001:6597: gnyis sam / pas na / dang / ngan song gi sdug bsngal gnyis med de /
NK078(tshu)001:6598: slar spyod lam ci spyod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:6599: mi 'dzin pa'i ye shes dang ma 'gag pa'i bsod nams kyi tshogs chen gnyis rdzogsa par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:6600: gsum pa mtha' gsum bral zhing don gsum rdzogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6602: rnal 'byor pa gang gis gong gi don de ltar
NK078(tshu)001:6603: lta ba mnyam pa nyid dbyer med rtogs par gyur
NK078(tshu)001:6604: pa de ni / yod par sgro 'dog pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6605: med pa skur ba 'debs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6606: mnyam pa nyid lung ma bstan gyi mtha' dang gsum las yongs su grol ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6608: de'i don 'bras bu rnams mngon sum du 'byina cing thob par byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:6609: gtan tshig de ltar bas na bdag don thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6611: chos dang mthun pa'i chos don te /
NK078(tshu)001:6613: bzhi pa shes rab chen pos 'khor bar mi gtong zhing bde ba dang ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6615: de ltar lta ba rtogs pa'i gang zag de'i blos gzhi ltar thug pa med pas rgya che zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:6616: rgya mtsho ltar gting zab pa /
NK078(tshu)001:6617: bar snang ltar yangsa shing glog ltar shes rab myur bas /
NK078(tshu)001:6618: chos nyid zab mo'i don rtogsa shing /
NK078(tshu)001:6619: lta ba de dang ma bral na /
NK078(tshu)001:6620: 'khor ba ngan song du mi ldog sdug bsngal med pas bde ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6621: sems nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pa med pas blo
NK078(tshu)001:6622: grol bas yangsa pa'i don dang ldan pas bde ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:6623: // brgyad pa drod la dbye ba med do //
NK078(tshu)001:6625: rnal 'byor pa brtson 'grus dang ldan pas lta ba rtogsa par byed pa lhur len par byed na /
NK078(tshu)001:6626: kun 'dus ltar rmi lam du chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6627: rin po che'i sa gling du phyin pa dang me tog dang 'bras bu'i char bab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6628: rin po che'i glegs bam dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6629: gser gyi 'khor lo la sogs pa lag tu gtad nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6630: dung dang rnga bo che'i sgra la sogs pas stong gsum gang bar sgrags pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6631: nyi zla lag tu thogs nas 'jig rten gyi mun pa bsel ba la sogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6632: bden pa mthong ba'i rmi ltas ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6633: sngar ma mthong ba'i yul khams chen po mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6634: byang chub chen po'i mchod rten la 'dzegs shing thams cad mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6635: ri bo'i rtse nas phyogs thams cad du bltas shing mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6636: nam mkha'i khams kun mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6637: rang las 'od byung nas snang srid thams cad gsal ba la sogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6638: gzhan yang rmi ltas kyi mtshan ma bzang po mthong zhing 'byung ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6639: gzhan yang sgrib pa dag pa la sogs pa 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:6640: bar gsung ste sgren mor bud nas lus kyi dri
NK078(tshu)001:6641: ma thams cad dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6642: chu bo che la rkyal zhing khrus byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6643: rnag khrag nang khrol la sogs pa thams cad phyir la sangs kyis thon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6644: lus mes bsreg ste mi snang bar byas pa la sogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6645: lus ngag yid gsum gyi rtsa ba'i drod de las gzhan pa yan lag gi drod kun /
NK078(tshu)001:6646: lta ba rtogs par byed pa'i shugsa kyis 'byung bar tha tshama med do //
NK078(tshu)001:6647: dmigs ngos bzung ni 'og de bzhin nyid dang mthun no //
NK078(tshu)001:6648: dgu pa lta ba rtogs pa'i rtags bstan pa la dbye ba med do //
NK078(tshu)001:6650: lta ba rtogs pa de las rtags kyi mtshan ma mngon du 'byung ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6651: shes rab kyi stobsa kyis lta ba rtogsa pa'i ngang
NK078(tshu)001:6652: la rig pa klong du phebs pa'i don dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:6653: pas / rnal 'byor ba des rang tshe 'pho zhing spyod yul 'gyur bar mthong yang /
NK078(tshu)001:6654: skye 'chi med pa'i don rtogs pas de la 'jigsa pa med cing /
NK078(tshu)001:6655: snang srid chos skur shes pas 'khrul ba'i khams la skyo ba med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6656: 'bras bu sangs rgyas grub pa'i gnas 'og min dga'
NK078(tshu)001:6657: ldan la sogs la skye ba'i smon pa med de
NK078(tshu)001:6658: / 'doda pa'i yon tan lnga'i longsa spyod la gtsang
NK078(tshu)001:6659: sme med par rol cing chos nyid dang mnyam par
NK078(tshu)001:6660: / sbyor ba dang / lus kyi na tsha dang sems kyi sdug bsngal drag po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6661: nyon mongsa pa chags sdang la sogs skye dus lta
NK078(tshu)001:6662: ba las ma g.yos pas bzod pa chen po thob
NK078(tshu)001:6663: ste / dge ba'i las rlab po che rnams dang
NK078(tshu)001:6664: gzhan don gang la'ang dka' bas khur du mi blta
NK078(tshu)001:6665: zhing rtsol med du grub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6666: tan+t+ra rgyud sde'i lung rnams dang rang gi bya spyod 'gal ba med par spyod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:6667: so sor skye bo tha mal pa'i spyod pa rang
NK078(tshu)001:6668: ga ma rnams las khyad par du lhag par 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:6669: ba dang / sgo gsum gyi spyod pa la rgyun gyi ma 'agags par spyod pas bsod nams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6670: de las mi gzhan pa'i ye shes te grogsa gnyis zung 'jug tu rdzogsa par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:6671: lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan rnams mdo tsam du
NK078(tshu)001:6672: smos kyis tha dad du rgyas par spros na yon
NK078(tshu)001:6673: tan brjod kyis mi langa ba yod do //
NK078(tshu)001:6674: bcu pa tshad la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6676: dang po thos bsam gyi sgo nas tshul mthun du rtogs shing mthar phyin pa'i tshad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6678: dper na rgya mtsho rnyogs ma dangsa pa'i nang du
NK078(tshu)001:6679: nyi zla gza' skar gyi gzugsa brnyan 'char ba ltar
NK078(tshu)001:6680: / rang rig pa'i chos nyid mngon sum du gsal bar mthong ba'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:6681: chos nyid de mtshon byed kyi sgra tshig tsam la
NK078(tshu)001:6682: brten nas don spyi yida la byed pa min par
NK078(tshu)001:6683: / mngon sum bzhi las rang rig pa'i mngon sum du dmigsa pa'i yul dang bral bar /
NK078(tshu)001:6684: yul med rang gsal du mthong ba la blta bya
NK078(tshu)001:6685: blta byed lta ba'i ngo bo gsum dang bral te
NK078(tshu)001:6686: / grub mtha' gzhan gyi rkyen gyis mi bsgul bar /
NK078(tshu)001:6687: don nges par rang rig pa'i gdengsa su chud par gang byas pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6688: thos bsam la brten nas tshul mthun du rtogs pa'i lta ba mathara phyin pa'i tshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:6689: de ltar zag bcas su chos nyid rang mtshan mthong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6690: gal te ma mthong zer na /
NK078(tshu)001:6692: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:6693: mthong lam gnyis su gyur pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:6696: gsum pa bden gnyis rang mtshan du //
NK078(tshu)001:6697: mgo mthong gnyis med bzod ma thob //
NK078(tshu)001:6700: zag med bden mthong dang khyad med du 'gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6701: nyon mongs mngon gyur gyis sgrib pa rag pa de
NK078(tshu)001:6702: chos nyid mthong ba'i sgrib byed ma yin par 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:6703: ro zhe na / nye ston chos kyi seng ge ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6706: gnas pa yun ring thung du bzhed do //
NK078(tshu)001:6707: 'di la zur thams cad mkhyen pa chos kyi rje chen po byams pa seng+ge ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6708: skabs 'grel ltar zag bcas su chos nyid rang mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:6709: mgo tsam mthong ba la sngar gyi nyes pas gnod
NK078(tshu)001:6711: gsal mi gsal yod pas gong 'og khyad med du mi 'gyur zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:6712: nyon sgrib shin tu rags pa thos bsam gyis dag la /
NK078(tshu)001:6713: des dag ma nus pa'i nyon mongs pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6714: chos nyid gsal ba stobs rdzogs su gyur pa'i sgrib byed yin kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:6715: mgo mthong tsam gyis ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:6716: mi gsal bas ma mthong ba yang ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:6717: rgyang ring po'i mi mthong ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:6718: drung gi mi ltar ma gsal bas dang mtshan ma mthong na /
NK078(tshu)001:6720: don gang nye ba dang mi nye ba las //
NK078(tshu)001:6721: shes pa tha dad par snang ba ni rang gi mtshan nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:6722: zhes pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:6724: gnyis pa tshig tu go na ngo bo gcig kyang
NK078(tshu)001:6725: gsal du 'gro ba'i rim pa dpe dang bcas pa
NK078(tshu)001:6727: 'on kyang zhes pa mi mthun pa mthun par ston pa'i tshig ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6728: thos bsam la brten nas lta ba rtogs ma nus kyang rtogs bya lta ba tsam du mthun pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6729: de yangs gong ma gong ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6730: sa 'og ma 'og ma'i rim pa bzhin du lta ba'i khyad yod ces pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6731: gang gis khyad yod zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:6732: gsal la mi gsal gyis khyad ston pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6733: dper na mig gi dbang po shin tu dngas ma'i spyod yul du gzugs mthong ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:6734: nye na gsal ring na mi gsal drung na shin
NK078(tshu)001:6735: tu gsal ba bzhin bsgom byung gi stobsa lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:6737: de bas rgyu shes pa'i lta ba dang rkyen 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:6738: pa ting nge 'dzin gnas skabsa kyi 'bras bu rnams
NK078(tshu)001:6739: re re la'ang lam dus kyi gong ma rgyu dang
NK078(tshu)001:6741: lta ba'i don nyid lam snga ma bas phyi ma
NK078(tshu)001:6742: gsal du song ba'i bye brag goms ma goms kyi
NK078(tshu)001:6744: je gsal je gsal gyis stobs cher 'gro ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6745: lta ba gsal mi gsal yod pa de yis chas
NK078(tshu)001:6746: phye bas lam gong 'og gi gnas skabsa kyi lta
NK078(tshu)001:6747: ba la / de bzhin nyid kyi lta ba la
NK078(tshu)001:6748: sogs pa'i ming so sor tha dad du brjod kyis
NK078(tshu)001:6749: ba la / / lta ba rang rig dngos po'am ngo bo gcig pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6750: sems kyi gnas lugs yin pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:6751: bcu gcig pa ma rtogs pa'i skyon la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6752: ma rtogs pa'i skyon dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6753: rtogs pa'i don la brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6754: ting nge 'dzin rnams dang rgyu 'bras su 'brel tshul bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6757: dang po blo ngan gyis ma rtogs par le lo
NK078(tshu)001:6758: byas pa'i skyon gyis ngan song du ltung ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:6760: gong gi lta ba'i tshad kyis don ltar ma rtogsa
NK078(tshu)001:6761: par shes rab med pa'i blo ngan tshig gis chos
NK078(tshu)001:6762: thams cad mnyam par bshad pa'i lung khung bzang po
NK078(tshu)001:6763: rnams nas phyungs te brjod nas /
NK078(tshu)001:6764: lta ba mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogsa pa dman pa'i le lo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6765: spyod pa rang ga mar snyomsa las byas pas tshe
NK078(tshu)001:6766: 'di ru dgos pa'i don ma 'grub par phyi mar
NK078(tshu)001:6768: gnyis pa tshig gi lta bas 'tshang mi rgya bas tshig don ldan par gdams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6770: sems kyi chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don gcig
NK078(tshu)001:6771: gting 'byin par ma rtogsa na kha tshig tsam gyis
NK078(tshu)001:6772: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid yin zhes brjod pas
NK078(tshu)001:6773: / 'bras bu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang mi rgya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6774: don ma rtogs na skyon yod pa de bas na
NK078(tshu)001:6775: don dang tshig tu 'brel cing ldan par gyis la
NK078(tshu)001:6777: 'o na lta ba ma rtogs nas lam la 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:6778: pa la dgos pa med do ce na ma yin
NK078(tshu)001:6779: te / 'on kyang tshig don 'brel bar gyur nas
NK078(tshu)001:6780: the tshom med par go na 'dod pa'i don gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6781: 'bras bu thams cad phun sum tshogs pa 'grub par
NK078(tshu)001:6782: te / 'gyur ro // gsum pa lta ba med
NK078(tshu)001:6783: na lam kun zag cing 'ching bas lta ba rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:6784: shig par gdams pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6786: dper na spyan bzang ste long ba lam du zhugsa
NK078(tshu)001:6787: kyang 'gro sar mi phyin pa ci lta ba bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:6788: gyi phyir / lta ba ma rtogs par lam du
NK078(tshu)001:6789: zhugs na lam kun 'khor bar zag cing 'ching ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:6791: bdag gzhan gyi 'bras bu thob pa'i don du mi
NK078(tshu)001:6792: 'gyur pa'i phyir na sems ngan song du brlag par
NK078(tshu)001:6794: de bas na lta ba'i don la brtson zhing 'grub par gyis shig ces gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6795: gnyis pa rtogs pa'i don la brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6797: gong du lta ba rtogs pa'i tshad bstan pa de
NK078(tshu)001:6798: ltar rang gsal gsum bral gyi chos nyid lta ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:6799: don phyin ci ma log par mthonga ba'i rten gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6801: lta ba'i don las gzhan du mi bsam par lta
NK078(tshu)001:6802: ba'i don de kho na la blo 'drisa shing goms
NK078(tshu)001:6803: par bya'o // skyes bu dam pa 'bras bu mchog
NK078(tshu)001:6804: gi dngos grub rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par 'doda
NK078(tshu)001:6805: par bya'o // pas / lta ba de la dus
NK078(tshu)001:6806: rtag tu brtson 'grus kyis don gsal bar gyis la
NK078(tshu)001:6807: sgoms shig ces gdams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6808: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin rnams dang rgyu 'bras su 'brel tshul bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6810: dper na mgron po rnams lam rgyus shes nas lam
NK078(tshu)001:6811: du 'jug pa ji bzhin du lta ba rtogs nas
NK078(tshu)001:6813: rgyu shes pa lta ba dang rkyen 'jug pa'i ting
NK078(tshu)001:6814: nge 'dzin rnams dang snga ma ni rgyu dang phyi
NK078(tshu)001:6815: ma ni 'bras bu'i tshul du 'brel ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6816: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6818: gzhi gnas lugsa don dam kun rdzob dbyer med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:6819: ye shes ye nas rang la rang chas su gnas
NK078(tshu)001:6820: pa'i don rang rig pa'i mngon sum du mthonga ba
NK078(tshu)001:6821: lta ba ston par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don
NK078(tshu)001:6822: rnams / mtshams dang ris su gcod cing 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na le'u zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6823: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:6824: yas bgrang gnyis pa'i don du gada'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6825: spyi don gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6827: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad pa dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6829: de'ang le'u gong mar chos kun sems nyid rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:6830: bdag nyid chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i dang chen
NK078(tshu)001:6831: po de la lta ba rtogsa pas mos zhen thun
NK078(tshu)001:6832: mong ma yin pa rtogs pa'i mjal ba'i sgo nas
NK078(tshu)001:6834: lta ba rtogs pa de'i rjes su gomsa par byed pa'i lam /
NK078(tshu)001:6835: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin bshad par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6836: gnyis pa don rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6838: dang po lam gong 'og gi 'brel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6840: de yang lam grangs sam dus kyi snga ma snga
NK078(tshu)001:6841: ma de ting kun ting la sogs gang dang gang
NK078(tshu)001:6842: yin pa de / lam grangs sam dus kyi phyi
NK078(tshu)001:6843: ma phyi ma'i gcig spros la sogs gang yin te
NK078(tshu)001:6844: bskyed pa'i thabsa dang rgyu yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:6845: snga ma snga ma thabs sam rgyu yin pa de bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:6846: lam phyi ma phyi ma gcig spros la sogs gang yin pa de /
NK078(tshu)001:6847: lam snga ma snga ma de ting la sogs pa'i thabs las byung ba de'i 'bras bu yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:6848: de yang spyir rgyu 'bras rnam grangs kyi rnam dbye
NK078(tshu)001:6849: rnams le'u gong ma'i 'grel pa dang gzhan du shes
NK078(tshu)001:6850: la / 'dir sa bon dang myu gu ltar bskyed byed dam /
NK078(tshu)001:6851: phan gdag bya gdag byed kyi rgyu 'bras su shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6852: gnyis pa lam gyi dmigs rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6854: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6856: gong du bstan pa de ltar lam snga phyi la rgyu dang 'brasa bu'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:6857: thabsa dang thabs las byung ba'i 'brel ba yod pa'i lam pa de'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:6858: dper na srid pa 'khor ba'i skye gnas kyi 'khor lo la bardzusa te skyes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6859: mngal skyes la myur bul yod pa'i tshul bzhin du shes rab kyi dbang po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6860: don du gnyer ba'i brtson 'grus bzang ba srid pa bardzusa nas skye ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6861: ngan pa srid pa rim par skye ba'i tshul gyis
NK078(tshu)001:6862: phye bas rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:6863: 'di la'ang / rnam par dbye ba cig char ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6864: rim gyis pa'i lus gnyis su bstan par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6865: 'dir glan chu bar gyi sh+aakya bzang pos 'di bzhed
NK078(tshu)001:6866: kyi lam rim gyi dbu zhabs kyi ngag don dril
NK078(tshu)001:6867: na don brgyad de shes rab che chung ngam bde
NK078(tshu)001:6868: ba lam du khyer mi khyer gyi sgo nas thabs
NK078(tshu)001:6870: blo che chung gi sgo nas rim dang cig char gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6871: rim pa 'dor mi 'dor gyi sgo nas mthar chags dang thod rgal gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6872: rang stobs dang gzhan stobs kyi sgo nas gdams ngag dang shes rab kyi stobs gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6873: dngos yul dang mos yul gyi sgo nas rdzogs slob dang smin slob gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6874: skye ba len mi len gyi sgo nas zag pa yod med gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6875: spyod pa dus tshod kyi sgo nas ldog pa yod med gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6876: mya ngan las 'da' tshul gyi sgo nas lhag ma yod med gnyis so //
NK078(tshu)001:6879: gzhi dang skabs nas skye 'gyur ba //
NK078(tshu)001:6880: grol lam thabs su rnam par bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:6883: dbu ma rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:6884: grol lam thabs su rnam par bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:6886: 'di nyid las thabs dang shes rab lam nyid kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:6890: yod pa grol lam yod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:6891: thabs dang gdams ngag gtsor byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:6892: spyod pa thabs kyi gdams ngag dang ldan pas /
NK078(tshu)001:6893: bde ba la spyod kyang mi 'ching zhing grol ba thabs lam dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6894: yod pa thabs dang gdams ngag yod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:6895: shes rab gsum gtso bor byas nas sems nyid rang
NK078(tshu)001:6896: byung ye shes kyi don thos bsam sgom gsum gyis
NK078(tshu)001:6897: rgyud grol bar byed pas grol lam zhes so //
NK078(tshu)001:6900: rje sgro phug pa rjes 'brang dang bcas pas 'go 'brel lam du bzhed do //
NK078(tshu)001:6901: 'o na thabs lam dang grol lam so sos 'tshang rgya bar bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:6902: de ni rang gi lam gyi che ba brjod pa yin gyi /
NK078(tshu)001:6904: 'brel pa gang du 'brel zhe na gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6908: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba nas yar 'brel lo //
NK078(tshu)001:6910: tshogs sgrub kyi 'khor khang dang por sbyor sgrol gyi
NK078(tshu)001:6911: mchod pa 'bul ba de thabs lam de la shes
NK078(tshu)001:6912: rab kyi rtsis ma zin na chags sdang rang rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:6913: du 'gro bas shes rab kyi rtsis zin pa de
NK078(tshu)001:6915: gsum pa sngon du gang 'gro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:6916: snga rabs pa'i lugs kyi thos bsam la 'jug pa'i sngon du thabs lam 'gro ste /
NK078(tshu)001:6917: thabs lam dbang yin pas de ma bskur bar thos bsam byar mi rung bar gsungs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6918: gzhung 'di nyid kyi dgongs pa ltar na /
NK078(tshu)001:6919: thog mar g.yo smon gyi sems sngon du song nas 'jug pa'i sems bskyed de /
NK078(tshu)001:6920: de nas thabs lam phan nus kyi dbang bskur nas thos bsam la gnas par byed par bshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:6921: de yang thabs lam gtso bor byas nas grol lam cha rkyen du byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6922: grol lam gtso bor byas nas thabs lam cha rkyen du btong ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:6925: lam gyi shes rab sngon 'gro ba //
NK078(tshu)001:6926: thabs la de nyid rim par bslab //
NK078(tshu)001:6928: gnyis pa rim dang cir char ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6929: bden pa bzhi cig char du rtogs shing sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6930: bden bzhi rim gyis nyams su len pa gnyis ni
NK078(tshu)001:6931: de ma thag 'og tu bshad pa ltar shes par
NK078(tshu)001:6933: lam bor rung du yod pa thod rgal dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6934: mthar chags su bsgrod pa rim gyis pas gnyis ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6935: le'u lnga pa'i skabs nas shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6937: rang stobs dang gzhan stobs kyi don ni le'u gsum pa la sogs pa'i skabs nas shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6938: lnga pa smin slob dang rdzogs slob kyi don la'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:6940: de ting la sogs pa rnal 'byor bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6941: thun re'i cho ga la rdzogs par bsgoms nas bdag
NK078(tshu)001:6942: gzhan gyi don la sbyor ba yin te 'di nyid
NK078(tshu)001:6944: shes 'jug kun kyang gzhan don du //
NK078(tshu)001:6945: zhes sogs tshig skang drug gis ston no //
NK078(tshu)001:6947: de ting la sogs pa re re la'ang nyams lnga
NK078(tshu)001:6948: mthar phyin nas lam gong ma la sbyor ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:6950: snga ma snga ma gang dang gang //
NK078(tshu)001:6952: sngon du stong sgom rnal 'byor pas //
NK078(tshu)001:6953: zhes sogs tshig rkang bzhis ston no //
NK078(tshu)001:6954: drug pa zag pa yod med dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6955: bdun pa ldog pa yod med gnyis ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6958: brgyad pa gsum gyi skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6959: brgyad pa lhag bcas dang lhag med kyi 'bras bu la sbyor tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:6961: brgyad pa'i skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6963: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:6968: dang po spyir cig char ba'i ting nge 'dzin sgom tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6970: cig char ba ni srid pa bardzusa nas skye ba
NK078(tshu)001:6971: de lus rdzogs pa cig char du smin pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:6972: bzhin du / rim gyis pas lta sgom las lhag
NK078(tshu)001:6973: par bden gsum dbyer med rtog pa'i gdengsa dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:6975: de ting kun ting phyag rgya gcig spros kyi sgom pa rnam pa bzhi las /
NK078(tshu)001:6976: dang po de ting ni chos kun rang byung gi
NK078(tshu)001:6977: ye shes bcos bslad med pa'i ngang la gnas pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:6979: chos kun rang rig pa'i ye shes ma 'gag par cir yang gsal ba'i ngang la gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6981: rang byung lha'i skur rang rig pa'i ye shes las ma g.yos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:6982: spros bcas ni snod bcud rang bzhin gyis sku dang
NK078(tshu)001:6983: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du ma 'dres par ye
NK078(tshu)001:6984: nas gsal ba'o // de ltar bzhi po zung 'brel gnyis med du ldan para /
NK078(tshu)001:6985: dus gdoda mar lta ba rtogs ma thag nyid nas
NK078(tshu)001:6986: bden pa rnam bzhi cig chod du gomas par byeda
NK078(tshu)001:6987: pa'o // lta ba rang byung gi yeshesa mtha' dbus
NK078(tshu)001:6988: med pa'i thig le chen po'i rang bzhin du gsal
NK078(tshu)001:6989: pa'o // ba de la / rim gyis bsgom pa de ting stong chen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6990: kun ting ye shes sgyu ma dang //
NK078(tshu)001:6991: dbyer med rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin dang rnam pa gsum ka dus gcig la tha mi dad du /
NK078(tshu)001:6992: gnyis med thig le chen po rdzogsa la de ni
NK078(tshu)001:6993: bcos bslad med pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi don ni
NK078(tshu)001:6995: de ni cir yang ma 'gags par gsal bas kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:6996: thig le chen po de ni rdzogs la dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:6997: kyi sku ye shes su gsal bas rgyu'i ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:6998: 'dzin no // rim gyis pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsum rim par bsgom pa rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:6999: 'dir cig char dus gcig tu ldan pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:7001: de nyid ma bcos mi g.yo'i tshul //
NK078(tshu)001:7002: de ni de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK078(tshu)001:7003: de nyid kun gsal ye shes phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:7004: de ni kun tu snang gi ngang //
NK078(tshu)001:7005: 'bras bu'i chos rnams kun dngos pas //
NK078(tshu)001:7006: de ni rgyu yi rim par ldan zhes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7007: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:7008: lhun gyis rtogs nas lhun gyis bsgom //
NK078(tshu)001:7009: rim bral de nyid gsal gyur pa //
NK078(tshu)001:7010: skabs kyi rdzogs pa chen por brjod //
NK078(tshu)001:7012: gnyis pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogs shing bsgoms pa las mi 'da' bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7014: sems rnams par shes pa tshogsa brgyad ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gsal bar rtogsa pa'i don ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7015: sngar lta ba'i ngo bo'i skabs su rgyas par bshad pa dang mthun la /
NK078(tshu)001:7017: rtsa ba'i rnam par shes pa las ni me long lta bu'i ye shes su snang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:7018: dmigs pa'i rnam par shes par las ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7019: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su snang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:7020: snang ba'i rnam par shes pa las ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7021: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes su snang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:7022: 'jug pa'i rnam par shes pa las ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7023: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su snang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:7024: sems kyi chos nyid las ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su snang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:7026: lta ba rtogs pa'i don de la bsgom pa ting
NK078(tshu)001:7027: nge 'dzin gyis rig pa la rang dbang bsgyur nasa
NK078(tshu)001:7029: tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga'i ngo bo ru yul med
NK078(tshu)001:7030: du rang gsal ba nyid ni rnam par mi rtog
NK078(tshu)001:7031: pa'i thugsa ye shes lnga'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub
NK078(tshu)001:7032: pa las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya chena pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7033: gsum pa bye brag phyes te bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7035: rab zag med kyi bden pa rtogs nas sangs rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7036: 'bring zag bcas kyi bden pa cig char du rtogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7039: de dang mthun par spyod pas sangs rgyas tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:7040: dang po la gnyis te bgrang /
NK078(tshu)001:7041: dang po mnyam pa nyid kyi don lta ba bsgom las mi 'da' bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7043: gzhi don mnyam pa nyid la lta bas mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:7044: nyid yin par rtogs nas sbyor ba'i sgom pa mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:7045: pa'i don las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig de'i don
NK078(tshu)001:7047: gang yang ma spangs par 'bras bu mnyam rdzogsa bdag
NK078(tshu)001:7048: nyid chen pa'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po dbye
NK078(tshu)001:7049: ba med pa'i sa thob par 'gyur bas so //
NK078(tshu)001:7050: mnyam pa nyid kyi don de las 'das na sangs rgyas thob pa ni ma yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:7051: gnyis pa spyod pa las mi 'da' zhing tshogs gnyis rdzogs par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7053: yang na zhes pa 'dam ka'i tshig yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:7054: bsrung du med pa spyod pa'i dam tshig 'og nas 'byung ba 'di lta bu /
NK078(tshu)001:7055: lta bsgom gyi ngang nas sgo gsum gyi spyod pa
NK078(tshu)001:7056: ca ltar spyad kyang bdag nyid chen po mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:7057: nyid kyi sdoma pa'i don las mi 'ad'a ba'i steng
NK078(tshu)001:7058: nas / sgo gsum gyi bya spyod thams cad mi 'gags pa bsod nams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7059: ma dmigs pa ye shes kyi tshogs chana po gnyis su rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:7060: gnyis pa spyod pas sangs rgyas tshul de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7062: dang po spyod lam mnyam pa nyid las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7064: rnal 'byor pa de 'gro 'ong gi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7066: nyal zhing gnyid log pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7067: za zhing longs spyod pa'i dus na lta sgom gyi
NK078(tshu)001:7068: don las ma nyamsa pa mnyam pa nyid de'i dbyingsa
NK078(tshu)001:7069: su gnas par gang gis spyod na /
NK078(tshu)001:7070: rnal 'byor pa shes rab mchog tu gyur pa cig
NK078(tshu)001:7071: char ba dag gis dus rtag tu de ltar spyod
NK078(tshu)001:7072: par bya'o // gnyis pa lta spyod dang ldan pas sangs rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7074: dbyingsa nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don gnas pa la ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7075: blos rtog par byas nas dbyingsa de la spyod pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:7076: dbyings gang la spyod na skye ba med pa'i dbyingsa
NK078(tshu)001:7077: nyid la lhag pa'i 'bras bu mchog gi 'byung gnas
NK078(tshu)001:7078: gnyis med mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings la spyod pas
NK078(tshu)001:7079: / mthar gnyis med mnyam pa nyid de nyid rang
NK078(tshu)001:7080: yang mi gnas pa'i mya ngana las 'das te sangs
NK078(tshu)001:7081: / rgyas so // de yang rdo rje las /
NK078(tshu)001:7082: dang po blo ldan gang zag ni //
NK078(tshu)001:7083: ma lus bden pa dbyer med pas //
NK078(tshu)001:7084: rang bzhin rig pa'i gtan tshig gis //
NK078(tshu)001:7085: phung po khams dang skye mched la //
NK078(tshu)001:7086: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med don //
NK078(tshu)001:7087: ye nas rdzogs sangs rgyas pa nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:7088: gang la brten nas rtogs pa nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:7089: lam gyi yan lag kun rdzogs te //
NK078(tshu)001:7090: sa bcu rim par ma bkod rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:7091: ma lus yon tan rang shar ba'i //
NK078(tshu)001:7093: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:7094: dbang po cig char spyod yul yin //
NK078(tshu)001:7095: ces pa dang sa dang pha rol phyin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7096: lam dang yon tan dus gcig rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:7097: zhes gsungs pa'i don gyis gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:7098: gnyis pa 'bring zag bcas kyis bden mthong cig char ba la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7100: dang po lta ba yul sems dbyer med du rtogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7102: lta ba rtogs pa rang rig pa'i ye shes ni
NK078(tshu)001:7103: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i
NK078(tshu)001:7104: gter ltar gang bsam pa thams cad 'byung ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:7105: te / des chos thamsa cad la bltas kyang me
NK078(tshu)001:7106: long gi gzugs brnyan snang la rang bzhin med pa
NK078(tshu)001:7107: te / bzhin du / phyi nang gi chos thams
NK078(tshu)001:7108: cad la bltas kyang gzugs snang rang rgyud du mi
NK078(tshu)001:7109: te / bzhin du / snang ngo // gnyis pa bzhag thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7110: rtogs pa'i don bsgom thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7114: dang po rtogs pa'i don la bzhag pas 'bras bu thob tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7116: rang gi shes pa'i rgyud kyi chos nyid ci yin
NK078(tshu)001:7117: pa rnal 'byor pa gang gis ye shes su ngo
NK078(tshu)001:7118: shes shing lta bas rtogs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:7119: de'i ngang la bsgom bya sgom byed gnyis su 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:7120: pa las 'phagsa te blo gyi na 'dra rtsol med
NK078(tshu)001:7121: du 'dug par byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang zhig
NK078(tshu)001:7122: /rang gi chos nyid rtogs pa'i blo la rtsol med
NK078(tshu)001:7123: du longs spyod pa de dag gis byang chub thob
NK078(tshu)001:7124: pa'o // gnyis pa dgongs pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7126: gdod ma nas gnyis 'dzin rnam par dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7127: chos nyid 'gyur med skye 'jigs med pas g.yunga drung lta bur ye nas sangsa rgyas pa'i don la /
NK078(tshu)001:7128: lta ba 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye gdod
NK078(tshu)001:7129: ma nyid nas bden gsum mnyam pa nyid du ngo
NK078(tshu)001:7130: bo rnama par dag par rtogs shing /
NK078(tshu)001:7131: ting nge 'dzin yul du mi rtog pa gzhi gnas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7132: sa ler gnas pa lhag mthong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7133: de gnyis zung du 'brel ba las yang dag pa'i rtogsa par mdzad ces smos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7134: gsum pa yon tan 'byung tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:7136: de'i nyams ni phyogs gcig tu 'di 'drar bsnyad du
NK078(tshu)001:7137: med pas drod rtags kyi yon tan sna tshogsa pa
NK078(tshu)001:7139: de chos kyi bdag gnyis su med pa'i sems nyid
NK078(tshu)001:7140: snang stong tha dad med cing bdag nyid chen po
NK078(tshu)001:7141: la yon tan nam 'bras bu thamsa cad zad 'phel
NK078(tshu)001:7142: med par 'byung ba'i gter lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7143: gnyis pa skyon bcos thabs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7145: dang po rnam rtog ye shes yin pas gnyen po mi bsten pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7147: tshogs drug ma bkag pa las rnam rtog sna tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:7148: rgyu zhing 'byung yang 'byung dus rang bzhin med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7149: rnam rtog skye ba'i dus nyid ngo shes na ye
NK078(tshu)001:7150: shes kyi rang bzhin yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:7151: yul sems dbang po rnam pa gsum du ma 'gag
NK078(tshu)001:7152: par snang zhing snang dus rang rgyud du grub pa
NK078(tshu)001:7153: med pas ngo bo rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong
NK078(tshu)001:7155: des na rnam par rtog pa'i rkyen rang ga ma mi skye zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:7156: de las gzhan du ye shes bya ba bzang po
NK078(tshu)001:7157: zhig brjod du med de gnyis med du rang grol
NK078(tshu)001:7158: ba'o // gnyis pa blo thams cad 'dzin rtsol med par rang byung rang zhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7161: chos thamsa cad semsa nyid kyi ngang du 'dus te /
NK078(tshu)001:7162: de'i ngo bo gang du'ang ma grub pas semsa zhes
NK078(tshu)001:7163: bya ba phyogs gcig tu ming gdamsa su med do
NK078(tshu)001:7164: // de nyid byed pa por ma bcosa 'khor 'das
NK078(tshu)001:7165: lhun grub tu gansa pas ye gdod ma nasa byang
NK078(tshu)001:7166: // chub yin canga / de nyid ma gtogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7167: 'bras bu thoba par bya rgyu zhig gzhan na med
NK078(tshu)001:7168: pas ye gdod ma nas rang bde bar gshegsa pa
NK078(tshu)001:7169: // chub yin canga / yin no // dper na
NK078(tshu)001:7170: kha dog sngon po la nam mkha'a zhes bya bar
NK078(tshu)001:7171: rang rgyud pas bzung bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:7172: de la sprin gyis khebsa par 'gyur gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:7173: nam mkha' ngo bo la ngos bzung med cing grub
NK078(tshu)001:7174: pa med par mkhas pa gang gis shes pa de
NK078(tshu)001:7175: la ni / sgrib byed kyi sprin zhig dag 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:7176: zhing spri na gyis nam mkha' khebsa par mi srid
NK078(tshu)001:7177: la ni / de bzhin du / rnal 'byor pas bsgom pa'i sems kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:7178: rnam rtog ye shes su ma shes na rtog pas sgrib la /
NK078(tshu)001:7179: rnam rtog ye shes su shes na rtog pas mi sgrib la /
NK078(tshu)001:7180: gnyis med du rang grol bas gong gi dpe de ltar blta bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7181: gsum pa bcos slad med par bzhag pas 'bras bu rang byung tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:7183: rtogs pa'i don la blo ma bcos rtsol med lhun
NK078(tshu)001:7184: grub tu gnas pa ci bzhin pa'i ngang du mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:7186: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med par ye nas lhun gyis
NK078(tshu)001:7187: grub pa'i dkyil 'khor mthar thug gi 'bras bu rang
NK078(tshu)001:7189: gsum pa ji bzhin mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:7191: gnas lugs de bzhin nyid la ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:7192: gnas bca' zhing bsgom na yon tan ni 'khor bar
NK078(tshu)001:7193: byed pa'i rgyu nyon mongsa pa dang 'bras bu sdug
NK078(tshu)001:7195: dus rtag tu zag pa med pa'i bde ba la gnas shing /
NK078(tshu)001:7196: 'bras bu bdag don byang chub chen po chos sku thob cing /
NK078(tshu)001:7197: gzhan don du gdul bya'i ngo la thun mong dang
NK078(tshu)001:7198: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan bzang po sum cu
NK078(tshu)001:7199: rtsa gnyis dang / dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu
NK078(tshu)001:7200: kun dang ldan pa'i gzugs sku gnyis su snang nas
NK078(tshu)001:7202: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa non pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7203: des na 'bras bu sku gnyis thob pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:7204: gnyis pa rim gyis pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7206: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7208: dper na srid pa bcud kyi 'gro ba 'ga' zhig
NK078(tshu)001:7209: rim para mngal nas skyes shing lus smin pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:7210: gyis / rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i yan lag la /
NK078(tshu)001:7213: phyag rgya gcig pa spros pa /
NK078(tshu)001:7214: tshogs sgrub dang lnga ru lus rnam par bzhag na /
NK078(tshu)001:7215: lam pa gang dag phyi nang gi dngos po shes
NK078(tshu)001:7216: bya'i chos kun rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi
NK078(tshu)001:7218: gsang ba'i mkhar lnga zhig ste sh+ri ba'i tshe rig pa brgyal ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:7219: tshogs drug yul la snang ba'i rtog pa 'gags pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7220: nang 'dzin zhen gyi rtog pa gnyis dang bral bas /
NK078(tshu)001:7221: don dam pa'i bden pa bsgom pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7222: de ting stong pa chen po dang 'dra ba'i phyir dper brjod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7225: de nas 'di phyi gnyis kyi skye ba bar ma ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7226: srid pa bar do da ltar gyi lus gdos bcas dang bral /
NK078(tshu)001:7227: sgyu ma'i lus dang bcas te dbang po kun gsal /
NK078(tshu)001:7228: gang la'ang thogs med du 'gro nus pa de kun
NK078(tshu)001:7229: rdzob kyi bden pa kun ting snying rje sgyu ma
NK078(tshu)001:7230: dang 'dra ba'i phyir dper brjod pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:7233: des las kyi rlung gis brdas te /
NK078(tshu)001:7234: skye gnas kyi dang po ma'i mngal du nyid mtshams sbyor ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7235: rten khu ba dkar dmar nyi zla'i gdan /
NK078(tshu)001:7236: rnam par shes pa ni gsung yig 'bru dang 'dra /
NK078(tshu)001:7237: de nas gtun shing ltar skyed rtags rgyur gyur pa ni thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje dang 'dra /
NK078(tshu)001:7238: de nas kha mig gdod pa ni sku phra mo dang 'dra /
NK078(tshu)001:7239: de nyid la rang bzhin gyi dge slong zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7240: skra dang kha spu med cing phrul ma'i chos gos dang ldan te /
NK078(tshu)001:7241: a ham gi sngags brjod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7242: de nas bltams te skyes pasa lo bcu gnyis man
NK078(tshu)001:7243: chad ni gzhon nu ste rim pa dang po phyag
NK078(tshu)001:7245: de nas lo nyi shu rtsa lnga'am bdun man chad
NK078(tshu)001:7246: la khyim thabs byas te bu tsha dang ldan pa
NK078(tshu)001:7247: ni phyag rgya spros pa dang 'dra ste rim pa
NK078(tshu)001:7248: gnyis pa'o // de nas yo byad la sogs 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:7249: rten pa'i bya ba sna tshogs bsgrub pa ni tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:7250: sgrub sa dang 'dra ste rim pa gsum pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7251: de ltar phyag rgya gcig pa spros pa tshogs sgrub gsum ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7252: don dam kun rdzob gnyis med du bsgom pa'i lam
NK078(tshu)001:7253: pa yin pas bden pa dbyer med rtogs pa'i thabs
NK078(tshu)001:7254: sam bslab byar brjod do zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7255: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7256: tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7257: sbyor lam bar chad med par tshogs sgrub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7258: dang po la le'u bzhis ston te /
NK078(tshu)001:7259: de la dang po le'u gsum pa de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7261: dang po lus mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7263: de la dang po don dam stong pa chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:7264: lam la brten par byed pa'i rnal 'byor pas chos
NK078(tshu)001:7265: thams cad de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la
NK078(tshu)001:7266: gsal stong gi ngo bo nyid du gomsa par bya
NK078(tshu)001:7267: ba'i thabs bstan pa la don bco lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7269: spyi dang khyad par gyi sngon du bya ba dang gcig /sgom pa'i dgos ched dang gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:7270: sgom pa la blo bzhag pa'i thabs dang gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:7271: sgom pa'i nga bo rnam grangs nges tshig dang bcas pa dang bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:7272: ting nge 'dzin gyi mi mthun pa'i skyon ngos bzung ba dang lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:7273: skyon de dag bcos pa'i thabs dang drug sgom pa'i nyamsa kyi rim pa dang bdun /
NK078(tshu)001:7277: rtagsa dang bcu gcig rmi ltas kyi mtshan ma dang bcu gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:7278: ting nge 'dzin gyi yon tan dang bcu gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:7279: 'da' ka ma'i man ngag dang bcu bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:7280: de ting rang gi 'bras bu dang bco lngas stong
NK078(tshu)001:7281: pa chen po'i rnal 'byor yongs su rdzogsa par 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:7282: ro // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la don bco lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7283: sgom pa'i sngon du bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7297: rang gi 'bras bu thob tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:7299: thun mong spyi'i sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7300: khyad par gyi sngon du bya ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7303: dang po sngon du dbang thob dgos par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7305: gsang sngags kyi rigs can skyes bu gang zhig dper na senga ge gcig pur gnas pa /
NK078(tshu)001:7306: 'jigs pa dang bral ba gzhan zin gyis gnon pa bzhin du grogs ngan spangs te gcig pu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7307: bar chad la sogs pa'i 'jigs pa dang bral ba /
NK078(tshu)001:7308: lta ba dman pa dang nyon mongs pa zin gyis
NK078(tshu)001:7309: gnon par gnas shing gcig pur rgyu ba yin pas
NK078(tshu)001:7310: na / de yang bsam gtan chos drug las /
NK078(tshu)001:7311: mang po rtag tu 'thab gyur te //
NK078(tshu)001:7312: gnyis pa dag kyang 'gran zlar gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:7313: gzhon nu ma yi gdug gu bzhin /
NK078(tshu)001:7314: gcig pur rab tu rgyu bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:7316: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la 'jug pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7317: sngon du lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK078(tshu)001:7318: ri mor phyi nang gsang gsum gyi dbang rnams rim
NK078(tshu)001:7319: pa bzhin du rdzogsa par mnos shing /
NK078(tshu)001:7320: gnyis pa lhag pa'i yo byad lnga rdzogs par bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7322: rgyud lung man ngag gi don phyin ci ma log
NK078(tshu)001:7323: par ston pa'i rdo rje slob dpon gyi rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:7324: brgyad ni / 'di nyid kyi le'u bdun pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:7325: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:7326: gnyen ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK078(tshu)001:7327: man ngag drod 'chang brgyad 'chang ba zhes so //
NK078(tshu)001:7328: de lta bu'i bla ma la /
NK078(tshu)001:7329: sgo gsum gus pa'i sgo nas mnyes pa gsum gyis mchod cing /
NK078(tshu)001:7330: brtson 'grus kyis rang gi rgyud yongs su sbyangsa pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7331: sgo nas rtogsa pa'i lta ba bden pa dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:7332: mngon sum du byas shing gasla bar byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:7334: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7335: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnams gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7336: spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid shes pa'i shes rab lta ba'i gdeng dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7337: kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i byang chub sems bskyed pa dang snying rje che ba dang lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:7338: 'jig rten pa'i yo byad las lhag pa byang chub
NK078(tshu)001:7339: bsgrub pa'i yo byad gang gi lnga po rgyud la
NK078(tshu)001:7340: rdzogs par bya'o // gsum pa yo byad lnga'i nang
NK078(tshu)001:7341: nas khyad par gzhan don du sems bskyed nas sgom
NK078(tshu)001:7344: gong gi yo byad lnga rdzogs pa de'i nang nas
NK078(tshu)001:7345: bu gcig pa la ma byams pa'i sems dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:7346: pas / khams gsum 'khor ba na gnas pa'i rigsa
NK078(tshu)001:7347: drug gi sems can thams cad thar pa mya ngan
NK078(tshu)001:7348: las 'das pa'i sar 'god par dam bcas nas sems
NK078(tshu)001:7349: pas / bskyed cing / bzhi pa tshad med du sngon du song bas sa bslang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7351: sems bskyed mi nyams pa'i thabs la tshangsa pa la
NK078(tshu)001:7352: sogs pa'i gnas su skye bar byed pa'i tshad med
NK078(tshu)001:7353: pa bzhi sngon du song ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:7354: rnal 'byor pa'i yid du 'onga zhing sa dgra la
NK078(tshu)001:7355: sogs ngan pa'i skyon med pa'i sa btsal nas sa
NK078(tshu)001:7356: bslang ste sa chog rgyas par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7357: lnga pa gnas brtsigs shing gdan bshams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7359: gnas khang che chung ran cing mtshams par byas te zhal la'i byi dor dang ldan par byas la /
NK078(tshu)001:7360: rin po ches sa'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7361: sman gyis nad kyi skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7362: gla rtsis sprul gdug pa can gyi skyon rnams bsrung bar byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:7363: yul lam si sar ta'i ras kyi stan tshang can dang ldana para bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7364: drug pa tshogs bsags cing 'brel thag bcad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7366: byang chub sgrub pa'i lam gyi phyi nang gi 'gal
NK078(tshu)001:7367: rkyen gyi bar chada thams cad bsal zhing lam gyi
NK078(tshu)001:7368: cha rkyen tshogsa gnyis yongs su rdzogsa par bya ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:7369: phyir / tshogs 'khor dang sbyin bsregs brgya rtsa la sogs bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7370: mdo sde 'bum lnga la sogs 'don pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7373: chu gtor gtong ba bskor ba la sogs pa dge ba'i dpung tshogsa la 'bad par bya'o /
NK078(tshu)001:7375: nang slob dpon dang mched lcam rnams kyi bu lon
NK078(tshu)001:7376: dang 'brel chags pa thamsa cad kun ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:7377: las gzhan pa rnams gegs yin pa'i phyir dur rkun
NK078(tshu)001:7378: wa sdar ma lta bu'i semsa kyis gong gi rkyen
NK078(tshu)001:7380: bdun pa cha rkyen bsdus zhing grogs btsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7382: khams gso ba'i cha rkyen sman zas rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7383: ting nge 'dzin skye ba'i cha rkyen bla ma'i gdam ngag zab mo'i dpe cha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7384: grogs nyams can la sogs pa mkho ba'i cha rkyen rnams bsdus la /
NK078(tshu)001:7385: lam gyi bar chad bgegs dang nang bsrung ba'i cha rkyen nam /
NK078(tshu)001:7386: cho ga rnams sngon du rdzogsa par byas nas phyi 'dod pa'i longsa spyod lnga'am /
NK078(tshu)001:7387: gsang ba'i longs spyod rigsa ma'ang mtshan nyid dang ldan pa brten par byas la /
NK078(tshu)001:7388: 'o na gong gi skyes bu seng ge bzhin rgyu bas zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal lam zhes na /
NK078(tshu)001:7390: seng ge ni de ting kun ting la sogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7391: dus su rnam g.yeng grogs ngan spang ba'i dpe yin
NK078(tshu)001:7392: la / rig ma ni phyag rgya spros pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7393: tshogs sgrub kyi dus su thun mong dang mchog gi
NK078(tshu)001:7394: dngos grub bskyed pa'i grogs yin pas 'gal ba med
NK078(tshu)001:7395: de / mchod bstod bshags pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:7396: sgrub pa'i rten mchog shes rab gzung ma dang //
NK078(tshu)001:7398: dgra bgegs nad gsum gyis 'tshe ba bzlog pa'i cha rkyen /
NK078(tshu)001:7402: gu gul la sogs pa'ang nye rdzogsa su bzhag go //
NK078(tshu)001:7403: gnyis pa khyad par gyi sngon du bya ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7405: de ltar thun mong du kun gyi spyi'i sngon du
NK078(tshu)001:7406: 'gro ba rnams rdzogas par byas nas khyad par de
NK078(tshu)001:7407: ting 'di nyid kyi sngon du bya ba ni mchod
NK078(tshu)001:7408: pa 'bul ba'i rten du dngos grub nye ba'i lha
NK078(tshu)001:7409: / yi dam gyi lha sku'i gzugs brnyan rab gnas can /
NK078(tshu)001:7410: rang gi mdun du bzhugs su gsol ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:7414: bshags pa yi rangs sems bskyed /
NK078(tshu)001:7416: bsngo ba'i yan lag brgyad pa de dag 'bul ba'i tshul yongs su bzung la de tshar nas /
NK078(tshu)001:7417: tshogs rten dbang po'i lha rnams 'od zhu yongas su gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:7418: bdag gi spyi gtsug tu thim par byas pas bdag
NK078(tshu)001:7419: gi sgo gsum gyi bsgrib pa bsregs nas rang nyid
NK078(tshu)001:7420: kyang 'od du zhu ba'i rjes la ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:7422: gnyis pa dgos ched la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7423: lam rim par bgrod nas sangs rgyas pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7424: de ting rang la 'jug pa'i dgos ched do //
NK078(tshu)001:7427: dang po lung gis 'thad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7429: snod bcud rgyud rnams rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7430: ye shes lngar dag pa rnam pa gsum ma nor bar rtogs shing /
NK078(tshu)001:7431: ting nge 'dzin gyis rang rig pa'i rgyal po la
NK078(tshu)001:7432: rang dbang bsgyur nas rtogs pa de nyid bsgom pa
NK078(tshu)001:7433: yin / 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK078(tshu)001:7434: kyi mchog chos sku 'di nyid rnyed par 'gyur ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:7435: yin / // gnyis pa des grub pa'i don no //
NK078(tshu)001:7437: gang gi gtan tshig de'i phyir lta ba mthong ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:7438: rjes la de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:7439: mo // de ni snying rje chen po kun snang
NK078(tshu)001:7440: gi ting nge 'dzin 'byung ba'i gzhi'am sgyu ru bzhag
NK078(tshu)001:7441: mo // ces bya ste / lam gong 'og gi
NK078(tshu)001:7442: go rim 'byung ba snga ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:7443: rjes la phyi ma 'byung ba'ang de bzhin du nges
NK078(tshu)001:7444: mo // ces bya ste / so // gnyis pa
NK078(tshu)001:7445: de ting rang la 'jug pa'i dgos ched la gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:7446: mo // ces bya ste / so // te / dgos ched dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7447: ting nge 'dzin 'di med pa'i skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:7452: lam pa gang dag gsang sngags kyi skal ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:7453: ldan yang blo cung zad dman pa rim gyis pas
NK078(tshu)001:7454: / mi mthun pa'i phyogs gzhan sel ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7455: mthun pa'i phyogs bsgrub bya chos sku don du /
