NK078(tshu)001:7456: gnyer pa'i dgos ched gnyis yod pa'i phyir bsgom dgos pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7457: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7459: dang po gzhan sel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7461: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par 'jug par byed pa
NK078(tshu)001:7462: de'ang dkyus kyi snga ma gzhan sel ba'ang bdag gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:7463: gnyis kyi don du bsgom pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7464: bsal bya rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7465: rkyen kun brtags kyi ma rig pas phyin ci log
NK078(tshu)001:7466: tu 'khrul ba'i snang ba las thar dka' bas na
NK078(tshu)001:7467: 'dam rdzab dang 'dra ba'i dbyingsa su sel byed rang
NK078(tshu)001:7468: rig pa'i ye shes kyis spyod yul du gsal bas
NK078(tshu)001:7469: sgron ma dang 'dra ba'i mda' ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:7470: 'phangsa nas / de'i yon tan rang gi rgyud la
NK078(tshu)001:7471: yod pa'i dngos 'dzin gati mug gi mun pa rnams
NK078(tshu)001:7472: ma spangs gnas su dag pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:7474: gang mi snang snang bar byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:7475: don dam pa'i bden pa sems nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i ngang la /
NK078(tshu)001:7476: nyon mongs pa'i rtogs pa'i zung rngu med pas na
NK078(tshu)001:7477: bde ba'i nang nas mchog tu gyur pa de nyid
NK078(tshu)001:7479: de yang mdor bsdu na sgrib pa'i tshogs rnams ting
NK078(tshu)001:7480: nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i dus su sgrib pa ma spangs
NK078(tshu)001:7481: par dag pa'i dpe khrigs mun pa sgron me btegs
NK078(tshu)001:7482: pas / mun pa ma spangs bar snang bar song ba'i tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:7483: gnyis pa don gnyer la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7485: dang po chos nyid don du gnyer ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7487: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid dbyingsa nam mkha' lta bu'i thog tu pheb pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7488: dkyil phyogs su thug pa med pas yangsa pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:7489: chos nyid rtogs pa'i blos shes rab kyis dus myur
NK078(tshu)001:7490: ba gcig chod du don chos nyid la 'gro ba'ang
NK078(tshu)001:7491: / don la 'gro ba med cing 'ong ba med
NK078(tshu)001:7492: de mtha' gang la mi gnas pas gnas lugs byang
NK078(tshu)001:7493: chub kyi semsa mchog ma skyes pa'i zug rngu med
NK078(tshu)001:7494: pas a rab tu bde ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7495: gnyis pa dngos grub don du gnyer ba'i dgos ched do //
NK078(tshu)001:7497: dper na nyi ma shar dus mun pa snang bar gyur pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7498: dug sprul gla bas zos pa'i tshe gla rtsir gyur
NK078(tshu)001:7499: pa'i tshul bzhin du rtogsa pa'i ngo bo ma spang
NK078(tshu)001:7500: par chos nyid du dbang bsgyur bar byed pa ting
NK078(tshu)001:7502: lam pa kun gyi don du gnyer ba'i mchog thun
NK078(tshu)001:7503: mong gi dngos grub gang dag ma lus pa kun
NK078(tshu)001:7504: / de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di yis thob pa'i grogs byed par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:7508: gal te de ting stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor 'di med pas skyon ci yod ce na /
NK078(tshu)001:7509: dper na rgya mtsho 'jing gi pha bong de steng
NK078(tshu)001:7510: du mi thon zhing dkyil skam por yod pa ltar
NK078(tshu)001:7511: yul bskal ba dpag tu med par mtshan bcas kyi
NK078(tshu)001:7512: ting nge 'dzin lam la 'bad nas 'bras bu btsal
NK078(tshu)001:7513: bar byas kyang / gnas lugs de bzhin kyi don
NK078(tshu)001:7514: gyi rlan med na bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK078(tshu)001:7515: snying po'i myu gu bskamsa pa yin te 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:7517: gsum pa sgom pa'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7519: dang po lus kyi 'dug thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7521: de ting med na skyon yod pa de bas na
NK078(tshu)001:7522: de ting sgom dgos pa de'i phyir lhag ma'i lus
NK078(tshu)001:7524: lus bde ba dang ldan zhing sems thar ba la brod pas lus chos bdun gyi tshul te /
NK078(tshu)001:7526: rkang pa mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung bca' ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7527: g.yas g.yon gyi bo la gong gnyis kyi barla'i 'phar
NK078(tshu)001:7528: rtsa bo bzhi mnan nas lus la drod rang shugs
NK078(tshu)001:7529: kyis skye'o lag pa manyama pa'i phyag rgya lte 'og
NK078(tshu)001:7530: tu bca' ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7531: rtsa thams cad 'dus pa'i mdo de mnan pas rlung
NK078(tshu)001:7532: a ba rdu tir rang shugs kyis tshud nas 'ong
NK078(tshu)001:7533: / rked pa dngul gyi dung rtse brtsegs pa ltar
NK078(tshu)001:7534: bsrangs pas de'i dgos ched ni lus kyi ljid cha
NK078(tshu)001:7535: mnyam pas nad mi ldang ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7536: de yang lus mdun du rgu na mchin pa bab /
NK078(tshu)001:7537: ltag pa'am ro stod dgyes na snying rlung ldang /
NK078(tshu)001:7538: g.yas g.yon du yo na mkhal ma na ru 'ong ba yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:7539: lus cha bsrangs pas de dag mi 'ong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7540: mgrin pa lcags kyu ltar dgug pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7541: de'i dgos pa ni steng rlung rang bzhin gyis non nas sems zin pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7542: ol bdud non pas gnyid log pa'i rtsa gnyis non nas mi rtog pa skye ba'i gnad do //
NK078(tshu)001:7543: mig ri dwags kyi rgyal po sha ra na bag pheb pa ltar sna rtser dbab pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7544: de'i dgos pa ni shes pa yul gzhan du mi 'phro ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7545: lce ya rkan la sbyar bas gre ba mi skam mo //
NK078(tshu)001:7546: mchu so tha mal du bzhag pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7547: lus sems la lhod chags so //
NK078(tshu)001:7548: de ltar byas pas lus gnas su rtsa tshud /
NK078(tshu)001:7549: rtsa gnas su rlung tshud nas rlung rang gnas su tshud /
NK078(tshu)001:7550: de tshud pas dbus kyi rta pho la sems kyi
NK078(tshu)001:7551: mi phos zhon nas rlung zin pas sems rang shugs
NK078(tshu)001:7553: gnyis pa sems kyi bzhag thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7557: lus su 'dzin pa dang rtsol ba'i rtogs pa med
NK078(tshu)001:7558: pa'i semsa kyis ting nge 'dzin la 'dug par bya
NK078(tshu)001:7559: ba de yang blo chung ba bla ma'i gdamsa ngag
NK078(tshu)001:7560: la brten nas mnyam par 'jog pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7561: blo che ba rang gi shes rab kya stobsa kyis
NK078(tshu)001:7562: lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang la blo bzhag pasa de
NK078(tshu)001:7563: ting la gomsa para byed pa gnyis yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:7564: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7566: dang po blo chung ba gdams ngag gi stobs kyis bzhag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7568: mdor bstan gyis sngon du brjod pa'i gdams ngag gi
NK078(tshu)001:7569: stobs kyis bzhag pa'i slob bu de grong yul ngang
NK078(tshu)001:7570: 'du 'dzi'i bya ba las ring du dben pa'i sar
NK078(tshu)001:7571: khrid la / gser g.yu la sogs pa rin po che dang lhab lhub dar zab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7572: bza' btung la sogs pa'i longs spyod kyi bye brag sna tshogs kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:7573: bla ma dam pa manyes par byasa nas slob bu
NK078(tshu)001:7574: de slob dpon gyi dpang du ste mdun du drang
NK078(tshu)001:7575: por bzhag la / mkha' 'gro dang rna nyan la
NK078(tshu)001:7576: sogs pa'i bgegas rnams drag sngags kyis bskrad la rat+na'i
NK078(tshu)001:7577: sbubsa mchus rna ba la gtad de /
NK078(tshu)001:7578: gzhan gyis ma thos par gdams ngag zhib par shub bus /
NK078(tshu)001:7579: rna ba g.yon par bsgrags shing sems su gtim mo //
NK078(tshu)001:7580: gdams ngag dngos ni mchog thun mong gi dngos grub
NK078(tshu)001:7581: dus myur du tshe 'di la 'grub par 'doda na
NK078(tshu)001:7582: / bsgom bya bsgom byed shin tu mi dmigs par
NK078(tshu)001:7583: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i dbyingsa su bsgom mo
NK078(tshu)001:7584: / // gnyis pa blo che ba shes rab kyi stobs kyis sgom pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7586: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7588: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma shes rab kyis stobs kyis bzhag pa la'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:7589: dper na gangs la nyi ma shar ma thag lhag gis gsal ba dang 'dra bar /
NK078(tshu)001:7590: rig pa gsal stong gi ting nge 'dzin spyi blugsa
NK078(tshu)001:7591: te rang lugs su blo g.yer gyis gnas pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:7592: / sngar gyi lta ba dran par byas shing mthonga
NK078(tshu)001:7593: ba'i rjes su gsal stong gi ting nge 'dzin la
NK078(tshu)001:7595: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7596: rig pa spyi blugs su bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7597: lta ba rtogs pa'i rjes su bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7600: dang po bdag dang bdag gir med par rig pa spyi blugs su bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7602: bdag ngar 'dzin pa rnam shes dang bdag gis myong ba'i phung po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7603: gzhan 'byung ba yul du snang ba rnams ni bsgom bya'i yul shin tu blos mi dmigas te /
NK078(tshu)001:7604: skye med de bzhin nyid kyi dbyingsa su grol bar
NK078(tshu)001:7605: sgom pa dran pa tsam yul med rang gsal du
NK078(tshu)001:7606: bsgom pa'o // de'i rgyu mtshan ni rnal 'byor pa
NK078(tshu)001:7607: rang gi rig pa chos nyid gsal stong gi ngang
NK078(tshu)001:7608: la gnas pa'i don de byed pa po sus kyang
NK078(tshu)001:7609: bsgom pa'o // ma byas shing / rgyu rkyen med pas rang byung yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:7610: des phyi nang gi chos thamsa cad skye med de
NK078(tshu)001:7611: bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gsal bar spyor ba ni
NK078(tshu)001:7612: / bsgom bya bsgom byed gnyis su 'dzin pa med pas skye med de /
NK078(tshu)001:7613: skye med chos dbyingsa kyi nganga du rig pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:7614: chos thams cad thimsa te ngo bo ma grub par yul sems gnyis su med par gsal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7615: gnyis pa rang byung spro bsdu med par rig pa spyi blugs su bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7617: rgyu rkyen med pa rang byung gsal bas ye shes ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khora gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:7618: shes bya phyi nang gi chos ma lus pa thams
NK078(tshu)001:7619: cad chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gsal
NK078(tshu)001:7621: 'o na bsdu bya sdud byed gnyis su yod dam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:7623: mi sdud par 'jog pa gnyis ka grub pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:7624: de nyid ma nor zhing mi bslu bas na yanga
NK078(tshu)001:7625: dag pa'i don ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid
NK078(tshu)001:7626: rig pa yul med du rang gsal bar 'dug pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:7627: // gsum pa bsgom bya bsgom byed med par rig pa spyi blugs su bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7629: bsgom par bya ba'i yul chos nyid bsgom par byed
NK078(tshu)001:7630: pa'i mkhan po gnyis ka don dam par ma skyes
NK078(tshu)001:7632: don chos nyid yid kyi yul du byas nas bsgom par bya ba'ang med de /
NK078(tshu)001:7633: de ltar dona dam par bsgom par bya ba'i yul med pasa na /
NK078(tshu)001:7634: bsgom bya'i yul gang la'ang sgom pa po'i blo yul du mi dmigs nas mi 'jug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7635: bsgom bya sgom byed gnyis su med par gsal ba
NK078(tshu)001:7636: de ka ting nge 'dzin la zhugsa pa'i mchog yin
NK078(tshu)001:7637: te / gzhal tu med pa'i bzhag thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:7638: bzhi pa bsam bya bsam byed med par rig pa spyi blugs su bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7640: chos nyid blo'i yul du bsam par bya rgyu cir yang bsam par mi bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7643: ched du bsam pa dgag pa'i phyir mi bsal par yang mi bsam mo //
NK078(tshu)001:7644: de nyid yongsa su bcud du med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:7645: bsam mi bsam gyi yul gang la'ang blo rnama par
NK078(tshu)001:7646: mi sems pa'i ting nge 'dzin de ni yul med
NK078(tshu)001:7647: rang gsal bas / rang rig mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la gnas pa nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:7648: gnyis pa lta ba rtogs pa'i rjes su bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7653: dang po shes rab mchog gi sa rtogs pa'i lta ba 'dir go ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7655: lhag pa don dam pa'i byang chub semsa kyi de bzhin nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7656: shin tu mi dmigsa shing nyi ma'i snying po ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:7657: blo phyogs zhen can gyis brtag par dka' bas de ni blo bar snang ltar yangsa la /
NK078(tshu)001:7658: sa gzhi ltar rgya che rgya mtsho ltar gting zab
NK078(tshu)001:7659: pa'i shes rab dang ldan pas gsang sngags zab pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7662: rtog dpyod kyis lta ba dran par byas te de'i rjes su bsgom par byas zhes pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7663: gnyis pa rang gi rtogs pa'i ngo bo la 'gro 'ong dang mtha' dbus med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7665: de ltar sgom pa'i byang sems de dang por gang
NK078(tshu)001:7666: nas kyang ma 'ongsa mthar gar yang mi 'gro bas
NK078(tshu)001:7667: des na 'gro ba dang 'ong bar bya ba gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:7669: don de ni rang gi ngo bo shin tu blos brtag par dka' zhing yul du mi dmigas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7670: spros pa'i mtha' dang bral bas dbus kyang 'di zhes brtag tu med do //
NK078(tshu)001:7671: gnyis pa sgom pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7673: dang po rtogs pa'i don la gnyis med rang snang gi sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7675: 'o na ci ltar yin na gzung 'dzin gnyis dang
NK078(tshu)001:7676: bral ba'i rang gi rig pa nyid dmigsa bya dmigs
NK078(tshu)001:7677: byed med pa'i tshul du rang gsal bas der snang
NK078(tshu)001:7678: ngo // de yang bsgom bya don dam chos kyi dbyingsa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7679: dbyingsa de rtogs byed kyi ye shes gnyis kyang gzhan na yod pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:7680: rang gi rig pa gsal stong de kho na tsam
NK078(tshu)001:7681: du zad pas yul shes gnyis su med par bstan
NK078(tshu)001:7682: pa'o // gnyis pa sgom thabs de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7684: dang po dmigs pas gol la dmigs med sangs rgyas yin par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7686: gang zag blo chung ba gang zhig gis bsgom bya'i
NK078(tshu)001:7687: yul du dmigsa nas ting nge 'dzin la blo 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:7688: pa ni / dmigs pa yod pa de srid du
NK078(tshu)001:7689: 'jig rten rgyang 'phen pa'i lta ba dang 'dra la
NK078(tshu)001:7690: stong pa la yul du dmigs nas blos 'jug tu
NK078(tshu)001:7691: med cing yul med rang gsal ba de ni sangsa
NK078(tshu)001:7692: rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7693: thub pa'i dbang po nyid dang rgyal ba kun gyis gsungsa te /
NK078(tshu)001:7695: gang gis dmigs med mi shes par //
NK078(tshu)001:7696: de yis chos kyi dbyings mi shes //
NK078(tshu)001:7699: rang byung ye shes nam mkha' che //
NK078(tshu)001:7700: yod med gnyis su dmigs su med //
NK078(tshu)001:7702: gnyis pa dmigs med mi mthong ba dpe dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7704: blos nges par bsgom bya chos nyid cig blo'i yul
NK078(tshu)001:7705: du bsam zhing de la yul du byas shing dmigsa
NK078(tshu)001:7707: dper na phra raba khab mig tu 'then thag skud pa 'dzud pa lta bus /
NK078(tshu)001:7708: don chos nyid de bzhin nyid dmigs su med pa de'i don mi mthong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7709: 'then thag skud pa khab mig tu 'dzud pa'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:7710: su nam mkha' chen po mi mthong ba bzhin no
NK078(tshu)001:7711: // bzhi pa ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7715: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor skye med mnyam pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7716: de bzhin nyid ngo bo tha dad du ngos bzung
NK078(tshu)001:7717: ba bzhin du rnam grangsa kyang 'jug cing /
NK078(tshu)001:7718: zhor la nges tshig dang rnam pa gsum nges par 'byung ba yina te /
NK078(tshu)001:7719: de bas kun snang la sogs lam phyi ma kun
NK078(tshu)001:7720: la ngo bo nges tshig rnam grangs gsum du 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:7721: bar gyis shig /gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:7723: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi don gyi rnam grangs spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7725: nyan rang la ltos na chen po gsang sngags la
NK078(tshu)001:7726: ltos na dman pa dbu ma pas 'og ma'i grub
NK078(tshu)001:7727: mtha' brgyad po bkag cing bsal ba'i don dam pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7728: chos nyid rgyu rkyen las ma skyes shing /
NK078(tshu)001:7729: ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i stong pa nyin du 'dod do //
NK078(tshu)001:7730: de yang sngar ma stong pa zhig 'phral du stong par song ba ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:7731: ye gdod ma nas stong pa la stong pa nyid bya ba'i tha snyad tsam yang bral bas /
NK078(tshu)001:7734: gcig dang du ma'i spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral
NK078(tshu)001:7735: bar 'dod la bral ba tsam 'dzin pa yang ma
NK078(tshu)001:7736: yin no // sngags kri ya ba gang gis rang
NK078(tshu)001:7737: gi semsa nyid dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma med
NK078(tshu)001:7738: pa'i de bzhina nyid rnam pa daga pa'i chos nyid
NK078(tshu)001:7740: rnal 'byor yo ga bas chos dbyings mnyam pa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:7741: la spros pa'i matshana ma meda pa'i de bzhina nyid
NK078(tshu)001:7743: ma h+aa yo gas 'khor 'das gnyis med lhun grub mnyam pa chen po'i de bzhin nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:7744: gnyis pa khyad par du ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid rgyas par bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7746: dang po ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid dpag tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7748: de bzhin nyid kyi rnam grangs bzhi'i rim pa tha
NK078(tshu)001:7749: ma ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid ni byin rlabsa cir
NK078(tshu)001:7751: yon tan mthar thug gi 'bras bu lhun grub thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7752: ngo bo dkor bdun snang stong gnyis su med pas na kun gyi bla mar gyur pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7755: yon tan gyi dpag pa rnams go rim ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:7756: dbu mas don dam stong zhing spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba'i stong pa phyogs gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7757: kri yas sems dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma dang bral ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7758: yo gas chos dbyings mnyam pa nyid la spros pa'i mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7759: ma h+aas snang ba gang yang ma spangs pa'i stong chen du 'dug pas dpag go //
NK078(tshu)001:7760: byin rlabs kyi dpag pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7761: dbu ma'i don dam la cir yang mi 'char ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7762: kri ya la rigs gsum tsam dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7763: yo ga la rigs lnga tsam las mi snang la /
NK078(tshu)001:7764: ma h+aa'i don dam la lha stong dang nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs pa snang bas dpags so //
NK078(tshu)001:7765: yon tan gyis dpag pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7766: dbu mas don dam mthar phyin pa'i yon tan kun tu 'ong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7767: de bzhin du kri yas rig gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7768: yo gas stug por bkod par rigs lnga tsam las mi thob la /
NK078(tshu)001:7769: ma h+aa yo gas pad+ma spyan la sogs pa thob pas dpags so //
NK078(tshu)001:7770: gnyis pa rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7772: dang po rnam grangs ma 'dres par yon tan gyi cha nas ming grangs bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7774: bla mar gyur pa'i don bshad pa de la yang /
NK078(tshu)001:7775: lung man ngag rigs pa gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:7776: rig pa la ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7778: de la ngo bo ni thun mong ma yin pa'i ngos nas bzhag pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:7779: de la'nga skabsa kyi ming gi rnam grangs su phyes na /
NK078(tshu)001:7780: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bzang ngan ma spangs bas mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7781: gang yang phyogs gcig ma grub pas lhun grub dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7782: mtha' gang yang ma spangs bas mtha' bral dang ming
NK078(tshu)001:7783: du brtags pa ltar snang bas tha snyad med pa
NK078(tshu)001:7784: dang / sna tshogs su snang bas stong chen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7785: cir yang ma 'gag pas ma skyes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7786: gang yang 'byung ba med pas chos dbyingsa la sogas
NK078(tshu)001:7787: pa ngo bo'i yona tan gyi bye brag cha re
NK078(tshu)001:7788: nas ming re brjod par zad do //
NK078(tshu)001:7790: ming gi dam tshig sgra don gyi sgo nas bzhag pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:7791: de yang gnas skabs kyi ming gis rnam grangs su phyes na /
NK078(tshu)001:7792: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bzang ngan med pas mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7793: ma btsal bar cir yang snang bas lhun grub dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7794: mtha'i zhen pa med pas mtha' bral ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7795: bye brag tu ming du btags pa med pas tha snyad med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7796: snang ba gang yang ma spang bas stong chen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7797: rgyu rkyen med pas ma skyes pa dang kun gyi
NK078(tshu)001:7798: 'byung khungs su gyur pa'i phyir chos dbyings la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:7799: pa nges tshig gi yon tan gyi bye brag cha
NK078(tshu)001:7800: re nas ming re brjod par zad do //
NK078(tshu)001:7801: gnyis pa de gang yang mi 'gal bar gtan tshig gsum dang ldan par gnas tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:7803: de ltar mnyam nyid la sogs bdun po re re
NK078(tshu)001:7804: la'ang gnas skabas kyi phye bas gong du bshad pa
NK078(tshu)001:7805: ltar ngo bo thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7806: sgra'i ming gis don mtshon pa'i nges tshig thun mong du brjod pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:7807: de dag sgrub par byedapa'i gtan tshig gi yan lag tu dang ldan pa yin zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:7808: lung man ngag rig pa rnam pa gsum thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:7809: la 'phrug par sbyor ba rgyud las 'byung ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:7810: te / rdo rje me long las /
NK078(tshu)001:7811: lung dam man ngag rig pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:7812: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal ba //
NK078(tshu)001:7813: shes byed de yang tshad mar gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:7816: gzhi lam 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK078(tshu)001:7817: dris lan dam bcas mthar dbyung ba //
NK078(tshu)001:7818: lung dang man ngag rigs sgo nas //
NK078(tshu)001:7819: rtog par bya phyir rnam bshad bya //
NK078(tshu)001:7821: de ltar na sa mig bdun po de dag re
NK078(tshu)001:7822: re la'ang lung man ngag rig pa gsum gsum du
NK078(tshu)001:7823: 'byung ste / rig pas bsgrub pa ni gong du song la /
NK078(tshu)001:7824: lung la mnyam pa nyid kyi lung ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7826: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yis //
NK078(tshu)001:7827: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK078(tshu)001:7829: snang zhing grags pa'i chos rnams dang //
NK078(tshu)001:7830: mthong thos sgo lnga ci shar yang //
NK078(tshu)001:7831: rang zhal rang gis mthong bas na //
NK078(tshu)001:7832: gnyis su lta ba'i yul gzhan med //
NK078(tshu)001:7833: gnyis su med do mnyam pa che //
NK078(tshu)001:7836: yul sems mnyam pa'i klong du grol //
NK078(tshu)001:7837: chu zla'i tshul du mi dmigs gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:7838: mi dmigs pa nyid sna tshogs snang //
NK078(tshu)001:7839: de bzhin gshegs par ye nas mnyam //
NK078(tshu)001:7840: mnyam pa'i don rtogs mchog gi gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:7843: thams cad mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK078(tshu)001:7844: rang byung ye shes 'phro ba yis //
NK078(tshu)001:7848: bcing med rnam par dkrol med pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:7849: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK078(tshu)001:7851: rtsol sgrub gnyis kyi spros dang bral //
NK078(tshu)001:7852: lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras bu yin //
NK078(tshu)001:7855: lhun grub rdo rje zhes bya ba dam tshig ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7858: chos rnams dbyer med gcig pa ste //
NK078(tshu)001:7861: de phyir ma yin kun yin pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:7862: ci yang yin no lhun gyis grub //
NK078(tshu)001:7866: gcig dang du mar bral ba yis //
NK078(tshu)001:7867: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:7869: rgyas pa las kyang mtha' 'bral rdo rje zhes bya ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7872: ma lus gcig dang tha dad min //
NK078(tshu)001:7873: gang gi mtha' las yongs grol te //
NK078(tshu)001:7874: mtha' dang dbus med du mar bral //
NK078(tshu)001:7876: mtha' dang bral phyir ma bral ba //
NK078(tshu)001:7877: ma bral phyir na bral zhes bya //
NK078(tshu)001:7879: tha snyad med pa'i lung ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7881: ming med tshig med brjod du med //
NK078(tshu)001:7884: thams cad thams cad ji snyed pa //
NK078(tshu)001:7885: tshig gi tha snyad tsam dag las //
NK078(tshu)001:7886: 'di las bya ba ci yang med //
NK078(tshu)001:7887: rang bzhin nyid de ye sangs rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:7890: ming med tshig med brjod du med //
NK078(tshu)001:7891: bla dwags tsam du brjod pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:7893: chos dbyings tha snyad med pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:7895: stong pa chen po'i lung ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7897: yang dag rtogs pas rab brtag na //
NK078(tshu)001:7898: dngos po thams cad stong pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:7902: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK078(tshu)001:7904: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen po //
NK078(tshu)001:7905: sangs rgyas bas kyang sngar sangs rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:7909: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK078(tshu)001:7910: skyes pa nyid na skyes pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:7913: skye med chos kyi dbyings na gsal //
NK078(tshu)001:7916: rang byung ye shes rgyus ma skyes //
NK078(tshu)001:7917: skye med rang gsal rgyun mi chad //
NK078(tshu)001:7919: chos kyi dbyings kyi lung ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7921: chos dbyings rdo rje zhes bya ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7924: shes rab dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:7925: thabs kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:7928: mi dmigs chos dbyings la sogs pa //
NK078(tshu)001:7931: dbyings la dbyings ni rnam par sbyor //
NK078(tshu)001:7934: chos dbyings nam mkha'i mtha' klas gang //
NK078(tshu)001:7936: gsum pa bsgom gyi ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7937: don dam ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7938: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyi 'bras bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7942: dang po don dang ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7944: theg pa 'og ma'i don dam gsum las lhag pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:7945: ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid kyi don mchog gang yin
NK078(tshu)001:7946: pa de ni / 'khor 'das kyi dngos po rnams
NK078(tshu)001:7947: su snang ba'i dus nyid na dngos po rang rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:7948: par grub pa med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:7949: rtogsa pa'i blo gang du'ang smra bsam gyi yul las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:7950: ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid rang bzhin don dam dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7951: mu mtha' med pa'i dbyingsa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7952: sgrib g.yogs dang bral bar gsal bas ye shes don dam ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7953: gnyis pa de nyid zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7955: 'di la btsegs sdeb gcig byed pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7956: don dam de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin gsal bar rtogs pa'i mthar mi g.yo ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:7957: spros pa'i mtshan ma zhi gnas chos nyid mi rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:7958: pa'i ngang la rtse gcig tu gnas pa zhi gnas
NK078(tshu)001:7959: / chos nyid yul med rig pa rang gsal rnal
NK078(tshu)001:7960: 'byor gyi mngon sum lhag gis mthong bas lhag mthong
NK078(tshu)001:7961: / / de gnyis tha mi dad cing dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:7962: pas zung du 'brel bar gsal bar zung du 'brel
NK078(tshu)001:7963: / / lo // gnyis pa dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med kyi 'bras bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7965: de tsam na chos thams cad rang bzhin med pas shes rab /
NK078(tshu)001:7966: mu mtha' med pas dbyingsa nyid du dbyer med pa de la /
NK078(tshu)001:7967: bsgom bya chos kyi dbyingsa la bsgom byed blo'i shes
NK078(tshu)001:7968: rab kyis rtogs pa'i dbyingsa de nyid ni tha dad
NK078(tshu)001:7969: med par rnam par sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7970: de ltar blo'i shes rab dang chos kyi dbyingsa nyid tha dad med par sbyor ba yis /
NK078(tshu)001:7971: byang ba stong pa chub pa snang ba dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:7972: pas rdo rje spros pa med pa'i thig le yin
NK078(tshu)001:7973: no // gsum pa bsgoms pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:7975: bsgom pa de yang so sor rtogsa pa'i shes rab
NK078(tshu)001:7976: kyis lta ba mthong ba'i rjes su bsgoma pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:7977: / gdam ngag gi stobs kyis bsgom pa gang gis yang bsgom tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:7978: bsgom bya mnyam bzhag gi yul mi dmigsa /
NK078(tshu)001:7979: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo shin tu'ang mi dmigsa pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7980: rjes su thob pa'i shes pa'ang mi dmigsa pa'i rim pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7981: bsgom bya' yul du mi gnas shing /
NK078(tshu)001:7982: sgom pa'i ngo bor mi rtog rjes bdag gis bsgom pa po'i nga rgyal gyis rlom semsa meda pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:7983: bzhi pa nges tshig la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:7985: dang po sgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi nges tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7987: stong pa'i ngang las rang bzhin ngang gisa chos dang
NK078(tshu)001:7988: gang zag gi bdag gnyis su grub pa med pas
NK078(tshu)001:7989: na / bsgom bya'i yul dang bsgom byed kyi shes pa gnyis ka rang bzhin mi dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:7990: nam mkha' ltar blo'i yul du byed pa med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:7991: bsgom par bya ba'i yul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:7992: sgom par byed pa'i 'adu byed kun dang bral ba /
NK078(tshu)001:7993: blo gang du'ang bsam du med pa'i ngang la 'dug
NK078(tshu)001:7994: pa tsam la sgom pa zhes tha snyad du brjod
NK078(tshu)001:7995: pa'o // gnyis pa 'du 'bral med par sgom pa'i nges tshig go //
NK078(tshu)001:7997: bsgom bya sgom byed kyi 'adu shes kyis yul snang
NK078(tshu)001:7998: stong la sogs pa gang du'ang 'dzin pa ma zhugsa
NK078(tshu)001:7999: na / chos nyid bsgom pa'i ro la 'doda cing
NK078(tshu)001:8000: chagas pa med par rang gi blo dang don gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:8002: lnga pa skyon la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8006: de ltar gdams ngag gi stobs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8007: de ltar shes rab kyi stobs kyis mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:8008: ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i dus kyi skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8009: rjes spyod lam gyi ting nge 'dzin la sgrib pa'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8010: khams kyi skyon rnamas nor sar skyon ngos zin nas
NK078(tshu)001:8011: bcos na ting nge 'dzin mi 'phrog par bya ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:8012: phyir skyon gyi rnam grangs mdo tsam zhig brjod par
NK078(tshu)001:8014: gnyis pa rgyas par de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8015: ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i dus kyi skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8017: spyod lam sgom chen gyi skyon drug go //
NK078(tshu)001:8020: dang po thun mong dang dogs log gi skyon bco brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8022: de la las dang po bas bla ma'i gdams ngag gi dmigsa pa brjed pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8023: dang po g.yo ba'i nyams kyi dus su dmigs med du bzhag pa'i dran pas bzung shor te /
NK078(tshu)001:8024: sems bying nas bsgom bya'i don mi gsal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8025: des zhi gnas lhag mthong zung 'brel spyir sgrib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8026: 'o na gong du gang zhig dmigs nas 'jug pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8028: zhes pa la sogs pa bsgom dmigs bya dmigs byed med par bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8029: 'dir dmigs pa brjod pa skyon du bshad pa gnyis 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:8032: stong pa nyid du dmigs nas yul du bsgom na /
NK078(tshu)001:8033: gnyis 'dzin yin pas de bzhin nyid mi mthong ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:8034: skyon yin pas dmigs med du bzhag par bstan pa
NK078(tshu)001:8035: yin la / 'di nyid ni dran pa'i gdams ngag gis bsgom du 'jog par ma byas na /
NK078(tshu)001:8036: phyal bar song nas dran med dam tha mal du
NK078(tshu)001:8037: lus na skyon du bstan pa yin pas mi 'gal
NK078(tshu)001:8038: lo // bying ba ni bsgom bya'i don mi gsal ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8039: shes pa bying thibs se song ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8041: rang bzhin gyis bying ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8043: ched du bya ba'i bying ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8045: gang zag 'du ba bad kan dang nyon mongs gti
NK078(tshu)001:8046: mug shas che ba rnams rang bzhin gyis lus lci
NK078(tshu)001:8047: zhing shes pa / mun nas 'ong ba de la
NK078(tshu)001:8048: ting nge 'dzin gsal cha chung ba zhig las mi
NK078(tshu)001:8049: zhing shes pa / 'ong ngo // gnyis pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8050: lus ngal dub kyi las byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8052: sha chang la sogs pa kha zas bcud chen bag
NK078(tshu)001:8053: med du bstan cing mal dron por bsgom na de
NK078(tshu)001:8054: dag gi skyon gyis shes pa mun thibs se 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:8056: kha zas bcud can bsten cing lus snyel mig btsum
NK078(tshu)001:8057: nas khang pa mun nag tu mal skyed par gos
NK078(tshu)001:8058: 'thug po gyon cing mgo dkris nas /
NK078(tshu)001:8059: mun pa'i mtshan ma yid la byas nas bsgoms na
NK078(tshu)001:8060: gnyid min sgom min du shes pa mun mun long
NK078(tshu)001:8062: de dag gis lhag mthong la sgrib pa'o rgod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8063: rig pa bzhag thog tu mi sdod par shes pa yul sna tshogs kyi rjes su 'phro ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8065: rang bzhin gyis rgod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8067: ched du byas pas rgod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8069: gang zag 'byung ba rlung shas che ba /
NK078(tshu)001:8070: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags che ba'i rigs la rang bzhin gyi shes pa sang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8071: sngar ma goms pa'i dbang gis bsgom yang gnas cha chung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8072: rang bzhin gyi chos nyid kyi don la blo gnas
NK078(tshu)001:8073: su mi 'dod par yul sna tshogs la 'phro ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:8078: dbang med du rkyen gang yang rung bas g.yengs nas ting nge 'dzin las nyams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8082: lha chos kyi sgrung gling rnams dang 'khrugs pa tshongs
NK078(tshu)001:8083: 'dus la sogs pa la bltas pa sogs kyis stobs
NK078(tshu)001:8084: kyis shes pa yul la 'phro ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8085: nub mo bsgom na de dag gi snang ba yid yul du 'char zhing shes pa 'phro ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8087: dgong mo rlung skye ba'i dus su gos srab mo gyon /
NK078(tshu)001:8088: snang g.yel che sar 'thon nas shes pa gzeng bstod /
NK078(tshu)001:8089: rig pa kha bteg /lta stangs bstod nas bsgom bya'i don gsal gsal po ched du gnyer te /
NK078(tshu)001:8091: de dag gis chos nyid zhi gnas rtse gcig la bsgrib te de ltar drug go //
NK078(tshu)001:8092: de rnams rgyu gang las byung /
NK078(tshu)001:8094: mi dgos bzhin du blo ched du rtsol ba la rgod pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8095: nges gos brtan la sgrib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8096: dgos bzhin du gnyen po ched du mi rtsol bar byed pa las bying ba 'byung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8097: des g.yo thob la sgrib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8098: khams gsum sa dgur gol du dgos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8099: mu stegs rtag chad gnyis su log pa'i dogs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8100: de gnyis dril bas bcu gcig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8101: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi po kun gyi thun mong gi skyon ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8102: gang gi dmigs pa brjed pa dang bying rgod drug dang bdun te rnam grangs bco brgyad do //
NK078(tshu)001:8103: gzhan yang bco brgyad kyi brtsi lugs 'ga' zhig snang ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8104: don chung bar snang nas ma bris so //
NK078(tshu)001:8105: gnyis pa g.yeng ba'i skyon drug dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8107: gong gi sgrib pa de bzhin du gzhan yang ting
NK078(tshu)001:8108: nge 'dzin la g.yengsa ba'i skyon rnam pa drug yod
NK078(tshu)001:8109: de / gang zhe na rang bzhin nam ngo bosa
NK078(tshu)001:8110: g.yeng ba ni sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa snang
NK078(tshu)001:8111: rkyang la sogs lnga' thog tu lung ma bstan du
NK078(tshu)001:8112: de / sdod pa'o // phyi rol 'dod yon gyi
NK078(tshu)001:8113: yul lngar shes pa 'phros pas ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:8114: rkyen byas te phyi rol gyi g.yeng ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8116: rgod pa med pa tsam gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:8117: ro myongsa nas zhen na nang gi g.yeng ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:8118: te / des zhi lhag zung 'brel la sgrib par byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:8119: gdul bya gzhan dad par bya ba'i phyir mtshan btsas
NK078(tshu)001:8120: kyi dge sbyor byed pa ni mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba
NK078(tshu)001:8121: ste des zhi gnas la sgrib pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8122: rang gi ting nge 'dzin las gzhan pa'i snyom par 'jug pa'i dgu yin pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8123: theg pa 'og ma gzhan gyi gzhung de'i lugsa kyis ting nge 'dzin la sems 'phro ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8124: yid la byed pa'i g.yeng ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8125: bsgom pa bzang po nga la yod pa'o snyam du
NK078(tshu)001:8126: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyom par
NK078(tshu)001:8127: 'jug pa ni snyom 'jug gi g.yeng ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8128: g.yeng ba drug po de dag gi dbang du song na /
NK078(tshu)001:8129: gnas ngan pa 'khor ba'i skye ba len para the tshom meda do //
NK078(tshu)001:8130: gsum pa bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8132: sngar gyi yul lam rtog pa'i dran pa byung nas
NK078(tshu)001:8133: de'i rjes su rtogs pa phyi ma lung btags shing
NK078(tshu)001:8134: blo 'brangsa te nyams g.yo thob la sgrib pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:8135: gcig /skyon ched du 'goga pa zung 'brel la sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:8136: pa dang gnyis / ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams su myong ba 'thas pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:8137: bdag tu ther zug pa dang gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:8138: sgom pa'i dmigs mi shes par don med phyal bar bzhag pa dang bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:8139: de gnyis ni lhag mthong la sgrib pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8140: ched du lus ngag yid gsum 'chosa nas chos nyid
NK078(tshu)001:8141: ce gsal du yid la byed pa ni zhi gnas
NK078(tshu)001:8143: ting nge 'dzin gyi ro nyams su myong du re
NK078(tshu)001:8144: ba dang drug /bdag tu 'du shes pas sgoms pa
NK078(tshu)001:8145: la gnas shing yul du dmigsa pas zung 'brel la
NK078(tshu)001:8147: shes pa nang du sdud pa lhag mthong la sgrib pa dang brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:8148: ting nge 'dzin gyi don ci snga mngon du byed 'dod pa dang dgu /
NK078(tshu)001:8149: yon tan gyi drod rtags gsal du 'ong bar 'dod
NK078(tshu)001:8150: pa'i re ba mang bar 'dod pa dang bcu ste
NK078(tshu)001:8151: / de gnyis kyis zhi lhag phyir sgrib pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8152: bzhi pa rtog pa'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8154: de yang sgrib pa'i skyon rtsa ba lnga yan lag bcu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8155: dang po rtsa ba lnga ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8163: yin min la sogs pa sems spyi'i rnam pa la rtog pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8165: 'du shes kyis yul mtshan mar 'dzin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8166: rgyu ba ni de'i rjes su dran pa'i rgyun ring thung du rgyu ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8167: tshor ba ni nyams su myong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8168: byung tshur ni rtog pa'i 'byung 'jug dus myur bul la ltos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8170: yang dag don gyi lam tshol na //
NK078(tshu)001:8171: rtog pa'i skyon lnga spang bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:8172: rtog pa rags pa'i rig pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8173: mtshan ma rgyu ba'i tshor ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8174: byung tshor skyon lnga spang bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:8176: gnyis pa yan lag bcu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8177: rtsa ba lnga po de dag re re la yang yan lag gnyis gnyis te bcu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8178: de yang rtog pa sems kyi rnam pa'i sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8179: khras dang rtse mo gzhan lta bu phra ragsa gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8180: mtshan ma 'dzin pa'i sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8181: dge bshes dang byis sba lta bu che chung gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8182: rgyu ba rgyun gyi sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8183: 'dod chags dang zhe sdang lta bu'i ring thung gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8184: tshor ba nyams myong gi sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8185: ngar gdong dang snag po che lta bu gsal mi gsal gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8186: byung tshor sgom pa'i sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8187: kha don byang ma byang la myur bul yod pa lta bu gnyis so //
NK078(tshu)001:8189: rtog pa la yang gnyis yod de //
NK078(tshu)001:8190: rags pa dang ni phra ba gnyis //
NK078(tshu)001:8191: de bzhin mtshan ma che chung gnyis //
NK078(tshu)001:8192: rgyu ba ring po thung ngu gnyis //
NK078(tshu)001:8193: de bzhin tshor ba gsal mi gsal //
NK078(tshu)001:8194: byung tshor gnyis su snang ba yang //
NK078(tshu)001:8195: myur ba dang ni bul ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8196: 'di ni sgra don la sgrib pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:8197: rtogs pa chen po'i gegs yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:8199: lnga pa dgos pa sa dgu dang log pa rtag chad kyi dmigs bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8201: 'jiga rten gsum gyi dang po 'dod khams gcig tu gol ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8202: rtog pa'i phra rags kyi skyon gyi ngan song gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:8203: mtshan ma che chung gis gling bzhi'i mi /
NK078(tshu)001:8204: rgyu ba ring thung gis rgyal chen dang sum cu rtsa gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:8205: tshor ba gsal mi gsal gyis 'thab bral /
NK078(tshu)001:8206: byung tshor myur bul gyis dga' ldan /
NK078(tshu)001:8207: sems sgyu ma shes pas 'phrul dga' dang gzhan 'phrul dbang byed du skye ba ste gol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8209: gnas ngan len dang phyed snang gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:8210: 'dod pa bzhi yi bden gnas dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8213: dang po gnyis kyis 'dod khams dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8214: de 'og gnyis kyis gzugs kyi bsam gatana bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8215: tha ma gnyis kyis gzugs med bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8216: spyir khams gsum sa dgur gol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8217: bcos thabs ni mdo'i le'u nga bzhi par gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:8218: de ting lhag mthong gsal stong gi ye shes zhi gnas su gol ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8219: de yang gsal cha'i ye shes la shugs gtad par
NK078(tshu)001:8220: byas nas bdag tu bzung ba ni bsam gtan bzhi'i
NK078(tshu)001:8221: gsal thog gi rtog med bsgoms te /
NK078(tshu)001:8222: de yang rtog dpyod kyi gnyen por mi 'jug cing
NK078(tshu)001:8223: mnyam bzhag gi gsal thog tu dga' ba de'i ngang
NK078(tshu)001:8224: du rtse gcig la bsam gtan dang po'i sa dang
NK078(tshu)001:8226: mnyam bzhag dga' bde la rtse gcig pa gnyis pa'i sa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8228: mnyam bzhag bde ba'i ngang du rtse gcig pa gsum pa'i sa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8229: bde ba la sogs pa'i skyon brgyad dang bral ba /
NK078(tshu)001:8230: gsal thog gi dwangs cha'i ngang la gnas pa ni bzhi pa'i sa dang bzhi'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8231: lhag mthong stong pa'i cha la gol ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8232: phyi rol gzugs kyi skye mched med pa /
NK078(tshu)001:8233: nang kun gzhi rig thog stong pa'i ngang la snyom
NK078(tshu)001:8234: par 'jug pa skye mched mu bzhira gol ba ste
NK078(tshu)001:8235: / de yang chos rnams sems yin /
NK078(tshu)001:8236: sems nam mkha' lta bu 'dun cing de la blo
NK078(tshu)001:8237: rtse gcig tu gnas pa nam mkha' mtha' yas skye
NK078(tshu)001:8239: rnam par shes par rang yang ma grub par 'dun
NK078(tshu)001:8240: cing de la rtse gcig pa rnam shes mtha' yas
NK078(tshu)001:8242: rnam shes de yang ye nas ci yang med par
NK078(tshu)001:8243: 'dun cing de la rtse gcig pa ni ci yang
NK078(tshu)001:8244: med pa'i skye mched kyi sa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8245: snang ngo thams cad 'gag cing shes ngo'i gsal rgyun
NK078(tshu)001:8246: tsam yod par 'dun cing de la rtse gcig pa
NK078(tshu)001:8247: ni yod min med min gyi skye mched kyi sa
NK078(tshu)001:8248: dang bzhi'o // de ltar khams gsum sa dgu ste de dag tu gol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8249: ther zug pa rtag par lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8250: snga phyi'i mtha' chad par lta ba gnyis ni phyin ci loga gi lta bar gol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8251: gnyis pa khams kyi skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8253: sgo gsum gyis 'jig rten gyi bya ba mang po byed la /
NK078(tshu)001:8254: ting nge 'dzin la blo mi 'byung ba'i rkyen byas shing /
NK078(tshu)001:8255: sgom pa nyams su len pa'ang ngang thung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8257: rna bas dug shanga gi sgra thos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8264: bad kan skya ba la sogs pa'i kha dog mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8265: nad khamsa 'khrug pa las gyur pa'i skyon gyi cha yang brtag cing shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8266: gsum pa spyod lam sgom chen gyi skyon drug go //
NK078(tshu)001:8268: rnal 'byor pa de yis 'gro ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8271: 'dod yon zas nor la longsa spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8272: lam du 'jug pa'i tshe na yang /
NK078(tshu)001:8273: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin dang bral ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8274: 'dug cing sdod pa'i tshe g.ye'u tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:8275: bya ra khra'i sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8276: 'gro ba'i sems tshol dur rkun wa' sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8277: sgom khang nang na gnas tshe nya lta bu'i sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8278: nyal ba'i tshe tho yor glad gnyid kyi sgom pa
NK078(tshu)001:8279: dang zas nor la longs spyod pa'i tshe skam chags
NK078(tshu)001:8280: che ba tshong pa'i semsa kyi sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8281: lam pas rang gi sgo gsum gyi bya byed mang
NK078(tshu)001:8282: bas spre'u yi spyod pa rnams sgom gyi skyon yin
NK078(tshu)001:8285: mtshan ma tshig gi rnal 'byor pa //
NK078(tshu)001:8286: tshig la zhib cing don la rtsing //
NK078(tshu)001:8287: yang dag don la ma 'byor pa //
NK078(tshu)001:8288: 'dug na mtshan ma'i bya ra byed //
NK078(tshu)001:8289: 'gro tshe ma rab 'phyo zhing rgyug /nyal na mtshan ma'i bsam dpyod gtong //
NK078(tshu)001:8290: 'dug tshe gnyis dang bying dbang song //
NK078(tshu)001:8291: za na skam chags dbang gis spyod //
NK078(tshu)001:8292: 'tshogs na ga zha bre mo'i gtam //
NK078(tshu)001:8293: sgom khang nang nas 'gro don mdzad //
NK078(tshu)001:8294: rdzas kyi bca' kha lon sems dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8295: bzhed pa mtho ris byang chub bzhed //
NK078(tshu)001:8298: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8299: ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i dus kyi skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8304: dang po blo che chung ngam nyams kyi rim pa
NK078(tshu)001:8305: dang sbyar te bcos thabs so sor bstan pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:8307: gong gi de ltar skyon ngo shes pa'i rnal 'byora pas /
NK078(tshu)001:8308: rtog pa'i skyon de dag spangs bar byed pa'i gnyen po ched du sems pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8309: mngon par 'adu byed pa'i grangs yan lag brgyad bsten cing bcos pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8310: de yang brgyad gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:8321: shin tu sbyangs pa dang bzhis /
NK078(tshu)001:8322: le lo dang g.yeng ba drug la sogs pa'i skyon sel lo //
NK078(tshu)001:8323: dran pas dmigs pa brjed pa la sogs pa'i skyon sel lo //
NK078(tshu)001:8324: shes bzhin gnas pa'i bying rgod dang dog pa la sogs pa bco brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8325: byung tshor dbang gis g.yeng ba la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8326: sgom chen gyi skyon drug la sogs pa sel sems gzeng bstod pas mi rtsol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8327: bying rmug la sogs sel lo //
NK078(tshu)001:8328: btang snyoms kyis rtsol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8329: yid la byed pa sel lo //
NK078(tshu)001:8330: de dag ni blo chung ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:8331: nyams g.yo thabs kyis bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:8334: shin tu sbyangs pas le lo sel //
NK078(tshu)001:8335: dran pas dmigs pa brjed pa sel //
NK078(tshu)001:8336: shes bzhin gnas pas bying rgod sel //
NK078(tshu)001:8337: mi rtsol sems gzengs bstod pas sel //
NK078(tshu)001:8338: rtsol drag btang snyoms gtib mgo mnan //
NK078(tshu)001:8340: skyon gang yin gang las byung so sor cung zad tsam blta bar byas pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:8341: gang yin yang ngo shes pas rang gi skyon dag par 'gyur ba ni tha ma'i bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:8342: yang na skyon byung yang sems nyid rang byung rang zhir bya ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8344: nyams goms brtan gyi bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:8345: gnyis pa mthar phyin pa'i dus su dgag sgrub med pa'i bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:8347: dpe ji ltar na byis pa brda don gnyis ka
NK078(tshu)001:8348: la blo shed ma bye ba dag rtsed mo'i bya
NK078(tshu)001:8349: byed mang posa sems g.yeng bar gnas pa ltar lam
NK078(tshu)001:8350: pas sgo gsum gyi bya byed mang pos sems g.yeng
NK078(tshu)001:8351: ba de lta bas na bdag med par rtogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8352: ngang la stong pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK078(tshu)001:8353: rang dbang du bsgyur nas rtog pa'i mtshan ma thams
NK078(tshu)001:8354: cad sems mnyam pa'i dbyings su zil gyis mnan pas
NK078(tshu)001:8355: / skyon dagga pa dang yon tan sgrub par bya ba ga la yin te min no //
NK078(tshu)001:8356: blo rab bam nyams mthar phyin pa'i bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:8358: khyad par du rtogs pa'i skyon rtsa ba lnga'am drug yan lag dang bcas pa'i skyon bcos thabs te /
NK078(tshu)001:8360: tshad ma gnyis kyis gzhal ba'i blos //
NK078(tshu)001:8361: rnam par rtogs pa'i rjes bcad pa //
NK078(tshu)001:8362: yod med sngon rtog gang la byung //
NK078(tshu)001:8363: brtag pas rtog pa brtas par byung //
NK078(tshu)001:8364: rtog pa sgyu mar rab shes na //
NK078(tshu)001:8365: rtog pa'i ri bo zhi bar 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:8366: des ni gnas ngan gsum du min //
NK078(tshu)001:8368: mnyam bzhag gi tshe rnam rtog gi skyon skyes pa shes bzhin gyi bya ra bas tshor ba'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:8369: lung man ngag gi tshad ma gnyis dang ldan pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8370: blo gros kyis rtog pa de nyid la bltas te
NK078(tshu)001:8373: rang bzhin ci yin rtsad bcad pas kun brtags kyi mthu brtas pa las byung bar ngos zin /
NK078(tshu)001:8374: de nyid la brtag pas yang dag par ma grub ste log rtog sgyu ma lta bur shes /
NK078(tshu)001:8375: rang bzhin sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes cir
NK078(tshu)001:8376: yang ma yin pa nyid cir yang snang ba'i ye
NK078(tshu)001:8377: shes sgyu mar shes pas rtog pa'i ri bo zhi
NK078(tshu)001:8378: bar 'gyur / yod med rtog pa'i ri bo zhi bar 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:8379: yod med rtog pa'i skye 'gag med pas ngan song du mi ltung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:8380: de yang rtogs pa gang las 'byung zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:8381: mtshan ma dag las byung ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:8382: mtshan ma sgyu mar rab shes na //
NK078(tshu)001:8383: mtshan ma'i chos rnams zhi bar 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:8384: de ni 'dod khams tha mar min //
NK078(tshu)001:8385: zhes pas mnyam par bzhag pa la 'du shes kyi
NK078(tshu)001:8386: mtshan ma skye na'ang snga ma ltar shes pas mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:8387: ma dgag mi dgos par zhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8388: gzung 'dzin tha mal ba'i bag chags med pas 'dod
NK078(tshu)001:8389: khams mtho ris tha ma gling bzhi'i mir skyes so
NK078(tshu)001:8390: // mtshan ma de yang ji ltar shes na /
NK078(tshu)001:8391: de yang dran pa dag las byung //
NK078(tshu)001:8392: dran pa skyon du shes gyur nas //
NK078(tshu)001:8393: rgyu ba'i skyon rnams sel bar byed //
NK078(tshu)001:8394: 'dod khams gnyis par tha mar min //
NK078(tshu)001:8395: zhes pas 'bras bu mtshan ma brtsad bcad pas dran pa rgyu ba las byung bar ngos zin /
NK078(tshu)001:8396: sngar gyi yul dran pa sgyu ma nyid du shes pas rgyu ba mi 'byung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8397: dran pa rgyu ba'i sa bon med pas mtho ris
NK078(tshu)001:8398: gnyis pa rgyal chen rigs bzhi dang sum cu rtsa
NK078(tshu)001:8399: gsum longs spyod mthun pas gcig tu brtsis pa der
NK078(tshu)001:8400: mi skye'o // rgyu ba de yang gang de bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:8401: de yang da ltar byung ba yin //
NK078(tshu)001:8402: de nyid de ltar shes gyur pa //
NK078(tshu)001:8403: skyon gyi tshor ba sel bar byed //
NK078(tshu)001:8404: 'dod khams gsum par de dag min //
NK078(tshu)001:8405: zhes pas tshor ba bde sdug skyes pa de skyon
NK078(tshu)001:8406: du bltas pas mi spang yon tan du bltas nas
NK078(tshu)001:8407: mi blangs te / blang dor gyi sems mi skye
NK078(tshu)001:8408: nas tshor ba gsum ye shes sgyu mar shes pas
NK078(tshu)001:8409: skyon gyi tshor ba mi mthun par ma dmigs pas
NK078(tshu)001:8410: 'dod khams kyi lha ris gsum pa mtshe ma'am dga'
NK078(tshu)001:8412: de nyid de ltar de bcad nas //
NK078(tshu)001:8413: gang de phyi nang nyid kho na //
NK078(tshu)001:8414: de nyid skyon du rab bshad na //
NK078(tshu)001:8415: dgag dang skye ba ga la yod //
NK078(tshu)001:8416: des ni 'dod khams bzhi par min //
NK078(tshu)001:8418: byung tshor skyes pa de skyon du ngos zin ma
NK078(tshu)001:8419: thag de ye shes sgyu mar ngos zin pas dgag
NK078(tshu)001:8420: skye med pa'i mthus 'thab bral du'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8421: de yang gang las skye mched na //
NK078(tshu)001:8422: sems kyi chos las gyur pa ste //
NK078(tshu)001:8423: sems nyid sgyu mar rab shes na //
NK078(tshu)001:8424: sems kyi chos rnams zhi bar 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:8425: phung po gzugs brnyan 'dra ba las //
NK078(tshu)001:8426: sems ni smig rgyu lta bu yin //
NK078(tshu)001:8427: yod med gnyis kyi mtha' las grol //
NK078(tshu)001:8428: de shes 'dod khams lnga par min //
NK078(tshu)001:8429: zhes pas byung tshor gang las byung rtsad bcad pas rgyu sems rtog bcas kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:8431: sems de ye shes sgyu mar shes nas /
NK078(tshu)001:8432: sems rtog mi dmigs te zhi bar 'gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:8433: de yang gzugs ni dpe gzugs brnyan ltar snang stong
NK078(tshu)001:8434: dbyer med semsa kyang dran stong dbyer med par go
NK078(tshu)001:8435: bas yod med du 'dzin pa'i mtha'i bcing pa dgrol
NK078(tshu)001:8436: bas 'dod khams kyi lha ris lnga pa 'phrul dga'
NK078(tshu)001:8437: dang gzhan 'phrul dbang byed du mi ltung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:8438: nges 'jig rten dang po 'dod khams pa'i skyon bcos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8439: yang na rang byung rang zhing bya //
NK078(tshu)001:8442: nyams na mthar phyin pa'i bcos thabs te /
NK078(tshu)001:8444: khyad par du khams gong ma'i rtog dpyod la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8445: mu bzhi'i 'du shes la sogs pa byung na /
NK078(tshu)001:8446: de dag nam mkha'i sprin rgya mtsho'i rlabs ltar shar
NK078(tshu)001:8447: ba'i rang gi sems nyid skye ba med pa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:8448: rang byung rang zhir rang shar bar shes pas rtog
NK078(tshu)001:8449: dpyod gnyen po mi dgos par sems nyid du rang
NK078(tshu)001:8452: drug gis spyod yul mtshan ma ste //
NK078(tshu)001:8453: mtshan ma dngos por snang bas na //
NK078(tshu)001:8454: ci dgar bzhag pas debazloga med //
NK078(tshu)001:8455: de stong yang zhing bzlog rgyu med //
NK078(tshu)001:8456: thams cad sems kyi chos nyid du //
NK078(tshu)001:8457: tshig min lta bas thag chod na //
NK078(tshu)001:8458: ma bcos ma yengs yeng thub snyam //
NK078(tshu)001:8459: rtsol sgrub re dogs ga la yod //
NK078(tshu)001:8460: mi mthun gnyen po sgom mi dgos //
NK078(tshu)001:8461: skyon yon spang len bying rgod rnams //
NK078(tshu)001:8463: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel //
NK078(tshu)001:8466: bying rmug can du ma gyur pas //
NK078(tshu)001:8467: bsam gtan gnas su de mi 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:8469: sems can gnas su de spangs min //
NK078(tshu)001:8470: ces khams gong ma gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8471: sems nyid yod pa'i dngos po'am //
NK078(tshu)001:8472: med ces bya bar ma blta bas //
NK078(tshu)001:8473: ya mtshan can du de mi 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:8474: zhes mu stegs kyi gol sa bcad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8475: gzhan yang mtshan nyid sde gsum gyi gol sa bcad pa yang gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:8476: zhes lce ston gyis 'grel bar gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:8479: cung zad khamsa las gyur pa'i skyon rnams kyi cha nyamsa pas /
NK078(tshu)001:8480: bsgom bya'i don mi gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8482: ting nge 'dzin la blo mi 'jug pa la sogsa
NK078(tshu)001:8483: khams kyi skyon gang yina pa ngos zin par byas
NK078(tshu)001:8484: nas khams 'khrugs na spyod lam du rang rang gang
NK078(tshu)001:8486: nad khams la mthun pa'i zas sman dpyad kyi cho gas khams gso bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8489: spyod lam bzhir ting nge 'dzin gyi rnal du ma
NK078(tshu)001:8490: 'byor ba'i dus su shes bzhin gyi bya ra ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:8491: so 'thas chod cing ngos zin nas skyon de dag
NK078(tshu)001:8492: dor bar bya zhing ting nge 'dzin la dran pa
NK078(tshu)001:8493: ma yengs pa'i thag pas bsdam par byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:8494: spyod lam gyi dus dang rnam pa kun tu ting nge 'dzin gyi don la nyamsa par mi bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8495: bdun pa nyams la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8499: de ltar skyon bcos shing don la nogs thub cing
NK078(tshu)001:8500: brtson 'grus kyi yun ring bar ting nge 'dzin la
NK078(tshu)001:8501: gnas pa'i dus gdoda ma 'jug pa nas mthar ma
NK078(tshu)001:8502: phyin gyi bar du nyams rim par 'phel ba'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:8507: mthar phyin pa'i nyams dang mu lngas de ting yongsa su rdzogsa par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:8508: gnyis pa rgyas pa la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8510: dang po g.yo ba'i nyams la brtson 'grus bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8512: rnal 'byor pa gang dag dper na ri gzar po
NK078(tshu)001:8513: la chu 'bab pa de dar cig kyang mi sdod
NK078(tshu)001:8515: mnyam bzhag ting nge 'dzin gsal stong la gansa pa'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:8516: skyon byung ma thag skyon dbang du 'gro ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8517: de yang sngar kun tu brtag pa'i shes pa phyin
NK078(tshu)001:8518: ci log la thog ma med pa nas gomsa pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8519: stobs kyis dper na rdza makhana gyis 'khor lo bskor
NK078(tshu)001:8521: ting nge 'dzin gyi thog tu mi sdod par rtog
NK078(tshu)001:8522: pa'i dbang du 'gro bas ting nge 'dzin la skyo
NK078(tshu)001:8523: bar byed pa de'i tshe mgo la ma 'bar ba
NK078(tshu)001:8524: myur du gsod par byed pa la ring ba bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:8525: du brtson 'grus bskyed la ting nge 'dzin la 'bad
NK078(tshu)001:8526: do // gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams la 'byung 'jug bsring ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8528: dang po skyon gyi rgyu brtag ste dor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8530: gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams kyi skabs su bar 'ga' ting nge 'dzin skyon dbang du 'tshor /
NK078(tshu)001:8531: bar 'ga' ting nge 'dzin thob pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:8532: khamsa dang spyod lam la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'chor ba'i rgyu brtags te /
NK078(tshu)001:8533: khams kyi skyon yin na khams gso /
NK078(tshu)001:8534: spyod lam la sogs pa'i skyon yin na dor bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8537: ting nge 'dzin cung zad tsam yod la rtogs pa de dag sngar bas nyung bar 'byung bas /
NK078(tshu)001:8538: skyon rnam par thub ste thun gcig tsam gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8539: de'i tshe ting nge 'dzin la dal busa 'byung ba dang 'jug par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8540: thun cung zad sngar bas bsring bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8541: gsum pa goms pa'i nyams la btang snyoms bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8543: de ltar thob pa'i nyams de gomsa nas ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:8544: 'dzin la brod pas ched du bsgom par bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:8546: dpe yur ba 'gying bo'i chu 'gro ba mi mngon pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:8547: skyon dbang du cung zad 'gro yang /
NK078(tshu)001:8549: rnam rtog 'og 'gyu'i skyon yod pas de chod par
NK078(tshu)001:8550: byed pa'i thabs la rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i btang
NK078(tshu)001:8551: snyoms dang / rtsol ba med pa'i ngang /
NK078(tshu)001:8552: dus phyad pa'i btang snyoms dang gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:8553: dang po rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i btang snyomsa blanga bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8554: bzhi pa brtan pa'i nyams la mi sun par bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8556: dper na ri bo rlung gis mi 'gul ba lta
NK078(tshu)001:8557: bu rnam par rtog pa'i rkyen gyis ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:8558: mi 'gul bar brtan pa thob ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8559: nyin zhag gcig la thun cig tu brkyang nas nyin mtshan 'brel bar sgom nus na yang /
NK078(tshu)001:8560: shes pa po ma mthud la ha cang sun sun du bsgoms par mi bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8562: rab kyis nyin zhag gcig la brgyad du bgos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8563: 'bring gis bcu drug /tha mas sum cu so gnyis su bgos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8564: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams la dga' brod mi bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8566: gnyen pos zin pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ro myong ba'i ma yengs pa'i zhen pa dor nas /
NK078(tshu)001:8567: rtsol med blo 'das de la ting nge 'dzin bskyed du byar med pas mthar phyin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8568: de ltar mthar phyin pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi shugs
NK078(tshu)001:8569: las snang ba brgyad mthong ba la dag'a ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:8572: me long skar mdas brgyan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8573: snang srid rdul phra rab tu mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8575: kun dga' ra ba mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8576: skyed mos tshal mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8577: glang po che la zhon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8579: stong gsum lag mthing ltar mnyam par mthong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8580: gsum pa brtson pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8582: ting nge 'dzin la shin tu ngang bsring nas yun
NK078(tshu)001:8583: ring por brtson 'grus bskyed cing bsgom pa yis yon
NK078(tshu)001:8585: nyams gong nas gong du bog chen po skyes shing 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:8586: brgyad pa spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8590: stong chen bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pas bdag gi don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8591: gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir du sgo gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:8592: bya ba'i spyod pa kun ji lta bu zhe na
NK078(tshu)001:8593: / gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8598: dang po nyams lnga char mi dmigs pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8600: dang po ting 'dzin gyi mgo slob pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:8601: nyams dang po g.yo ba'i nyams nas 'go bzung nas
NK078(tshu)001:8602: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams kyi bar thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:8603: / gnyis 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8604: tshul gyis ni spyod bya'i yul gang yang rung ba
NK078(tshu)001:8605: thams cad kun la 'dzin zhen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8606: thog chagsa med par rol bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8607: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8609: de ting nyams su len pa'i tshe chos spyod bcu
NK078(tshu)001:8610: yod pa la dgu po dor ba'i gcig la cha
NK078(tshu)001:8611: ste rtse gcig tu ting nge 'dzin bsgom par byed
NK078(tshu)001:8612: pa de yanga / chos spyod bcu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8614: yi ge bri mchod sbyin pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8615: nyan dang 'dzin dang klog pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8617: de sems pa dang bsgom pa ni //
NK078(tshu)001:8618: chos spyod bcu yi bdag nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:8620: de la 'dir mtshan ma med pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK078(tshu)001:8621: kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i skabs su chos spyod
NK078(tshu)001:8622: dgu ni mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba yin pa'i phyir dor
NK078(tshu)001:8623: te mi bya'o // 'dir mtshan ma med pa mi
NK078(tshu)001:8624: dmigs par bsgoms pa ni de bzhin nyid kyi ting
NK078(tshu)001:8625: nge 'dzin dang mthun pa'i spyod pa zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8626: gsum pa spyod lam bzhi la spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8628: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du 'gro ba
NK078(tshu)001:8629: dang 'ong ba'i rang rgyud kyi zhen pa med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8630: ngang las spyod lam 'gro ba dang 'ong ba ma
NK078(tshu)001:8632: de ltar 'gro 'ong gi spyad par snang ba'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:8633: de nyid na'ang chos nyid 'gro 'ong med pa las
NK078(tshu)001:8635: chos nyid de bzhin nyid la gnas bya dang gnas byed kyi zhen pa med pa'i ngang las /
NK078(tshu)001:8637: 'dug pa thamsa cad du gnas pa ltar ma 'gags par snang la /
NK078(tshu)001:8638: de ltar nyal 'dug gnas pa'i dus de nyid na'ang
NK078(tshu)001:8639: chos nyid gnas pa med pa las mi 'da' ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:8640: // chos nyid de bzhin nyid la longs spyod bya
NK078(tshu)001:8641: spyod byed kyi zhen pa med pa'i ngang las spyod
NK078(tshu)001:8642: lam bza' btung 'dod yon thamsa cad ma 'gag par
NK078(tshu)001:8643: // longs spyod la / de ltar longs spyod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8644: dus de nyid na'ang chos nyid longs spyod bya spyod
NK078(tshu)001:8645: byed med pa'i ngang las mi 'da' bas spyod lam
NK078(tshu)001:8646: rnam bzhir chos nyid gsal stong gi ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:8647: la nyamsa pa meda par longs spyod cing spyod bya
NK078(tshu)001:8648: la chags shing zhen par mi bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8649: bzhi pa spyod pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:8651: de ltar spyod lam rnam bzhin snang ba mi 'goga pa bsod nams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8652: mi 'dzin pa ye shes kyi tshogsa gnyis zung 'brel du ldan par spyod pa /
NK078(tshu)001:8653: bdag gi don gyi phyir spyod lam kun la yul yul can mi dmigsa par spyod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:8654: 'bras bu stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor myur du thob pa la the tshom med do //
NK078(tshu)001:8655: gnyis pa gzhan don gyi spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8657: dang po spyod lam chos nyid du slong zhing gzhan don rdzogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8659: de yang rnal 'byor pas 'gro zhing 'ong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8660: nyal zhing gnyid log pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8661: 'dug cing sdod pa dang bza' btung la longs spyod pa'i dus kyi tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:8662: de ltar bdag don gyi spyod pas ci spyad chos
NK078(tshu)001:8663: nyid du khyer nas spyod pa'i byin rlabsa las 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:8664: ba sgrol bas gcig shos gzhan don yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:8665: de'ang bdag don gang ltar nyams su blang yang gzhan gyi don du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:8666: de'i rgyu mtshan lam gyi sngon du semsa bskyed dgos pas /
NK078(tshu)001:8667: de bas bdag don de ting sgom pa la gzhan don rdzogsa pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8668: gnyis pa thugs rje thabs kyi spyod pas gzhan don bya ba de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8670: dang po skabs min kyang gzhan don bya bar gsungs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8672: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i gzhung las gragas pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8676: mi dor ba lnga la sogs pa rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:8677: rtogs kyang skye ba la rang dbang ma thob pas
NK078(tshu)001:8678: skye bo tshogs sbyor ba kun gyis 'chol nyog tu
NK078(tshu)001:8680: 'dir de dag la mos pa'i sgo nas slob pa
NK078(tshu)001:8681: lta ci smos sbyor sgrol la sogs pa gdul bya'i
NK078(tshu)001:8682: don du 'gyur ba'i rkyen mthonga na /
NK078(tshu)001:8683: lnga bzhi'i smad spyod de daga kun tu rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8684: gomas pa rkyen 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnams kyi gzhi ma de ting gi skabs la spyod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8685: gnyis pa phrin las la sogs gzhan don bya ba'i thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:8687: rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8688: rkyen 'jug pa de ting man chad kun gyis kyang gdul bya gzhan gyi dona 'gyur du snang na /
NK078(tshu)001:8689: phrin las bzhi spyod cing mchog thun mong gi dngos grub sgrub pa dang dbang bskur ba'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:8690: phyag rgya gcig pa man chad kyis lam kun skad
NK078(tshu)001:8691: cig tsam gyi chas rdzogsa par bsgom nas mthar zhi
NK078(tshu)001:8692: khro phyag rgya spros pa'i 'khora lo gang yin dngos
NK078(tshu)001:8693: su bsgom pa'i spyod yul min kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:8694: mos pa tsam gyis bsgom par bya zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:8695: ranga bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor 'og min nas snyan gsan phab /
NK078(tshu)001:8696: spyan drangs bstim brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba rdzogas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:8697: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK078(tshu)001:8699: phrin las sgrub pa'i dbang gang byed nus pa' gzi
NK078(tshu)001:8700: byin dang ldan par byas nas gzhan don rdzogsa par
NK078(tshu)001:8701: de ting gi skabs su'ang byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:8702: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8703: khyad par de ting rang gi dam tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8704: lam spyi'i dam tshig ji ltar bsrung tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:8706: bsrung bya dam tshig gi ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8711: dang po de ting gi skabs 'dir dam tshig kun
NK078(tshu)001:8712: dang ldan dgos kyang khyad par ting nge 'dzin las
NK078(tshu)001:8713: mi 'da' bar ldan dgos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8715: de ting stong chen gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas
NK078(tshu)001:8716: pa de'i tshe lam gong ma'i dam tshig dang sdom
NK078(tshu)001:8718: mos pa'i sgo nas slob cing mi gtong bar bsrung
NK078(tshu)001:8719: mod kyang khyad par ting nge 'dzina las mi 'da'
NK078(tshu)001:8720: ba'i dam tshig dang ldan par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8721: gnyis pa lta ba dam tshig gi ngo bo yin
NK078(tshu)001:8722: pas lta ba'i don 'dir goms dgos par bstan pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:8724: spyi dang khyad par ram rtsa ba'i dam tshaga dang
NK078(tshu)001:8725: yan lag gi dam tshig ces bya ba de yang
NK078(tshu)001:8726: sems las logsa shig na yod pa ma yin te
NK078(tshu)001:8727: / gang zhe na rang gi sems lta bas rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:8728: pa'i don las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig yin te
NK078(tshu)001:8729: / / lta ba rtogs pa'i gzugs kyis zin na
NK078(tshu)001:8730: 'khor ba ngan song du mi gtong ba'i phyir yang
NK078(tshu)001:8731: / / dam zhes bya / bla na med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8732: byang chub kyi gzungsa su gyur pas kyang dam zhes
NK078(tshu)001:8733: / / dam zhes bya / bya / lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:8734: rtogs pa'i don sngar nas ldan pa de yang 'dir
NK078(tshu)001:8735: de ting gis gomsa par byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8738: lta ba dam tshig gi mchog yin pa de bas
NK078(tshu)001:8739: na rang gi semsa nyid lta bas rtogsa par byas
NK078(tshu)001:8740: te / dman pa las gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8741: snyoms las su gyur pa'i le lo g.yeng ba'i skyon
NK078(tshu)001:8742: drug la sogs pa'i skyon rnams yongsa su spangsa la
NK078(tshu)001:8743: / gang zag gi nga dang chos kyi bdag med
NK078(tshu)001:8744: cing mnyam pa'i don la mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig
NK078(tshu)001:8746: gsum pa mi 'da' nges tshig go //
NK078(tshu)001:8748: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin las dus thams cad du 'da' bar mi byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:8749: de bzhin nyid kyi don rtogs pa dang goms pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8750: ting nge 'dzin dang ldan na dam pa yina te
NK078(tshu)001:8751: / de bzhin nyid de las 'das na rang gi
NK078(tshu)001:8752: bde 'bras thams cad 'tshig par 'gyur te 'khor bar
NK078(tshu)001:8753: / lhung la / de las ma 'das na rang
NK078(tshu)001:8754: rgyud kyi nyes skyon thams cad tshig par 'gyur bas
NK078(tshu)001:8756: gnyis pa lam spyi'i dam tshig ji ltar bsrung tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8758: dang po lam snga ma mthar phyin pa'i dus su
NK078(tshu)001:8759: gong ma'i dam tshig rgyud ldan du yod pas 'phar
NK078(tshu)001:8760: ba'i rgyu byas kyang dngos su spyod pa min par
NK078(tshu)001:8762: de yang lam snga ma snga mar lta ba'i skabs
NK078(tshu)001:8763: la sogs par lam rang rang gi dam tshig rdzogsa
NK078(tshu)001:8764: par byas pa de yang don gyi lam gong ma
NK078(tshu)001:8765: gong ma de ting la sogs pa'i rgyud la yar
NK078(tshu)001:8767: snga ma lta ba la spyod pa'i de ting yongs su 'phar ba'i rgyu byas kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:8768: de ting skabs su lta ba'i dam tshig dang spyod pa la mngon du spyod pa min no //
NK078(tshu)001:8769: de bas lam gong ma la 'phar ba'i thabs 'og
NK078(tshu)001:8770: ma'i spyod pa kun gong ma la mngon du 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:8772: gnyis pa de bas lam gong 'og gi dam tshig
NK078(tshu)001:8773: dang spyod pa la khyad yod par dpes bstan pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:8775: lam gong 'og gi dam tshig dang spyod pa la khyad yod pa de bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:8776: lam so so'i lta ba rtogsa tshab che chung gis
NK078(tshu)001:8777: gzhis phye ba las bdag don ting nge 'dzin dbang
NK078(tshu)001:8778: bsgyur gyi spyod pa la sogs pa kun la khyad
NK078(tshu)001:8779: yod par ni lung pa che chung gis phye bas
NK078(tshu)001:8780: nam mkha'i yul la rgya che chung yod pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:8781: 'dra bar / gzhan don byin rlabs kyi spyod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:8782: zhing khamsa rgya che chung ni mi'i dbang po gser
NK078(tshu)001:8783: dngul zangs lcags kyi 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po'i
NK078(tshu)001:8784: 'dul zhing gi sa khamsa rgya che chung yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:8785: 'dra bar / bzhin / bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i spyod pa'i dpe ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8786: spyod pa dang dam tshig dang ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa rnams la ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8787: nus pa'i stobs che chung gi khyad par ni stobsa
NK078(tshu)001:8788: ldan glang po che tsam du gcig kyang rtsal che
NK078(tshu)001:8789: chung dang sgyid drag gzhan gyis chu la thad gcong
NK078(tshu)001:8790: dang gzhol gcod byed pa dang 'dra ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8791: bcu pa drod la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8793: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8795: bzhag thabs gong du bstan pa de ltar bsgom bya
NK078(tshu)001:8796: sgom byed dang g.yeng ba drug la sogs bya byed
NK078(tshu)001:8797: med par yun bsringsa nas bsgoms na /
NK078(tshu)001:8798: phyi lus dang nang ngag dang gsang ba semsa la
NK078(tshu)001:8799: myong ba'i drod gsum 'byung ba ni 'di lta ste
NK078(tshu)001:8800: / gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8802: dang po drod gsum spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8804: phyi lus kyi drod na tsha med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8806: shig gis mi za ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8808: stan la tshugs pa la sogs pa'i bzod pa phra mo thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8809: nang ngag gi drod rlung rang shugs kyis zin pas
NK078(tshu)001:8810: phyi nang du rgyu ba'i dbugs mi tshor te btang
NK078(tshu)001:8811: bzung la rang dbang thob ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8813: gsang ba'i drod don chos nyid la sems rnal du phebs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8814: the tshom med cing nges par phyi nang gsang ba'i drod gsum rang gi nyams su myong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8815: gnyis pa de las gzhan pa'i phyi nang gi drod 'byung bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8817: drod gsum po de las gazhana du drod 'byung tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8818: phyi rol gyi snang ba rdul phran tsam du mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8822: kun+da'i 'od la sogsa pa'i mtshan ma bzang po mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8823: nang sems la snang ba'i drod ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8824: ma sgom par riga pa rang shugs kyis chos nyid kyi klong du phebs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8825: phyi 'doda pa'i yul 'dod yon lnga la sems mi 'gro zhing mi 'phro ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8826: 'di nas 'chi 'pho ba dang phyi mar 'gyur zhing
NK078(tshu)001:8827: skye ba len pa ngag la nyamsa mi nga ba
NK078(tshu)001:8828: dang / phyi zas nor dang nang 'khrigs pa'i 'dod
NK078(tshu)001:8829: chagsa kyis yul la sngar bas zhen pa chung ba
NK078(tshu)001:8830: dang / dang / de yang tha mal ba'am sngar
NK078(tshu)001:8831: lta ba'i dus bas drod khyad par du dpagsa pa
NK078(tshu)001:8832: nyamsa su myong bas 'byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8833: gzhan sems can sdug bsngal snying rje'i yul mthong na
NK078(tshu)001:8834: thugs rjes rang dbang med par semsa 'phroga pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:8835: / 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad sngar bas grangs nyung la /
NK078(tshu)001:8836: ngo bo cha phra bas na mnyam par snyoms pa la sogs pa'i yon tan phal cher 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8840: grags dang ma grags bstod smad bde dang sdug /rnyed dang ma rnyed 'jig rten chos brgyad po //
NK078(tshu)001:8842: gsum pa drod nyams lnga kun tu 'khor bar 'byung tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:8844: de ltar drod kyi rnal pa de kun yang nyams
NK078(tshu)001:8845: dang sbyar na g.yo ba'i nyams kyi skabs su res
NK078(tshu)001:8847: thob pa'i skabs su phal cher yod la /
NK078(tshu)001:8848: gom brtan gyi skabs su mi 'gyur bar yod pa'i go rim gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:8849: nyams kun tu drod 'khor bar 'byung ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:8850: bcu gcig pa rtags la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8852: dang po dpe don gnyis kyi drod rtags spyir bstan pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8854: bru sha'i skad du khu ljo /
NK078(tshu)001:8855: bod skad du byis sba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8856: de yang smin te nar son pa lo nyer lnga
NK078(tshu)001:8857: tsam lon pa'i rigsa de la pha mas khyer la
NK078(tshu)001:8858: khyim thaba 'di lta bu zhig lon no zhes khyims
NK078(tshu)001:8860: byis sba de khyim thab de la brod pas mdun
NK078(tshu)001:8861: bsu zhing zang zing gi nor mang po dag /don
NK078(tshu)001:8862: du gnyer ba la brtson par byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8863: dpe de bzhin du don stong pa chen po'i rnal
NK078(tshu)001:8864: 'byor pas 'bras bu byang chub kyi bde ba chen
NK078(tshu)001:8866: drod dang rtags kyi yon tan mngon du mthong ba'i 'bras bu la blo brod pa'i tshul gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:8867: drod rtags mthong ba des shin tu thar pa'i lam la brtson 'grus byed par 'gyur bas /
NK078(tshu)001:8868: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir rtags 'di dag drod kyi rjes su bstan par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8869: gnyis pa rtags bye brag tu bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8871: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8873: drod song nas phyi ma rtags la'ang lam gyi lta
NK078(tshu)001:8874: sgom gyi nus pa'i stobsa che chung gi cha las
NK078(tshu)001:8877: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8880: dang po rtags la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8884: de la snga ma rtags la'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:8887: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8891: phyi rol gyi yul 'di dag chu lta bu gcig pur snang zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:8892: gzhan zad pas na zad par skye mched de /
NK078(tshu)001:8897: kha dog bzhi la sogs pa zad par gyi skye mched brgyad dngos su mthonga ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8899: kun da'i mdoga la sogsa pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8900: phyag mtshan la sogs pas gang bar mthong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8903: nang du lus kyi na tsha la bzod pa thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8904: ting nge 'dzin gyi bye brag shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8905: nyon mongs pa'i chu bo lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8906: 'khor ba'i rgyun lam la mngon zhen shas chung bas
NK078(tshu)001:8907: ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs kyis bag chags shas kyis
NK078(tshu)001:8908: bcad de shas chung du 'gro ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8909: rnam rtog gi rkyen gyis ting nge 'dzin mi 'phrog cing /
NK078(tshu)001:8910: srin po 'bar ba nag po mthong yang myos shing skrag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8911: lha'i bu mo mthong yang dga' zhing brod pa med do //
NK078(tshu)001:8912: ched du ma byas kyang ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i shugsa las snang ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8913: glang po che zhon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8915: me long skar mdas brgyan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8916: nam mkha' rdul gyis gang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8918: kun dga' ra ba mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8919: zad par gyi skye mched mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8920: stong gsum lag mthil ltar mnyam par 'byung ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8921: de ltar brgyad po mthong ba'ang 'byung zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:8922: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad 'dir shugs la cha
NK078(tshu)001:8923: tsam du mthong ba yang le'u drug pa ltar 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:8924: ngo // gnyis pa mngon shes la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:8928: mngon sum par rtogs pa ni rtogs bral yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:8929: shes pa ni ma 'khrul ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8930: de la rnam pa drug ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8931: rtsa rgyud le'u gsum las bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8932: 'di nyid kyi tshe dbang gi skabs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:8933: gzhan du lha'i rna ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8934: spyan gyi mngon par shes pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8935: sngon gnas rjes su dran pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8936: pha rol rnams kyi sems shes dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8937: 'chi 'pho skye ba mkhyen pa dang rdzu 'phrul shes pa'am zag zad shes /
NK078(tshu)001:8939: de rnams kyang lam gyi gnas skabs kyi zag pa
NK078(tshu)001:8940: gsum yod pa tshogs sbyor dang zag gsum med pa
NK078(tshu)001:8941: mthong sgom yan chad kyi mngon par shes pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8942: de la zag bcas zag med kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8943: mkhas grub chen po bde gshegs /
NK078(tshu)001:8947: skye ba rnam bzhi'i sbubs su 'jug pa rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:8948: rang dbang med par ni lus khams skye gnas grag pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8949: de dang ldan pa zag bcas /
NK078(tshu)001:8950: de dang mi ldan pa zag med du gsung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:8951: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ltar na /
NK078(tshu)001:8953: zag pa de yi bdag nyid dang //
NK078(tshu)001:8956: zag pa'i rjes su 'brel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8957: zag pa'i rjes su mthun pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8958: zag pa'i rgyu las byung ba'i phyir zag bcas su blta bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8961: nyon mongs nye nyon rnams so //
NK078(tshu)001:8962: 'brel ba la skye ba'i gnas su dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8963: mtshungs ldan grogs su 'brel ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:8965: nyon mongs pa nye nyon rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8966: lhan cig 'byung ba'i sems sems byung rnams so //
NK078(tshu)001:8968: nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis byung ba'i las rnams so //
NK078(tshu)001:8970: khams gsum gyi bag chags la /
NK078(tshu)001:8971: gzhan gyi nyon mongs kyi gnas ngan len dang ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8974: rgyu las byung ba ni dgra bcom lhag bcas kyi phung po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8975: des na 'og ma ba lnga ni zag pa dang bcas pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:8977: gzhan yang khams gsum du zag pas zag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8978: zhes slob dpon seng ge bzang pos gsungs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8980: dper na rma yi bu ga nas /
NK078(tshu)001:8981: rnag dang chu ser la sogs pa zag pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:8982: skye mched drug gi rma nas /
NK078(tshu)001:8984: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa zag pas zag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8988: ma rig pa'i zag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:8990: dang po 'dod khams su gtogs pa'i nyon mongs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8991: gnyis pa gzugs med khams su gtogs pa'i nyon mongs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8992: gsum pa khams gsum char gtogs pa'i nyon mongs pa /
NK078(tshu)001:8993: bzhi pa lta ba lnga bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:8995: lam ma rtogs pa'i 'dus byas rnams //
NK078(tshu)001:8996: zag bcas gang phyir de dag la //
NK078(tshu)001:8997: zag rnams kun tu rgyas par 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:8999: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9000: zag bcas kyi mngon shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9001: zag med kyi mngon shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:9004: dang po mngon shes kyi ming dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9006: zag bcas zag med kyi mngon shes gnyis yod pa'i sngon ma zag bcas kyi mngon shes la /
NK078(tshu)001:9007: de ting kun ting gi skabs su mdun du 'dug
NK078(tshu)001:9008: pa'i mi la dmigs nas bsgom pas de'i sems shes
NK078(tshu)001:9009: pa ni dmigs pa'i mngon shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9010: phyag rgya gcig spros kyi skabs su mngon shes nyi
NK078(tshu)001:9011: shu rtsa lnga'i grangs yongsa su rdzogs par 'byung ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:9012: mngon shes zhes bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9013: lam pa'i ming mngon shes la btags pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9014: tshogs sgrub kyi lam gzhan gyi bar chad pa med pa'i lam pa yin pas de'i mngon shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:9015: gnyis pa mngon shes kyi yul gyi tshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:9017: de ting gi skams su lhan cig tu drung la
NK078(tshu)001:9018: 'dug pa'i ming la dmigs pa gtad nas 'ag'a ste
NK078(tshu)001:9019: gcig gnyis gsum tsam gyis sems shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9020: kun ting gi skabs su de bas mang du 'phel ba ste bcu tsam gyi sems shes pa dang /
