NK078(tshu)001:9021: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su dbang po lnga re
NK078(tshu)001:9022: res yul lnga lnga gcod pas mngon shes nyi shu
NK078(tshu)001:9023: rtsa lnga'i grangs tsam rdzogsa shing de bas rgya che
NK078(tshu)001:9025: spros bcas kyi skabs su 'bring gis yul khamas tshun chad mthong zhing thos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9026: rab kyis gling bzhi mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9027: bar chad med pa'i 'bring dang rab kyis gling bzhi'i
NK078(tshu)001:9028: grangsa gnyis gsum drug tshun chad lha'i mig gis gzugs
NK078(tshu)001:9029: mthong zhing rna bas sgra thos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9030: sngon gnas shes pa la sogs gcig spros dang bar
NK078(tshu)001:9031: chad med pa'i lam gyi blo'i rim pas phye ba
NK078(tshu)001:9032: yin no // 'di la nyang nag gis 'grel bar /
NK078(tshu)001:9033: de ting dmigs pa'i mngon shes ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9034: mngon shes drug po gcig 'byung bas 'ga' dang zhes smos la /
NK078(tshu)001:9035: kun ting la de bas gnyis tsam du 'phel zhing 'byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9036: phyag rgya gcig pas nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs pa de rnams kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:9037: tha mal pa'i sgo lnga'i yul du gyur tshad shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:9038: spros bcas kyi yul khams mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9039: tshogs sgrub kyi gling grangs mthong zhing thos pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:9040: lam gyi rim pas phye ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9042: de ting gi mngon shes kyis yul dmigs pas pha rol po de'i sems 'ga' tsam ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9043: yul ngo bo stobs chung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9044: kun ting la de bas nyis 'gyur tsam du 'phel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9045: mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9046: yul khams rgya chung ba mthong ba phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK078(tshu)001:9047: rgya che ba mthong ba spros bcas /
NK078(tshu)001:9048: gling grangs gsum tshun chad mthong ba tshogs sgrub pa /
NK078(tshu)001:9049: bzhi char mthong zhing thos pa rnam smin te de dag gi rim pas drug tu phye ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9050: gnyis pa zag med kyi mngon shes la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9052: dang po rig 'dzin gsum gyi mngon shes kyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9054: phyi ma zag med kyi mngon shes la tshe dbang
NK078(tshu)001:9055: gi stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya tshun chad
NK078(tshu)001:9056: mngon shes kyi yul du gyur pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9057: sa dang po'i mngon shes kyiis yul la stong gsum
NK078(tshu)001:9058: gyi stong chen po brgya yin pa la sogs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:9059: sgras bsgom lam sa dgu'i mngon shes kyis yul du
NK078(tshu)001:9060: 'gyur lugs yod pa'i nang nas sogsa sgras sa gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:9061: pa nas bdun pa'i bar sdud la /
NK078(tshu)001:9062: sa brgyad pa dang phyag rgya chen po ni stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya /
NK078(tshu)001:9063: de gcig nas gnyis su bgrang ba'i stong phrag bcu
NK078(tshu)001:9064: rdul snyed du byas pa'i grangsa med dang mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:9065: brgya / de gcig nas gnyis su bgrang ba'i stong
NK078(tshu)001:9066: phrag bcu'i rdul byas pa de snyed dang mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:9067: stong gsum mngon shes kyis yul du gyur pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9068: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi mngon shes ni mnyam bzhag
NK078(tshu)001:9069: tu rgyal ba sangs rgyas dang mnyam pa yin pa
NK078(tshu)001:9070: las / 'o na mthar lam pa dang sangs rgyas khyad med dam zhe na yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:9071: bag la nyal gyi dri ma yod med kyis phye ba de basa na /
NK078(tshu)001:9072: mthar lam pa dang rdzogsa pa'i sangs rgyas gnyis la khyad par yod pa yina te /
NK078(tshu)001:9074: 'dra la bag la nyal gyis phye /
NK078(tshu)001:9076: gnyis pa rgyu'i sems dpa' dang khyad par yod med phye ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9078: zag med mngon shes kyis yul de tsam yin pa
NK078(tshu)001:9079: de bas na rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i byang
NK078(tshu)001:9080: chub semsa dapa'a sa dang po rab tu dga' ba
NK078(tshu)001:9081: dang / sngags kyi mthong lam tshe dbang rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:9082: gnyis 'khor ba la mi ldog pa tsam du skal
NK078(tshu)001:9083: ba mnyam la khyad par yod rgyu'i sa brgyad pa
NK078(tshu)001:9084: dang sngags kyi phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:9085: dgongs pa mi g.yo ba tsam du skal pa mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:9086: dang / ste / rgyu'i sa bcu pa dang sngags
NK078(tshu)001:9087: kyi lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis 'bras bu thob ma
NK078(tshu)001:9088: rag pa tsam du skal pa mnyam pa'i phyir na
NK078(tshu)001:9089: de tsam du grangs mthun pa yin pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:9091: de yang dang po'i dang po dang //
NK078(tshu)001:9092: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog de //
NK078(tshu)001:9093: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK078(tshu)001:9094: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mo //
NK078(tshu)001:9096: mtshan mthun par mthong lam sgom lam mthar lam gsum du brjod kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:9097: 'on kyang dgongs pa yon tan gyi khyad tshul ni mi 'dra zhing mi mnyam ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9098: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba la dbyer med rtogs ma rtogs kyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9099: dgongsa pa'i ting nge 'dzin la dbyer med goms ma
NK078(tshu)001:9100: goms kyi khyad par yod pa'i gazha lam cha yis
NK078(tshu)001:9101: phye bas / rgyu'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9102: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi rig 'dzin gsum la khyad par yod par nges te /
NK078(tshu)001:9104: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho khyad par 'phags //
NK078(tshu)001:9105: lta ba'i sgrib pas phye phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:9107: don la tshe dbang sa brgyad dang mnyam la /
NK078(tshu)001:9108: phyag chen sa bcu dang mnyam ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9109: lhun grub bcu gcig kun tu 'od dang mnyam pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:9112: stong chen gyi rnal 'byor 'di bsgom pa'i tshe rdzu
NK078(tshu)001:9113: 'phrul nyi shu la sogs mthu 'byin nus pa rdzu
NK078(tshu)001:9115: 'gro ba so so'i skad du chos ston pa nus pa rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9116: sa gzhi phyogs cha drug tu g.yo bas nang du
NK078(tshu)001:9117: sems skye zhing sa 'phar bar byed pa chos snang
NK078(tshu)001:9119: phyi nang gi snod bcud thams cad gsang sngags kyi
NK078(tshu)001:9120: rang sgra di ri ri sgrogs pa kun tu brjod
NK078(tshu)001:9122: de ltar cho 'phrul bzhi po yang lam lta ba cig char ba la rdzogsa par 'byung gis /
NK078(tshu)001:9123: lam rim pas de ting 'di bsgom pa'i tshe cho 'phrul bzhi 'byung ba'i rgyu tsam yin gyi /
NK078(tshu)001:9124: 'o na dngos su 'byung ba med dam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:9125: nyams lnga mthar phyin pa'i skabs su cho 'phrul bzhi'i
NK078(tshu)001:9126: cha gcig tsam 'byung ba yang srid pa nyid do
NK078(tshu)001:9127: // bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9129: dang po sgrib pa dag cing bden pa mthong ba'i rmi ltas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9131: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor de bzhin nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:9132: ting nge 'dzin la blo gnas pa'i rmi lam la
NK078(tshu)001:9133: yang / sgrib pa dag pa'i rtags su lus gcera
NK078(tshu)001:9134: bur phyung bar rmis zhing rdzing bu rnam dag gam
NK078(tshu)001:9135: yang / / chu la khrus byed nas dri ma dag par rmi ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9136: bden pa mthong ba'i ltas su byang chub chen po'i mchod rten mthong ba rmi ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9137: spyir tshogs lam du bag chags sbyangs pa'i ltas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9138: spyor lam du 'jigs pa dang bral ba'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9139: mthong lam dus thob pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9140: bsgom lam du sa non pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9141: mthar lam du rgyal ba'i sras su nges pa'i ltas dang lnga 'byung bar bshad pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:9142: 'di ni bag chags byang ba dang bden pa mthong ba'i ltas so //
NK078(tshu)001:9143: gnyis pa byin gyis brlab cing lung bstan 'byung ba'i rmi ltas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9145: dam pa mchog sangs rgyas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9146: dam pa rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' de yis kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:9147: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sras dang rig 'dzin byang sems
NK078(tshu)001:9148: rnams kyi spun du dgongs shing byin gyis rlobs pa
NK078(tshu)001:9149: dang / zhor la ma mo dang mkha' 'gros ming por dgongs nas sdongs grogs byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9150: dam can chos skyongs rnams kyis rje dpon dam par dgongs nas phrin las sgrub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9151: gzhan yang rmi lam gyi mtshan mar rang gi bla
NK078(tshu)001:9152: ma sdug bsngal skyob pa'i mgon po mngon du snang
NK078(tshu)001:9153: bas rang la dbang bskur ba dang byin gyis brlabs
NK078(tshu)001:9154: pa la sogs sgras lung bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9157: byang chub kyi lam du 'jug pa'i rtags lnga byed cing de la bar chad 'byung mi 'byung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9158: legsa pa'i yon tan dang nyes pa'i skyon 'byung mi
NK078(tshu)001:9159: 'byung gi sgo nas lam la brtson 'grus gyis shig
NK078(tshu)001:9160: par lung ston pa rmis so //
NK078(tshu)001:9161: de'i zhor bshad la lugs gcig tu tshogs lam du
NK078(tshu)001:9162: sgrib pa byang ba'i ltas bla ma khrus bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:9163: dang / sbyor lam du chos la dbang thob pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:9164: ltas bla mas dbang skur zhing byin gyis rlobs pa
NK078(tshu)001:9165: dang / dang / mthong lam du bden pa mthong
NK078(tshu)001:9166: ba'i ltas bla mas khri gdan la bzhag nas chos
NK078(tshu)001:9168: sgom lam du lung bstan thos pa'i ltas bla mas
NK078(tshu)001:9169: bya ba gang yang rung bar lung ston pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:9170: / mthar lam du gzhan don nus pa'i ltas rang
NK078(tshu)001:9171: nyid khri gdan la bzhag cing gser gyi 'khor lo
NK078(tshu)001:9173: chos shod cig par bka' bsgo bar byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9174: gsum pa de nyid bdud dang cha dbye bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9176: lung ston pa'i mtshan ltas de yang bdud bla mar
NK078(tshu)001:9177: sprul nas bar chad byed pa'i nyes yod pas de
NK078(tshu)001:9178: dang / lam gyi nyams rtags gang yin cha dbye dgos te /
NK078(tshu)001:9179: de yang slob dpon du sprul pa'i bdud nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9181: bdud mkhan po dang slob dpon du sprul pa ni bzlog daka'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9183: ming gi gzhi las bdud ni nye bar 'ong gyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:9184: 'di skad smras te 'di ni khyod kyi pha ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9185: khyod kyi rgyud kyi ming ni 'di yin zhes /
NK078(tshu)001:9186: spyangs sdom rnal 'byor ldan pa ci 'dra byung gyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:9187: khyod sngon yon tan tshul yang 'di 'dra zhes /
NK078(tshu)001:9188: gang tsho khyod ni bud rdar gyur pa'i ming 'di yin /
NK078(tshu)001:9189: sbyang sdom rnal 'byor ldan pa ci 'dra byung gyur pa /
NK078(tshu)001:9190: khyod sngon yon tan tshul yang 'di 'drar byung gyur pa /
NK078(tshu)001:9192: bdud kyis byin gyis brlabs pa dang lung ston pa ltar snang nas bar chad byed pa 'byung bas /
NK078(tshu)001:9193: nyes pa'i bar chad byed pa'i ched du bdud 'byung ba yod srid pa'i phyira na /
NK078(tshu)001:9194: bdud kyi bar chad dang lam gyi grub rtags kyi
NK078(tshu)001:9195: cha gnyis ting nge 'dzin dang nyams rtogs bzang ngan
NK078(tshu)001:9196: la sogs brtag pa zag bcas lam gyi skabs su
NK078(tshu)001:9198: de'ang phyi'i bar chad dngos su lta bas ma chun pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9199: rmi lam rang rgyud par bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9200: ha cang re dogs che ba la sogs pas kyang bdud 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:9201: bzhi pa de'i bar chad bsal phyir bla ma la zhu ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9203: bdud kyi bar chad de dag bsal ba'i phyir rmi
NK078(tshu)001:9204: lam de dag kun rang gi bla ma la nyid
NK078(tshu)001:9206: gzhan du dri zhing smra ba ni min te /
NK078(tshu)001:9207: gal te bzang ngan gang yin na yang gsang na dngos grub myur bas so //
NK078(tshu)001:9208: bcu gsum pa phan yon la drug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9210: dang po dge sdig las kyis mi gos pa'i phan yon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9212: chos nyid de bzhina nyid du lta bas mthong zhing ting nge 'dzin gyis gomsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:9213: rgyu dge ba'i las dang mi dge ba'i las gnyis su 'dzin pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:9214: las dge sdig gi rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan ma rang rgyud du yongsa su mi 'dzin te /
NK078(tshu)001:9215: ci'i phyir na sems nyid rang bzhin skye med du
NK078(tshu)001:9216: ye nas 'od gsal ba'i ngang la las dge sdig
NK078(tshu)001:9217: gi rnam smin gyis gos pa med pas shin tu
NK078(tshu)001:9218: bde ba'o // gnyis pa bde sdug gnyis su med par grol ba'i ngang /
NK078(tshu)001:9220: 'bras bu bde ba mtho ris dang mi bde ba ngan song gnyis su 'dzin pa med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9221: gnyis med kyi don rang byung gi ye shes la
NK078(tshu)001:9222: bde sdug gnyis 'dzin gyi chags pa meda cing rnam
NK078(tshu)001:9223: par dag pas / mtho ris kyi bde ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:9224: ngan song gi sdug bsngal thamsa cad dbyer med de
NK078(tshu)001:9225: rang rig pa'i ye shes yin pas semsa nyid phyogs
NK078(tshu)001:9226: 'dzin gyi dri mas ma gos shing dangsa pas a
NK078(tshu)001:9227: skye ba med pa'i ngang du rnam rtog gi zug
NK078(tshu)001:9228: rngu med pas rab tu bde ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9229: gsum pa gtsang sme gnyis su med pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9231: 'dod pa'i longs spyod gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya
NK078(tshu)001:9232: ste lnga ldan thamsa cad la gtsang ba dang sme
NK078(tshu)001:9233: ba'i blo gnyis su ma 'dzin cig /de ci'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:9234: zhe na / gtsang sme thams cad chos nyid spros bral du ro gcig pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:9235: spang len gnyis su 'dzin pa'i zug rngu med pas kyang shin tu bde ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9236: bzhi pa 'khor ba ma spangs rang sar grol ba'i ngang /
NK078(tshu)001:9238: shes rab che ba cig char ba dang shes rab
NK078(tshu)001:9239: chung ba rim gyis pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsal mi
NK078(tshu)001:9240: gsal gyis / lta sgom spyod pa la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:9241: thamsa cad ma nora bar rgyud lung man ngag gi
NK078(tshu)001:9242: gzhung las byung ba'i lugsa bzhin du spyad na /
NK078(tshu)001:9243: 'khor ba ma spangsa chos nyid du rang dag pas sdug bsngal du 'dzin pa med cing /
NK078(tshu)001:9244: 'khor 'das gnyis su meda pa'i don rtogs shing nyams
NK078(tshu)001:9245: su myong ste des rgyud tshimsa pas khamsa a rab
NK078(tshu)001:9247: lnga pa chos nyid mngon sum du mthong ba'i tshe dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9249: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams ma lus pa thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:9250: sems nyid du gcig par rtogs pa'i nganga de la
NK078(tshu)001:9251: / lta bar bya ba'i yul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9252: blta bar byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis ka med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:9253: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis sgron me rgyun chad
NK078(tshu)001:9255: phyogsa bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing thamsa cad gnyis med rang snang du mthong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9256: drug pa ma bsgrod par sa non pa'i phan yon no //
NK078(tshu)001:9258: tshe 'di dang phyi ma pha rol de bzhin nyid
NK078(tshu)001:9259: la gnyis su med pa'i phyir 'di nas 'gro ba
NK078(tshu)001:9260: dang / pha rol du 'ong bar bya ba grub pa min te /
NK078(tshu)001:9261: lus kyi yan lag bzhi stobsa chen pos bsgrod cing ma mchong bar /
NK078(tshu)001:9262: phyogsa bcu'i stong khamsa kyi rtog pa thamsa cad stong pa chen po nyid du gsal bas /
NK078(tshu)001:9263: rtogs par rang ldan mi nus pa la tha snyad du mnan zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9264: bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9266: dang po mtshan ma med pa'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9268: de ting la gnas pa 'di'i tshe dbang po drug gis spyod yul 'gyur zhing 'chi bar mthong na /
NK078(tshu)001:9269: 'chi 'pho ba'i man ngag 'di ltar byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:9270: ngu skad la sogs pa phyi nang gi g.yeng ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:9271: mtshan ma kun bsal nas rnam pa kun ldan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:9272: stong pa nyid kyi ngang la rtse gcig tu 'dug
NK078(tshu)001:9273: par bya zhing / de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:9274: de dran pas sngar gyi la sa ngan gyi bag
NK078(tshu)001:9277: gsang ba'i yid ni 'pho gyur na //
NK078(tshu)001:9278: bya ba la sogs ring dor nas //
NK078(tshu)001:9279: rnam shes sa la thim gyur pa //
NK078(tshu)001:9280: sa yang chu la thim par gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:9281: chu ni me la thim gyur la //
NK078(tshu)001:9282: de nyid rlung la thim par 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:9283: rlung ni snying la thim pa ste //
NK078(tshu)001:9284: de las me long dbugs bzhin du //
NK078(tshu)001:9285: ma skyes stong pa'i grong du'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9287: de ltar zin na tshe phyi ma la 'dod khamas
NK078(tshu)001:9288: kyi lha dang mi'i rigs khyad par can du skyes
NK078(tshu)001:9289: nas gsang ba'i thega pa chen po la sbyor ba
NK078(tshu)001:9291: 'chi kha'i ye shes stobs che na //
NK078(tshu)001:9292: lo dang bskal pa'i bag chags kun //
NK078(tshu)001:9293: ye shes skad cig gcig gis sel //
NK078(tshu)001:9295: gnyis pa mtshan bcas kyi man ngag go //
NK078(tshu)001:9297: mtshan med kyi 'pho ba la dgar bas yang na zhes 'dam ka ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9299: snying gar rin po che'i gur phub pa lta bur
NK078(tshu)001:9300: gsang ba gsera gyi sgrom bu'i nang snying ga'i dkyil
NK078(tshu)001:9301: du / kun gzhi 'od phung kha dog lnga'i ngo bo tshon gang ba zhig bsam pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9302: de'i steng du nyon yid zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du bsam /
NK078(tshu)001:9303: de'i steng du yid shes h+aum ring po zhig tu bsgom zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:9304: de gsum brtsegas pa'i ting nge 'dzin la dmigsa pa rtse gcig tu brtan pa thob nas /
NK078(tshu)001:9305: dbugs sam rlung gis phar 'phra tshur 'dus h'u yig la thim de zla ba la thim /
NK078(tshu)001:9307: mthar 'od phung de nyid phyogs bcu'i stong khams thams
NK078(tshu)001:9308: cad la khyab par bdal te spyod yul thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:9309: 'od phung du bsam zhing stong pa'i ngang la 'dug
NK078(tshu)001:9311: gsang ba'i gnas su nyon mongs yid //
NK078(tshu)001:9312: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba las //
NK078(tshu)001:9313: kun gzhi'i ye shes snying po yi //
NK078(tshu)001:9314: 'od kyis khams su dbyings bsdus te //
NK078(tshu)001:9315: tshon gang 'od du gsal ba la //
NK078(tshu)001:9316: dkar po h'u gnas rnam shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:9317: de dag sku gsung thugs bdag ste //
NK078(tshu)001:9318: shin tu 'gres pa nyid du bya //
NK078(tshu)001:9319: rlung brtsegs bcud g.yos mtshan mthong nas //
NK078(tshu)001:9320: ring po'i h'u nyid gnas pa nas //
NK078(tshu)001:9321: du ba'i tshul drang 'od la bsdu //
NK078(tshu)001:9322: de bzhin zla ba'ang shes par bya //
NK078(tshu)001:9323: 'od zhu gsang ba'i lam zhugs te //
NK078(tshu)001:9324: phyir byung phyogs bcur khyab brda' bas //
NK078(tshu)001:9325: khams gsum dag phyir mtha' dbus dang //
NK078(tshu)001:9326: phyi nang yul sems bral ba'i don //
NK078(tshu)001:9327: dran pa las kyi rgyun bcad de //
NK078(tshu)001:9328: rang gnas mthong bar 'gyur ba yin //
NK078(tshu)001:9330: bco lnga pa 'bras bu bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9332: don snang stong dbyer med stong chen gyi rnal 'byor la goms pa'i mtha' ma /
NK078(tshu)001:9333: ting nge 'dzin des mangna du byasa pa'i 'bras bu dbu ma las lhag pa'i chos skur sbyor ro //
NK078(tshu)001:9334: 'o na lam gong ma kun ting yan chod la
NK078(tshu)001:9335: sogs rnams don med du 'gyur ro zhe na ma
NK078(tshu)001:9336: yin te 'bras bu chos sku gsal stong dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:9337: nyid la lam du byed pa'i phyir yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:9338: de bzhin nyid dang chos sku gnyis rnam pa mchog
NK078(tshu)001:9339: ldan gyi stong pa chen por phyogs mthun pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:9340: pas na / 'bras bu chos sku thob par brjod
NK078(tshu)001:9341: kyis des na 'bras bu dngos su thob pa'i rigsa
NK078(tshu)001:9342: pas na / ma yin te / rgyu 'bras ches mthun sbyor ba tsam la dgongs pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:9344: dngos po ma skyes yul sems med //
NK078(tshu)001:9345: mnyam dbyings dmigs yul med don gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:9346: blo yi rtsol dang rang gsal bas //
NK078(tshu)001:9347: de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin te //
NK078(tshu)001:9348: chos kyi sku dang kun tu 'ong //
NK078(tshu)001:9349: ngo bos tha dad med phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:9353: sa gsum chos mthun du bshad pas gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:9354: gnas skabs nye sbyor gyi 'bras bu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9355: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin la sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9356: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9358: rnam pa kun ldan gyi stong pa chen po'i don
NK078(tshu)001:9359: rnal ma la rang rig pa'i blo 'byor ba'i ting
NK078(tshu)001:9360: nge 'dzin bstan pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams 'tshams
NK078(tshu)001:9361: dang ris su gcod cing 'tshams 'dzin par byed pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:9362: don gyis na le'u zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9363: yas bgrang gsum pa'i don du gada'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9364: le'u bzhi pa kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9366: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9368: don dam gsal stong chos kyi sku'i ngo bo de
NK078(tshu)001:9369: la lta bas rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin gyis goms
NK078(tshu)001:9371: de ltar chos nyid stong pa la goms kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:9372: stong zhen gyi dri ma bsal dgos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9373: gdul bya sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'god pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:9374: snying rje 'di la sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9375: chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9376: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje dang gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:9377: 'dir yul bral dmigs med kyi snying rje chen po ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor bshad par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9378: de yang snying rje la dbye na bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9379: phyogs gcig pa'i snying rje dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9380: gtod pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9381: dmigs pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9382: rnam pa dang bcas pa'i snying rje'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9384: 'jig rten pa'i snying rje ste khra dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9386: mi sdig can rnams kyis kyang rang gi bu smad kyi sdug bsngal mthong na /
NK078(tshu)001:9387: snying rje nas rang gi srog 'dor phod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9390: rang rang gi bden bzhi dang rten 'brel gyi lam
NK078(tshu)001:9391: la 'jug pa'i rigs mthun gyi gdul bya la chos
NK078(tshu)001:9392: ston pa dang / rdzu 'phrul gyis mngon shes 'ga' byas nas 'dren pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9393: 'o na snying rje med cig gzhan don mi byed par bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:9394: snying rje ye med ma yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:9395: shas chung ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9396: gsum pa dmigs pa bcas pa ni bo d+hi ste
NK078(tshu)001:9397: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis
NK078(tshu)001:9398: sems can thams cad kyi don mdzad pa de snying
NK078(tshu)001:9399: rje skye ba'i yul sems can dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9400: bskyed byed kyi mkhan po rang nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9401: snying rje'i ngo bo gdung ba dang bcas pa gsum du dmigs zhing 'dzin pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9402: bzhi pa rnam pa dang bcas pa'i snying rje ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9404: snying rje'i rnam pa tsam yod kyang 'dzin pa med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9405: de la ma h+aa zhes pa'i rkyen gyis snying rje chen po zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9406: snying rje bya ba'i yul sems can rang rgyud pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:9407: rig pa ye shes sgyu mar gsal bas /
NK078(tshu)001:9409: rje byed kyi mkhan po yang ye shes sgyu mar gsal bas tshur rol na med /
NK078(tshu)001:9410: snying rje'i ngo bo yang rig pa ye shes sgyu mar gsal ba la la gzhan med de /
NK078(tshu)001:9411: mngon par gdung ba de la med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9412: de bas na rgyas pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:9413: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med gcig rtogs na //
NK078(tshu)001:9414: thugs rje chen po skye zhes de la bya //
NK078(tshu)001:9417: lang ka'i bdag po chos thams cad stong pa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:9418: la rang bzhin gyis gnas nas gnyis su ma mthong
NK078(tshu)001:9419: bas snying rje'i yul med pa ni thams cad snying
NK078(tshu)001:9420: rje chen po'o // der yongs su sgrol ba'i phyir snying rje chen po yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:9421: byams pa'i snying rje ngag gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i sems can gyi srog bton pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9422: gang thar bar bton pa de ni snying rje chung ngur rigs par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9424: gnyis pa gzhung don la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9426: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9429: rjes su mthun pa'i kun snang ni lus mdor bstan
NK078(tshu)001:9430: bco lnga po nyid ni yan lag rgyas bshad kyi
NK078(tshu)001:9431: sgo nas shes par gyis shig pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9432: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la don bco lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9434: dang po sngon du 'gro ba la dbye ba med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9436: snying rje sgyu ma'i sngon du stong pa chen po la gomsa pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9437: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad thugsa rjes rjes su bzung ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:9438: tshogs bsags pa'i don la yan lag brgyad pa sngon de ting bzhin du byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:9439: de'i rjes la ngo bo ye shes rang gsal rnams
NK078(tshu)001:9440: pa sgyu ma lta bus khyab pa'i snying rje chen
NK078(tshu)001:9441: po'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9442: gnyis pa dgos ched la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9446: gang zag dang chos kyi bdag gam /
NK078(tshu)001:9447: snying rje skye byed kyi mkhan po bdag dang skye
NK078(tshu)001:9448: bya'i yul gzhan dang gnyis su 'dzin pa tha dad
NK078(tshu)001:9449: kyi dri ma bsal ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9450: de ting la stong pa'i zhen pas 'ching ba de'i mdud pa gshig pa'i dgos ched yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9453: snying rje chen po'i sgo nas gdul bya sems can
NK078(tshu)001:9454: rnams tshad med pa bzhis yang dag pa thar pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:9455: sa la dgod pa'i dgos ched yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9456: de nyid mthar phyin pa 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig
NK078(tshu)001:9457: pa thob pa'i rgyur bya zhing de'i thabs la snying
NK078(tshu)001:9458: rje chen po'i rnal 'byor 'di nyid ni don du
NK078(tshu)001:9460: sems nyid gsal stong don dam bden pa de nyid
NK078(tshu)001:9461: kyi ngang la kun rdzob 'gags med ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:9462: mar snang ba gnyis phyogs dang ris su mi btang
NK078(tshu)001:9463: ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:9464: snying rje chen po ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:9465: 'di'i lam la blo rtse gcig tu gnas par bya
NK078(tshu)001:9466: ste / snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la 'jug pa'i thun mtshamsa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9467: de ting mthar phyin pa'i dus kyi bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9468: gsum pa bzhag thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9469: snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9470: 'og ma'i snying rje las khyad par dpags tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:9473: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9475: snying rje chen po bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang gis khamas gsum 'khor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9476: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad /
NK078(tshu)001:9477: dmigs pa med pa'i thugsa rje chen po rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:9478: sgyu ma'i ye shes su gsal ba'i ngang du mig
NK078(tshu)001:9480: rna bas sgra thos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9481: lce yis ro myong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9483: snas dri tshor ba rnams la rang snang 'gags med du sbyongs pa'i thabs la'ang gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9484: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis brtags pa'i rgyu'i sa thob pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:9485: snga ma de ting la goms pa'i rjes las ye shes sgyu mar gsal bas na thob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9486: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9488: dang po blo chung ba'i lta ba'am so sor rtogs pa'i rgyu'i sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9490: snying rje chen po sgom pa'i lam pa de yis
NK078(tshu)001:9491: 'khor 'das dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos so cog
NK078(tshu)001:9492: lhag ma ma lus thams cad rtag pa ther zug
NK078(tshu)001:9493: pa'i snying po rang rgyud du grub nas yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:9494: ma yin te / ye shes rang gsal sgyu ma
NK078(tshu)001:9495: ltar rtogs pa'i ngang la blo mi g.yor bar bzhag
NK078(tshu)001:9496: ma yin te / pa'o // 'o na sgyu ma ltar rtogs pa ci zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:9497: sgyu ma'i dpe'i dngos po drug gi tshul ni 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9498: snang la rang rgyud pas dben pa sgyu ma ste log rtog sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9499: snang ba ngo bo med pas mig yor te rten 'brel sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9500: cir yang ma nges pas sprul pa ste yang dag sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9501: snang la grub pas smig rgyu ste thabs sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9502: snang la rang bzhin med pas 'aja'a tshon ste ye shes sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9503: gsal la ngo bo stong pas chu zla ste phyag rgya sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9504: des na dpe drug gis mtshon pa'i tshul bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:9505: snying rje skye byed kyi rnal 'byor pa bdag dang
NK078(tshu)001:9506: skye ba'i yul 'gro ba kun ye shes sgyu mar
NK078(tshu)001:9508: 'o na sems can thams cad rgyud gcig tu gnas so zhe na ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:9509: ye shes sgyu ma de nyid ngo ma shes pas
NK078(tshu)001:9510: log rtog gi las snang la bde sdug tha dad
NK078(tshu)001:9511: pas gcig pa'i mtha' bsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9512: de yang rang gi blos kun tu brtag pa'i dbang
NK078(tshu)001:9513: gis bdag dang 'gro ba tha dad pa'i phyir gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:9514: su snang ngo // don ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bo la bdag gzhan gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9515: tha dad pa gnyis su dbye ba med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:9516: de yang snang ba bcu bdun pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:9517: rtog sems 'gro ba so so'i blo //
NK078(tshu)001:9518: gcig na dge sdig rnam smin yang /
NK078(tshu)001:9519: ma spyad kun gyis myong bar rigs //
NK078(tshu)001:9520: de min yang dag don mi rung //
NK078(tshu)001:9521: rnam smin thun mong mi 'byung phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:9522: gcig min de nyid ma skyes pas //
NK078(tshu)001:9523: tha dad du yang rung ba min //
NK078(tshu)001:9525: de yang snying rje bya'i yul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9526: rje bar byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis med /
NK078(tshu)001:9527: med bzhin du rje bya rje byed kyi snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:9528: 'goga pa yang med par rtogs pa'i lta ba mthong
NK078(tshu)001:9529: ba'i rjes su bsgom pa ma shor tsam du bya
NK078(tshu)001:9530: ba'o // de ltar lta ba dran pa'i rjes su
NK078(tshu)001:9531: chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje skyes nas stong pa
NK078(tshu)001:9533: yang na sems can la dmigs pa'i rtog dpyod sngon du btang spyi blugsa te /
NK078(tshu)001:9534: de yang sems can rnams thog med nas ma shes
NK078(tshu)001:9535: pas 'khrul zhing sdug bsngal nyam thag la brten nas
NK078(tshu)001:9537: gsal stong zung 'jug tu gomsa par bya ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9538: gnyis pa blo che ba dang bcas nas de ting
NK078(tshu)001:9539: goms pa'i rjes su bsgom pa de la gnyis te
NK078(tshu)001:9541: dang po rgyu snga ma gnyis sam de ting brtan
NK078(tshu)001:9542: pa'i steng nas dran pa spyi blugs ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:9543: mar gsal ba dpe dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9545: de bas lta ba mthong rjes dang rtog dpyod sngon
NK078(tshu)001:9546: 'gro gnyis la goms nas dran pa spyi blugs sam
NK078(tshu)001:9547: / yang na rgyu de ting gomsa pas rjes su
NK078(tshu)001:9548: dran pa gang yang ma bcos par ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:9549: / mar gsal ba'ang / blos sngon du lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:9550: dran pa'am rtog dpyod btang ba gang yang med de
NK078(tshu)001:9551: / mar gsal ba'ang / / dper na shar gyi
NK078(tshu)001:9552: nam mkhas nub kyi nam mkha' yul du mi byed
NK078(tshu)001:9554: gnyis pa gsal dus dmigs med nam mkha' ltar du bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9556: rnal 'byor pa rang gi lus ngag semsa ngang der
NK078(tshu)001:9557: ma zad 'khor 'das phyi nang gi chos thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:9558: don dam par sems nyid yin pas ganga na'ang mi
NK078(tshu)001:9559: gnas yul rang rgyud du mi dmigsa pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9560: dpe mig gi yul du tho yor mir 'dzin kyang
NK078(tshu)001:9561: mi ma grub pa'i tshul du sbyor ba'i tshul ni
NK078(tshu)001:9562: sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu las byung ba'i phyi
NK078(tshu)001:9563: nang gi chos thams cad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9564: sgom pa'i blos kyang rang rgyud du ma grub par rang gsal nam mkha' lta bur bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:9565: gsum pa de ma 'gags pa thabs kyis bsgoms pa'i yon tan 'bras bu dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9567: 'khor 'das kyis chos thamsa cad kyi gnas lugs rig
NK078(tshu)001:9568: pa ye shes sgyu mar 'gag par snang bas thabsa
NK078(tshu)001:9570: gzhi'i thabsa de la 'gags med du rtogs pa'i thabsa kyis gnyis med du rnam par sbyor bas /
NK078(tshu)001:9571: de ka sgom pa'i thabas chen po goms pa'i thabsa
NK078(tshu)001:9572: las byung ba'i 'bras bus sam yon tan gyi che
NK078(tshu)001:9573: ba de ni rtogs pa byang ba ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:9574: mar chub skye 'jig med pas rdo rje /
NK078(tshu)001:9575: yul yul can gnyis su 'dzin pa las khyad par
NK078(tshu)001:9576: du gyur pa'i phyir mchog yin no zhes smras so
NK078(tshu)001:9577: // gnyis pa khyad par la gnyis te //
NK078(tshu)001:9579: dang po snying rje'i ngo bo la tshad med bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:9580: tshang bas mngon par gdung ba yod med kyi khyad
NK078(tshu)001:9582: shes bya phyi nang gi chos thamsa cad du ni
NK078(tshu)001:9583: rig pa ye shes sgyu ma rang gasla ba'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:9584: / ye shes sgyu ma ma yin pa'i chos 'ga' tsam yang yod pa ma yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9585: rgyu'i theg pa'i snying rje ni mas bu la gdung
NK078(tshu)001:9586: ba dang 'dra bar yul yul can du 'gro ba
NK078(tshu)001:9587: ma bsgral bar 'dir yul bral gnyis med du dus
NK078(tshu)001:9588: gcig bsgral bas / gsod pa ste dgra gsod pa
NK078(tshu)001:9589: lta bu ni ma yin pas chen po ni gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:9590: su med pa'i snying rje tshad med pa'i rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:9591: gcig bsgral bas / yin te / de la bdag
NK078(tshu)001:9592: gzhan gnyis su mi 'byed pas phana pa ngang gis
NK078(tshu)001:9593: rdzogsa pa'i cha nas byams pa chena pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9594: gnyis med kyi ngang la 'gyod bya'i yul med pas
NK078(tshu)001:9595: mi 'gyod pa'i cha nas dga' ba'i mchog ste dga'
NK078(tshu)001:9597: bdag gzhan gnyis 'bral ba med pa 'gro ba kun
NK078(tshu)001:9598: la snyomsa pa'i cha nas btang snyoms tshad med pa
NK078(tshu)001:9599: ste / 'di ni ye shes rang gsal nyid la tshad med pa bzhi tshang tshul brtsis pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9600: de ltar lha tshangsa par skye ba'i rgyu tshad med
NK078(tshu)001:9601: bzhi snying rje chen po bsgom pa la tshang ste
NK078(tshu)001:9602: / ngo bo gcig par dus gcig la rdzogsa pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9603: de'i phyir rgyu'i theg pa ltar yul yul can gyi
NK078(tshu)001:9604: mngon par zhen pa'i gdung ba gsang sngags kyi snying
NK078(tshu)001:9605: rje chen po ye shes sgyu ma bsgom pa de
NK078(tshu)001:9606: la med do // gnyis pa snying rje'i yul la dmigs dgos mi dgos kyi khyad par ro //
NK078(tshu)001:9608: rgyu'i theg pa ltar yul yul can gyi gdung ba med pa de'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:9609: rgyu'i theg pas 'khor ba'i rgyu ma rig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9612: dus thog ma med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9613: rang bzhin de ma yin pa la der 'dzin pa'i 'khrul ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9614: 'khrul tshul rten 'brel bcu gnyis su dus rgyun gyis 'khor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9615: nyes pa yang dag pa'i don las nyamsa pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9616: ngo bo 'gro drug snod bcud sna tshogs su snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9617: des thar dka' bas na btson gyi ra ba lta bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9618: 'bras bu dang ngo bo gcig tu bsdus pas brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:9619: dang ldan pa'i yul sems can rnams la dmigsa nas
NK078(tshu)001:9620: tshad med bzhi skye ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9621: sngags kyi snying rje chen po de yis skye bya
NK078(tshu)001:9622: skye byed gcig par shes par tshad med bzhi snying
NK078(tshu)001:9623: rje chen po gcig la tshang bar 'byung ba ni
NK078(tshu)001:9624: / pha rol phyin pas yul yul can du tshad med bzhi tha dad du skye ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9625: sngags kyi tshad med bzhi ni ngo bo gcig cing
NK078(tshu)001:9626: yul bral gnyis med 'dod pa'i phyir de gnyis mtshungsa
NK078(tshu)001:9628: bzhi pa ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9632: snying rje chen po ye shes sgyu ma de dag
NK078(tshu)001:9633: rang gi ngo bo nyid bstan pa pa'ang gang zhe
NK078(tshu)001:9634: na / don ngo bo ngos bzung ba'i rnam grangs bzhin du ming gi rnam grangsa kyang 'jug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9635: bsgom bya dona gyi ngo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9636: bsgom byed rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel ba yin /
NK078(tshu)001:9637: bsgom bya sgom byed gnyis su phye bas na zung gcig ya gnyis su 'gyur la /
NK078(tshu)001:9638: zhor la sgom pa'i nges tshig dang gsum du 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:9639: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9640: ngo bo dang rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9643: bsgom bya don gyi ngo bo ni rnam grangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9644: bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9646: sgyu ma'i ngo bo drug gi dmigs rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9647: sgyu ma dmigs med rang snang dgos ched dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9650: dang po log rtog sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9652: dang po mdor bstan la gsum yod pa las ngo bo ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9653: de la drug yod pa las dang po ni //
NK078(tshu)001:9654: de ma yin pa la der 'dzin gyis log rtog
NK078(tshu)001:9655: snang dus ma grub pas sgyu ma de'i ngo bo
NK078(tshu)001:9656: ni / chos kyi bdag rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi phra 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9657: gang zag gi bdag phung po lnga'i rags 'dzin dang
NK078(tshu)001:9658: phyi nang gi snod bcud kyi dngos po rnams ngo
NK078(tshu)001:9659: bo med pa las ngo bo rang rgyud par yod
NK078(tshu)001:9661: bden pa la sogsa par rtog pas nan gyis sgro btags pas log pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9662: gnyis 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa bden pas stong
NK078(tshu)001:9663: pas na sgyu ma lta bu de goms pa'i klong
NK078(tshu)001:9664: 'ba' zhig tu gyur pas na log rtog ces bya
NK078(tshu)001:9665: / rgyu rkyen las skyes nas snang yang 'gyur nas
NK078(tshu)001:9666: mi bden cing bslu bas sgyu ma'i nges tshig 'grub
NK078(tshu)001:9667: / bo // gnyis pa rten 'brel gyi sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9669: kun rdzob rgyu rkyen la brten cing 'bras bu dang
NK078(tshu)001:9670: 'brel bar 'byung ba yang dpe shing rta'i 'phang lo
NK078(tshu)001:9672: de rang rgyud du ma grub ste 'jiga rten gyi
NK078(tshu)001:9673: rnam par rtog pa'i rten 'brel du snang ba des
NK078(tshu)001:9674: bslu bas gzugsa brnyan dang 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:9675: dper na sgyu ma'i rgyu rkyen la rta glang 'khor skye ba lta bu /
NK078(tshu)001:9676: las nyon gyi rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa las skyes shing /
NK078(tshu)001:9677: 'phral du bden pa ltar snang nas /
NK078(tshu)001:9678: sas brtan chus sdud pa la sogs pa'i bya ba kun don byed nus pa ltar snang yang /
NK078(tshu)001:9679: 'gro ba log rtog can rnams la rang rang dang mthun par snang bar zad kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:9680: don snang la rang bzhin med pas gzugs brnyan dang 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:9681: blo rig shes kyis brtag pas dngos po rang rgyud du grub pa med de dben pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9682: gtan tshig de'i phyir phyi nang gi chos thamsa cad
NK078(tshu)001:9683: mi bden te rdzun pa sgyu ma tsam yin te
NK078(tshu)001:9684: / kun rdzob tu ming tsam du snang ba las
NK078(tshu)001:9685: don dam par dngos po rang rgyud du med de
NK078(tshu)001:9686: / / de yang yang dag tu grub par bden pa 'doda pa min no //
NK078(tshu)001:9687: gsum pa yang dag sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9689: yang dag par bden pa nyid du gragsa so cog 'khor 'das sam /
NK078(tshu)001:9690: yul shes gnyis su snang ba'i dus nyid na phyogs gcig pa gang yang grub pa min pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9691: sems nyid rang snang phyir 'khor 'das kyi dngos po
NK078(tshu)001:9692: ji ltar snang yang rgyu rkyen med par rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:9693: rang 'char ba yin pas 'khor 'das la sogs tha
NK078(tshu)001:9694: dad par snang ba'i dus la ngo bo phyogs gcig
NK078(tshu)001:9695: pa gang yang nges pa med cing /
NK078(tshu)001:9696: med bzhin du rang gi blos phye bas ji ltar bltas pa ltar snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9697: snang bzhin du phyogs gcig par thera zug pa ma yin pas rtag mtha' dang bral la /
NK078(tshu)001:9698: snang cha ma 'gags pas chad pa'i mtha' dang bral ba'o /
NK078(tshu)001:9699: bzhi pa thabs sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9701: rgyal ba'i sku phyag rgyar snang ba yang rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed par /
NK078(tshu)001:9702: rang gi rig pa'i ya shes nyid lha'i sku phyag rgyar sgyu mar shar nas snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9703: khamsa gsum 'khor ba'i chos thams cad snang ba de yang /
NK078(tshu)001:9704: rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed par rig pa ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:9705: sgyu ma shar ba de bzhina du yina pa nges
NK078(tshu)001:9706: na chos thams cad rtsal 'gags pa med par thabs
NK078(tshu)001:9707: chen po rig pa ye shes sgyu ma nyid ni
NK078(tshu)001:9708: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun gyi ngo bo yin no
NK078(tshu)001:9709: // lnga pa ye shes sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9711: ye gdod ma nas chos kun ye shes sgyu mar
NK078(tshu)001:9712: gnas pa la ni rtog pa'i blo ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:9714: de ltar ye shes rol pa nyid kyang rang rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:9715: du ma grub pa gsog ste snying po med pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:9716: // 'o na snying po med pas 'gro ba'i don byed mi nus so zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:9718: drug pa phyag rgya sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9720: rgyal ba sprul pa'i sku 'gro drug gis mngon sum
NK078(tshu)001:9721: du byung zhing 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal skyob pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:9722: / sprul sku de dag 'byung ba'i phug po byin
NK078(tshu)001:9723: rlabsa kyis ston pa longs sku'i sangs rgyas thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:9724: / kyang / rang rgyud par ma grub pa'i dpe don gong du bshad pa de bzhin te /
NK078(tshu)001:9725: don chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:9726: gnyis pa sgyu ma gnyis med rang snang dgos ched dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9728: de rnams rgyu rkyen gzhan la rag lus med pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:9729: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor gnyis su med cing
NK078(tshu)001:9730: skye 'jig dang bral bas rdo rje de'i ngo bor
NK078(tshu)001:9731: 'gyur ba med pas btsan pa zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9732: 'dus byas las khyad par du gyur pas mchog kho na ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9734: rgyu nyid rdo rje rkyen dang bral //
NK078(tshu)001:9735: ma skyes pas na 'jig pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:9737: yin tshul ni don dam pa 'dus ma byas kyi
NK078(tshu)001:9738: sems nyid de kun rdzob tu 'dus byas 'di ltar
NK078(tshu)001:9739: du snang ba'i chos thams cad la shar nas snang
NK078(tshu)001:9740: / 'dus byas su shar nas snang ba'i dus na
NK078(tshu)001:9741: 'dus ma byas dang dbyer med pas rdo rje nyid
NK078(tshu)001:9742: yin pa'i phyir bden gnyis ngo bo gnyis su snang
NK078(tshu)001:9743: ba'i dus na tha dad med de dbyer med do
NK078(tshu)001:9744: / // 'o na snang stong res mos su bsgom pa ci yin zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:9745: gdul bya blo dman par snang ba la snang stong
NK078(tshu)001:9746: bden gnyis res mos su gomsa par byed pa'i thabs
NK078(tshu)001:9747: tsam du bstan par zad kyis don shes bya rang
NK078(tshu)001:9748: bzhin dbyer med pa la bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9749: de ltar bsgom bya don gyi ngo bo dang rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa 'di la /
NK078(tshu)001:9750: sgyu ma'i dngos po drug don la bden pa dbyer med du ston pa la bdun te /
NK078(tshu)001:9751: dang po sgyu ma'i dngos po drug ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9752: gsang bdag sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:9755: yang dag gam rig pa sgyu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9759: de dag la nye ston chos kyi seng ge na re /
NK078(tshu)001:9761: bdag gzhan dgra gnyen du snang ba'i log rtog mi bden cing bslu bas sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9762: gnyis pa rten 'brel sgyu ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9763: snang ba 'di dag rgyu rkyen rten 'brel las byung ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9765: don byed nus mthun par snang /
NK078(tshu)001:9766: yang dag par stong snang bas na rten 'brel sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9767: gsum pa yang dag gam rig pa sgyu ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9768: 'di ltar snang ba 'di dag thams cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:9769: rang rig ye shes kyi snang ba yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:9770: snang tsam na ngo bo grub pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:9771: ther zug rtag chad kyi mtha' las grol bas sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9772: bzhi pa phyag rgya sgyu ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9773: rgyal ba'i sku phyag rgya chen por ma 'gags par gsal la /
NK078(tshu)001:9774: lha rang rgyud par ma grub pas sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9775: lnga pa thabs sgyu ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9776: snang ba 'di 'gag med sna tshogs su shar bas thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:9777: de la rang rgyud pa med pas sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9778: drug pa ye shes sgyu ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9779: thams cad rang rig pa'i ye shes sgyu ma'i snang ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:9780: rang rig tu snang tsam rang rgyud du med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9781: bdun pa don la bden pa dbyer med ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9782: sgyu ma'i rnam grangs ci snyed brjod kyang don la bden pa gnyis su med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9783: de dag chos can tshar non lta bu gcig la sbyar na /
NK078(tshu)001:9784: tshar non gyi dbyibs kha dog tu snang ba log rtog /rang rgyud pa med pa sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9785: 'di ka rgyu rkyen rten 'brel las byung zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:9786: rang rgyud pa med pas rten 'brel sgyu ma /
NK078(tshu)001:9787: de ka sems nyid kyi snang ba yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9788: ngo bo med bzhin du snang ba ste ther zug
NK078(tshu)001:9789: rtag chad kyi mtha' las grol bas yang dag gam
NK078(tshu)001:9791: 'di ka bskyed rim lha sku bsgom pa rnams la
NK078(tshu)001:9792: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po snang zhing snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:9793: rang rgyud pa med pas phyag rgya sgyu ma /
NK078(tshu)001:9794: rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid dbyibs kha dog tu ma 'gag par shar bas thabs sgyu ma /
NK078(tshu)001:9795: 'di ka rang rig ye shes sgyu ma cis kyang mi sgrib par gsal ba las ma g.yos shing /
NK078(tshu)001:9796: rang rgyud pa med pas ye shes sgyu ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9797: 'di la bka' sde zur pa tsho byin gyi po'i bzhed kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:9798: bsgom bya don gyi ngo bo sgyu ma'i dngos po drug tu bzhed do //
NK078(tshu)001:9799: de ltar sgyur ma drug po spyir kun bsgom mam /
NK078(tshu)001:9800: bye brag gcig bsgom zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:9802: de yang gnyis med phyag rgya dngos //
NK078(tshu)001:9803: phyag rgya shes mod dus min phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:9804: mi bsgom gcig shos rang rig la //
NK078(tshu)001:9806: 'dir phyi nang yul sems kyi dngos po rnams snang
NK078(tshu)001:9807: la rang bzhin med pa ye shes sgyu ma'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:9808: du bsgom mo // chos kyi spyan ldan gsang bdag sgro phug pa'i gsung gis /
NK078(tshu)001:9810: sgyu ma'i rnam grangs la dbye ba yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:9812: ye shes sgyu ma kho na gsungs pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9813: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dgongs pa kho na dang mjal ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:9814: nye ston chos kyi seng+ge na re /
NK078(tshu)001:9815: kun snang gi skabs 'dir phyag rgya sgyu ma bsgom mam mi bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:9816: bsgom na phyag rgya gcig pa dang khyad med cing /
NK078(tshu)001:9817: mi bsgom na phyag rgya sgyu ma bshad pa la
NK078(tshu)001:9818: dgos pa med do ce na 'dir phyag rgya sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:9819: ma bsgoms la / ma kir phyag rgya dbyer med du bsgoms pas khyad yod do zhes gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:9820: bla ma rtsang pa na re /
NK078(tshu)001:9821: log rtog sgyu ma bsgom mam mi bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:9822: bsgom na khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad grol zhing thar bar 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:9823: log rtog sgyu mar bsgom gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:9824: yang lce ston gyi 'grel bar snga ma gsum goms pas 'khor ba'i bden 'dzin 'jig la /
NK078(tshu)001:9825: phyi ma gsum bsgoms pas mya ngan las 'das pa'i bden 'dzin 'jig par 'dod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9826: rtsom pa po'i thugs dgongs yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:9827: 'khor ba ngan zhen gcod pa'i sgyu ma gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:9828: 'das pa'i bzang zhen gsum bcad pa'i sgyu lus gsum yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:9829: zhes dkyus la gsal bas rim par 'dzin no //
NK078(tshu)001:9830: gnyis pa sgom gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ni /
NK078(tshu)001:9832: 'gro ba sems can la shes pa'i semsa rgyud skad cig ma gcig la /
NK078(tshu)001:9833: nyon mongs pa dang ye shes gnyis dus gcig tu mi ldan te /
NK078(tshu)001:9834: de ltar shes pa'i rgyud gciga po nyid don dam
NK078(tshu)001:9835: par ma skyes la kun rdzob sgyu mar cir yang
NK078(tshu)001:9837: de gnyis dbyer med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:9838: gzung ba'i yul dang 'dzin pa'i sems gnyis dang bral ba'i rang rig pa nyid /
NK078(tshu)001:9839: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor mi g.yo bas zhi gnas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9840: thams cad gsal bas lhag mthong yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:9841: dpe chu dngas pa'i nang du zla ba'i gzugs brnyan snang ba ci bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:9842: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong tha mi dad de mtshungsa
NK078(tshu)001:9843: par gasla ba ye shes sgyu mar bsgom pa'i ting
NK078(tshu)001:9844: nge 'dzin gyi nga bar brjod do /
NK078(tshu)001:9847: rang gi semsa nyid las ma gtogsa pa'i 'khor 'das kyi chos gzhan med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:9848: bsgom bya ye shes sgyu ma yang sems las gzhan na med de //
NK078(tshu)001:9849: ye shes sgyu mar snang ba'i sems nyid kyang sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:9850: ma tsam du'ang chagsa zhen dang bral bar gnas pa
NK078(tshu)001:9851: de la tha snyad kyi tshig tsam du bsgom zhes
NK078(tshu)001:9853: lnga pa mi mthun pa'i skyon la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9855: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9857: kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin dang mi mthun pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:9858: sgrib pa'i skyon gyis dmigsa bzung ba ni gsum ste
NK078(tshu)001:9859: gang zhe na / skyon bskyed par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9860: skyon rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9861: skyon dbang du song ba'i nyes pa bstan pa dang gsum zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9862: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9864: dang po skyon gyi rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9866: sngar snying rje sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin la ma gomas pas g.yo thob kyi dus kyi skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9867: mi dgos bzhin du brtson 'grus ched du byed pa goms brtan gyi skyon 'byung bar byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:9868: dper na rgyu me yod pa dang 'bras bu du
NK078(tshu)001:9869: ba shugs las 'byung bar 'gyur ba'i tshul bzhina du
NK078(tshu)001:9870: / rgyu bdag tu 'dzin pa bsgom bya sgom byed dam /
NK078(tshu)001:9871: gang zag dang chos kyi bdag rnam pa gnyis kyis
NK078(tshu)001:9872: 'bras bu sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin gsal du mi
NK078(tshu)001:9873: ster ba'i sgribsa pa'i skyon rnams rgyud la /
NK078(tshu)001:9875: gnyis pa ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9876: ting nge 'dzin la gnas dus kyi skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9880: dang po spyi'i skyon 'bring dang nyung bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9882: snying rje ye shes sgyu ma'i sngon du de ting
NK078(tshu)001:9883: stong pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin ji bzhin pa
NK078(tshu)001:9884: nyid la brtan pa thob mod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:9885: rgyu de ting dang 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig spros
NK078(tshu)001:9886: gnyis kyi mtshams sbyor ba'i snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs
NK078(tshu)001:9887: 'dir skyon g.yunga ba tsam ma gtogs pa mi 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:9888: ba min pas / 'on kyang de ting skabs su brjod pa'i skyon gyis bye brag kun /
NK078(tshu)001:9889: de ting las 'dir ngo bo 'bring po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9890: grangs bag tsam gyis nyung bar 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:9892: tha mal ba'i rtog pa rags pa dang mang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:9893: skyon gyis rkyen rnams spang ba'i 'du byed brgyad kyis
NK078(tshu)001:9894: spangs shing / de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la sngar gamas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9895: tha mala gyi rkyen rags pa sngar bas dkon no //
NK078(tshu)001:9896: gnyis pa khyad par gyi skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:9898: 'on kyang snying rje chen po 'di nyid rang bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:9899: pa'i dus su rgod pa'i skyon sems yul la 'phro
NK078(tshu)001:9900: ba dang / bying bas nang du sdud pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9901: yul ma nges pa'i sa phyogs su makhara khyim dang
NK078(tshu)001:9902: bcas pa mthong nas sems de phyogs su shor ba
NK078(tshu)001:9903: dang / sa chu me rlung la sogs zad par
NK078(tshu)001:9904: gyi skye mched mthong nas de'i rjes su sems 'brang
NK078(tshu)001:9905: dang / ba dang / kha dog gcig tu ma nges pa'i mdoga sna tshogs mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9906: gnyis pa khams kyi skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:9910: sa bad kan te 'byung ba bzhi'i khams kyi cha 'khrul bas /
NK078(tshu)001:9911: ting nge 'dzin don mi gsal ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:9913: mkhris pa ljang gu'am ser po /
NK078(tshu)001:9916: bad kan smug po la sogs pa'i nad khams kyi kha dog mthong nas /
NK078(tshu)001:9918: rtog pa'i skyon rnams gang yin pa blta bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9923: nyams rtags dang khams 'khrug pa de dag gang yin gyi cha dbye bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9924: gsum pa skyon gyi nyes pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9926: dper na nam mkha' dwangs pa la sprin gyi nyi ma sgrib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9927: ling tog gis mig sgrib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9928: mun pas rdzas mi gsal bar sgrib pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:9929: skyon gyi rnam pa gang yin pa de dag rgyud gzhung las gragsa pa'i thun mong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9930: khyad par skyon gyi bye brag phra ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9931: rigsa pa'i cha yis ye shes sgyu ma'i dana blo la mi gasla ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9932: nyams skye ba shin tu bul bar byed pa'i skyon yod do //
NK078(tshu)001:9933: drug pa skyon bcos thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9935: dang po nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9937: sngon de ting gi skabs su bstan pa bzhin du
NK078(tshu)001:9938: rnam par rtog pa'i nad kyi skyon bcos pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:9939: 'di lta ste / gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:9940: ting nge 'dzin la gnas dus kyi skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9941: khams kyi skyon bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:9943: nyams sam blo dang sbyar te bcos pa'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9948: dang po blo rab la rang byung rang shar du grol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9950: sngon du rang gi shes bzhin gyi bya rabs rtog
NK078(tshu)001:9951: skyon so 'thas chod de skyon ngos zin par bya
NK078(tshu)001:9952: ste / de ltar skyon ngos zin par gyur na
NK078(tshu)001:9953: rkun po byung bar tshor na bros pa' tshul bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:9954: ste / du / skyon ched du ma bsal kyang
NK078(tshu)001:9955: skyon rang bazhana chos nyid ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang
NK078(tshu)001:9957: de'i ci'i phyir zhe na rnam rtog gi skyon gyi
NK078(tshu)001:9958: mtshan ma bzang ngan dang phra rags ci dang ca
NK078(tshu)001:9959: skyes kyang / sems nyid ye shes sgyu ma nyid du rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:9960: don chos nyid dam ting nge 'dzin gyi bde ba
NK078(tshu)001:9961: la chagsa shing rtog pa'i skyon la zhe sdang ba
NK078(tshu)001:9962: dang / drod rtags 'byung du re ba dang gol du dogas pa'i blo mi 'byung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:9964: skyon gyi bye brag thams cad kyang ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:9965: ma nyid rang snang ba las gzhan du grub pa
NK078(tshu)001:9966: min pa'i phyir rang byung rang zhi'o //
NK078(tshu)001:9967: gnyis pa 'bring la rtog pa'i gnas yul blta ste
NK078(tshu)001:9968: snying rje skye nas stong pa dang zung 'jug tu
NK078(tshu)001:9970: yang na blo 'bring gi rtog pa gang nas skye ba'i gnas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9971: yul gang las byung ba bltas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:9972: rtog pa de gzhan med do //
NK078(tshu)001:9973: rang gi sems nyid ye shes sgyu mar mthong bas
NK078(tshu)001:9974: sgrib pa'i mun pa ma spangs la rnam par dag
NK078(tshu)001:9975: pa'i tshul gyis sangsa par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:9976: gsum pa tha ma 'khrul ba'i lo rgyus byas te
NK078(tshu)001:9977: snying rje bskyed nas stong pa dang zung 'jug tu
NK078(tshu)001:9980: gong gi skyon bcos thabs gnyis po de ltar gyi
NK078(tshu)001:9981: don dang ma ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa blo chung
NK078(tshu)001:9983: rtog pa'i skyen skye ba tshor nas rtog pa de dag lo rgyus de nyid de /
NK078(tshu)001:9984: dang po rgyu gang las byung bar du ngo bo
NK078(tshu)001:9985: gang yin la sogs shes rab kyis dpyad pas skyon
NK078(tshu)001:9986: de nyid stong nyid snying rjer shar nas skyon zhi
NK078(tshu)001:9987: bar 'gyur ro // gnyis pa rgod pa'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:9989: sngon de ting bzhin sngar 'das kyi dran pa'i rjes
NK078(tshu)001:9990: su 'brang ba dang phyis ma 'ongs pa yid la
NK078(tshu)001:9992: de ltar rang bzhin gyi yul gyi rkyen gyis dgyes
NK078(tshu)001:9993: shing rgod par tshor na 'khor ba'i thog mtha'i nyes
NK078(tshu)001:9995: 'khor ba la skyo ba bskyed la snying rje bskyed
NK078(tshu)001:9996: nas rgod pa'i skyon rnams dor te ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:9997: la dran pa'i thag pas bcing ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:9998: gsum pa bying ba'i skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:10000: gang zhig bsgom pa'i tshe na sems nang du thim
NK078(tshu)001:10001: pas ste bying rmug tu song na khrus bya bskor
NK078(tshu)001:10002: ba bya zhing lus bcag zhabs kyis bcag zhes 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:10004: drod rtags la brod pas dad pa bskyed nas ting
NK078(tshu)001:10005: nge 'dzin la 'jug cing sems gzings bstod par bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:10006: // gnyis pa khams kyi skyon bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:10008: rang nyid kyi 'dod pa mina pa'i kha dog lnga
NK078(tshu)001:10009: la sogs pa ma nges shing mi gsal ba mthong
NK078(tshu)001:10010: ba na / 'byung ba rlung mkhris bad kan 'du ba dang bzhi'i gnyen pos te /
NK078(tshu)001:10011: zas dang sman gyis bcos la gzhila bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10012: bdun pa nyams la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10016: gong du bstan pa de ltar blo bzhag thabs kyis
NK078(tshu)001:10017: bzhag /skyon bcos thabs kyis de ltar bcos shing brtson
NK078(tshu)001:10018: 'grus kyi bsgom par 'gyur ba'i skabsa su ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:10020: nyams gong nas gong du 'phel ba'ang lnga ste gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:10025: mthar phyin pa'i nyams kyis 'og nas gong du 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:10026: ba bsgom bya'i don gyi ngo bo ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:10027: ma la tha dad med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:10028: sgom byed kyi blo'i sgrib par rab rib dag ma
NK078(tshu)001:10029: dag go tshab che chung gi chas nyams rim pa
NK078(tshu)001:10030: lngar brjod do // gnyis pa rgyas pa de la lnga te /
NK078(tshu)001:10032: dang po g.yo ba'i nyams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10034: ting nge 'dzin la blo rtse gcig tu mi sdod
NK078(tshu)001:10035: par 'pho zhing yul la so sor dgyes pa'i rgod
NK078(tshu)001:10036: pa dang / nang du thim pas bying pa'i skyon
NK078(tshu)001:10037: rnams dper na rlung drag pos ded pa'i chu'i gnyer
NK078(tshu)001:10038: ma dang 'dra bar don la blo gnas pa de
NK078(tshu)001:10039: pa dang / / ting nge 'dzin dang rtog pa 'dres mar cung zad yod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10040: nyin zhag gcig la thun drug cu rtsa bzhir phye
NK078(tshu)001:10041: ba'i thun gyi tshad gcig gi sum gnyis rtog pa
NK078(tshu)001:10042: nyi tshe ba rgyu ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10043: sum char rtog pa dang chos nyid 'dres mar yod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10044: gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10046: nyin zhag gcig la thun so gnyis su bgos pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10047: thun gcig gi bzhi cha'am lnga char rtogs pa de
NK078(tshu)001:10048: med cing chos nyid 'ba' zhig rgyu la /
NK078(tshu)001:10049: bzhi gsum mam lnga bzhi ni rtog pa dang chos
NK078(tshu)001:10050: nyid 'dres mar rgyu bas na thob pa'i nyams so
NK078(tshu)001:10051: // 'o na thob pa'i nyams kyi skabs su g.yo ba'i nyams las zhen du song ngam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:10052: zhen du song ba ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:10053: g.yo ba'i skabs su sum gnyis rtog pa nyi tshe dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10054: sum cha la yang rtog pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10056: thob pa'i skabs 'dir thun yang nyis 'gyur gyis che zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:10057: bzhi cha'am lnga char chos nyid 'ba' zhig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10058: de las gzhan du ste bzhi gsum mam lnga cha'i bzhi ni rtog pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10059: chos nyid 'dres mar rgyu bas dpags so //
NK078(tshu)001:10060: yang na 'dir bzhi gsum mam lnga bzhi'i char rtog med kyi ting nge 'dzin 'byung la /
NK078(tshu)001:10061: bzhi cha lnga cha la rtog pa'i dbang du 'gro ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10062: gsum pa goms pa'i nyams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10064: nyin zhag gcig la bcu drug tu bgos pa'i cha
NK078(tshu)001:10065: gcig la thun rer byas pa'i thun rkyang tsam du
NK078(tshu)001:10066: rtog pa med par bsgom nus shing chos nyid gsal
NK078(tshu)001:10068: rtog pa'i dbang du cung zad tsam 'gro ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10069: dper na chu klung dal bar 'bab pa'i yul ba
NK078(tshu)001:10070: 'gying po'i chu dang 'dra bar 'gro yang 'gro bar
NK078(tshu)001:10071: mi mngon pa'i tshul bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:10072: sems la lhod dam dal ba cung zad rnyed pas
NK078(tshu)001:10073: rtog pa'i rkun bu'i dbang du cung zad tsam 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:10074: yang 'gro bar mi mngon pa ste mi tshor ba
NK078(tshu)001:10075: bzhin no // bzhi pa brten pa'i nyams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10077: sga brten pa'i rdzas rgyang 'dan bcug na rlung gis mi bsgul ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:10078: zhag gcig la brgyad du bgos pa'i thun rer /
NK078(tshu)001:10079: rnam par rtog pa'i rlung gisa ting nge 'dzin mi
NK078(tshu)001:10080: bsgul bar rtse gcig tu gzhi rig pa sgyu ma
NK078(tshu)001:10082: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams so //
NK078(tshu)001:10085: mig gis gzugs la blta ba ltar dbang pos mngon
NK078(tshu)001:10086: sum du phyi nang gi snang ba gang snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:10087: thams cad snang la rang bzhin med pa rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:10088: rang gsal bar byas pa'i don ye shes sgyu ma
NK078(tshu)001:10089: la skyed 'don zhing bog dbyung du bya ba med
NK078(tshu)001:10090: pa'i phyir / nyams lnga'i mtha' ma mthar phyin pa'i nyams zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10091: brgyad pa spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10092: sngon byung rgyal ba'i mdzad spyod spyod pa'i gzhir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10093: rjes 'jug gi lam pa rnal 'byor pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10096: dang po lam zung 'jug tu bsgoms pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs par shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10098: snying rje chen po ye shes sgyu ma bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK078(tshu)001:10099: srid gsum 'khor ba'i chos thams cad don dam byang chub sems sam /
NK078(tshu)001:10100: ye shes sgyu ma dang 'dra bar ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10101: yang dag par rdzogsa pa'i sangs rgyas bla na med
NK078(tshu)001:10102: pa'i byang chub thob zin pas shes bya thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:10103: mkhyen pa la mkhas pas shes pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:10104: de ltar shes par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:10105: kun rdzob byang chub sems kyis 'gro ba sems can
NK078(tshu)001:10106: rnams 'khor ba las bsgral ba'i ched du gzhan don
NK078(tshu)001:10108: srid pa gsum gyi 'gro ba sems can rnams ye
NK078(tshu)001:10109: shes sgyu ma dang 'dra bar de ltar snga ma
NK078(tshu)001:10111: gnyis pa 'bras bu thams cad mkhyen pas gdul bya la gzigs pa ltar shes pa gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10113: dus thams cad du 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang rig pa kho na yin pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:10114: gzung 'dzin gnyis su 'dzin pa med pa la gnyis su 'dzin pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10115: de ma yin la der 'dzin pas log par rtog pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10116: de ltar gnyis med kyi ye shes rang ngo ma
NK078(tshu)001:10117: shes pas lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:10118: / de goms pa'i rgyun gyis gzung 'dzin de nyid
NK078(tshu)001:10119: du snang ba ni kun tu brtag pa'i ma rig
NK078(tshu)001:10120: / pa ste / gshis la ma grub bas glo bur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10121: gang gnyis su snang ba dang zhen pa de las
NK078(tshu)001:10122: log pa ni rnam par dag cing rgyud dag pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10124: de ltar log rtog dag pa'i phyir 'gro ba drug
NK078(tshu)001:10125: po ril rang rig pa'i ye shes mnyam pa'i dbyings
NK078(tshu)001:10126: las mi gzhan par gsal bas 'gro ba thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:10127: ye shes des zin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10128: chos kyi dbyings des khyab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10129: rgyal ba dngos kyi don gnyis su mi rtog pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10130: phyir gtan tshig gsum po des grub pa'i phyir zhes
NK078(tshu)001:10131: bya ste / de nyid gsang sngags ma h+aa yo
NK078(tshu)001:10132: ga'i lugs kyis yul yul can gnyis su med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10133: phyir thugs rje chen po sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:10134: bya ste / dang / sems can gyi sems kyi chos nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10135: 'khor 'das thams cad ngo bo bdag nyid gcig par 'brel basa na /
NK078(tshu)001:10137: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med rtogs na /
NK078(tshu)001:10138: thugs rje chen po'i skyes zhes de la bya /
NK078(tshu)001:10140: gnyis su med pa'i phyir 'gro ba rigs drug gi snang ba rang rgyud du ma grub pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:10141: ma grub pa ltar mkhyen pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10142: ci lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:10143: gshis de ltar yin kyang gdul bya'i 'khrul ngor dus
NK078(tshu)001:10144: snga phyi dang gnas mtho dman la sogs par snang
NK078(tshu)001:10145: ba kun / lhag ma ma lus par /
NK078(tshu)001:10146: rgyal ba'i ye shes rtog pa med par gsal bar mkhyen pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10147: ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes kho na'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10148: mdor na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med par mkhyen pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10149: dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye shes zhes bya bar tha snyad du 'dog go //
NK078(tshu)001:10151: shes rab chen pos skad cig la //
NK078(tshu)001:10152: chos kun khong du chud pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10154: rgyal ba de'i rjes su 'jug pa'i snying rje chen
NK078(tshu)001:10155: po rnal 'byor pas spyod pa'nga gang du bstan pa
NK078(tshu)001:10156: de bazhana du shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10157: gnyis pa rjes 'jug gi rnal 'byor pa'i spyod pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10162: dang po ye shes sgyu mar shes pa dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10164: don dam chos nyid de bzhin nyid skye ba med
NK078(tshu)001:10165: pa'i dbyings nyid kun rdzob tu chos kyi bye brag
NK078(tshu)001:10166: rnam pa sna tshogs pa manga po'i rnam grangs su
NK078(tshu)001:10168: snang ba'i thabs su snang zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10169: thabsa ma 'gag par snang ba de nyid snang la
NK078(tshu)001:10170: ma 'gag pas sgyu ma snang la ngo bo med
NK078(tshu)001:10171: pas miga yor / snang la bzung du med pas
NK078(tshu)001:10172: chu zla gsal la stong pas gzugas brnyan bzhina du
NK078(tshu)001:10173: thabs sna tshogs su snang ba de nyid rang gi
NK078(tshu)001:10174: rig pa ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor snang bas
NK078(tshu)001:10175: gang la yang chagsa pa med cing sna tshogs kun
NK078(tshu)001:10177: gnyis pa de la gnas pa'i phan yon no //
NK078(tshu)001:10179: de ltar sgyu mar snang ba'i thabsa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10180: rang rgyud du mi 'dzin pa'i shes rab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10181: de gnyis dbyer med du rtogs pa'i gdeng dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:10182: para theg pa mchog gi ting nge 'dzin la gnas
NK078(tshu)001:10183: pa'i rnal 'byor pas gzhan don gyi spyod pa ji
NK078(tshu)001:10184: ltar spyad kyang bag chags su mi 'gyur la /
NK078(tshu)001:10185: yon tan zad pa med cing bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis kyi tshogs gnyis 'grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10186: lam la sgrib par mi 'gyur zhes pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10187: don la sgrib par mi 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:10188: rang rgyud par mi 'dzin pa'i shes rab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10189: ma 'gag pas thabsa chen de gnyis su med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10190: mchog rtogs pa'i ngang la ye nas gnas pa bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:10191: du 'dzin med du spyod pas rol ba yin zhes
NK078(tshu)001:10192: smos pa'o // gnyis pa spyod tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10193: gzhan don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10196: tshad med bzhis gzhan don byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10197: gong bzhin rkyen dang 'phrad na phrin las la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:10198: byed cing bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:10199: / don byed bya'i yul la sogs pa 'og ma las khyad par dpags tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:10202: dang po chos kun byang chub sems su gcig pa'i rtsal snying rje kun la khyab tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10204: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang du byang chub sems su
NK078(tshu)001:10205: sangs rgyas dang sems can ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu
NK078(tshu)001:10206: gcig pa yin pas na tshad med pa bzhi'i rtsa
NK078(tshu)001:10207: ba gnyis su med pa'i snying rje chen po las
NK078(tshu)001:10208: 'byung ba'o // 'o na gnyis med yin na /
NK078(tshu)001:10209: de la snying rje'i nges tshig med do snyam pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:10210: sangsa rgyas dang semsa can gnyis su med par ye shes sgyu mar gcig tu rtogs na /
NK078(tshu)001:10211: gnyis med du rtogs pa'i snying rje chen po skye zhes de la bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10212: thams cad la khyab brda' chen por rtogs pa'i blo ni phyogs gcig tu thug pa med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:10213: chos kun tu shar bas na snang zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10214: gnyis pa snying rjes phan 'dogs shing skyob pa'i byams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10216: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i thabs chen kun gyi gdul bya'i
NK078(tshu)001:10217: don mdzad pa de'i ngo bo ni ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:10218: ma yin la / de la sgrib pa med pas
NK078(tshu)001:10219: 'oda gsal ba gdul bya 'dul byed gnyis su mi
NK078(tshu)001:10220: phyed pas byams pa tshad med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10221: de ltar byams pa thabs chen po des gdul bya
NK078(tshu)001:10222: thams cad dgyes par mdzad pa de nyid 'byung khungs
NK078(tshu)001:10223: su gyur pas dbyingsa snying rje chen po ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:10224: sgyu ma ste de bsgom pa'i dus su mas bu
NK078(tshu)001:10225: la gdung ba dang 'dra bar 'gro drug gi semsa
NK078(tshu)001:10226: can lhag ma ma lus pa thamsa cad la /
NK078(tshu)001:10227: byams pa dang snying rje chen po'i thag pas dus
NK078(tshu)001:10228: rgyun du ma chad par nyon mongsa pas bcing pa
NK078(tshu)001:10229: 'khor ba'i lam las byams pas grol bar byed cing
NK078(tshu)001:10230: / gdul bya dang 'dul byed mi 'byed pas phan
NK078(tshu)001:10231: 'dog pas byamsa pa tshad med pa dag gis gdul
NK078(tshu)001:10232: bya mnyen par gyisa shig /gsum pa 'gro ba'i don
NK078(tshu)001:10233: la mi skyo zhing dga' bas dga' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10235: byams pa'i don snying rje las 'byung de bzhin du
NK078(tshu)001:10236: 'khor ba las thar dka' ba'i brtson ra dang 'dra
NK078(tshu)001:10237: bar chud pa'i sems can la /
NK078(tshu)001:10238: snying rje chen po zhagsa pa dang 'dra ba cher brkyangsa nas /
NK078(tshu)001:10239: 'khor ba nyon mongsa pa 'dam pa 'dra ba'i nang
NK078(tshu)001:10240: nas thar pa'i skam sar 'dren para byed pa la
NK078(tshu)001:10241: / snying rje chen po ye shes sgyu ma'i sgo
NK078(tshu)001:10242: nas 'gro don 'byung ba la skyo bar ma byed
NK078(tshu)001:10243: cig /snying rjes 'gro don la mi skyo ba de
NK078(tshu)001:10244: bzhin du don bya ba'i yul skye bo phala mo
NK078(tshu)001:10245: / che rnams la / las ngan gyi sgrib pas
NK078(tshu)001:10246: rang rgyud la mi gos shing skye bo sems can
NK078(tshu)001:10247: thams cad ye shes sgyu mar rtogs te mngon par
NK078(tshu)001:10248: rdzogs par sangsa rgyas par gyur nas dga' ba tshad
NK078(tshu)001:10249: med pa dag la 'gyod pa ma byed cig /bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:10250: pa phyogs ris med par snyams pa'i btang snyoms so
NK078(tshu)001:10252: khams gsum gyii semsa can thams cad la gang zag
NK078(tshu)001:10253: gi bdag dang chos kyi bdag gnyis rang bzhin med
NK078(tshu)001:10254: pa la gnyis med du rtogs pa'i thugsa rje chen
NK078(tshu)001:10255: pos bdag gzhan nam nye ring gnyis su rtog pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10257: sems can thams cad la bu gcig la mas byams
NK078(tshu)001:10258: pa dang 'dra bar byams snying rje'i blo nye bar
NK078(tshu)001:10260: de yang dus thamsa cad du sems can la phyogs
NK078(tshu)001:10261: ris kyi dri ma med par btang snyoms par bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:10262: // gnyis pa gong bzhin rkyen dang 'phrad pa na
NK078(tshu)001:10263: phrin las la sogs byed cing bdag don la gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:10266: stong chen sngon du rdzogsa pa'i don bya ba'i rkyen
NK078(tshu)001:10267: gdul bya dang 'phrad na gzhan don gyi spyod pa
NK078(tshu)001:10268: byed pa sngon de ting gis skabs bzhin du gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:10270: de'ang snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor bsgom pas bdag
NK078(tshu)001:10271: don nyid las gdul bya'i don du sems bskyed pa
NK078(tshu)001:10272: song bas na gzhan gyi don shugs kyis rdzogsa par
NK078(tshu)001:10273: byed pa'o // gsum pa don bya ba'i yul la
NK078(tshu)001:10274: sogs pa 'og ma las khyad par du dpag tshul
NK078(tshu)001:10276: de yang rgyu'i theg pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:10277: 'bras bu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhi'i khyad par ston pa 'di la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10278: dmigs pa yul gyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10279: ngo bo'i khyad par dang byed las kyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10280: phan yon gyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10281: phyogs gtad yod med kyi khyad par ro //
NK078(tshu)001:10282: dang po dmigs pa yul gyi khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10283: tshad med bzhi'i don bya ba'i dmigsa pa'i yul du gyur pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10284: rgyu yi theg pa yi gong du bshad pa yi /
NK078(tshu)001:10285: de phyir rgyu rkyen 'bras bu dang dus dang rang bzhin 'khrul pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10286: tshul gyis nyes dang ngo bo dang //
NK078(tshu)001:10287: btson ra lta bu brgyad la dmigs //
NK078(tshu)001:10289: 'khor ba'i rgyu rkyen gnyis gcig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10290: ngo bo 'bras bu gnyis gcig ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10291: de ltar bdun la dmigs nas thugs rje skye ba'i yul rgya chung la /
NK078(tshu)001:10292: 'bras bu'i theg pas bdun po de'i steng du nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:10293: phyi rgyud sde gsum po dang bdun po de bsnan
NK078(tshu)001:10294: pas bdun gnyis bcu bzhi'i gdul bya la dmigs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10295: yul rgya che bas khyad par 'phags te /
NK078(tshu)001:10296: rje 'bangs gnyis nor 'dren pa lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10297: yang lce ston gyis 'gro ba ris drug mu stegs rtag chad gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:10299: phyi rgyud sde gsum ste bdun bdun bcu bzhi la dmigs nas skye bar 'thad gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:10300: gnyis pa ngo bo'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10301: theg pa 'og ma'i thugs rje skye bya dang skyed
NK078(tshu)001:10302: byed kyi cha nas tshad med bzhi ngo bo tha
NK078(tshu)001:10304: 'bras bu'i theg pas yul bral gnyis med kyi snying
NK078(tshu)001:10305: rje ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang du tshad med bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:10306: lhun gyis grub pas dpag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10307: gsum pa byed las kyi khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10308: rgyu'i theg pas snying rje rtsol bcas kyi sgo nas 'gro don byed la /
NK078(tshu)001:10309: ma h+aa'i snying rje chen pos bdag gzhan gnyis med kyi sgo nas 'gro don byed pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10310: yang na rgyu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhi ni phyogs re'i don byed las mi nus la /
NK078(tshu)001:10311: 'dir 'bras bu'i theg pa'i snying rje ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:10312: ma gcig pu la tshad med bzhi tshang ba'i sgo
NK078(tshu)001:10313: nas don byed nus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10314: bzhi pa phan yon gyi khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10315: rgyu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhis rang gzhan gyi don byas pa'i 'bras bu la /
NK078(tshu)001:10316: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa'i sku gsum 'grub la /
NK078(tshu)001:10317: 'bras bu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhis don byas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10318: 'bras bu pad+ma spyan la sogs pa'i sku lnga 'grub
NK078(tshu)001:10319: pas yon tan gyis dpags pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10320: lnga pa phyogs gtad yod med kyi khyad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10321: rgyu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhis rang man chad kyi
NK078(tshu)001:10322: gdul bya la mngon par gdul ba'i phyogs gtad yod
NK078(tshu)001:10323: pa yin la / 'dir ma h+aa'i ni yul bral
NK078(tshu)001:10324: gnyis med kyi tshad med bzhis gdul bya la phyogs
NK078(tshu)001:10325: dang ris med de kun tu don byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10326: khyad lnga po de'i phyir thun mong gi rgyu'i theg pa chena po dag gi tshad med bzhi las /
NK078(tshu)001:10327: sngags kyi theg pa ma h+aa yo ga'i tshad med
NK078(tshu)001:10328: chen po bzhi ni kun gyi blar gyur pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:10329: no // gnyis pa bdag don la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10331: dang po spyod lam thams cad du ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10333: snying rje ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor pa bdag
NK078(tshu)001:10334: nyid kyi don bya ba'i phyir 'di ltar du phyi
NK078(tshu)001:10335: nang gi spyod yul gyi snang ba thamsa cad kun
NK078(tshu)001:10336: ye shes sgyu mar rang snang bar rtogs pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:10338: nang sems gnyis su 'dzin pa'i sgrib pa med par ye shes su gsal ba'i nganga du shes pas /
NK078(tshu)001:10339: ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin la blo brtan pa'i spyod pas shin tu bde ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10340: gnyis pa 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa la spyod par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10342: 'dod pa'i longsa spyod gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga dang ldana pa thamsa cad la /
NK078(tshu)001:10343: gsang sngags phyi pa ltar dkar gsum mngar gsum la sogs pa gtsang ba'am bzang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10344: dam rdzas lnga la sogs pa mi gtsang zhing sme ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10345: ngan pa'i blo gnyis su ma 'dzin te 'dzin pa med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10347: longs spyod thams cad rang rig pa'i ye shes sgyu mar ro gcig cing tha dad med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:10348: gang la'ang bzang ngan dang gtsang sme gnyis su 'dzin pa med pas shin tu bde ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10349: rgyu mtshan de bas na spyad par bya ba ta na ga na dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10350: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10353: mi spang pa nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10354: dang du len pa dam rdzas lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10355: 'doda pa'i yon tan gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya
NK078(tshu)001:10356: lnga la sogsa pa 'khor ba'i chos nyi shu po
NK078(tshu)001:10357: thams cad ye shes la ye shes sgyu mar rol
NK078(tshu)001:10358: bar spyod do // dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10360: dang po sngon byung rgyal ba'i mdzad spyod dngos bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10362: 'khor ba'i g.yul dang bdud kyi dpung bcom pas thub
NK078(tshu)001:10363: pa chen po lha mi'i ston pa sprul pa'i sku
NK078(tshu)001:10364: sh+aakya thub pa'i spyod yul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10365: chos thams cad la dbang thob pas ji ltar thugs la dgongs shing dmigsa pa bzhina du 'grub /
NK078(tshu)001:10366: 'o na dmigs bya dmigs byed du song ngam snyams la /
NK078(tshu)001:10367: don dam 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams thamsa cad rang
NK078(tshu)001:10368: rgyud med par yul yul can du dmigsa su meda
NK078(tshu)001:10369: pas / kun rdzob tu ye shes sgyu ma nyid
NK078(tshu)001:10370: cir yang 'char zhing gang du'ang 'grub ste sna tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:10371: pas / su snang ba'o // gnyis pa rjes 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:10372: rnal 'byor pas de ltar nyams su len tshul la
NK078(tshu)001:10373: pas / su snang ba'o // gnyis te / bgrang /
NK078(tshu)001:10374: dang po khyad par gyi dam tshig ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10376: rtog pa'i chos nyid zag pa med pa'i zab mo'i don ye shes sgyu mar rtogs na /
NK078(tshu)001:10377: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor dag par ma gyur pa'i chos ni gang yang med de /
NK078(tshu)001:10378: ye shes sgyu ma ye nas yin pa la byed
NK078(tshu)001:10379: pa pos ma bcos par chos kun tu ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:10380: sgyu mar rang gsal bas na chos thams cad kyi
NK078(tshu)001:10381: rang bzhin ye shes sgyu mar rnam par dag pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:10382: // thams cad ye shes sgyu ma yin pa de'i
NK078(tshu)001:10383: phyir spyod lam bzhi po'i dus thams cad kun tu
NK078(tshu)001:10384: // / sgyu ma lta bu'i ye shes rang gsal ba las 'da' bar mi bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10385: gnyis pa thun mong gi dam tshig snga ma dang mthun par 'phel ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10387: rtsa ba'i dam tshig dang yan lag gi dam tshig
NK078(tshu)001:10388: thams cad kun snga ma de ting bzhin yin te
NK078(tshu)001:10389: snga ma bas 'dir nus pa'i stobs cher 'phel ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:10390: // bcu pa drod la dbye ba med do //
NK078(tshu)001:10392: gong du bstan pa de ltar ye shes sgyu ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:10393: don lta bas rtogsa shing ting nge 'dzin gomsa pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10394: sems las nyams su myong ba'i drod ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10395: 'khor ba'i chos sdug bsngal gyi phung po 'di la
NK078(tshu)001:10396: byams snying rje tshad med bzhi dang ldan pa'i byang
NK078(tshu)001:10397: chub semsa kyis rang dbang med par snying rje skye
NK078(tshu)001:10399: sems nyid rang snang ba'i don ye shes sgyu ma
NK078(tshu)001:10400: ma 'khrul ba ngo ma shes pas blo 'khrul bar
NK078(tshu)001:10401: snang bas 'di ci yin snyam du ya mtshan skye
NK078(tshu)001:10402: zhing / don la blta rgyu med par ting nge 'dzin bsgom par byed pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10403: le lor 'dug pa'ang de bzhina du ya mtshan skye ste snying rje skyes so //
