NK078(tshu)001:10404: phyi nang gsang ba'i drod rnam pa gsum lus ngag
NK078(tshu)001:10405: yid gsum la 'byung ba'ang snga ma de ting las
NK078(tshu)001:10407: bcu gcig pa rtags la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10411: de ltar snying rje sgyu ma'i nyamsa lnga'i rima pa gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i don /
NK078(tshu)001:10413: ting nge 'dzin las su rung bas lus shing bal
NK078(tshu)001:10414: gyi 'dab ma lta bur shin tu yang ba 'phur
NK078(tshu)001:10416: lus kyi na tsha la sogs bzod pa phra mo
NK078(tshu)001:10417: thob pa de ting bas 'dir yun ring ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:10418: 'byung 'dus kyi phung po khamsa bde ba dang mi
NK078(tshu)001:10419: bde ba gnyis med par bde bar snyoms pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:10420: / 'dir dus skabs phal cher rtags de tsho yod
NK078(tshu)001:10421: cing 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad 'go snyom pa 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:10422: / ngo // 'di'i skabs su sngon lha rje glen chab bar pas /
NK078(tshu)001:10423: lam rim legs par mkhyen nas tshar 'ga' bshad pa dang 'di'i 'bras bu ma mkhyen nas /
NK078(tshu)001:10424: yang nyan pas 'di'i don sgrims te nyan kyang shor nas /
NK078(tshu)001:10425: lan cig rgya thob la 'di'i 'bras bu zhus pas /
NK078(tshu)001:10426: ngan pa skyug bro ba 'di tsam gnyid log pa'i rmi lam mam /
NK078(tshu)001:10427: srang phugs su khyis ded kyang sha ra ra yod ran dza /
NK078(tshu)001:10428: da rung 'bru ka 'dri ba ci gsung nas bka' bkyon skad /
NK078(tshu)001:10430: 'o na chos brgyad de ting gi skabs nas yang mnyam pas khyad med dam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:10431: yod de de ting gi skabs su chos brgyad chung ngu mnyam pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10432: grangs kyang nyung ngu mnyam pa las med la /
NK078(tshu)001:10433: 'dir de ting bas chos brgyad grangs mang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10434: ngo bo phra rags 'bring po la ngo mnyam pa 'ong ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:10435: de yang de ting skabs su ngo bo tha ma
NK078(tshu)001:10436: ste cha phra ba khab tsam zhig stor rnyed lta
NK078(tshu)001:10437: bu mnyam pa tsam 'ong ba yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:10438: 'dir ngo bo 'bring po de bas che ba khal
NK078(tshu)001:10439: gcig re ba tsam la dga' mi dga' mnyam par
NK078(tshu)001:10440: 'byung ba'o // grangs kyang de ting la /
NK078(tshu)001:10441: bstong smad dam snyan mi snyan gang rung re mnyam pa las med la /
NK078(tshu)001:10442: 'dir de bas chos brgyad kyi grangs kyang mang du
NK078(tshu)001:10443: snyom shing ngo bo la yang gsal brtan du gyur
NK078(tshu)001:10445: drod rtags gzhan yang de dang mtshungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:10446: gnyis pa lam 'og ma bas 'dir 'phel zhing gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10448: de la sogs pa'i drod rtags gzhan kun kyang lam
NK078(tshu)001:10449: snga ma de ting las grangs mang du 'phel zhing
NK078(tshu)001:10450: rtags kyi ngo bo yang gsal la /
NK078(tshu)001:10451: dus kyang yun ring du 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10452: gsum pa mngon shes dang ting nge 'dzin 'di la blo brtan dgos par gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10454: rang dang lhan cig tu drung na 'dug pa'i gang
NK078(tshu)001:10455: zag pha rol po de yi sems la dmigs pa
NK078(tshu)001:10456: gtad de ting nge 'dzin la bzhag pa tsam gyis
NK078(tshu)001:10457: / pha rol po de'i sems rgyud shes pa'i mngon
NK078(tshu)001:10458: par shes pa de'ang de ting bas 'dir grangs mang
NK078(tshu)001:10460: ngo bo cung zad gsal zhing brtan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10461: de las gzhan pa'ang sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa la sogs pa'i mngon shes sam /
NK078(tshu)001:10462: mig gis gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10463: sgra shes pa la sogs pa cung zad tsam 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:10464: goms na yon tan yod pa de bas na lam
NK078(tshu)001:10465: pa rnams kyis snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor gyi
NK078(tshu)001:10466: ting nge 'dzin la blo brtan zhing 'grus par bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:10470: grangs dang ngo bo snga las 'phel //
NK078(tshu)001:10471: bya ba gcig chad pas kha bskang gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:10472: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la dbye ba med do //
NK078(tshu)001:10474: ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa
NK078(tshu)001:10475: 'di'i tshe dbang po sgo drug gi spyod yul gyi
NK078(tshu)001:10476: snang ba ma lus pa thamsa cad kun dngos su
NK078(tshu)001:10477: sgyu mar snang ba lta ci smos kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:10478: gnyid log pa'i rmi lam du'ang spyod yul thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:10479: snang la rang bzhin med pa sgyu ma lta bur
NK078(tshu)001:10480: mthong ba dang / khams gsum thams cad snying rje'i
NK078(tshu)001:10481: yul gyis gang ba rnams rig pa ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:10483: rmi lam gyi mtshan ma bla ma mgon po nyid
NK078(tshu)001:10484: kyis snang nas bdag la byin gyis brlabs pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:10485: / dbang bskur ba la sogs lam du 'jug pa
NK078(tshu)001:10486: lnga byed cing bar chad legs nyes brtson lung ston
NK078(tshu)001:10487: / pa rnams / sngar bas mang ba mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10488: bdud gyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang mtshan ma lnga mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10489: de la sogsa pa shugs snang brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10490: gzhan yang rmi lam bzang po ci snang ci byung
NK078(tshu)001:10491: yang thams cad ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang du shes
NK078(tshu)001:10492: pas blo dga' zhing chags par mi bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10493: bcu gsum pa phan yon la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10495: dang po yon tan tshad med par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10497: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin la goms par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:10498: rnal 'byor pa gsang sngags gnyis med kyi don chen
NK078(tshu)001:10499: po lta ba rtogsa pa yis yon tan yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:10500: de bas na / dus thog ma dang tha ma
NK078(tshu)001:10501: med par gong gi ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:10503: de bsgom pa'i yon tan tshad med pa'i dpe ni
NK078(tshu)001:10504: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa ste tshad du bzung
NK078(tshu)001:10505: du med la / rnal 'byor ba'i spyod yul ni
NK078(tshu)001:10506: ye shes sgyu mar rang snang bas yang dag par
NK078(tshu)001:10507: rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas nyid dang cha mthun pas gcig
NK078(tshu)001:10508: du med la / pa'o // gnyis pa tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing phyag rgya gcig par sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10510: chos thams cad rig pa ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo
NK078(tshu)001:10511: bor ma 'gag par spyod pas bsod namsa kyi tshogsa
NK078(tshu)001:10513: sgyu ma de yang rang rgyud pa med pas ming
NK078(tshu)001:10514: tsam las de nyid la yang ma chagsa te rang
NK078(tshu)001:10515: bzhin med par shes pas ye shes kyi tshogs chen
NK078(tshu)001:10516: dang ldan no // de ltar snying rje chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:10517: rnal 'byor 'di la goms na rnal 'byor phyi ma
NK078(tshu)001:10518: phyag rgya gcig pa rtsol ba med pa 'grub ste
NK078(tshu)001:10519: dang ldan no // / gnas skabs nye sbyor gyi 'bras bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10520: bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma la dbye ba med do //
NK078(tshu)001:10522: lam gong mar ma sleb par de nyid sgom 'phro la 'chi 'pho dgos na /
NK078(tshu)001:10523: sems 'pho ba'i dpe nyi ma las ma g.yos par 'od zer 'byung ba dang 'dra ba /
NK078(tshu)001:10524: da lta'i rig pa las ma g.yos par ma 'ongs pa'i sems su shar ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10525: lus 'pho ba'i dpe sa bona las ma g.yos par myu gur 'gyur ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:10526: da lta'i lus las ma g.yos par phyi ma'i lus kyi snang ba shar ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10527: ngag 'pho ba'i dpe skyu ru ra las ma g.yos par skyur mo'i ro 'byung ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10528: brag las ma g.yos bar ka ke la sogs pa brag cha'i sgra 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:10529: da ltar gyi ngag las ma g.yos par ma 'ongs pa'i ngag tu 'pho zhing 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:10530: mdor na lus ngag yid gsum kyang don rig pa sgyu ma las ma g.yos pas /
NK078(tshu)001:10532: lam pa'i ngo la ma 'ongs pa'i snang bar 'pho
NK078(tshu)001:10533: zhing da ltar gyi snang ba 'gyur bas 'chi ba
NK078(tshu)001:10535: ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:10537: duhkha mi bsam gnyen mo bsam //
NK078(tshu)001:10538: dgra la mi bsam gnod mi bsam //
NK078(tshu)001:10539: kha chems mi bor don la bzhag /ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:10541: shes pa nad dang duhkha'i dbang du mi btang bar
NK078(tshu)001:10542: sngar nas chos thams cad rig pa ye shes sgyu
NK078(tshu)001:10543: mar yul med rang gsal rtog med chen po'i don
NK078(tshu)001:10544: la / gsal ba yul rkyen gyis mi 'phrog par bstan par /
NK078(tshu)001:10546: de ltar dran par byas pa'i ngang las 'das na /
NK078(tshu)001:10547: kun gzhi la tshe snga ma nas las ngan la
NK078(tshu)001:10548: spyod pa'i bag chags kyi rgyun thams cad gcod par
NK078(tshu)001:10549: 'gyur te / bar do rang snang las /
NK078(tshu)001:10550: 'chi kha'i ye shes stobs che na //
NK078(tshu)001:10551: lo dang bskal pa'i bag chags kun //
NK078(tshu)001:10552: ye shes skad cig gcig gis sel //
NK078(tshu)001:10554: de lha mi'i lus thob nas sngar sbyongs pa'i las
NK078(tshu)001:10555: 'phro'i 'brel bas gsang sngags ma h+aa'i lam dang dus
NK078(tshu)001:10556: dang gnas sogs kyis bkol bar mi 'gyur te 'phrad
NK078(tshu)001:10558: bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10560: dang po gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10562: blo che na phyi ma phyag rgya gcig spros tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:10563: sgrub thog nas thod rgal mthar chags kyi sgo nas
NK078(tshu)001:10565: blo chung na lan grangsa skye ba gzhan dag la
NK078(tshu)001:10566: phyag rgya gcig spros tshogs sgrub thog nas thod rgal
NK078(tshu)001:10567: mthar chags kyi sgo nas 'khor ba la phyir mi
NK078(tshu)001:10568: ldog par tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rigs su 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:10570: rnam smin rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:10571: gnyis pa gzhung bzhin bsgrub pas mthar thug gi 'bras bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10573: snying rje sgyu mar bsgom pa'i lam 'dir /
NK078(tshu)001:10574: 'di nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang lam gong ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:10575: cha rkyen kun rdzogsa par bsgrubs pas thun mong dang
NK078(tshu)001:10576: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan bzang po sum cu
NK078(tshu)001:10577: rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu kun
NK078(tshu)001:10578: dang ldan pa'i 'khor 'das gnyis la mi 'dzin par
NK078(tshu)001:10579: longs spyod pas dbang phyug chen po longs sku'i gnas
NK078(tshu)001:10580: 'og min nyid du brgyud nas mngona sum 'byung bar
NK078(tshu)001:10582: 'o na 'dir 'bras bu longs sku thob na /
NK078(tshu)001:10583: lam gong ma gzhan rnams don med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:10584: gong gi 'bras bu nyid la lam phyir te //
NK078(tshu)001:10585: phyogs mthun brjod kyis ris ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:10586: zhes pa dang phyogs mthun par kun ting ye shes sgyu mar bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10587: longs sku ye shes sgyu ma'i sku gnyis ye shes sgyu ma tsam du phyogs mthun par brjod kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:10588: dngos su thob pa dang ris su chad pa ni ma yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:10589: de yang longs sku'i ngo bo ye shes sgyu ma lam du byed pa la dgongs so //
NK078(tshu)001:10591: 'gyu snang ye shes sgyu ma rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs gtso chen ba yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:10592: de la 'bras bu gzugs kyi sku longs sku thob ces rgyu 'bras chos mthun par bshad de /
NK078(tshu)001:10593: de yang rgyud bla ma las sangs rgyas gzugs kyi sku 'di ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10594: bsod nams tshogs las byung ba ste //
NK078(tshu)001:10595: sangs rgyas chos kyi sku 'di ni //
NK078(tshu)001:10596: rgyal po ye shes tshogs las byung //
NK078(tshu)001:10598: gnas skabs nye sbyor gyi 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK078(tshu)001:10599: thun mong gi 'bras bu lha mi'i mtshan rdzogs thob bo //
NK078(tshu)001:10600: gsum pa ma rtogs le lo byas pa'i skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:10602: ye shes sgyu ma'i don lta ba ma rtogsa par ting nge 'dzin bsgoms pa la le lo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10603: spyod pa rang kha ma snyoms las kyi le lo byas na /
NK078(tshu)001:10604: tshe 'di la bdag gzhan gyi gnas skabs dang mthar
NK078(tshu)001:10605: thug gi don ma 'grub par phyi ma ngan song
NK078(tshu)001:10607: de bas na sgom la brtson 'grus kyis shig par shugs la gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10608: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10610: yul bral gnyis med kyi snying rje chen po ye
NK078(tshu)001:10611: shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor bstan pa'i gzhung don rnams
NK078(tshu)001:10612: gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas bgrang
NK078(tshu)001:10613: bzhi pa'i don du gad'o ////le'u lnga pa phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:10616: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10618: snying rje dang stong pa gnyis su med pa'i ye
NK078(tshu)001:10619: shes sgyu ma'i ngang la goms pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:10621: don lus snang sems gsum dbyer med la sbyangs thabs /
NK078(tshu)001:10622: rtags zhi khro'i phyag rgya gcig pa'i lha snang stong
NK078(tshu)001:10623: dbyer med du bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rnal
NK078(tshu)001:10625: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10627: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10629: snying rje sgyu ma la gom pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK078(tshu)001:10630: phyag rgya gcig pa bsgom par 'dod pa gang dag
NK078(tshu)001:10631: yin zhe na / lus sku rdo rje /
NK078(tshu)001:10633: yid thugs rdo rje gsum ldan du bsgom pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:10634: snga mar 'das pa'i de ting gi skabs kyi sngon dgos thabs dang ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10635: zhes pa la sogs don bco lnga sngar ston pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10636: lus kyi sgo nas shes par gyis shig /gnyis pa
NK078(tshu)001:10637: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la don bco lnga
NK078(tshu)001:10638: ste / sngon du bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10649: rmi lam ltas kyi mtshan ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10653: dang po sngon du bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10655: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi dang sbyor lam spyi'i sngon du bya ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:10656: dbang thob cing lhag pa'i yo byad lnga dang ldan par bya ba la sogs pa bdun dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10657: sngon de ting gi skabs su bshad pa bzhin rdzogs par bya ba yis /
NK078(tshu)001:10658: khyad par phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor 'di nyid
NK078(tshu)001:10659: kyi sngon du ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:10660: mthar phyin pa sngon du byas shing /
NK078(tshu)001:10661: dmigs pa'i rten rgyal ba'i sku gser dngul la sogs pa lugs su blugs pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10662: rwa shing la 'bur du gtod pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10664: 'jim pa la 'der so byas pa la sogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10665: yi dam gyi lha'i mtshan ma'i sku phyag rgya rab
NK078(tshu)001:10666: gnas can mdun du bzhag pa de la yan lag
NK078(tshu)001:10667: brgyad pa 'bul ba sngon de ting gi skabs su
NK078(tshu)001:10671: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs su mi zad pa rgyan
NK078(tshu)001:10672: gyi 'khor lo yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i lam
NK078(tshu)001:10673: zhi khro phyag rgya gcig pa 'di bsgom dgos shing
NK078(tshu)001:10674: / phyag rgya spros pa ni rgyu phyag rgya gcig
NK078(tshu)001:10675: pa 'di'i steng nas thob par bya ba'i dgos ched
NK078(tshu)001:10676: / yod pa dang / rgyu stong phyogs gcig tu
NK078(tshu)001:10677: zhen pa'i rtog pa lha'i dbang du bya ba'am yang
NK078(tshu)001:10678: na snying rje sgyu ma la snang zhen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10679: de bzhin nyid la stong par zhen pa yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:10680: de gnyis dbyer med du dbang du bya ba'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:10681: phyag rgya gcig pa bsgom dgos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10682: rtog pa'i yan lag phung po khams dang skye mched
NK078(tshu)001:10683: la sogs pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas su 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:10684: bar bya zhing phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:10685: la brtan pa thob nas gdul bya gzhan dag yongs
NK078(tshu)001:10686: su smin par bya ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10687: de ltar dgos ched lnga yod pa de'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:10688: lha'i sku phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnam 'byor bsgom pa 'di shin tu gces so //
NK078(tshu)001:10689: gsum pa bzhag thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10693: de yang phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la 'jug pa'i thabs la rnam pa gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10695: lha bsgom pa'i sngon du rnal 'byor pa'i sems kyi rtsal yi ge la sbyangs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10696: de dbyungs nas zhi khro'i lhar bskyed cing bsgom pa'i thabs bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10697: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10698: yi ge la sems sbyangs ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10702: dang po bsgoms thabs spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10704: mdor bstan gyi snga ma yi ge la sems sbyang ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:10705: blo chung ba gdams ngag gi stobs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10706: blo che ba shes rab kyi stobs kyis lha bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:10707: pa la 'jug pa'i gzhi'am rtsa ba rgyu'i yi ge
NK078(tshu)001:10708: la aa'am h'u 'di nyid yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:10709: don gyis de la sems 'dzin pa'am sems sbyangs pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10711: de las dang po la shin tu gces te /
NK078(tshu)001:10713: dper na btso bslag mkhan dag gis //
NK078(tshu)001:10714: ras sbyangs gang du bstan pa ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:10715: gang de las kyi dang po bas //
NK078(tshu)001:10716: gong du sbyangs pa rab tu gces //
NK078(tshu)001:10718: ji ltar gser sbyangs 'tsher ba ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:10719: sems nyid sbyang ba rab tu gces //
NK078(tshu)001:10721: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10723: dang po a la sems sbyang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10725: a ni bsgom rgyu'i yi ge'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10726: kha dog ni dkar la 'tsher ba //
NK078(tshu)001:10727: don rang gi rig pa nyid gzung 'dzin gyi dri
NK078(tshu)001:10728: ma dag pa'i phyir yi ge a dkar po bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:10729: pa'o // de yang spar khab las /
NK078(tshu)001:10730: a ni a ste dkar ba ni byang chub sems kyi phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:10732: de yang bsgom pa yul gyi gnas ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10733: bskyed rim la snying kha rdzogs rim la lte bar bsgom te /
NK078(tshu)001:10735: bskyed rim la nges par snying ga ste //
NK078(tshu)001:10736: rdzogs pa'i rim pa la ni lte ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10738: 'dir bskyed rim bsgom pa'i dbang du byas ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10739: rang gi snying gar rig pa nyid a dkar po ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10741: gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan par bsgom ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10742: de yang rab tu brtan pa'i tshad bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10744: mi g.yo ba ni rig pa nyid ar gsal ba'i don rtogs pa'i mthar mi g.yo ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10745: mi 'gyur ba ni rkyen gyis dbang du mi 'gyur ba /
NK078(tshu)001:10746: mngon par mi 'gyur ba ni rkyen gyi dbang du mngon par mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10747: cir yang bsgyur btub pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10748: ka la sogs pa'i yi ge zhe gnyis su 'char bas cir yang bsgyur du rung bar bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10749: 'o na de brtan pa'i tshad du ci 'gro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:10750: ci bsgyur bsgyur du rung ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10751: shin tu brtan pa thob pa'i tshad de /
NK078(tshu)001:10752: dper na skyes bus rta'am rkyal 'byangs pa lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10753: de ltar rang rig ara snang ba de nyid gzung
NK078(tshu)001:10754: 'dzin dang bral zhing nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos
NK078(tshu)001:10756: gsal ba'i tshad bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10759: sems nyid ar gsal ba de nyid rtog pa'i rnyog ma med par shel ltar seng nge ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10761: a nyid sgrib g.yog med par sa le ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10763: de nyid skar ma pa ba sang ltar ting nge 'dzin lhang nge ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10764: lhag ge ba ni de nyid me long la nyi
NK078(tshu)001:10765: ma shar ba ltar rgyang nas kyang lhag ge ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:10766: // de la yang a s+phar na phata ces spros pas /
NK078(tshu)001:10767: gzhi'i a de las shin tu phra ba'i a dpag
NK078(tshu)001:10768: tu med pa rnams sprosa pas phyogs bcu thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:10769: asa gang bar gsal bar gyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:10770: sam ha ra na h'u zhes bsdus kyang gzhi ma'i a de la 'phel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10771: phyogs bcu'i a de la 'grib pa med par ting nge 'dzin brtan pa'i tshad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10772: gsal ba yul rkyen gyis mi 'phrog pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10774: goms dang goms par byed pa yis //
NK078(tshu)001:10775: gang de dag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:10776: bsam yul bye ba mang po la //
NK078(tshu)001:10777: de snyed yul gyi rtsal rnams sbyangs //
NK078(tshu)001:10780: dang po spro bsdu tshad kyi rtsod spang ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10782: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur ba //
NK078(tshu)001:10786: tshogs lam gyi spro bsdu blo chung na dbugs yul /
NK078(tshu)001:10787: blo che na sna'i dri tshor tshar tshun chad spro
NK078(tshu)001:10788: bsdu bya bar bshad pa gnyis 'gal lo zhe na
NK078(tshu)001:10789: mi 'gal ste / rtsa rgyud sogs kyi don ni mos slob kyi dbang du yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:10790: mdo'i don ni dngos yul gyi dbang du yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:10791: gnyis pa rgyu'i yi ge la 'phel 'grib yod med kyi rtsod spang ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10792: spro bsdu la 'phel 'grib me pa mi 'thad de /
NK078(tshu)001:10793: spro bsdu la 'phel 'grib dngos su gsal ba'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:10794: lan la rje sgro phug pas ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10795: snang ba ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi gnas yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:10796: snang ba ma 'dres par 'char bas a grangs med
NK078(tshu)001:10797: spros kyang gzhi ma'i a la 'grib pa med pa
NK078(tshu)001:10798: / dper na nam mkha'i zla ba la gzugs brnyan
NK078(tshu)001:10799: du mar shar kyang gzhi ma mi 'grib pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:10800: / 'dra la / snang ba yongs su rdzogs pas
NK078(tshu)001:10801: bsdus kyang gzhi ma'i a la 'phel ba med pa
NK078(tshu)001:10802: / 'dra la / / dper na phyogs bcu'i gzugs
NK078(tshu)001:10803: brnyan du ma bsdus kyang gzhi ma'i zla ba la
NK078(tshu)001:10804: 'phel ba med pa lta bu yin gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:10806: dngos po'i dbang btsan la spro bsdu la 'phel 'grib yod la /
NK078(tshu)001:10807: 'dir ni don rtags gnyis su gsal te /
NK078(tshu)001:10808: don sems nyid la sems byung gi chos du ma spros kyang sems nyid 'grib pa med la /
NK078(tshu)001:10809: sems byung gi chos du ma bsdus kyang sems nyid la 'phel ba med pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:10810: rtags bzhi po'i a dang phyogs bcu'i a la 'phel 'grib med pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:10811: a gcig dang a du ma rnams gzugs rang rgyud can du grub pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:10812: a rnams sems nyid rang snang yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:10813: dper na nor bu rin chen gyi yon tan lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10814: gnyis pa h'u la sems sbyang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10816: blo chen a de la sems sbyangs nas lha bskyed pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:10817: yang blo chung na a la sems sbyangs pa tshar
NK078(tshu)001:10818: nas thugs ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i yi ge h'u
NK078(tshu)001:10819: mthing nag gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan pa
NK078(tshu)001:10820: bsgom mo // gong gi a la sems sbyangs pa
NK078(tshu)001:10821: de bzhina du h'u la spro bsdu bya ba yang
NK078(tshu)001:10822: nas yang du goms 'dris te las su rung bar
NK078(tshu)001:10823: bsgom mo // byas nas / don ye shes lnga
NK078(tshu)001:10824: gsal ba las ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10825: rtags su snang srid phyi nang snod bcud kyi dngos
NK078(tshu)001:10826: po thams cad yi ge h'u ye shes lnga ldan
NK078(tshu)001:10827: tu gsal bar bsdusa la 'o na rnal 'byor pa
NK078(tshu)001:10828: rang nyid h'u du mi sdud dam snyams na ma
NK078(tshu)001:10829: bsgom mo // byas nas / yin te / rang
NK078(tshu)001:10830: gi lus kyi yan lag lnga dang sems la rnam
NK078(tshu)001:10831: par shes pa tshogs brgyad rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:10832: lnga ye nas yin pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:10833: rtags rang snang gi yi ge h'u du gsal bar shin tu yang basngu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10834: h'u de nyid gsal ba'i tshad ni ni ste mi'i
NK078(tshu)001:10835: snying po yin pa de yi miga gi dbang pos
NK078(tshu)001:10836: mngon sum du mthong ba ltar yod pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:10837: h'u de la 'dris shing goms nas gsal bas bdag
NK078(tshu)001:10838: dang gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir h'u grangs med
NK078(tshu)001:10839: par spro bas 'phags pa mchod cing sems can gyi
NK078(tshu)001:10840: don bya ba rdzogs nas slar gzhi bo'i h'u du
NK078(tshu)001:10841: bsdus te / h'u nyid kyang 'od du zhu nas
NK078(tshu)001:10842: sems nyid mi dmigs pa chos kyi dbyingsa su gasla
NK078(tshu)001:10843: bsdus te / ba sgom mo // de ltar yi
NK078(tshu)001:10844: ge la sems sbyangs ba 'dres shing gomas para bya
NK078(tshu)001:10845: ba ste shina tu gces so //
NK078(tshu)001:10846: zhes gal che bar gdams ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10847: gnyis pa lhar bskyed pa la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10849: phrin las kyi rim pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10851: thun mtshams kyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK078(tshu)001:10857: 'dul ba gnyis kyi khyad par las //
NK078(tshu)001:10858: mnyes pa'i tshul du gdug pa 'dul //
NK078(tshu)001:10859: zhes pas lha bsgom pa la mdor bstan gyi phyi ma lhar bskyed pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:10860: tshangs pa'i phru gu'i cha lugs can gyi zhi ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10861: srin po'i phru gu'i tshul can khro bo ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10862: de lta bu'i zhi khro'i lha ting nge 'dzin yongs
NK078(tshu)001:10863: su rdzogsa pa sgom par bya ba'i thabs zhi khro
NK078(tshu)001:10864: zung gcig tu ston par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:10865: 'o na zhi khro gnyis 'go 'brel lam stag sha
NK078(tshu)001:10866: gang zhe na sgyu 'phrul dbang btsan du stag sha
NK078(tshu)001:10867: ste / tshogs lam nas bsgom lam gyi bar du stag sha'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10868: yang dag dbang btsan du snga ma las ni dbang bsgyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:10869: zhes zhi ba la bsnyen pa byas nas khro bo la sgrub pa byed pas mgo 'brel lo //
NK078(tshu)001:10871: zhi bar bsnyen cing khro bor sgrub //
NK078(tshu)001:10873: 'o na zhi khro la tha dad dang bzang ngan can du 'gyur ro zhe na ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:10875: mos pa tha dad kyi snang ngo la zhi khro
NK078(tshu)001:10876: tha dad ltar snang la don la de bzhin gshegs
NK078(tshu)001:10877: pa'i snang ba la bzang ngan dang tha dad med
NK078(tshu)001:10878: de zhi khro kun gyi spyi'i gzugs can yin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10880: khro bo'i rang bzhin gdug par gnas 'gyur yod ma yin /
NK078(tshu)001:10881: zhi ba'i rang bzhin mdzes shing yid du 'ong ma yin /
NK078(tshu)001:10882: de gnyis gnyis med gnyis su med min zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:10883: cho 'phrul bsam yas thams cad kun tu khyab /
NK078(tshu)001:10885: gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10890: dang po spyir gang mos su sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10892: dang po tshangs pa'i phru gu'i cha lugs can gyi
NK078(tshu)001:10893: zhi ba'i yi dam gyi lha yongs su rdzogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:10894: bsgom par bya ba'i thabs la'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:10895: yi dam gyi lha rigs lnga gang bsgrubs kyang sa
NK078(tshu)001:10896: bon gyi yi ge h'u swa +aam h+aa lnga po
NK078(tshu)001:10898: 'o na bzang ngan yod dam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:10899: de yang spyir ni yi dam gyi lha rigs lnga gang bsgoms kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:10900: rgyal ba la gcig du ma bzang ngan tha dad
NK078(tshu)001:10901: du grub pa med bas kun tu 'dra zhing mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:10902: la / 'dir thugs sgrub sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i skabs
NK078(tshu)001:10903: yin pas rdo rje sems dpa' bsgom pa nyid du
NK078(tshu)001:10904: thams cad 'dus te rigs thams cad kyi gtso bo
NK078(tshu)001:10906: gnyis pa bsgom thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10907: blo chung bas rim gyis bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10908: blo che bas cig char du bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10910: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10914: dang po la a la sems sbyangs shing gdan bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10916: de nyid sgom thabs 'og nas ston pa 'di ltar
NK078(tshu)001:10917: lha'i ting nge 'dzin de nyid la goms par bya
NK078(tshu)001:10918: ba'ang / gzhal yas khang bskyed cing lha bsgom pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:10919: sngon du de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin cir
NK078(tshu)001:10920: yang mi dmigs pa skye med dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10921: snying rje chen po kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i ngang nyid las /
NK078(tshu)001:10922: rang rig pa nyid a dkar bo gsung yig 'bru ngag gi phyag rgya 'od 'bar ba /
NK078(tshu)001:10923: kha dog shin tu gsal zhing 'od zer 'tsher bar ting nge 'dzin la gsal bar bsgoms la /
NK078(tshu)001:10924: phyi nang snod bcud kyi chos thams cad don byang chub sems /
NK078(tshu)001:10925: rtags yi ge a dkar por ni gyur par bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:10926: a ra bsgom pa'i don de ji bzhin pa gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:10927: med nyid du blo goms shing 'dris par gyur nas
NK078(tshu)001:10928: / mar me gcig las gnyis chad kyi tshul du rgyu'i yi ge a dkar po de las /
NK078(tshu)001:10929: a s+pha ra na phata ces ma dmar po'i dkyil 'khor grangs med pa spro /
NK078(tshu)001:10930: de ltar spros pas phyogs bcu thams cad a dang
NK078(tshu)001:10931: ma gnyis kyis gang ba gsal bar ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:10932: gyi blo la 'byor bar gyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:10933: sam ha ra na h'u gis bsdus te 'od du
NK078(tshu)001:10934: zhu ba las nyi zla gang ba sbrel mar bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:10935: / sur+ya tsan+da man+dala zhes pa la nyi ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10936: a la sa zla ba'i dkyil 'khor nya gang ba sbrel ma ste brtsegs mar bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:10937: de'i 'og tu h+r+aih dmar po gsal ba 'od du zhu ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:10938: pad+ma 'dam skyon gyis ma gos pas chags pa med pa kha dog sna tshogs shig bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:10939: gnyis pa gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10941: don ye shes lnga rtags b+h+r+aum las rin chen 'od
NK078(tshu)001:10942: 'bar ba'i gdan gyi 'od las zhi ba'i gzhal yas
NK078(tshu)001:10943: khang sbra gur lta bur bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:10944: yang na gdan de'i 'og tu ye shes rin po
NK078(tshu)001:10945: che 'od 'bar ba'i gdan gyi 'od las zhi ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:10946: gzhal yas khang sbra gur lta bur bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:10947: de ltar nyi zla pad+ma rin po che'i gdan dang rin po che'i gzhal yas khang bsgom pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:10948: rin po che'i za ra tshag la sogs rgyan thams
NK078(tshu)001:10949: cad bsdus shing tshangs pas ngo bo cha phra bar
NK078(tshu)001:10951: gnyis pa brten pa lha bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10952: rtsa ba'i lha cho ga yan lag gsum gyis bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10953: yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10958: gzhal yas kyi nang na gdan de'i dkyila du gsung gi yi ge h'u zhig gnas par bsgom ste /
NK078(tshu)001:10959: h'u de nyid kha dog mthing ka 'od 'tsher la
NK078(tshu)001:10960: gsal ba'i don ye shes rtags h'u gi 'od zer
NK078(tshu)001:10961: phyogs bcur 'phro ba rnam par bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:10962: de ltar h'u de las 'od zer 'phros 'phags pa
NK078(tshu)001:10963: mchod sems can gyi don byas sam ha ra na
NK078(tshu)001:10964: h'u gis dbyings su slar bsdus nas 'od du zhu
NK078(tshu)001:10966: gnyis pa thugs phyag mtshan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10968: badz+ra zhes pas rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa
NK078(tshu)001:10969: shin tu phra ba nas 'bras tsam du gyur par
NK078(tshu)001:10970: bsgom / rdo rje las 'od zer 'phros chod don
NK078(tshu)001:10971: byas te kha dog gsal zhing 'od zer 'bar bar
NK078(tshu)001:10972: gyur nas mchod don byas slar dbyings su yang ni
NK078(tshu)001:10973: rdo rje la bstim par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10974: gsum pa sku phyag rgya la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10976: dang po sku phra ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10978: badz+ra sa t+wa ces pas rdo rje de nyid 'od
NK078(tshu)001:10979: tu zhu ba las rdo rje sems dpa' mthing ga
NK078(tshu)001:10980: rdo rje dang ril bu can tshon gang ba'i skur
NK078(tshu)001:10981: gyur nas / sku de yang shin tu cha phra
NK078(tshu)001:10982: zhing rgyan dang cha lugs thams cad tshang zhing 'dus
NK078(tshu)001:10983: gyur nas / par bsgom mo // gnyis pa yongs rdzogs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:10985: dang po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10987: gong gi de bzhin du sku phra mo de 'phros
NK078(tshu)001:10988: 'dus pas gnyis su med par gsal bar gyur nas
NK078(tshu)001:10989: / h'u badz+ra d+h+rig ces pas sku rags pa rang
NK078(tshu)001:10990: lus tsam zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas rdo rje g.yon
NK078(tshu)001:10991: dril bu 'od 'bar ba bsnams pa tshul dgu dang
NK078(tshu)001:10992: / ldan par bsgom / gnyis pa zhal gsum phyag drug bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:10994: gong gi zhal gcig phyag gnyis bskyed pa de bzhin du goms shing brtan par gyur pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:10995: rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dbu gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:10996: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug pa nyid du bsgoma te /
NK078(tshu)001:10997: de yang g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje /
NK078(tshu)001:10999: g.yon tha ma ral gri 'od 'bar ba /
NK078(tshu)001:11002: g.yon dang po dril bu 'od 'bar ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11003: gnyis pa yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgur bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11005: 'di la brtsegs sdeb gcig byas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:11006: lha de'i tsit+ta'i gnas gcig pa ru /
NK078(tshu)001:11007: cha phra ba'i 'od kyis gzhal yas khang pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan dang ldan pa der /
NK078(tshu)001:11008: ye shes sems dapa'a rtsa ba'i lha ci 'dra ba bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:11009: rtsa ba'i lha'i spyi bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11012: nyi zla pad+ma gsum gyi steng du +aahmh'u gsum las
NK078(tshu)001:11013: byin rlabs kyi lha sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum
NK078(tshu)001:11014: bsgom par bya'o // rtsa ba'i lha'i dbu'i gnas spyi bo mtshogs ma /
NK078(tshu)001:11016: ltag khung rna ltag g.yon dang lngar rin po che'i
NK078(tshu)001:11017: khang bu lnga'i nang du h'u swa +aam h+aa ste
NK078(tshu)001:11019: shu nya t+aa la sogs kyi sngags brjod pas don
NK078(tshu)001:11020: ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i chu rgyun gyis dbang rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:11021: par bskur bas / rtags rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan par bsam mo //
NK078(tshu)001:11022: gnyis pa gcig char du bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:11024: dang po gcig char du bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11026: de yang rnal 'byor pas blo'i shes rab kyi rtsal che bas gcig char du bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11027: chung bas rim gyis bsgom pa'i khyad par yod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11028: blo'i dbang gis phye bas yang blo che na dang
NK078(tshu)001:11029: nas lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por rags pa cig
NK078(tshu)001:11031: dper na chu las nya ldang ba'i tshul ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:11032: snying po brjod pa tsam gyis rnal 'byor pa badga
NK078(tshu)001:11033: nyid yi dam lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po nyid
NK078(tshu)001:11034: du gcig char du bsgom ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11035: de yang dang po rang nas rnam thar gsum mtshon pa'i zhal gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11036: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i phyag drug pa dus rtag tu bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:11037: gnyis pa gzhal yas khang dang lhag pa'i lha snga ma dang mthun par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11039: gnas dgu 'od kyi gzhal yas khang dang pad+ma nyi
NK078(tshu)001:11040: zla'i gdan bsgom pa la sogs snga ma rim gyis
NK078(tshu)001:11041: pa'i skabs bzhin du bsgom zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:11042: de'i gdan steng du yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu
NK078(tshu)001:11043: bsgom pa'ang rim gyis pa'i skabs de bzhin du bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:11044: pa yin no // ting nge 'dzin de la shin tu 'dres shing goms par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11045: de ltar na a nu yo ga dang khyad med par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:11046: snying po brjod pa tsam gyis sku rdzogs tshul du bsgom nus pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:11048: a nu ni dang po gcig char ba rtogs pa'i rjes nas rdzogs tshul du bsgom nus la /
NK078(tshu)001:11049: 'di ni rim gyis pa rgas po de cig char du song ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:11050: de ting kun ting gnyis la sngon du sbyangs pa
NK078(tshu)001:11051: song nas rdzogs tshul du bskyed pa yin pas so
NK078(tshu)001:11052: // gnyis pa khro bo bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:11054: dang po bsgom thabs rim cig char spyir zhi ba dang mthun par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11056: dkyus kyi phyi ma rak+sha ste srin po'i phru gu'i
NK078(tshu)001:11057: cha lugsa 'dzin pa khro bo phyag rgya gcig pa
NK078(tshu)001:11058: bsgom pa la'ang / cho ga gsum gyis bskyed pa rim gyis pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11059: chu la nya ldang tshul du bskyed pa gcig chara
NK078(tshu)001:11060: ba dang gnyis su yod pa'ang sngon zhi ba'i skabs
NK078(tshu)001:11061: su bstan pa de bzhin yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:11062: gnyis pa khyad par du zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur te bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11064: sku rdo rje gsung rdo rje thugs rdo rje'i go cha ste cho ga gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11065: kha dog mthing ga 'tsher ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11066: tha dad pa'i gzhal yas khang la sogs pa yang zhi ba las bsgyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:11067: khro bo'i gzhung ltar bsgom par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11068: thugs kyi rigsa badz+ra he ru ka las gzhan rigs bzhi po gang rung la mos pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:11069: rigs bzhi'i kha dog yig 'abru rnams kha dog smug
NK078(tshu)001:11070: ser dmar ljang bzhi la sems sbyangs te lha bskyed
NK078(tshu)001:11071: pa ni / gdan dang bzhugs gnas dang rgyan la
NK078(tshu)001:11072: sogs pa phal cher gong gi rdo rje'i rigs badz+ra
NK078(tshu)001:11073: he ru ka dang gcig go //
NK078(tshu)001:11074: sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i cho ga rnam pa gsum
NK078(tshu)001:11075: yang rigs bzhi gang yin gyi rigs su basgyur cing
NK078(tshu)001:11076: / de la sku phyag rgya chen po rags pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11077: zhal gsum phyag drug tu bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11078: yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu sgom pa'ang zhi ba
NK078(tshu)001:11079: las khro bor bsgyur ba gong gi de bzhin no
NK078(tshu)001:11080: // mdor na phyag rgya gcig pa ni rtsa ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:11081: lha gcig la yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:11082: // pa'o // 'o na spros bcas su thal lha du ma bsgom pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:11083: lha rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:11084: yan lag gi lha dgu bsgoms pa yang rtse ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:11085: lha gcig las med pas phyag rgya gcig pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:11086: te / rtsa ba gcig pa'i lha bsgom pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor yin /
NK078(tshu)001:11087: zhes pas rtsa ba'i lha yi ngos nas bzhag gi /
NK078(tshu)001:11088: yan lag gi lha yi ngos nas ma bzhag pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11090: yan lag gi lha sgom yang /
NK078(tshu)001:11091: rtsa ba'i lha gcig bsgoms pas phyag rgya gcig par 'gro na /
NK078(tshu)001:11092: de tshod du spros pa'i stong dang nyi khri bzhi stong la slob pa'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:11093: thub pa re re la lha stong stong bsgom pa de yang phyag rgya gcig par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:11094: yan lag stong 'dug kyang rtsa ba gcig las med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11095: 'dod na spros pa yin pas bsal la /
NK078(tshu)001:11097: spros bcas bya ba rtog pa du ma lha du mar spros nas bsgoms pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:11098: 'dir rtsa ba'i rtog pa gcig pu lha'i sku gcig tu bsgom pa yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:11099: yan lag gi lha du ma bsgom yang spros bcas su mi 'gro gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:11100: lce ston gyis rtsa ba'i lha gcig la yan lag gi lha dgu bsgoms yang /
NK078(tshu)001:11101: nying lag gi lha mi bsgom pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:11102: spros pa dang mtshungs pa min no snyam mo gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:11104: de nyid yan lag spros bcas bdag /ces bshad pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:11105: gnyis pa phrin las kyi rim pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11107: de ltar zhi khro gnyis ka blo chung bas rima gyisa bsgom pa la brtan pa thob pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:11108: blo che bas gcig char bsgom pa'i dus su phrin las kyi rim pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11109: yan lag brgyad pa'i mthar mtshams bcad /
NK078(tshu)001:11113: h'u zhes 'od dang gzi byin rang la thim pa las yid dam gyi lhar bskyed la /
NK078(tshu)001:11114: phyi nang gi mchod pa rnams gzhung bzhin du byin
NK078(tshu)001:11115: gyis brlabs nas stong pa dang sgyu ma'i ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:11116: 'dzin cung zad tsam sngon du song nas rang gang
NK078(tshu)001:11117: bsgom lha'i skur rim gyis sam cig char du bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:11118: ste / yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:11119: par bskyed pa yan chad rdzogs nas snyan gsan dbab
NK078(tshu)001:11120: ste / spyan drangs bstim / brtan par byas la /
NK078(tshu)001:11121: de la phyi nang gsang bas mchod cing bstod pa bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11122: gsum pa bzlas pa byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11124: de nas gang bsgom gyi lha'i sngags kyis yan lag ma nyams par sngags bzlasa pa'nga /
NK078(tshu)001:11125: bzlas pa'i skyon bcu spangs te /
NK078(tshu)001:11126: bdag dam tshig gi sems dpa' lha ye shes sems
NK078(tshu)001:11127: dpa'i bar 'phro 'du rnam pa gsum gyi bzlas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11128: grangs ji bzhin tsam dam bcas pa bzhin rdzogs par
NK078(tshu)001:11129: bya ba'o // de yang bzlas pa'i skyon bcu la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:11130: sngags bzlas pa'i sgra skyon dang bar chad skyon bcu spang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11131: sngags la bsam dpyod kyi bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcu spangs ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11137: sgra chen ma yin sogs de dag spang ba shin du gal che te /
NK078(tshu)001:11138: sgra che na 'byung bo dang snod med kyis thos na bar chad 'byung /
NK078(tshu)001:11142: myur na lce dub bul na grangs mi thon sgra med na tshig nyams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11145: sgra chen ma yin chung ba min //
NK078(tshu)001:11146: mgyogs par ma yin bul ba min //
NK078(tshu)001:11147: drag par ma yin zhan ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:11148: yig 'bru'i yan lag nyams ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:11149: yeng ba nga rgyal dang ldan min //
NK078(tshu)001:11150: rgyu ba'i sems pa spang bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:11152: gnyis pa bar chad kyi skyon lnga ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11155: gnyis dang bzhi pos bar chod na byin brlabs yal /
NK078(tshu)001:11156: sems yengs na ting nge 'dzin gyi srog med pas don gyi nus mthu med de /
NK078(tshu)001:11157: tshig tsam gyi nus pa bas mi 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:11161: snod med thos gyur bar chad 'byung //
NK078(tshu)001:11162: sgra med bar chad mthu med 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:11163: rkyen gyur lus kyi 'phrad par nyams //
NK078(tshu)001:11164: de la sngags kyi nus pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:11165: bul na bzlas pa'i grangs med pas //
NK078(tshu)001:11167: glo dang sbrid dang gtam dang ni //
NK078(tshu)001:11168: gnyid la sogs pas bar chad na //
NK078(tshu)001:11169: des ni yi dwags bdud la sogs //
NK078(tshu)001:11170: spros nas bar chad sbyor bar byed //
NK078(tshu)001:11171: sems g.yeng nus mthu mi 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:11173: gnyis pa bsam dpyod kyi skyon bcu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11174: nyon mongs pa dug lnga bsam pa'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11175: brtson 'grus chung ba bsam pa'i skyon dang drug /
NK078(tshu)001:11176: 'dod chags che ba re dogs kyi skyon dang bdun /
NK078(tshu)001:11177: ting nge 'dzin dang bral ba yengs ba'i skyon dang brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:11178: yid ches med pa the tshom gyi skyon dang dgu /
NK078(tshu)001:11179: don dang mi ldan pa rang rgyud pa'i skyon dang bcu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11180: de yang nag po drug cu pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:11181: sngags kyi bsnyen pa byed dus su //
NK078(tshu)001:11182: me dang 'dra ba'i zhe sdang gis //
NK078(tshu)001:11183: sngags kyi 'bras bu bsregs par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:11184: kun nas 'khrigs pa'i chags pa yis //
NK078(tshu)001:11185: yon tan rgyan rnams 'ching bar byed //
NK078(tshu)001:11186: mun pa lta bu'i gti mug gis //
NK078(tshu)001:11187: dngos grub nye ba rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:11188: glang bu lta bu'i nga rgyal gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:11189: dngos grub chu 'dra rtsi nas snyil //
NK078(tshu)001:11190: sngags kyi yon tan sprin 'dra la //
NK078(tshu)001:11191: phrag dog rlung gis 'thor bar byed //
NK078(tshu)001:11192: dngos grub chu bo'i rgyun bsdu la //
NK078(tshu)001:11193: brtson 'grus rdo rje'i brag med na //
NK078(tshu)001:11194: le lo'i rba rlabs chen po 'khrugs //
NK078(tshu)001:11196: sngags kyi dngos grub 'dod pas spang //
NK078(tshu)001:11197: bzlas brjod me yi rgyun 'dra la //
NK078(tshu)001:11198: sdig pa chu dang 'dra bas gsod //
NK078(tshu)001:11201: bsnyen pa'i dus su bzlas pa'i 'od zer phar 'phros 'phags pa mchod sems can gzhan gyi don byas /
NK078(tshu)001:11202: tshur bsdus bdag gi sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs
NK078(tshu)001:11203: shing dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar bsam zhing
NK078(tshu)001:11204: bzlas pa bya / sgrub pa'i dus su 'od zer spros 'phags pa mchod sems can gyi don byas /
NK078(tshu)001:11205: tshur 'dus pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11206: sgrub pa chen po'i dus su tshur bsdu ba kho
NK078(tshu)001:11207: nas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam
NK078(tshu)001:11208: zhing / bdag gzhan gyi don yongs su rdzogs par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11210: bsnyen pa'i dus su dam tshig sems dpa' dang ye
NK078(tshu)001:11211: shes sems dpa' tha dad du gsal bar byas nas
NK078(tshu)001:11214: sgrub pa'i dus su de gnyis tha mi dad du gsal bas bzlas pa byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11216: sgrub pa chen po'i dus su bdag dam tshig pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11217: thugs ka nas yig 'bru byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK078(tshu)001:11219: ye shes sems dpa'i zhal du thim zhing klad pa'i rgyas su byung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11220: a ba d+hu ti nas mar zhugs shing gsang ba'i rdo rje nas bdag gi rdo rjer thim /
NK078(tshu)001:11221: a ba d+hu ti nas yar zhugs /
NK078(tshu)001:11222: bdag gi zhal nas ye shes sems dpa'i zhal du thim /
NK078(tshu)001:11223: mkha' nas mkha' ru thim par bsam zhing bzlas te /
NK078(tshu)001:11224: de ltar phyi nang gsang gsang gsum la blo che
NK078(tshu)001:11225: chung gi sgo nas gang mos su yi dam lha'i
NK078(tshu)001:11226: snying po de yang yang bskyar zhing bsgrangs pas na
NK078(tshu)001:11228: de la yang gsum ste bzlas brjod grangs kyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11230: mtshan ma rtags kyi bsnyen pa rtags dbyung bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11232: spyir bye ba sa ya yin gsungs /
NK078(tshu)001:11237: rtags kyi mtshan ma ma byung gi bar du'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11238: de rnams tshad du phyin par skyol bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11239: bzhi pa thun mtshams kyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK078(tshu)001:11241: de ltar lo zla du mar lha'i bsgom bzlas kyis khams dub par gyur na /
NK078(tshu)001:11242: thabs lam gyi dbang du lte ba la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:11243: 'khor lo bzhi'i thig le la bltas pas bde ba
NK078(tshu)001:11244: 'bar ram / khyad par snying ga'i rtsa kun rdar
NK078(tshu)001:11245: ma'i nang du dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi bcud srog
NK078(tshu)001:11247: ye shes snying po'i 'od kyis thig le dkar po
NK078(tshu)001:11248: zlum po sran ma tsam yod pa me tog kun
NK078(tshu)001:11249: rda'i kha dog lta bur gnas pa de la ting
NK078(tshu)001:11251: nub mo'i de'i ngang nyal bas khams dub pa sang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:11252: nang par kyang de nyid kyi ngang las langs nas
NK078(tshu)001:11253: gsung yig 'bru h'u la sogs pa zhi khro gang
NK078(tshu)001:11254: yin gyi cho ga gsum gyis bsgyur te sku phyag
NK078(tshu)001:11255: rgya gcig pa yongs su rdzogs par bsgom pa la
NK078(tshu)001:11256: las rim mchod bstod bzlas pa la sogs pa sngon
NK078(tshu)001:11257: gong gi ji ltar byed pa bzhin du sgo gsum
NK078(tshu)001:11258: rab tu brtson pas lha'i rnal 'byor la 'dris shing
NK078(tshu)001:11259: goms par bya'o // spyir rim gcig char dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11260: thabs grol dang lha dang mi rtog pa rnams mgo 'brel lam stag sha zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:11261: rim dang gcig char thams cad du stag sha yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:11263: lha dang mi rtog pa gnyis sgyu 'phrul du 'go 'brel zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:11264: mdo'i dbang btsan du stag sha'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11265: bzhi pa ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11267: dang po bsgom byed ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo dmigs med rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11269: rten zhi khro'i gzhal yas khang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11270: brten pa zhi khro'i lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba yang /
NK078(tshu)001:11271: rang las gzhan zhig tu grub pa min te /
NK078(tshu)001:11272: rang gi rig pa sems kyi cho 'phrul nyid lha'i dkyil 'khor de dag rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:11273: bsgom bya zhi khro'i lha'i yang blo'i yul du dmigs
NK078(tshu)001:11274: nas sgom du med de rang gi rig pa de
NK078(tshu)001:11275: nyid lha'i sku gsung thugs mdzad pa phrin las kyi
NK078(tshu)001:11276: phyag rgya dang bzhi rdzogs pa'i lha'i sku'i phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:11277: chen po'i gang bsgom pa de nyid rig pa rang
NK078(tshu)001:11278: snanga ba'o // gnyis pa bsgom bya don gyi ngo
NK078(tshu)001:11279: bo yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i dpe don dang
NK078(tshu)001:11281: thun mong gi rgyal ba'i yang rgyal ba sku lnga
NK078(tshu)001:11282: lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa'
NK078(tshu)001:11283: la sogs pa rnams kyi sku ru gsal ba ni
NK078(tshu)001:11284: dus dang gnas skabs kuna tu yid bzhin gyi nor
NK078(tshu)001:11285: bu rin chen lta bu ste sku lnga'i yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:11286: thams cad lhun grub du rdzogs pas 'di la phan
NK078(tshu)001:11287: gdags mi gdags kyi rnam par rtog pa'i rtsol ba
NK078(tshu)001:11288: med par gdul bya 'khor lnga'i re ba yid bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:11289: gyi skong ba'i dus su yon tan mi zad pa
NK078(tshu)001:11290: dang / ma byas pas 'phel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11291: dgongs pa'i ngang nas gdul bya'i don la phar 'gro ba dang tshur 'ong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11292: thugs rje la nye ba dang ring ba'i 'du shes
NK078(tshu)001:11293: gang yang med par gdul bya'i don mdzad pa bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:11294: / rjes 'jug gis kyang de bzhin du shes nas bsgom dgos so //
NK078(tshu)001:11295: gsum pa sgom pa'i nges tshig go //
NK078(tshu)001:11297: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po de bsgom pa'i tshe yod pa'i skyon las grol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11298: ma bsgom pa tsam na med pas ma grol ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:11299: 'dzin pa med de gang yang thams cad rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:11300: bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir dgongs pa la
NK078(tshu)001:11301: phyogs ris med cing spyod pa lha la blang bya
NK078(tshu)001:11302: dang / rtog pa la dor bya med de /
NK078(tshu)001:11303: lha'i sku bsgom pa la bying ba dang rgod pa
NK078(tshu)001:11304: shas chen ba'i skyon la med par de snyom pa
NK078(tshu)001:11305: tsam la ting nge 'dzin mnyam pa la bzhag pa'am
NK078(tshu)001:11306: bsgom zhes bya ba'i sgra don nam nges tshigs su
NK078(tshu)001:11307: brjod pa'o // lnga pa mi mthun pa'i skyon la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:11309: dang po thun mong gi skyon phra bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11311: ting nge 'dzin ngo bo dang mi mthun pa'i skyon bye brag rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:11312: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas pa 'di'i tshe skyon rnams dmigs ngos bzung ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11313: dang po yi ge la sems sbyang ba nas bzung ste sku yongs su rdzogs pa bsgom pa'i bar /
NK078(tshu)001:11314: dmigs pa brjed pa dang bying rgod la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:11315: thun mong gi skyon kun tu 'byung ba 'dir rags
NK078(tshu)001:11318: tha ma skyon phra ba phyag rgya gcig pa 'di
NK078(tshu)001:11319: bsgom pa'i skabs las 'byung ba de shes bzhin bya
NK078(tshu)001:11320: ra bas so 'thas bcad pa gces so //
NK078(tshu)001:11321: khyad par gyi skyon bcu gcig bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11323: phyag rgya gcig pa 'di nyid kyi khyad par gyi skyon la gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:11324: dang po yi ge la sems sbyangs pa'i skyon gsum ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11325: smig rgyu ltar blo yul du yi ge a h'u rab rib tsam las mi snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11326: yi ge snang yang du ba'i gsebs kyi rdzas ltar
NK078(tshu)001:11327: gsal ba med par mog mog tu 'dug pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:11328: / yi ge gsal ba 'grib nas 'gro ba griba ma lta bu'i nag nog gis chod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11329: gnyis pa lha bsgom pa'i dus su 'gyur ba'i skyon brgyad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11330: lha rang gi lus gang gi tshad du dmigs nas
NK078(tshu)001:11331: bsgom pa la che chung gi tshad 'gyur ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:11334: bzhengs pa dang bzhugs pa'i tshul 'gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11336: zhi khro'i cha lugs dur khrod dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11337: rin po che'i rgyan 'gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11338: sku mdog dkar po la sogs 'gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11341: kha dog ste sku mdog 'ba' zhig las mi snang ste sku'i dbyings med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11342: dbu'i gtsug tor nas rim para nub cing mi gsal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11343: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11345: dang po skyon bcos thabs spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11347: de ltar skyon dbang du 'gyur ba shes bzhin gyi bya ra bas tshor bar byas tee /
NK078(tshu)001:11348: mtshan ma'i 'du byed kyi rnam rtog gi rlung gi
NK078(tshu)001:11349: skyon byung bsam nas ting nge 'dzin bskyod par mi
NK078(tshu)001:11350: bya'o // gnyis pa bye brag tu khyad par gyi skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11352: gong du bstan pa de ltar skyon ngos zin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11353: rnal 'byor pas skyon de dag kuna gyi bcos thabs
NK078(tshu)001:11355: 'dir khyad par gyi skyon la'ang yi ge mi gsal
NK078(tshu)001:11356: ba'i skyon rab rib mog mog grib ma gsum la
NK078(tshu)001:11357: mtshan ma'i 'du byed kyi rnam rtog gi rlung gi
NK078(tshu)001:11358: skyon byung bsams nas ting nge 'dzin lam snga ma
NK078(tshu)001:11359: ma brten pa'i skyon yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:11360: snying rje 'gyur ba sgyu stong ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang la yun ring du 'dug la /
NK078(tshu)001:11361: de goms pa'i rjesa la phra ba yi ge'i ting
NK078(tshu)001:11362: nge 'dzin rang shugs kyis bsgom pa thob pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:11363: te / de yang yun ha cang mi ring bar
NK078(tshu)001:11364: byas te thun tshod ma sun tsam du 'dug cing
NK078(tshu)001:11365: te / sgom par bya'o // lha bsgom pa'i dus su 'gyur ba'i skyon brgyad kyiis /
NK078(tshu)001:11366: snga ma drug la sku ri bo lta bu che
NK078(tshu)001:11367: zhing gdos bcas rang rgyud du sgom par bya zhing
NK078(tshu)001:11368: / bdun pa kha dog 'ba' zhig gsal kyang dbyibs med pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:11369: kha dog la brten nas sku'i dbyibs dang gnyis bsres te bsgom par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11370: brgyad pa rim par nub pa'i skyon la spyi'i rnam
NK078(tshu)001:11371: pa gsal ba med kyang bye brag zhal phyag gam
NK078(tshu)001:11372: / phyag gi sor tshig nas dpung pa tsam la
NK078(tshu)001:11373: sogs pa gang gsal ba la blo gnas par bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:11374: / // gsum pa spyod lam gyi skyon bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:11376: sgo gsum gyi bya bar 'os pa min pa ting nge 'dzin dang mi mthun pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:11377: yi ge bri mchod pa la sogs pa kun dor bar byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:11380: zhes sogs spyod lam rnam bzhi rnal du ma 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:11381: ba'i skyon rnams thams cad dor zhing btang bar bya
NK078(tshu)001:11382: ba'o // bdun pa nyams la gsum te /
NK078(tshu)001:11384: dang po nyams snga ma bzhin 'phel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11387: kun ting gnyis la nyams lnga zhugs nas brten mod
NK078(tshu)001:11388: kyang phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'di la
NK078(tshu)001:11389: / gomsa pasa nyams rim lnga gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i tshul bstan pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:11391: kun ting gnyis su bstan pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11392: gnyis pa nyams lnga'ang mtshan ma dang sbyar te bshad ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11394: g.yo ba'i nyams kyi dus su smig rgyu de chu
NK078(tshu)001:11395: dngos su min kyang chur sring sring yod pa ltar
NK078(tshu)001:11397: yi ge dang lha dngos su wal le mi snang yang yid yul na sring sring yod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11398: thob pa'i dus su me stag chung ngu tsam la lci skams dum bu gcig lhan na /
NK078(tshu)001:11399: phog cig du ba sngo lang gis byung nas de ma thag med pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:11400: thang cig yi ge dang lha wal le gsal nas gsal ma thag med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11401: goms pa'i dus su lho mon kun na srin bu
NK078(tshu)001:11402: me khyera bya ba'i sems can zhig 'od 'dom re
NK078(tshu)001:11403: tsam dang bcas nas nub mo 'phur nas 'ong ba
NK078(tshu)001:11404: de / mda' rgyang re tsam du dmar na ra
NK078(tshu)001:11405: ra byung nas shing la sogs pa'i phag tu hrib
NK078(tshu)001:11406: kyis song nas mi snang bzhin du snga ma bas
NK078(tshu)001:11407: lha gsal ba de rgyun ring du gsal nas yang
NK078(tshu)001:11408: de / mi gsal ba'o // brten pa'i dus su mar me rlung gis ma bskyod pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:11409: thun bar du lha gsal la rtog pa med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11410: mthar phyin pa'i dus su nam mkha' dwangs pa la nyi ma shar ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:11411: dus thun nam nyin mtshan phyed par rigs pa lhar gsal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11412: de lhar nyams lnga la mtshan ma lnga'i tshul de dag dang sbyar te shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11413: 'o na mtshan ma lnga po 'di nyams lnga la sbyar ba ci zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:11414: 'di dag dngos su mthong ba ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:11415: nyams lnga po la gsal mi gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:11416: brtan mi brtan gyi khyad yod pa'i dbang du'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11417: dang po yi ge la sems sbyangs pa'i dus su dpe don de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11418: gsum pa rtsol ba che chung rang gi nyams dang sbyar ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11420: de yang nyams de dag gi dus su rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i btang snyoms dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11422: dus phyad pa'i btang snyoms dang gsum gyi rim pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11423: brtson pa ni ting nge 'dzin la sems mngon par
NK078(tshu)001:11424: spro ba'i sgo nas sgo gsum gyi rtsol ba byed
NK078(tshu)001:11425: pa'o // mdor na de dag gi blang dor nyams kyi skabsa dang sbyar la shes par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11426: g.yo thob gnyis kyi skabs su rtsol ba dang bcas
NK078(tshu)001:11427: pa'i btang snyoms dang rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i brtson
NK078(tshu)001:11429: goms brtan gnyis kyi skabs su rtsol ba med pa'i btang snyoms dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11430: rtsol ba med pa'i brtson 'grus blangs /
NK078(tshu)001:11433: dus phyad pa'i btang snyoms dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11434: dus phyad pa'i brtson 'grus gnyis blangs /
NK078(tshu)001:11436: yang g.yo thob kyi skabs su /
NK078(tshu)001:11437: brtson 'grus blang shing btang snyoms dor ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11438: goms brtan yan chad du btang snyom blang zhing brtson pa dor te /
NK078(tshu)001:11439: goms pa la rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i btang snyoms blang /
NK078(tshu)001:11440: brtan pa la rtsol ba med pa'i btang snyoms blang /
NK078(tshu)001:11441: mthar phyin pa'i dus su dus phyed pa'i btang snyoms
NK078(tshu)001:11442: dang du blang zhing rtsol ba dor ro brgyad pa
NK078(tshu)001:11444: bdag don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11445: gzhan don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11446: ting nge 'dzin bstan pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:11449: dang po spyod lam bzhi la zhi khro gang yin gyi skabs dang sbyar ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11451: rang gi spyi bo mgrin pa snying ga lte ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:11452: gnas bzhir yig 'bru h'u bzhi las khro bo bzhir
NK078(tshu)001:11453: bskyed la dul rtag tu mtshams bcad de bsrung ba
NK078(tshu)001:11454: ni / de la lte bar h'u las gshin rje
NK078(tshu)001:11455: gshed smug nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas be con
NK078(tshu)001:11458: snying gar h'u las stobs po che dud kha /
NK078(tshu)001:11460: mgrin par h'u las rta mgrin dmar nag spu gri zhags pa /
NK078(tshu)001:11461: spyi bor h'u las bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag ral gri rgya gram mo //
NK078(tshu)001:11462: chos kun rang byung ye shes kyi ngang las rang
NK078(tshu)001:11463: lus lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bas tshogs 'bul bya
NK078(tshu)001:11464: 'bul byed med par rig par bdag nyid chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:11465: longs spyod chogs kyi mchod pa bya ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11466: nang gi sbyin bsreg kyang za tshogs gtor lung ltar dang du blang bar bya zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:11467: gzugsa sgra dri ro reg chos la sogs yul drug
NK078(tshu)001:11468: po de la mtshan med ltar na spros pa med
NK078(tshu)001:11469: pa'i thig le mi rtog par shes par bya ste
NK078(tshu)001:11470: / chos nyid la chos nyid rol ba mtshan bcas
NK078(tshu)001:11471: ltar na 'dod yon gyi lha mo drug tu gsal
NK078(tshu)001:11472: bas lha la lha thim par rol zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:11473: dbang po rnam shes sems dpa' brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:11474: yul dang dus phyi nang gi sems ma ste yab yum du sbyor bar shes par bya /
NK078(tshu)001:11475: de yang yi dam gyi lha zhi khro phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:11476: gcig pa gang yin pa'i skabs kyi sems dpa' dang
NK078(tshu)001:11477: sems ma / ko'u ri dang sing+ha la sogs pa'i tshul du bsgyur bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11478: gnyis pa bdag nyid chen po'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11480: gong ltar chos thams cad rig pa bdag nyid chen
NK078(tshu)001:11481: po'i ngang du sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis med
NK078(tshu)001:11482: du gsal ba rang la mchod pa 'bul ba'i yon
NK078(tshu)001:11483: tan ni / sangsa rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus
NK078(tshu)001:11484: pa bdag nyid kyi rang rig pa'i ye shes dang
NK078(tshu)001:11485: tha dad med pas na mnyes shing /
NK078(tshu)001:11486: rtog tshogs rang rig par gsal bas srid pa khams gsum gyi sems can rigs drug dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11487: de dag bskyed pa'i sa bon a ni su tri
NK078(tshu)001:11488: pre duh thams cad la byang chub sems kyi bde
NK078(tshu)001:11489: ba'i ro dga' ba chena pos khyab nas tshim par
NK078(tshu)001:11490: 'gyur ro // gsum pa dus dang gnas skabs thams cad du bsgom pa'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11492: rnal 'byor pa phan tshun du 'gro ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11495: zas la longs spyod pa'i tshe dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11496: nyon mongs pa chags sdang la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11498: sems kyi sdug bsngal 'byung ba'i tshe na yang /
NK078(tshu)001:11499: gsang ba'i theg pa chen po gsang sngags yi dam
NK078(tshu)001:11500: gyi lha'i sku phyag rgya bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK078(tshu)001:11502: dus thams cad du lha'i nga rgyal ba dang ma
NK078(tshu)001:11503: bral ba sngon bzhina dbang po yul dus thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:11504: lha yab yum du sbyor bas dus myur du 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:11505: bu lha'i dngos grub 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11506: bzhi pa bya ba spangs pas phyogs gcig pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11508: rgyu de ting dang 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig pa
NK078(tshu)001:11509: de gnyis mtshams sbyor bas kun snang dang gsum gyis
NK078(tshu)001:11510: bar skabs kun tu bsgom pa kho na min pa
NK078(tshu)001:11511: chos spyoda dgu'i spros pa dor te /
NK078(tshu)001:11512: gtan du dor ba min pas rgyud la ldan yang
NK078(tshu)001:11513: bsgom pa'i skabs 'dir dang du blang bar bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:11514: min te / de ci'i phyir zhe na de dag
NK078(tshu)001:11515: thams cad g.yeng ba drug las mtshan ma'i g.yeng bar
NK078(tshu)001:11516: gyur pa yin pa'i phyira ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11517: lnga pa spyod pa dag cing brtson pa dang ldan pa'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11519: lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:11520: gsum du bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pas gzhan rang bas
NK078(tshu)001:11521: dman pa rnams la phyag dang bskor ba mi bya
NK078(tshu)001:11523: bla ma yi dam lha spyi bor bsgom la bya gsungs /
NK078(tshu)001:11528: sgom sgrub can gyi zas lci /
NK078(tshu)001:11531: zhi khro phyag rgya gcig pa'i lha'i rnal 'byor gyi
NK078(tshu)001:11532: ting nge 'dzin la sbyor cing nyams su len pa
NK078(tshu)001:11533: la / gnyis med kyi rtogs pa'i lta dgongs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:11534: don dang ldan cing dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:11535: ma nyams par spyod lam dag par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:11536: yid dam lha'i bsgom bzlas la sgo gsum brtson 'grus
NK078(tshu)001:11537: shin tu cher bskyeda de bsgrubs na dus myur bar
NK078(tshu)001:11538: 'bras bu yi dam gyi lha 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK078(tshu)001:11539: // drug pa tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11541: spyod lam thams cad du lha yin pa la lhar
NK078(tshu)001:11542: gsal ba'i rol pa ma 'gags par bsoda namsa kyi
NK078(tshu)001:11543: tshogs te / de la spyod bzhin du rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:11544: med pa sems nyid du shes pas ma chagsa shing
NK078(tshu)001:11545: 'dzin pa med pa'i ye shes kyi tshogs dang gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:11547: gnyis pa gzhan gyi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11549: gdul bya gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir bzlas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11550: 'od zer gyi 'phro 'dus rim pas bdag gzhan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:11552: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi don bya ba'i yul gyi rkyen dang 'phrad pa de'ang mi 'dor te /
NK078(tshu)001:11553: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs 'dir spros pa bsgom pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11554: dus min yang gdul bya gzhan gyi don du dbang
NK078(tshu)001:11555: bskur ba la sogs pa bya ba'i phyir phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:11556: spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin de'ang 'di nyams su len
NK078(tshu)001:11557: par byed cing sgom par ston no //
NK078(tshu)001:11558: de'i phyir gdul bya gang dang 'dul thabs 'tshamsa par bstan pa gzhan gyi don rdzogsa par byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:11559: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin brtan pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:11561: de yang rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyi don bsgrub pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:11562: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub sgrub pa rnams
NK078(tshu)001:11563: phyag rgya gcig pa 'di la brtan pa thob na
NK078(tshu)001:11564: dngos grub sbyor bas gang yang the tshom med par
NK078(tshu)001:11565: 'gyur ro // dgu pa dam tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11567: phyag rgya gcig pa 'di la gnas pa'i tshe lam
NK078(tshu)001:11568: gyi gzhi 'dzin pa sa gzhi dang 'dra ba'i rtsa
NK078(tshu)001:11569: ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig kun dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:11570: mod kyang / khyad par du gsunga gi dam tshig
NK078(tshu)001:11571: gi gzhi la sngags phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa
NK078(tshu)001:11573: yi dam lha'i sku'i phyag rgya chen po'i rnal 'byora
NK078(tshu)001:11574: du gsal ba'i ngang las spyod yul thams cad kyang
NK078(tshu)001:11575: lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba'i ting
NK078(tshu)001:11576: nge 'dzin las mi 'da' bar bsdam par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11581: gsang ba sems kyi drod gsum po yang /
NK078(tshu)001:11584: gnyis su drod g.yo ba dang thob pa'i tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11585: 'dir snga ma bas goms pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11588: phyi'i drod 'dod pa'i longs spyod la zhen pa med pas sngar bas chung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11589: dbang po yul dusa snang ba kun lha'i ting nge 'dzin la gomas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11590: nang gi drod dbugs phyi nang du rgyu ba chad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11591: gsang ba'i drod ting nge 'dzin gyi thun mtshams dang bral te /
NK078(tshu)001:11592: gong du bstan pa'i phyi nang gsang ba'i drod kyi
NK078(tshu)001:11593: bye brag ma lus pa kun dang gsal brtan du
NK078(tshu)001:11595: bcu gcig pa rtags la gzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11599: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rtags chen po ni ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:11600: 'dzin goms shing mthar phyin pa'i tshe smrig rgyu du
NK078(tshu)001:11601: ba srin bu me khyer mar me nyi ma lta
NK078(tshu)001:11602: bu'i mtshan ma lnga po de dngosa su mthong ba
NK078(tshu)001:11603: dang de yanga / rlung gi mtshan ma rnam lnga yang /
NK078(tshu)001:11604: du ba lta bu'i lang long dang //
NK078(tshu)001:11605: smig rgyu lta bu gya gyu dang //
NK078(tshu)001:11606: srin me lta bu dmar 'phro dang //
NK078(tshu)001:11607: mar me lta bu dmar skams gsal //
NK078(tshu)001:11608: mkha' la nyi shar lta bur snang //
NK078(tshu)001:11610: yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum gyi gsung yig 'bru thugs phyag mtshan /
NK078(tshu)001:11611: sku yongs rdzogs kyi skye mcheda dngos su mthong ba rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:11612: lha grub pa'am rtags sam mtshan ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:11613: 'bras bu grub pa'i rtags kyi thog ma yin pas dang po'i rtags zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11616: de ting kun ting gnyis pas dmigsa pa rgya che ba'i phyag rgya gcig pa'i mngon shes kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:11617: ting nge 'dzin snga ma gnyis las 'dir grangs mang bas nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11618: yul rgya che ba dang gnyis kyi bla na med de /
NK078(tshu)001:11619: gzhan yang sgo lnga'i dbang po re res yul lnga
NK078(tshu)001:11620: lnga gcod nus pas nyi shu rtsa lnga'i mngon shes
NK078(tshu)001:11621: rnams kyang / phyag rgya gcig pa'i skab 'dir g.yo thob tsam du 'byung bar the tshom med do //
NK078(tshu)001:11624: lus kyi rtags rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul /
NK078(tshu)001:11625: ngag gi rtags kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul /
NK078(tshu)001:11626: sems kyi rtags rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul mthu'i rtags byin rlabs rnams kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:11628: de rnams kyang g.yo thob tsam du 'byung bar byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:11629: bzhi pa rtags sngar bas gsal zhing brtan par 'byung tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:11631: drod rtags de dag las gzhan yang phyi nang gi rtags dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11633: bdud kyi spyod yul la sogs pa kun sngon du
NK078(tshu)001:11634: song ba de ting snying rje gnyis pas phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:11635: gcig pa'i skabs 'dir ngo bo gsal zhing brtan pa
NK078(tshu)001:11637: de rgyu ci las byung zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:11638: ting nge 'dzin gong ma gnyis bden pa kha phral nas bsgom pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:11639: 'dir phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byora bden pa dbyer
NK078(tshu)001:11640: med bsgom pa de ni lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:11641: goms pa'i stobs kyis thob pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:11642: bcu gnyis pa mtshan ma rmi lam la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:11644: dang po legs nyes gsal brtan du 'byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11646: spyod lam bzhi las nyal ba gnyid kyi rmi lam
NK078(tshu)001:11647: du lam sgrub pa legs pa'i yon tan dang nyes
NK078(tshu)001:11648: pa'i skyon 'byung ba'i bye brag kun /
NK078(tshu)001:11649: lam snga ma gnyis bas 'dir gsal bar 'byung zhing sngar bas kyang shin tu brtana par 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11650: gnyis pa grub pa'i rtags kyis rmi ltas bcu bzhi 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11652: zhi khro gang yin gyi lha'i bsam gtan ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:11653: 'dzin la gnas shing sngags la 'bad pas bzlas pa
NK078(tshu)001:11654: byas pa yis / sgrub pa pos ni grub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11655: rmi ltas bcu bzhi po 'di dag ni rtags su
NK078(tshu)001:11656: byas pa yis / mthong ba ste / ji ltar mthong zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:11658: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11659: sangs rgyas kyi mthu dang mtshungs shing mnyam par mthong
NK078(tshu)001:11661: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas longsa spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dpes brgyan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11662: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid dang tha dad med pa
NK078(tshu)001:11663: ni dus myur du thob par 'dug snyam du mthong
NK078(tshu)001:11665: byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11666: brgya byin la sogs pa khams gsum na gnas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:11667: rnal 'byor pa bdag la mchod pa byas par rnal
NK078(tshu)001:11668: 'byor pa des rang gi rmi lam na mthong ngo
NK078(tshu)001:11670: gnyis med kyi ye shes chen po 'od dang 'dra
NK078(tshu)001:11671: ba'i gzugs skur snang ba'i sangsa rgyas dang byang chub
NK078(tshu)001:11672: sems dpa' yis gzugs la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon
NK078(tshu)001:11673: tan lnga po rnams kyis dus rtag tu bdag la
NK078(tshu)001:11674: mchod pa byas pa mthong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11676: rdo rje sems dpa'i gzugs chen po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11677: grags chen phyag na rdo rje'i gzugs mchog dag tu
NK078(tshu)001:11678: gnyid log pa'i rmi lam dag na rnal 'byor pa
NK078(tshu)001:11679: rang gis gzugs lha de dag tu mthong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11681: gragsa chen phyag na rdo rje gsang ba'i bdag po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11682: byang chub sems dpa' 'khor lo bsnams par can sgrib pa rnal sel dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11683: sangs rgyas chen po rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa rnams kyis bdag la phyag 'tshal ba'i /
NK078(tshu)001:11684: rmi lam 'di 'drara sgrub pa pos mthong bar gyur pa de ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11687: sems thugs kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i mthu las skyes pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:11689: rin po che dang dar gyi rgyan bcu gsum brgyan
NK078(tshu)001:11690: rnams thams cad kyis yongs su rdzogs par brgyan pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11691: lha'i bu mo yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11692: mi'i khye'u dang bu mo yid du 'ong ba dag
NK078(tshu)001:11693: gis bdag la 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa byed
NK078(tshu)001:11694: pa mthong na / rtags de ni dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur ba'i ltas yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:11696: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cada rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:11697: rang rang gi zhing na gnas pa dag bdag gis nges par mthong ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11698: rgyal ba de dag bdag la thugs ni shin tu dgyes par gyur nas kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:11699: chos kyi mdzod po ti dang glegs bam la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:11700: yid du 'ong ba'i gtam la sogs bdag la snang
NK078(tshu)001:11702: chos kyi 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i mthu dang sprul sku thub pa lta bu la /
NK078(tshu)001:11703: 'khor semsa can kun gyis yongs su bskor nas chos ston pa mthong ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11704: rnal 'byor pa lha'i bsam gtan lus ngag yid gsum
NK078(tshu)001:11705: rdo rje gsum la dbyer mi phyed par gnas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11706: dam tshig las mi 'da' ba'i sbyor bas mthong bar
NK078(tshu)001:11708: nyams dga' ba'i sa phyogs sna tshogs pa kun bdag
NK078(tshu)001:11709: gis mthong ba ni skyeda mo'i tshal la lha'i bu
NK078(tshu)001:11710: mo la sogs pas brgyan pa na /
NK078(tshu)001:11711: bdag nyid la sangs rgyas kun gyis byin gyis brlabs par mthong ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11712: yi dam lha'i bsam gtan gyi ting nge 'dzin las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig can gyis mthong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11714: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub semsa dpa' mang
NK078(tshu)001:11715: po yis rnam 'byor pa yi dam gyi lha bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:11716: pa de la ni mngona sum par dbang bskur ba
NK078(tshu)001:11717: mthong ba dang / bcu gnyis pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11718: rig 'dzin gyi rgyal po chen po mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin pa de yis /
NK078(tshu)001:11719: bdag nyid la mchod pa byas par rnal 'byor pa des mthong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:11720: lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:11721: gsum du bsgom pa las byung ba'i yon tan sna
NK078(tshu)001:11722: tshogs pa'i rmi lam yang dag par gsal bas skyon
NK078(tshu)001:11723: gyi dri ma med pa de mthong ba na /
NK078(tshu)001:11724: yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gsum
NK078(tshu)001:11725: bsgom pa las skyes pa'i 'bras bu bla na med
NK078(tshu)001:11729: khyi'i sbyor ba byed pa la sogs pa'i khong nas
NK078(tshu)001:11730: phag dang stag la sogs pa gcan gzan gzhan gyis
NK078(tshu)001:11731: sbyor ba byed pa rnal 'byor pa rdo rje 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:11732: pas mthong bar gyur na ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11733: rigs ngan pa ltar mthong yang blang dor med par
NK078(tshu)001:11734: rtog pa'i blo dang ldan pa rdo rje sems dpa'
NK078(tshu)001:11735: yi ngo bor / rang gi sems kyi ngo bo
NK078(tshu)001:11736: gzhi ye nas gnas pa de ni 'bras bu'i rdo
NK078(tshu)001:11739: gsung yi ge dang thugs dang sku'i phyag rgya rnam
NK078(tshu)001:11740: gnyis kyi skye mched gsum mthong bar 'byung ba'ang sems
NK078(tshu)001:11741: kyi gnas lugs 'grub pa gong gi tshul de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:11742: no // bcu gsum pa phan yon la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11743: lha bsgom pa'i phan yon dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11744: ma bsgom pa'i skyon gyi ngos nas brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11745: zhal mthong bas mos shing bsgrub pa'i phan yon no //
NK078(tshu)001:11748: dang po tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11750: rnam 'byor pas yi dam lha'i sku ni gsal la ma 'gag par bsgomsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:11751: rgyu bsod namsa kyi tshogs chen po rdzogs nas gzugs sku thob par 'gyur la /
NK078(tshu)001:11752: lha de nyid chu zla'i tshul du snang la rang bzhin med par shes par gyur na /
NK078(tshu)001:11753: 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs chen po gnyis rdzogs te chos sku thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11754: gnyis pa yon tan chung yang bsgrub na 'grub pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:11756: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyi sgo gsum yi dam
NK078(tshu)001:11757: lha'i sku gsung thugs dang tha dad med par mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:11759: de las gzhan pa'i rigs pa'i gnas lnga la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:11760: pa mkhas pa'i yon tan chung yang 'bras bu yi
NK078(tshu)001:11761: dam lha ni 'grub par 'gyur ba la the tshom
NK078(tshu)001:11762: med do // de yang ye gdod ma nas lha
NK078(tshu)001:11763: dang bdag gnyis ngo bo dbyer med pas mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:11765: yi dam gyi lha nyid yin pa nyid du ni dus rtag tu bsgom par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11766: gsum pa lha gcig bsgom pas 'bras bu kun thob pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:11768: de ltar bdag nyid yi dam gyi lha dang mnyam par sbyor bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:11769: rgyal ba thams cad gcig dang tha dad las grol ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:11770: bde bar gshegs pa kun dang mnyam par sbyor bar 'gyur basa /
NK078(tshu)001:11771: de'i phyir rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kuna dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i 'bras bu thob par 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:11772: des na bdag nyid rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun dang
NK078(tshu)001:11773: mnyam par sbyor ba'i phyir mthar thug /rgyal ba'i sku
NK078(tshu)001:11774: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11775: ye shes lnga yongs su rdzogs shing 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11776: gnyis pa ma bsgoms pa'i skyon gyi ngos nas brtson 'grus gyis shig pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:11778: dang po lha ma bsgom pa'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11780: yid dam lha'i mtshan nyida ni gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:11781: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:11782: kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag po yin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11783: phyir / yi dam gyi lha spangs nas gzhan dge
NK078(tshu)001:11784: ba ci spyad kyang 'dod pa'i don 'bras bu med
NK078(tshu)001:11785: phyir / par 'gyur te / dper na sman pa
NK078(tshu)001:11786: mkhas pa bor ba'i nad pa mi mkhas pas gso
NK078(tshu)001:11788: gnyis pa brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa la
NK078(tshu)001:11789: phyir / par 'gyur te / ba dang 'dra'o // gsum ste / bgrang /
NK078(tshu)001:11790: dang po brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11792: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig tshul bzhin du bsrung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11793: skyon bcu spangs te sngags bzlas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11794: yi dam gyi lha'i sku phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad
NK078(tshu)001:11795: par dam tshig las chos sku phyag rgya chen po
NK078(tshu)001:11796: dang bzhi bsgom pa rnams la sgo gsum gyis brtson
NK078(tshu)001:11797: 'grus che bar bya zhing blo brtan para byas la
NK078(tshu)001:11798: bzung ngo // gal te rnal 'byor pa lha'i bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:11799: bzlas la brtson 'grus chung bar gyur na skyon ci
NK078(tshu)001:11800: bzung ngo // yod ce na / 'dod pa'i 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:11801: bu mi 'gruba cing slar yang rdo rje'i dmyal ba
NK078(tshu)001:11802: la sogs par ltung bas nyes shin tu yang che
NK078(tshu)001:11803: bzung ngo // yod ce na / bar gsungs te / rtsa rgyud las /
NK078(tshu)001:11804: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:11806: gnyis pa gal te nan tan ma byas pa'i skyon gyi dpe don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11809: ral kha 'gyed pa'i tshe ral gri'i so la bag zon gyi nan tan du dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11810: yu ba nas legsa par ma bzung na skyon ni
NK078(tshu)001:11811: rang gi lag pa gcod par 'gyur ba de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:11812: du lha bsgom zhing sngags bzla ba la nan tan
NK078(tshu)001:11813: med pa'i gsang sngags las byas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:11814: tshe 'dir phung ba'am yang na phyi mar bsgrub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:11815: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub med par
NK078(tshu)001:11816: 'gyur ro // gsum pa brtson 'grus med pa'i skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:11818: skyon 'dug pa de bas lha'i bsgom bzlas la bar chad cing brtson 'grus med par gyur na /
NK078(tshu)001:11819: dpera na sa bon mes tshig pa btab pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:11820: 'bras bu myu gu 'byung bar 'dod pa dang 'dra ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11821: tshe 'dir ched du gnyir nas bsgrub par bya ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:11822: 'bras bu mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub gang
NK078(tshu)001:11824: phyi mar mi khoms pa'i gnas brgyad la sogs pa 'khor bar kha brgyud par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11825: gsum pa zhal mthong bas mos shing sgrub pa'i phan yon no //
NK078(tshu)001:11827: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i rnam 'byor pa gang
NK078(tshu)001:11828: zhig gis yi dam lha'i zhal mthong zhing mos pa
NK078(tshu)001:11829: byas pa yis / de la bsnyena cing bkur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11830: mchod pa byas pa'i bsod namsa kyi sa mi dge ba bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11831: mtshams med pa lnga ste bco lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:11833: lci ba bzhi log pa brgyad la sogs pa las ngan sgrib pa thams cad sbyangsa te /
NK078(tshu)001:11834: rnam smin nam tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyi sa la sbyor bar 'gyur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11835: bcu bzhi pa 'das ka ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11837: phyag rgya gcig pa'i gang zag gang gisa mi rtag ste tshe 'pho ba'i dus mthong na yang /
