NK078(tshu)001:11838: yi dam lha'i sku'i phyag rgya ma nyams par ting nge 'dzin gsal bar yid la bzung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11839: sngar mi dge ba'i las bsags pa'i las kyis ngan
NK078(tshu)001:11840: song la sogs pa'i 'khor bar mi 'khora bar rang
NK078(tshu)001:11841: nyid kyi gang 'dod pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams
NK078(tshu)001:11843: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du rang yi dam gyi sku bsam la /
NK078(tshu)001:11844: 'og nas yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor gyis stobs kyis btegs las /
NK078(tshu)001:11845: a yam si ti dzah a s+pha ra na phatahcesa brjod de /
NK078(tshu)001:11846: shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba /
NK078(tshu)001:11847: nub phyogs bde ba can la sogs pa rang gi gang mos kyi gnas su bskul bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11848: bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11850: dang po gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin la sbyor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11852: nyams mthar phyin cing blo che na thod rgal gyi
NK078(tshu)001:11853: dbang du rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa
NK078(tshu)001:11855: nyams mthar ma phyin cing blo chung bas na 'on te rnam smin du tshe 'dir ma gyur na'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:11857: blo rtsal dang brtson pa che chung gi rim pa yisa /
NK078(tshu)001:11858: rnam smin rig 'dzin de nyid bar do'am phyi ma'am
NK078(tshu)001:11859: skye ba lan grangs gzhan bdun tshun chad la thob
NK078(tshu)001:11860: bar 'gyur ro // nyams mthar phyin cing /
NK078(tshu)001:11862: brtson pa rab yin na tshe la dbang ba'i rig
NK078(tshu)001:11863: 'dzin 'ang tshe phyi ma la spros pa dang tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:11865: gzhan skye ba lan grangs bdun tshun chad la tshe dbang thob par nges so //
NK078(tshu)001:11866: de yang phyag rgya gcig pa 'di'i lam ma nor
NK078(tshu)001:11867: bar tshul bzhin du nyams su blang ba'i 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:11868: ni / phyogs mthun du gzugs sku gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11869: thun mong du lha mi'i lus khyad par can thob pa ni spyi tsam yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:11870: bye brag tu nye sbyor ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11871: blo rtsal dang brtson pa che ba thod rgal du rnam smin rig 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11872: blo rtsal dang brtson pa chung na mthar chags su phyag rgya spros bcas rtsol med du 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11873: de ltar na lam thod rgal dang mthar chags kyi khyad gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:11874: bu chung skas la 'dzegs pa bzhin lam lnga rim
NK078(tshu)001:11875: pa krig krig khrigs chags su bsgrod pa ni mthar
NK078(tshu)001:11877: gyad stobs po ches skas la 'dzegs pa bzhin chol
NK078(tshu)001:11878: bu'am 'dor len gyi tshul du la la bor zhing
NK078(tshu)001:11879: bgrod pa ni thod rgal zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11880: de yang thod rgal sgrub byed kyi gtan tshig la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11882: go ba dang rgyu mtshan no //
NK078(tshu)001:11883: dang po la'ang zag bcas phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11884: zag med mthong sgom gnyis so //
NK078(tshu)001:11888: khyung dang seng+ge ji bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:11889: spros tshogs skabs na smos ci dgos //
NK078(tshu)001:11892: gcig dang du ma'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK078(tshu)001:11896: phyag rgya gcig pa nas mthong sgom gnyis su thod rgal ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11898: rnam smin rig la the tshom med //
NK078(tshu)001:11900: gnyis pa spros pa nas de gnyis la sbyor ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11902: las ngan lam zhen rgyun bcad nas //
NK078(tshu)001:11903: bar ma'am phyi mar gnyis sbyor 'dzin //
NK078(tshu)001:11905: tshe dbang la sbyor ba'ang srid pa tsam ngos bzung du rung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11907: bzhi bcu gnyis dang stong sogs slob pa ste //
NK078(tshu)001:11908: goms nas tshe yi rig 'dzin du //
NK078(tshu)001:11909: sbyor nas mngon par sangs rgyas tshul //
NK078(tshu)001:11911: gnyis pa zag med nas 'byung ba la gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:11912: dang po tshe dbang nas 'byung ba'i thod rgal la chung ngu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11913: sgom lam bar do nas mthar lam la sbyor te /
NK078(tshu)001:11915: rgya dor gcig char mthar grol ba //
NK078(tshu)001:11917: chen po ni sgom lam mthar lam gnyis ka bor nas sangs rgyas kyi sar sbyor te /
NK078(tshu)001:11919: kha cig dbang bsgyur rigs nyid nas //
NK078(tshu)001:11920: bcu drug rgyun gyi sku lnga rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:11922: gnyis pa phyag rgya chen po nas mthar lam bor nas sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor te /
NK078(tshu)001:11924: kha gcig phyag rgya chen po nas bla ma kun tu bzang por sbyor /
NK078(tshu)001:11928: grangs kyi 'og ma nas don gyi gong ma la sbyar ba zhig yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:11929: gsum pa 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11930: blo ngang gis che dang gcig /lam bar nas bor blang du bgrod du yod pa dang gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:11931: snang stong dbyer med bsgom nus pa dang gsum gzhi gcig tu 'tshogs na 'byung /
NK078(tshu)001:11932: de las gzhan du mi 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:11934: de ting kun ting gnyis ni /
NK078(tshu)001:11935: lam gong ma phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis tshogs sgrub dang gsum bor du yod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:11936: snang stong dbyer med sgom pa'i lam pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11937: tshogs sgrub blo che shos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11938: lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis ngang gis blo che ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11939: snang stong dbyer med bsgom nus kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:11940: lam bar nas bor du med pa'i phyir mi 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:11942: snang stong dbyer med sgom nus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11943: lam bar nas sgom lam mthar lam gnyis bor rgyu yod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:11944: blo ngang gis chung ba'i phyir mi 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:11945: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11947: rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba rnams kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:11948: yi dam lha'i sku'i phyag rgya chen po rang rig
NK078(tshu)001:11949: pas mngon sum du gsal bar rdzogs par 'gyur zhing
NK078(tshu)001:11950: / sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ba'i tshad
NK078(tshu)001:11951: yul gyis mi 'phrog pa la brtan pa thob nas
NK078(tshu)001:11952: yid gnyis dang the tshom med par bsgrub pa byas
NK078(tshu)001:11953: / na / mthar thug gi 'bras bu rgyal ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:11954: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dngos grub chen
NK078(tshu)001:11955: po 'bar ba yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi
NK078(tshu)001:11957: gsum pa ma thob kyang ngan song dang theg dman du ltung bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:11959: phyag rgya gcig pa 'di ltar bsgom shing bsgrub par byas na /
NK078(tshu)001:11960: 'bras bu tshe 'di dang bar dor mngon du ma gyur yang /
NK078(tshu)001:11961: tshe rabs sam skye ba brgyud pa thams cad du
NK078(tshu)001:11962: lha dang mi'i lus rnam par dag pa dbang po
NK078(tshu)001:11964: mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa thob nas bdag gzhan gyi sdug bsngal sel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11965: bde gshegs sprul pa'i sku 'jig rten du 'byung ba
NK078(tshu)001:11966: dang gnas dang dus kyis mi bkol zhing 'phrad pa
NK078(tshu)001:11967: dang / 'phrad nas kyang mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dman par 'jug par mi 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:11968: theg pa mchog gsang sngags bla na med pa'i byang
NK078(tshu)001:11969: chub las phyir mi ldog pa'i gzungs la zhugs pa
NK078(tshu)001:11970: yin no // de lta bu'i yon tan yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:11971: de bas na phyag rgya gcig pa'i lam 'di nyid
NK078(tshu)001:11972: dang dus skabs kun tu sbyar bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:11975: don bden pa dbyer med rtags yi dam lha'i sku
NK078(tshu)001:11976: phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa ston
NK078(tshu)001:11977: par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:11978: mtshams dang ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyi na le'u ste /
NK078(tshu)001:11979: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:11980: yas bgrang lnga pa'i don du gada'o ////le'u drug pa spros bcas kyi rnal 'byor la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:11982: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11984: rang gi yi dam gyi lha zhi khro phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:11985: gcig pa la lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK078(tshu)001:11987: lha gcig du mar spros pa'i tshul du bsgom pa
NK078(tshu)001:11988: phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i rnal 'byor ting
NK078(tshu)001:11989: nge 'dzin gyi rim pa bshad par bya ba ni
NK078(tshu)001:11990: 'di lta ste / gnyis pa gzhung don la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:11992: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:11994: phyag rgya spros bcas sgom pa'i gzhi bo lus mdor bstan pa yang /
NK078(tshu)001:11995: sngar de ting gi skabs su don bco lnga bshad
NK078(tshu)001:11996: pa de lta bur 'dir yang don bco lnga bzhag
NK078(tshu)001:11997: pas de rnam par dgrol ba'i phyir yan lag rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:11999: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la bco lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12011: rmi ltas kyi mtshan ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12015: dang po sngon du bya ba la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12017: dang po lam snga ma la goms pa'i rten bzhengs shing rab gnas bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12019: de ting kun ting phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:12020: dang rnam pa gsum phyag rgya spros pa'i sngon du
NK078(tshu)001:12022: sa dang gser dngul rwa shing la sogs pa rnams
NK078(tshu)001:12023: la lha'i sku'i phyag rgya byas te ras shog bu
NK078(tshu)001:12025: thang la rdul tshon te ri mo'i rgyu bzhi'am /
NK078(tshu)001:12026: rwa shing rus pa la 'bur du bskos pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:12027: rin po che la lugs su blugs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12028: 'jim pa las 'der so byas pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12029: de ltar las dang bya ba'i lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan
NK078(tshu)001:12030: gyi dkyil 'khor ni sgrub pa'i khang bu dngosa su
NK078(tshu)001:12031: bya zhing de la rab gnas byas pas ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:12033: ldan pa nye bar brten par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12034: gnyis pa mchod rdzas bshams shing cha rkyen bsdu ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12036: ma h+aa ba ling ta gtor ma chen po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12037: a mri ta bdud rtsi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12039: phyi'i mchod pa rnam lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12040: nang gi mchod pa gsum po rnams dgram /
NK078(tshu)001:12041: rola mo'i mchod pa la sogs mchod pa'i cha rkyen rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12042: gzhan yang mchod pa'i yo byad ci ltar bsdu bar 'os pa rnams gzhung bzhin bsdu bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12043: gsum pa sngon 'gro'i las kyi rim pa bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12045: dang po bsrung ba'i 'khor lo khro bo bcus phyogs mtshams bcingas /
NK078(tshu)001:12046: de nas yan lag brgyad pa nas bzung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12048: byin dbab yan chad kyi rim pa rdzogs par byas
NK078(tshu)001:12049: nas bdag nyid las kyi lha bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'am
NK078(tshu)001:12050: / yi dam ganga yin gyi rnal 'byor dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:12051: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis phyi nang gi mchod rdzas
NK078(tshu)001:12052: rnams tshul bzhin du byin gyis brlabs par byas la
NK078(tshu)001:12053: de yang thog mar bdud rtsi'i chus bsang ba /
NK078(tshu)001:12055: mchod pa rnams byin gyis brlabs la stan la 'dug go //
NK078(tshu)001:12056: gnyis pa dgos ched la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12058: dang po bdag don gyi dgos ched bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12060: lha'i sku du mar gsal bar byas pas bsod nams kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs par byas shing /
NK078(tshu)001:12061: phyi nang gi spyod yul phung po khams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12062: skye mched rnams lha yi dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs pa'i dgos ched yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12063: 'bras bu yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa brgyud nas mthar dbyung bar bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12064: tshom bu tshogs sgrub la spros pa mthar phyin pa'i dus kyi bsgrub dgos pa'i phyir bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12065: gnyis pa gzhan gyi dgos ched brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12067: dbang gi las dgra bgegs dang gzung ma la sogs dgug pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12068: drang po'i las dgra bgegs gling khams gzhan du btang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12069: dbang gi las 'byung ba'i kha bcing ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12070: gzhan gyis byad du bcug pa dgrol ba dang rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:12071: pa'i las sri'u lo tog nad pa la sogs gso
NK078(tshu)001:12072: ba dang / drag po'i las dgra bgegs bsad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12073: gzhan gyi phyogs pham par bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12074: rgyas pa'i las bdag gi phyogs rgyal bar bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:12075: rnam phyag rgya spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'dis 'grub
NK078(tshu)001:12077: lam pa gang dag spros pa'i gdul bya ci snyed pa thams cad kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:12078: phyag rgya spros pa bsgom pa'i phrin las kyis yang dag pa'i sa la 'don pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:12079: yang na gong gi dgug btang gi las brgyad ni bzhir 'dus te /
NK078(tshu)001:12083: pham bsad gnyis drag po'i las yin par lce ston gyis gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:12084: gsum pa sgom thabs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12085: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12086: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstim pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12087: de la mchod cing phrin las kyi rim pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12090: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12092: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor la brtan pa thob nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12093: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa'ang zhi khro rnam pa gnyis yod pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12095: phyag rgya gcig pa dang rjes su mthun par zhi ba spros bcas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12096: khro bo'i spros bcas gnyis ston to //
NK078(tshu)001:12097: zhi khro de gnyis gang rung re re'ang rim cig char gyi tshul gnyis kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:12098: gdul bya'i blo che chung gi rim pa dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:12099: par rim cig char gang 'tshams su bsgom par ston
NK078(tshu)001:12100: pa yin no // gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12101: zhi ba la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12107: mdor bstan gyi snga ma zhi ba spros pa rang
NK078(tshu)001:12108: la'ang rim gyis pa dang cig char ba gnyis so
NK078(tshu)001:12109: // gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12111: dang po cig car ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12113: mdor bstan la gnyis su phye bas phyi ma cig
NK078(tshu)001:12114: char ba'ang phyag rgya gcig pa bzhin du spros pa
NK078(tshu)001:12115: la cig char du 'jug pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12116: nam mkha'i nyi zla dang gza' skar thams cad dus
NK078(tshu)001:12117: gcig tu chu dkyil rnyogs ma dwangsa par gzugs brnyan
NK078(tshu)001:12118: ma 'dres par gsal zhing 'char ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:12119: phyag rgya spros pa'i lha'i sku gsal ba skad cig ma gcig la 'od du 'abra bar sgom pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:12120: snying po h'u badz+ra d+h+rika la sogs pa brjod pa
NK078(tshu)001:12121: tsam gyis zhi ba'i 'khor lo lha'i dkyil 'khor rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:12122: bsdus 'bring gsum yongs su rdzogs pa gsal bar shar
NK078(tshu)001:12123: ba'o // gnyis pa rim gyis pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12125: dang po ngo bo spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12127: rim gyis pa de mdor bstan gyi sngon du bstan
NK078(tshu)001:12128: pa ni phyag rgya gcig pa'i rim gyis pa bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:12129: du / 'dir spros bcas la rim gyis 'jug pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12130: snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor du lta bas mthong ba
NK078(tshu)001:12131: dang lam snga ma phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:12132: la goms pa'i stobs kyis phyag rgya spros pa'i ting
NK078(tshu)001:12133: nge 'dzin thob pa las dper na shes bya gcig
NK078(tshu)001:12134: shes kyang du ma la slob pa'i tshul du /
NK078(tshu)001:12135: phyag rgya spros pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du mar shar
NK078(tshu)001:12136: ba yang rnal 'byor pa gcig gis rig par gsal
NK078(tshu)001:12137: bar byed pa'ang / gnyis pa dbye bas bye brag tu bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12141: khro bor ma bsgyur bar ma bcos rnal ma zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK078(tshu)001:12142: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khora lo spros pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12145: zhal phyag spros pa la bslab pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12146: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12148: dang po dkyil 'khor spros pa la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12150: dang po dkyil 'khor spros pa la gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:12151: bsdus pa la lha rigs lnga yab yum bcu sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:12152: 'bring po la gzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:12153: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor la pho brang gi lha lnga bcu /
NK078(tshu)001:12154: sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug kun bzang yab yum gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:12155: thub pa drug /sgo ba yab yum brgyad de brgyad cu rtsa gnyis rnams la rim par slob bo //
NK078(tshu)001:12156: gnyis pa tshom bu spros pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12158: dang po tshom bu gcig pa la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12160: mdor bstan gyi gnyis pa tshom bu spros pa la gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:12161: dang po gcig pa la bslab pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12162: rnal 'byor pa bdag cag gtso bo mi skyod pa
NK078(tshu)001:12163: yab yum gnyis su gsal bar gnas pa'i gzhal yas
NK078(tshu)001:12164: khang / 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba mu khyud
NK078(tshu)001:12165: gru chad sgo btod du gsal bar sgom par byas
NK078(tshu)001:12166: te gdan lnga brtsegs dang ldan pa'i dbus kyi lte
NK078(tshu)001:12167: ba na rigs kyi bdag po rdo rje sems dpa'
NK078(tshu)001:12169: de la rdo rje rigs kyi sems dpa' ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12170: shar du rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12172: lhor rdo rje'i rin chen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12174: nub tu rdo rje chos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12176: byang du rdo rje las dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12178: de ltar yab yum brgyad dang phyogs bzhi'i khro bo
NK078(tshu)001:12179: yab yum brgyad kyis bskor bas na lha bco brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:12180: do // gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12182: de ltar tshom bu gcig pa la blo brtan pa
NK078(tshu)001:12183: thob nas mdun du sku'i rigs rnam par snang mdzad
NK078(tshu)001:12184: yab yum la / shar du rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12186: lhor rdo rje rgyal po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12188: nub tu rdo rje chags pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12190: byang du rdo rje legs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12191: rdo rje phreng ma ste bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12192: rgyaba tu gsung gi rigs snang ba mtha' yas yab yum la /
NK078(tshu)001:12193: shar du rdo rje chos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12195: lhor rdo rje rnon po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12197: nub tu rdo rje rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12199: byang du rdo rje smra ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12200: rdo rje gsal bkra ma ste bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12201: thugs kar rdor sems la yab yum bcu ste 'khor lo'i pho brang du lha sum cu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12202: phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo yab yum bcu drug ste
NK078(tshu)001:12203: lha zhe drug rdzogs par bsgom pa la yi ge
NK078(tshu)001:12204: +aahmh'u 'bru gsum sku gsung thugs kyi lha bskyed pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:12205: barda'o // lha grangs nyung ting nge 'dzin blo stobs chung ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:12206: mi la lus ngag yid gsum yod pa'i dbang du
NK078(tshu)001:12207: tshom bu gsum pa'i lha zhe drug gi ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:12208: 'dzin la shin tu goms shing 'dris par bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:12210: gsum pa tshom bu lnga pa la bslab pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12212: de ltar tshom bu gsum pa la blo brtan pa thob nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12213: gtso bo'i zhal shar du gzigs ba'i g.yas lho'i rtsibs
NK078(tshu)001:12214: steng du yon tan gyi rigs rin 'byung yab yum
NK078(tshu)001:12215: la / shar du rdo rje rin chen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12217: lhor rdo rje gzi brjid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12219: nub tu rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12221: byang du rdo rje bzhad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12222: rdo rje bde ba ma ste yab yum bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12223: g.yon byang gi rtsibs nyid du phrin las kyi rigs don grub yab yum la /
NK078(tshu)001:12224: shar du rdo rje las dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12226: lhor rdo rje bsrung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12228: nub tu rdo rje gnod sbyin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12230: byang du rdo rje khu tshur dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12231: rdo rje 'beb ma ste yab yum bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12232: de ltar yon tan phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis bzhag pas pho brang gi lnga bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12233: phyogs mtshams steng 'og gi khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste lha bdun bcu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12234: gsum pa bas lnga pa ting nge 'dzin stobs che bas sam /
NK078(tshu)001:12235: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i don rnal
NK078(tshu)001:12236: ma la blo 'byor ba'i lha'i dbang du tshom bu
NK078(tshu)001:12237: lnga ste / de la shin tu 'dris shing goms
NK078(tshu)001:12238: nas mthar phyin pa'i dus na tshogs sgrub pa sbyor
NK078(tshu)001:12239: lnga ste / ro // de yang dkyil 'khor spros
NK078(tshu)001:12240: pa ni bsgom bya'i ngos nas btag /tshom bu spros
NK078(tshu)001:12241: pa ni sgom byed kyi cha rkyen las btag /
NK078(tshu)001:12242: 'og gi rnam grangs dang zhal phyag spros pa ni yan lag la btag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12243: 'o na dkyil 'khor dang tshom bu'i khyad par gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:12244: bsgom bya lha'i khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12245: sgom byed rnal 'byor pa'i khyad par gnyis so //
NK078(tshu)001:12247: pho brang gtso bo'i cha nas smos pa tshom bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12248: de'ang gtso bo rigs gcig gis byas pa tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12249: gtso bo rigs gsum gyis byas pa tshom bu gsum pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12250: gtso bo rigs lngas byas pa tshom bu lnga pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12251: gtso 'khor gnyis ka'i cha nas smos pa dkyil 'khor ro //
NK078(tshu)001:12252: yang rnam grangs yongs rdzogs kyi cha nas dkyil 'khor /
NK078(tshu)001:12253: rnam grangs yongs su ma rdzogs pa tshom bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12254: yang rigs kyi gter kha bye ba dkyil 'khor /
NK078(tshu)001:12257: rang rang gi rigs chung gis rgyas pa'ang yod //
NK078(tshu)001:12258: ma rgyas pa'ang yod pa dkyil 'khor //
NK078(tshu)001:12259: rang rang gi rigs chung gis rgyas pa tshom bu gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:12260: mdor na tshom bu yin tshad la dkyil 'khor gyis khyab cing /
NK078(tshu)001:12261: dkyil 'khor yin tshad la tshom bus ma khyab pas
NK078(tshu)001:12262: khyab che chung gi ngo bo gcig la ldog pa
NK078(tshu)001:12264: sgom byed rnal 'byor pa'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12265: spros pa'i skabs 'dir dkyil 'khor dang tshom bu la sbyang ba mthun la /
NK078(tshu)001:12266: tshogs sgrub kyi skabs su tshom bu la'ang mi gcig gis kun sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12267: mi grangs lha grangs sprad nas sgom pa gnyis ka yod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12268: gal te dkyil 'khor dang tshom bu 'di gnyis gang rung gis chog na /
NK078(tshu)001:12269: gnyis la slob pa la dgos pa med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12270: gnyis ka la slob dgos na /
NK078(tshu)001:12271: spros pa nas thod rgal mi srid par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:12272: blo chung na gnyis ka dgos shing /
NK078(tshu)001:12273: che na dkyil 'khor kho nas sbyor ba srid do //
NK078(tshu)001:12274: gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12276: dang po rtsa ba'i rnam grangs spros pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12278: mdor bstan gyi gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa la bslab pa'i dang po ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12279: rtsa ba'i rnam grangs lha gtso bo thugs rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:12280: sems dpa' yab yum gyi sku nyid du gsal ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:12281: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12283: gsung snang mtha' gtso bor byas pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba /
NK078(tshu)001:12284: de ltar gsum po'i ting nge 'dzin la 'chor ba med par brtan pa thob pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:12287: rigs lnga char rdzogsa par bsgom de yang yaba yum
NK078(tshu)001:12288: zung du 'brel bar sgom pa la blo brtan pa
NK078(tshu)001:12290: rigs lnga poo'i don rang rang gi rigs su spros
NK078(tshu)001:12291: pas sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su byed pa
NK078(tshu)001:12292: pos ma bcos par rang bzhin ngang gis gnas pa
NK078(tshu)001:12293: las / de ltar rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi lhag
NK078(tshu)001:12294: pa ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i dkyila 'khor bsgom mo
NK078(tshu)001:12295: las / // gnyis pa yan lag la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12296: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12297: nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12298: bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12301: dang po bslab pa dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12303: yan lag thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rtsa
NK078(tshu)001:12304: ba'i lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par sgom pa
NK078(tshu)001:12305: yin te / de yang rtsa ba'i lha mi bskyod
NK078(tshu)001:12306: pa yab yum yin pa'i dbang btsan du byas na
NK078(tshu)001:12308: gzhan yan lag gi lha yab nyi shu rtsa bzhi rtsa ba'i lha yab la bkod de /
NK078(tshu)001:12309: lag pa g.yas pa la mi bskyod pa /
NK078(tshu)001:12312: rkang pa g.yon pa la snang mtha' /
NK078(tshu)001:12314: mig gi rtsa'i nang du sa snying /
NK078(tshu)001:12315: rna ba'i rtsa'i nang du nam snying /
NK078(tshu)001:12316: sna'i rtsa'i nang du spyan gzigs /
NK078(tshu)001:12317: lce'i rtsa'i nang du phyag rdor /
NK078(tshu)001:12318: mig gi rtsa'i phyi ru byams pa /
NK078(tshu)001:12319: rna ba'i rtsa'i phyi ru sgrib sel /
NK078(tshu)001:12320: sna'i rtsa'i phyi ru kun bzang /
NK078(tshu)001:12322: lag pa g.yas pa'i mthil du gshin rje gshed po /
NK078(tshu)001:12324: rkang pa g.yon pa'i mthil du rta mgrin /
NK078(tshu)001:12326: brang gi rgya mdud lding khang kun tu bzang po /
NK078(tshu)001:12327: mtshogs mar lha'i thub pa lta zur du g.yas su lha ma yin gyi thub pa /
NK078(tshu)001:12329: lte bar byol song gi thub pa /
NK078(tshu)001:12330: mgrin par yi dwags kyi thub pa /
NK078(tshu)001:12331: gsang gnas su dmyal ba'i thub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12332: de ltar rtsa ba'i lha yab la yab nyi shu rtsa bzhi bkod pa de bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:12333: rtsa ba'i lha yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma la yang /
NK078(tshu)001:12336: sngar gyi yab la bkod pa dang mtshungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:12337: de ltar yab nyi shu rtsa bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:12338: yum bco brgyad bkod par byas pas zhe gnyis 'byung yang /
NK078(tshu)001:12339: bdag rtsa ba'i lha mi bskyod pa yab yum la
NK078(tshu)001:12340: bkod pa'i mi bskyod pa yab yum gnyis ma bgrangs
NK078(tshu)001:12341: pas / yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu dang ldan par bsgom pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12342: rags pa'i cha nas bzhag pas thabs kyi lha bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:12343: bcu po de nyid kyi snying gi nang du phra
NK078(tshu)001:12344: ba shes rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' tshon
NK078(tshu)001:12346: 'og gi sku gsung thugs kyi lha rnams la yan
NK078(tshu)001:12347: lag spros pa'i bdag po rigs lnga lngas dbu brgyan
NK078(tshu)001:12348: pa ste / de yang thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu
NK078(tshu)001:12349: rtsa gnyis rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis la bkod
NK078(tshu)001:12350: pa rnams la sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum gsum
NK078(tshu)001:12352: mdor na thabs dang shes rab kyi lha brgyad cu /
NK078(tshu)001:12353: sku gsung thugs kyi lha brgya nyi shu /
NK078(tshu)001:12354: dbu rgyan ye shes kyi lha stong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12355: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12356: 'o na stong dang nyis brgya yod do ce na /
NK078(tshu)001:12357: spar khab ltar rtsa ba'i lha nyis brgya po mi
NK078(tshu)001:12358: bsgrang bar dbu rgyan ye shes kyi lha stong kho
NK078(tshu)001:12359: nar bzhed do // gnyis pa de ji ltar ldan tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:12361: de ltar rtsa ba'i lha stong ste yab rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12362: dpyal te yum nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma gnyis kyi sku phyag rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12363: de la bkod pa'i sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor yang /
NK078(tshu)001:12364: sku ri rab tsam la bzhugs gnas kyi rtsa'i snod
NK078(tshu)001:12365: til 'abru tsam gyi nang du shong ba'i tshul bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:12366: tu / rtsa ba'i lhas mi che yan lag gi
NK078(tshu)001:12367: lha mi chung bar thun mong dang khyad par gyi
NK078(tshu)001:12368: dpe byad brgyad bcu dang mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa
NK078(tshu)001:12369: gnyis kyi rgyan gyis spras par bzhugs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12370: gnyis pa nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12372: de ltar gtso mchog rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la lha stong dang ldan par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12373: chos bya ba mo dang yid byed pa po kun bzang yab yum la stong /
NK078(tshu)001:12374: rgyal ba rigs bzhi yab yum la'ang stong tsho re re bsgom par bya zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:12375: sems dpa' yab yum zung brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:12376: sgo ba yab yum bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12377: de ltar yab yum zung bzhi cu gnyis la stong tsho bcu gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12378: gong gi drug bsnan pas stong tsho bco brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:12379: thub pa drug gi lha'i gnas mal du lha yab
NK078(tshu)001:12380: yum 'khril sbyor du bkod pas stong tsho drug go
NK078(tshu)001:12381: // kun tu bzang mo ma gtogs so //
NK078(tshu)001:12382: de ltar lha stong tsho nyi shu rtsa bzhi po
NK078(tshu)001:12383: rnams kyang 'od zer 'phro zhing gzi brjid 'bar bar
NK078(tshu)001:12384: sgom pa ni / sangs rgyas nyi khri bzhi stong
NK078(tshu)001:12385: gi dkyil 'khor de dag kyang ting nge 'dzin la
NK078(tshu)001:12387: gsum pa bsam yas lhun grub la bslabs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12389: phyi snod phyogs bcu 'jig rten gyi khams ma lus
NK078(tshu)001:12390: pa thams cad lha'i gzhal yas khang du bsgom la
NK078(tshu)001:12391: / nyi zla dang gza' skar thams cad gdan dang rgyan du gsal zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:12392: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor ma lus par bsgom pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12393: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin nyid la slob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12394: bzhi pa zhal phyag spros pa la bslab pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12396: mdor bstan gyi bzhi pa zhal phyag spros bcas ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12397: dang po tshom bu gcig pa la zhal gsum phyag drug tu sgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:12398: de la ting nge 'dzin brtan pa thob nas tshom bu gsum pa la'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:12399: zhal gsum phyag drug sgom pa de bzhin te /
NK078(tshu)001:12400: de la brtan pa thob nas tshom bu lnga pa
NK078(tshu)001:12401: la'ang zhal gsum phyag drug snga ma dang rjes su
NK078(tshu)001:12403: de ltar dkyil 'khor dang rnam grangs spros pa'i skabs
NK078(tshu)001:12404: su lha kun la zhal gsum dang phyag drug rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:12406: gnyis pa khro bo la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12410: gdul bya'i dbang gis zhi ba las khro bor bsgyura ba'i lha'i 'khor lo la'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:12411: dkyil 'khor tshom bu rnam grangs zhal phyag spros pa
NK078(tshu)001:12412: dang bzhi yod pa rnams zhi ba'i skabs su bstan
NK078(tshu)001:12413: pa de bzhin du yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:12414: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12416: dang po dkyil 'khor spros pa la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12418: dang po dkyil 'khor spros pa la gsum las bsdus pa la lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad de /
NK078(tshu)001:12422: sgo ma bzhi ste nyi shu /
NK078(tshu)001:12423: dbang mo nyer brgyad de lnga bcu nga brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:12424: de bsgom zhing goms par gyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12425: 'bring po la de'i steng du khro bo bcu bsnan pas drug cu rtsa brgyad la goms nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12426: khro bo rgyas pa'i dkyila 'khor ni sngon zhi ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:12427: skabs la dkyil 'khor rgyas pa byung ba de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:12428: du 'dir rgyas pa la lha brgya rtsa brgyad yod
NK078(tshu)001:12429: pa yin te / 'og gi rnam grangs spros bcas kyi skabs su gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:12430: gnyis pa tshom bu la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12432: dang po gcig pa dang gsum pa la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12434: dang po tshom bu la gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:12435: gcig pa ni dbus kyi lte ba la thugs badz+ra
NK078(tshu)001:12436: he ru ka la yab yum gzhi bo gnyis kyis
NK078(tshu)001:12437: gtso byas pa la 'khor thugs kyi rigs chung gi
NK078(tshu)001:12438: khro bo yab yum brgyad bsgom pa la brten nas
NK078(tshu)001:12439: / gsum pa ni mdun shar gyi rtsibs steng du sku bud+d+ha khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12440: rgyab nub kyi rtsibs steng du gsung pad+ma khrag 'thunga
NK078(tshu)001:12441: yab yum du gsal bar bsgom pa de la brtan
NK078(tshu)001:12442: pa thob nas 'khor sku gsung gi rigs chung khro
NK078(tshu)001:12443: bo yab yum brgyad dang bcas pa bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:12444: gnyis pa lnga pa la bslab pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12446: de ltar gong gi sku gsung thugs kyi khrag 'thung yab yum la shin tu brtan par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12447: g.yas lho'i rtsibs steng du yon tan rat+na khrag 'thung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12448: g.yon byang gi rtsibs steng du /
NK078(tshu)001:12449: phrin las karma khrag 'thung ste khro bo yab yum
NK078(tshu)001:12450: rnams ting nge 'dzin gyis gsal bar bsgoms nas 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:12451: rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad dang bcas
NK078(tshu)001:12452: pa tshom bu 'khor lo'i lha tshogs rnams rdzogs para
NK078(tshu)001:12453: sgom pa'i nyams rim pa bzhin du tshom bu gcig
NK078(tshu)001:12454: gsum lnga pa'i lha gang sgom gsal bar byas pa
NK078(tshu)001:12455: la ting nge 'dzin ma sun par je gsal du
NK078(tshu)001:12456: gyen la 'phar bar bstan par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12457: yang na tshom bu gcig pa la gtso bor badz+ra
NK078(tshu)001:12458: he ru ka yab yum la rigs chung gi khro
NK078(tshu)001:12462: khro bo yab yum nyi shu dang lha bdun cu don brgyad do //
NK078(tshu)001:12463: gsum pa pho brang gi lha sum cu la /
NK078(tshu)001:12464: 'khor mthun par lha dgu bcu go brgyad do //
NK078(tshu)001:12465: lnga pa la pho brang gi lha lnga bcu /
NK078(tshu)001:12466: 'khor yang mthun par lha brgya dang bco brgyad du 'dod pa yang snang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:12467: gsum pa nam grangs spros pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12469: dang po rtsa ba'i rnam grangs spros pa la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12471: gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa la zhi ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:12472: rjesa su mthun pas 'jigs byed khro bo'i rnam grangs
NK078(tshu)001:12474: gcig ni rdo rje'i rigs badz+ra he ru ka dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12475: gnyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs b+hud+d+ha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12477: bzhi pa rin po che'i rigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12478: lnga pa las kyi rigs karma he ru ka ste
NK078(tshu)001:12479: gtso bo rigs lnga yaba yum bcu ka'i ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:12480: 'dzin gsal bar sgom pa mthar phyin nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12481: de ltar re re la'ang 'khor lo lnga'i rtsibs kyi chas phye bas /
NK078(tshu)001:12482: rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad brgyad kyis
NK078(tshu)001:12483: bskor ba'i pho brang gi lha lnga bcu'i tshom bu
NK078(tshu)001:12484: la gnas ma ma mo brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12485: yul ma phra men ma brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12487: slas ma dbang mo nyer brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12488: h'u chen khro bo bcu ste brgya rtsa brgyad kyi lha gsal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12489: gnyis pa yan lag gi rnam grangs so //
NK078(tshu)001:12491: gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gnyis la yan lag gi lha bkod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12492: rtsa ba'i lha yab kyi lag pa g.yas la badz+ra khrag 'thung /
NK078(tshu)001:12496: dbus na bu d+d+ha khrag 'thung bkod /
NK078(tshu)001:12497: rmig rna ba sna lce'i 'doms rtsa'i nang du /
NK078(tshu)001:12499: phyi la phyi'i ma mo bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:12500: mthil bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:12501: rgal tshigs la dbang mo nyer brgyad bkod do //
NK078(tshu)001:12502: yum gyi yan lag lnga la yab lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:12505: lce dang bzhi'i 'doms rtsa'i nang du phyogs kyis phra men bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:12506: phyi la mtshams kyi phra men bzhi bkod pa'i thabs
NK078(tshu)001:12507: kyi lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyada po de la shes
NK078(tshu)001:12508: rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' re re /
NK078(tshu)001:12509: sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum gsum ste nga brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:12510: pa cha lnga'i grangs ni nyis brgya dang dgu bcu'i
NK078(tshu)001:12511: lha rnams kyi yan lag tu ldan pa de rnams
NK078(tshu)001:12512: la dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga ste stong dang
NK078(tshu)001:12514: de ltar lus la bkod pa'i lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la brtsis pas /
NK078(tshu)001:12515: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu yod do
NK078(tshu)001:12516: ces bla ma gtsang pa byis ston gyis gsungs so
NK078(tshu)001:12517: // bzhi pa zhal phyag la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12519: dang po zhal phyag spros pa la bslab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12521: dang po khro bo zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:12522: de la brten nas zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK078(tshu)001:12523: de la brten nas dbu dgu dang phyag bco brgyad lha kun dang ldan par sgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12524: de nas dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:12525: dbu dgu brgya phyag stong brgyad brgya /
NK078(tshu)001:12526: de nas zhal phyag grangs med pa'i bar du slob par byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12527: gnyis pa de lam pa gang gi spyod yul yin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12529: zhal phyag gi rnam grangs de dag gang zag rim
NK078(tshu)001:12530: gyis pas slob pa'i thabs su brjod kyi dngos kyi
NK078(tshu)001:12531: spyod yul ni / tshogs lam phyag rgya gcig spros la zhal gsum phyag drug dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12532: sbyor lam du dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12533: mthong lam du dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag zhe gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12534: sgom lam du dbu dgu brgya phyag stong brgyad brgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12535: zhal phyag grangs med par sgom pa de mthar lam
NK078(tshu)001:12536: lhun grub kyi spyod yul yin pa ltar rim par
NK078(tshu)001:12537: ldan pa'o // gnyis pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyon drangs shing bstim pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12539: gong du bstan pa de ltar rim cig car gyi
NK078(tshu)001:12540: bsgom thabs gnyis dang ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzina gyisa
NK078(tshu)001:12541: / dang po zhugs bar du slob tha ma mthar
NK078(tshu)001:12542: phyin gyi bar du skabs su dam tshig gi dkyil
NK078(tshu)001:12544: ye shes rang bzhin gyi yula 'og min nas snyan gsan dbab spyan drangs par byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:12545: phyag rgya bzhis gnyis su med par gzhug cing sku
NK078(tshu)001:12546: gsung thugs brtan par bzhugs pa la sogs pa'i cho
NK078(tshu)001:12547: ga dang ldan par byas ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12548: gsum pa phrin las kyi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12550: dang po phrin las gzhung gi rim pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12551: drang de nas phyag 'tshal ba la sogs mchod rdzas
NK078(tshu)001:12552: dang tshig sngags phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin rnams kyi
NK078(tshu)001:12553: rim pa bzhin du mchod la /
NK078(tshu)001:12554: bstod pa bya smon lam gdab pa dang ldan nas bsnyen pa'i dzab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12556: gnyis pa lhag ma mjug gi rim pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12558: nang nub thun mtshams kyi bar skabs su zhi khro
NK078(tshu)001:12559: gang yin gyi lhag ma la dbang ba'i gnas kyi
NK078(tshu)001:12560: re ba bskangs te mchod nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12561: rang gi sngon dam bcas pa'i dam tshig bsgrags la phrin las bcol zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:12562: ya hi gats+tshasa zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las la dgye brtan ma bskyang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:12563: de nas 'khor lo ste dkyil 'khor bsdus shing lus
NK078(tshu)001:12564: bsrung go bgo spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:12565: la gnas pa kun zhi khro gang yin gyi man
NK078(tshu)001:12566: ngag gi sgom khog gi gzhung bzhin du bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12567: bzhi pa ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12569: dang po ngo bor rang snang yul med zhi gnas lhag mthong zung 'brel du dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12571: phung po khams dang skyed mched la sogs pa'i rtog
NK078(tshu)001:12572: tshogs thams cad zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gyi lhar snang
NK078(tshu)001:12573: ba yang / dper na rgya mtsho dwangs pa'i nang
NK078(tshu)001:12574: na nyi zla skar gsum gyi gzugs brnyan snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:12575: ba yang / ci bzhin du / phyi nang snod
NK078(tshu)001:12576: bcud phung khams skye mched la sogs pa chos kun
NK078(tshu)001:12577: gyi dngos po yang rang rig pa zhi khro'i lha
NK078(tshu)001:12578: du mar gsal bas gcig pa'i mtha' dang bral la
NK078(tshu)001:12579: ba yang / ci bzhin du / / de dus
NK078(tshu)001:12580: rig pa rang las ma g.yos pas lha du ma
NK078(tshu)001:12582: rig pa lhar gasla ba la yul yul can gang du zhen pa med pas lhag mthong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12583: de'i ngang las mi g.yo bas zhi gnas /
NK078(tshu)001:12584: de gnyis zung du 'brel ba ni bsgom bya'i rnal
NK078(tshu)001:12585: 'byor ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo yin par rgyal
NK078(tshu)001:12586: bas bka' brgyud kun nas gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:12587: gnyis pa rnam grangs spros pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12589: rtog tshogs rang bzhin gyis lhar gnas pa spros pas /
NK078(tshu)001:12590: de nyams su len pa'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin yang lha du mar spros /
NK078(tshu)001:12591: lha de'ang gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i ngo la khro bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12592: zhi ba gnyis su spros so //
NK078(tshu)001:12593: de re re la'ang 'khor lo dkyil 'khor spros pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12594: phyag rgya rnam grangs spros pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12597: de ltar gzhi lam po kun nas spros pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:12598: gzhi mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu'ang yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12599: de'ang sku dang ye shes du mar spros pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12600: gsum pa nges tshig bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12602: de ltar spros par nyams su myong zhing gsal ba
NK078(tshu)001:12603: ni phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor gyi sgra don
NK078(tshu)001:12605: lnga pa skyon la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12607: dang po le lo la zhugs pa dang mtshan ma la zhen pa'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12609: spros pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas pa 'di'i tshe gdod
NK078(tshu)001:12610: bya long yod snyam pa snyoms las su gyur pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:12611: le lo dang / mi dge ba'i las byed pa
NK078(tshu)001:12612: sbyor ba dman pa las gyur pa'i le lo rnam
NK078(tshu)001:12618: nyi ma la sogs pa mtshan ma'i mtha' lnga po
NK078(tshu)001:12619: dngos su 'byung ba mthong zhing de la yang dag
NK078(tshu)001:12620: tu 'dzin na skyon du 'gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12621: gnyis pa bdud kyi spyod yul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12623: dang po nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12625: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor pas grub rtags kyi
NK078(tshu)001:12626: spyod yul 'di dag la dam par bzung nas zhen
NK078(tshu)001:12627: na bdud kyi spyod yul bac+wo brgyad du mthong ba
NK078(tshu)001:12629: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12631: dang po bdud kyi spyod yul bac+wo brgyad dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12633: dang po snang ba gzugs kyi bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12634: sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa grangsa med pa 'jig rten
NK078(tshu)001:12635: du 'gyed pa mthong ba dang gcig /gnyis pa 'du
NK078(tshu)001:12637: bdag gzhan gyi nang nas dam par 'dug pa mthong ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:12638: yang na sangs rgyas byang sems kyi sa dam par 'du na cing dam par mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12639: gsum pa grags pa sgra yi bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12640: sangs rgyas dang byang sems kyis bdag la skyes bu dam par smra ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12641: bzhi pa bar chad g.yeng ba'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12642: rgyal bas gsungsa pa'i bstan pa mdo sngags kun gsal
NK078(tshu)001:12643: bar mthong zhing thos pa med par 'chad nus pa
NK078(tshu)001:12644: dang / lnga pa mngon shes log pa'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12645: skad cig ma gcig la dus gsum gyi chos thams cad gsal bar shes shing mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12646: drug pa skye gnas la zhen pa'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12647: rgyud drug gi spyi'i lam bar do na gnas pa'i sems can kun gsal bar mthong ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:12648: yang na rgyud drug gi lam dang gnas kun mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12649: bdun pa snying rje sprul pa'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12650: sems can de dgal snying rje'i sems rang dbang med par shugs kyis 'byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12651: brgyad pa snang ba 'od kyi bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12652: phyi nang gi snod bcud kun kyang nyin mtshan med par gsal bar mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12653: dgu pa rdzu 'phrul ston pa spyod pa'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12654: ri brag la sogs ci la'ang bdag gi lus thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12655: bcu pa nga rgyal dregs pa'i bdud ni nam mkha'
NK078(tshu)001:12656: la sa la byed pa bzhin du 'phur nas 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:12658: bcu gcig pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12659: rgyal bas phyag brkyangs nas bdag gi mgo la byug ste sangs rgyas par lung ston pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12660: bcu gnyis pa bslu ba rdzun gyi bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12661: lha klu la sogs pa 'gro ba kun gyi so
NK078(tshu)001:12662: so'i skad du bdag gis chos smra zhing ston nus
NK078(tshu)001:12664: bcu gsum pa mtshan mas g.yeng ba'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12665: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad kyis bdag la bkur sti dang rim gro'i gnas su mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12666: bcu bzhi pa re dogs the tshom gyi bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12667: ting nge 'dzin gyi shugs la stong gsum thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:12668: mtho dman med par lag mthil ltar mnyam par bkod
NK078(tshu)001:12669: pa dang / bco lnga pa chags pa gegs byas kyi bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12670: stong gsum de nyid kyi rang bzhin skyu ru ra
NK078(tshu)001:12671: lag pa'i mthil du bzhag pa ltar gsal bar snang
NK078(tshu)001:12672: ba dang / bcu drug pa don du mi 'gyur bar gol ba'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12673: sems ting nge 'dzin las su rung bas bdag gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:12674: gyi don spyod pa ci la'ang thogs pa med par
NK078(tshu)001:12675: spyod nus so snyams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12676: bcu bdun pa che ba'i nga rgyal snyam pa'i bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12677: dam pa'i chos ston pa'i don la rtog pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:12678: mos par gyis shig ces sangs rgyas byang sems kyis
NK078(tshu)001:12679: bdag la bka' bsgo ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12680: bco brgyad pa bkur sti bar chad gyi bdud ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12681: 'jig rten pa'i gtso bo lha chen po rnams kyis
NK078(tshu)001:12682: bdag la mchod pa 'byung ba dang bco brgyad po
NK078(tshu)001:12684: 'di yan chad nas thod rgal 'ong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12685: blo rab 'bring tha ma la nges pa med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:12688: tha ma rmi lam du 'ong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:12689: gnyis pa de rang bzhin med par shes na grub rtags dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12691: rnal 'byor pa gang gis spyod yul bco brgyad po de dag mthong ba'i dus na /
NK078(tshu)001:12692: de dag la rang bzhin med par rang snang gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:12693: med du rtogs na lam ma nor bar dam pa
NK078(tshu)001:12695: gsum pa mi shes dga' brod byed na bdud du gyur tshul bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12697: de ltar sems kyi chos nyid rang snang du mi
NK078(tshu)001:12698: shes par grub rtags dam par bzung nas dga' brod
NK078(tshu)001:12700: bdud kyi bar chad kyi las su gyur pa yin pas na bdud kyi spyod yul te /
NK078(tshu)001:12701: de ci'i phyir na 'jig rten gyi khe dang snyan
NK078(tshu)001:12702: grags thob par 'dod pas sems rang dbang med par
NK078(tshu)001:12703: 'phrog pa dang / gzhan gyis bdag la skyes bu
NK078(tshu)001:12704: dam par basngagasa pa ste bstod pa'i che ba brjod
NK078(tshu)001:12705: pa thos nas 'du 'dzi dang longs spyod kyi mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:12707: 'bras bu thob du re ba dang ma thob kyi
NK078(tshu)001:12708: gol du dogs pa cung zad cig yod pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:12709: / rtags byung mang tsam mam nga zhes pas sems
NK078(tshu)001:12710: khengs pa che bas nga rgyal 'phel nas g.yeng bar
NK078(tshu)001:12711: / shor ba'o // gsum pa thun mong gi skyon phra ba 'byung tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:12713: thun mong gi skyon tha mal ba'ang sngar bas 'dir
NK078(tshu)001:12714: grangs nyung bar 'byung la ngo bo shin tu cha
NK078(tshu)001:12715: phra ba ste / dbugs kyi rgyu ba'i skad gcig
NK078(tshu)001:12716: gi nang du ting nge 'dzin gzung 'dzin gyi dbang
NK078(tshu)001:12717: du song ma song bye brag rnams shes pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12718: drug pa skyon bcos thabs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12720: dang po le lo'i skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12722: rgyu shes pa'i lta ba dang rkyen 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin gnyis 'go 'byor ba'i nyams thob cing /
NK078(tshu)001:12723: lta sgom zung du 'brel ba'i nyams len la bskyed du byar med pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:12724: tshogs lam mthar phyin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12725: snang stong dbyer med 'bras bu lha'i dkyil 'khor lam
NK078(tshu)001:12726: du shes shing ting nge 'dzin la blo brtan par
NK078(tshu)001:12727: gyur pa yis / le lo gnyis po'i dbang du
NK078(tshu)001:12728: mi btang bar 'bras bu thob pa'i rtsol ba'i bya
NK078(tshu)001:12729: gyur pa yis / ba med cing / don yal
NK078(tshu)001:12730: bar dor ba med pa'i brtson 'grus dang du blang
NK078(tshu)001:12731: gyur pa yis / ba med cing / bar bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:12732: // gnyis pa mtshan ma'i skyon bcos thabs dpe dang
NK078(tshu)001:12733: gyur pa yis / ba med cing / bar bya'o // bcas pa dang / drang /
NK078(tshu)001:12734: smig rgyu la sogs pa'i mtshan ma lnga ci ltar
NK078(tshu)001:12735: byung yang rang rig pa'i cho 'phrul du snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:12736: yin pas / de dag rang gi sems nyid yin par shes pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:12737: mtshan ma de dag mthong ba la 'bras bu thob du re ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12738: ma thob cing gol du dogs pa med par shes par gyis shig pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12739: dper na nam mkha' dwangs pa'i rang bzhin de la nyi zla dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12743: sprin mang po phan tshun du 'khrug par 'gyur yang
NK078(tshu)001:12744: nam mkha' ni rang bzhin nam dbyings de las gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:12745: du 'gyur zhing nyams pa med pa'i dpe bzhin tu
NK078(tshu)001:12746: / don sems nyid mi dmigs pa chos kyi dbyings ni gdul bya'i blo la bsam yas par /
NK078(tshu)001:12747: 'das pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba nyer lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12748: nyams kyi mtshan ma bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:12749: la sogs pa sna tshogas pa rnal 'byor pa'i nyams
NK078(tshu)001:12751: chos nyid de bzhin nyid las gzhan du nyams shing 'gyur ba meda par shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12752: gsum pa bdud kyi spyod yul gyi skyon bcos thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:12754: spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs
NK078(tshu)001:12755: dang yon tan thams cad yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:12756: yang gang zag dang chos kyi bdag gnyis med par
NK078(tshu)001:12757: shes pas nga rgyal dang rlom sems med de /
NK078(tshu)001:12758: bdud kyi spyod yul du rtags dang mtshan ma'i bye
NK078(tshu)001:12759: brag gang mthong ba de yang gzhan ma yin par
NK078(tshu)001:12760: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shesa su rung snang
NK078(tshu)001:12761: ba nyid du lta bas shes shing ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:12762: gyi rgyud la sbyar bas re dogs la sogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:12764: bdun pa nyams la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12766: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12768: rtog pa'i snang ba lha'i snang bar 'byed pa phyag
NK078(tshu)001:12769: rgya spros pa'i nyams gong nas gong du 'phel bar
NK078(tshu)001:12771: gong du bshad pa'i shes bya slob pa'i rim pa
NK078(tshu)001:12772: snga ma goms nas phyi ma slob pa ji bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:12773: du nyams kyi rim pa yang 'phel te /
NK078(tshu)001:12774: phyag rgya gcig par nyams lnga sngon du brten cing
NK078(tshu)001:12775: mthar phyin mod kyang phyag rgya spros pa 'di la
NK078(tshu)001:12776: da gzod slob pa yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:12777: sngar snang 'byed spros pa la ma goms pa'i dbang
NK078(tshu)001:12778: gis g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin pa'i nyams rnam
NK078(tshu)001:12780: gnyis pa rgyas par nyams lnga rim par skye tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12782: rigs sam tshom bu gsum pa dang lnga pa'i lha
NK078(tshu)001:12783: gsal ba'i tshe rtog pa'i dbang du cung zad g.yo
NK078(tshu)001:12784: bas / ting nge 'dzin la rtog pa'i bar tshad
NK078(tshu)001:12785: 'byung ba de nyams lnga'i dang po g.yo ba'i nyams
NK078(tshu)001:12786: bas / yin pa'o // lha gsal ba'i tshod la
NK078(tshu)001:12787: nyin zhag phrug gcig la thun bzhir bgos pa'i cha
NK078(tshu)001:12788: gcig tsam skyon dbang du 'gyur zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:12789: cha gsum tsam du lha'i ting nge 'dzin gsal bar
NK078(tshu)001:12790: rtogs pas mi g.yo ba de ni gnyis pa thob
NK078(tshu)001:12792: rkyen med na rtog par med par thun rkyang gcig
NK078(tshu)001:12793: bsgom nus pa ni gsum pa goms pa'i nyams yin
NK078(tshu)001:12794: pa'o // thun rkyang gcig bsgom nus pa de nyid
NK078(tshu)001:12795: rtog pa'i rkyen dbang du mi 'gro zhing lhar gsal
NK078(tshu)001:12796: ba de ni bzhi pa brtan pa'i nyams yin pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:12797: pa'o // // de nas nyin zhag gam dus phyed
NK078(tshu)001:12798: para ting nge 'dzin la gang gnas pa de la
NK078(tshu)001:12799: pa'o // // / shin tu yang rtog pa'i rkyen
NK078(tshu)001:12800: gyis mi 'phrog pa ni nyams lnga pa ste mthar
NK078(tshu)001:12802: gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa la sbyor bas brtsad pa'i skyon spang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12804: stong dang nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs pa rnam grangs spros pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:12805: nyams rim lnga po de dag sbyar na zag med
NK078(tshu)001:12806: mthong sgom mthar lam gsum gyi rig 'dzin du thal
NK078(tshu)001:12808: de bas na rtsa ba'i rnam grangs zhi khro'i tshom
NK078(tshu)001:12809: bu dang dkyil 'khor la nyams lnga sbyar ba'i tshod
NK078(tshu)001:12811: brgyad pa spyod pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12812: lta dgongs chos nyid kyi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12813: rmad byung thabs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12814: khyad par tshogs kyi spyod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12817: dang po lta dgongs nyams nga med par spyod pa dpe dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12819: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor chen po'i lta ba las mi 'da' ba'i spyod pa'i tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12820: 'dod yod la ci ltar spyad kyang lta bas rang bzhin med par shes pas /
NK078(tshu)001:12821: dper na nam mkha' la bya chen khyung lding ba bzhin du g.yang mi za /
NK078(tshu)001:12822: chu la rkyal chen 'phyo ba'i nya mo bzhin nyam nga med /
NK078(tshu)001:12823: nam mkha' la rlung chen 'phyo ba la thogs chags phyogs ris med pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:12824: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnam 'byor pas spyod pa'i lta ba yang dpe gsum po de bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:12827: thogs pa med par blta zhing spyod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12828: gnyis pa lta ba'i don las mi 'da' bas ci spyod tshogs gnyis rdzogs par spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12830: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byora chen po'i sgo gsum gyi spyod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12831: spyod pa ci la'ang thogs chag med pa'i lta bas zin par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:12832: snang grag gi chos spyad bya'i yul thamsa cad kun
NK078(tshu)001:12833: la spyad bya spyod byed dbyer meda par spyod pasa
NK078(tshu)001:12834: / snang ba ma 'gags pa bde ba chen po'i ro mchog myong bar 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:12835: de la rnal 'byor pa su zhig zhen pa dang chags par mi byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:12836: de ltar spyad bya'i yul la ma 'gags par spyod
NK078(tshu)001:12837: bzhin du de la ma chags shing mi 'dzin pas
NK078(tshu)001:12838: ye shes kyi tshogs su 'gyur ba yin /
NK078(tshu)001:12839: spyad pas bde ba'i ro mchog myong ba nyid ma 'gag pa bsod nams kyi tshogs su 'gyur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12840: de ltar chogs gnyis rdzogs pa de lta bu'i ngang
NK078(tshu)001:12841: 'ba' zhig tu spyad bya'i yul thams cad la spyad
NK078(tshu)001:12842: pas / 'di ni tshogs gnyis cig char du rdzogs pa'i spyod pa rlabs chen po yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:12843: gsum pa lta spyod 'brel bar gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12845: lta ba spyod pa ya char ma gyur te lta
NK078(tshu)001:12846: spyod 'brel bar sngags 'chang lam pa rnams kyis dus
NK078(tshu)001:12848: gnyis pa rmad byung thabs kyi spyod pas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12851: mi spang ba lnga dang du blangs ba lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:12852: 'dod yon lnga ste lnga tshan bzhi po ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12853: theg pa 'og mas spang par bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12854: smad par bya ba'i spyod pa ma lus pa kun /
NK078(tshu)001:12855: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi don dang gdul bya gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:12856: gyi don phyir bkag pa med par 'jol nyog tu
NK078(tshu)001:12857: spyad de / lnga bzhi la sogs par gang yang
NK078(tshu)001:12858: ma 'gag par spyod par byas la spyod bya spyod
NK078(tshu)001:12860: 'dzin chags med pas ma thogs shing /
NK078(tshu)001:12861: dbyer med du spyod pas tshogs gnyis su 'gyur ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12862: pad+ma 'dam nas skyes kyang 'dam skyon gyis ma gos
NK078(tshu)001:12863: pa bzhin du gong gi spyod pa gang spyod la
NK078(tshu)001:12864: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos par spyod pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:12865: thabs la mkhas pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12866: gsum pa khyad par gyi tshogs spyod pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:12867: spyod yul lha'i dkyil 'khor du spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12868: 'dod yon snang ba lhar bsgom nas spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12869: stong khams srid tshad kyi shes rab yum dang 'dod
NK078(tshu)001:12870: yon rnams la rab 'bring tha mar spyod tshul lo
NK078(tshu)001:12876: dang po spyod byed ye shes sam yab tu bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12880: rnam shes tshogs brgyad po kun tu rang rig rang snang bar shes pas /
NK078(tshu)001:12881: de dag rnam pa rang ga ma min te /
NK078(tshu)001:12882: mtshan med ltar na yi ge gyis mtshon nas ye shes lnga ru lta bas shes par bya /
NK078(tshu)001:12883: 'dir mtshan bcas ltar na zhi ba rdzogs pa'i yab kyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:12884: zhi ba la dgar bas yang na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:12885: gnyis pa spyod bya dbyings sam yum du bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12891: reg la sogs pa yul gyi rtog pa kun /
NK078(tshu)001:12892: rnam pa rang ga mam min te /
NK078(tshu)001:12893: mtshan med ltar na yi ge m+aum du mtshan pa mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su shes par bya /
NK078(tshu)001:12894: 'dir mtshan bcas ltar zhi ba yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:12895: zhi ba la dgar bas yang na khro mo yum gyi dal nyid du bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:12898: mdor na spyod lam gyi yul 'di ltar du snang
NK078(tshu)001:12899: ba thams cad lha dang lha mor gsal bas lha
NK078(tshu)001:12900: la lha 'am / ye shes la ye shes /
NK078(tshu)001:12901: chos nyid la chos nyid rol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12902: gnyis pa 'dod yon la spyod thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12904: dang po 'dod yon snang ba ltar shes nas bsgom pa dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12906: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya la sogs pa'i 'doda yon lnga po thams cad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12907: gzhan yang rtog pa sna tshogs su snang ba thams cad kuna /
NK078(tshu)001:12908: 'bras bu de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12909: gzugs mdzes pa'i lha mo la sogs pa 'dod yon gyi lha dang lha mor brtag go //
NK078(tshu)001:12910: gnyis pa 'dod yon la spyod pa'i rtog pa lhar
NK078(tshu)001:12911: dag pa'i spyod yul thams cad kun tu bzang por
NK078(tshu)001:12913: rtog pa thamsa cad spyod yul lhar dag pa kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin du shes pas /
NK078(tshu)001:12914: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga po rnams thams cad la
NK078(tshu)001:12915: thogs pa dang 'dzin chags med par ma 'gag par
NK078(tshu)001:12917: de kho nas bsod namsa kyi tshogs chena po yin par brtag go //
NK078(tshu)001:12918: yang na 'dod yon lnga po de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngara yang brtag cing shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12920: gsum pa stong khams srid tshad kyi shes rab yum dang 'dod yon la sbyor tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:12922: spyod yul 'di las gzhan pa yang stong gsum 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:12923: rten gyi khams thams cad na gnas pa'i shes rab
NK078(tshu)001:12925: 'dod yon lnga po thams cad rnams la /
NK078(tshu)001:12926: bzang ngan rab 'bring tha ma thams cad kun la blang dor med par spyad do //
NK078(tshu)001:12927: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:12928: dam tshig bsrung ba'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12929: zag ldog yod pa'i phyir ma bsrung ba'i skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:12931: bdag don gyi dam tshig bsrung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12932: gzhan don du gang ltar mtshams pa ltar bsrung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12935: cig char ba'i dam tshig go //
NK078(tshu)001:12938: dang po mi spang zhing dang du blang ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12940: dang du blang ba dam rdzas lnga dang mi spang ba nyon mongs pa lnga po kun kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:12941: spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa yis dus rtag tu spyad bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12942: spyad pa de la chags shing zhen pa med par gyur pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12944: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ngo mtshar ba ya mtshan chen po 'byung ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12945: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga mdo tsam du bshad pa rgyas pa'i nga gsum pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12946: le'u lag gi nyer bdun pa'i nang nas 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12947: de yang dngos grub ya mtshan chen po ni /
NK078(tshu)001:12948: tshe la dbang dang rig pa 'dzin //
NK078(tshu)001:12949: mkha' la spyod dang thog med 'grub //
NK078(tshu)001:12950: mthar ni skye shi med pa'i sa //
NK078(tshu)001:12951: gzhan yang ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:12954: gnyis pa spyod lam kun la spros pa'i rnal 'byor las mi 'da' bar bsrung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:12956: dbang po'i spyod yul du mthong thos thams cad kun dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12958: nyal ba la sogs pa'i tshe na /
NK078(tshu)001:12959: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis bsgom pa spros bcas kyi
NK078(tshu)001:12960: rnal 'byor las ma nyams par ting nge 'dzin de'i
NK078(tshu)001:12961: dbyings na gnas par lam pa'i shes rab kyi dbang
NK078(tshu)001:12962: po mchog dang ldan pa dag gis dus rtag tu
NK078(tshu)001:12963: spyod par bya'o // gnyis pa gcig char ba'i dam tshig go //
NK078(tshu)001:12965: rim gyis pa'i dam tshig las yang na /
NK078(tshu)001:12966: gcig char ba'i dam tshig 'og nas 'byung ba 'di lta bu rtogs na /
NK078(tshu)001:12967: thams cad dbyer med pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:12968: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa ji ltar spyad kyang rig
NK078(tshu)001:12969: 'dzin sngags kyi sdom pa las mi 'da' ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:12970: no // de ji ltar mi 'da' zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:12971: snang srid kyi chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus
NK078(tshu)001:12972: pa ra lha'i dkyil 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:12974: 'bras bu bsgrub cing dam tshig bsrung bar bya ba med de /
NK078(tshu)001:12975: de bsrung ba las dge ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:12976: ma bsrungs bas mi dge ba'i rnam smin gnyis ka
NK078(tshu)001:12977: dbye ru med pa rmi lam ltar rtogs tsa na
NK078(tshu)001:12978: / ye nas dbyer med du sangs rgyas pa de
NK078(tshu)001:12979: la dam tshig bsrung rgyu rdul phra mo tsam yang
NK078(tshu)001:12980: / med do // gnyis pa gzhan don gang ltar 'tshams pa gcig car ba'i /
NK078(tshu)001:12983: gzhan don bya ba'i phyir rgyud las grags pa'i rtsa ba yan lag gi bsrung bya'i dam tshig kun /
NK078(tshu)001:12984: gdul bya gang la mos pa ltar blo dang 'tshams
NK078(tshu)001:12985: par 'da' bar mi byed par srungs shig /gnyis pa
NK078(tshu)001:12986: zag ldog yod pa'i phyir ma bsrungs ba'i skyon no
NK078(tshu)001:12988: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa'i bka' nas bshad pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:12989: sdom pa'i rtsa ba lnga dang yan lag gi dam
NK078(tshu)001:12990: tshig thams cad kun gzhung nas bshad pa'i lta spyod
NK078(tshu)001:12991: dbyer med kyi de bzhin nyid ni ma bsrungsa na
NK078(tshu)001:12993: dbang bskur ba'i dus su dam chu blud pa de
NK078(tshu)001:12994: yak+sha khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin tsha ba me'i
NK078(tshu)001:12995: dbal lta bu lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu par
NK078(tshu)001:12996: gyur ba can gyis khyod kyi snying la gnas bcas
NK078(tshu)001:12997: nas tshe 'di la snying rtsad nas drangs te khrag
NK078(tshu)001:12998: 'thung nas dus ma yin par 'chi zhing tshe thung
NK078(tshu)001:12999: bar 'gyur la / phyi mar ngan song gsum du
NK078(tshu)001:13000: skye bar 'gyur zhing de'i sdug bsngal tsha grang bkres
NK078(tshu)001:13001: skom glen lkugs la sogs bzod pa'i glags ni tshad
NK078(tshu)001:13003: dam tshig nyams na ngan song gsum du ltung ba de'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:13006: spros pa dang tshogs lam bzhir 'khor bar ldog cing
NK078(tshu)001:13007: ngan song gsum du ltung ba dang zag pa gsum
NK078(tshu)001:13010: chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK078(tshu)001:13011: dang po'i don rtogs mthar mi gtong //
NK078(tshu)001:13013: zab pa'i don rtogs mi ldog bde //
NK078(tshu)001:13014: zhes pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:13015: de'i don ni nyes ltung med cing bde legs thob pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13016: lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan bshad pa'i skabs yin pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:13017: 'dir ltung bar bshad pa ni dam tshig nyams pa che zhing bshags sbyangs ma byas par 'chi na /
NK078(tshu)001:13018: lan cig ngan song du ltung ba ni nyams pa'i skyon gyis de ltar gyur kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:13019: lta sgom gyi stobs kyis der yun ring mi gnas par myur du thar ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:13021: theg chen gsang bar rab nges na //
NK078(tshu)001:13022: rnam smin drag pos gar 'phang kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:13023: ji ltar pho long brdab pa bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:13025: ci phyir thams cad stong nyid pas //
NK078(tshu)001:13026: sdug bsngal gnas su bcas te yang //
NK078(tshu)001:13027: sems can bcas te stong nyid phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:13030: 'dir re zhig nyes pa'i dbang gis ltung yang /
NK078(tshu)001:13031: lta sgom gyi stobs kyis mthar mi bslu ba la dgongs so //
NK078(tshu)001:13032: chos kyi spyan ldan sgro phug pa'i gsung nas ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13033: dam tshig gi ngo bo lta ba yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:13034: de rtogs na dam nyams mi srid pas /
NK078(tshu)001:13035: de'i rkyen gyis ltung ba med la /
NK078(tshu)001:13037: lta ba ma rtogs par bsgom pa 'ga' zhig la /
NK078(tshu)001:13038: nyams pa 'byung srid pas rkyen gyis ltung ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:13039: zur byams pa seng ge'i gsungs gis ni rtogs pa rgyun chags pa rnams ngan 'gror mi ltung la /
NK078(tshu)001:13040: res 'ga' ba rnams 'gal rkyen gyis ltung srid pa la dgongs la /
NK078(tshu)001:13041: snga phyi'i lung gnyis ka dang mi 'gal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:13043: des na spros pa man chad ldog zag gnyis ka yod pa'i mu yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:13044: sbyor lam ni ldog med zag yod kyi bar mthong
NK078(tshu)001:13045: lam yan chad zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i mu
NK078(tshu)001:13046: / zag med ldog yod kyi mu ni 'dir mi bshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:13049: phyi'i drod lus shing bala gyi 'dab ma lta bur shin tu yang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13050: nang gi drod dbugs phyi nang gi rgyu ba yun ring du bral ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13051: gsang ba sems kyi drod rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin mkha' la gza' skar shar ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:13052: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams ma 'dres par gsal ba lhag mthong yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:13053: rtogs pa'i mthar mi g.yo ba zhi gnas /
NK078(tshu)001:13054: bsgam bya sgom byed kyi spyod yul du zhen pa med par zhi lhag zung 'jug tu gsal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13055: drod gsum po des zhor las 'byung ba'i drod kun kyang tshogs lam chen po 'dir rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:13056: 'di tsam zhes grangs kyis bgrang ba'i cha las 'das te /
NK078(tshu)001:13058: bcu gcig pa rtags la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13062: spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba'i rtags rnams kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:13063: sngon phyag rgya gcig pa la 'byung bar bstan pa rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:13064: 'dir de rnams las stobs su gyur pas ngo bo gsal brtan du 'phel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13065: lus kyi khams bde mi bde snyoms shing /
NK078(tshu)001:13066: na tsha'am nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu med pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:13067: rang gi lus bde basa gang bas shin tu rgyas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13068: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa'i nad 'du ba rnam
NK078(tshu)001:13069: pa bzhi dang bral bas lus kyi na tsha la
NK078(tshu)001:13070: bzod pa thob pa sngar bas tshab che ba 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:13071: ngo // gnyis pa mngon shes dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13073: sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa la sogs pa'i mngon par shes pa drug dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13074: dbang po'i sgo'i re res kyang yul lnga lnga gcod
NK078(tshu)001:13075: pas nyi shu rtsa lnga'i grangs kyang rdzogs par 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:13076: zhing / spros pa'i blo'i mngon shes rab 'bring gi cha yis phye bas yul khams tshun chad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13077: gling gcig tsam tshun chad kyi yul gsal bar mthong
NK078(tshu)001:13078: zhing de nyid kyi gdul bya 'dul bar byed do
NK078(tshu)001:13079: // de rgyu ci las byung zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:13080: 'jug pa'i rnam shes tshogs drug rang rgyud par tha
NK078(tshu)001:13081: dad du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dag cing dwangs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13082: stobs las gyur pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:13083: 'dir tshogs drug dag gam ma dag /dag na tshe dbang gi skabs su yang /
NK078(tshu)001:13084: mthong ba'i dri ma drug sbyangs phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:13085: gcig gis yul lnga gcod byed pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:13086: tshad dang ma tshad 'jigs dogs med //
NK078(tshu)001:13087: ces gsungs pa dang khyad med par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:13088: ma dag na dag ces pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:13089: 'di mnyam bzhag tu bsgom pa'i stobs kyis rig pa dwangs snyigs 'byed pas /
NK078(tshu)001:13090: tshogs drug rang bzhin gyis gsal bar gyur pa la brjod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13091: tshe dbang gi skabs su rjes shes tshogs drug mngon
NK078(tshu)001:13092: gyur dag nas chu bo'i rgyun bzhin du gyur pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:13095: sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyi bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:13096: nyi shu po yang rab 'bring gi cha yi g.yo
NK078(tshu)001:13097: ba dang / thob pa tsam 'byung ba rung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:13098: de yang mdo'i le'u bcu drug pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:13100: las kyi rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gnyis las /
NK078(tshu)001:13102: lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa 'gro ba thams cad la /
NK078(tshu)001:13103: rang rang gi skad du mthun par chos ston nus pa rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13104: mngon shes kyi yul tshun chad sa g.yos 'byung ba
NK078(tshu)001:13105: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul ston par byed pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:13106: / bdag gis sngags brjod pa kun yi ge'i sgrara
NK078(tshu)001:13107: snang nas gsang sngags brjod par byed pa kun brjod
NK078(tshu)001:13109: bzhi pa mthong snang la re dogs mi bya ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13111: de ltar cho 'phrul bzhi po 'di dag mthonga ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13112: gong ltar bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13113: glang po che zhon pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13114: grur zhugs pa la sogs ting nge 'dzin shugs la snang ba brgyad mthong ba'ang 'byung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13115: de dag ci byung yang re ba dang dgos pa'i rtogs pa dor la gnyam par bzhag go //
NK078(tshu)001:13116: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13118: dang po rmi lam snga ma dag mthun cing rdzogs par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13120: spros pa'i skabs 'dir rmi lam gyi mtshan ma yang
NK078(tshu)001:13121: phyag rgya gcig pa dang chos mthun pa ste ngo
NK078(tshu)001:13122: bo gcig par grub pa'i rmi ltas bcu bzhi la
NK078(tshu)001:13124: 'o na khyad med dam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:13125: ngo bo gsal ba dang brtan par gyur pa las khyad phye ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13126: gzhan yang rgyud kun kyang las mtshan ma bzang po'i ltas su rgyal bas lung bstan pa kun /
NK078(tshu)001:13127: tshogs lam chen po spros pa'i skabs 'dir thams cad rdzogs par 'byung ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:13128: de yang mdo chen po'i don gsum pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:13129: lam gong ma thob pa'i snga ltas su /
NK078(tshu)001:13130: bag chags sbyangs pa'i ltas brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13131: 'jigs pa dang bral ba'i ltas brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:13134: sangs rgyas kyi sras kyi ltas brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:13135: chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas bco lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:13136: bden pa mthong ba'i ltas brgyad lung bstan thob pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13137: ltas bcu la sogs pa rnams tshogs lam chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:13139: gnyis pa rmi ltas kun 'byung ba'i gtan tshig go //
NK078(tshu)001:13141: de dag rdzogs pa'i rgyu mtshan ni tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13142: 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa'i rmi ltas yang spros
NK078(tshu)001:13143: pa'i lam 'di nyid du 'byung dgos te /
NK078(tshu)001:13144: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu pa'i mtshan nyid rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:13145: rnams kyi dngos sam brgyud pa'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:13146: ro // mthar phyin pa'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:13147: ma rmi ltas bzang po thams cad 'byung ba'i sa
NK078(tshu)001:13148: phyag rgya spros pa 'di yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:13149: de ma zad bar chad med par tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13150: skabs su'ang mtshan ma rmi ltas 'di kho na ltar
NK078(tshu)001:13151: yang 'byung ste / 'on kyang gsal brtan gyi khyad tsam yod par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13152: bcu gsum pa phan yon la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13154: dang po rtogs tshogs lhar gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13156: gzugs la sogs pa'i phung po lnga nyid de bzhin gshegsa pa rigs kyi yab lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:13157: sa la sogs pa'i 'byung ba lnga po nyid bde bar gshegs pa rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13158: mig la sogs pa dbang po bzhi dang rnam shes
NK078(tshu)001:13159: bzhi ni phyi nang gi byang chub sems dpa' brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:13160: / mig gi yul gzugs la sogs pa bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13161: 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus bzhi ni byang chub sems ma chena mo brgyad yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:13162: bdag tu rtog pa rags pa las skyes pa'i lus
NK078(tshu)001:13163: kyi chos rnam pa bzhi po khro bo bzhi yina
NK078(tshu)001:13164: / rtag chad bdag mtshan mu bzhi khro mo bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:13165: shugs la yid chos kun bzang yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:13166: nyon mongs pa drug thub pa drug yin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13167: gnyis pa lha sems nyid rang snang du rtog nas sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13169: rtog tshogs thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba
NK078(tshu)001:13170: de yang sems rang gi rig pa nyid lha dang
NK078(tshu)001:13171: lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba yin zhes bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:13172: // de bzhin du rtog pa lhar mnyam par rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:13173: pa la 'bras bu kun lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags
NK078(tshu)001:13174: de bzhin gshegsa pa lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13175: don ye shes lnga po nyid du rgyu rkyen med
NK078(tshu)001:13176: par rang byung chen po'i ngang la lha dang lha
NK078(tshu)001:13177: mo'i dkyil 'khora du gsal bar bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13178: gsum pa bsgom pa'i yon tan spyod yul dag cing cir yang 'grub par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13180: bzang ngan nam gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa gnyis dang
NK078(tshu)001:13181: bral ba'i spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa thabs mkhas pa
NK078(tshu)001:13182: nyid kyis / rtog tshogs thams cad zhi khro'i lha
NK078(tshu)001:13183: ru gsal bas lha de yang dngos po rang rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:13185: mig gis gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13186: rna bas sgra thos pa la sogs pa tshogs drug
NK078(tshu)001:13187: gi spyod yul 'di dag rang rgyud pa med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13188: tshul gyis / rang gi rig pa'i ye shes lhar gsal bar bsgom pa'i dus na /
NK078(tshu)001:13189: don dam ltar na lha'i rang bzhin cir yang grub pa med par gsal ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:13190: kun rdzob tu ji ltar bsam pa ltar snang bas bsgrubs na cir yang 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:13191: bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13193: dang po 'da' tshul yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13195: spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang zhig 'chi ba'i rkyen
NK078(tshu)001:13196: gyis spyod yul 'gyur zhing tshe 'pho ba'i dus byung
NK078(tshu)001:13197: na / zhi khro'i phyag rgya spros pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:13198: dang tshom bu la sogs bsgom pa gang yin dran
NK078(tshu)001:13199: pas bzung nas sgom pa yis /
NK078(tshu)001:13200: rang rgyud kyi las ngan pa ngan 'gro'i lam gyi zhen pa'i blo rgyun bcad nas 'das na /
NK078(tshu)001:13202: tshe phyi mar blo chung na rnam smin che na
NK078(tshu)001:13203: tshe dbang gnyis la sbyor te mthong lam gyi rig
NK078(tshu)001:13204: 'dzin thob bo // gnyis pa nus pa zhan cing
NK078(tshu)001:13205: sgom pa'i skabs med kyang gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:13208: rnal 'byor pa blo chung ba gang zhiga ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:13209: 'dzin dang brtson 'grus kyi nus pa zhan pa la
NK078(tshu)001:13210: 'da' ka mi'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa'i skabs med
NK078(tshu)001:13212: sngar gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi 'phen pa'i 'brel ba
NK078(tshu)001:13213: spros bcas sgom pa'i sa bon rgyun la yod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13214: rkyen gyis / tshe rabsa skye ba phyi mar kun
NK078(tshu)001:13215: tu bde 'gro lha mi'i go 'phang khyad par can
NK078(tshu)001:13216: rkyen gyis / thob nas / dkon mchog gsum 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:13217: ba dang dus dang gnas kyi mi bkol bar gsang
NK078(tshu)001:13218: sngags kyi lam la spyad pas 'bras bu rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:13219: rkyen gyis / thob nas / thob bo // bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gnyis ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13221: dang po gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13223: rnal 'byor gang gis snyoms las kyi le lo med par brtson 'grus cher byas na /
NK078(tshu)001:13224: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin gnyis gang rung zhig thob par gyur pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:13225: gang gi stobs kyis thob ce na chos nyid rtog pa'i lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13226: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams par bsrung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13227: rkyen smon lam rnam dag btab pa'i mthu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13228: sgrub pa'i cha rkyen gyi yan lag cho ga lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:13230: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas bsgrub na 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:13231: bu mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro
NK078(tshu)001:13232: // gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13234: zhi khro phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa ting
NK078(tshu)001:13235: nge 'dzin yang nas yang du rgyun chags par bsgoms
NK078(tshu)001:13236: pa'i bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:13238: mun pa ma spang bar snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13239: dug ma spang bar sman du 'gyur pa'i tshul ci bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:13240: rtog tshogs ma spangs par 'bras bu sku dang ye
NK078(tshu)001:13241: shes su gsal ba yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK078(tshu)001:13242: gyis mchog brnyesa pa ste thob pa ni phyogs mthun
NK078(tshu)001:13244: blo che na rnam smin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13245: blo chung na tshogs sgrub thob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13246: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13248: zhi khro'i lha sku phyag rgya du mar spros nas
NK078(tshu)001:13249: sgom pa'i rnam 'byor ting nge 'dzin la bslab pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13250: thabs ston par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams
NK078(tshu)001:13251: / mtshams dang ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na le'u zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13252: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:13253: 'dir yas bsgrang drug pa'i don du gada'o ////spyi don
NK078(tshu)001:13254: gnyis pa bar chad med par tshogs sgrub pa la
NK078(tshu)001:13256: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13258: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor spros bcas gnyis la rtogs shing
NK078(tshu)001:13259: goms pa'i phyag 'tshal nas lam zag bcas de zag
NK078(tshu)001:13260: med la sbyor ba'i lam gang gi yang bar chad
NK078(tshu)001:13261: med par zag med mthong lam rig 'dzin la sbyor
NK078(tshu)001:13262: bar byed pa'i / sprosa pa mthar phyin pa'i dus kyi rjes thog tu /
NK078(tshu)001:13263: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs sgrub par bshad par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13264: gnyis pa gzhung don la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13266: dang po spyir bsnyen sgrub bzhi tshogs sgrub kyi skabs 'dir shes par gdams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13268: de la sbyor lam bar chad med pa'i lam du zhi khro'i tshom bu tshogs bsgrub par bya ba'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:13269: bsnyen pa dang ni nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13270: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13271: bsnyen sgrub bzhi po'i don rdzogs pa'ang tshogs sgrub kyi skabs 'dir shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13272: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhi bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13275: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13278: lam dus kyi bsnyen sgrub dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13280: de'i cha rkyen sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13281: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13282: lam rim 'jug gi bsnyen sgrub bzhi dang sbyor ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:13283: snyen sgrub 'og mchod pa'i skabs su kha 'phang ba
NK078(tshu)001:13284: dang / sgrub pa'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi gtso bor bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13289: de ltar bsnyen sgrub bzhi cha gsum yod pa'i dang po lam gyi rim pa'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13290: de la bzhi yod pa'i dang po bsnyen pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13291: byang ba don dam dang chub pa kun rdzob sems
NK078(tshu)001:13292: dbyer med kyi don rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK078(tshu)001:13293: goms pa la brtson 'grus byed pa de ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13294: grangs dus rtags kyi bsnyen pa gsum yod pa'i nang
NK078(tshu)001:13295: nas dam pa las byas pa chud mi za ba
