NK078(tshu)001:13296: dang / 'grub sla ba yin pa'i phyir byang chub
NK078(tshu)001:13297: kyi sems cha gsum du phye bas de ting byang
NK078(tshu)001:13298: dang / ba dang / kun ting snying rje chub
NK078(tshu)001:13299: pa ga nyis rtogs shing goms pa man chad bsnyen
NK078(tshu)001:13300: dang / ba dang / par brjod do // gnyis pa nye bsnyen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13302: de la brten nas lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por du mar gsal ba ste bsgom pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13303: 'og ma bas yang 'bras bu la nye ba'i phyir nye ba'i bsnyen pa yin pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:13304: gtan tshigs de'i phyir zung 'jug phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13305: snang byed phyag rgya spros pa gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13309: sgrub pa nyid ni sbyor lam bar chad med pa'i lam du tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13310: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13313: zhag sum cu phrag drug la sogs kyi dus kyi
NK078(tshu)001:13314: tshogs sgrub pa'i mthar mtshan ma rtags kyi bsnyen pa
NK078(tshu)001:13315: rdzogs nas bsgrub pa chen po ni nub tha ma
NK078(tshu)001:13317: des 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid mthong lam tshe rnams gang thob kyi 'bras bu 'grub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13318: gnyis pa sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi kha 'phang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13320: mdor bstan gyi gsum pa sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:13321: ni 'og khro bo'i gsang ba'i mchod pa'i skabs su
NK078(tshu)001:13324: gsum pa bsgrub pa'i bsnyen sgrub la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13326: sgrub pa'i yon tan dang bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13329: dang po sgrub thabs spyir bstan pa'i ngos nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13331: mdor bstan gyi gnyis pa sgrub pa'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:13332: gtso bor tshogs sgrub kyi skabs 'dir rgyas par bstan
NK078(tshu)001:13333: pa ni / sgrub pa'i gzhi dang sgrub gzhung dag gis tshogs sgrub pa'i thabs rdzogs par 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:13337: sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung la /
NK078(tshu)001:13339: sgrub pa dang sgrub pa chen po bzhis sgrub pa'i gzhung bsrang bar bya ba'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:13340: rnal 'byor ba gang dag phyag rgya gcig spros kyi
NK078(tshu)001:13341: skabs su zhi khro gang la mos pa ci bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:13342: du / 'dir yang zhi ba tshogs sgrub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13343: khro bo tshogs sgrub par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13344: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13345: zhi ba tshogs sgrub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13349: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13351: spyir bstan la zhi khro gnyis yod pa de la
NK078(tshu)001:13352: yang snga ma zhi ba'i sgo nas tshogs sgrub pa
NK078(tshu)001:13353: la / dus phun sum tshogs pa dang gcig /gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:13354: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa dang gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:13355: ston 'khor sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa dang bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:13356: sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa dang lnga yis /
NK078(tshu)001:13357: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang sbyor bas zhi ba tshogs sgrub kyi gzhung rdzogs par shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13358: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13359: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13360: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13362: sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13365: sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13368: dang po sgrub pa po spyi'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13370: phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan pas bsgrub dgos
NK078(tshu)001:13371: pa de la sgrub pa po zhi ba phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:13372: spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin nas las su
NK078(tshu)001:13373: rung ba'i rnal 'byor pas sgrub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13374: de bzhin nyid kyi cho ga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13376: phyag rgya gcig pa la gsung yig 'bru dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13378: sku yongs rdzogs kyi cho ga dang lnga ni mngon
NK078(tshu)001:13379: ru rdzogs par byas shing zhes spar khab dang si
NK078(tshu)001:13380: 'dar gnyis dgong pa mthun par gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:13381: yang na bla ma gong ma rnams kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:13384: phyag rgya gcig pa la phra rags gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:13385: spros pa dang lngar gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:13387: yid skyob pa dang byin rlabs kyi phyir sngags te lha'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13389: de nyid lus kyi yan lag mgo bo la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:13390: pa la phyag rgya lnga bcu tham pa rgyas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13392: rtog pa'i yan lag phung po la sogs pa dkyil
NK078(tshu)001:13393: 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su snang ba rnam par
NK078(tshu)001:13394: 'byed pa dang / de nyid yan lag gcig la'ang de dag tshang bar dgod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13395: de dag la yang rdo rje gsum gsum bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13396: dbang bskur ba'i yan lag dang lnga rdzogs ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13397: snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin la dbang thob nas bro gar 'du 'phro'i /
NK078(tshu)001:13400: bza' dang btung ba'i +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad
NK078(tshu)001:13401: dang lnga ni tshogs sgrub pa'i sngon tu rdzogs par
NK078(tshu)001:13402: ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa tshom bu lnga pa la
NK078(tshu)001:13404: gsum pa la pho mo bzhi bcu zhe drug /gcig
NK078(tshu)001:13405: pa la pho mo bco brgyad 'tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:13407: the tshom med pas na nges par 'grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13409: sgro skur med par la sogs pa'i dgos pa yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas /
NK078(tshu)001:13410: gnas skabs su zag med kyi mthong lam rig 'dzin gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13411: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga yongs su 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:13414: sgyu 'phrul rtsa bshad kyi don ston pa'i bla ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13416: ting nge 'dzin gyi mdzod a nu /
NK078(tshu)001:13417: spyod pa'i mdzod ma h+aa dang gsum ldan nam /
NK078(tshu)001:13418: yang na lta ba bden gsum dbyer med mngon sum rtogs pa /
NK078(tshu)001:13419: ting nge 'dzin spros bcas mthar phyin pa /
NK078(tshu)001:13420: dam tshig spyir kun dang ldan yang khyad par du
NK078(tshu)001:13421: sgrub pa'i don las mi 'da' ba'i lta sgom spyod
NK078(tshu)001:13422: gsum gyi mdzod gsum dang ldan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13423: phyi nang gsang gsum de kho na nyid kyi dbang bzhi'i chu bo bzhi rdzogs pa dang bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:13424: phyi bar chad kyi dgra bgegs bzlog pa /
NK078(tshu)001:13425: nang nyon mongs lam du slong ba /
NK078(tshu)001:13426: gsang ba bde sdug ro mnyam pa /
NK078(tshu)001:13427: snying rje phan sems kyis slob ma 'dzin pa'i gnyer bzhi dang ldan pa lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:13428: rgyud sde la mkhas shing lung gi don khrol ba
NK078(tshu)001:13429: dang drug /phrin las kyi chog khrig la mkhas pa
NK078(tshu)001:13430: dang bdun / bla ma brgyud pa'i man ngag zab
NK078(tshu)001:13431: mo nyams myong gi drod 'chang ba dang brgyad rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:13432: dang bdun / la 'chang bas / rnal 'byor pa
NK078(tshu)001:13433: zag bcas spros pa mthar phyin pa dang ldan nas
NK078(tshu)001:13434: zag med pa sbyor nus pa'i ston pa shin tu
NK078(tshu)001:13435: dang bdun / la 'chang bas / bsten par bya'o // gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13437: ston pa rdo rje slob dpon la sgo gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:13438: mnyes pa gsum gyis mchod cing dbang rdzogs par thob
NK078(tshu)001:13439: nas brtsona 'grus kyi sgo gsum gyis rgyud yongs su
NK078(tshu)001:13440: sbyong ba'i sgo nas rtogs pa'i lta ba bden pa
NK078(tshu)001:13441: dbyer med mngon du byas shing /
NK078(tshu)001:13442: de bzhin nyid sogs kyi ting nge 'dzin bzhi gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13443: bla med mi spang ba sogs rtsa ba lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13444: mi spang mi dor ba la sogs pa yan lag bcu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13445: rtsa ba yan lag bco lnga la sogs pa'i dam tshig ma nyams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13446: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13447: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang bzlas pa las rim gyi sngags ste gsum mam /
NK078(tshu)001:13448: sngags kyi yan lag lnga dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13451: sku phyag rgya chen po dang bzhi po rnams ma nyams par shes shing /
NK078(tshu)001:13452: gnas khang dben par bza' dang btung pa'i yo byad /
NK078(tshu)001:13453: rgyan dang bgo ba'i yo byad /
NK078(tshu)001:13456: +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:13457: de rnams dang ldan pa'i 'khor gyis tshogs bsgrubs na 'grub par 'gyur la /
NK078(tshu)001:13458: gong gi de rnams dang mi ldan na bsgrub kyang don med cing brlag par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:13459: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir yo byad de dag nges par rdzogs par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13460: 'di'i skabs su tshogs bsgrubs kyi gang zag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13461: ngan song du ldog par mi 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:13462: yo byad lnga po dang mi ldan na chogs sgrub par mi rung ba la dgongs pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:13463: gnyis pa gnas la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13465: dang po gnas btsal zhing brtags nas sa chog bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13467: dgra bgegs kyi sde dpung gi bar chad chen posa mi tshugs pa'i ganasabatsana pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13468: rdo rje las rim nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:13469: sa gzhi dang bar snang gi mtshan nyid la sogs bkra shis pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13471: lha chos kyi lo rgyus rnam pa gnyis ka bkra shis pa dang ldan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13472: rang nyid kyis shin tu yid du 'ong ba'i sa phyogs brtsal ba der /
NK078(tshu)001:13473: las rim nas 'byung ba ltar sa'i cho ga rgyas par bya ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13474: gnyis pa der gnas brtsigs shing byug bsrung dang brgyan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13476: gnas chos mthun rnyed na sa tshom bu gcig gsum
NK078(tshu)001:13477: lnga pa gang byed pa'i lha'i grangs gang yod kyi
NK078(tshu)001:13478: rim pa bzhin du gnas khang che chung gi tshad
NK078(tshu)001:13479: kyang rkyen sgrub pa po mang nyung gi rim pa
NK078(tshu)001:13481: de'ang 'khora khang phyi mar g.yos byed /
NK078(tshu)001:13483: bar mar gsang spyod bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13484: rim pa gsum dang ldan pa'i khang par /
NK078(tshu)001:13485: rin chen gser dngul la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13486: tsan+dana gla rtsi la sogs pas byugs pas gnas khang gi bar chad bsrung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13487: rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis mdzes par spras pa'i sgrub gnas gzhal yas khang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13488: rang nyams dga' zhing yid du 'ong bar bya ba shin tu gces so //
NK078(tshu)001:13489: gsum pa dus la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13491: dang po sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13493: sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus kyi tshes grangs ni
NK078(tshu)001:13494: zla ba yar gyi ngo'i tshes brgyad la lha'i tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:13495: 'dus pa'i dus yin pas brtsam par bya ba ste
NK078(tshu)001:13496: / shin tu yang tshes grangs de dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13497: skar ma rgyal dang gza' phur bu rnams 'dzom pa'i dus la 'jug na /
NK078(tshu)001:13498: bla na med pa'i byang chub sgrub pa'i spyod pa
NK078(tshu)001:13499: rlab po che cher spyod pa 'di ni rang bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:13500: gyis nus pa yod pas gsang sngags mchog gi dngos
NK078(tshu)001:13501: grub myur du thob pa'i rten 'brel yod pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:13502: / tshes grangs dang gza' dang skar ma bkra shis pa ste bzang po rnams blang bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13503: gnyis pa bsgrub pa 'grub pa'i dus so //
NK078(tshu)001:13505: lta sgom dam tshig dang ldan pas blo dang brtson
NK078(tshu)001:13506: 'grus rab kyis zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam
NK078(tshu)001:13507: ste zla ba drug /rab 'og gi zla ba bcu
NK078(tshu)001:13509: 'bring gis zla ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis sam /
NK078(tshu)001:13510: tha mas kyang zla ba bcu drug ste lo gcig
NK078(tshu)001:13511: dang zla ba bzhi dag gis tshe la dbang bsgyur
NK078(tshu)001:13512: ba'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi nang nas lam mchog yongs
NK078(tshu)001:13513: su rdzogs pa tshe dbang 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:13514: sbyor lam gyi rnal 'byor pa'i shes rab dang brtson
NK078(tshu)001:13515: 'grus rnams rab 'bring che chung tha ma'i chas dus
NK078(tshu)001:13516: nye ring rim pa bzhin du 'grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:13517: de yang dbang po rtul na rnam smin rig 'dzin thob bo //
NK078(tshu)001:13518: bzhi pa spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13520: spyir yo byad 'tshogs par bsog pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13522: gos rgyan te rgyan dang bgo ba'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13525: gsang ba +aa li k+aa li dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13527: glu tshig sgra yi yo byad de sgrub pa byed pa'i dus kyi yo byad lnga rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13528: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan gyi yo byad steng 'og logs rgyan gyi rnam pa yo byad du ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13529: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi mchod pa'i rdzas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13530: dngos grub rten gyi yo byad thod sku mar me rdor dril la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13531: dgra bgegs nad kyi bar chad rkyen bzlog gi yo byad /
NK078(tshu)001:13535: sman dang sman par bcas pa rnams bsdus so //
NK078(tshu)001:13536: gnyis pa bye brag tu yo byad dag par bsdu zhing 'tsho ba'i yo byad byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13538: yo byad rnams dam nyams kyi lag nas ma byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13540: sme sha can la sogs pa'i lag nas ma byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13541: phud nyams pa ma yin pa /
NK078(tshu)001:13542: rnam par dag par bsdu bar bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13543: de la yang dag ltar du tsho gsum du bcad la byin gyis rlabs par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13544: tsho dang po tram las rin po che'i mchod sdong
NK078(tshu)001:13545: 'od 'bar ba'i rtse la yi ge +amo +aahmh'u gsum
NK078(tshu)001:13546: las phyi nang gi longs spyod 'byung bar bsam te
NK078(tshu)001:13547: / phyi nang gi gtor ma bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13548: tsho bar ba la nyi zla'i steng du dpa' bo
NK078(tshu)001:13549: 'bru lnga'i 'phro 'dus pa 'dod yon gyi lhar brlabs
NK078(tshu)001:13550: te rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis rol lo //
NK078(tshu)001:13551: tsho tha ma la sa las nam mkha' mdzod kyi
NK078(tshu)001:13552: sngags dang phyag rgyas yang shing rgya che bar spel
NK078(tshu)001:13554: lnga pa sgrub thabs phun sum chogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13556: sgrub pa'i thabs bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang sbyar bas sgrub pa'i gzhung bsrangs te /
NK078(tshu)001:13557: de yang zhag grangs bco lnga lta bu la ngos bzung na /
NK078(tshu)001:13558: tshes gcig gis nyin mo la sgrub gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga 'tshogs te /
NK078(tshu)001:13559: dang po shom ra dkyil 'khor bzhengs te phyi mtshams gcod pa nas /
NK078(tshu)001:13560: mchod pa byin rlabs yan chad yan lag dang 'brel ba ni bsnyen pa /
NK078(tshu)001:13561: de nas cho ga gzhung bsrang te /
NK078(tshu)001:13562: zhag bdun bar bzlas pa'i dus su 'od zer dkar
NK078(tshu)001:13563: po phar 'phros pas sgrib pa sbyongs shig par bskul
NK078(tshu)001:13564: / tshur 'dus pas bdag gi sgo gsum gyi sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:13565: pa sbyangs te snod du rung bar byed pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:13566: / nye bsnyen no // de nas mar phyed zhag bdun la /
NK078(tshu)001:13567: bzlas pa'i 'od zer dmar po phar 'phros pas dngos grub rtsol cig par bskul /
NK078(tshu)001:13568: tshur 'dus pas dngos grub thob par bsam pa ni sgrub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13569: tha ma zhag gcig la bzlas pa'i 'od zer mthing
NK078(tshu)001:13570: ga de phar mi spro bar tshur sku gsung thugs
NK078(tshu)001:13571: kyi 'od zer bdag la sdud pa ni sgrub pa
NK078(tshu)001:13572: chen po'o // de yang sgrub pa'i gnas la ting
NK078(tshu)001:13573: nge 'dzin gyi bar chad dang srog gi bar chad
NK078(tshu)001:13575: 'grul srang med cing 'tsho ba'i bar chad dang mis
NK078(tshu)001:13576: dbang ma byas pa'i gnas shin tu dben pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:13577: nye bar dgos pa'i longs spyod kyi yo byad de
NK078(tshu)001:13580: sgrub rdzas la sogs pa phun tshogs pa bsogs shing
NK078(tshu)001:13581: ci bde bar 'jol nyog tu longs spyod rgyu dang
NK078(tshu)001:13583: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyamsa
NK078(tshu)001:13584: shing longs spyod ting nge 'dzin 'brel ba'i blo dang
NK078(tshu)001:13585: ni rab tu ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo 'tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:13586: pas / tshogs sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dang por
NK078(tshu)001:13587: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang yin la 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:13589: dus ci tsam sgrub par khas blangs shing dam mnos pa bzhin du sgrub pa mthar phyin par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13590: de yang dus ji srid 'bras bu ma 'grub kyi
NK078(tshu)001:13591: bar du sgrub par dam bcas pa dang ldan pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13592: rnal 'byor pho mo 'dus te bsgrub par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13593: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13594: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13595: sgrub pa'i grogs yo byad la spyad thabs bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13600: sgrub pa chen po dang zhor la zhag grangs rgyud bzhin shes nas bsgrub dgos par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13603: dang po lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:13604: gsal ba'am gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bri zhing rgyan
NK078(tshu)001:13607: sgrub gzhi song nas yang na zhes pa rgyud kyi tshig shug go //
NK078(tshu)001:13608: sgrub thabs bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i dang po las dang bya
NK078(tshu)001:13609: ba'i bsnyen pa las lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:13610: pa'i gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dpag tshad dang rgyang
NK078(tshu)001:13612: tshom bu gsum po so so rang rang gi blo
NK078(tshu)001:13613: dang 'tshamsa pa'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dal lus
NK078(tshu)001:13617: nyer lnga la sogs pa bri ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13618: de la dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13619: phyi nang gi mchod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13620: sgrub rdzas la sogs pas dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' 'khor bar dgram pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13621: gnyis pa phyi mchod bya zhing 'tshams bcad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13623: de nas gnas kyi phyi rol du cha gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:13624: gtor mas mchod pa'i las rnams rdzogs par bya ste
NK078(tshu)001:13625: / rgyal chen phyogs skyong gi tho btsugs nas phyi mtshams bcad cing bsrung /
NK078(tshu)001:13627: sgo byang gdag cing mtshams rim pa bzhin du bcad par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13628: gsum pa sngon du bya ba'i las rnams rdzogs par bya dgos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13630: grangs rtag dus bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:13631: bzhi las 'di bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa bya
NK078(tshu)001:13632: ba'i don du sngon du 'gro bar bya ba gong
NK078(tshu)001:13633: gi de rnams rdzogs pa'i las rnams thon zin para
NK078(tshu)001:13635: gnyis pa nye bsnyen la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13637: dang po sngon 'gro bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13639: de nas rnal 'byor pa rnams nang du 'dus pas tshul phyag bya /
NK078(tshu)001:13640: khro bo bcus phyogs bcingsa shing mtshams bcad /
NK078(tshu)001:13644: phyi nang gi mchod rdzas rnams byin gyis rlabs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:13645: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13646: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13647: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang zhing mchod bstod
NK078(tshu)001:13648: smon lam tshogs mchod lhag ma 'dzab bsnyen gyi las
NK078(tshu)001:13649: rim dang / nye bsnyen gyi tshad dang byed las bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13651: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13652: rtsa ba'i lha bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13653: yan lag dbang bskur byin rlabs kyi lha bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13656: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13658: rnal 'byor pa gcig gis lha kun spyir sgom pa'am
NK078(tshu)001:13659: yang na rnal 'byor pa yab yum re re dang
NK078(tshu)001:13660: lha yab yum re re grangs sprad nas bsgom zhing
NK078(tshu)001:13661: / tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i 'khor lor rim pa bzhin du bsgom par bya ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13662: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13664: dang po tshom bu gcig gsum lha grangs sprad nas bsgom lugs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13666: rnal 'byor pa thabs yab dang shes rab yum gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:13667: yab rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa rigs kyi yab lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13668: yum rnams kyis rigs kyi yum du bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:13669: 'khor yab rnams kyis rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13670: yum rnams kyis rang gi rigs chung gi sems ma yum nyid du bsgoma /
NK078(tshu)001:13671: lha so so'i rigsa gang yin pa dang phyag rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13672: ting nge 'dzin ma 'dres par yang dag par so sor gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:13673: gnyis pa gcig gis kun sgom byed lugs de la gsum te /
NK078(tshu)001:13675: dang po tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13677: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs ci snyed pa thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:13678: kyi 'dus tshul ni rigs lngar 'dus pa yin te
NK078(tshu)001:13679: / de yang bsdu na thugs sgrub sgyu 'phrul gyi
NK078(tshu)001:13680: lugs kyi rigs kyi gtso bo rdo rje'i rigs su
NK078(tshu)001:13683: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs mkhyen pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13684: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab brjod kyis mi lang
NK078(tshu)001:13685: ba yang / rigs bsdu na thugs ye shes lngar 'dus pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:13686: ye shes lnga po de yang thugs kyi mchog stong
NK078(tshu)001:13687: pa nyid kyi ye shes kho nar 'dus pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:13688: ro // de nas rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:13689: rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum dang bcas pas zung lnga ya bcu /
NK078(tshu)001:13690: khro bo sgo ba yab bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:13691: yum bzhi'i tshogs dang ldan pa'i tshom bu gcig pa la lha bco brgyad bskyed do //
NK078(tshu)001:13692: de ltar gtso bo rigs gcig gis byas pa'i tshom
NK078(tshu)001:13693: bu gcig pa'i lha yab yum gyi tshogs rnams bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:13694: mo // gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13696: gang gi tshom bu las lho byang gnyis bzhag pas /
NK078(tshu)001:13697: mdun nam shar gyi phyogs su de bzhin rigs kyi tshom bu yab yum zung lnga ya bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13698: dbus su rdo rje'i rigs tshom bu ya bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13699: rgyab bam nub tu pad+ma'i rigs kyi tshom bu la ya bcu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13700: de ltar sku gsung thugs kyi tshom bu cha gsum gyi mthar /
NK078(tshu)001:13701: phyogs mtshams brgyad du khro bo yab brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13702: khro mo yum brgyad de bcu drug zhal sbyor ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:13703: tshogs dang ldan pa'i tshom bu gsum gyi lha zhe
NK078(tshu)001:13704: drug gi tshogs rnams bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:13705: gsum pa tshom bu lnga pa bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13708: gtso mo yum lnga'i thabs dang shes rab gnyis su
NK078(tshu)001:13709: med par zhal sbyor ba can du bzhugs pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:13710: ni ci lta bu zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:13711: 'og gzhi 'khor lor rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa lnga po re re la yang /
NK078(tshu)001:13712: rtsibs chung bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa re re ste pho brang cha lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:13713: dbus kyi 'khor lo'i lte ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:13714: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:13715: rtsibs bzhir rdo rje'i rigs kyi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad rnams kyis bskor ba /
NK078(tshu)001:13716: rdo rje'i rigs kyi tshom bu ltar gsal pa'i rnal 'byor pa yab yum bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13717: de bzhin du shar lho nub byang bzhir /
NK078(tshu)001:13721: don grub yab yum gyi gtsor byas pa rnams la /
NK078(tshu)001:13725: las kyi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad kyis bskor ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13726: rigs bzhi'i tshom bu la lha bzhi bcu /
NK078(tshu)001:13727: gong gi dbus kyi tshom bu'i lha bcu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13728: de ltar tshom bu lnga cha'i tshom bu'i lha lnga bcu /
NK078(tshu)001:13729: rnal 'byor pa pho mo lnga bcur gsal bar bsgom pa bkod la /
NK078(tshu)001:13730: tshom bu cha lnga po de'i mthar /
NK078(tshu)001:13734: rnal 'byor yab yum cha bcu la /
NK078(tshu)001:13737: lha nyi shu gsal bar bkod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:13738: de ltar gtso bo rigs lngas byas pa'i tshom bu
NK078(tshu)001:13739: lnga'i lha bdun cu po de dag kyang dkyil 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:13740: gyi 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam par gsal bar bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:13741: mo // gnyis pa yan lag dbang bskur byin rlabs kyi lha bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13743: de dag la sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13744: lha gsum ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba'i rtags su
NK078(tshu)001:13745: rigs lngas dbu rgyan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13746: thugs ye shes sems dpa' dang ldan par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:13747: gnyis pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing
NK078(tshu)001:13748: mchod bstod smon lam tshogs mchod lhag ma 'dzab bsnyen
NK078(tshu)001:13751: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor 'og min gyi gnas nas snyan gsan dbab par byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:13752: spyan drangs gnyis su med par gzhug cing brtan par
NK078(tshu)001:13753: bzhugs su gsol bar byas la phyag nas bzung ste
NK078(tshu)001:13754: phyi nang gsang ba'i pu tsa'i rim par mchod pa
NK078(tshu)001:13755: rdzogs nas glu ye shes kyis bstod dee smon lam
NK078(tshu)001:13756: btab la dzaba kyi bsnyen pa bya /
NK078(tshu)001:13757: de tshar nas mchod bstod bshags pa rig pa'i me
NK078(tshu)001:13758: tog dor dngos grub bskul zin nas 'dzab khang bsdus
NK078(tshu)001:13759: te / de nas skal ldan rnal 'byor pa mi'i
NK078(tshu)001:13760: tshogs kyis dgyes ldan lha'i tshogs la 'byor ldan yo
NK078(tshu)001:13761: byad kyi tshogs tshul bzhin du mchod pa'i phrin las
NK078(tshu)001:13763: de ltar bsgrubs pas nang nub kyi bar skabs kun
NK078(tshu)001:13764: tu mkha' 'gro so gnyis la sogs pa'i lhag mgron
NK078(tshu)001:13765: rnams la lhag ma gzhung bzhin du sbyin cing phrin
NK078(tshu)001:13766: las bcol / sgrub pa la bar chad byed pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13767: nyul le ma yang dus su bzlog cing bsnyen pa
NK078(tshu)001:13768: las bcol / bya'o // de la dus tshod bcu gnyis kyi nyul le ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13769: sgrub pa la zhugs nas dgong mo nyi ma nub
NK078(tshu)001:13770: kha'i zer la nyul le bya rog skad 'gyur ma
NK078(tshu)001:13771: 'ong ste / rtags su nyams mi dga' gnyid 'thib pa 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:13772: srod la brang rkun nag mo 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13773: rtags su shes pa bying snying rje mi skye ste sha khrag za 'dod pa 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:13774: nam gung la gti mug rgyan byed ma 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13775: rtags su mar me'i bkrag nyams /
NK078(tshu)001:13778: nam phyed na 'dod chags dmar mo ra nu can bya ba 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13779: rtags su dal steng du zhing spags mgo thur la bstan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13780: gang nas srung mar bardzusa te /
NK078(tshu)001:13781: chags pa spyod tshul ston du 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:13782: phyed yol nam smad du dun ser tser 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13783: nyams zing nge byin med cing 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:13784: tho reng skya reng shar tsa na lag bse ma 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13786: nyi ma shar tsam na gnam thil nag mo 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13788: nyi ma dros pa la klu srin sngon mo 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13789: rtags su snying chu hril byed sgrub mched la nad drag po gtong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:13790: nyi ma phyed tshod la klu chen bzhi 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13791: rtags su nyal snying 'dod sdug sems skye /
NK078(tshu)001:13792: dkar po re re nor snying la 'dod pa 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:13793: nyi ma phyed yol la sa bdag ma yam 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13794: rtags su nyams chung zhing bying bying byed pa 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:13795: nyi snyul smad la bdud the'u rang stong sde 'ong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13796: rtags su tshig pa za rnam smin mi dran sdig spyod 'dod pa 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:13797: de yan chad ni dus bcu gnyis kyi nyul le mas bar du gcod pa'i rtags yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:13798: mdor na dam sri rgyal 'gong klu srin sngags pa dam nyams /
NK078(tshu)001:13800: bon bo mthar lhung la sogs shi 'dre nyams pa
NK078(tshu)001:13801: can rnams bdud kyis bskul nas dus thams cad du
NK078(tshu)001:13803: bzang por ston yang nyams mi dga' bar 'ongs /
NK078(tshu)001:13804: dgong kha bya mchu nag mo 'ong ba shas che bas /
NK078(tshu)001:13806: dri log pa ting nge 'dzin mi gsal byin chung /
NK078(tshu)001:13809: chos byed snying mi 'dod the tshom phyogs med skye /
NK078(tshu)001:13810: bla ma dang mched la snang ba log /glu gzhad la dga' /
NK078(tshu)001:13811: sems las su mi rung ba thams cad do //
NK078(tshu)001:13812: de tshe nyul le bskrad pa ni las slob pas ging chas thogs la 'jigs pa la zhugs /
NK078(tshu)001:13813: mi rkang mi lpags 'bras mchan sngags ldan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13814: bong mdze 'ug mgo skam po'i tho ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13815: gu gul sbyar ma yang bshams te /
NK078(tshu)001:13817: e gru gsum dong nang du /
NK078(tshu)001:13818: nyung le ma rnams kyi ming gi dril bskor bar byas la /
NK078(tshu)001:13820: pho nya btang nas bskrad dgos par gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:13821: gnyis pa nye bsnyen gyi tshad dang byed las bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13823: de yang zla ba phyed zhag bdun du nye ba'i bsnyen pa bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13824: bdag dam tshig gi lha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13825: mdun ye shes kyi lha rang bzhin lhun grub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13826: ye shes kyi lhar gsal ba'i bar du bzlas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13827: 'od zer dkar po 'phro bas bde bar gshegs pa
NK078(tshu)001:13829: tshur 'dus bdag gi sgrib pa sbyang nas dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13832: de nas zhag bco lnga'i nub tha ma zhag gcig
NK078(tshu)001:13833: ma gtogs pa mar phyed zhag bdun du sgrub pa
NK078(tshu)001:13834: bya ste / bzlas pa'i 'od zer dmar po phar
NK078(tshu)001:13835: 'phros pas dngos grub stsol cig par bskul tshur 'dus
NK078(tshu)001:13836: pas dngos grub thob par bsgom ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13837: de gnyis bsnol mar byas bas don gnyis bsgrub par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13838: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po dang zhor la zhag
NK078(tshu)001:13839: grangs rgyud bzhin shes nas bsgrub dgos par bstan pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:13841: de ltar sgrub pa'i zhag grangs zla ba drug bcu
NK078(tshu)001:13842: gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gang dang gang yin pa
NK078(tshu)001:13843: dang / bzlas pa'i grangs tshang nas 'grub pa'i rtagsa 'od la sogs pa rnams byung na /
NK078(tshu)001:13844: nub tha ma la ye shes lha'i sku gsung thugs
NK078(tshu)001:13845: kyi dngos grub bzlas pa'i 'od zer kha dog mthing
NK078(tshu)001:13846: ga tshur bdag la 'dus nas blang ba ni sgrub
NK078(tshu)001:13848: dngos grub yum gyi mkha' las blang ba ni sgrub pa chen po +aa li nyams su len pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13849: gong gi dus zla phyed la sogs pa de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:13850: du brtsis pas chog gam zhe na mi chog ste
NK078(tshu)001:13851: / bsnyen sgrub kyi yun rgyud kyi nang nas gsungs
NK078(tshu)001:13852: pa'i zhag grangs ni sum cu phrag drug la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:13853: pa bshad pa bzhin du cha bgo la bsgom bzlas
NK078(tshu)001:13854: la bar chad med par tshom bu tshogs bsgruba para
NK078(tshu)001:13855: / bya'o // gnyis pa sgrub pa'i grogs yo byad la spyad thabs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13857: dang po yo byad lnga la spyad thabs mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13859: tshogs sgrub pa'i dus su spyir spyod lam du yo byad lnga la longs spyod cing rol la /
NK078(tshu)001:13860: gnyis pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa dngosa su spyod lugs khro bo'i skabs su bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13862: bye brag tu dngos su phyungs pa sbyor sgrol gyi
NK078(tshu)001:13863: mchod pa rnam pa gnyis po tshogs sgrub kyi skabs
NK078(tshu)001:13864: su gal che bas gtsos su dgos pa gang ltar
NK078(tshu)001:13865: yin pa'i tshul rgyas bshad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:13866: dkyus kyi phyi ma gdug pa 'dul bar byed po khro bo'i skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13867: gsum pa yo byad lnga la spyad thabs yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:13868: dang bcas pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:13870: dang po mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang nas chos nyid la chos nyid /
NK078(tshu)001:13871: ye shes la ye shes rol pa'i tshul gyis spyad thabs zhi khro gnyis thun mong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13873: gong du bstan pa'i snga ma yo byad lnga la
NK078(tshu)001:13874: spyad thabs rgyas par bshad cing gsal bar bstan par
NK078(tshu)001:13876: gos dang rgyan gyi yo byad bza' ba dang btung ba'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13879: rang rig pa'i ye shes yi ge h'u gis mtshon
NK078(tshu)001:13880: nas ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du shes pas yo
NK078(tshu)001:13881: byad rnams la spyod bzhin ma chags pa'i tshul gyis
NK078(tshu)001:13883: ngo mtshar ba 'bras bu'i tshogs chen gnyis 'byung ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:13884: dkyil 'khor thams cad bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pas
NK078(tshu)001:13886: gsang ba +aa li k+aa li la sogs pa'i yo byad bza' btung gos rgyan /
NK078(tshu)001:13887: bro grar glu tshig ste lnga po rnams rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:13888: don dam ma skyes pa'i chos nyid rang rig pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13889: ye shes kyi ngo bo gsal bas mi rtog pa
NK078(tshu)001:13890: chos nyid la / chos nyid thim pas kun rdzob
NK078(tshu)001:13891: du ma 'gag pa'i ye shes gnyis med kyi rol
NK078(tshu)001:13893: zhi ba las cig shos khro bo tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13894: yo byad la spyod pa'i tshe na'ang mtshan ma med
NK078(tshu)001:13895: pa'i spyod thabs ting nge 'dzin de bzhin du bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:13896: par bya ste mthun par bya ba bstan pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:13897: no // gnyis pa mtshan bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang nas spyad thabs de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13898: lha bye brag tu gsal ba'i ngang nas yo byad lnga la spyad bye brag tu bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13899: spyir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:13900: ngang nas yo byad la longs spyod pa'i yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:13901: bstan pa'o // dang po la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13902: yo byad bzhi la spyad thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13903: yo byad bzhi la spyad pa'i rjes su gsang ba'i yo byad la spyad thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:13905: bsam yas lhun grub kyi ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:13906: ngang nas lus bsgul yan lag bsigs pa'i yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:13907: dang gtso bo lha rang rang gi lus la lus
NK078(tshu)001:13908: kyi yan lag dang rtog pa'i yan lag gis lha
NK078(tshu)001:13909: gsal ba'i ngang nas bro glu gos rgyan la spyod
NK078(tshu)001:13911: tshom bu rang rang gi lha gsal ba'i ngang nas
NK078(tshu)001:13912: bro glu dang bza' btung la spyod pa'i yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:13913: no // dang po la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13917: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i mtha' yas ba'i snod
NK078(tshu)001:13918: bcud 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad rang rig pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:13919: ngang du dbyer med pa'i man+dal te dkyil 'khor /
NK078(tshu)001:13920: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i phyir nyi zla shar
NK078(tshu)001:13921: ba'i gdan dang bcas ba'i gzhal yas khang de la
NK078(tshu)001:13922: pad+ma ltar chagsa pa med pa'i gdan bting nas /
NK078(tshu)001:13923: rgyu ye shes rin po che yon tan zad pa
NK078(tshu)001:13924: med par 'byung ba'i pho brang gi lha'i gzhal yas
NK078(tshu)001:13925: khang dbus kyi lte ba la sogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13926: de yang rgya che chung gi tshad blos dpag tu med pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:13927: lha'i ngo bo rang rig byang chub bde ba chen
NK078(tshu)001:13928: po dang ldan pa bzhugs pa'i gzhal yas khang gi
NK078(tshu)001:13930: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i bde ba
NK078(tshu)001:13931: chen po dang ldan pa'i byang chub kyi sems lha
NK078(tshu)001:13932: dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor te tshom bu gang yin
NK078(tshu)001:13933: gyi lha ting nge 'dzin gyis rab tu bkod nas
NK078(tshu)001:13934: 'dod pa ci byed na yo byad la longs spyad
NK078(tshu)001:13935: pa'o // snod bcud kyi rtog pa ma lus pa
NK078(tshu)001:13936: thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings
NK078(tshu)001:13938: gnyis pa spyod lugs kyi yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:13940: lus bskyod pa dang yan lag bsgul cing bsigs na /
NK078(tshu)001:13941: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po lnga'i spyod yul lha rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba kun kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:13942: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po nyid du ye nas yin par bshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:13943: gnyis pa lus dang yan lag gi lha gsal ba'i dang nas spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13948: dang po gzhal yas khang dang lha bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13950: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor spros pa
NK078(tshu)001:13951: 'ba' zhig bsgom pa'i skabs na mi re lha re
NK078(tshu)001:13952: bsgom pa'i lus la lus kyi yan lag dang rtog
NK078(tshu)001:13953: pa'i yan lag gi lha bkod nasabasgoma mam /
NK078(tshu)001:13954: cig gis kun bsgom byed na 'dir bro sogs byed
NK078(tshu)001:13955: pa'i tshe na rang lha gsal lus la yan lag
NK078(tshu)001:13956: gi lha bkod nas sgom pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:13957: b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang dang 'og gzhi tsakra rtsibs
NK078(tshu)001:13958: bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor du gdan
NK078(tshu)001:13959: nyi zla gnyis zung du 'phrul par brtsegs pa'i sa
NK078(tshu)001:13960: gzhi la / pad+ma chags med kyi gdan bting nas /
NK078(tshu)001:13961: gong gi gdan de'i steng du rnal 'byor ba thabsa
NK078(tshu)001:13962: lha yab dang shes rab lha yum du gsal bas
NK078(tshu)001:13963: gcig la gcig chags pa med pa'i tshul du bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:13964: pas / gnyis pa yan lag gi lha bsgom pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13968: lus kyi yan lag bzhi mgo dang lnga po thams cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:13969: rang rgyud pa'i rnam pa min te rang bzhin ngang
NK078(tshu)001:13970: ngam yongs kyi lha rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du rnam
NK078(tshu)001:13971: par dag pa yin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13972: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13973: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:13977: ye nas rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pas byed pa
NK078(tshu)001:13978: po sus kyang ma bcos par yongs kyis grub pa
NK078(tshu)001:13979: la de rang rgyud du grub pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:13980: gzhi ye nas de ltar yin pa la yin pa
NK078(tshu)001:13981: ltar du bsgom pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:13982: rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha ji ltar bsgom zhe
NK078(tshu)001:13983: na / rnal 'byor pas tshom bu'i lhar gsal ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:13984: dbu la de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi gtso bo
NK078(tshu)001:13986: yana lag bzhi la rigs bzhi'i gtso 'khor gyi lha bcu bcu ste bzhi bcu bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:13987: de yang lag pa g.yas rdo rje'i rigs kyi lha bcu /
NK078(tshu)001:13988: g.yon rin chen rigs rkang g.yon pad+ma'i rigs /
NK078(tshu)001:13990: lha de dag gi kha dog dang dbyibs dang phyag rgya phyag mtshan rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:13991: thabs yab dang shes rab yab yum ste tshom bu bcu gsal bar bsgom ste /
NK078(tshu)001:13992: gnyis pa 'phro 'du byas pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:13994: lha de dag las 'od zer phyogsa bcura spros shing
NK078(tshu)001:13995: don gnyis byas khyad par du ngan song gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:13997: slar rang lhar gsal ba'i yan lag gi gansa su bsdu zhing dkyil 'khor la bstim mo //
NK078(tshu)001:13998: 'das pa theg 'og dang ma 'das pa 'khor ba'i sems can thams cada kun /
NK078(tshu)001:13999: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhing khams khyad par can du rnam par sbyongs te sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14000: gnyis pa spyad thabs kyi yan lag la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14001: spyod pa'i yon tan bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14004: bro gar glu tshig thun mong du spyad thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14005: gar dang mngon shes kyi spyad thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:14010: de ltar rnal 'byor pas lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK078(tshu)001:14011: ba'i yan lag chen po mgo bo la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:14012: lnga bskyod na / gnyis pa yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:14014: rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thugs rjes gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:14015: don la g.yo nas don ci mdzad na 'gro ba
NK078(tshu)001:14016: lnga'i sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i byang
NK078(tshu)001:14017: chub kyi lam du 'dzud par mdzad cig /dus /
NK078(tshu)001:14021: nyon mongs pa'i snyigs ma lnga yang sems nyid bde ba'i ngang du rnam par dag go //
NK078(tshu)001:14022: gnyis pa bgo ba gos la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14026: rgyu bzang la kha dog mdzes shing bzo legs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:14027: dar gyi chas gos lnga bgos nas ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:14028: gyi ye shes lnga'i 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro bar
NK078(tshu)001:14029: bsgoms na yon tan ni 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro
NK078(tshu)001:14030: bar 'gyur te / gnyis pa yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:14032: de nas dus mthar thug med kyi bar du /
NK078(tshu)001:14033: ye shes lnga rtogs pa yis rang la brgyan par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:14034: gsum pa rgyan la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14038: rin po che'i rgyan brgyad la sogs pa'i rgyan mchog mdzes pas rnal 'byor pa'i lus brgyan nas /
NK078(tshu)001:14039: lha'i ting nge 'dzin gyi tshom bu'i lha tshogs la 'od zer 'bar zhing gsal bar bsgom ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14040: de las phyogs bcu gang bar lha'i dkyil 'khor spro zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:14041: spro dus rig pa bdag nyid chen po lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:14042: gsal dus sems nyid mi dmigs pa skye ba med
NK078(tshu)001:14043: pa'i dbyings kyi ngang nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams
NK078(tshu)001:14045: 'dod yon lnga ru gsal ba ma 'gags pa thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14046: rang bzhin med pa'i shes rab kyi tshul du gnas par spyad pas /
NK078(tshu)001:14047: bde ba mchog gi ro yang myong zhing bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs par byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:14048: bde ba de la ma chags shing 'dzin pa med
NK078(tshu)001:14049: pa'i ye shes kyi tshogs dang tshogs chen po gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:14051: gnyis pa bro gar glu tshig la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14052: thun mong du spyad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14053: gar bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14058: rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i gar thab kya phyag rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14059: ngag gis snyan pa'i glu dbyangs bden pa'i tshig dang
NK078(tshu)001:14060: ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa dag gis sgra bsgrags
NK078(tshu)001:14061: na yon tan gang 'byung snyam pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:14064: phyogs bcu'i 'gro drug gi skye gnas bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can ma lus pa kun /
NK078(tshu)001:14065: sku lnga lhun grub drug pa rdo rje 'chang chen po'i sku ru mthong bar 'gyur zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:14066: glu'i yo tan gyi sgra skad thams cad gsung lnga
NK078(tshu)001:14067: lhun grub dam pa chos kyi dung chen po'i sgra
NK078(tshu)001:14069: nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa gnyis byang
NK078(tshu)001:14070: nas lhag pa'i 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang
NK078(tshu)001:14072: de yang sgrib pa gnyis po ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:14073: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pas blo la chos nyid gsal du mi ster ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14074: shes bya'i sgrib pas shes bya la ye shes 'phel du mi ster ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14075: yang na nyon sgrib kyis tshogs spyod kyi chos nyid gsal du mi ster ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14076: shes sgrib kyis mthong sgom yan chad kyi chos nyid gsal du mi ster ba'ang yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:14077: de ltar na lam pa gang la sgrib pa gang yod ce na /
NK078(tshu)001:14078: 'di'i lugs la tshogs lam la las sgrib /
NK078(tshu)001:14080: mthong lam la kun 'gro'i sgrib pa /
NK078(tshu)001:14081: sgom lam la lhan cig gnas pa'i sgrib pa /
NK078(tshu)001:14082: mthar lam la bag la nyal ba'i sgrib pa rnams yod par 'dod do //
NK078(tshu)001:14083: sgrib pa de dag spang tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14084: des lam ji bzhin pa'i dbang du lta ba sngon du 'gro ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:14085: de yang rtogs nas goms dgos pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:14086: shes sgrib thog mar spangs bar 'dod la /
NK078(tshu)001:14088: lam rtogs thabs kyi dbang du sgom pa sngon du 'gro ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14089: de yang nyon mongs phra rags ci rigs pa dag nas ye shes 'phel ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:14090: nyon sgrib thog mar spang bar 'dod do //
NK078(tshu)001:14091: bro'i sgo nas bden pa mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14092: glu'i sgo nas snyan pa dang grags pa thob cing /
NK078(tshu)001:14093: bsod nams kyi tshogs chen po 'grub la /
NK078(tshu)001:14094: de la yang chags pa med cing mi 'dzin pas
NK078(tshu)001:14095: ye shes kyi tshogs chen po gnyis dang ldan par
NK078(tshu)001:14096: 'gyur ro // gnyis pa gar bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14098: rnal 'byor pho mo lhar gsal ba'i thabs yab dang
NK078(tshu)001:14099: shes rab yum thams cad kun langs la gar bya
NK078(tshu)001:14100: ba ni / mi gcig gi kun sgom par byed
NK078(tshu)001:14101: na gar byed dus 'khor bsdus la rang rang gtso
NK078(tshu)001:14102: ba ni / bor gsal bas / dbus nas shar gyi phyogs su kha bltas te /
NK078(tshu)001:14103: rtogs pa zil gyis gnon pa seng ge'i ltabs chen gyis mchong bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14104: lnga pa mngon shes la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14106: dang po spyod pa dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14111: lus kyi dbang po ste snying ga'am lte ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:14112: lnga la rigs lnga'i yi ge lnga sgom tshul ni
NK078(tshu)001:14116: lce la h+r+aih lus la +aahste de rnams gsal ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:14117: ye shes las 'od zer 'phros pa 'phags pa mchod
NK078(tshu)001:14119: tshur 'dus bdag gi la sogs pa la thim pas
NK078(tshu)001:14120: mig gis gzugs nye ring med par mthong ba la
NK078(tshu)001:14121: sogs pa'i mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs so
NK078(tshu)001:14123: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14124: shar gyi phyogs su kha bltas te //
NK078(tshu)001:14125: seng ge'i stobs chen mchongs bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:14126: lce dkyil yi ge h+r+aihbasgoma nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14127: lce ni bsam gyis mi khyab dang //
NK078(tshu)001:14128: h+r+aihyanga bsam gyis mi khyab spro //
NK078(tshu)001:14129: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mtha' yas su //
NK078(tshu)001:14131: gsung gcig dkyil 'khor yan lag ni //
NK078(tshu)001:14132: bsam gyis mi khyab kun tu grags //
NK078(tshu)001:14133: sgra dang ming tshig so sor grags //
NK078(tshu)001:14134: ljags kyi dbang po bgram las gsungs //
NK078(tshu)001:14135: thar dang ma thar gnyis ka brjod //
NK078(tshu)001:14136: des pa kho nar yang dag 'dus //
NK078(tshu)001:14137: de bzhin nyid kyis gcig ma gsungs //
NK078(tshu)001:14138: rna ba'i dbang po'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK078(tshu)001:14139: tram gi yi ge gsal bsgoms nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14140: mtha' yas bsam gyis mi khyab spro //
NK078(tshu)001:14142: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor ma lus thob //
NK078(tshu)001:14144: sgra dang thos pa gnyis med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14145: de bzhin dri dang ro reg rnams //
NK078(tshu)001:14146: so so'i mtshan nyid gsal bsgom na //
NK078(tshu)001:14147: yig 'bru'i snying po ji bzhin dgod //
NK078(tshu)001:14148: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus dang //
NK078(tshu)001:14149: 'gro drug ma lus thams cad kun //
NK078(tshu)001:14150: chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis rol //
NK078(tshu)001:14151: dri la sogs pa bde mchog gis //
NK078(tshu)001:14152: kun la tshims par yang dag mchog /
NK078(tshu)001:14153: 'gro drug ma lus thams cad la //
NK078(tshu)001:14154: ji ltar 'tshams pa'i don yang byed //
NK078(tshu)001:14155: thabs mkhas thugs rje de ltar ston //
NK078(tshu)001:14156: kun byas byang chub nyid du 'ong //
NK078(tshu)001:14158: gnyis pa spyod pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:14160: des 'dod pa'i yon tan gzugs sogs yul lnga la 'dzin pa med par rol pas /
NK078(tshu)001:14161: yon tan des rnal 'byor ba bdag gi don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14162: gdul bya sems can gzhan gyi don rnams yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:14163: gsum pa tshom bu rang rang gi lhar gsal ba'i ngang nas spyod thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14165: dang po spyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14167: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang yang rung ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:14168: lhar gsal ba'i rnal 'byor pa yab yum rnams kyi
NK078(tshu)001:14169: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14170: phan tshun gcig la gcig 'od zer phar 'phro zhing
NK078(tshu)001:14171: tshur bsdu ba'i ngang las mthar bdag nyid la bstim
NK078(tshu)001:14172: par byas te / de ltar rnal 'byor pa lhag
NK078(tshu)001:14173: pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor tshom bu gang
NK078(tshu)001:14174: rung gi lha 'od 'bar ba ting nge 'dzin gsal
NK078(tshu)001:14175: bar gyur nas rnal 'byor pas bdag cag tshom bu'i
NK078(tshu)001:14177: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad gnyis su med par bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:14178: gnyis pa spyod thabs de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14180: dang po bro gar glu la spyod pa'i thabs yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14182: de nas rigs lnga po'i gtso bo dbus na gnas pa'i de bzhin rigs shar dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14185: las byang phyogs te rang rang gi phyogs su rim pa bzhin du kha bltas te /
NK078(tshu)001:14190: las kyi rigs don grub gyi glu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14191: bro'i tshig rgyas pa'i rgyud nas 'byung ba ltar brjod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14192: de'ang ye shes lngas brgyan pa'i glu bro bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14193: rigs lnga spyi'i glu tshig brjod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14194: bro bya ba ni seng ge /
NK078(tshu)001:14198: rnam pa lnga yi stobs lnga dang glu dang ldan par bya ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:14199: rang rang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi srog dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:14200: pa'i rigs lnga'i bro glus bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:14202: de yang bro tshig brjod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14204: dbus nas shar du kha bltas te //
NK078(tshu)001:14205: rkang pa'i stabs chen bskyod byas shing //
NK078(tshu)001:14206: lag gi 'du byed bskyod byas nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14207: bro dang gar gyi phyag rgya bya //
NK078(tshu)001:14209: byang chub sems su rnam par dag /shin tu gsal dang 'od zer 'bar //
NK078(tshu)001:14210: thabs dang shes rab bde bar 'grub //
NK078(tshu)001:14211: cing kyang mi tshugs rdo rje yin //
NK078(tshu)001:14212: bdud bzhi dag ni 'joms par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:14213: theg mchog rdo rje'i rig 'dzin pa //
NK078(tshu)001:14214: thabs dang shes rab bde 'grub shog /mnyam nyid rigs pa rdo rje yis //
NK078(tshu)001:14215: nyon mongs sdug bsngal med par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:14216: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:14217: thabs dang shes rab gsal 'gyur shog /nyon mongs sdug bsngal brtsad bcad nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14218: ma rig mun pa med par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:14219: thugs rje'i 'od zer nyi shar bas //
NK078(tshu)001:14220: thabs dang shes rab 'od 'bar shog /shin tu sra zhing skye shi med //
NK078(tshu)001:14221: rdo rje thugs rje rol ston pa //
NK078(tshu)001:14223: thabs dang shes rab byams ldan shog /de nas sku de bzhin gshegs pa'i bro glu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14225: glang po che yi stangs stabs kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:14226: bde gshegs ma lus thams cad kun //
NK078(tshu)001:14227: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK078(tshu)001:14228: mi dmigs thugs rje'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK078(tshu)001:14229: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /thabs chen dkyil 'khor yang dag pa //
NK078(tshu)001:14230: bde gshegs kun la yang dag 'phro //
NK078(tshu)001:14231: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yis //
NK078(tshu)001:14232: bde bas dkyil du mkhas pas bsdus //
NK078(tshu)001:14233: thams cad ma lus rigs bzhi yi //
NK078(tshu)001:14234: nang du ma lus gang yang med //
NK078(tshu)001:14235: de ni bde gshegs dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:14236: thabs dang shes rab bde 'grub shog /de nas yon tan rin 'byung gi bro glu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14237: rta mchog gi stangs stabs bya zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:14238: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur pas //
NK078(tshu)001:14239: yon tan phyogs su kha bltas te //
NK078(tshu)001:14240: lus bsigs yan lag bsgul bskyod nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14241: stabs chen dag kyang brdung bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:14243: zag med nor bu rin po che //
NK078(tshu)001:14244: ma lus kun gyi re ba skong //
NK078(tshu)001:14245: thabs dang shes rab bde 'grub shog /de nas gsung snang ba mtha' yas kyi bro glu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14246: rma bya'i stangs stabs bya zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:14247: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14248: nub phyogs su ni kha bltas te //
NK078(tshu)001:14249: lus bsigs yan lag bsgul bskyod cing //
NK078(tshu)001:14250: yan lag lnga po bskyod byas te //
NK078(tshu)001:14251: gar rnams shin tu gsal byas nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14252: stabs chen dag kyang brdung bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:14253: chos rnams ma lus kun bskyod kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:14255: chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:14256: thabs dang shes rab bde 'grub shog /de nas phrin las don grub kyi bro glu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14257: shang shang gi stangs stabs bya zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:14258: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur pas //
NK078(tshu)001:14259: byang phyogs su ni kha bltas nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14260: lus bskyod yan lag gar bskyod cing //
NK078(tshu)001:14261: phyag rgya so sor gsal gyur nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14262: rkang pa'i stabs chen brdung bar bya //
NK078(tshu)001:14263: yang dag rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:14264: bskal pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:14265: sgrib pa thams cad byang byas nas //
NK078(tshu)001:14266: thabs dang shes rab myur 'grub shog /ces so //
NK078(tshu)001:14267: gnyis pa bza' btung la spyad thabs de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14271: bza' ba dang bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14272: mur ba dang btung ba'i bye bra ga gi yo byad rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:14273: de dag tu snang ba ma 'gags pa thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14274: rang bzhin med pa shes rab de nyid gnyis su med pa'i ngang la gnas shing /
NK078(tshu)001:14275: mchod bya mchod byed tha mi dad par shes pas
NK078(tshu)001:14276: bdag nyid chen po gnas su stobs pa'i mchod pa
NK078(tshu)001:14277: phul ba yis / gnyis pa spyod pa'i yon tan de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14279: dang po mchog gi dngos grub tu gyur pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14281: sems nyid kyi ngang du bdag dang sangas rgyas gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:14282: su med pas sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK078(tshu)001:14283: thams cad la mnyes pas khyab cing /
NK078(tshu)001:14284: bdag dang sems can dbyer med pas srid pa gsum gyi sems can ma lus pa thams cad la /
NK078(tshu)001:14285: dga' ba dang bde ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:14286: gnyis pa zas bdud rtsi mchog tu bsgyur zhing thun mong gi dngos grub pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:14288: zas dug can la yi ge +aahbakoda de 'ju 'dul
NK078(tshu)001:14289: byed pa tsam gyis bdud rtsir 'gyur zhing de'i yon
NK078(tshu)001:14291: yon tan gang zhe na bdud rtsi'i zas de zos pas /
NK078(tshu)001:14292: rlung mkhris ban kan 'du ba bzhi bo re re la yang brgya rtsa gcig re re ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14293: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel cing bdud rtsi'i 'od
NK078(tshu)001:14294: zer las longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa 'byung zhing
NK078(tshu)001:14295: / ngan song gsum du skye ba'i sa bon tri pre duhrnamasa sbyang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14296: de las gzhan pa ci yang gzhan du ste bye
NK078(tshu)001:14297: ma las gser du 'gyur ba la sogs pa phan
NK078(tshu)001:14298: tshun mi mthun pa 'gyur bar 'grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:14299: gnyis pa gsang ba +aa li sbyor ba'i yo byad la spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14301: dang po yab yum gyi mkha' gsang brlabs nas bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i sbyang thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14303: de ltar yo byad bzhi dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:14304: pa yis thabs yab dang shes rab yum du ldan
NK078(tshu)001:14305: par gyur nas / phung po khams dang skye mched
NK078(tshu)001:14306: rnams lha dang mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mara byin
NK078(tshu)001:14307: gyis brlab cing 'dod pa sbyor ba'i bstan chos kyis
NK078(tshu)001:14308: bde ba rgyas pa'i cha rnams kyang rdzogs par bya
NK078(tshu)001:14309: par gyur nas / ba ste / bsnyen pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14312: sgrub pa chen po gsang ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i rim pas /
NK078(tshu)001:14313: rtog pa thams cad bde stong gnyis su med pa'i yum gyi mkha' dbyings su sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14314: gnyis pa yon tan de la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14316: dang po zab mo'i dbang gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14318: yab yum thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i gsang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:14319: mkha' dbyings nas nyi zla byang chub kyi sems bde
NK078(tshu)001:14321: 'od zer lus la 'phro zhing bde ba 'bar ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:14322: lus kyi phyogs bcur rtsa khams kyi rang bzhin bde
NK078(tshu)001:14323: ba'i ye shes su gsal zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:14324: zag med kyi bde bas lus la khyab pas na
NK078(tshu)001:14325: thabs chen po snying rje bas lhag pas na thabs
NK078(tshu)001:14326: kyi mchog shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang bde
NK078(tshu)001:14327: ba'i mchog shin tu brtan pa dang ldan pas dbang
NK078(tshu)001:14328: yang rdzogs pa'o // gnyis pa gsang ba'i lha mo
NK078(tshu)001:14329: bcu gnyis rdzogs par rol ba'i dus su lha'i dkyil
NK078(tshu)001:14332: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje dang yum gyi mkha'
NK078(tshu)001:14333: dril bu gnyis sbyor ba las byung ba yang dag
NK078(tshu)001:14334: pa'i bde ba dang ldan pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:14335: phyag rgya bzhi ni g.yas kyis bzung ba lcags kyu ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14336: g.yon gyis 'khyud pa zhags pa ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14337: stod smad bsdom pa lcags sgrog ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14338: bde ba skyod pa dril bu ma dang lha mo brgyad ni yab yum chas kyis sgeg pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:14339: nyi zla dkar dmar gyi mdzes pa l+aa s+ye ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14340: bde ba rgyun mi 'chad pa m+aa le ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14341: rtsa gnas ha si'i sgra sgrog pa girti ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14342: rtsa mdud grol ba'am bskyod pa ni nirti ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14343: bde ba'i ros chi ma pa d+hu pe ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14345: bde stong gi don gsal ba +aa lo ke /
NK078(tshu)001:14346: bde bas bsil zhing ros gang ba g+ha n+d+he ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14347: de ltar gsang ba'i lha mo bcu gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:14348: rdzogs par yab yum rol bas nyi zla byang chub
NK078(tshu)001:14349: kyi sems gnyis dus gcig tu mkha' la ldan nas
NK078(tshu)001:14350: / yab yum thabs shes gnyis med du nyi zla zung du 'brel bar gyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:14351: rtog tshogs thams cad bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khora
NK078(tshu)001:14352: du gsal bas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK078(tshu)001:14353: 'byung zhes bya'o // gsum pa thun mong gi dngos grub 'grub pa'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14355: de'i dus su yab yum gyi thig le nyi zla
NK078(tshu)001:14356: slar bzlog nas rlung dang 'dres pas skye 'jig med
NK078(tshu)001:14357: pa rdo rje'i gzugs su chags pas thabs las gyur
NK078(tshu)001:14359: de ltar sbyor ba'i mchod pa chen po des thun mong gi dngos grub ni tshe ring ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14360: mkha' la bya bzhin 'gro ba dang kha dog gsal zhing 'od zer 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:14361: bzhi pa mchog gi dngos grub 'bras bu 'grub pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:14364: dang po yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14366: sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum 'phrul pa mtshon pa
NK078(tshu)001:14367: lha yab ste phung po lnga la sogs pa rtog
NK078(tshu)001:14368: pa thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:14369: su snang ste / yab yum 'brel ba dra ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:14370: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rang rig pa'i mgon
NK078(tshu)001:14371: sum du gsal bar rdzogs shing grub pas /
NK078(tshu)001:14372: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:14373: thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bas na spyod
NK078(tshu)001:14374: yul dang bral ba yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK078(tshu)001:14375: gyi sa mngon sum du rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu ni
NK078(tshu)001:14376: / rgyal rnams gcig dang du ma'i mtha' las grol pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:14377: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor lhag ma ma lus pa thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:14378: gnyis pa ye shes bla ma'i sa mthong ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14380: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:14381: la brtan pa thob pa'i tshad gsal ba yul rkyen
NK078(tshu)001:14382: gyis mi 'phrog pa'i rnal 'byor pa yis 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:14384: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir yang dag pa'i sa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:14385: 'gro ba'i don la gshegs pa'i sangsa rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14386: khams gsum 'gro ba sems can rnams kyi khams dang
NK078(tshu)001:14387: bsam pa thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum du
NK078(tshu)001:14388: gnyis med gsal bar 'gyur ba ni ye shes bla
NK078(tshu)001:14389: ma'i sa thob pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:14390: gnyis pa spyir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:14391: gsal ba'i ngang las yo byad la spyod pa'i yon
NK078(tshu)001:14393: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i lha ya ba yum zung du 'brel ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14394: sgyu 'phrul dra ba ste de dag rang rig pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:14395: mngon sum du rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang rnam grangs
NK078(tshu)001:14396: spros pa la brtan pa thob pa'i snang ba rnam
NK078(tshu)001:14397: 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa des yo
NK078(tshu)001:14398: byad lnga la spyod pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14399: de yang bro gar 'du 'phro la spyod pa'i dus su /
NK078(tshu)001:14400: lus dang rtog pa'i yan lag la lha gsal bar bkod de /
NK078(tshu)001:14401: rkang ba'i bro stabs dang lag gi gar stabs sna
NK078(tshu)001:14402: tshogs kyi glu tshig dang bcas pa blang ba'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:14403: na / sprul pa'i 'phro 'du dang bcas pa'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:14404: su lha'i sku gsung thugs mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:14405: yi sgo nas bro gar byas pa'i yon tan ni
NK078(tshu)001:14406: na / / ri brag dang sa la thogs chags
NK078(tshu)001:14407: med par 'dzul zhing rkang 'og gi klu'i bu mo
NK078(tshu)001:14408: la longs spyod pas dbang du 'dus la nam mkha'
NK078(tshu)001:14409: la bya bzhin du 'phur nas 'gro zhing lha dang
NK078(tshu)001:14410: gnod sbyin gyi bu mo rnams la longs spyod pas
NK078(tshu)001:14411: thams cad bran du khol zhing dbang du 'du bar
NK078(tshu)001:14413: chos thams cad rang rig pa kho nar rang snang ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:14414: de yang ngag gi sgo nas glu tshig dang sgra yi yo byad la /
NK078(tshu)001:14415: spyod pa'i dus su lha'i sku gsung thugs su 'da'
NK078(tshu)001:14416: med pa'i phyag rgya yi ngang nas lce'i steng du
NK078(tshu)001:14418: de yang yar rgyal ba la bstod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14419: mar 'gro ba rang rang skad du mos pa ltar
NK078(tshu)001:14420: chos ston par bsgom pa'i 'bras bu gdul bya so
NK078(tshu)001:14421: so la / chos kyi 'khor lo so sor ston pa'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:14422: zhi ba'i chas gos lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14423: rin po che'i rgyan de bcu gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14424: khro bo bsgrub na rus pa'i rgyan lnga dang sbrul gyi rgyan brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14425: glang chen gyi ko rlon la sogs pa bgo ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:14426: yo byad la spyod dus sku gsung thugs las mi
NK078(tshu)001:14427: 'da' ba'i phyag rgya yi ngang nas spyod pa'i 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:14428: bu ni / lus shin tu 'phags pa'i gzi byin
NK078(tshu)001:14429: gyi 'od 'abra ba'i rgyal bo des gzhan thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:14430: zil gyis gnon pa sus kyang thub pa med pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:14431: seng ge lta bur gnas pa 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK078(tshu)001:14432: bu ni / // dam rdzas lngas bzhi byas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:14433: bza' ba dang btung ba'i longs spyod sna tshogs rnams
NK078(tshu)001:14434: 'dod yon gyi lha mor byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:14435: rang lhar gsal ba'i sku gsung thugs su gsal ba'i phyag rgya yi mchod pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14436: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin chen gyi tshon shel
NK078(tshu)001:14437: gyi par khab tu bcug pa lta bu'i sku gzi
NK078(tshu)001:14439: zas thams cad bdud rtsi'i bcud zag pa med pas
NK078(tshu)001:14440: 'gro ba thams cad kyang tshims par byed pa 'grub
NK078(tshu)001:14441: par 'gyur ro // brda tshig tu bstan pa'i k+aa
NK078(tshu)001:14442: li sgrol ba dang +aa li sbyor ba'i yo byad
NK078(tshu)001:14443: par 'gyur ro // dang / yang na k+aa li thabs yab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14444: +aa li shes rab yum gnyis kyi phung khams skye
NK078(tshu)001:14445: mched lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar gsal ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:14446: ngang du snyoms par zhugs pa yis 'bras bu ni
NK078(tshu)001:14447: / phrin las bzhi po thams cad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14448: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad ci
NK078(tshu)001:14449: 'dod pa rnams bdag gi bsam pa yongs su skong
NK078(tshu)001:14450: ba 'grub cing thob par 'gyur ba kho na'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14451: spyi don gnyis pa khro bo'i tshogs sgrub pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14452: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14453: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14458: gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba khro bo'i tshogs rnams bsgrub par bya ba 'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:14459: gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14460: zla rog sgrub pa po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14462: dus dang sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa rnams ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14463: khro bo'i tshogs sgrub kyi mchog tu dmigs pas sgrub gzhi bzhag pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14464: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14466: dang po gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14468: dur khrod dam rtsi shing gi nags tshal chen po yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14469: grong las dpag tshad rgyang grags kyi las ring ba /
NK078(tshu)001:14470: dgra bgegs nad gsum gyi bar chad kyis dbena pa'i sar /
NK078(tshu)001:14471: rngams glog dang rdo rje las rim la sogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:14472: gzhung nas bshad pa dang mthun pa'i gnas rnyed nas
NK078(tshu)001:14473: ni / sa'i cho ga bya ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14474: dang po sa phyogs de yi gdon bgegs la zhi ba'i sgo nas glud gtor sbyin /
NK078(tshu)001:14475: khro bo'i phur pas bskrad cing sa la gter mnan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14476: sa gzhi dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang ngam /
NK078(tshu)001:14477: ye shes rin po che'i gzhal yas khang du byin
NK078(tshu)001:14478: gyis brlabs pa la sogs pa gzhi mnyam pa ste
NK078(tshu)001:14479: sa'i cho ga rnams rdo rje las rim ltar rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:14480: par bya ba'o // gnyis pa sgrub pa po la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14482: dang po spyir ting nge 'dzin mthu mnyams pas bsgrub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14484: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste khro bo yab yum lha
NK078(tshu)001:14485: zung du 'brel ba'i mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:14486: pa'i khrag mthung khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha lnga
NK078(tshu)001:14487: bcu rtsa brgyad la sogs bsgom pa'i spros pa'i skabs
NK078(tshu)001:14488: su blo brtan pa thob pa'i stobs kyis cho ga
NK078(tshu)001:14489: lnga dang / sngags kyi yan lag lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14491: chas bco lnga tshang zhing rdzogs pa khro bo mthar phyin pa yis /
NK078(tshu)001:14492: rnal 'byor pa pho mo bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14497: brgya dang bco brgyad la sogs pa sbyor lam pa
NK078(tshu)001:14498: mthu dang skal ba mnyam pa 'dus pas tshogs bsgrubs
NK078(tshu)001:14499: na nges pa the tshom med bar mthong lam gyi
NK078(tshu)001:14501: gnyis pa bye brag tu ston 'khor mtshan nyid dang ldan pas bsgrub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14503: de yang ston pa rdo rje rgyal po dam pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:14504: mdzod gsum la sogs yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa
NK078(tshu)001:14505: dbang gi chu bo rdzogs pa can dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14506: rdo rje rgyal theb yang rdo rje rgyal po dang
NK078(tshu)001:14507: lta bsgom gyi yon tan mnyam par mtshungs pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:14508: / karma las mkhan skad kyi gdangs che zhing snyan la /
NK078(tshu)001:14509: phrin las kyi 'grigs kyi rim pa ma nor ba'i phreng bar ldan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14510: gzhan yang sgrol thabs la mkhas pa rdo rje ging /
NK078(tshu)001:14511: sbyor stongs la mkhas pa rdo rje rgyal mo /
NK078(tshu)001:14512: dgyes pa skong ba'i 'khor gzung ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14513: mched lcam gyi nang du legs nyes kyi stong 'byed pa'i rdo rje spyan ma /
NK078(tshu)001:14514: sgrub pa'i dus tshod 'dzin pa'i rdo rje dus 'dzin /
NK078(tshu)001:14515: kha bskang la g.yos kyi bye brag la mkhas pa'i rdo rje byan po /
NK078(tshu)001:14516: phyi nang gi phrin sbyor ba'i rdul phyag skyes bu'i
NK078(tshu)001:14517: 'khor la sogs pa thams cad 'tshogs pas dkyil 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:14518: zhes bya ste / ji skad du /
NK078(tshu)001:14519: nyung yang pany+tsa yan chad do //
NK078(tshu)001:14521: las bzhi'i yum gyi dpe bstan pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14522: shing ljon pa ltar skyed bya bzang zhing rgyud zhi zhing 'jom dpe dang ldan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14524: skra ni mthon mthing lcang lor 'khyil //
NK078(tshu)001:14525: srid du ring la phra la ldem //
NK078(tshu)001:14526: ljon pa ma zhes bshad pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:14529: skye rgyud dang spun zla mang pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14531: 'dod pa che la brtul zhugs che //
NK078(tshu)001:14532: shes pa che la byad bzhin bzang //
NK078(tshu)001:14533: bu mo mig ring ma ru bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:14534: sbas pa'i brda dang thabs la mkhas //
NK078(tshu)001:14535: lcug phran ma ru bshad pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:14537: shing sdong gcig bzhin spun dang skye rgyud med pa gcig pur 'dug pa de'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14539: skye ba'i rgyud med bkra mi shis //
NK078(tshu)001:14540: gcig pur 'dug pas sdong gcig ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14542: shing me reg tshul du sdug bsngal gyi mes reg ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14543: khyo yang dang yang du shi ba'i yug sa mo lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14545: yan lag thams cad mes tshig bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:14546: gtan du 'phel ba'i rgyu med pa //
NK078(tshu)001:14547: mes reg ma yi rigs su bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:14549: de nyid la sa bzhi'i yum bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14550: ljon pa ma ni zhi ba'i yum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14552: dkar mo bong chung skad che ba //
NK078(tshu)001:14553: bzhin lud gtsug phud g.yas su 'khyil //
NK078(tshu)001:14554: yan lag phra 'jam skad gsal zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:14555: bslu khar lci bas zhi ba bya zhes so //
NK078(tshu)001:14556: lcugs phran ma ni rgyas pa'i yum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14558: zla dang yan lag mang ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:14559: phra zhing yan lag zengs su ring //
NK078(tshu)001:14560: bzhin lus ser zhing gru bzhir gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:14561: rna 'phyang sha dang nu ma rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:14564: sdonga gcig ma ni dbang gi yum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14566: bzhin mdog pad 'dra sog kha ma //
NK078(tshu)001:14567: smin khyug ring la stod smad phyed //
NK078(tshu)001:14568: lus dang chu rlung dri zhim cing //
NK078(tshu)001:14569: bde ba ldan zhing yal ga med //
NK078(tshu)001:14572: me rega ma ni drag po'i yum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14574: nag mo gru gsum rtsid mgo ma //
NK078(tshu)001:14575: khro gnyer pa yi lus ldan zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:14576: gtum zhing barlanga tshig 'dzem bag med //
NK078(tshu)001:14577: btsang sme'i rtog bral gsod par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:14579: de ltar spyi dang bye brag gi mtshan ma rnams rdzogs par btsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14580: rnala 'byor pho mo de dag rnams ni sems nyon
NK078(tshu)001:14581: mongs pa'i chags sdang med par ming po dang sring
NK078(tshu)001:14582: mo'i tshul du gcig la gcig brtse gdung che zhing
NK078(tshu)001:14584: tshom bu lnga pa man chad gcig gis kun bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:14585: byed pa'am yang na mi grangs lha grangs dang sprad
NK078(tshu)001:14586: nas pho mo zung 'brel gyis bsgrub par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14587: gsum pa yo byad la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14588: yo byad rnams 'tshogs par gsogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14589: de ji ltar spyad thabs dang dgos ched do //
NK078(tshu)001:14592: dang po sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14594: dkar rtsi ste yab kyi byang sems dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14595: dmar rtsi ste yum gyi rak+ta /
NK078(tshu)001:14599: rdo rje dung chen te thod pa rak+ta dmar gyisa dgang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14601: srog shing snying ste mi'i sgal tshig gsar rnying dang
NK078(tshu)001:14602: lha'i rten khro bo'i gzugs bris sku dang lugs chen
NK078(tshu)001:14603: te lugs sku dang dung mchog ste thod sku dang
NK078(tshu)001:14604: / dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14605: dpal gyi chas brgyad de bcu drug tshang pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14607: rnams 'tsho ba'i yo byad kha zas rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14608: sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad rdo rje dril bu /
NK078(tshu)001:14609: mar me la sogs pa rnams dang dkyil 'khor gyi
NK078(tshu)001:14610: mchod rdzas phyi nang gi bye brag rnam dang zhing
NK078(tshu)001:14611: du gyur pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14612: bkra shis dag pa'i zhing skye ba bdun pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14613: 'dir thugs rjes bsgral ba'i zhing la bcu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14614: mchog mi las gyur pa bdun dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14615: mchog phran ngan song gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14616: gnyis pa bar chad rkyen bzlog gi yo byad do //
NK078(tshu)001:14618: bar chad rkyen bzlog gi yo byad la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14619: bar chad bgegs kyi rkyen bzlog pa la nyungs kar rgyal po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14621: lce dpog te gu gul nag po sbyar ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14622: 'du ba nad kyi rkyen bzlog pa la sman dang sman par bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14623: sdang ba dgra'i rkyen bzlog pa la rdo rje go cha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14624: mtshon cha mda' mdung ral gri dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14625: de dag la sogs pa khro bo'i tshogs bsgrub pa
NK078(tshu)001:14626: la dgos pa ji snyed pa'i rdzas rnams thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:14627: kun / gnyis pa de ji ltar spyad thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14629: rnal 'byor pa rang nyid 'jigs byed dpal chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:14630: skur gsal ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis thams cad sems
NK078(tshu)001:14631: su shes pas / nyams nga ba dang bag tsha
NK078(tshu)001:14632: ba'i 'jigs pa med pa'i sems kyis spyad par bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:14633: su shes pas / // gsum pa dgos ched do //
NK078(tshu)001:14635: yo byad de rnams bsdus te yo byad tshogs su bya zhing bsgrub pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:14636: rang gi dngos grub ci 'dod pa'i yo byad gang
NK078(tshu)001:14637: dgos par snang ba thams cad bdag gis tshang bar
NK078(tshu)001:14638: dgod par bya'o // bzhi pa dus la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14640: dang po sgrub pa'i dus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14642: bsgrub pa'i zhaga grangs ni blo tha mas sum cu phrag drug ste zla drug gam /
NK078(tshu)001:14643: rab kyi zhag drug cu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14645: 'bring gi zhag dgu bcu rtsa drug ste zla ba gsum dang zhag drug gi bar du /
NK078(tshu)001:14646: 'jigs byed chen po khro bo'i tshom bu tshogs kyi ting nge 'dzin gsal bar bsgom par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14647: 'o na zhi khro'i tshogs sgrub pa'i 'bras bu thob
NK078(tshu)001:14648: pa la dus nye ring byung bas zhi khro'i lha
NK078(tshu)001:14649: la bzang ngan can du 'gyur ro zhe na ma
NK078(tshu)001:14650: yin te / don bsgom bya lha la bzang ngan med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:14651: sgom byed gang zag la blo che chung yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:14652: de yang zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor dang tshom bu la
NK078(tshu)001:14653: lha grangs mang nyung yod pa dang snang ba 'jam
NK078(tshu)001:14654: gcod dang rtsub gcod kyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14655: khro bo la bar chad chung ba'i phyir dus myur ba yin par gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:14656: gnyis pa dus la re dogs med par bsgrub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14658: sgyu 'phrul dra ba khro bo'i lha yab yum zung du 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK078(tshu)001:14659: lta sgom gyi gdengs dang bcas pa'i bsam pa yis
NK078(tshu)001:14660: 'bras bu thob du re ba dang thob kyi dogs
NK078(tshu)001:14661: pa med par rab tu brtson 'grus bskyed la bsgrub
NK078(tshu)001:14662: bo // lnga pa sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14664: rgyas pa'i le'u don brgyad pa ltar tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:14665: glu tshig sgra dang bro gar 'du 'phro dang phyag
NK078(tshu)001:14666: rgya dang / shes rab thabs su sbyor shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14667: thabs shes gnyis su med par rol pa'i nyi zla
NK078(tshu)001:14668: byang chub sems kyi bdag gzhan la mchod pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:14669: / sgrub pa'i dus kyi lus ngag gi brda la sogs pa'i yon tan ni ji ltar zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:14673: phal pa'i yid tshod du mi 'gyur ba la sogs pa'i dgos ched du ma yod do //
NK078(tshu)001:14674: rgyas par kun 'dus kyi brda'i le'u las shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14675: bza' ba dang bca' ba dang btung ba rnams ro
NK078(tshu)001:14676: zhim pa dang bgo ba reg bya 'jam pa la
NK078(tshu)001:14677: sogs pa 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga dang ldan pa
NK078(tshu)001:14678: rnams / rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin mthun pa
NK078(tshu)001:14679: thams cad kyis mdor na khro bo tshogs sgrub kyi
NK078(tshu)001:14680: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga po rnams mngon sum du
NK078(tshu)001:14681: rnams / bsgrub par bya'o // gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14683: dang po spyi'i bsnyen sgrub sngon bzhin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14685: lam spyi'i bsnyen sgrub sngon zhi ba'i skabs su bshad pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14686: gnyis pa bsgrub pa'i bsnyen sgrub de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14687: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14688: sgrub pa'i grogs yo byad la spyad thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:14691: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14693: khro bo tshogs sgrub pa'i thabs kyi bsnyen pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14696: sgrub pa chen po bzhi ni gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:14697: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14704: dang po ting nge 'dzin nam dal brtsigs shing bri ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14706: dang po bsnyen pa byed pa'i dus kyi tshe na
NK078(tshu)001:14707: gong du bshad pa'i gnas chen po dben pa'i sa
NK078(tshu)001:14708: phyogs der dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa'i tshad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14709: slob dpon mthar nye ba'i lam pas rgyang grags dang
NK078(tshu)001:14710: dpag tshad la sogs pa mchog gi dkyil 'khor bya
NK078(tshu)001:14711: ba dang blo chung ba rnams kyis lhag pa gzugs
NK078(tshu)001:14712: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor tshom bu gcig pa la lus
NK078(tshu)001:14713: gang ngam / gsum pa la lus do'am /
NK078(tshu)001:14714: lnga pa la lus gsum gyi tshad /
NK078(tshu)001:14715: dpon slob gnyis ka blo che na lhag pa ting
NK078(tshu)001:14716: nge 'dzin gyi gzugs brnyan rang gi rig pas dpag
NK078(tshu)001:14717: tshad rgyang grags su sgom ci nus par lha'i dkyil
NK078(tshu)001:14719: blo chung na gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la phyag rgya ste thugs phyag mtshan /
NK078(tshu)001:14720: gzugs te sku ts+aa ka li dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14721: snying po ste gsung yig 'bru dang bcas pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:14722: rnams kha doga lnga'i tshon gyis dkyil 'khor bri bar
NK078(tshu)001:14723: bya'o // gnyis pa yo byad byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14725: de nas yo byad rnams sngon zhi ba'i skabs su
NK078(tshu)001:14726: bstan pa bzhin du tsho gsum bcad la byin gyis
NK078(tshu)001:14727: brlabs nas / gsum pa phyi mchod bya zhing phyi mtshams bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14729: phyi mchod bya ba ni rang nyid rdo rje sems
NK078(tshu)001:14730: dpa' la lha mo bcu gnyis kyis bskor bar bsgoms
NK078(tshu)001:14731: la / 'phags pa rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:14732: rnams spyan drangs shing mchod cing phyi rol pa'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:14733: la / skyong ni / phyogs skyong bcu dang rgyal
NK078(tshu)001:14734: chen bzhi la gtor ma dang pos mnyes par bya
NK078(tshu)001:14735: la / skyong ni / ba dang / snying rje dang lan chags kyi mgron gnyis po yang /
NK078(tshu)001:14737: tha ma sbyin pas shes pa'i rgyud tshims par byas la /
NK078(tshu)001:14738: phyogs skyong dang rgyal chen la bstan pa srung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14739: rigs drug 'byung po la rang gnas su dengs shig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14740: bgegs la bar chad ma byed cig ces bka' bsgo bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14741: bzhi pa srung 'khor gyis mtshams bcad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14743: de nas phur mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14744: 'jigs byed zhe sdang rdo rje'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dabnga du bdag rnal 'byor pa zhugs ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14746: ta ka ri tsa la sogs pa rim par bskul nas /
NK078(tshu)001:14747: snying po brjod pa tsam gyis khro bo bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14748: khro mo bcu 'khor du bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14749: rang rang las ta ki ra tsa spros pa de
NK078(tshu)001:14750: rang rang gi bskul nas khro bo bcu'i gdan nyi
NK078(tshu)001:14751: zla pad ma'i steng du phyogs skyong bcu bkug la
NK078(tshu)001:14752: gzer zhing phur pa ni stod khro bo smad phur
NK078(tshu)001:14753: pa bsgom la bdud rtsi 'khyil bas phur bu rnams
NK078(tshu)001:14754: rim par gdab par bsgoms la gdab /
NK078(tshu)001:14755: de la ye shes kyi khro bo yab yum rnams
NK078(tshu)001:14756: rang bzhin gyi gnas 'og min nas snyan gsan dbab
NK078(tshu)001:14757: spyana drangs stims la mchod pa dang bstod de /
NK078(tshu)001:14758: sgrub la bar chad byed pa'i bgegs thams cad khro
NK078(tshu)001:14759: bo bcu'i ting nge 'dzin mchog gis bzlog par bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:14760: // de ltar bsnyen sgrub kun gyi thun mong du
NK078(tshu)001:14761: mtshon cha lnga yi srung ba'i 'khor lo bsgom par
