NK078(tshu)001:14762: // bya'o // gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14764: dang po sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14766: bsnyen pa song ba de nas gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:14767: dal gyi rgyan zhing gi bla re dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14768: rgyu ma'i lda ldi la sogs steng 'og log gi rgyan rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14769: rdo rje dril bu thod sku la sogs pa sgrub pa'i rdzas gang yin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14770: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi mchod rdzas rnams dgrama par rdzogs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:14771: phyi mtshams ni bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:14772: mtshan nyid sde gsum la bka' bsgo log pa'i bgegs bsrung /
NK078(tshu)001:14773: nang mtshams ni rnam par rgyal ba'i spyi bo nas mi g.yo ba bskyed pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:14774: phyi rgyud sde gsum la bka' bsgo log pa'i bgegs bsrung /
NK078(tshu)001:14776: gsang ba bskyed rdzogs gsum las bka' bgo log pa'i bgegs bar chad bsrung bar bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14777: yang chos sgor ma zhugs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14779: dam tshig gcig pa'i 'drer song ba la rim pa bzhin du bsrung ngo zhes gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:14780: sngon dpal chen pos las kyi srin po'i rgyal po
NK078(tshu)001:14781: ma tam ka ru tra mnan pa'i tshul bzhin du
NK078(tshu)001:14782: / pha las bus blangs te rjes 'jug bsgrub pa pos bar du gcod pa'i bgegs rnams mnan te /
NK078(tshu)001:14783: ma tram gi gzugs bya ba dang ma tra bskyed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14787: khog dbugs bkral ba la sogs pa byas la mnan no //
NK078(tshu)001:14789: ma tam bsgral ba'i khog par gzhal yas khang bskyed bas bgegs gzhan gyis mi tshugs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14790: dper na seng ge'i ro la gcan gzan gzhan gyis nye mi nus pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:14791: ma tam lta bas mnan pas /
NK078(tshu)001:14792: nang ltar las kyi srin po rang gi bdag 'dzin yin pa /
NK078(tshu)001:14794: de nas rdzas rnams byin gyis brlabs /
NK078(tshu)001:14795: sgrub pa po ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir rtags gsum dang ldan par bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14797: gsum dang mi gnyis gcig pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:14798: dbyangs gsum rtags kyi mtshan ma gdab //
NK078(tshu)001:14800: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang gcig pa'i phyir skra mtshams su zhag gi zo ris bya /
NK078(tshu)001:14801: ging chen bco brgyad dang tha mi dad pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:14802: dpral ba'i dbyes su thal chen gyi tshom bu bya
NK078(tshu)001:14803: / ma mo mkha' 'gro dang tha dad med bar
NK078(tshu)001:14804: bya ba'i phyir smin mtshams su rak+ta'i thig le b+han+d+ha'i
NK078(tshu)001:14807: khrag zhag thal chen mtshan ma ni //
NK078(tshu)001:14808: steng 'og phyogs dang dbyes su gdab //
NK078(tshu)001:14810: brjod med kyi bshags pas sgrib pa sbyangs dam bca' ye shes lha'i byin dbab bar bya /
NK078(tshu)001:14811: de nas rang lhar gsal bas phyi nang gi mchod
NK078(tshu)001:14812: rdzas rnams gzhung bzhin du byin gyis rlabs par bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:14813: // gnyis pa gzhung bzhin bya ba de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14814: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14815: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing phrin las kyi rim pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14818: tshom bu'i lha bskyed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14819: rgyan dang cha lugs rdzogs par bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14820: yan lag gi lhas dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14825: sngon 'gro rdzogs pa de nas khro bo'i lha'i 'khor lo ste tshom bu gcig pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:14826: tshom bu gsum pa dang tshom bu lnga ru bsgom bar bya ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14827: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:14829: dang po gzhal yas khang du lha bsgom tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14831: gnas gzhal yas khang ni tshom bu gcig pa la
NK078(tshu)001:14832: 'og gzhi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar 'khor lo
NK078(tshu)001:14833: rtsibs bzhi dang / gsum pa la shar nub kyi rtsibs dang lte ba la rtsibs bzhi pa gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:14834: lnga pa la ste ba dang rtsibs bzhi la 'khor lor rtsibs bzhi pa lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14835: bar 'khyams sgo gnyis rim rnams su /
NK078(tshu)001:14836: lha ji ltar bsgom na dpal 'jigs byed chen po
NK078(tshu)001:14837: khro bo'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang ldan pa'i dbus
NK078(tshu)001:14838: kyi lte ba la rigs kyi gtso bo btsun mo
NK078(tshu)001:14839: dang bcas pa la rigs chung gi khro bo'i tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:14840: dang ldan par bsgom pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14841: gnyis pa tshom bu'i lha bsgom thabs bye brag tu bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14843: dang po tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14845: de yang zhi ba shar dang draga po byang dbang
NK078(tshu)001:14846: nub dang rgyas pa lho'i rtsibs chung bzhi po gdul
NK078(tshu)001:14847: bya 'jigs par byed pa'i tshogs chen b+hud+d+ha dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14850: rat+na he ru ka bzhi po de bzhugs pa'i sa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:14851: de'i dbus su rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid zhi ba
NK078(tshu)001:14852: las drag por bcos pa badz+ra he ru ka'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:14853: du / rang gi sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil /
NK078(tshu)001:14854: gtso bo yab yum dang 'khor rigs bzhi yab yum du gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:14855: de ltar rdo rje rigs kyi de bzhin rigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14859: ral gri las kyi rigs kyi tshom bu pho brang gi lha yab yum bcu sgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:14860: gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14862: tshom bu gcig pa las gzhan pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK078(tshu)001:14863: rdo rje tshom bu gsum pa la mos pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:14864: na / mdun du sku bud+d+ha'i tshom bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14865: rgyab tu gsung pad+ma'i tshom bu /
NK078(tshu)001:14866: dbus su thugs rdo rje rigs kyi 'jigs byed khro
NK078(tshu)001:14867: bo'i tshom bu de dag re re la lha bcu
NK078(tshu)001:14868: bcu ste pho brang gi lha sum cu bskyed do
NK078(tshu)001:14869: // gsum pa tshom bu lnga pa'i lha bskyed cang bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14871: 'jigs byed khro bo'i tshom bu lnga po nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14872: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad rigs lngar 'dus pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:14873: phyir na tshom bu cha lnga'i rigs lnga po re
NK078(tshu)001:14874: re la'ang rigs chung dang bcas pa'i yab yum zung
NK078(tshu)001:14875: nyi shu rtsa lnga ste de 'khor lo cha lnga
NK078(tshu)001:14877: mdun sku'i rigs bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum la /
NK078(tshu)001:14878: 'khor rigs chung ni byams pa'i snying po yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14879: thugs rje'i snying po yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14880: lo ka'i snying po yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14881: btang snyoms yab yum ste tshom bu bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14882: rgyab gsung gi rigs pad+ma he ru ka yab yum gyi 'khor ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14883: rgyal bar byed pa yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14884: rol bar byed pa yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14885: sems za bar byed pa yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14886: 'byung bar byed pa yab yum ste tshom bu bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14887: dbus thugs kyi rigs badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyi 'khor ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14888: rdo rje snying po yab yum rin chen snying po yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14890: karma snying po yab yum ste bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14891: g.yas yon tan gyi rigs rat+na he ru ka yab yum la /
NK078(tshu)001:14893: rdo rje rol pa yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14894: rdo rje srin po yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14895: rdo rje lha min yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:14896: sna tshogs rdo rje yab yum ste bcu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14897: g.yon phrin las kyi rigs karma he ru ka yab yum gyi 'khor ni /
NK078(tshu)001:14898: sgrol bar byed pa mthar byed /
NK078(tshu)001:14899: rol pa nyams myong yab yum dang bcu ste pho
NK078(tshu)001:14900: brang gi lha lnga bcu yongs su rdzogs par bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:14901: mo // 'khor gyi lha'i rnam grangs 'dir ma smos kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:14902: shugs la 'chad pas tshom bu gsum ka'i pho brang gi lha'i 'khor la /
NK078(tshu)001:14905: khro bo yab yum nyi shu dang bcas pa'i bdun cu don brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:14907: brgya dang bco brgyad yod do //
NK078(tshu)001:14908: gnyis pa rgyan dang cha lugs rdzogs par sgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14910: de dag kyang dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad /
NK078(tshu)001:14912: 'bar ba'i gar dgu'i cha lugs la sogs pa gdul
NK078(tshu)001:14913: bya gdug pa can 'jigs par byed pa khro bo'i
NK078(tshu)001:14914: tshogsa ni / rang bzhin gyi gnas 'og min na
NK078(tshu)001:14915: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor ci bzhin par
NK078(tshu)001:14916: tshogsa ni / / sgrub pa po yab yum zung cig gi lha yab yum spyir bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14917: yang na rnal 'byor pa re res lha re re tu bsgom pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14918: de dag kyang 'tshams rngamsa chen po'i rol pa khro bo'i cha lugs su gsal bar bsgom pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14919: gsum pa yan lag gi lhas dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14921: de nas lha thams cad la yan lag lhag pa'i dkyil 'khor dbu rgyan lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:14922: sku gsung thugs gsum ye shes sems dpa' dang dgu dgur lha re re la ldan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14923: de ltar sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa'i lha gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14924: ye shes lngas dbang bskur thob pa'i rtags su dbu rgyan rigs kyi lha lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:14925: thugs ye shes sems dpa' ste lha dgu dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:14926: pa'i bdag nyid dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa
NK078(tshu)001:14927: la / gnyis pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs ba la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:14929: dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing mchod pa'i las rim bstan pa dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14931: rang bzhin ye shes pa'i dkyil 'khor snyan gsan dbab /
NK078(tshu)001:14932: spyan drangs la lcags kyus phyag rgyas bkug /zhags pas gzhug /lcags sgrog gis bcing /
NK078(tshu)001:14933: dril bus dgyes pa bskyed nas brten par gzhugs su gsol ba la /
NK078(tshu)001:14934: phyag 'tshal nas sman mchod yan chad kyi rim pa bzhin mchod par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14935: gnyis pa bdud rtsi dngos grub blang ba'i sngags dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14940: khong la yod pa'i kha bskangs ba'i dgongs pa ltar bshad na /
NK078(tshu)001:14941: sku'i snying po su ra to bde ba /
NK078(tshu)001:14955: mo sku'i gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:14958: w+aa ka gsung am am am gsung gi sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:14961: tsit+ta thugs h'u h'u h'u thugs kyi sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:14962: lung gra chad la nyal ba zur la bslang ba s+w+aa dang h+aa gnyis yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:14963: s+w+aa yon tan gyi snying po /
NK078(tshu)001:14965: gu na yon tan s+w+aa s+w+aa s+w+aa yon tan gyi sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:14966: ha phrin las kyi snying po /
NK078(tshu)001:14969: ha ha ha phrin las kyi sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:14970: badz+ra rdo rje ma h+aa chen po k+aa pa la
NK078(tshu)001:14971: thod pa khar ka snying po d+ha na sbyin pa
NK078(tshu)001:14972: dz+wa la 'bar ba sid+d+hi dngos grub bde ba bdud
NK078(tshu)001:14973: rtsi chen po lnga dpal 'bar ba khrag 'thung chen
NK078(tshu)001:14974: po sngags kyi dkyil 'khor rigs lnga'i sku'i sku gsung
NK078(tshu)001:14975: thugs gsum mo // gsung gi thugs kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:14976: yon tan gyi phrin las kyi sku gsung thugs gsum la /
NK078(tshu)001:14977: rdo rje k+aa pa la chen po'i snying po sbyin
NK078(tshu)001:14978: pas 'bar ba khro bo'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos
NK078(tshu)001:14980: de ni bdud rtsi 'bul zhing dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14981: gsum pa rnams lnga'i mchod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14983: ma h+aa chen po shes rab dpal he ru ka
NK078(tshu)001:14984: khrag 'thung a me me tog bdug me bdug spos
NK078(tshu)001:14985: si d+ho grub pa b+ha wa tu gyur cig /sa
NK078(tshu)001:14986: ha ra na sdud cig /h'u h'u h'u sdud pa
NK078(tshu)001:14987: ste / dpal khrag 'thung chen po la me tog
NK078(tshu)001:14988: bdug spos kyi mchod pas don gnyis grub par gyur
NK078(tshu)001:14989: cig /de nas lha mo rang la bsdu bas thugs
NK078(tshu)001:14990: badz+ra khrag thung gi sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub
NK078(tshu)001:14991: ste / thob par bsam / de ni gtor ma'i steng 'dod yon gyi lha mos mchod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:14992: bzhi pa gsang nan 'bul ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:14997: sa ma ya dam tshig /ru lu ru lu hub gsum btung ba /
NK078(tshu)001:15000: de ni rnal 'byor chen po nang ba'i dam tshig las mi 'da' ba'i phyir dam blang ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15001: gtor ma hub gsum btung bas sku gsung thugs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:15002: dam tshig las mi 'da' bas dngos grub ngo mtshar
NK078(tshu)001:15004: lnga pa gtor ma 'bul zhing mchod bstod bya ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15010: ma h+aa chen po su kha mnyes pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15011: ma le phreng ba ma nu yid sa ma na
NK078(tshu)001:15012: dam dza la 'bar ba d+ha na sbyin pa a
NK078(tshu)001:15013: wa mchod sbyin yo ga rnal 'byor kh+aa hi gsol
NK078(tshu)001:15014: cig a la la ho mnyes pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15015: gtor ma bdud rtsi bde ba'i phreng ba rgyun chad med par 'bul bas /
NK078(tshu)001:15016: mnyes pa chen po'i phreng ba rgyun chad med pa
NK078(tshu)001:15017: 'byung ba'i gnas yi dam 'bar ba khrag 'thung tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:15018: kyi gtso bo la mchod cig 'khor rnal 'byor ma
NK078(tshu)001:15019: la sbyin pa gsol cig mnyes par gyis shig pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:15020: // de nas sbyor sgrol la sogs pas mchod nas bstod pa smon lam yan chad rdzogs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15021: gsum pa bsnyen pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15023: dang po bsnyen pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15026: bdag dam tshig sems dpar gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15027: lha ye shes sems dpa'i dza b+ha khang mdun du lhags pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15028: mda' gang tsam gyis nam mkha' la bzlas pa gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15029: bar ting nge 'dzin sems dpa' gsum ldan gyi sgo nas bzlas pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:15033: ni ye shes lnga ldan sngags kyi mgo 'dren /
NK078(tshu)001:15034: badz+ra rdo rje ma h+aa chen po kro d+ha khro bo sh+r+ai dpal he ru ka khrag 'thung /
NK078(tshu)001:15035: badz+ra rdo rje kro ti khro mo shwa ri dbyings
NK078(tshu)001:15036: phyug ma sarba thams cad dush+ta na sdang ba h'u
NK078(tshu)001:15037: sdud cig phata sgrol cig pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15038: ming nas bos pa'i sngags so //
NK078(tshu)001:15039: ru lu ma h+aa sa ma ya h'u ni thugs dam gnad nas dbab pa'i sngags so //
NK078(tshu)001:15040: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u ni bsnyen sngags
NK078(tshu)001:15041: sam che yon gyi sgo nas bstod pa'i sngags so
NK078(tshu)001:15042: // 'di la lce ston gyi nye ba'i bsnyen pa byed pa'i sngags ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15044: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK078(tshu)001:15046: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /ru lu ru
NK078(tshu)001:15047: lu ma h+aa sa ma ya h'u phatah sgrub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:15048: dus su badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /badz+ra
NK078(tshu)001:15049: kro ti shwa ri sarba dush+tana h'u phatah sgrub pa
NK078(tshu)001:15050: chen po'i dus su thams cad dril te bzla gsungs
NK078(tshu)001:15051: so // gsum pa rigs gzhan la 'ang bsnyen dus kyi dmigs pa de ltar du bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15053: de ltar badz+ra he ru ka la bzlas bsnyen skyon
NK078(tshu)001:15054: nas sogs khong na rigs lnga gzhan yang 'don te
NK078(tshu)001:15056: lce ston gyi 'grel bar b+hud+d+ha he ru k+aa la /
NK078(tshu)001:15057: bud+d+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /bud+d+ha kro ti
NK078(tshu)001:15058: shwa ri sarba dush+tana h'u phatah ru lu ru lu
NK078(tshu)001:15059: ma h+aa sa ma ya h'u phatah ru lu 'gres
NK078(tshu)001:15063: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK078(tshu)001:15068: badz+ra +aar+ya ti dza ti nga dza /
NK078(tshu)001:15069: ru lu mi srin mo la /
NK078(tshu)001:15070: b+h+yo ma nu rak+sha si ru lu /
NK078(tshu)001:15072: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK078(tshu)001:15073: gardza gardza lu ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK078(tshu)001:15076: de'ang ye shes kyi lha mdun gyi bar snang du
NK078(tshu)001:15077: bzhugs pa la dam tshigs sems dpa'i thugs ka nas
NK078(tshu)001:15079: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar 'phros thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK078(tshu)001:15080: tshur 'dus sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyongs nas dngos
NK078(tshu)001:15081: grub kyi snod du rung bar byed para bsam zhing
NK078(tshu)001:15082: / 'phro 'du bsnol mar byed pa ni bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15085: dper na lton mo zhig byed pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:15086: sngon du yo byad dang spyod cha thams cad bsogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15087: de nas bud med gshin pos spyad sogs 'khrud pa
NK078(tshu)001:15088: dang de nas chang btsag pa de la them bu
NK078(tshu)001:15089: phar bsgul bas / tshur chang rgyang rgyang 'ong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15090: de nas mgron rnams la drangs bas tim ting 'thung bar byed pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:15091: dang po bsnyen pa'i yo byad bsag cing /
NK078(tshu)001:15093: de nas nye bsnyen gyi sgrub pa zhag grangs du
NK078(tshu)001:15094: byed kyi phyed du cho ga gzhung bsrang zhing dkyil
NK078(tshu)001:15095: 'khor gnyis phye nas bzlas pa'i 'phro 'dus sgrib pa
NK078(tshu)001:15096: sbyangs shing sid+d+hi'i snod du rung bar byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15097: de nas sgrub pa'i dus su zhag grangs du byed kyi phyed man chad du /
NK078(tshu)001:15099: bdag gi sgrib pa sbyangs la k+aa w+aa ci sid+d+hi stsol cig par bskul /
NK078(tshu)001:15100: de nas nub tha ma la sgrub pa chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:15101: dus su bzlas pa'i 'od zer phar mi 'phro bar
NK078(tshu)001:15102: tshul sib sib 'du bar bsam zhing dngos grub len
NK078(tshu)001:15103: pa'o // gsum pa sgrub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15105: lha bskyed pa dang sngags bzlas pa nye bsnyen de bzhin du sgruba par bya ba'i dus su'nga /
NK078(tshu)001:15106: bzlas pa'i 'od zer kha dog dmar po phar 'phrosa
NK078(tshu)001:15107: pas dngos grub rtsol cig par thugs dam kyi rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:15108: bskul ba dang / tshul 'dus bas bdag la dngos grub sdud par bsam zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:15109: sngags bzlas pa'i skyon bcu gong phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs ltar spangs te sgrub par bya ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15110: de ltar bsgrub pa byed pa'i dus su dgos par shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15111: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15113: dang po sgrub pa bya ba dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15115: de yang nub tha ma'i zhag gcig de la sgrub
NK078(tshu)001:15116: pa'i dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams shin tu bstar zhing
NK078(tshu)001:15117: sngags bzlas pa'i 'od zer mthing ga phar mi 'pho
NK078(tshu)001:15118: bar tshur bsdu ba'i dgongs pa 'ba' zhig bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:15119: ni sgrub pa chen po'i dus su dngos grub len
NK078(tshu)001:15120: pa yin par shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15121: gnyis pa spyir 'dzab dgongs kyi ting nge 'dzin bya thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15123: de yang nye bsnyen gyi dus su sgo gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:15124: sdig sgrib sbyangs shing nyes skyon thams cad dag par
NK078(tshu)001:15125: byed pa'i rtags su bzlas pa'i 'od zer yig 'bru
NK078(tshu)001:15126: shel gyi bung ba lta bu kha dog dkar po
NK078(tshu)001:15128: dang po shel gyi kha dog la /
NK078(tshu)001:15130: shel gyi bung ba mang po dag /khyung chen lding ba'i bang tshod tsam //
NK078(tshu)001:15131: phar lding bcud phyungs tshur bsrigs pas //
NK078(tshu)001:15133: bag chags 'khrud cing phung po bsreg /phar 'phros thugs dam las la bskul //
NK078(tshu)001:15134: ji ltar nyi zer tsha tsha ltar //
NK078(tshu)001:15135: rgyun mi chad par rtse gcig 'bar zhes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15136: sgrub pa'i dus su dngos grub la chags shing dbang
NK078(tshu)001:15137: du sdud pa'i rtags su bzlas pa'i 'od zer yig
NK078(tshu)001:15138: 'bru rnams byi ru'i bung ba lta bu kha dog
NK078(tshu)001:15141: bar du byi ru'i kha dog la //
NK078(tshu)001:15142: gong ma bzhin du bkod gsal ba //
NK078(tshu)001:15143: byi ru'i bung ba mang po dag /gong ma bzhin du 'phar lding bas //
NK078(tshu)001:15144: bcud phyung bstim zhing slar yang 'phar //
NK078(tshu)001:15146: dpal be smug po'i steng du bstim //
NK078(tshu)001:15148: sgrub pa chen po'i dus su dngos grub gzhan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:15149: dbang du mi 'gyur ba'i rtags su bzlas pa'i 'od
NK078(tshu)001:15150: zer mthing ga'i bung mang po dag mthing gar bsam
NK078(tshu)001:15152: kun gyi tha mar bsdu ba ni //
NK078(tshu)001:15153: bkod pa'i gong ma thams cad kun //
NK078(tshu)001:15154: mthing ga 'bar bar bsgyur nas ni //
NK078(tshu)001:15155: khyung chen gcan gzan 'dzum tshod tsam //
NK078(tshu)001:15156: h+aum sgra 'byin cing phan tshun lding //
NK078(tshu)001:15157: mtsho la ser chen 'gril bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:15159: de ltar bsnyen sgrub kyi rim pa bzhin du nye bsnyen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15160: sgrub pa'i dus su bung ba me tog la phar
NK078(tshu)001:15161: 'gro tshur 'ong byed pa ltar 'od zer phar 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:15163: sgrub pa chen po'i dus su mtsho la ser ba
NK078(tshu)001:15164: chen po 'bab pa bzhin du 'od zer tshur bstim
NK078(tshu)001:15165: pa yin no // gsum pa rtags byung na bar chad brtag cing dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15169: dkar sngo dmar nag mtshan mthong na /
NK078(tshu)001:15171: 'od dkar po byung na srog bdag gam /
NK078(tshu)001:15173: sngon po byung na klu dug can /
NK078(tshu)001:15175: nag po byung na sngags pa dam log gi rtags yin nam /
NK078(tshu)001:15176: lha'i sku gsung thugs grub pa'i rtags gang yin brtag pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15177: dang po nyams dga' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15178: bar du sems gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15179: tha mar bogs thon na lha'i rtags su bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15181: the'u rang gswe yi yar shod kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:15182: gla rtsi tsam zhig log pa'i mchod //
NK078(tshu)001:15187: ya la skyes gcig gi dri yin nam /
NK078(tshu)001:15188: lha'i rtags gang yin brtag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15189: dri zhim la nyams dga' na lha'i rtags dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15192: srin mo'i gdon rgod kho yi sgra //
NK078(tshu)001:15195: gnod sbyin rgod ma'i sgra yin nam /
NK078(tshu)001:15197: sgra mi snyan la yun thung na gdon /
NK078(tshu)001:15198: snyan nas yun ring na lha'i rtags dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15200: de yang gzugs kyang mi rtags ko tsa li /
NK078(tshu)001:15202: srin po ko tsa li'i gzugs mi rtag la cho 'phrul du 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:15203: gsal zhing nyams dga' na lha'i rtags so //
NK078(tshu)001:15204: phyag mtshan dang sgrub rdzas rnams nam mkha' la 'khor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15206: sman raka khol ba la sogs pa'i rtags byung na /
NK078(tshu)001:15207: bdud kyi bar chad dang lha'i grub rtags kyi cha
NK078(tshu)001:15208: rnams gang yin dpal he ru ka'i sngags dang phyag
NK078(tshu)001:15209: rgya'am / thod pa tshar gsum gyi phyag rgya dang
NK078(tshu)001:15210: sngags rang gi nyams kyi brtags par bya ba ste
NK078(tshu)001:15211: rgya'am / / de yang bdud yin na med nas 'gro la /
NK078(tshu)001:15212: grub rtags yin na je gsal du 'agro'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15213: gal te bar chad yin na rdo rje drag po'i
NK078(tshu)001:15214: sngags dang phyag rgya dang rdzas dang ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:15215: gyis bskrad de bdag nyid lhar gsal ba'i go bgo
NK078(tshu)001:15217: sgrub pa'i zhag grangs tshang zhing dngos grub kyi rtagsa byung na /
NK078(tshu)001:15218: dngos grub blang ba ni rtogs pa'i gnas su lha bstim pa yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:15219: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor gang bsgrub kyi sku gsung thugs
NK078(tshu)001:15220: kyi dngos grub rnams rang rang gi lus ngag yid
NK078(tshu)001:15221: gsum gyi rtogs pa'i gnas su mthun pa nyid du
NK078(tshu)001:15222: sbyar zhing / mngon shes dbang po lnga la /
NK078(tshu)001:15224: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa la bstim pa la sogs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:15225: rtog tshogs kyi gnas su lha'i dngos grub bstim zhing
NK078(tshu)001:15226: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta ma h+aa tish+tha badz+ra dang
NK078(tshu)001:15227: / sems can gyi don gyi phyir dngos grub brtan par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15228: rtags dang ldan nas dngos grub blangs pa des na
NK078(tshu)001:15229: sngon zhi ba tshogs sgrub kyi skabs su bshad pa
NK078(tshu)001:15230: bzhin du yi ge 'khor lo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15232: yo byad la spyad pas so so'i yon tan rnam pa gsum thob pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:15233: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rnam gsum thob par 'gyur zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:15234: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i grogs yo byad la spyad thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:15235: sbyor sgrol gnyis la spyod pa'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15236: yo byad bzhi la spyod pa'i thabs so //
NK078(tshu)001:15239: dang po bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15241: las gzhung rnams rdzogs nas zhi bar khas blang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:15242: gsang ba sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa rgyas par bshad
NK078(tshu)001:15243: par bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15244: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:15249: bsgral bas mi gos pa'i gtan tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15251: sbyor sgrol don la tha dad med par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15254: dang po mngon du phyung ba'i sgrol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15256: bsgral ba lnga yi go don ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15257: spros pa mthar phyin pas zhing bcu dngos su sgrol ba ni mngon du phyung ba'i sgrol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15258: sngon byung dus dpal chen pos ru tra bsgral ba
NK078(tshu)001:15259: ltar rnal 'byor pas gnas lugs rtogs pa'i lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:15261: bag chags kyis mi gos pa ni thabs chen po'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15262: dbang pos yul mthong zhing thos pa la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:15263: dbang po rnam shes rnams lha yab dang yul dus
NK078(tshu)001:15264: rnams lha yum du shes pas yul shes rang ga
NK078(tshu)001:15265: ma'i rtog pa dag pa ni dbang po yul dus
NK078(tshu)001:15266: kyis so // chos thams cad chos dbyings spros bral
NK078(tshu)001:15267: tu rtogs pas dngos po rang ga ma dag pa
NK078(tshu)001:15269: rang lhar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas ram las me byung ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15270: 'gro drug gi lus dang bag chags bsreg pa ni ting nges sgrol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15271: de yang zhing du gyur pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:15272: bkra shis dag pa'i zhing dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15273: thugs rjes bzung zhing sgrol ba'i zhing ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:15276: de'i rtags ni skra nag la li ba mig bya mig bzhin mas nas 'dzum pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15277: zla ba nya ba'i nub mo grib ma bdun bdun 'ong ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15278: de'i gdung la brten nas bsgrub na mchog thun mong
NK078(tshu)001:15279: gi dngos grub khyad par can 'byung ba'i phyir ro
NK078(tshu)001:15280: // phyi ma ni mchog mi las gyur pa gdun dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15281: mchog phran ngan song gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15283: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra dang //
NK078(tshu)001:15284: dam las log dang 'khu ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:15286: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK078(tshu)001:15287: ngan song gsum dang bcu po ni //
NK078(tshu)001:15288: rnal 'byor kun gyi dang du blangs //
NK078(tshu)001:15291: bcu po de rnams shin tu snying rjes phan gdag pa'i phyir du bsgral ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15292: gang gis bsgral na bar chad med pa'i lam pas bsgral ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15293: dgos ched ci'i phyir sgrol na /
NK078(tshu)001:15294: bdag gzhan chos gsum gyi don du 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:15295: dus nam gyi tshe bsgral na /
NK078(tshu)001:15296: tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi nub tha ma'i nam gung gi dus su bsgral bar bya /
NK078(tshu)001:15298: rdo rje slob dpon bsgral ba'i thabs la mkhas pa dang ldan pas bsgral bar bya ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:15299: de yang rang bzhin gyis sgrol ba lta ba la mkhas pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15300: ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol ba sgom pa'i thabs la mkhas pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15301: dbang po yul dus kyis sgrol ba spyod pa'i thabs la mkhas pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15302: thabs chen pos sgrol ba gdams ngag gi thabs la mkhas pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15303: mngon du phyung ba'i sgrol ba mdzad spyod kyi thabs
NK078(tshu)001:15304: la mkhas pa lnga dang ldan pas bsgral bar bya
NK078(tshu)001:15306: dkyil 'khor gyi lho phyogs su drag po'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum bri ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15307: e ram gyis drag po'i dal bskyod la /
NK078(tshu)001:15308: a dang ma las dbyung ba'i nyi zla'i gdan steng du /
NK078(tshu)001:15309: bsgral ba'i thabs la makhasa pasa bdag nyid ging gi
NK078(tshu)001:15310: nga rgyal dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin las ma
NK078(tshu)001:15311: yengs par / bsgral bya de nyid sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gyi nus pas dngos su bkug la /
NK078(tshu)001:15312: gru gsum gyi steng du mgo lho nub /
NK078(tshu)001:15313: rkang pa byang shar du bstan te /
NK078(tshu)001:15314: 'khor ba ru bzlog pa'i tshul du gan rkyal du
NK078(tshu)001:15315: bsgyel ba'i snying gar rdo rjes mnan la bzhag go
NK078(tshu)001:15316: // tshul ji ltar na bsgral zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:15317: nga rgyal rnam pa lnga dang ldan pa'i tshul gyis bsgral bar bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15318: de yang sgrub dpon dpal chen po'i nga rgyal bas /
NK078(tshu)001:15319: kun brtags kyi rtog pa zil gyis gnon pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15320: sgrol ging ta ki ra tsar nga rgyal bas /
NK078(tshu)001:15321: 'khor ba rgyu bzlog pa'i ngang gri 'jam dpal rnon por nga rgyal bas /
NK078(tshu)001:15322: ma rig pa'i rgya mo dral ba'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15323: ging gi lag por dpa' bo 'bru lngar nga rgyal bas /
NK078(tshu)001:15324: bdag 'dzin drung nas phyungs ba'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15325: bsgral byar ru trar nga rgyas bas dug gsum rtsad nas gcod pa'i dgos ched dang ldan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15326: de ltar nga rgyal rnam pa lnga dang ldan pa'i tshul gyis lag pa'i 'du byed kyis bsgral lo //
NK078(tshu)001:15327: bsgral ba'i ting nge 'dzin gang bsgom na /
NK078(tshu)001:15328: gri 'jam dpal rnon por gsal ba des /
NK078(tshu)001:15329: bsgral bya'i khog pa shags kyis gshags pas ma rig pa'i rgya mo bkral bar bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:15330: lag sor dpa' bo 'bru lngar gsal ba des /
NK078(tshu)001:15332: snying rtsa bzhi la gnas pa'i sa bon zung gsum gnyid dang bcas pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15333: dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i 'phro 'du'i 'od zer gyis bsregs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15334: bsgral bya'i shes pa yig 'bru h'u dkar po drug tu gyur pas /
NK078(tshu)001:15335: 'khor bar skye ba'i sa bon drug bag chags dang
NK078(tshu)001:15336: bcas pa rnam par dag h+aum drug po de yang
NK078(tshu)001:15337: / thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes gcig las ma 'das pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:15338: chos nyid du gcig pa'i phyir h'u dkar po zhig tu gyur par bsgom ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15339: de ni phyi ltar na bsgral bya'i khog dbugs dral
NK078(tshu)001:15340: nas khong gi tsit+ta dngos su phyung ba yin la
NK078(tshu)001:15341: / nang ltar na thos bsam gyi shes rab kyis gzung 'dzin gyi rgya mo dral nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15342: bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis bdag 'dzin drung nas phyung ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:15343: shes pa chos nyid du bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15344: de nas h'u dkar po de bdag nyid rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:15345: rgyal po lhar gsal bas yab yum sbyor ba mdzad
NK078(tshu)001:15346: pas shangs khung g.yon gyis rngub klad pa'i rgyas su
NK078(tshu)001:15348: srog dag pa rdo rje'i lam nas phyung /
NK078(tshu)001:15349: yum gyi mkha' la bab pas /
NK078(tshu)001:15350: gsang ba'i dbyings su thim par bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:15351: de ni yum gyi mkha' la bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15352: de nas yum gyi mkha' la gsung yig 'bru de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:15353: thugs phyag rgya rdo rje 'od 'bar ba gcig tu gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:15354: rdo rje de yongs su gyur ba las sku yongs
NK078(tshu)001:15355: su rdzogs pa rdo rje sems dpa'i sku phra mo
NK078(tshu)001:15357: de yang nyon mongs pa lnga rnam par dag pas
NK078(tshu)001:15358: 'khor 'das gnyis med du longs spyad pas na longs
NK078(tshu)001:15359: spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan
NK078(tshu)001:15360: pa / 'od zer sna lnga 'phro ba rab tu brjid pa dang ldan pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15361: rdo rje sems dpa'i spyi gtsug tu 'khor ba las
NK078(tshu)001:15362: rnam par rgyal ba mtshon pa rigs kyi bdag po
NK078(tshu)001:15363: mi bskyod pa tshon gang ba bsgom /
NK078(tshu)001:15364: yang na dbus na bee ro tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:15365: ces rnam par snang mdzad bsgom pa'ang bzhed do //
NK078(tshu)001:15366: rdo rje sems dpa' mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa'i sa la bsgral zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15367: de ltar bsgral ba'i shes pa nyid de bzhin gshegs
NK078(tshu)001:15368: pa rdo rje sems dpar byin gyis brlabs pa de
NK078(tshu)001:15369: yang / a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK078(tshu)001:15370: du bzhag /yam las rlung gis btegs nas a yam
NK078(tshu)001:15371: s+pha ra na phatah ces dus gsum gyi rgyal ba
NK078(tshu)001:15372: kun gyi bzhugs gnas 'og min du 'phangs te /
NK078(tshu)001:15373: 'og min gyi rgyal ba rdo rje sems dpa' yab
NK078(tshu)001:15374: yum gyis sbyor ba mdzad pa'i mkha' mtshams su bstims
NK078(tshu)001:15375: te song nas / gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dbang yang bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:15377: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika /mum da du shwa ri /
NK078(tshu)001:15379: rgyal ba'i rigs nges pa'i sras su gyur pa rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi skur gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:15380: phata dzahs phyir bton pas yab yum gyi skur rags
NK078(tshu)001:15381: pa mtshan dpe yongs su rdzogs pa zhig tu gyur
NK078(tshu)001:15382: nas / gnas de nyid du bzhugs par bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:15383: de ni shes pa 'og min du bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15384: de ni yang dag ltar na /
NK078(tshu)001:15385: sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs rnams la bskos btab ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15387: dug gsum gyi mchod pa la sogs phul bas /
NK078(tshu)001:15388: dkyil 'khor kyi lha tshogs rnams mnyes par bsgom mo //
NK078(tshu)001:15389: de ni sha khrag rus pa'i phung po dur khrod du bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15390: gnyis pa thabs chen pos bsgral dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15392: de yang sngon byung dus sku gsung thugs shin tu
NK078(tshu)001:15393: khros pa'i khro bo dpal chen po rdo rje srin
NK078(tshu)001:15394: po yis thugs rje dang bsgral ba'i thabs kyi sgo
NK078(tshu)001:15395: nas lha chen r+au tra 'khor dang bcas pa bsgral
NK078(tshu)001:15396: ba ltar / rjes 'jug gi rnal 'byor bas chos
NK078(tshu)001:15397: nyid mngon sum du lta bas rtogs pa'i gdeng dang
NK078(tshu)001:15398: ldan zhing sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis goms nas
NK078(tshu)001:15399: ba ltar / / sbyor lam mthar phyin pa'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:15400: su bsgral bya ba bsgral byed gnyis su med par
NK078(tshu)001:15401: thabs kyi sgo nas bsgral zhing gi rnam shes chos
NK078(tshu)001:15402: kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15403: gsum pa dbang po yul dus kyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15405: de yang gang gis bsgral na /
NK078(tshu)001:15406: sbyor lam pa'i thugs rje chen po'i sgo nas dgongs pa'i byin rlabs kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:15408: a n+ri su tri pre du dza zhes lam rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:15409: lnga'i sems can ma lus pa'i shes pa kun bkugs
NK078(tshu)001:15410: nas bsgral bya la bstims te /
NK078(tshu)001:15412: sems can thams cad kyi bdag 'dzin ma lus pa
NK078(tshu)001:15413: rnams chos nyid gnyis su med pa'i ngang du bsgral
NK078(tshu)001:15414: bar bya'o // bzhi pa rang bzhin gyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15416: bsgral zhing ni phyi snod dang nang bcud kyi 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:15417: rten ji snyed na gnas pa'i 'gro drug gi sems
NK078(tshu)001:15418: can phra rags ma lus pa kun /
NK078(tshu)001:15419: bsgral mkhan ni sems nyid gnyis su med pa'i ye
NK078(tshu)001:15420: shes kyi bdag nyid chen por blta bas rtogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:15423: rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su yang ni
NK078(tshu)001:15424: rtogs pas bsgral ba la gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa
NK078(tshu)001:15426: lnga pa ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15429: phyi ltar dbus kyi ri raba chen po'i phyogs bzhi'i
NK078(tshu)001:15430: gling bzhi phran brgyad la gnas pa'i sems can bsgral
NK078(tshu)001:15432: bsgral ba'i mkhan po thugs rje che po dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:15433: pa'i sbyor lam gyi rnal 'byor pa lta ba rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:15434: shing ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i byin rlabs kyis
NK078(tshu)001:15436: ting nge 'dzin gyi rang rig pa ram du gsal
NK078(tshu)001:15437: ba'i ye shes kyi me chen po 'bar bar bsgomsa
NK078(tshu)001:15438: par byas te / ye shes kyi me des ri
NK078(tshu)001:15439: rab gling bzhi la sogs pa'i sems can thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:15440: kyi rgyud la yod pa'i rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:15441: ma dang bag chags ma lus pa bsreg par bya'o
NK078(tshu)001:15442: par byas te / // de nas sems can thams
NK078(tshu)001:15443: cad kyi sems gnyis med chos kyi dbyings su yang
NK078(tshu)001:15444: ni rang grol du bstim pa ste rtogs par bya
NK078(tshu)001:15445: par byas te / // / de ltar rtog pa de dag phyi na /
NK078(tshu)001:15447: sa 'og /sa steng na srid pa khams gsum mam /
NK078(tshu)001:15448: nang ltar na lus ngag yid gsum gyi mtshan ma thams cad bsreg pa'i me yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:15449: de yang me rang rgyud pas srid gsum dngos su bsreg pa ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:15450: rnal 'byor pa'i yid kyis rnam par shes pa lta
NK078(tshu)001:15451: dgongs las su rung bas ye shes kyi me ru
NK078(tshu)001:15452: rab tu 'bar te bsreg pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:15453: ye shes kyi me bskyed pa'i sa bon ni ram yin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15454: gnyis pa bsgral bas mi gos pa'i gtan tshig la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15456: dang po bden pa gnyis kyi tshul du rtogs pas sbyor sgrol gyis mi gos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15458: de lta bu'i bsgral thabs khyad par can 'di ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15459: bdag la sgrib pas mi gos /
NK078(tshu)001:15460: gzhan la sdug bsngal mi bskyed pas ngo mtshar zhing
NK078(tshu)001:15461: las ngan sbyang pas gnas ngan par 'gro ba'i rgyu
NK078(tshu)001:15462: / zhing bcu po thams cad kyang sdug bsngal las
NK078(tshu)001:15463: thar bar byed pa'i thabs khyad par can 'di las
NK078(tshu)001:15464: lhag pa gzhan med pas phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:15465: de ltar sgrol ba 'di dag log par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:15466: nyon mongs pas kun nas bslang nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15467: sems can gyi srog la 'tshe ba byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15468: byed du bcug na skyon du 'gyur bas 'bras bu 'byung mod kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:15469: 'dir skyon med de gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:15470: ye gdod ma nas skye ba med pa don dam
NK078(tshu)001:15472: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta bas de bzhin nyid kho nar rtogs shing /
NK078(tshu)001:15473: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams su blangs bas /
NK078(tshu)001:15474: kun rdzob tu lus sgyu mar snang ba 'di yang /
NK078(tshu)001:15475: des tho yor la mir 'dzin pa de nyid tho yor du nges pas mir 'dzin grol ba bzhin /
NK078(tshu)001:15476: snang ba thams cad mig yor gyi tshul du shes nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15477: dngos grub gnyis bsgrub pa'i don du g+ha na sbyor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15478: sta na sgrol ba'i bya ba kun byas kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:15479: sbyor sgrol rang rgyud du byas pa'i dri ma rdul
NK078(tshu)001:15480: phra rab kyi cha shas tsam yang byas pa med
NK078(tshu)001:15481: pas na / sbyor sgrol gyi skyon gyis mi gos par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15482: gnyis pa phung po la rnam par dbye bas he dus sgrol bas mi gos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15484: tshul de ltar rtogs na kun rdzob tu zhing bcu la sogs bsgral ba'i bya ba kun nam /
NK078(tshu)001:15485: yang na bsgral thabs lnga po gang byas kyang don
NK078(tshu)001:15486: dam ltar na bsgral ba'i dngos po de dag ma
NK078(tshu)001:15487: grub pas bsgral ba'i dngos po rang rgyud par gang
NK078(tshu)001:15488: yang med do // de'i rgyu mtshan ni log rtog
NK078(tshu)001:15489: gi ngo bo snang ba'i phung po lnga po 'di
NK078(tshu)001:15491: rang bzhin med par bshig par bya /
NK078(tshu)001:15492: bye brag tu gzugs phung la sogs rigs pas bshigsa
NK078(tshu)001:15493: na sha rus la sogs 'byung ba lnga'i bag la
NK078(tshu)001:15494: zha la / 'o na bkag pa'i stong pa snyam nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15495: rigs pas ma bshig tsa na yang sha rus la
NK078(tshu)001:15496: sogs 'byung ba lnga yi ngo bo yin pas bsgral
NK078(tshu)001:15497: rgyu med do // gsum pa rnam shes la dmigs su med pas sgrol bas mi gos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15499: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad rang rgyud du
NK078(tshu)001:15500: gzugs su grub pa med par shes pas bsad par
NK078(tshu)001:15501: byas na / dper na rmi lam du srog gcod
NK078(tshu)001:15502: par snang ba yang don la ma grub pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:15503: byas na / ci bzhin du / 'khrul ngo na
NK078(tshu)001:15504: srog gcod bya gcod byed du gnas pa nyid na
NK078(tshu)001:15505: yang dag pa'i don la dngos po rang rgyud par
NK078(tshu)001:15507: bzhi pa rang sems kyi rang bzhin la sgrol du med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15509: 'o na sems nyid bsgral lam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:15510: kun gzhi byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba'i chos nyid de la ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15511: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad dgrar
NK078(tshu)001:15512: langs kyang gnyis snang du grub pa med pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:15513: na / sems kyi rang bzhin de sangs rgyas la
NK078(tshu)001:15514: sogs pa susa kyang zin cing sod pa med pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:15515: na / // gsum pa sgrol ba'i nges tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15517: 'o na dngos su sgrol rgyu grub pa med na /
NK078(tshu)001:15518: rnal 'byor pa'i thugs rjesa gang bsgrala ba yin zhe
NK078(tshu)001:15519: na gdul bya'i bdag 'dzin la sogs pa rnam par
NK078(tshu)001:15520: rtog pa'i mtshan mar zhen pa thams cad kuna /
NK078(tshu)001:15521: 'khrul ba'i log rtog phyin ci log tu zhen cing 'dzin pa las bzlog par byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:15522: bsgral ba'i lta dgongs ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15523: sngags dang phyag rgya dang gsum la blo shin tu
NK078(tshu)001:15524: goms shing brtan par gyur pas bsgral bya'i shes pa
NK078(tshu)001:15526: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi zhing la dgod par bya /
NK078(tshu)001:15527: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir de ltar log rtog rgyun chad
NK078(tshu)001:15528: nas byang chub la bkod pa de ka tsam las
NK078(tshu)001:15529: ni / 'khor ba las bsgral ba'i don gyis na
NK078(tshu)001:15530: bsgral ba zhes bya bar tha snyad du gdags so
NK078(tshu)001:15531: ni / // bzhi pa sbyor sgrol don la tha dad med par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15533: de yang gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa bsgral ba'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:15534: nyid na chos nyid gnyis med du sbyor ba yang
NK078(tshu)001:15536: de ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:15537: bsgral bya'i rgyu nyon mongs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15538: 'bras bu sdug bsngal ma lus pa kun rtsad nas bcad nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15539: 'bras bu bla na med pa byang chub kyi zhing du bsgral bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:15540: bsgral bya sgrol byed gnyis su med pa chos nyid
NK078(tshu)001:15541: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su sbyor ba yin no
NK078(tshu)001:15542: // gnyis pa g+ha na sbyor ba la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15543: mngon du phyungs pa'i sbyor ba dang rang bzhin gyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15544: dbang po yul dus kyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15546: thabs chen po'i sbyor ba'i phan yon gyi ngos nas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15549: dang po gang la sbyor ba'i yul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15551: de yang sbyor ba'i go don ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15552: mngon du phyung pa'i sbyor ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15553: spros pa las su rung ba'i rnal 'byor pas dngos su lha mo bkugs nas sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15555: spyod yul gyi rtog pa lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du gnas par sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15557: dbang po rnam shes lha yab yul dus lha yum du shes par sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15559: rtog tshogs lha'i dkyil 'khor du ting nges sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15560: thabs chen po'i sbyor ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15561: sngon byung du dpal chen pos dbang phyug ma la rol ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:15562: rnal 'byor pas spyod bzhin ma chags par sbyor ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15563: de yang phyi ltar na lha mo dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15567: de dag sngags dang phyag rgyas dngos su bkug pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15569: lha mo klu mo gnod sbyin sogs //
NK078(tshu)001:15570: mdor na 'jig rten khams rnams na //
NK078(tshu)001:15571: mi yi lus can gang yang rung //
NK078(tshu)001:15572: thabs la mkhas pas skabs kyis sbyor //
NK078(tshu)001:15574: gal te bkug ma nus na /
NK078(tshu)001:15575: rig ngan mi'i bu mo la brda'i sgo nas dbye ba la bzhi las /
NK078(tshu)001:15576: dang po lo grangs kyi sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15577: lo bcu gnyis ma mtshan dang ldan pa ni lha mo rab ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15578: bcu drug ma mtshan dang ldan pa ni klu mo ste 'bring /
NK078(tshu)001:15579: nyi shu 'am nyer lnga mtshan dang ldan pa ni rigs ngan mo ste tha ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15580: gnyis pa rtsa'i sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15581: rtsa mdud pa can te 'dab ma brgyad pa lha mo /
NK078(tshu)001:15582: mnyam pa ste 'dab bzhi klu mo /
NK078(tshu)001:15583: zhar ma ste 'dab gnyis rigs ngan mo /
NK078(tshu)001:15584: gsum pa byang sems kyi sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15585: nyi zla gnyis ka 'dzag pa lha mo /
NK078(tshu)001:15587: gnyis ka mi 'dzag pa ni rigs ngan mo'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15588: bzhi pa sbyor thabs kyi sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15589: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i bde ba bskyed nus pa lha mo /
NK078(tshu)001:15591: bdag bde ba tsam rigs ngan mo'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15593: bud med rgyan po byed pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:15594: nye tshong rku byed dge slong ma //
NK078(tshu)001:15595: slong mo ma dang de bzhin du //
NK078(tshu)001:15596: khyim tshes ma la grogs mi bya //
NK078(tshu)001:15597: zhes pas de rnams spangs la /
NK078(tshu)001:15599: ngag 'jam mthun smra mang nyung zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:15600: dad ldan blo rnon shes rab che //
NK078(tshu)001:15601: 'phral dal brtag thub grogs dad che //
NK078(tshu)001:15602: bka' blo bde zhing sbyor thabs mkhas zhes pas /
NK078(tshu)001:15603: lus ngag yid gsum la yon tan gsum gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15604: spyod lam gyi yon tan bzhi ste bcu gsum dang ldan pa btsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:15605: rnal 'byor pa rang gi sbyor thabs kyi spyod pa la lta sgom gyi nus pa chung na /
NK078(tshu)001:15606: gong gi mi mo la bzang ngan dbye nas bzang rigs brten cing /
NK078(tshu)001:15609: rnal 'byor pa nus pa che na phyag rgya'i mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:15610: bzang ngan mi mo la mi dbye bar bya ste
NK078(tshu)001:15611: / dngos su lha mo klu mo bkug pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:15612: gnyis pa ji ltar sbyor ba'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:15614: dang po ma dor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15616: de yang gsum pa sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15617: yum mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la khrus gsum bya /
NK078(tshu)001:15618: rgyan gsum gdag /chos gsum bshad nas sta gon du byas pa ni bsnyen pa'i yan lag go //
NK078(tshu)001:15621: yo byad bzhi dang 'dod pa'i bstan chos drug cu
NK078(tshu)001:15622: rtsa bzhis bde ba rgyas par byed pa ni nye
NK078(tshu)001:15623: ba'i bsnyen pa phyag rgya bzhis rol pa ni sgrub
NK078(tshu)001:15624: pa dang / nyi zla rdo rje'i lces blang ba ni sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15625: nub tha ma la mthong lam gyi ye shes chen po rgyud la skye bar byed pa /
NK078(tshu)001:15626: dngos grub chen po yab yum gyi mkha' las blang ba'i dbang du'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15627: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15631: shes rab bam dbyings kyi cha 'dzin pa'i yum gzung ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:15634: dri bzang gis khrus gsum byas la /
NK078(tshu)001:15635: dar dang rin po che rus pa'i rgyan gsum brtags nas chas su gzhug la /
NK078(tshu)001:15636: gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15638: de nas yum gyi lus la bde gshegs yum gyi dkyil 'khor bkod de /
NK078(tshu)001:15639: phung khams skye mched kyi rtog tshogs rnams lhar byin gyis brlabs la /
NK078(tshu)001:15640: mkha' gsang gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:15641: nang du tshom bu gang rung gi lha bkod la
NK078(tshu)001:15642: / rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid rig pa'i lha rdo rje sems dpa' bsgom nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15643: gsum pa sgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15645: dang po sbyor ba dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15647: phyag rgya bzhis rol pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15648: yab yum thabs shes gnyis su med par zung 'brel du ldan par bya /
NK078(tshu)001:15649: gnyis pa sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15651: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15652: yum gyi dril bu gnyis su med cing las su rung ba dang ldan par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15653: yum gyi mkha' gsang pad+ma 'dab brgyad pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:15654: gzhal yas khang du bskyed pa nyid du yab kyis
NK078(tshu)001:15655: gu h+ye badz+ra ga zhug la yab yum gyi nyi
NK078(tshu)001:15656: zla byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po thugs
NK078(tshu)001:15657: kyi dkyil 'khor nas yum gyi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor du
NK078(tshu)001:15659: g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems /
NK078(tshu)001:15662: mthar phyin pa'i sems dang lnga'i rim pa byung ba
NK078(tshu)001:15663: de bzung ba'i thabs kyis ngos zin pa yis lus
NK078(tshu)001:15664: dang mkha' gsang du bkod pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK078(tshu)001:15665: 'khor ma lus pa la byang chub kyi sems dgyes
NK078(tshu)001:15666: pa chen po bde ba'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK078(tshu)001:15669: sems can thams cad rang rig pa'i ngo bor mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:15670: de bas yab yum rol ba'i bde bas bdag mchod
NK078(tshu)001:15671: pas rgyal ba mnyes shing 'gro ba tshim pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:15672: mchog gi sbyin pa yin pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:15673: bdag dang rgyal ba sems can gsum gnyis su med pa'i bde ba chen po gcig tu bstim mo //
NK078(tshu)001:15674: gsum pa sbyor ba'i yon tan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15676: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsum mnyes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15677: rnal 'byor pa'i rig pa dang 'gro drug gi sems
NK078(tshu)001:15678: can thams cad dbyer med pas 'gro ba sems can
NK078(tshu)001:15679: mang bos kyang dgyes pa'i bde ba mnyam du thob
NK078(tshu)001:15680: nas / slar yang yab yum bde stong gnyis su
NK078(tshu)001:15681: med pa'i mkha' dbyingsa su sgrol bas na thim zhes
NK078(tshu)001:15682: nas / bya'o // de ltar thim par gyur nas
NK078(tshu)001:15683: yum gyi mkha' dbyings nas lha'i sku phyag rgya chen
NK078(tshu)001:15685: de yang bde bar gshegs pa thams yab dang shes
NK078(tshu)001:15686: rab yum gnyis med du rdzogs shing rigs lnga dang
NK078(tshu)001:15687: lhun gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya drug pa kun bzang
NK078(tshu)001:15688: dang / thub pa drug kyang yang dag par rdzogs /
NK078(tshu)001:15689: de ltar snang ba ma 'gags pa bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15690: de la ma chags pa ye shes kyi tshogs te /
NK078(tshu)001:15691: tshogs chen po gnyis kyang rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:15692: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:15694: dang po dngos grub chen po yab yum gyi mkha' las blang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15696: de ltar bde ba'i ye shes chen po bsgrub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:15697: thabs sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhis sgrub pa chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:15698: dus su / dngos grub chen po blang bar bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15700: yub yum gnyis su med par rol pa las byung ba'i thig le nyi zla gnyis 'dres /
NK078(tshu)001:15701: yon tan thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'i snying po de /
NK078(tshu)001:15702: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bdag nyid ye shes lngar gsal bar byed pa'i rten yin pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:15704: sus blang na bar chad med pa'i lam pas blang bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15705: dus nam gyi tshe blang na /
NK078(tshu)001:15706: tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa'i nub tha ma'i tho rengs kyi dus su blang bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15708: yum gyi mkha' nas blang bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15709: gang gis blang na thig le 'dren bzlog la mkhas pa'i yab kyi rdo rje'i lces blangs te /
NK078(tshu)001:15710: gsang ba rdo rje nyid do //
NK078(tshu)001:15711: yang na lce rdo rje rtse lngar bsgoms pa de yis blang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:15712: tshul ji ltar blang na bung bas me tog 'jib pa'i tshul du blang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:15713: dgos ched ci'i phyir blangs na /
NK078(tshu)001:15714: dngos grub rnam gnyis bde blag tu thob bar bya ba'i phyir blang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15715: gnyis pa dngos grub blangs ba'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:15717: de yang dngos grub gnyis gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:15718: mkha' la bya bzhin 'gro zhing lha'i bu mo la spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15720: 'od zer dang gzi brjid 'bar ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15721: tshe ring ba la sogs pa'i sogs khang nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15722: sa la byi ba bzhin du 'dzul nas klu'i bu mo la spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15723: gzhan yang mngon par shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15725: mchog gi dngos grub ni yid bzhin nor bu rin
NK078(tshu)001:15726: po che las ma g.yos bzhin du dgos 'dod char
NK078(tshu)001:15727: bzhin 'byung bas na sprin gyi tshogs te /
NK078(tshu)001:15728: dpe de dang 'dra ba'i rigs thams cad kyi bdag
NK078(tshu)001:15729: po rgyal ba drug pa yang thob par 'gyur ro
NK078(tshu)001:15730: // yang na gsang ba'i rdo rjes blangs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15731: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag po mchog gi dngos grub
NK078(tshu)001:15732: thob par 'gyur la phyi ma lce rdo rje rtse
NK078(tshu)001:15733: lnga par bsgoms nas blang ba'i yon tan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15734: mkha' 'gro gsal 'bar tshe la sogs pa thun mong gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:15735: gsum pa de ltar sbyor ba'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15737: 'gro drug gi dus dang gnas nas yang tha mal
NK078(tshu)001:15738: pa'i bde ba la sbyor ba'i yon tan de dag
NK078(tshu)001:15739: snang zhing yod pa yin yang ngo ma shes pas
NK078(tshu)001:15740: thabs kyis ma zin pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:15741: sbyor ba'i mchod pa byas pas mtshon cing ngo shes
NK078(tshu)001:15742: par byas te thabs kyis zin nas gsang ba byang
NK078(tshu)001:15743: sems kyi mchod pa chen po'i bde ba yab yum
NK078(tshu)001:15745: rtog pa thams cad bde stong dbyer med kyi dbyings su sbyor bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:15746: de'i yon tan gyis ngan 'gro gsum por mi ltung
NK078(tshu)001:15747: zhing yang dag pa'i 'bras bu mthong lam 'grub par
NK078(tshu)001:15748: 'gyur ro // bzhi pa sbyor sgrol gnyis don la tha dad med par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15750: sbyor ba'i sgo nas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:15751: ye shes chos nyid kyi don rtogs pa 'di ni
NK078(tshu)001:15752: / gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa rang ga ma rnams bsgral ba chen po la'am /
NK078(tshu)001:15753: ngan song las bsgral ba yang yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:15754: chags rtog bsgral ba nyid na chos nyid du 'am /
NK078(tshu)001:15755: byang chub la sbyor ba yang yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:15756: de ltar sbyor ba'i dus nyid na rtog pa rang kha ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:15757: sbyor sgrol gnyis don la tha dad med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15758: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi sbyor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15760: gzhi ye 'am gdod ma nas rtog pa rags pa thams cad lha yab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15761: phra ba thams cad yum lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du
NK078(tshu)001:15762: gsal bar gnas pa yang dag pa'i sa la sbyor
NK078(tshu)001:15763: ba dang / gsum pa dbang po yul dus kyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15765: dbang po rnam shes brgyad lha sems dpa' yab brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15766: yul dus brgyad lha sems ma brgyad du gsal ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15767: de gnyis 'phrad pa ni lha yab yum gnyis med
NK078(tshu)001:15768: du sbyor ba ste dbang po yul dus kyi sbyor
NK078(tshu)001:15769: ba'o // bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15771: phung po lnga po nyid rigs lnga'i de bzhin gshegs
NK078(tshu)001:15772: pa dang sa la sogs pa'i 'byung ba lnga nyid
NK078(tshu)001:15773: rigs kyi yum lnga nyid du sbyor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15774: dbang po bzhi rnam shes bzhi sems dpa' brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15775: yul bzhi dang dus bzhi lha mo sems ma brgyad nyid du sbyor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15776: bdag rtog rnam bzhi khro bo bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15777: rtag chad mu bzhi khro mo bzhir sbyor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15778: yid chos gnyis kun bzang yab yum /
NK078(tshu)001:15779: nyon mongs drug thub pa drug dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15780: de las gzhan pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:15781: pa rtog tshogs thams cad ma lus par 'byung ba
NK078(tshu)001:15782: kun / chos nyid mnyam pa'i dbyings dang de rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:15783: pa'i rang rig pa'i ye shes su lhag pa ting
NK078(tshu)001:15784: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam par sbyor ba'o
NK078(tshu)001:15785: kun / // lnga pa thabs chen po'i sbyor ba'i phan yon gyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15787: sngon byung du dpal chen pos ma chags thabs kyis sbyor ba srin mo skam ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15788: dbang mo rnams la rol kyang nyes pas ma gos pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:15789: rjes 'jug rnal 'byor pas yab yum gnyis su med
NK078(tshu)001:15790: par sbyor ba'i dus nyid na sbyor thabs la mkhas
NK078(tshu)001:15791: pas dga' bde'i ro la chags pa rang ga ma
NK078(tshu)001:15792: med pa'o // de ltar bde ba'i ro la ma
NK078(tshu)001:15793: chags pa ye shes su shar ba la pho mo
NK078(tshu)001:15794: gnyis su snang nas chags pa rang ga ma dang
NK078(tshu)001:15795: tshul mthun par chags pa spyod pa'i dus nyid na
NK078(tshu)001:15796: med pa'o // / chags pa'i ro nyid ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:15797: su gsal bas chags pa zin pa dang chags pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:15798: skyon gyis gos pa med pa'i don 'dir ni tshangs
NK078(tshu)001:15799: par spyod pa'i mchog bde ba'i ye shes la dbang
NK078(tshu)001:15800: bsgyur bas rgyal po yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:15801: de ni shin tu yang dag pa'i chags pa chen
NK078(tshu)001:15802: po spang gnyen ro gcig tu gyur pas de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:15803: gshegs pa'i dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:15804: gsum pa rang ga mar spyad pa'i skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:15806: de ltar gsang ba'i mchod pa sta na sgrol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15807: g+ha na sbyor ba de gnyis po'i dus su chos
NK078(tshu)001:15808: nyid don gyi lta ba ma rtogs pa pa'i rnal
NK078(tshu)001:15809: 'byor pa yis / kha 'byams tshig gi lta ba ste sgra'i rjes su 'brang nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15810: sbyor sgrol gnyis rang ga mar spyad par gyur na /
NK078(tshu)001:15811: nyes skyon ci yod snyam par las /
NK078(tshu)001:15812: sbyor ba'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu'i yi dwags dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15813: ro myags kyi 'dam gyi dmyal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15814: rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu mngal gyi srin bur skye bar bshad cing /
NK078(tshu)001:15815: sgrol ba'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu'i yang sos kyi dmyal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15816: rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu las kyi srin po'i gnas su skye bar bshad pas /
NK078(tshu)001:15817: sbyor sgrol rang ga ma de dag la log pa'i lam du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:15819: gsang sngags kyi lam nyams su len pa'i rnal 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:15820: pa gang gis sems nyon mongs pa'i kun nas bslangs
NK078(tshu)001:15821: nas 'dod chags tha mal du spyad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15822: sems can gyi srog la 'tshe ba byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15823: byed du bcug na nyes skyon chen por 'dug pas de dag brtson pa chen pos spangs la /
NK078(tshu)001:15824: yang dag pa'i lta sgom spyod gsum dang ldan pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:15825: rnal 'byor bas mchog tu gyur pa'i gsang spyod thun
NK078(tshu)001:15827: sbyor sgrol gnyis bdag gzhan chos gsum gyi don du longs spyod par gyis shig ces gdams pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15828: gnyis pa yo byad bzhi la spyod thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:15833: dang po spyad thabs kun spyir zhi ba dang mthun par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15835: sbyor lam la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pas tshogs sgrub pa'i mchod pa byed pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:15836: 'gro nyal 'dug sdod la sogs spyod lam bzhi po thams cad du /
NK078(tshu)001:15837: dur khrod chasa brgyad kyi rgyan rnams bgos shing gdag par byas te /
NK078(tshu)001:15838: baza'a ba dang btunga ba'i yo byad rnams zhi ba
NK078(tshu)001:15839: tshogs sgrub kyi rjes su mthun par mtshan med kyi
NK078(tshu)001:15840: ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par longs spyod cing /
NK078(tshu)001:15841: rkang bas bro dang lag pa'i gar ngag gi glu
NK078(tshu)001:15842: tshig rnams kyang mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin gsal
NK078(tshu)001:15844: gnyis pa bro gar gyi spyad thabs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:15846: dang po lta bu'i phyag rgyas lha gsal ba'i ngang las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15850: rig pa rnam shes te rtog tshogs de rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:15851: dbang po dang rnam shes ni thabs yab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15852: yul dus ni shes rab yum du gsal ba gnyis su med par ldan par 'gyur zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:15853: thabs shes rab gnyis med mnyam pa'i nganga nyid du
NK078(tshu)001:15854: gnas pa de lta bas rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:15856: rtog tshogs thams cad lha yab yum zung du 'brel
NK078(tshu)001:15857: ba las mi 'da' ba'i don gyis na gnyis med
NK078(tshu)001:15858: bde ba chen po mchog gi phyag rgya yin pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:15859: // gnyis pa bro gar gyi dus su lha bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:15860: pa'i ting nge 'dzin yon tan dang bcas pa de
NK078(tshu)001:15862: dang po yan lag lnga la rigs lnga'i lha bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:15863: zhing bsgul bskyod byas pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:15866: yab yum rnams kyis bskyod chen te yan lag bzhi
NK078(tshu)001:15867: mgo bo dang lnga la b+h+r+aum las 'khor lo rtsibs
NK078(tshu)001:15868: bzhi pa'i gzhal yas khang re re bsgom pa de
NK078(tshu)001:15869: rnams su / mgo bo la bud+d+ha la sogs rigs
NK078(tshu)001:15870: chung dang bcas pa khro bo yab ste nyer lnga
NK078(tshu)001:15871: rnams su / / khro mo nyer lnga yum lnga ste lha lnga bcu po thams cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:15872: ting nge 'dzin gsal zhing de dag la 'od zer mang po 'phro bar bsgomsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:15873: lus bsgul ba dang yan lag bskyod pa thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:15874: lhar gsal ba las mi 'da' ba'i don gyis na
NK078(tshu)001:15875: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:15876: gnyis pa goms pa 'dor dus ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15878: de ltar lhar gsal ba'i rkang pa g.yas pa thabs yab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15879: g.yon pa shes rab yum du ldan pa'i zhabs gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:15880: dus rtag tu rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'od 'bar
NK078(tshu)001:15882: thabs chen goms pa re re sa la bskyod cing
NK078(tshu)001:15883: dor bar byas na don chags pa med pa'i rtags
NK078(tshu)001:15884: su rkang rjes la me tog pad+ma re re 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:15885: bar bsgom / rkang pa'i rdo rje de dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15886: sa gzhi'i pad+mo de gnyis ting nge 'dzin gsal bar 'byor na /
NK078(tshu)001:15887: de bar du gang song ba'i sems can thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:15888: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi zhing du skye
NK078(tshu)001:15889: bar 'gyur ro // gsum pa yan lag so sor
NK078(tshu)001:15890: lha bsgoms nas bskyed pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:15893: yan lag lnga rigs lnga ye nas yin pa rang bzhina gyi dkyil 'khor zhi ba'i lha rnams kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:15894: da res 'dir khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha lnga
NK078(tshu)001:15895: bcu yan lag bzhi mgo dang lnga la sgom par
NK078(tshu)001:15896: bya ste / dbu'i gnas su de bzhin rigs bud+d+ha
NK078(tshu)001:15897: he ru ka rigs chung dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:15898: gsal ba de nyid bsgul zhing bskyod na /
NK078(tshu)001:15899: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor te zhing khams thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:15900: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don la g.yo bar nus pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:15901: // lag pa g.yas pa rdo rje'i rigs badz+ra he
NK078(tshu)001:15902: ru ka dang g.yon rin po che'i rigs rat+na he
NK078(tshu)001:15903: ru ka rigs chung dang bcas pa gsal ba'i lag
NK078(tshu)001:15904: gi 'du byed bskyoda par byas na /
NK078(tshu)001:15905: rig 'dzin gyi zhing khams thams cad ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:15906: gyi nus mthu skyes nas rang don du sa 'og
NK078(tshu)001:15908: gzhan don du thugs rjes 'gro ba'ii don la g.yo bar nus pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15909: rkang pa g.yas las kyi rigs karma he ru ka dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15910: g.yon pad+ma he ru ka rigs chung dang bcas pa
NK078(tshu)001:15911: gsal ba'i rkang pa'i stabs chen mnan zhing mchong na
NK078(tshu)001:15912: / g.yon gyis sems can gyi sdug bsngal mi bzad
NK078(tshu)001:15913: pa dmyal ba la sogs pa thams cad las grol
NK078(tshu)001:15914: / ba dang / g.yas kyis bar du gcod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:15915: bdud dang log par 'dren pa bgegs thams cad gnon
NK078(tshu)001:15916: / ba dang / par nus pa'o // de ltar
NK078(tshu)001:15917: dbu dang phyag zhabs kyi bskyod pa'i yon tan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:15918: rim pa de dag ni sangs rgyas rigs lnga dang
NK078(tshu)001:15919: / ba dang / par nus pa'o // / lus
NK078(tshu)001:15920: kyi mgo bo dang phyag zhabs rnams la mthu che
NK078(tshu)001:15921: chung gi khyad yod pa ni ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:15922: lus kyi gnas rim nas smos pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:15923: de yang chos can yan lag mtho dman gyi cha nas bzhags pa yin gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:15924: chos nyid rig pa rang byung gi ye shes la bzang ngan med do //
NK078(tshu)001:15925: bzhi pa yan lag kun bskyod cing ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:15927: spyir lus kyi yan lag thams cad dus gcig la bsgul zhing bsigs na /
NK078(tshu)001:15928: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi ba spu'i bu ga re re nas /
NK078(tshu)001:15929: khro bo'i sprul pa rdul phra rab snyed grangsa med par spros /
NK078(tshu)001:15930: khro bo de'i yang sprul pa grangs med pa rnams kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:15931: don bya ba'i gnas phyogs bcu'i stong gsum gyi stong
NK078(tshu)001:15932: chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams dag dang ma dag
NK078(tshu)001:15933: bar ma rnams la rdul phra rab kyi grangs de
NK078(tshu)001:15934: snyed du 'gro ba'i don byed mkhan khro bo'i gdul
NK078(tshu)001:15935: bya 'dul ba'i phrin las kyi sgo nas don mdzad
NK078(tshu)001:15936: pa rnams kyi rdul phran gyi grangs de snyed du
NK078(tshu)001:15937: snang nas don byed tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:15938: de dag gi thugs rjes gdul bya 'gro ba rnams 'dul zhing slar rang gi ba spu'i bu ga'am /
NK078(tshu)001:15939: chos nyid dbyings su bstim mo //
NK078(tshu)001:15940: gsum pa spyad thabs kun zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur te spyad thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15942: khro bo la khyu mchog ma he la sogs pa'i bro stabs sam /
NK078(tshu)001:15943: yang na rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i gar ngag gi glu tshig dang mig gis lta stangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15944: ting nge 'dzina gyis yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i thabs thams cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:15945: sngar gyi zhi ba'i tshogs sgrub kyi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su bstan pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:15946: 'dir bro gar rtsed 'jo la sogs khro bor bsgyur bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15947: bzhi pa lhag ma la sogs 'jug bsdu ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15949: bar skabs su tshogs bya de nas dpal chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:15950: 'khor gyi phra men dbang mo rnams lhag mas tshims
NK078(tshu)001:15951: par bya ste / rta gdong gi phyag rgyas dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15952: so sor mchod pa dang las la bka' bsgo ba
NK078(tshu)001:15953: la sogs pa rnams las gzhung ltar rgyas par byas
NK078(tshu)001:15954: nas las la bkye la brtan ma skyong /
NK078(tshu)001:15956: spyod lam bzhir lha'i ting nge 'dzin dang mi 'bral bar spyad do //
NK078(tshu)001:15957: tshul de ltar bsgrubs pas 'bras bu mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin 'grub pa la the tshom med do //
NK078(tshu)001:15958: gnyis pa spyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:15960: tshogs sgrub kyi rnal 'byor pa thabs yab dang shes
NK078(tshu)001:15961: rab yum thams cad kyis gong gi ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:15962: gyi tshul de lta bu dang ldan pa'i yo byad
NK078(tshu)001:15964: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams rnal 'byor pa'i rig pa dang tha dad med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:15965: bdag gis yo byad la longs spyod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:15966: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa rnams kyang mnyes pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15967: srid pa khams gsum gyi 'gro ba sems can thams
NK078(tshu)001:15968: cad la 'dod yon gyi 'od zer 'phros pas bde
NK078(tshu)001:15969: ba'i ro dga' ba chen pos khyab pas sbyin par
NK078(tshu)001:15970: 'gyur ba'o // de yang rang bzhin gcig pa la dgongs pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:15971: spyi don gnyis pa tshogs sgrub pa'i yon tan la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:15973: dang po rtags 'phel ba la brten pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15975: drod rtags kyi cha rnams sngon spros pa'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin du 'byung zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:15976: 'o na khyad med dam zhe na ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:15977: tshogs sgrub kyi skabs 'dir gong gi drod rtags de
NK078(tshu)001:15978: dag grangs mang du 'phel zhing ngo bo gsal la
NK078(tshu)001:15979: yun ring du brtan par 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:15980: gnyis pa mngon shes brtan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15982: mngon shes kyis yul la gling grangs 'phel ba gling bzhi drug tshun tshad kyang mthong ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:15983: yang na spros pa bas gling grangs gnyis gsum la sogs pa 'phel ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15984: mngon shes drug kyang gsal la brten par 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:15985: 'dir sbyor lam gyi mngon shes de ltar 'byung na /
NK078(tshu)001:15986: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi skabs su /
NK078(tshu)001:15987: dpag tshad gling grangs don la sbyor //
NK078(tshu)001:15989: mthong lam pa bas sbyor lam pas mngon shes rgya che bar 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:15992: thod rgal bas phyag rgya gcig spros kyi sa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:15993: mthar chags pas tshogs sgrub kyi thog nas thob pa dang gsum gyis 'bras bu yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:15994: de bas na thob pa gsum la mtho dman yod pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:15995: 'bras bu rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi mngon shes la rgya che chung yod pa mi 'gal te /
NK078(tshu)001:15997: bar tshad med pa'am smin pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:15998: mngon par shes pa de ming can //
NK078(tshu)001:16000: dpag tshad gling grangs yul la sbyor //
NK078(tshu)001:16002: gsum pa rmi ltas lung bstan thob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16004: rna bas sgra snyan du thos pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:16005: gnyid kyis rmi lam dag tu yang bde ba can
NK078(tshu)001:16006: la sogs pa'i 'jig rten sangs rgyas kyi bzhugs gnas
NK078(tshu)001:16007: kyi zhing khams rnams su skye bar lung bstan pa
NK078(tshu)001:16008: dang / lha mi'i skye ba khyad par can gang dag 'dzin par lung bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16009: rig 'dzin gyi sa thob par lung ston pa 'byung ba rnams yang dag pa'i rtags yin nam /
NK078(tshu)001:16010: bdud kyi bar chad yin nam brtag par bya ba shin tu gal che ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:16011: spyi don gsum pa tshogs sgrub pa'i 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16012: blo che bas lhag bcas tshe dbang thob tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16013: blo chung bas lhag med rnam smin thob tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:16015: sgrub pa mthar phyin tshe 'di la tshe dbang thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16016: mthar ma phyin kyang phyi ma la thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16017: lan grangs gzhan la tshe dbang thob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16020: dang po tshe dbang thob nas sangs rgyas tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16022: tshogs sgrub ba'i zhag grangs sum cu phrag drug gam bcu gnyis sam /
NK078(tshu)001:16024: bcu drug tshun chad kyis nang du 'byung ba'i lus
NK078(tshu)001:16025: 'di nyid ma spang bar skye 'chi med pa rdo
NK078(tshu)001:16027: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi sa non te /
NK078(tshu)001:16028: dus der rang don du lo stong drug brgya la
NK078(tshu)001:16029: sogs yun ring por zag med mthong lam pa'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:16030: nyid kyi bde ba la longs spyod nas /
NK078(tshu)001:16031: lam mthar chags sam thod rgal gang rung gi sgo
NK078(tshu)001:16032: nas bla na med pa rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:16033: yongs su rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa thob ste
NK078(tshu)001:16034: / sangs rgyas de'i yon tan thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i dpe byad brgyad cu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16035: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis rnam par brgyan cing /
NK078(tshu)001:16036: zag pa med pa'i mngon par shes pa drug dang
NK078(tshu)001:16037: ldan la shes bya ci lta ba dang ji snyed
NK078(tshu)001:16038: pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mnga' ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16039: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs chen po gnyis kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:16040: mngon sum du rdzogs par rol pa'i bdag nyid yang
NK078(tshu)001:16041: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas longs sku'i zhing khams
NK078(tshu)001:16042: kyi gdul bya la rang dbang bsgyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:16043: spyod yul ma lus pa kun sku dang ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:16044: kyi man+dala te lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bas yi
NK078(tshu)001:16045: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:16046: pas na / bde bar gshegs pa'i snang bas ji
NK078(tshu)001:16047: ltar dmigs shing dgongs pa bzhin du lhun gyis grub
NK078(tshu)001:16048: pas na / par 'gyur ro // gnyis pa de
NK078(tshu)001:16049: yang las dang dus la rag lus med par tshe
NK078(tshu)001:16052: gong gi de bas na mtshan nyid pa ltar sngar bsags pa'i las 'phro dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16053: dus grangs med la sogs la rag lus med pa de /
NK078(tshu)001:16054: las dus la rag lus pas sems zhum pa dor
NK078(tshu)001:16055: bar byas nas sgo gsum gyi brtson 'grus chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:16056: sgo nas zag pa med pa'i don mthong lam la
NK078(tshu)001:16057: sbyor nas / mthong pa'i chos tshe 'di la mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16058: gnyis pa phyi ma tshe dbang thob pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16060: mjug bsdus te the tshom med par thob tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:16063: dang po phyi ma la lha mi khyad par can
NK078(tshu)001:16064: thob cing theg mchog mi brjed par bstan pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:16066: tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin bzhi las su rung ba'i lam pa rnams kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:16067: sbyor lam tshogs sgrub pa 'di lta bu'i las la 'bad par byas na'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:16068: blo dang brtson 'grus zhan pas 'bras bu mthong lam tshe 'di la mdon du ma gyur yang /
NK078(tshu)001:16069: tshe 'di la rang gi lus ngag yid gsum lha'i
NK078(tshu)001:16070: sku gsung thugs bsgom pa la rang dbang thob pas
NK078(tshu)001:16071: bar do nas / sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:16072: rten gyi khams gang du 'byung bar shes nas de
NK078(tshu)001:16073: dang skal ba mnyam par lha mi'i skye ba can
NK078(tshu)001:16075: de yang gsang sngags la sbyongs pa'i las 'phro de dang 'brel ba'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:16076: gsang sngags 'di nyid dang 'phrad cing thega pa dman
NK078(tshu)001:16077: pa nyan rang la sogs pa la 'jug cing spyod
NK078(tshu)001:16078: pa'i sar yang mi skye ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16079: yo byad lnga la spyod pa'i bsod nams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16080: thams cad chos nyid du shes pas ye shes kyi tshogs chen gnyis dang ldan pa'i dpunga tshogs kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:16081: skye ba snga ma phan chad kyi rgyu las ngan
NK078(tshu)001:16082: gyi sgrib pa ma rig pa'i mun pa rnams sbyangs
NK078(tshu)001:16083: ba'i phyir / 'bras bu ngana songa gsum gyi gnas su yongas su mi lhung zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:16084: mtho ris su skyes na yang gansa ngan pa dang longs spyod chung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16085: mi bde zhing sdug bsngal ba'i dam pa'i chos byar mi khoms pa'i gnas ngan song gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16088: lta ba log pa dang sangs rgyas mi bzhugs pa'i zhing stong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16089: dbang po mi tshang ba dang brgyad du 'gro zhing skye bar mi 'gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:16090: mi brjed pa'i gzung mchog dam pa lta ba rtogs
NK078(tshu)001:16091: shing ting nge 'dzin goms pa dang ldan pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:16092: / skye bas bar chod kyang gsang sngags rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:16093: theg pa mchog gi brjod bya brjod byed gang yin
NK078(tshu)001:16095: de la 'jug cing nyams su len nus pa'i dran pa phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16096: de yang tshe ring zhing nad med pa dang bde
NK078(tshu)001:16097: zhing 'byor ba phun sum tshogs pa ste tshe phun
NK078(tshu)001:16098: sum tshogs pa'o // gnyis pa mtshan dang ldan zhing yon tan rdzogs tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16100: lha dang mi'i skye gnas kyi mchog stod rigs thob pa'i sa'am gnas skabs der /
NK078(tshu)001:16101: lus dang byad bzhin bzang zhing mdzes la yan lag lhag chad med par rdzogsa pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16102: dabnga po lnga tshang zhing nying lag la lhag chad
NK078(tshu)001:16103: med pa ste gzugs phun sum tshogs pa thob par
NK078(tshu)001:16104: 'gyur ro // skad kyi gdangs bzang la snyan cing
NK078(tshu)001:16105: phun sum tshogs pa tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu dang
NK078(tshu)001:16106: ldan pas 'gro ba'i don byed nus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16107: skad gdangs phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16108: bdag gi 'byor ba'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:16109: log 'tsho'i sgo nas sems can gzhan la gnod pa
NK078(tshu)001:16110: med par yang dag pa'i 'tsho ba rtsol med du
NK078(tshu)001:16111: 'grub ste / longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16112: gzhan gyis mi thub pa tshan po che'i mthu stobs
NK078(tshu)001:16113: dang ldan pa phyag na rdo rje lta bur 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:16114: zhing de yang 'gro ba'i don du 'gyur ba'i mthu
NK078(tshu)001:16115: stobs phun sum tshogs pa yang dag pa dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:16116: pa ste / mthu stoobs phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16117: de ltar stobs dang ldan yang sems can gzhan la
NK078(tshu)001:16118: gnod pa yongs mi byed pa'i thog nas sems can
NK078(tshu)001:16120: gsang sngags kyi don rtogs nus pa'i shes rab dang
NK078(tshu)001:16121: ldan pa ste bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa thob
NK078(tshu)001:16122: par 'gyur ro // tshogs sgrub pa'i mthu stobs che
NK078(tshu)001:16123: zhing yo byad la spyod pa'i thabs la mkhas pa
NK078(tshu)001:16124: dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas bdag dang gdul bya
NK078(tshu)001:16125: gzhan gyis don rdzogs par byed nus pa'i phrin las
NK078(tshu)001:16126: phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16127: gsum pa der tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:16129: dbang po rab kyis de lta bu'i lus de la
NK078(tshu)001:16130: brten nas zag bcas kyi lam rnams mthar phyin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16131: 'bras bu skye shi med pa tshe la dbang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:16133: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku'i che ba'i yon tan la
NK078(tshu)001:16134: dgos pa 'byung ba'i yid bzhin nor bu rin po
NK078(tshu)001:16135: che lta bu / bkoda pa'i zhing khams tshad gzhal ba las yas pa thams cad las /
NK078(tshu)001:16136: dper na 'dod khams na lha rigs drug po yod
NK078(tshu)001:16137: pa'i drug pa gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha'i longs
NK078(tshu)001:16138: spyod rang las sprul nas rang gis longs spyod pa
NK078(tshu)001:16139: ji ltar bar / yo byad lnga la dbang bsgyur
NK078(tshu)001:16140: zhing longs spyod pa'i 'bras bu mthong lam gyi dngos
NK078(tshu)001:16141: grub dam pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16142: gnyis pa mjug bsdus te the tshom med par thob tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:16144: 'bring gis tshe phyi ma la tshe dbang du gyur pa de'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:16145: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin tshe phyi ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:16146: dus de nyida du sbyor ba la'ang lta smos kyang
NK078(tshu)001:16147: ci dgos te nges par gdon mi za bar 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:16148: ro // gsum pa lan grangs gzhan la tshe dbang thob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16150: gong du bstan pa'i tshul de ltar sbyor lam tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:16151: sgrub pa la sgo gsum brtson 'grus rab dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:16152: pas ni / dbang po dang brtson 'grus rab kyis mthong lam tshe 'di nyid la thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16153: 'bring gis tshe phyi ma la tshe dbang thob par ma gyur na yang /
NK078(tshu)001:16154: tha mas kyang skye ba brgyud pa'i lan grangs de
NK078(tshu)001:16155: las gzhan du'ang tshe dbang thob ste skye ba bdun
NK078(tshu)001:16156: nyid las mi 'da' bar mthong lam gyi'am /
NK078(tshu)001:16157: tshe dbang rang la bzhi yod pa'i nang nas rig
NK078(tshu)001:16158: 'dzin gyi dam pa lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16160: gnyis pa rnam smin thob tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16162: dang po sgrub pa mthar phyin pas tshe dbang ma
NK078(tshu)001:16163: thob kyang tshe 'di la rnam smin thob pa'i dpe
NK078(tshu)001:16165: de yang cho ga lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16166: sngags kyi yan lag lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16167: yo byad lnga po dag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16168: lnga gsum bco lnga po de dag sbyor lam gyis
NK078(tshu)001:16169: mngon sum rdzogs par byas nas dam tshig ma nyams
NK078(tshu)001:16170: pa dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams nges par
NK078(tshu)001:16171: 'tshogs te tshogs sgrubs shing yo byad lnga la spyad
NK078(tshu)001:16172: na / 'bras bu tshe dbang rig 'dzin tshe 'di nyid la mngon du ma gyur yang /
NK078(tshu)001:16173: blo chung bas rnam smin thob ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16174: dper na rgyal po zhig gis bran mo ngan pa dang bshos pa ste sbyor bas kyang /
