NK078(tshu)001:16175: rgyal po'i sras 'byung ba'i sa bon nur nur po
NK078(tshu)001:16176: bran mo'i mngal du chags pa'i bu de yang rgyal
NK078(tshu)001:16178: de skye ba mthong ma thag nas rgyal bu de
NK078(tshu)001:16179: dmangs thams cad kyis blar te bskur ba'i 'os su
NK078(tshu)001:16180: 'gyur zhing / rgyal sar bton pa'i tshe 'khor 'bangs
NK078(tshu)001:16181: kun la dbang bsgyur ba'i stobs dang ldan pa de
NK078(tshu)001:16182: 'gyur zhing / la / 'jig rten pa'i lha rnams
NK078(tshu)001:16183: kyis kyang gsol mchod la sogs re bas mthu 'am
NK078(tshu)001:16185: rang rang gi mthu stobs bskyed pas rgyal bu de la bsrung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16187: mchod pa byeda pa'i dpe de ltar du /
NK078(tshu)001:16188: tshogs grub kyi rnal 'byor pa yang dag pa'i lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16189: dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gyis stobs dang ldan pa rnam smin rig 'dzin du gyur pa na /
NK078(tshu)001:16190: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i dam can ma mo
NK078(tshu)001:16191: mkha' 'gro la sogs pa'i chos skyong srung ma ma
NK078(tshu)001:16192: lus pa kun gyi dgongs pa lhar smin pa de
NK078(tshu)001:16193: yi dbang gi spyi gtsug tu khur cing bsrung bar
NK078(tshu)001:16194: byed la / nam smin gyi lus kyis spyod yul
NK078(tshu)001:16195: dor nas shi 'phos ma thag yi dam lha'i skur
NK078(tshu)001:16196: smin pa de dngos su gsal ba phyag rgya chen
NK078(tshu)001:16197: po'i rig 'dzin du nges par rdzogs par 'gyur ro
NK078(tshu)001:16198: byed la / // gnyis pa mthar ma phyin kyang
NK078(tshu)001:16199: phyi ma la thob par gdams pa dang bcas pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:16201: dbang po tha ma'i nang nas blo che ba'i gang
NK078(tshu)001:16202: zag la la gong du bstan pa de ltar tshe
NK078(tshu)001:16203: 'dir rnam smin de nyid thob nges na yang /
NK078(tshu)001:16204: blo chung ba la la dag de ltar ma gyur
NK078(tshu)001:16205: pas phyi ma la bsod nams bsags pa'i sa la
NK078(tshu)001:16207: de yang tshe rabs skye ba thams cad kyi bar
NK078(tshu)001:16208: du bral ba'i 'bras bu las ngan par gyur pa
NK078(tshu)001:16212: log pa brgyad la spyod pa'i sa dang gnas kun
NK078(tshu)001:16213: tu tshogs sgrub kyi rnal 'byor pa de skye bar
NK078(tshu)001:16214: mi 'gyur la / lha mi'i theg pa la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:16215: pa nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi la'ang 'jug cing
NK078(tshu)001:16217: thob pa'i 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16218: rigs mchog 'dzin pa'i bshes gnyen dag tu 'gyur te
NK078(tshu)001:16219: skye ba phyi ma lan grangs gzhan la rnam smin
NK078(tshu)001:16220: rig 'dzin thob par byas nas sngon gong du spyod
NK078(tshu)001:16221: yul dor nas phyag rgyar rdzogs ces bstan pa bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:16222: du phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor bar
NK078(tshu)001:16223: 'gyur te / de bas phyi ma la rnam smin
NK078(tshu)001:16224: thob nas phyag chen la sbyor ba 'di la the
NK078(tshu)001:16225: tshom dang som nyi ldan pa min pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16226: las 'phro skal ba dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK078(tshu)001:16227: kun gyis dus rtag tu tshogs sgrub pa la brtson
NK078(tshu)001:16229: 'o na de ltar tshe rnam gnyis bar do nas thob pa yod dam med /
NK078(tshu)001:16230: med na 'di nyid kyi le'u drug pa'i skabs su /
NK078(tshu)001:16231: las ngan lam gzhan rgyun bcad nas //
NK078(tshu)001:16232: bar ma'am phyi mar gnyis sbyor 'dzin //
NK078(tshu)001:16234: tshe rnam gnyis gang rung la sbyor bar bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16235: rnam smin bar do nas thob pa'i lung ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16237: yid kyi lha yi gzugs brten cing //
NK078(tshu)001:16238: phyag rgya'i sku nyid gsal gyur na //
NK078(tshu)001:16239: lhag ma bzhag pa'i bar ma la //
NK078(tshu)001:16240: de med phyag rgya chen por smin //
NK078(tshu)001:16242: yod na rnam smin de cha lugs ji ltar yod /
NK078(tshu)001:16243: lha'i cha lugs su yod na phyag chen dang khyad
NK078(tshu)001:16244: med pas tshe dbang bas rnam smin bzang bar 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:16245: la / med na yid lhar ma smin par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16246: yang b+hi ma la'i gsung pa dang 'gal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:16247: tshe dbang bar do la thob pa yod na /
NK078(tshu)001:16248: phyag chen gyi cha lugs dang khyad med du 'gyur ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:16249: yang na lus snga ma ni dor zin la /
NK078(tshu)001:16250: gzhan lus med pas lhag bcas su mi 'gyur ba'ii skyon yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16252: de dag gis skyon med de /
NK078(tshu)001:16253: bar do nas tshe dbang thob pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16254: bar dor 'byung ba dwangs ma 'od kyi lus lha
NK078(tshu)001:16255: mi'i cha lugs su yod pa der rnam smin thob
NK078(tshu)001:16256: ste / de nyid dor nas phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16257: slob dpon b+hi ma la'i gsung dang mi 'gal te /
NK078(tshu)001:16258: mi yi lus la phyag rgya che //
NK078(tshu)001:16259: rgya mig rgya sa khyung phrug bya //
NK078(tshu)001:16260: gsal rdzogs smin phyir bar chad med //
NK078(tshu)001:16262: che dbang bar do nas thob pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16263: 'byung ba dwangs ma'i lus lha mi'i cha lug de
NK078(tshu)001:16264: nyid mi 'dor bar ye shes 'ja' lus snang nas
NK078(tshu)001:16265: phyag chen dang lhun grub la sbyor ba yin pas
NK078(tshu)001:16269: ngan song du ldog pa'i bar chad med pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:16270: lam gzhan gyi bar chad med pa'i sbyor lam du
NK078(tshu)001:16271: tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas
NK078(tshu)001:16272: mthong lam bsgrub pa'i thabs ston par byed pa'i gzhung
NK078(tshu)001:16273: gi tshig don rnam gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na
NK078(tshu)001:16274: le'u ste / yas bgrang bdun pa'i don du gada'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16275: spyi don gsum pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu zag med kyi lam la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16277: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16279: thun mong gi dngos grub las khyad par du gyur
NK078(tshu)001:16280: pa lhag pa'i ste mchog gi dngos grub rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:16281: de nyid 'grub par 'dod pa la'ang bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i
NK078(tshu)001:16282: sgrub pa'i sgo nas mos par byas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:16283: sdug bsngal gyi zug rngu med pas bde ba chen
NK078(tshu)001:16284: po rig 'dzin gyi sa la gdul bya dgod par
NK078(tshu)001:16285: bya ba'i phyir / zag bcas tshogs sbyor gnyis kyi
NK078(tshu)001:16286: lam mthar phyin pa'i gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu'i mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:16287: nyid zag med mthong sgom mthar gsum gyi rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:16288: bzhi po bshad par bya ba ni 'di lta ste
NK078(tshu)001:16290: 'di yang mthong dang sgom pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:16291: mthar phyin rim pa gsum du bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:16292: dang po mthong ba'i lam bstan pa //
NK078(tshu)001:16293: bya ba gcig yod na legs par gda' ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16294: sgom bu sangs rgyas gsang ba sgoms la yongs nas chad par gada'o gsungs skad /
NK078(tshu)001:16295: gnyis pa gzhung don la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16301: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16303: phyag rgya spros bcas mthar phyin nas zla ba bcu
NK078(tshu)001:16304: drug la sogs pa rab 'bring tha ma'i dus kyi
NK078(tshu)001:16305: zhi khro'i tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa'i sbyor lam bar
NK078(tshu)001:16306: chad med pa'i lam pa nas /
NK078(tshu)001:16307: sngar 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas /
NK078(tshu)001:16308: brgyud pa'i lam smin pa las grub pa'i phung po
NK078(tshu)001:16309: 'di yi lhag ma'i lus 'bras bu'i sa la med
NK078(tshu)001:16310: pa rnam smin dang yod pa tshe dbang las mya
NK078(tshu)001:16312: zag bcas mthar phyin nas zag med la sbyor ba yang /
NK078(tshu)001:16313: thun mong gi theg pa nyan thos la lhag bcas dang lhag med gnyis yod pa lta bur /
NK078(tshu)001:16314: rig 'dzin gyi skabs 'dir yang lhag bcas lhag med gnyis zung gcig tu ston par 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16315: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16316: lhag med rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16317: lhag bcas tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin no //
NK078(tshu)001:16319: rnam smin thob pa'i rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16325: lam gong ma la sbyor tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16329: dang po thod rgal ba gcig spros dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16331: de ltar gnyis yod pa de la thog ma lhag
NK078(tshu)001:16332: med du sbyor ba rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:16333: bshad pa ni gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:16334: thod rgal gyi dbang btsan du rab phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16335: 'bring phyag rgya spros pa lha du ma'i rnal 'byora
NK078(tshu)001:16336: ting nge 'dzin la nyams brtan zhing mthar phyin byas
NK078(tshu)001:16337: pa nyid kyi sa nas rnam smin la sbyor tshul
NK078(tshu)001:16338: lam / gnyis pa mthar chags tshogs sgrub nas so //
NK078(tshu)001:16340: mthar chags dbang du phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor de mthar phyin pa thob nas /
NK078(tshu)001:16341: sbyor lam du blo rab 'bring tha ma'i chas zla druga gam /
NK078(tshu)001:16345: bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i tshogs sgrub pa'i tshe rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa yin zhes smos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16346: tshe dbang lta bur skye shi med pa rdo rje'i lus su smin cing grub par ma gyur bar /
NK078(tshu)001:16348: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin goms pa'i stobs chunga ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16350: smon lam gyi mthu zhan pa'ii phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:16351: sngar nas las kyi lus la bdag tu rtog pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16352: bag chags las grub pa rnam par rtog pa'i lus
NK078(tshu)001:16353: dang / 'byung ba bzhi 'dus pa las grub pa 'byung ba'i lus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16355: sngar gyi las kyi 'phen pa las ma grub pas
NK078(tshu)001:16356: las kyi lus de bzhag nas 'bras bu rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:16357: 'chang chen po sangs rgyas kyi sar /
NK078(tshu)001:16358: phyag rgya chen po dang lhun grub brgyud nas rig pas 'gro bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:16359: lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16360: gnyis pa ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16362: dang po rnam smin thob pa'i ngo bo dpe don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16364: yid yi dam lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po'i rnal
NK078(tshu)001:16365: 'byor ting nge 'dzin mngon sum du gsal zhing rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:16366: par smin kyang / lhag ma'i lus kyi rnam par 'ching ba'i dra basa sgrib par gyur pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16367: dper na ka la ping ka ste bya khyung phrug sgong rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16368: mi 'jigsa pa seng phrug mngal rgya dang bral ma thag rtsal ma dang mnyam pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:16369: tha mal gyi lus rgya 'di dang bral nas yid yi dam lha'i sku /
NK078(tshu)001:16370: ngo bo phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin nyid du
NK078(tshu)001:16371: snang bar byed pa de la rnam par smin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16373: de yang rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin gyi mtshan
NK078(tshu)001:16374: nyid gong du bshad pa ltar chos gsum dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:16377: yid yi dam gyi lha zhi khro gang yin pa
NK078(tshu)001:16378: de'i sku phyag rgya chen por smin pa dang gcig
NK078(tshu)001:16379: /de tha ma la gyi lus kyi dra bas sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:16380: pa dang gnyis / lus rgya dang bral ma thag
NK078(tshu)001:16381: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin du snang ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:16384: las kyi lus sbubs rnal 'byor smin //
NK078(tshu)001:16385: ma dag cha las ming btags pa //
NK078(tshu)001:16389: seng ge mngal rgya'i nang du /
NK078(tshu)001:16392: sgong shun dang mngal gyis bsgrib nas mi snang bas /
NK078(tshu)001:16393: sgrib byed dang bral ma thag nam mkha' dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16394: gangs ri la 'gro nus pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:16396: gal te 'byung ba'i lus zhig nas //
NK078(tshu)001:16397: bdag nyid sgo gsum lhar gsal zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:16398: 'byung ba bsags pa'i lus las grol //
NK078(tshu)001:16399: ting 'dzin phyag rgya chen por smin //
NK078(tshu)001:16400: khyung phyug sbubs dang bral ma thag /ma lus phyag
NK078(tshu)001:16401: rgya sgyu ma'i mchog /rnam par smin ces de la
NK078(tshu)001:16403: de ltar na rnam smin rig 'dzin 'di zag bcas yin nam zag med yin /
NK078(tshu)001:16404: zag bcas yin na zag med kyi mthong lam pa ma yin par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:16405: zag med yin na tshe dbang rig 'dzin dang khyad med par thal zhe na de'i lan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16406: chos kyi spyan ldan sgro phug pa na re /
NK078(tshu)001:16407: zag pa'i gtso bo skye gnas kyi zag pa med pas na zag med yin no gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:16408: rnam smin rang sa'i tshe tshad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16410: lha mi phal pa'i tshe tshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:16412: des na rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16413: sngags phyi rgyud pa dang mthun par nyon mongs pa'i zag pa med bas na zag mid yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:16415: bde ba chen por lung bston pas //
NK078(tshu)001:16416: zag bcas bslab pa'i chos dang bral //
NK078(tshu)001:16420: rtog pa'i rtsa ba phyi nang gi //
NK078(tshu)001:16421: kun nas zag pa rnam pa lnga //
NK078(tshu)001:16423: de yang rtsa nyon dang nye nyon gyi zag pa med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16424: zag pa'i sgo drug gi skyon dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:16425: skye gnas kyi zag pa med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16427: lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum gting nas bral ba'i zag med ni ma yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:16428: brgal lan rgyas pa ni 'grel ba gzhan du shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:16429: gnyis pa rnam smin gyi nges tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16431: rnal 'byor pa'i yid kyisa yi dam gyi lha gang
NK078(tshu)001:16432: yin pa'i sku gzugs gsal bar bzung zhing tha mal
NK078(tshu)001:16433: pa'i lus kyi rgya mdud kyis bsdom pa de ni
NK078(tshu)001:16434: grol bar gyur pa dang de nas 'bras bu phyag
NK078(tshu)001:16435: rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin lha'i sku nyid mngon sum
NK078(tshu)001:16436: du gsal bar gyur pa'i chos dang ldan na rnam
NK078(tshu)001:16437: par smin pa'i rig 'dzin zhes de la gdags so
NK078(tshu)001:16440: rgya mig skol phor nang du rgya pa 'dam pa
NK078(tshu)001:16441: btab pas nang du gzugs dod kyang rgya mig dang
NK078(tshu)001:16442: ma bral bar du mi gsal ba'i dpe ji lta
NK078(tshu)001:16443: bar / yi dam lhar smin pa de lus rgya
NK078(tshu)001:16444: dang bral ma thag phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:16445: thob la ma rag pa'i cha dang ldan pa /
NK078(tshu)001:16446: yid yi dam lha'i sku gzugas su rtsal rdzogs par
NK078(tshu)001:16447: smin pa'i ting nge 'dzin stobs chen du gyur pa
NK078(tshu)001:16448: de kho na rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:16450: bzhi pa ming gi rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16452: dang po thob pa'i ming grangs gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16454: rnam smin de la'ang lta dgongsa bzang ngan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16455: spyod pa zab mi zab rnams lam gong 'og gi phye ba'i khyad par gnyisa yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:16456: de yang phyag rgya gcig spros nas thob pa'i rnam smin de ni dgongs spyod dma' zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:16457: tshogs sgrub nas thob pa'i rnam smin de ni dgongs spyod bzang zhing mtho ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16458: rgyu mtshan des na gcig spros nas thob pa de
NK078(tshu)001:16459: dgongas spyod rgya mtsho snga ma gcig spros dang rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:16460: mthun la / tshogs sgrub nas thob pa de dgongs
NK078(tshu)001:16461: spyod rgya mtsho phyi ma tshogs sgrub dang rgyud mthun
NK078(tshu)001:16462: mthun la / pas / de ltar dgongs spyod rnams
NK078(tshu)001:16463: stobs che chung gi chas rnam smin du ming grags
NK078(tshu)001:16464: mthun la / pas / pa yin no // gnyis pa thob pa'i ngo bo'i ming grangs gsum mo //
NK078(tshu)001:16466: lhag ma'i lus med 'byung ba'i lus med lasa kyi
NK078(tshu)001:16467: lusa med par dgongs pa mya ngan lasa 'adsa pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16468: 'bras bu phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin du smin
NK078(tshu)001:16470: lnga pa spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16474: rang don du ci spyad zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor du gsal zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:16475: lha la lha rol pa'i tshul du spyod pas ma 'gag pa bsod nams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16476: mi dmigs pa ye shes kyi tshogsa gnyis zung 'jug
NK078(tshu)001:16477: tu rdzogs par byed pa de ni rnam smin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:16478: bdag gi don du spyod pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16481: yid yi dam lha'i skur smin pa'i phrin lasa zhi
NK078(tshu)001:16482: rgyas dbang drag bzhis gzhan don yongs su rdzogs par
NK078(tshu)001:16483: byed cing / gdul bya gang yang yal bar mi 'dor bar yang dag pa'i sa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:16484: don la dgod pa ni gzhan gyi don du spyad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16487: phyag rgya gcig spros nas rnam smin thob pa de dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16488: tshogs sgrub nas thob pa de'ang rab kyis tshe 'di la thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16490: phyi ma nas thob pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16491: tha mas kyang lan grangs brgyud pa gzhan bdun tshun
NK078(tshu)001:16492: chad du blo dang brtson pa rab 'bring tha ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:16493: tshul dag gis rnam smin thob par 'gyur gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:16494: de nas phyag chen la sbyor nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:16495: mtshan nyid pa ltar bskal pa grangs med par mi 'gyang ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16498: tshogs kyi spyod pa'i brtul zhugs dang ldan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16499: sgo gsum gyi brtson 'grus bskyed pa rnams gtso bor byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16500: bdun pa lam gong ma la sbyor tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16502: dang po sbyor tshul dngos po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16504: gang rnam smin rig 'dzin de lus rgya dang bral ma thag gi skabs su /
NK078(tshu)001:16505: bar do med pa'i ngang du yi dam lha'i sku
NK078(tshu)001:16506: phyag rgya chen po la sogs pa bzhi rdzogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16507: skur bdag nyid mngon du 'gyur bas rdo rje dang
NK078(tshu)001:16512: lnga rdzogs pa'i rigs gang yin pa de rig pas 'dzin pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:16513: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16514: rnam smin gyi gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu yin pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:16515: gnyis pa lam gyi dbye ba dang 'du ba gcig par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16517: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu phyag chen yin pa de'i phyir phyag rgya chen po thob pa /
NK078(tshu)001:16518: phyag rgya gcig spros dang sbyor lam bar chad med
NK078(tshu)001:16519: pa'i thog nas lam mchog rnam smin la dbye ba
NK078(tshu)001:16521: phyag chen du gcig pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16522: dper na wa brgyun gyi dkyil chu lta bu yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:16523: yang na de phyir phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16524: sbyor lam bar chad med pa gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:16525: lam mchog tshe rnam gnyis kyi rigs dbye sa dang 'du sa gcig yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:16528: sbyor lam bar chad med pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:16529: phyag rgya gcig spros kyi thog nas rnam smin thob pa'i mngon par shes pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:16530: de nyid kyi ming can mngon shes yul grangs mi 'gyur kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:16531: 'dir zag med thob pa'i nus pas yul gsal ba
NK078(tshu)001:16532: nges pa nyid du khyad yod par 'gyur ba'ang yin
NK078(tshu)001:16533: te / phyag rgya gcig pa nas thob pa'i rnam smin gyi dpag tshad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16534: spros pa nas gling bzhi gcig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16535: tshogs sgrub nas gling grangas gnyis nas drug gi bar du mngon shes kyis yul la sbyor ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16536: gnyis pa lhag bcas tshe dbang la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16538: dang po tshe dbang gi khyad par spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16540: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma lhag bcas tshe dbang gi
NK078(tshu)001:16541: phyag rgya spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16542: dus kya tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK078(tshu)001:16543: / lta ba dang dgongas pa ting nge 'dzin gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16544: tshogs kyi spyod pa +aa li k+aa li la spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16545: sgrub pa la ba rtson 'grus bskyed pa chen po dang ldan pa'i stobs kyis sbyangs pa /
NK078(tshu)001:16546: lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa tshe dbang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16547: gsang ba'i yo byad la +aa li ste sbyor lam
NK078(tshu)001:16548: thabs lam sbyangs pa las byung ba thabs kyi tshe
NK078(tshu)001:16549: dbang dang / steng 'og gi rlung bzung ba'i thabs
NK078(tshu)001:16550: kyi nub pa'i stobs rdzogs pa las skyes pa sgrol
NK078(tshu)001:16551: ma rlung las gyur pa'i tshe dbang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16552: lam sbyangs pa de dag las gzhan pa'i sman gyi sgo nas tshe sgrub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16553: dza gad dang 'brang rgyas la sogs pa'i yo byad
NK078(tshu)001:16554: la brten nas tshe bsgrubs pas 'grub pa'i rtags dang
NK078(tshu)001:16555: ldan pa dang / dngos grub la rol cing longs
NK078(tshu)001:16556: spyod pa'i nus mthu las byung ba bdud rtsi sman
NK078(tshu)001:16557: las byung ba'i tshe dbang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16558: de dag rang rang gi thob par byed pa'i thabs ni sman za ba'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16559: thig le bzung ba'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16562: rgyu ni ra mo shag la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16565: tshogs sgrub pa'i shes rab dang bzhis phye ba'i tshe
NK078(tshu)001:16566: dbang bzhi po so so tha dad par byung na
NK078(tshu)001:16567: yang / 'dir tshogs sbyor gyi lam sbyangs pa'i stobs las skyes pa'i tshe dbang te /
NK078(tshu)001:16568: tshe dbang gzhan gsum po las mchog tu gyur pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:16569: zag pa med pa'i rig 'dzin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16570: gnyis pa lam mchog gi tshe dbang bye brag tu bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16581: lam gong ma la sbyor ba'i tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16582: bzhi gnyis brgyad kyi tshe dbang gi lus rnam bzhag
NK078(tshu)001:16583: mdor bstan gyi rnam grangs rgyas pa rdzogs par bshad
NK078(tshu)001:16585: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la brgyad de /
NK078(tshu)001:16586: tshe dbang thob pa'i rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16593: lam gong ma la sbyor tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:16596: dang po drang don gyi rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16598: lam pa gang dag 'bras bu thob par byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16599: 'bras bu la mos pa drang ba'i don tsam du
NK078(tshu)001:16600: tshe dbang thob pa'i rgyur byas pa ni drang don
NK078(tshu)001:16601: rgyu'o // gnyis pa nges don gyi rgyu de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16603: dang po spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16605: nges pa'i don du zag bcas kyi thos bsam sgom
NK078(tshu)001:16606: gsum gyi shes rab rnam pa gsum la rim cig
NK078(tshu)001:16607: char du goms par byas nas tshe dbang thob pa
NK078(tshu)001:16608: la / gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16610: dang po gcig char ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16612: de yang lam cig char ba'i dbang du bden pa
NK078(tshu)001:16613: gnyis su med pa'i lta ba chos nyid mnyam pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16614: don ma nor ba cig chod du thos pa'i shes
NK078(tshu)001:16615: rab kyis thos / des bsam pa'i shes rab kyis rtogs te /
NK078(tshu)001:16616: bden pa gnyis med kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi dgag sgrub dang bral bas /
NK078(tshu)001:16617: dus dang gnas skabs kun tu chos nyid mtha' bral
NK078(tshu)001:16618: yangs pa chen por cig char du bsgom pa yin
NK078(tshu)001:16619: la / gnyis pa rim gyis pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16621: lam rim gyis pa'i dbang du rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16627: lam tshogs sbyor gyi rnal 'byor rnam pa lnga pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16628: lta ba'i skabs su thos bsam gyi shes rab kyi
NK078(tshu)001:16629: rim gyis rtogs ting nge 'dzin rim gyis goms par
NK078(tshu)001:16630: gyur pa tshogs 'grub pa'i rnal 'byor pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16631: sbyor lam du zla ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16632: zhag gi grangs rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po'i le'u dgu pa nas /
NK078(tshu)001:16633: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam /
NK078(tshu)001:16634: la sogs gsungs bzhin du tshogs sgrub par byed pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16635: 'bras bu skye shi med pa rda rje lta bu'i
NK078(tshu)001:16636: lus su tshe dbang 'grub par the tshom med de
NK078(tshu)001:16641: lhag ma'i lus nyid ma spang bar skye shi med
NK078(tshu)001:16642: pa rdo rje'i lus su gyur tshul ni de lta
NK078(tshu)001:16643: bur gyur pa'o // gnyis pa dus la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16645: dang po tshe dbang thob pa'i dus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16647: bsgrub cing 'grub pa'i zhag grangs ni rab kyis zhag gsum cu phrag drug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16648: zla ba drug gam 'bring gi zla ba bcu gnyis ste lo gcig gam /
NK078(tshu)001:16649: zla ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis sam /
NK078(tshu)001:16650: tha ma'i zla ba bcu drug ste lo gcig dang
NK078(tshu)001:16651: zla ba bzhi po dag gis blo dang brtson 'grus
NK078(tshu)001:16652: rab 'bring tha ma'i rim pas gzhung nas ji ltar
NK078(tshu)001:16653: bshad pa bzhin du nyams su blangs nas bsgrub na
NK078(tshu)001:16654: nges par mi bslu bar tshe la rang dabnga bsgyur
NK078(tshu)001:16655: zhing lus mi 'dor ba sprul sku'i rig 'dzin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16656: rig 'dzin gyi dam pa lam mchog yongs su rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:16657: pa'i tshe dbang nyid 'grub par 'gyur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16658: gnyis pa lam gong ma la sbyor te sangs rgyas pa'i dus so //
NK078(tshu)001:16661: 'bras bu lha'i sangs rgyas gnyis gzhi la ye gdod
NK078(tshu)001:16662: ma nas dbyer med par dus gcig tu rdzogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16663: don de nyid ranga rig byang chub kyi sems nyid
NK078(tshu)001:16664: la rang dbang thob ste rtogs nas mngon du gyur
NK078(tshu)001:16665: te / de'i rang don gyi tshe tshad ni tshe
NK078(tshu)001:16666: lo brgya ba'i dbang du lo brgya phrag bcu dang
NK078(tshu)001:16667: drug ste lo stong drug brgya gnas pa yi bar
NK078(tshu)001:16668: lo brgya re brgya re na je gzhon la byis
NK078(tshu)001:16669: pa gzhon nu lo brgyad pa lon pa dag tu
NK078(tshu)001:16670: bsnur zhing 'jig rten du gnas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:16671: mthar da ltar gyi lus 'di ma bor bar yang
NK078(tshu)001:16672: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa la khyer
NK078(tshu)001:16673: nas 'gro ba'i don nus pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16674: gsum pa ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16680: sprul pa'i lus kyi cha byad do //
NK078(tshu)001:16685: gzhi bden pa dbyer med kyi don rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta bas mthong /
NK078(tshu)001:16686: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi mthar phyin pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16687: sbyor lam du zhi khro'i tshogs kyi longs spyod yo byad lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:16688: khyad par +aa li spyod cing tshogs sgrub pa'i dngos grub khyad par can blangs pa'i stobs kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:16691: de yang lusa kyi zag pa lus rang dbang med
NK078(tshu)001:16692: par rgas rgud dang 'dor len gyi sdug bsngal dang
NK078(tshu)001:16693: / khams kyi zag pa bshang gci dang 'du ba bzhis khams bde mi bde dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16694: skye gnas kyi zag pa skye gnas bzang ngan la
NK078(tshu)001:16695: rang dbang med par 'jug pa la sogs pa'i zag
NK078(tshu)001:16696: pa gsum po zad cing med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16697: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i lus su 'grub par
NK078(tshu)001:16698: 'gyur bas tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin thob
NK078(tshu)001:16699: pa'o // de yang sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho las /
NK078(tshu)001:16700: zag pa gsum dang bral 'gyur bas //
NK078(tshu)001:16701: rnam par smin pa'i lus de'am //
NK078(tshu)001:16702: tshe la dbang bsgyur gnas thob nas //
NK078(tshu)001:16703: goms nas phyag rgya'i rigs su nges //
NK078(tshu)001:16707: de yang mthong ba'i chos tshe 'di nyid la mya ngan las 'das pa thob pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16708: lhag ma'i lus 'di nyid ma bor bar 'di dang
NK078(tshu)001:16709: bcas bzhin du mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa la
NK078(tshu)001:16710: 'gro nus pa'o // bzhi pa yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:16713: nyon mongs pa lnga po kun dang bral zhing 'og nas ston pa'i cho 'phrul bzhi yang rdzogsa pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16714: gnyis pa sprul pa'i lus kyi cha byad do //
NK078(tshu)001:16716: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin de'i cha byad ni lha dang mi'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzina te /
NK078(tshu)001:16717: 'dod lha drug gi rgyal po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16718: mi'i rgyal po 'khor los sgyur ba la sogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16719: gzugs khams kyi lha tshangs pa la sogs pa'i cha lugs su gnas pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16720: de rnams kyi skye ba rnam par dag pa rang
NK078(tshu)001:16721: dbang can dbang po dang yan lag la lhag chad
NK078(tshu)001:16722: dang / zha grum la sogs pa med pa 'dzin mod kyi /
NK078(tshu)001:16723: 'o na de rnams dang khyad med dam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:16724: kyang zhes pas khyad yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:16725: de dag gi khyad par ni zag med kyi sa
NK078(tshu)001:16726: la gnas pa dang mi gnas par 'gyur ba'i khyad
NK078(tshu)001:16727: par yod pa yina bzhin du lha mi'i rgyal po'i
NK078(tshu)001:16728: cha byad de nyid kyis gdul bya de yi rigs
NK078(tshu)001:16729: can la skyed rdzogs gsum gyi chos ston te sprul
NK078(tshu)001:16730: pa'i sku'i rgyal tshab byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16731: de ltar na tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:16732: de'i rtsa ba'i lus lha mi'i skye ba khyad par
NK078(tshu)001:16733: can skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i las su khyer
NK078(tshu)001:16734: ba'o // de yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK078(tshu)001:16735: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:16736: lha mi'i cha byad 'dzin mod kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:16737: zhing dang longs spyod dag pa yis //
NK078(tshu)001:16738: gong nas gong du mnyam par sbyor //
NK078(tshu)001:16739: rdo rje rig pa 'dzin pa'i sku //
NK078(tshu)001:16740: zhing rnams kun la gnas par byed //
NK078(tshu)001:16742: zag pa med pa rdo rje'i sku //
NK078(tshu)001:16744: bde bar chen por lung thob pas //
NK078(tshu)001:16745: zag bcas bslab pa'i chos dang bral //
NK078(tshu)001:16747: sgrub pa nus pa gang ldan pa //
NK078(tshu)001:16748: rdo rje'i lus su 'jig pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:16749: 'jig pa lnga bral zag pa zad //
NK078(tshu)001:16750: dbang bsgyur gsum la dbang thob pas //
NK078(tshu)001:16751: bde ba'i longs spyod dpag tu bshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:16752: sprul pa'i sku ni 'dul ba'i dbang gis ma nges te //
NK078(tshu)001:16754: zhing la dbang bsgyur sprul pa'i lus //
NK078(tshu)001:16755: ting 'dzin longs spyod dpag tu med //
NK078(tshu)001:16757: bdun pa yon tan la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16759: dang po bral ba'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16761: dper na 'gro ba gang dag sbrul dug gis mi
NK078(tshu)001:16762: 'jigs pa la rtsi ma ki ta 'chang ba de
NK078(tshu)001:16763: nyid dug gi 'jigs pa dang bral ba ltar du
NK078(tshu)001:16764: / tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin de yang 'jigs pa lnga dang bral te /
NK078(tshu)001:16766: 'tsho ba med dang mi basngagasa 'khor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16767: 'khor gyi 'jigs bral 'chi ba'i bag chags spang //
NK078(tshu)001:16769: 'tsho ba med kyis dogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16774: dang po ni khams kyi zas dang bral zhing zag
NK078(tshu)001:16775: med kyi bde bas rgyas shing nam mkha' mdzod kyi
NK078(tshu)001:16776: ting nge 'dzin la mnga' brnyes pas 'tsho ba'i 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:16778: gnyis pa ni bdag 'dzin med cing chos kun mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16779: gzhan gyi nyes skyon la sogs tshig brjod kyang nyes pa'i gzhi med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16780: gsum pa ni nyon mongs pa gtan nas grol zhing
NK078(tshu)001:16781: 'khor bar dbugs dbyung bas 'khor bar 'khyams kyis dogs
NK078(tshu)001:16783: bzhi pa ni shes rab stobs chen du gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:16784: sh+aa ri'i bu la sogs pas dus gcig tu dris kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:16785: the tshom gyi lan dus gcig tu thebs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16786: lnga pa ni rigs pa la rang dbang thob cing
NK078(tshu)001:16787: rdo rje'i lus su gyur bas 'chi ba'i dogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:16788: med pa'o // de yang sogs khung du 'jigs pa
NK078(tshu)001:16789: brgyad dang 'khor ba'i nyes skyon thams cad dang brala
NK078(tshu)001:16790: med pa'o // ba'o // gnyis pa thob pa'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16793: cho 'phrul bzhi po dag gi yan lag nyer lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16794: nyi shu la sogs pa kun gyi rtsal dang grangs yongs su rdzogs shing /
NK078(tshu)001:16795: gsum pa skye ba'i yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16797: tshe'am rig pa dang skye ba la rang dbang bsgyur
NK078(tshu)001:16798: ba'i stobs kyis lha mi'i rgyal po'i skye ba rnam
NK078(tshu)001:16799: dag khyad par can blang ba yis /
NK078(tshu)001:16800: bzhi pa 'dul zhing gi yon tan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16802: gzhan don du stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:16803: rten gyi khams brgya tshun chad kyi gdul bya 'dul
NK078(tshu)001:16804: bar byed do // lnga pa rgyu'i sa dang po dang skal pa mnyam pa'i yon tan no //
NK078(tshu)001:16806: rgyu'i theg pa chen po'i sa dang po rab tu dga' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16807: tshe dbang rig 'dzin gnyis 'khor ba la phyir mi ldog pa tsam du skal ba mnyam pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16808: de'i shugs la lam gong ma yang de ltar du shes pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:16810: de yang dang po'i dang po dang //
NK078(tshu)001:16811: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog ste //
NK078(tshu)001:16812: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK078(tshu)001:16813: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mod //
NK078(tshu)001:16814: dgongs spyod rgya mtshos khyad par 'phags //
NK078(tshu)001:16816: gsum pa sku tshe'i tshad la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:16818: dang po bdag don gyi tshe tshad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16820: bdag gi don gyi phyir thos bsam la sogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16821: lam don du gnyer ba 'bras bu thob pa'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:16822: ni / lo brgya phrag bcu drug ste lo stong
NK078(tshu)001:16823: drug brgya'i tshe yi rang don rdzogs nas 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:16824: ni / la sbyor ba'o // gnyis pa gzhan don gyi tshe tshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:16826: gdul bya gzhan gyi don du tshe la rang dbang
NK078(tshu)001:16827: thob pa yin pa'i phyir tshad bzung du med de
NK078(tshu)001:16828: / bzhugs par bzhed na dus bskal pa grangs med
NK078(tshu)001:16829: pa'i bar du 'jig rten gyi khams su gnas par
NK078(tshu)001:16830: / 'gyur yang / bgres rgud mi mnga' ba'i sku
NK078(tshu)001:16831: ni shina tu gzhon pa lo brgyad pa'i tshul du
NK078(tshu)001:16832: / 'gyur yang / snang ste / rtsa ba'i lus la skye 'jig med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:16833: gdul bya rtag par 'dzin pa sun phyungs nas /
NK078(tshu)001:16834: le lo can rnams 'dul ba'i dus kyisa sprul pa'i lus 'chi 'pho ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16835: mi 'dul na 'dug par yang byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:16836: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16838: de la dngos su lung ston cing dbang bskur 'byung
NK078(tshu)001:16839: bar bstan pa dang gnas dang skye ba dang cha
NK078(tshu)001:16840: byad kyang gzhan don gyi skabs kyi ma nges pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:16846: dang po tshe dbang rig 'dzin spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16848: ngo bo ngos bzung ba bzhin du rnam grangs kyang rnam par 'jug ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16850: ra mo shag dang rtag ngu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16851: phyi nang gi bdud rtsi lnga yi sman gyis bcud len pa'i tshe dbang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16852: 'og sgo sbyor ba'i thabs las gyur pa'i tshe dbang rig 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16853: rnal 'byor rlung bzung ba'i tshe ring bar gyur ba
NK078(tshu)001:16854: sgrol ma rlung las gyur pa'i tshe dbang rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:16855: dang / ma h+aa yo ga'i tshogs sbyor gyi lam
NK078(tshu)001:16856: mchog lta sgom spyod gsum gyi rtsal yongs su rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:16857: pa'i tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16858: de ltar tshe dbang la rim pa'ang bzhi po de /
NK078(tshu)001:16861: tshe la dbang bas 'khor ba ji srid bzhugs //
NK078(tshu)001:16862: skye la dbang bas rigs kyi sprul skur ston //
NK078(tshu)001:16863: yo byad dbang bas 'dod yon lnga la rol //
NK078(tshu)001:16864: mos la dbang bas bdag gzhan mos bzhin snang //
NK078(tshu)001:16865: rdzu 'phrul dbang bas rdzu 'phrul cho phrul snang //
NK078(tshu)001:16866: chos la dbang bas chos skad so sor sgrog /ye shes dbang bas shes bya kun ma rmongs //
NK078(tshu)001:16867: sems la dbang bas ting 'dzin 'bum phrag rol //
NK078(tshu)001:16868: las la dbang bas 'byor ba'i phrin las mdzad //
NK078(tshu)001:16869: smon lam dbang bas ji ltar btab bzhin 'grub //
NK078(tshu)001:16871: de ltar dbang bcu yod pa'i dang por tshe la dbang ba tsam du 'dra mod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:16872: de dag la khyad yod de gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:16873: gnyis pa lam mchog rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang khyad par du bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16875: tshe dbang bzhi po de dag nyid la khyad par drug las /
NK078(tshu)001:16876: dang po mthu dang byin rlabs la che chung gi khyad par yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:16877: gsum po bdag don kun 'gro spang mi nus shing /
NK078(tshu)001:16878: rdzu 'phrul nyi shu sogs 'byin mi nus la /
NK078(tshu)001:16880: gnyis pa zag pa yod med kyi khyad ni gsum po la zag pa yod la /
NK078(tshu)001:16881: 'di la snga ma bzhin mi zag ste zag med kyi mthong lam pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:16882: gsum pa bskyed pa rgyu'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16883: gsum po'i rgyu ni sman la sogs pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:16884: 'di'i rgyu ni tshogs sgrub kyi shes rab gsum yin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16885: bzhi pa ngo bo'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16886: gsum po ni 'jig rten pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:16887: 'di'i ngo bo ni lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pas 'das pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16888: de ltar 'khor 'das dang zag bcas zag med rnam pa gnyis su 'gyur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16889: lnga pa lta dgongs kyi khyad par ni gong du bshad pa'i khyad yod pa de bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:16890: gsum po la zag med kyi dgongs pa med la /
NK078(tshu)001:16891: 'di ni zag med kyi chos nyid rang mtshan gyi dgongs pa la mda' brnyes pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16892: drug pa spyod pa'i khyad ni /
NK078(tshu)001:16893: gsum pos ni bdag gzhan gyi don rgya chen po spyod mi nus la /
NK078(tshu)001:16894: 'dir ni bdag ga zhan gyi don rlabs po tshe spyod nus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16895: sangs rgyas sprul sku'i rgyal tshab byed nus pa des
NK078(tshu)001:16896: na dgongs pa spyod pa la khyad par yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:16898: lam mchog 'di las gzhan pa sman dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16900: rlung las grub pa'i tshe dbang thob pa de gsum kyang tshe dbang tsam po yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:16901: lam mchog yongs rdzogs gi tshe dbang rig 'dzina dang 'dra ba min no //
NK078(tshu)001:16902: gnyis pa ming gi rnam grangs gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16904: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16906: lam mchog gi tshe dbang rang la'ang yon tan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:16907: mtshan gyi rnam grangs mi 'dra ba'i cha nas brjod
NK078(tshu)001:16909: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16911: dang po ming bzhi'i lus dang bcas nas mya ngan la 'da' bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16913: lhag ma'i lus ste gzugs kyi phung po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16914: ming bzhi'i phung por bcas pa'i skal pa grangs med
NK078(tshu)001:16915: la sogs ci tsam gnas par 'dod pa la rang
NK078(tshu)001:16916: dbang thob pa'i tshe dbang ba'i rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:16920: las kyi lus dang bcas pa ma spang bar mya
NK078(tshu)001:16921: ngan las 'das pas lhag bcas kyi mya 'das zhes
NK078(tshu)001:16922: bya'o // gnyis pa zag ldog med par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16924: lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum po kun
NK078(tshu)001:16925: zad pas tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin chen po
NK078(tshu)001:16926: mthong lam pa 'dis bdag gzhan gyi don du sgo
NK078(tshu)001:16927: gsum gyi spyod pa ji ltar spyod kyanga 'khor ba
NK078(tshu)001:16928: la ldog pa med pas zag ldog med pa'i lam
NK078(tshu)001:16929: pa zhes bya'o // de yang ldog pa med ces pa 'di la /
NK078(tshu)001:16930: ngan song du ldog pa med dam /
NK078(tshu)001:16932: theg dman du ldog pa med /
NK078(tshu)001:16933: dang po ltar na sbyor lam dang khyad med du 'gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:16934: gnyis pa ltar na lha mi stod ris kyi skye ba 'dzin par bshad pa dang 'gal la /
NK078(tshu)001:16935: gsum pa ltar na chos spyir btang dang 'gal te /
NK078(tshu)001:16937: ci srid sa brgyad ma non par //
NK078(tshu)001:16938: de srid theg pa dman pas 'jig /ces pas /
NK078(tshu)001:16939: dus mtha' yun ring ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16940: sems can mang la gnod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16941: rang don la zhen pas sa brgyad ma non bar du theg dman la ldog te /
NK078(tshu)001:16942: theg chen sgor zhugs pa gcig la bdud rigs can
NK078(tshu)001:16943: gyi dmigs blangs nas kho rang gi rtsar gcar bas
NK078(tshu)001:16944: blo log nas theg chung du ltung bar bshad pa
NK078(tshu)001:16946: mi ldog rnam gsum goms byas nas //
NK078(tshu)001:16947: zhes bzod thob ngan song dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16949: sgom lam sa brgyad pa theg pa dman par mi ldog pa bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:16950: 'dir gong ltar mi ldog pa gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:16951: gong 'og gnyis su tshogs sbyor mthar phyin nas mi
NK078(tshu)001:16952: ldog par bshad la 'di ni 'khor ba rang dbang
NK078(tshu)001:16954: gsum pa dbugs dbyung nas bden pa mthong bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16956: rig pa la rang dbang thob pas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis 'jigs pa las dbugsa dbyung ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:16957: ngal bso ba'i phyir dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16958: tshe dbang gi skabs 'dir rnam smin dang sbyor lam la zur za ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:16959: de yang zag bcas dang zag med sangs rgyas kyi
NK078(tshu)001:16960: sa'i bden pa gsum las 'dir bden pa bar ma
NK078(tshu)001:16961: zag med rang gi mtshan nyid mthong bas zag med
NK078(tshu)001:16964: nus pa thob dang ma thob las //
NK078(tshu)001:16965: mthong lam gnyis su gyur pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:16969: ye shes can gyi spyod yul te //
NK078(tshu)001:16970: kun dang thun mong de ma yin //
NK078(tshu)001:16971: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul te //
NK078(tshu)001:16972: skyes bu blo rtsal rab kyis rtogs //
NK078(tshu)001:16975: gsang ba'i bdag po gsang sngags kyi ngo bo sems
NK078(tshu)001:16976: kyi de kho na nyid de gang gi spyod yul
NK078(tshu)001:16978: lang ka'i bdag po de ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi spyod yul du gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:16979: sa dang sa la gnas pa rnams kyis ma yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:16981: bzhi pa rig pa 'dzin par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16983: chos rang dang spyi'i don rnams la mkhas pa'i lta
NK078(tshu)001:16984: ba rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin goms par spyod pas
NK078(tshu)001:16985: rig pa ye shes dang mi 'bral bar 'dzin pas
NK078(tshu)001:16987: rig 'dzin de'i cha lugs kyang lha dang mi la sogs pa'i cha lugs yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:16988: ting nge 'dzin gyi yi dam gyi lha zhi khro
NK078(tshu)001:16989: gang yin pa'i rdo rje'i rigs la sogs pa'i rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:16991: mi gtong ba'i gzung dang ldan pa las rig 'dzin gyi ming thob pas rig 'dzin zhes kyang bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16992: gsum pa don bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:16994: de la sogs pa mthong lam pa'i yon tan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:16995: rnam grangs la btags na mtshan gyi rnam grangs kyang
NK078(tshu)001:16996: bsam gyis mi khyaba cing brjod kyis mi lang ngo
NK078(tshu)001:16997: // gnyis pa de la dngos su lung ston cing dbang bskur 'byung bar lung bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:16999: tshe dbang 'di la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis dngosa su sa khams te /
NK078(tshu)001:17000: zhing khams 'di dang 'dir rgyug la sgro 'dogs chod cig ces pa'i lung ston pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17001: gsang mtshan rdo rje che ge mo zhes bos nas rdo rje'i ming gis dbang bskur bar 'byung ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:17002: 'o na lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor bsgom lam dang khyad med du thal /
NK078(tshu)001:17003: dngos su lung bstan thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:17005: mtshan nyid theg pa ltar na /
NK078(tshu)001:17006: sa bdun pa man chad nyams snang ngam /
NK078(tshu)001:17007: rmi lam du lung ston la /
NK078(tshu)001:17008: sa brgyad pa la dngos su lung ston par bshad do //
NK078(tshu)001:17010: sa bdun pa man chad du nyon yid ma log pas bdag 'dzin phra mo yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:17011: dngos su lung bstan na nga rgyal dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17012: rlom sems phra mo skye srid la de skyes na theg dman du ldog go //
NK078(tshu)001:17013: sa brgyad pa nyon yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su gnas 'gyur bas /
NK078(tshu)001:17014: ngar 'dzin zad de dngos su lung bstan pa 'byung bar bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17016: mthong lam tshe dbang la sprul skus dngos su sa
NK078(tshu)001:17017: khams su lung ston cing chos 'chad pa yin la
NK078(tshu)001:17018: / sgom lam phyag rgya chen po la longs sku'i zhing khams su lung ston pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17020: rmi lam sgra snyan pa khams dang //
NK078(tshu)001:17021: zhing khams sangs rgyas nyid du bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:17023: gsum pa gnas dang skye ba cha byad kyang gzhan don gyi skabs kyi ma nges pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17025: lta ba mthong zhing ting nge 'dzin goms pa'i nus
NK078(tshu)001:17026: mthu dang ldan pas spyod yul thams cad rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:17027: rang byung gi ye shes nyid du rang snang ba
NK078(tshu)001:17028: ma gtogs pa gzhan med pas na tshe la dbang
NK078(tshu)001:17029: ba'i rig pa 'dzin pa'i gnas de yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:17030: de ltar thams cad rig pa rang snang bas gnas
NK078(tshu)001:17031: su ma gyur pa med pas brten pa'i gnas la
NK078(tshu)001:17032: phyogs gcig tu nges pa med la /
NK078(tshu)001:17033: skye ba dang cha byad kyang gdul bya'i don bya ba'i skabs kyi 'gyur zhing ma nges so //
NK078(tshu)001:17035: rdo rje'i sku la skye shi med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17036: lha mi'i rgyal po'i cha byad du yod par dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17038: gong ma ni rtsa ba'i lus yin la 'di ni sprul pa'i lus yin pas so //
NK078(tshu)001:17039: lnga pa dgongs pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17040: mi dmigs pa chos nyid kyi dgongs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17041: ma 'gag pa phyag rgya'i dgongs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17042: dgongs pa la gnas nas mthar 'bras bu la sbyor tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:17045: dang po dgongs pa mthong bya mthong byed med par
NK078(tshu)001:17046: chos nyid mngon sum du mthong ba la sogs sgo
NK078(tshu)001:17047: lnga yul med du rang gsal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17049: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams rig pa badga nyid chen
NK078(tshu)001:17050: po rang snang du rtogs pa yin pa'i phyir yul
NK078(tshu)001:17053: chos can kun kyang yul yul can du mi mthong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:17054: 'o na de'i chos nyid mthong ngam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17055: chos nyid kyang yul yul can du mi mthong bas
NK078(tshu)001:17056: des na sangs rgyas kyi thugs kyang yul yul can
NK078(tshu)001:17058: 'o na 'khor ba mthong ngam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17060: nang bcud 'gro drug gi sems can kyang rang gi
NK078(tshu)001:17061: sems nyid rang snang ba las gzhan du mi mthong
NK078(tshu)001:17062: ngo // des na yul med rang gsal gnyis med du gang mthong ba /
NK078(tshu)001:17063: des ni mtha' bral lhun grub kyi don yul med
NK078(tshu)001:17064: rang gsal gyi ngo la yul yul can dang phyogs
NK078(tshu)001:17065: re'i nyes skyon med pas yang dag pa zag med
NK078(tshu)001:17066: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17067: gtan tshigs de bas rna ba'i sgra yul yul can
NK078(tshu)001:17068: gang du thos pa med par sgra grags stong zung
NK078(tshu)001:17069: 'jug rang snang du thos pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17070: de bzhin du lces ro myong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17073: yid kyis yul rig pa la sogs pa yul med
NK078(tshu)001:17074: rang snang gnyis med du mthong bas na mthong ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:17075: lam mo // gnyis pa de'i rgyu lta sgom gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17076: stobs las byung bas zag bcas las khyad par du
NK078(tshu)001:17078: de ltar bden pa mthong ba'i rgyu gang las byung zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17079: rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17080: rkyen 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin bzhi dang bar chad med pa tshogs sgrub pa las skyes pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17081: de'i phyir na bden pa dbyer med rang rig mngon sum du rtogs pa'i mchog tshe dbang ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17082: bden pa dbyer med kyi rig pa la rang dbang
NK078(tshu)001:17083: thob nas sngon ngo bo'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:17084: yin te / lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa
NK078(tshu)001:17085: gsum gyis 'khor bar zag pa ni lam mchog yongs
NK078(tshu)001:17086: rdzogs kyi tshe dbang rig 'dzin 'di la med do
NK078(tshu)001:17087: yin te / // gnyis pa ma 'gag pa phyag rgya'i dgongs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17089: sngon chad tshogs sbyor gnyis kyi lam gyi spangs bya'i
NK078(tshu)001:17090: rtsol ba dang gnyen po'i rtsol ba'i 'du byed rnams
NK078(tshu)001:17091: kyang zag med kyi tshe dbang 'di la med de
NK078(tshu)001:17092: / de'i rgyu mtshan ni 'dir mnyam rjes 'dres shing
NK078(tshu)001:17093: nyon mongs mngon gyur dag pas 'bras bu thob tu
NK078(tshu)001:17094: / re ba dang / ma thob kyi dogs pa'i 'dzin chags dang bral ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:17095: de 'ang blo che chung gi dbang gis /
NK078(tshu)001:17096: blo chung na lha stong nas nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs rim par bsgom pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:17097: blo che na rim pa med par gcig car du rdzogs pa'i tshul gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:17098: stong nas nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs bsam yas
NK078(tshu)001:17099: grangs mang po lha'i 'khora lo rang rig par gsal
NK078(tshu)001:17100: ba rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin la gnas
NK078(tshu)001:17101: nas zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor rnam pa gnyis kyis rang
NK078(tshu)001:17102: bzhin gyi don thams cad bsgrub par mdzad do //
NK078(tshu)001:17103: gsum pa dgongs pa la gnas nas mthar thug 'bras bu la sbyor tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:17105: dgongs pa de'i ming ni tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:17106: rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:17107: te / rang don du lo brgya phrag bcu drug gi cha ma rdzogs kyi dus kyi bar du /
NK078(tshu)001:17108: rang gi shes rab gsum gyi lam goms par byas nas mthar chags pa phyag rgya chen po /
NK078(tshu)001:17109: thod rgal ba lhun grub gnyis thob pa'i tha ma
NK078(tshu)001:17110: skad cig ma gcig gi cha yis rdo rje lta
NK078(tshu)001:17111: bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis shes sgrib 'joms pas dpa'
NK078(tshu)001:17112: bo mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas la sbyor
NK078(tshu)001:17113: ba'o // 'dir zag med kyi lam gsum gyi sgrib pa spang tshul la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17114: spang bya sgrib pa'i don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17115: spang byed gnyen po'i don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17116: ji ltar spang ba'i tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:17119: bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17120: 'di gsum yang spyir shes bya'i sgrib par 'dus /
NK078(tshu)001:17121: bye brag tu lpags kyi shun la gnas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17123: rkang gi dkyil la gnas pa'i tshul gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:17126: khyab che chung gi tshul gyis tha dad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17127: gnyis pa ni mthong lam dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17129: mthar lam gyi rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17131: rig 'dzin gsum po rang rang gi gnyen po ye shes skye ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17132: spang bya sgrib pa dag pa dus mnyam pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:17133: de yang spang bya shar ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17134: gnyen po ye shes su grol ba gnyis spang gnyen ro gcig pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17135: dper na nyi ma shar ba dang mun pa sangs ba dus mnyam pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17136: drug pa spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17138: dang po bdag don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17140: tshe dbang rang dang rigsa mthun yang blo che zhing
NK078(tshu)001:17141: dgongs pa mchog tu gyur pa'i tshe dbang rgan po
NK078(tshu)001:17142: rnams dang / phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku rnams la /
NK078(tshu)001:17143: gsang sngags zag med kyi ngang nas bogs dang rtsal
NK078(tshu)001:17144: 'don pa'i don la thos pa'i shes rab kyis thos
NK078(tshu)001:17145: / bsam pa'i shes rab kyis don rig par byas shing rtogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17146: bsgom pa'i shes rab kyis don rang gi rgyud la sbyor bas /
NK078(tshu)001:17147: dper na dkyus sar phyin pa'i rta cang shes te /
NK078(tshu)001:17148: dkyus su zhugs nas kun tu thogs med du 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:17149: lta ba de lam mgo mjug kun gyi sngon du 'gro ba yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17150: lta ba de'i ngang nas shes rab gsum gyis sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:17151: pa sbyang shing dgongs pa'i rtsal 'don pa ni bdag
NK078(tshu)001:17153: gnyis pa gzhan don yon tan dang bcas pa de la /
NK078(tshu)001:17156: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17160: rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17161: kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul te bzhi po de dag dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17162: mngon par shes pa drug kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:17163: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba de nyid kyi ming dang ldan pa yis /
NK078(tshu)001:17164: tshe la dbang bsgyur bas rtsa ba'i lus skye 'jig
NK078(tshu)001:17165: med pas rdo rje'i sku las ma g.yos pa'i sprul
NK078(tshu)001:17166: pa'i sku lha mi'i rgyal po'i cha byad kyis gdul
NK078(tshu)001:17167: bya gzhan gyi don la phrin las kyi bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:17168: byed cing 'gro don thams cad yongs su rdzogs par
NK078(tshu)001:17170: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17171: cho 'phrul bzhis gzhan don bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17172: gzhan don mdzad nas 'bras bu la sbyor tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17173: rmad du byung ba'i spyod pas gdul bya gdul bar bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17175: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17178: kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gyis gzhan don mdzad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17181: dang po rdzu 'phrul nyi shu bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17183: cho 'phrul bzhi'i thog mar sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17184: cho 'phrul gyis gdul bya gzhan gyi don spyod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:17187: lam lta sgom gyi nus pa'i mthu can du gyur
NK078(tshu)001:17188: pa'i skye ba rang dbang can tshe la dbang bsgyur
NK078(tshu)001:17190: rdzu 'phrul nyi shu la spyod pa'i tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17191: ci lta bu nus zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17192: de yang lus shing bal gyi 'dab ma lta bu
NK078(tshu)001:17193: yangs bas nam mkha' la bya bzhin 'phyo ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:17194: / rig 'dzin gyi gnas thams cad bsgrod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17195: ngag gi bden pa grub pas chu bo'i rgyun gyen
NK078(tshu)001:17196: la bzlog par gyur cig ces brjod pa tsam gyis
NK078(tshu)001:17197: bzlog pa dang / rlung zhi bar gyur cig byas
NK078(tshu)001:17198: pa tsam gyis mi 'gul bar 'ching bar nus pa
NK078(tshu)001:17199: bzlog pa dang / dang / ri dang brag la
NK078(tshu)001:17200: sogs pa la thogs pa med par 'dzul nus pa
NK078(tshu)001:17201: bzlog pa dang / dang / dang / chu la mi bying ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17203: dug dang mtshon gyis 'jigs par mi 'gyur te mi tshugs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17204: lus 'di mngon sum du mi snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17205: lus gcig la mang por sprul pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17206: de dag las gzhan pa yang rang nyid yid la
NK078(tshu)001:17207: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du 'grub ste gang zhe
NK078(tshu)001:17208: na / 'jig rten gyi lha ma srin sde brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:17209: rnams la bdag gis dbang bsgyur zhing bran du 'khol
NK078(tshu)001:17210: na / pa dang / rang bzhin gyi tshe dang
NK078(tshu)001:17211: dus la bsring bar 'dod na bsring bar nus la
NK078(tshu)001:17212: na / pa dang / / bstung bar 'dod na bstung bar nus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17213: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK078(tshu)001:17214: thams cad yungs 'abru gcig gi nang du shong ba
NK078(tshu)001:17215: dang / yungsa 'abru gcig gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po thams cad dang par nus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17216: ba spu nyag gcig gis stong gsum gang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17217: stong gsum pa spu'i bu gar bsdu ba'ang gong gi yungs 'bru'i tshul de bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17218: snod bcud srid pa thams cad bsreg par byed pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:17219: me'i bskal pa chen po yang gzhila bar nus pa
NK078(tshu)001:17220: dang / rang gi lus la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'bum dus gcig la 'gyed nus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17221: sa phyogs skam po'i sar chu dbyung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17222: bye ma la gser du 'byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17223: sol ba la ljon shing du 'byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17224: gnyis pa 'byung ba lnga stobs chen du bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17226: nam mkha' la rdo rje'i skas bsgoms pas rdo rje'i brag ltar sra ba'i skas 'byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17227: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bar bsgoms nas
NK078(tshu)001:17228: tha mal gyi me yang tshig par 'gyur ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:17229: / kham las ye shes kyi chu rgyun 'bab pa'ang
NK078(tshu)001:17230: dpe gong gi de bzhin du tha mal gyi chu
NK078(tshu)001:17232: yam las ye shes kyi rlung gis 'jig rten gyi khams 'a thor bar bsgoms pa gtor ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17233: e las thams cad stong par bsgoms pas 'jig rten
NK078(tshu)001:17234: gyi khams thams cad stong zhing steng nas 'og tu
NK078(tshu)001:17235: lhung ba dang / 'og nas steng du 'phen par bya ba 'grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:17236: gsum pa las kha tshar brgyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17238: ting nge 'dzin gyis dgra bgegas thams cad dgug pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17239: gling khams gzhan du btang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17240: dgra bgegs kyi kha bcing ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17241: gzhan gyis byad du bcug pa dgrol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17242: sri'u dang lo thog nad pa gso ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17244: gzhan gyi g.yul pham par bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17245: bdag gi g.yul rgyal bar byed pa la sogs pa rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:17246: rang gi ji ltar dmigs shing bsam pa bzhin du 'grub ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17247: de yang ting nge 'dzin las su rung bas so //
NK078(tshu)001:17248: bzhi pa gdug pa can dbang du bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17250: dang po dud 'gro gdug pa can dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17253: stag dang dom la sogs pa'i gcan gzan gdug pa can rnams kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:17254: khyi la zan byin pa bzhin du bdag gi phyi bzhina du rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:17255: gnyis pa bar chad gdug pa can dbang du bsdu ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17257: gzhan yang bar du gcod pa'i bdud gnod sbyin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17258: lha srin lus sems gdug pa can la sogs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17259: bdag la bar chad kyis tshugs par mi 'gyur gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:17260: slar bran g.yog bzhin du bdag gi bka' nyan pas
NK078(tshu)001:17261: phriin las ci bcol ba thams cad thogs pa med
NK078(tshu)001:17263: gnyis pa rjes su byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17265: lha mi'i lus 'di ma bor bar tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi sa ra gnas nas /
NK078(tshu)001:17266: de'i thugs rje sprul pa'i byin rlabsa kyi sprul sku'i rgyal tshab mdzad nas /
NK078(tshu)001:17267: lha klu la sogs 'gro ba so so'i skad dang
NK078(tshu)001:17268: mthun pa'i 'gro ba so sor thara bar byed pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:17271: ngan song gsum po'i gnas stong zhing mtho ris kyi dge ba'i las la bskul ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17272: gdul bya de nyid lam stegs kyi theg pa chung ngu nyan rang la dgod cinga /
NK078(tshu)001:17273: nyan rang de dag nyid theg pa chen po byang chub sems dpa'i lam la dgod cing /
NK078(tshu)001:17274: de nas gsang sngags kyi lam la bkod par mdzad do //
NK078(tshu)001:17275: so so'i skye bo rnams thar ba la bskul zhing
NK078(tshu)001:17276: nyan rang rnams zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i mtha' la
NK078(tshu)001:17277: zhen pa slong bar byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17278: rab dga' la sogs pa'i sa bcu'i byang chub sems
NK078(tshu)001:17279: dpa' rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i shes bya'i sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:17280: pa rnams rim par sbyong bar byed cing de ltar
NK078(tshu)001:17282: tshe dbang sa dang po dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17284: lhun grub sa bcu dang skal ba mnyam par bshad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17286: rgyu yi dang po skal mnyam pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17287: zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17288: bla ma gong ma rnams ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17289: tshe dbang gis chos nyid dbyer med kyi don mthong bas lta sgrib med la /
NK078(tshu)001:17290: sa bcu pas dbyer med ma mthong ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17291: lta sgrib yod pas sgrib pa sbyang du btub pa yin gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:17292: kho bo'i slob dpon thams cad mkhyen pas ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17293: tshe dbang thog nas cig char du 'gro ba'i 'phags
NK078(tshu)001:17294: pa la bsam yas lhun grub kyi dgongs pa mnga'
NK078(tshu)001:17296: sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin la sogs pa'i byang
NK078(tshu)001:17297: chub sems dpa' rnams kyis sgrib pa sbyongs pa'i dbang
NK078(tshu)001:17299: gzhan yang tshe dbang thod rgal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17300: rim gyis pas rang rang man chad kyi gdul bya'i
NK078(tshu)001:17301: sgrib pa sbyang ba'i dbang po mdzad ces gsungs so
NK078(tshu)001:17302: // bde bar gshegs pa longs sku dang sprul sku'i
NK078(tshu)001:17303: 'khor sa la gnas pa dang mos pas spyod pa
NK078(tshu)001:17304: rnams la'ang chos ston par madzada do //
NK078(tshu)001:17305: 'o na longs sprul gyi ston pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17306: tshe dbang gi ston pa gnyis su 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17307: gzhan don byed pa'i phyir du /
NK078(tshu)001:17308: bla chos dang zur chos kyi tshul du yin pas 'gal ba med de /
NK078(tshu)001:17309: sprul sku'i rgyal tshab kyi ston pa byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:17310: gsum pa chos snang ba'i don /
NK078(tshu)001:17312: stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya tshun chad kyang
NK078(tshu)001:17313: mngon shes kyi yul yin pas 'jig rten de rnams
NK078(tshu)001:17314: ni / phyogs cha drug tu g.yo ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17315: tshab che ba rab tu g.yo ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17316: kun tu khyab cing tshab che bas shin tu g.yo
NK078(tshu)001:17317: ba la sogs pa chos snang ba'i mdzad par snang
NK078(tshu)001:17318: bas / de'i yon tan ni zhing khams de na
NK078(tshu)001:17319: gnas pa'i sems can rnams mi rtag pa rgyud nas
NK078(tshu)001:17320: skye zhing lam la zhugs pa rnams kyis phyi ltar
NK078(tshu)001:17321: bas / sa g.yos pas / nang ltar ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams g.yos nas /
NK078(tshu)001:17322: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin pa'i rim pa gong nas gong du g.yo bar byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:17323: bzhi pa kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gyis gzhan don mdzad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17325: mthong lam tshe la dbang ba de nyid kyis gsang ba sngags kyi rang sgra bsgrags pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17326: sgra skad kun kyang yon tan rmad du byung ba gsang sngags kyi sgra ti ri ri bsgragsa pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17327: de'i yon tan ni phyi nang gi bdud bzhi po la sogs pa dang bgegs rnams 'dul zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:17328: sems can rnams kyi rgyud la ngan song gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17329: las dang nyon mongs pa yod pa rnams sbyangs la
NK078(tshu)001:17330: / 'gro ba drug gi sems can lhag ma ma
NK078(tshu)001:17331: lus pa'i don yang rang rang gi blo dang ji
NK078(tshu)001:17332: ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:17333: gnyis pa gzhan don mdzad nas 'bras bu la sbyor tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17335: zhi rgyas dbang drag la sogs pas bdag gzhan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17336: don sgrub pa'i phrin las rnam pa bzhi po thams
NK078(tshu)001:17338: mthar thug gi 'bras bu skye shi dang 'pho 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:17339: med pa'i g.yung drung chos kyi sku rgyud nas thob
NK078(tshu)001:17340: la / gdul bya'i ngor mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17341: dpe byada brgyad cu po kun gyis brgyan pa'i gzugs skur snang nas /
NK078(tshu)001:17342: lam mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu lam gyi rtsol ba bya ba gang yang med par pad+ma spyan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17343: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi mngon sum du 'grub bo //
NK078(tshu)001:17344: gsum pa rmad du byung ba'i spyod pas gdul bya 'dul bar bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17346: rgyas pa la sogs pa'i rgyud las gsungs pa'i mi spangs ba lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17347: dang du blang ba lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17348: spyad par bya ba lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17349: 'dod yon lnga ste lnga tshan bzhi'i spyod pa la
NK078(tshu)001:17350: bye brag bcu tshan gnyis te 'khor ba'i chos nyi
NK078(tshu)001:17352: phrin las zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi po rnams kyis gzhan don byed pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17353: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba tshe dbang thob pa'i skabs 'di nyid du thogsa pa med par 'byung bas /
NK078(tshu)001:17354: sngon cho 'phrul gyi skabs su bstan pa bzhin du
NK078(tshu)001:17355: stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya'i yul khyon de
NK078(tshu)001:17356: dag gi gdul bya ma lus pa 'dul bar byeda
NK078(tshu)001:17357: do // lnga pa mngon shes la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17359: dang po mngon shes 'byung ba'i rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17361: mig la sogs pa'i skye mched bcu gnyis po yang
NK078(tshu)001:17362: ngo bo rang byung gi ye shes rang yin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:17363: phyir na / skye mched bcu gnyis po de nyid cir yang 'char bas gcig gi mtha' dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17364: ngo bo rang byung gi ye shes las ma g.yos
NK078(tshu)001:17365: pas du ma'i mtha' gnyis su med par rang rig
NK078(tshu)001:17366: pa'i mngon sum du lta bas rtogs shing ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:17368: de bas na skye mched kyi yul dang dbang po gnyis rang rig gnyis med du mthong bas /
NK078(tshu)001:17369: tshogs drug gi yul shes tha dad du 'dzin pa'i dri ma drug sbyangs pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:17370: gnyis pa mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17372: gong du bstan pa'i stong gsum brgya'i yul de snyed tshun chad kyi gzugs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17376: dbang po lnga po re res kyang yul lnga lnga
NK078(tshu)001:17377: gcod pas mngon par shes pa'i bye brag nyi shu
NK078(tshu)001:17378: rtsa lngara shar bas de bas na dbang po sgo
NK078(tshu)001:17379: lnga gcig gis yul lnga lngar gcod par byed pas
NK078(tshu)001:17380: / dbang po lnga tshang ba dang ma tshang ba'i 'jigs pa'i dgos pa med do //
NK078(tshu)001:17381: gsum pa drug rdzogs par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17383: mngon shes nyer lnga po de las gzhan du ste
NK078(tshu)001:17384: lha'i rna ba'i mngon shes kyi stong gsum brgya tshun
NK078(tshu)001:17385: chad kyi sgra che chung nye ring med par thos
NK078(tshu)001:17386: pa dang / lha'i spyan gyis mngon par shes pas
NK078(tshu)001:17387: gzugs che chung rnams nye ring med par mthong ba
NK078(tshu)001:17388: pa dang / dang / rang gzhan gyi sngon tshe
NK078(tshu)001:17389: rabs mang po nas kyi gnas dang skye ba ci
NK078(tshu)001:17390: blang rjesa su dran pa'i mngon par shes pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:17391: pa dang / dang / / sems can pha rol
NK078(tshu)001:17392: po rnams kyi sems kyi rtog pa ci rgyu ba
NK078(tshu)001:17393: shes pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17394: 'gro ba gzhan 'di tsam nas 'chi 'pho ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:17395: skye ba gang du len pa'i bye brag rnams mkhyen
NK078(tshu)001:17396: pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17397: rdzu 'phrula gyis bya ba shes pa ste mi mthun pa brgyad la sogs pa ston pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:17398: gong gi spyod yul de rnams la 'dzin pa med
NK078(tshu)001:17399: pas na zag pa zad pa'i mngon par shes pa
NK078(tshu)001:17400: dang drug go // bzhi pa mngon shes kyis yul dang ming gi rnam grangs so //
NK078(tshu)001:17402: stong gsum brgya de snyed tshun chad kyi yul dang
NK078(tshu)001:17403: gdul bya'i bye brag rnams mngon sum du shes pas
NK078(tshu)001:17404: / gdul bya mongs pa tha dad pa gang dang
NK078(tshu)001:17405: gang yang rung ba rnams la 'dul thabs gang dang
NK078(tshu)001:17406: gang mtshams kyi sgo nas 'dul bar mdzad do //
NK078(tshu)001:17407: mngon shes de'i ming gi rnam grangs ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17408: 'khor bar mi ldog pa'i mngon shes zhes kyang bya /
NK078(tshu)001:17409: zag pa med pa'i mngon par shes pa zhes kyang bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17410: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin gyi mngon shes zhes kyang bya /
NK078(tshu)001:17411: de ltar mngon shes kyi mtshan gyi rnam grangs ni
NK078(tshu)001:17412: yon tan gyi cha las mngon shes kyi ming yang
NK078(tshu)001:17413: brjod pa ste / de nas tshe la dbang ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:17414: mngon shes zhes pa la sogs mtshan gyi rnam grangs
NK078(tshu)001:17415: brjod pa ste / la / mngon shes kyi ming grangs kyang brjod pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17416: brgyad pa lam gong ma la sbyor tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17420: bdag don gam gzhan don bya ba'i phyir tshe la rang dbang can gyi rig 'dzin des /
NK078(tshu)001:17421: rang don du sku tshe'i tshad lo stong drug brgya nyid dam /
NK078(tshu)001:17422: gzhan don du bskal pa grangs med ci snyed par
NK078(tshu)001:17423: 'jig rten du bzhugs pa'i mtha' la rang gi bsgrub
NK078(tshu)001:17424: pa'i 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17425: sngon zag bcas phyag rgya gcig spros kyi skabs su
NK078(tshu)001:17426: blo che chung yod pa bzhin du 'dir 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:17427: la sbyor ba la mthar chags rim gyis sbyor ba
NK078(tshu)001:17428: dang / thod rgal gcig char du sbyor lugs gnyis 'byung ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17429: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17431: dang po rim gyis bsgrod pa mthar chags pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17433: de yang mdor bstan gyi snga ma mthar chags rim gyis pas spyod tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17434: zag med mthong ba'i lam tshe dbang 'di nyid du /
NK078(tshu)001:17435: tshe dbang rang gi zag med kyi thos bsam sgom
NK078(tshu)001:17436: pa'i shes rab gsum la blo goms par byas pas
NK078(tshu)001:17437: / mthong spang sgrib pa dag pas tshe dbang rang
NK078(tshu)001:17438: gi rtsa ba'i lus skye 'chi med pa rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:17439: / lta bu des / rgyal ba'i sku phyag rgya chen por /
NK078(tshu)001:17440: sngon lam gyi dus nas yi dam zhi khro rigs lnga ganga bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17441: mngon sum du gsal bar gyur pa'i phyir lha'i sku'i
NK078(tshu)001:17442: cha lugs 'dzin pa phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:17443: thob ste der sgom lam de nyid yongs su gyur
NK078(tshu)001:17444: nas sgom spangs kyi sgrib pa dag ste mthar lam
NK078(tshu)001:17445: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob nas sangs rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:17448: kha cig rnam gsum bsgrod pa'i mthar //
NK078(tshu)001:17449: lhun grub rigs la rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:17451: gnyis pa gcig char du bgrod pa thod rgal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17453: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma thod rgal la cig char du sbyor ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17454: mthong lam gyi rigs mchoga lam sbyangs pa'i tshe dbang de nyid nas /
NK078(tshu)001:17455: sngon rim gyis pa'i skabs bzhin du rang gi thos
NK078(tshu)001:17456: bsam sgom pa'i shes rab gsum la goms par byas
NK078(tshu)001:17457: pas sgom lam phyag rgya chen po dor nas mthong
NK078(tshu)001:17458: sgom gyi spang bya rnams cig char du dag nas
NK078(tshu)001:17459: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin la 'gro ba yin
NK078(tshu)001:17460: te / de'i rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17461: rgyu lta bas chos nyid rtogs tshab che ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17462: rkyen dam tshig gtsang mar bsrung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17463: smon lam gyi nus mthu btsan pa yang yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17464: de ni gnas skabs kyi gcig char ba'am /
NK078(tshu)001:17466: 7 /gnyis pa sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17468: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17470: zag med kyi lam gsum po de nyid kyi bar
NK078(tshu)001:17471: ma sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin bshad
NK078(tshu)001:17472: par bya ba'ang / sngon gyi tshe dbang gi lus
NK078(tshu)001:17473: kyi mdor bstan bzhin du 'dir yang bzhi gnyis brgyad
NK078(tshu)001:17474: kyi lus rdzogs par bya ba ni 'di lta ste
NK078(tshu)001:17475: par bya ba'ang / / gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la brgyad de /
NK078(tshu)001:17477: dang po thob pa'i rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17479: tshogs lam phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor dang du ma sgom pa spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa yisa /
NK078(tshu)001:17480: rang gi 'byung bzhi 'dus pa'i lus kyang ngo bo
NK078(tshu)001:17481: sems nyid yin pas phyir rtog tshogs thams cad rang
NK078(tshu)001:17482: bzhin gyi lha'i dkyil 'khor du lta bas mngon sum
NK078(tshu)001:17484: ting nge 'dzin goms par byas shing spyod pa tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:17485: gnyis bsags pa'i mthar sbyor lam du tshom bu tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:17486: bsgrubs pas mthong lam du rnam smin tshe dbang gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:17487: thob nas / lta ba ched du 'dzin pa'i kun
NK078(tshu)001:17488: 'gro'i sgrib pa mthong lam pa'i rgyud la yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:17489: dag pa de nyid sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:17490: rig 'dzin gyi ngo bo'i rgyu yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17491: de yang rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin gyis phyag chen la sbyor tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17492: lus lha mi'i lus la sems phyag rgya chen por
NK078(tshu)001:17493: smin pas phyir lus dor nas phyag rgya chen por
NK078(tshu)001:17495: tshe dbang gis phyag chen la sbyor ba la de ltar du 'dod pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:17496: de ltar bskyed bya skyed byed kyis snga phyi'i rgyu 'bras su 'dod pa min te /
NK078(tshu)001:17497: lus sems gnyis ka phyag rgya chen por smin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17498: gnyis pa thob pa'i dus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17500: rgyu 'bras dus snga phyi rim gyis bsgrubs na thob
NK078(tshu)001:17501: par 'doda pa min te rgyu 'bras dbyer med ngo
NK078(tshu)001:17502: bo gcig tu 'dod pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:17503: rgyu 'bras dbyer med ngo bo gcig pa'i de nyid
NK078(tshu)001:17504: lam du byas pas tshe dbang thob nas lhag ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:17505: lus dang bcas pa lo brgya brgya nas gzhon nu
NK078(tshu)001:17506: lo brgyad pa lta bur bsnur zhing bsgrub pa'i mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:17507: ma la tshe dbang de phyag rgya chen po de
NK078(tshu)001:17508: nyid du gyur pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:17509: de'i thog nas lam gong ma la sbyor ba'i dus
NK078(tshu)001:17510: la nges pa tshad gcig tu bzung du med do
NK078(tshu)001:17511: // gsum pa ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17512: sems phyag rgya chen po longs sku'i ngo bor snang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17513: lus phyag rgya chen po longs sku'i cha byad du snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17516: dang po ngo bor snang ba dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17518: mthong lam pa rang nyid sems nyid lha'i sku phyag rgya chen pora gyur pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:17519: de'i don rtogs shing lam phyag rgya gcig pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:17520: spros pa gnyis su lha bsgoms pa'i mthar yi dam
NK078(tshu)001:17521: gyi lha zhi khro gang yin pa de nyid mangna
NK078(tshu)001:17522: sum du gyur pa'i sku la /
NK078(tshu)001:17523: thun mong dang mchog gi mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17524: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa longs sku'i rig 'dzin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17525: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang 'dra bas na longs
NK078(tshu)001:17526: sku gnyis pa lta bu sgom lam phyag rgya chen
NK078(tshu)001:17528: de yang tshe dbang phyag chen la sbyor ba'i dus na /
NK078(tshu)001:17530: dor na tshe dbang chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:17531: skye shi med pa rdo rje'i lus sam lhag bcas ma yin par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:17535: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas pa //
NK078(tshu)001:17538: phyag rgya chen po chos can /
NK078(tshu)001:17539: rdo rje'i lus yod par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:17540: rdo rje'i lus mi dor ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:17542: ye shes sku yi cha lugs can //
NK078(tshu)001:17543: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus las grol //
NK078(tshu)001:17544: zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal zhe na brtags te /
NK078(tshu)001:17545: ngo bo dor ram ma dor zer na dor la /
NK078(tshu)001:17546: rgyun dor ram ma dor zer na /
NK078(tshu)001:17548: de yang spyir grol tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17549: rgyun dor ba'i tshul gyis grol ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17550: ma dor ba'i tshul gyis grol ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17552: rnam smin nas phyag chen la sbyor ba'i tshe lus
NK078(tshu)001:17553: gsum dang bzhi spangs nas ye shes kyi skur 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:17555: tshe dbang nas phyag chen la sbyor ba'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:17556: rdo rje'i lus ma dor bar rgyun 'gyur ba'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:17557: gyi rdo rje'i lus nyid 'ja' lus ye shes kyi
NK078(tshu)001:17558: skur grol ba'o // 'o na grol du mi btub po zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17562: lcags gser gyi rtsi lta bu 'am /
NK078(tshu)001:17563: de yang mun snang dug rtsi'i tshul bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:17564: ci bzhin ma spang de nyid 'gyur /
NK078(tshu)001:17566: gnyis pa rigs lnga so so'i rig 'dzin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17568: de yang bye brag tu rdo rje rigs kyi phyag chen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17569: de bzhin du 'khor lo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17572: ral gri las kyi phyag rgya chen po ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17573: phyag mtshan lngas mtshon nas rigs lnga gang yin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17574: sku phyag rgya chen po'i rigs dang cha byad 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:17575: par gyur pas phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin no
NK078(tshu)001:17576: // gnyis pa longs sku'i cha byad du snang ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17578: dang po cha lugs snang ba dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17580: de yang rang gi lus nyid ye gdod ma nas lha'i sku'i phyag rgya chen por gnas pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17582: ting nge 'dzin gyis yang yang bsgoms pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17583: yi dam gyi lha rigs gang yin pa dbang pos mngon sum du gyur pa'i lha'i sku la /
NK078(tshu)001:17584: thun mong dang mchog gi mtshan dang dpe byad dang
NK078(tshu)001:17585: cho 'phrul bzhi dang mngon shes drug dang nyer lnga
NK078(tshu)001:17586: rdzogs pa ni / de ka la phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi mtshan dpe /
NK078(tshu)001:17587: cho 'phrul mngon shes zhes su grags so //
NK078(tshu)001:17588: gnyis pa ye shes sku'i cha lugs 'dzin cing tshe
NK078(tshu)001:17589: dbang las khyad par du gyur pas sku tshe'i tshad
NK078(tshu)001:17591: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku longs sku'i cha lugs can te /
NK078(tshu)001:17592: rnam smin ltar 'byung ba yi lus dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17593: tshe dbang ltar skye 'jig med pa 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus bgres rgud can las kyang grol la /
NK078(tshu)001:17594: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku thob pa de'i phyir phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la /
NK078(tshu)001:17595: sku tshe'i tshad bzung du med de /
NK078(tshu)001:17596: tshe dbang ltar lo brgya brgya dag tu bsnur zhing
NK078(tshu)001:17597: 'bras bu mngon du thob par bya ba'i rtsol ba
NK078(tshu)001:17598: dang bral nas tshe dbang las dpags pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17599: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17601: dang po phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi rnam grangs spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17603: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin de nyid kyi nang la kri ya rigs gsum gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17604: u pa ya rigs bzhi'i phyag rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17605: yo ga rigs lnga'i phyag rgya dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17606: ma h+aa yo ga mchog gi rigs lnga'i phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:17607: ste lnga'i phyag rgya ste lha de rnams kyi rigs
NK078(tshu)001:17608: dang cha byad 'dzin pas na phyag chen po'i rig
NK078(tshu)001:17609: 'dzin te / de la yang rnam grangs sam rigs rnam pa bzhi ru sngon tshe dbang la yang /
NK078(tshu)001:17610: ngo bo sman dang thabs rig 'dzin zhes sogs rnam
NK078(tshu)001:17611: grangs yod pa bzhin du 'dir yang bzang ngan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17613: gnyis pa khyad par ma h+aa'i phyag rgya chen po'i rnam grang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17615: de ltar phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi
NK078(tshu)001:17616: nad nas mchog tu gyur ba ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK078(tshu)001:17617: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin de dag gi ming
NK078(tshu)001:17618: gi rnam grangs ni gnyis pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17621: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las mi g.yo zhing gnas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17622: mi g.yo grub pa'i rnal 'byor zhes kyang bya /
NK078(tshu)001:17623: tshe la dbang ba sgyur ba'i skabs su lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:17624: la ched du 'dzin pa kun 'gro'i rtsol ba'i 'du
NK078(tshu)001:17625: byed dang bral bas mthong lam gyi 'du byed dang
NK078(tshu)001:17626: bral ba'i lam pa zhes kyang bya /
NK078(tshu)001:17627: mthong lam du zag pa med pa chos nyid rang
NK078(tshu)001:17628: mtshan mthong ba'i rgyun la gnas pa'i sgom pa'i lam
NK078(tshu)001:17630: dgongs pa chos nyid mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yo bas /
NK078(tshu)001:17631: mi g.yo ba grub pa'i rnal 'byor zhes kyang bya /
NK078(tshu)001:17632: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ba nyid
NK078(tshu)001:17633: du 'ang brjod de ming gi rnam grangs lnga pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:17634: // gnyis pa lung chen dngos su 'byung bas bdud dang cha dbye mi dgos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17636: de la rgyal bar 'gro bar lung ston pa'i sangs
NK078(tshu)001:17637: rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dngos su 'byung bas
NK078(tshu)001:17638: / lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17639: de la lung chen po la bdud dang cha dbye
NK078(tshu)001:17640: zhing brtag pa'i bye brag zag med kyi bsgom lam
NK078(tshu)001:17641: phyag chen po'i rig 'dzin 'di la'ang med de mi
NK078(tshu)001:17642: dgos so // lnga ba dgongs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17644: longs sku ye shes sgyu ma'i sku'i cha lugs su
NK078(tshu)001:17645: yod pa'i sgom lam gyi rnal 'byor pa phyag rgya
NK078(tshu)001:17647: sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi ganyis pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i shes rab lta ba'i spyan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17648: dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin yod kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:17649: de bas dman la phyag chen de mar tshe dbang
NK078(tshu)001:17650: dang gnyis lta dgongs kyi rgyud zag med rang mtshan
