NK078(tshu)001:17651: mthong bar mthun par snang mod kyang khyad yod de
NK078(tshu)001:17652: gang zhe na / tshe dbang ni dgongs pa mi ga yo ba thob pa tsam yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:17653: phyag chen ni dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid las mi
NK078(tshu)001:17654: g.yo ba la dbang thob cing ting nge 'dzin shin
NK078(tshu)001:17655: tu brtan pas rig pa klong du bab par gnas
NK078(tshu)001:17656: pa ste / nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:17657: grangs can gyi lha'i 'khor lo mngon sum gsal bar
NK078(tshu)001:17658: pa ste / snang ba'o // 'o na bsgom mi
NK078(tshu)001:17659: dgos pa sangs rgyas longs sku dang khyad med dam
NK078(tshu)001:17660: pa ste / snang ba'o // snyam pa las / 'on kyang da dung lam pa yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17661: sgom lam gyi rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par 'jog cing /
NK078(tshu)001:17662: mthar lam gyi bar du dgongs pa'i rtsal chen 'don
NK078(tshu)001:17663: pa'i don la mi yengs pa'i rtsol ba can yin
NK078(tshu)001:17664: pas na / sangs rgyas dang de ltar rtsol ba yod med kyi khyad par yod do //
NK078(tshu)001:17667: rang don du dgongs pa mnyam par bzhag pa'i ngang
NK078(tshu)001:17668: las ma g.yos bzhin du gzhan don du stong gsum
NK078(tshu)001:17669: gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams brgya gcig
NK078(tshu)001:17670: nas gnyis su bgrang ba'i stong phrag bcu'i 'jig rten
NK078(tshu)001:17671: gyi khams rnams rdul phran du bsil ba'i grangs de
NK078(tshu)001:17672: snyed dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rtena khams kyi rnams gdul
NK078(tshu)001:17673: bya dang / sangs rgyas sprul pa'i zhing khams de
NK078(tshu)001:17674: lta bu grangsa kyi gnas gzhan drug cu las 'das
NK078(tshu)001:17675: pas bgrang du med pa gcig gzhir bzhag nas bgrangs
NK078(tshu)001:17676: bya dang / pas / grangs med bargya gcig nas
NK078(tshu)001:17677: gnyis su bgrang ba'i stong phrag bcu'i 'jig rten gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17678: khams rnams rdul phra rab tu bsil ba'i grangs dang
NK078(tshu)001:17679: grangs de snyed kyi mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK078(tshu)001:17680: bya dang / pas / khams rnams su / rtsa
NK078(tshu)001:17681: ba'i lus las ma g.yos par rngon pa dang smad
NK078(tshu)001:17682: tshong ma la sogs pa rigs bzang ngan dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17683: mtho dman gyi bye brag sna tshogs par sprul pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:17684: lus gang la gang 'tshams kyis 'dul bar byed do
NK078(tshu)001:17685: // phrin las sam cho 'phrul bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17686: mngon shes drug la sogs pa'i sgo nas don byed pa'i yul gang du bstan pa de bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17690: dbang po sgo lnga'i mngon shes re re la yan
NK078(tshu)001:17691: lag lnga lnga ste nyer lnga dang bcas pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:17692: gyi mngon par shes pa'ang tshe dbang dang 'dra mod
NK078(tshu)001:17693: / 'o na tshe dbang phyag chen gnyis mngon shes khyad med dam zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17696: mngon shes drug la sogs pa kun /
NK078(tshu)001:17698: zhing grangs med pa la sogs de snyed du 'dul
NK078(tshu)001:17699: zhing gi yul la rgya che chung gi khyad yod
NK078(tshu)001:17700: pa dang / zag med kyi bsgom lam du mthong lam gyi don rdzogsa pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17701: gzhan don yongs su rdzogs par byed pa la nus mthu che chung gi khyad dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17702: tshe dbang rang phyag chen gyi gdul byara gyur pas
NK078(tshu)001:17703: gdul bya rgya che chung gi sgo nas kyang dpag
NK078(tshu)001:17704: pa'o // brgyad pa 'bras bu la sbyor tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:17706: phyag rgya chen po rang gi dgongs pa mi g.yo ba'i don lta bas mthong zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:17707: ting nge 'dzin gyis goms par byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17708: 'bras bu don du gnyer ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17709: lha'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha' khyab sogs man chad rim par bsgoms pa'i rtsol ba yis /
NK078(tshu)001:17710: sgom pa'i lam man chad kun rdzogs pa'i byin rlabs
NK078(tshu)001:17711: dang mthu stobs kyisa mi g.yo ba'i rnal 'byor bsgom
NK078(tshu)001:17712: lam gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsol ba dang bral
NK078(tshu)001:17713: nas mthar lam du lha bsam yas lhun gyis grub
NK078(tshu)001:17714: pa'i ting nge 'dzin la dbang thob pa'i dus su
NK078(tshu)001:17715: sgom lam la sngar yod pa'i mnyam gzhag gi thog
NK078(tshu)001:17716: tu lhan cig tu gnas pa'i tshe na /
NK078(tshu)001:17717: bsam yas lhun grub kyi don mi gsal ba ni dri ma'am sgrib pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:17718: de ltar sngar bsgom pa la ched du 'dzin pa'i lhan gcig gnas pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK078(tshu)001:17719: de nas ched du gzhan nas btsal ba med par lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa'o /
NK078(tshu)001:17720: 7 /gsum pa lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17722: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17724: thod rgal ba mthong lam tshe dbang de dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17725: mthar chags pa sgom lam phyag rgya chen po des mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu /
NK078(tshu)001:17726: rtsa ba'i lus la sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i cha byad dam rig 'dzin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17727: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17728: rang rgyud la lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma cha phra ba dag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17729: ye shes rtsal rdzogs pas rang rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17730: de la yang sngon tshe dbang gi skabs su bstan
NK078(tshu)001:17731: pa bzhin du 'di la yang bzhi gnyis brgyad kyi
NK078(tshu)001:17732: lus rnam bzhag dgod par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17733: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa de la brgyad de /
NK078(tshu)001:17735: dang po thob pa'i rgyu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17737: lam snga ma phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la
NK078(tshu)001:17738: lta sgom nus pa'i mthu rdzogs pas gong du bshad
NK078(tshu)001:17739: pa bzhin du lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag
NK078(tshu)001:17740: nas / sangs rgyas longs sku'i cha byad can gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17741: gnyis pa phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi thog
NK078(tshu)001:17742: nas thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab gsum gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:17743: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dngos su 'byung ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17746: de yang phyag chen gyi lta spyod sgom gsum mthar phyin nas /
NK078(tshu)001:17747: lhun grub rig 'dzin thob pa'i gnas skabs der sngon
NK078(tshu)001:17748: phyag chen thob pa'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin du
NK078(tshu)001:17749: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab gsum rdzogs par byed
NK078(tshu)001:17750: lugs ni / rgyal ba longs spyod rdzogs pa chen po'i sku rgyal ba drug pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:17751: mthar thug gi gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa' lung
NK078(tshu)001:17752: yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug /yum gyi dga' ba
NK078(tshu)001:17753: bcu drug /yab yum gyi dga' ba bcu drug re
NK078(tshu)001:17754: re la yang ye shes lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan
NK078(tshu)001:17755: pa thos shing bsam pa rtogs shing sgom pas rang
NK078(tshu)001:17756: gi dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin dang rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK078(tshu)001:17757: spyod pa'i nus pa mthu can du gyur nas yi
NK078(tshu)001:17758: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa mthar dbyung ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:17759: dus la bab te sangs rgyas so //
NK078(tshu)001:17760: de'i tshad la bzung du med do //
NK078(tshu)001:17761: gsum pa ngo bo la gsum te /
NK078(tshu)001:17763: dang po sku lnga lhun grub kyi rigs 'dzin cing sgrib pa sbyang tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17765: de ltar kun 'gro dang lhan cig gnas pa'i rang
NK078(tshu)001:17766: rgyud kyi dri ma dag pa'i shes pa de nyid
NK078(tshu)001:17767: / sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rigs mi gtong
NK078(tshu)001:17768: zhing 'dzin pas rdo rje 'dzina pa zhes bya ste
NK078(tshu)001:17769: / / dgongs pa lhun grub mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:17770: ngang las mi g.yo zhing chos nyid rnam par mi
NK078(tshu)001:17771: rtog pa nyid du mnyam par bzhag nas bzhugs pa
NK078(tshu)001:17772: / / ste / de'ang 'di'i don ni lhun grub
NK078(tshu)001:17773: de lam la slob pa'i rtsol ba ni med kyi
NK078(tshu)001:17775: rtog pa'i ye shes ngang gis 'byung ba'i mthar skad
NK078(tshu)001:17776: cig gis bag la nyal ba bcom ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17778: ye shes brgyad cu la yun se gol gdab tsam
NK078(tshu)001:17779: du sgrib pa'i nyon mongs bag la nyal ba ste
NK078(tshu)001:17781: nyin par skar ma lta bu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17782: de rdo rje'i lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'joms par byed cing /
NK078(tshu)001:17783: sangs rgyas pa la dus mtha' skad cig ma tsam
NK078(tshu)001:17784: la rag las nas sangs rgyas pa yin pas na
NK078(tshu)001:17785: rig 'dzin de ni lam pa rnams kyis mtha' ma
NK078(tshu)001:17786: yin pa'o // gnyis pa cha lugs dang rgyal tshab kyi nges tshig dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17788: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin de'i sku'i cha byad
NK078(tshu)001:17789: lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa kun bzang
NK078(tshu)001:17790: rdo rje 'chang chen nyid kyi cha byad du gnas
NK078(tshu)001:17791: pa ste / rigs sam sku lnga po gcig la dbyer med du lhun gyisa grub pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:17792: rgyal ba drug pa'i sku de nyid dang 'dra bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:17793: drug pa de nyid kyi rgyal tshab kyi skyes bu
NK078(tshu)001:17794: byas nas 'khor gdul bya rnams la chos kyang ston
NK078(tshu)001:17795: pa'o // sku lnga lhun grub kyi bdag nyid rgyal ba drug pa de'i rgyud mi gtong bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:17796: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi ming don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17797: nges tshig rnams grub pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17798: gsum pa ngo bo'i mdzad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17800: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin nyid kyi rtsa ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:17801: lus de la skyes shi dang 'pho 'gyur mi mda'
NK078(tshu)001:17802: ba'i phyir / skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i sku
NK078(tshu)001:17803: yin pas de ltar na yang gzhan don du gdul
NK078(tshu)001:17804: bya'i ngo la nyid kyi sprul pa'i lus rnams ni
NK078(tshu)001:17805: mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul ston par byed de
NK078(tshu)001:17806: ba'i phyir / / dper na rgyal bu don 'grub
NK078(tshu)001:17807: kyis mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas don mdzad
NK078(tshu)001:17808: pa la sogs pa'i tshul ji lta bar lhun grub
NK078(tshu)001:17810: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17814: bya ba'i rgyud kri ya'i lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17815: rnal 'byor yo ga'i rgyud kyi lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzina dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17816: rnal 'byor chen po gsang sngags nang pa ma h+aa yo ga'i lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17817: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17819: dang po sngags phyi ma'i rnam grangs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17820: dkyus kyi snga ma sngags phyi pa la kri ya'i rigs gsum lhun grub dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17821: yo ga'i sems dpa' dang po'am /
NK078(tshu)001:17822: rigs bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17823: kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyi cha lugs 'dzin cing /
NK078(tshu)001:17824: rang rang gis ston pa de gnyis kyi rgyal tshab dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17825: de gnyis kyi sdud pa po yang byed do //
NK078(tshu)001:17826: gnyis pa ma h+aa'i lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi rnam grangs so //
NK078(tshu)001:17828: de ltar grangs gsum gyi tha ma ma h+aa'i lhun grub kyi ming gi rnam grangs la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17829: lam zad sar skyol bas mthar phyin pa'i lam pa zhes kyang bya /
NK078(tshu)001:17830: rang gi rgyud la sgrib pa mngon gyur med pas rgyud dag pa'i sangsa rgyas zhes bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17831: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ba de nyid dang ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17832: mthar lam dngos su sbyor bas sbyor ba'i lam zhes kyang bya /
NK078(tshu)001:17833: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas drug po rdo
NK078(tshu)001:17834: rje 'chang kun tu bzang po'i rgyal tshab byed pas
NK078(tshu)001:17835: na / rgyal tshab skyes bu zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17836: lnga pa dgongs pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17838: dang po dgongs pa dang mkhyen pa sangs rgyas dang mnyam la shes sgrib phra mos phye ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17840: chos thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor gdul bya'i blos bsam
NK078(tshu)001:17841: yas lhun gyis rdzogs shing grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:17842: gsal ba'i phyir / shes bya'i chos ji lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:17843: dang ji snyed pa thams cad lta ba mnyam bzhag
NK078(tshu)001:17844: la mkhyen pa'i ye shes sangs rgyas kyi spyan mchog
NK078(tshu)001:17845: gsal ba'i phyir / 'chang bas / bcu gsum yi
NK078(tshu)001:17846: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa yang rnal 'byor
NK078(tshu)001:17847: gyis mngon sum du gzigs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17848: de ni dgongs pa chos nyid mi g.yo ba'i don
NK078(tshu)001:17849: la blos gang du yang mi rtog par bsgom dgos
NK078(tshu)001:17850: pas na / mnyam rjes kyi cha phra ba yod
NK078(tshu)001:17851: bas da rung mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang mi rgya
NK078(tshu)001:17852: pas na / ste / dus nam gyis tshe rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:17853: na dus mtha'i skad cig ma gcig la rdo rje
NK078(tshu)001:17854: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin nyid kyis bag la nyal
NK078(tshu)001:17855: gyi sgrib pa bcom nas sangs rgyas kyi sa la
NK078(tshu)001:17856: pas na / ste / gshegs pa'o // 'o na da rung sangs mi rgyas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17857: skad cig nyid kyis gshegs ces pa 'di gnyis 'gal te /
NK078(tshu)001:17858: snga ma ltar na sangs rgyas pa la da rung cung zhig 'thog par 'dug la /
NK078(tshu)001:17859: phyi ma ltar na tshegs med de skad cig gcig gis sangs rgyas pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:17862: lhun grub thob pa mgo zug nas cung zhig thog pas na sgra drang 'thad yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:17863: phyi ma ni mthar lam rdzogs nas sangs rgyas la
NK078(tshu)001:17864: sbyor ba'i tshe thung tshad bzung ba yin pas mi
NK078(tshu)001:17865: 'gal lo // gnyis dgongs pa'i ming gi rnam grangs bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17867: 'di la brtsegs sdeb kyis 'chad par byed pas /
NK078(tshu)001:17868: de yang lta ba dang dgongs pa sngar bstan pa
NK078(tshu)001:17869: ltar yin la des na mthar lam lhun grub rig
NK078(tshu)001:17870: 'dzin gyi dgongs pa rgya matsho lta bur zab cing
NK078(tshu)001:17871: rlabs che ba kun thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:17872: kyi rtsal rdzogs pa zhes bya ba'i dgongs pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:17873: / mthar phyin pa'i lam gyi dgongs pa zhes bya
NK078(tshu)001:17874: ba la sogs dgongs pa'i ming gi rnam grangs dang
NK078(tshu)001:17875: / / spyod pa rgya tsho ltar zab cing rlabs
NK078(tshu)001:17876: che ba thams cad kun lam snga ma'i rtsol bas
NK078(tshu)001:17877: bya ba med pa'i spyod pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:17878: bya byed kyi rtsol ba dang bral bas bya bral
NK078(tshu)001:17879: lhun grub kyi spyod pa zhes bya ba la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:17880: pa spyod pa'i ming gi rnam grangsa de dag kun
NK078(tshu)001:17881: / lta spyod kyi yon tan gyi cha la brjod par zad kyis don la tha dad med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17882: drug pa spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:17884: dang po bdag don du sgrib pa bcom nas sangs rgyas tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17886: mthar lam bdag nyid kyi don bya ba'i phyir sku
NK078(tshu)001:17887: lnga lhun grub drug pa rdo rje 'dzin pa chen
NK078(tshu)001:17888: po yang dag par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa la
NK078(tshu)001:17889: / lam gyi spang rtogs kyi bya ba mthar phyin
NK078(tshu)001:17890: pa'i dus kyi mtha' skad cig gi ltos skyes te
NK078(tshu)001:17892: skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:17894: de'i skad cig ma'i dus kyi thag lta bas bcad
NK078(tshu)001:17895: pa la sogs pa bslaba pa'i mtha' bcu yongs su
NK078(tshu)001:17897: lam mthar phyin pa'i tha ma lhun grub rig 'dzina
NK078(tshu)001:17898: gyi rgyud la yod pa'i bag la nyal gyi sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:17899: pa cha phra ba de dag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17900: mnyam par bzhag ma bzhag las 'das te bcom ldan
NK078(tshu)001:17901: 'das kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas par 'gyur pa
NK078(tshu)001:17902: yin no // de yang bslab pa'i mtha' bcu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17904: dam tshig gzhi dang rgyud grol dang //
NK078(tshu)001:17905: sgo bsdur ba dang phul dbyung dang //
NK078(tshu)001:17906: thag bcad pa dang nyams blangs dang //
NK078(tshu)001:17907: la dor spyod dang dbang rim dang //
NK078(tshu)001:17908: man ngag don dang mdor bsdus ni //
NK078(tshu)001:17909: rnal 'byor bslab pa'i mtha' bcur bshad //
NK078(tshu)001:17911: dang po gzhi dam tshig gis bzung ba sa gzhi
NK078(tshu)001:17912: gshin po lta bur bslab pa dang gcig /rgyud thos
NK078(tshu)001:17913: pas grol ba gyi ling cang shes sgrog bkrol ba
NK078(tshu)001:17915: sgo kun nas bsdur ba bung bas rtsi tshol ba ltar bslab pa dang gsum /
NK078(tshu)001:17916: phul mkhas pas dbyung ba ri bo mthon po'i rtser phyin pa lta bur bslab pa dang bzhi /
NK078(tshu)001:17917: go 'phang dbang gis bsgrod pa rgyal rigs rgyal sar
NK078(tshu)001:17918: byung ba lta bur bslab pa dang lnga la sbyod
NK078(tshu)001:17919: pas dor ba glang po che chur 'jug pa ltar
NK078(tshu)001:17920: bslab pa dang drug /thag lta bas bcad pa khyung
NK078(tshu)001:17921: nam mkha' la lding ba ltar bslab pa dang bdun
NK078(tshu)001:17922: / nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba rgya
NK078(tshu)001:17923: mtsho'i gling nas nor bu len pa ltar bslab pa
NK078(tshu)001:17924: / dang brgyad / don man ngag gis bsgrub pa gser 'gyur gyi rtsi'am /
NK078(tshu)001:17925: sman ma ki ta ltar bslab pa dang dgu /
NK078(tshu)001:17926: mdo gcig tu bsdu ba so nams mkhan gyis lo thog bsdu ba ltar bslab pa dang bcu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17927: 'o na zag bcas su bslab pa'i mtha' bcu la
NK078(tshu)001:17928: bslab par bshad pa dang khyad med du thal zhe
NK078(tshu)001:17931: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu sgra gcig la //
NK078(tshu)001:17932: zag bcas bzhi dang bar chad med //
NK078(tshu)001:17933: zag med lnga yi bslab pa dag /slob pa'i lugs dang lob pa dang //
NK078(tshu)001:17934: nus dang ngo bo khyad par dang //
NK078(tshu)001:17935: bslab bya yul gyis khyad par 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:17938: dang po slob lugs kyi khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17939: zag bcas su tshig dang yi ge la brten nas slob la /
NK078(tshu)001:17940: bar chad med pas tshig dang yi ge 'am rig pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:17941: ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas slob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17942: zag med kyi chos nyid mngon sum ma rtogs pa la bslab pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17943: gnyis pa lob pa'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17944: zag bcas kyi skabs su chos nyid kyi don rgya mtshor gzugs brnyan ltar lob pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:17945: bar chad med pas rnal 'byor mngon sum du lob ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17946: zag med kyis rang rig mngon sum du lob pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17947: gsum pa nus pa'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17948: zag bcas kyis las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa
NK078(tshu)001:17949: rags pa dag cing gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu thob
NK078(tshu)001:17950: la / bar chad med pas las dang nyon mongs
NK078(tshu)001:17951: pa'i sgrib pa 'bring dag ste mthong lam la sbyor
NK078(tshu)001:17952: la / ro // zag med kyis shes bya'i sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:17953: pa phra ba dag ste sangs rgyas la sbyor ro
NK078(tshu)001:17954: la / ro // // bzhi ba ngo bo'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17955: zag bcas kyi bzhi ni zag ldog dang bcas pa'i lam pa'i bslab pa yin /
NK078(tshu)001:17956: bar chad med pas zag pa yod la ldog pa med pa'i lam pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:17957: tshe dbang yan chad la zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam pa'i bslab pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17958: lnga pa bslab pa yul gyi khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:17959: zag bcas ni gang zag chos kyi mig can nam /
NK078(tshu)001:17960: lta dgongs kyi drod can la slob la /
NK078(tshu)001:17961: bar chad med pa ni rig 'dzin la slob ste /
NK078(tshu)001:17962: zag med ni rang gi rigs mthun dang sangs rgyas sku gsum la rim par slob bo //
NK078(tshu)001:17963: des na 'dis mthar lam la bslab pa'i mtha' bcu rdzogs nas sangs rgyas la sbyor ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:17964: gnyis pa gzhan don thugs rje'i mdzad pa la gsum te /
NK078(tshu)001:17965: sku'i mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17966: thugs kyi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17967: gsung gi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:17970: dang po sku'i mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17972: bdag don lhun grub thob pa de'i tshe de la
NK078(tshu)001:17973: bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa cha phra mo tsam
NK078(tshu)001:17974: yod kyang lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi sar
NK078(tshu)001:17975: zhugs nas gzhan don du sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:17976: zhing khams kyi grangs kyi mtha' thug pa med pa
NK078(tshu)001:17977: de dag gi gdul bya rnams 'dul ba'i phyir sangs
NK078(tshu)001:17978: rgyas sprul pa'i sku'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis ltar du'ang
NK078(tshu)001:17980: don bya ba'i yul srid pa khams gsum gyi 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:17981: ba rigs drug gi 'jig rten bsam yas rnams su
NK078(tshu)001:17982: / lhun grub rig 'dzin de'i thugs rjes 'dul byed
NK078(tshu)001:17983: kyi ston pa sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK078(tshu)001:17984: / snang nas / gdul bya lugs 'byung la bsam
NK078(tshu)001:17985: pa'i don dang mthun pa'i mdzad pa 'ba' zhig ston
NK078(tshu)001:17986: / snang nas / la / gdul bya lugs bzlog
NK078(tshu)001:17987: la drag po'i sgo nas mi mthun pa'i 'dul thabs
NK078(tshu)001:17988: kyang ston cing thugs rjes zhags pas 'khor ba'i las
NK078(tshu)001:17990: gnyis pa mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyis don mdzad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:17992: dus dang gnas skabs la lar dga' ldan la sogs gnas nas 'pho ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17993: yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17996: la lara mchod rten rnam dag gi drung sogs su nyid las nyid rab tu byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17997: chu bo nee ran+dza na ra sogs dka' thub lo drug sogs mdzad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17998: la lara btsun mo brgyad khri bzhi stong sogs khab tu bzhes pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:17999: rgyal srid lo nyi shu rtsa dgu sogs skyong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18000: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18002: cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18004: gdul bya la chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor ba ston pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18005: grong khyer rtsa mchog sogs su mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18006: sku gdung cha brgyad du bgos pa la sogs pa ston pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18007: gnyis pa thugs kyi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18009: gnas skabs res 'ga' zhi bas 'dul ba la zhi bar ston pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18010: res 'ga' drag pos 'dul ba la drag po khro bo la sogs su snang nas 'dul ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18011: gdul bya g.yem pa 'dod chags can la g.yem par ston pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18012: zhe sdang can la zhe sdang can la zhe sdang gi tshul du ston pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18013: rig pa ste nga rgyal can rnams la nga rgyal ri bo lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18014: mun pa ste gti mug can la gti mug mun pa ltar 'thib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18015: phrag dog rlung ltar 'tshubs pa la 'dul thabs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18016: gnyen po'ang de bzhin du bstan nas gdul bya dang
NK078(tshu)001:18018: gdul bya dang mi mthun pa'i gnyen po'i sgo nas kyang 'dul ba'i thabs sna tshogs mdzad do //
NK078(tshu)001:18019: rgya mtsho lta bur thabs zab cing rgya che ba'i spyod pa rlabs po che dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18020: mdzad pa'i phrin las gong du bstan pa de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:18021: du mthun pa dang mi mthun pa sna tshogs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18022: sgo nas 'gro ba 'khor ba las sgrol par 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:18023: ro // gsum pa gsung gi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:18025: lha gnas gsum du sngar gsungs pa'i gsang sngags rdo
NK078(tshu)001:18026: rje theg pa'i tan+t+ra ste rgyud 'chad pa'i ston pa
NK078(tshu)001:18028: de bzhin du rgyud kyi don rnams kyi bsdu ba po'ang mdzad pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18029: dman pa'i lus ngan song gsum dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18030: bsod nams dang ldan pa lha mi khyad par can gyi gnas su /
NK078(tshu)001:18031: lha klu la sogs rang rang dang mthun pa sna
NK078(tshu)001:18032: tshogs pa'i lus can dam pa'i rigs can lnga la
NK078(tshu)001:18034: gsang sngags kyi 'khor lo bskor ba 'ang mdzad do //
NK078(tshu)001:18037: mngona shes drug dang ldan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18038: mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18039: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu rnams 'go ma phyag
NK078(tshu)001:18040: rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin man chad rnams las 'dir
NK078(tshu)001:18042: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po rgyal ba drug pa kun tu bzang po'i cha byad 'dzin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18043: kun mkhyen gyi ye shes mnga' ba rgyal ba drug pa nyid dang mtshungs pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:18044: mngon shes kyis yul khyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18045: gdul bya grangs tshad bzung du med de /
NK078(tshu)001:18046: rgyal ba drug pa nyid dang gcig go //
NK078(tshu)001:18047: de yang ji ltar na gsal la rtogs pa med
NK078(tshu)001:18048: par mkhyen pas na me long lta bu'i tshul du
NK078(tshu)001:18049: rgyal ba drug pa la mnga' ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:18050: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:18051: brgyad pa 'bras bu sangs rgyas la sbyor tshul la gsum te /
NK078(tshu)001:18053: dang po rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK078(tshu)001:18054: shes bya'i sgrib pa dang bdud bcom nas sangs rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:18057: rang rgyud la spang bya mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18058: mtshan ma shes sgrib bag la nyal cha phra ba
NK078(tshu)001:18059: de gzhom pa'i phyir gnyen por gyur pa 'bigs shing
NK078(tshu)001:18060: 'jam dpal rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK078(tshu)001:18061: / spang byar gyur pa shes bya la bdag tu
NK078(tshu)001:18062: rtog pa'i sgrib pa'am nyon mongs sam mtshan ma cha
NK078(tshu)001:18063: phra ba bag la nyal ba zhig yod pa de
NK078(tshu)001:18064: kun rtsa ba nas bcom nas mthar rdo rje lta
NK078(tshu)001:18065: bu'i ting nge 'dzin nyid kyang chos nyid mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:18066: nyid kyi dbyings su thim par byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:18067: bsgom bya sgom byed las 'das so //
NK078(tshu)001:18069: yang na mthar gnyen po rdo rje'i lta ba'i ting
NK078(tshu)001:18070: nge 'dzin nyid kyis 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18071: dbyings su thim par byed de gnyin po dang bral
NK078(tshu)001:18072: bas bsgom bya sgom byed las 'das so //
NK078(tshu)001:18073: 'o na 'dir mthar lam du bdag rtog mtshan ma bcom bya yod pa mi 'thad de /
NK078(tshu)001:18074: rang gi tshogs sbyor gyi skabs nas bdag med par
NK078(tshu)001:18075: rtogs par bshad pa dang khyad med du thal zhe
NK078(tshu)001:18076: na / khyad par yod de tshogs sbyor gyi skabs
NK078(tshu)001:18077: su rags pa dag /mthong sgom gyi skabs su 'bring
NK078(tshu)001:18078: na / po dang / 'dir shin tu cha phra ba de bcom par byed de /
NK078(tshu)001:18079: mdor na spyi'i spang bya thams cad kyi rtsa ba cha phra ba bag la nyal 'joms pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18080: de bas bdag tu 'dzin pa med par rtogs pa dang rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK078(tshu)001:18081: dngos po snang ba dang dngos med stong par 'dzin pa'i bag chags thams cad bsreg te /
NK078(tshu)001:18082: phyi'i yul la rang gi mtshan nyid dang spyi'i mtshan nyid kyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18083: nang gi semsa kyi cha phra ba'i rtog pa bag la nyal ba thams cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:18084: phyogs res dngosa po med par rang byung gi ye
NK078(tshu)001:18085: shes 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du rtogs par byas
NK078(tshu)001:18086: pasa / sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la phyogs zhen thams cad 'joms pa'i dpa' bo yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:18087: de'i sar 'gro bar byed pa na dpa' bar 'gro ba' rnal 'byor dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18088: mi 'thun pa'i phyogs 'joms pas na rdo rje ste
NK078(tshu)001:18089: gnyis med kyi ye shes mthar thug pas gong na
NK078(tshu)001:18090: gzhan med pas rtse mo mchog gi ting nge 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:18091: thob pas / theg 'og gi 'bras bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18092: 'di'i lam pa man chad kyi yid tshod du gyur pa med pas zhen pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18093: bdud bzhi'i sde dang bcas pa rnams tshar bcad cing gtan nas 'joms pa'i dpa' bo yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:18094: bdud bzhi bcom pa de'i rjes la 'bras bu 'grub pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:18095: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad pa
NK078(tshu)001:18096: rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i man+dala ste yi ge 'khor lo
NK078(tshu)001:18097: tshogs chen gyi sa'i dgongs pa bsam yasa lhun rdzogsa
NK078(tshu)001:18098: shes bya ma lus pa kun yul med rang gsal
NK078(tshu)001:18099: mkhyen pa lta ba'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog go
NK078(tshu)001:18100: // gnyis pa de'ang 'bras bu gzhan na med de
NK078(tshu)001:18101: rang la gnas pa mngon du gyur tshul de la
NK078(tshu)001:18103: dang po 'bras bu rang la byung ba mngon sum du snang ba'i rkyen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18105: de'ang 'bras bu rang snang ba'i rkyen la lhun grub
NK078(tshu)001:18106: rig 'dzin gyi ye shes kun mkhyen gyi lta ba
NK078(tshu)001:18108: de mnyam par bzhag nas ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin
NK078(tshu)001:18109: pa'i mthus phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams kyi ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:18111: phyag rgya mo la brten nas dbang bsgyur ba'i mthu dang zhing ni 'brel mtshams sbyor ba yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:18112: 'bras bu don du gnyer pa'i smon lam rnam par dag pa'i mthu bzhi la brten nas sam /
NK078(tshu)001:18113: yang na lhun gyis grub pa'i mnyam bzhag ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:18114: kyi ngang la rig pa rang dbang bsgyur zhing 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:18115: bu don du gnyer ba'i smon lam gyi mthus rkyen
NK078(tshu)001:18116: byas nas / gnyis pa 'bras bu rang la byung
NK078(tshu)001:18117: ba mngon du snang ba dngos de la gnyis te
NK078(tshu)001:18119: dang po spyir bsdus te bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18121: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las re
NK078(tshu)001:18122: re la'ang lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lnga lam
NK078(tshu)001:18123: pa'i rig pa la rang snang du thob pas /
NK078(tshu)001:18124: gzhan gcig las yod pa gcig 'dir 'ong nas thob pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18125: gnyis pa bye brag rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18127: dang po 'bras bu rang gnas mngon du gyur pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18129: yon tan thams cad kyi rten byed pas sku lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18130: brda' sprod pa'i gsung lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18131: dgongs pa zag pa'i thugs lnga dang dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i yon tan lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18132: don mdzad pa'i phrin las lnga la sogs pa gzhan la ngo mtshar zhing rmad du byung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18133: 'bras bu'i chos kun tu grags pa ni gsal ba ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18134: de dag rang rig par lhun gyis grub pa la
NK078(tshu)001:18135: gzhan nas yod pa zhig 'dir bkug nas 'ong ba
NK078(tshu)001:18137: sems nyid rgyu rkyen dang bral bas rang byung gi
NK078(tshu)001:18138: ye shes de nyid gnas bya'i yul dang gnas byed
NK078(tshu)001:18139: kyi shes pa / yul yul can gyi mtha' gang
NK078(tshu)001:18140: du yang gnas pa med pa mngon du gyur pa
NK078(tshu)001:18141: 'bras bu chos kun tu snang ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18142: gnyis pa de gzhan nas 'ong ba ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:18143: lam gyis rang gnas mngon du byas par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18145: 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rang snang ba de bas
NK078(tshu)001:18146: na ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba skye ba med
NK078(tshu)001:18147: pa las skye ba'i cho 'phrul du shar ba 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:18148: bu'i chos nyer lnga po thams cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:18149: sems nyid ye nas yin pa las ma gtogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:18150: gzhan nas yod pa zhig 'dir bkug nas gsar du
NK078(tshu)001:18151: thob pa ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:18152: thabs snang la ma 'gag pa bde ba'i ye shes
NK078(tshu)001:18153: la blo brtan pa'i shes rab rang bzhin med pa
NK078(tshu)001:18154: dang dbyer med pa nyid du shar ba'i 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:18155: sku dang ye shes sna tshogs snang ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18156: gong gi 'bras bu'i chos nyer lnga po de lta bu'i nganga du rang snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18158: rang bzhin gnas phyir gzhan nas 'ong ba med //
NK078(tshu)001:18159: zhen pa log pas bdag zhal bdag gis mthong //
NK078(tshu)001:18161: gsum pa 'khor ma spang rang sar grol nas sangs rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18163: de yang dper na mun pa las snang bar 'gyur
NK078(tshu)001:18164: ba'am sbrul dug de nyid rtsi ma ki ta sman
NK078(tshu)001:18165: du 'gyur ba ji bzhin du rtog tshogs ma spangs
NK078(tshu)001:18166: par de nyid sku dang ye shes su 'gyur bas
NK078(tshu)001:18167: / des na khams gsum 'khor ba'i zhen snang 'di
NK078(tshu)001:18168: ma spang bar 'bras bu myang 'das su rnam par
NK078(tshu)001:18169: / daga pas / gsar du mya ngan las mi
NK078(tshu)001:18170: 'da' ste ye gdod ma nas 'bras bu 'das pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18171: sangs rgyas kyi ngo bor gnas pa yin pa la
NK078(tshu)001:18172: / daga pas / / de bas na 'khor ba
NK078(tshu)001:18173: nas 'das pa'i sar 'gro ba dang sa de la
NK078(tshu)001:18174: gansa par bya ba'i rtog pa yod pa min te
NK078(tshu)001:18175: / daga pas / / / rtog pa thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:18176: rang bzhin dbyer med sku dang ye shes kyi tshogs
NK078(tshu)001:18178: gsum 'bras bu thob pa'i tshe rig 'dzin gyi tha
NK078(tshu)001:18179: snyad dang bral bar bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18181: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi mnyam bzhag la dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18182: ma bzhag na mi mnyam pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18183: sangs rgyas ni mnyam par bzhag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18184: ma bzhag pa med par mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18185: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyis mnyam bzhag la gzhan don
NK078(tshu)001:18186: gyi bya ba lhun gyis grub pa dang ma bzhag
NK078(tshu)001:18187: na gzhan don mi bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18188: sangs rgyas kyis mnyam rjes kyi bya ba med par gzhan don lhun grub du byas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18189: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi mnyam bzhag la 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18190: rjes shes lam grub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18191: sangs rgyas kyi mnyam rjes med par 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18192: rgyu mtshan gsum po de'i phyir na 'bras bu sangs
NK078(tshu)001:18193: rgyas thob pa'i tshe na rig 'dzina gyi tha snyad
NK078(tshu)001:18195: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18197: lam la mtshan nyid gsum yod pa las mthar phyin
NK078(tshu)001:18198: pa'i lam gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid rig
NK078(tshu)001:18199: 'dzin rnams kyi don ma nor bar bstan pa'i gzhung
NK078(tshu)001:18200: gi tshig don rnams mtshams gcod cing 'dzin pas na
NK078(tshu)001:18201: le'u ste / yas bgrang brgyad pa'i don du gada'o
NK078(tshu)001:18202: ////spyi don gsum pa mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:18203: sangs kyi dgongs pa bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18205: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18207: rang bzhin gzhi ji bzhin pa'i gnas tshul lhag pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18208: chos sku chen po nyid du ye nas sangs rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:18209: pa'i don ji bzhin pa lam gyi mngon sum du
NK078(tshu)001:18210: stobs rdzogs par bya ba'i sangs rgyas /
NK078(tshu)001:18211: lhun grub rgyal ba rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po /
NK078(tshu)001:18212: kun tu bzang po nyid la mos shing gus pas 'dud pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18213: don gyi na rtogs pa mjal ba'i phyag 'tshal ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18214: dper na srid pa 'khor bar skye ba len lugs la mngal skyes rim gyis pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18215: bardzusa skyes rdzogs tshul cig char du smin pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:18216: lam rim dang cig car gnyis kyi sgo nas gzhi don ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:18217: mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu'i rnam dag gcig /lam
NK078(tshu)001:18218: bgrod pa la don yod par bya ba'i phyir mthar
NK078(tshu)001:18219: thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa bshad
NK078(tshu)001:18220: par bya ba'o // gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:18224: spyir lam la mtshan nyid gsum yod pa'i tha ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18225: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid rig 'dzin rnams yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:18226: de'i tha ma mthar thug sangs rgyas lugs ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18227: 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18229: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu'i khyad par bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18230: gsum gyis 'bras bu'i lus rnam bzhag gsum gyi don mngon sum gyi tshul du snang ba rnams ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18231: yan lag rgyas bshad kyi sgo nas ji lta ba bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18232: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum te /
NK078(tshu)001:18233: rgyal ba drug pa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18234: 'bras bu thob nas dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18238: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18240: de ltar lus rnam bzhag la don gsuma yod pas
NK078(tshu)001:18241: dkyus kyi snga ma 'bras bu'i ngo bo la brjod
NK078(tshu)001:18243: yon tan gyi rten byed pa'i sku dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18244: go bar brda sprod pa'i gsung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18245: dgongs pa zab pa'i thugs nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18247: bya ba byed pa'i phrin las rnams ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos te /
NK078(tshu)001:18248: de ltar lnga po de re re la'ang lnga lnga
NK078(tshu)001:18249: ste nyi shu rtsa lnga nyid kyi ngo bor gnas
NK078(tshu)001:18250: so // gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:18251: dbyer med lhun 'grub kyi ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18252: ma 'dres rnam grangs su snang ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18255: dang po yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas drug pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18256: mtshan gyi rnam grangs kyi 'og ma'i sangs rgyas las
NK078(tshu)001:18257: dpag tshul ngo bo nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i dpe
NK078(tshu)001:18259: e ma ho ni lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:18260: khyad par can ye nas gnas pa mngon sum du
NK078(tshu)001:18262: dgongs pa de'i ngo bo phyogs res nyes skyon dang
NK078(tshu)001:18263: bral zhing yang dag par dbyer med du mngon sum
NK078(tshu)001:18264: du rdzogs pa'i don la gzhi dang lam gyi nyes
NK078(tshu)001:18265: pa gnyis dang bral bas sangs la ye shes mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:18266: dbus med par bdal bas rgyas pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18268: sangs pa'i ye shes phyogs bral rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:18270: thun mong gi rgyal ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18271: sku gser gyi gtams pa la sogs pa phyi'i bdud bzhi las rgyal ba yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:18272: de las lhag pa 'di'i rgyal ba ni phung po
NK078(tshu)001:18273: lnga rigs lngar shar ba la sogs pa nang gi
NK078(tshu)001:18275: thun mong gi lha ni rgyu'i theg pa ji lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18276: phyi rgyud kyi ji snyed pa'i bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa rnam par dag pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:18277: de las lhag pa 'di'i lha ni mnyam pa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:18278: kyi ngang la bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa rnam
NK078(tshu)001:18279: par dag pa'o // thun mong gi 'phags pa ni rgyu'i theg pas chos nyid ji lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18280: phyi rgyud kyi chos nyid ji snyed mkhyen pa nyid bdag med pa mngon du gyur pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:18281: de las lhag pa 'di'i 'phags pa ni dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:18282: mnyam pa nyid la bdag mtha' dang dag bral ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:18283: ngang la spyod yul yongs su dag pas kun tu
NK078(tshu)001:18284: bzang po'o // thun mong gi de bzhin gshegs pa
NK078(tshu)001:18285: ni rgyu'i theg pa spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral
NK078(tshu)001:18286: bzang po'o // ba dang / kri yas dag pa mtha' bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18287: yo gas mtshan ma med pa'i de bzhin nyid la sogs pa nar son pas gshegs la /
NK078(tshu)001:18288: de las lhag pa 'di'i de bzhin gshegs pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:18289: gnyis med lhun grub mnyam pa nyid kyi de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:18290: nyid nar son nas gshegs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18291: thun mong gi bde bar gshegs pa ni rgyu'i theg
NK078(tshu)001:18292: pas nyon mongs pa chos nyid du sbyong ba dang
NK078(tshu)001:18293: / phyi rgyud kyi lhar bsgyur nas zug rngu zhi bas bde bar gshegs la /
NK078(tshu)001:18294: 'dir de las kyang lhag pa 'dir bde bar gshegs pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18295: nyon mongs ye shes su rang dbang bsgyur nas zug rngu zhi bas bde ba /
NK078(tshu)001:18296: de mthar phyin nas gshegs pa ni dper na yid
NK078(tshu)001:18297: bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che la dgos 'dod
NK078(tshu)001:18298: lhun gyis grub pa bzhin du bzhugs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18299: de yang dgos pa tshang ba /
NK078(tshu)001:18305: yang na yon tan la zad 'phel dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18307: thugs rje la nye ring med pa'i chos drug dang
NK078(tshu)001:18308: ldan pa nor bus mtshon pa'i rgyal ba drug pa
NK078(tshu)001:18309: de ni / yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs pas dgos pa tshang ba /
NK078(tshu)001:18310: gdul bya'i re ba skong ba /
NK078(tshu)001:18312: zad mi shes pa bdag dang gzhan du rtog pa med pa /
NK078(tshu)001:18314: 'bras bu'i chos nyer lngar ma 'dres par shar ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:18315: ngos nas rigs du mar snang bas gcig pa'i mtha'
NK078(tshu)001:18316: dang bral la / yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas rang
NK078(tshu)001:18317: byung gi ye shes su lhun gyis grub pas du
NK078(tshu)001:18318: ma'i mtha' kun dang bral zhing des na gcig du
NK078(tshu)001:18319: ma gnyis ka'i bdag nyid yid pas ldan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18320: gnyis pa rigs lhun grub de nyid phyogs med du
NK078(tshu)001:18321: shar yang rigs phyogs gcig tu chad pa med par
NK078(tshu)001:18323: kun bral ldan pa'i sku lnga lhun grub drug pa
NK078(tshu)001:18324: de nyid rigs thams cad kun gyi dngos gzhi yin
NK078(tshu)001:18325: pas / phyogs gcig pa'i rigs dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:18326: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po'am drug pa zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18328: rgyal ba kun dang dus gsum chos //
NK078(tshu)001:18329: bdag nyid kun gyi spyi gzugs can //
NK078(tshu)001:18332: rgyal ba drug pa de nyid kyi sku gsung thugs
NK078(tshu)001:18333: yon tan phrin las re re la'ang lnga lnga ste
NK078(tshu)001:18334: nyi shu rtsa lnga ldan pa de zhing khams phyogs
NK078(tshu)001:18335: dus kyi rgyal ba kun gyi ngo bo nyid yin
NK078(tshu)001:18336: pas / gdul bya rnams la rang rang ci ltar mos bzhina du /
NK078(tshu)001:18337: gang mos de'i rigas dang mthuna par sku lnga la sogs par snang la /
NK078(tshu)001:18338: yanga dag pa'i don rang bzhin nyid kyi dbang btsan du byas na /
NK078(tshu)001:18339: rigs rang rgyud pa 'di kho na'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18340: zhes phyogs gcig tu grub pa med do //
NK078(tshu)001:18341: gsum pa ngo bo lhun grub kyi yon tan phyogs re nas mtshan gyi rnam grangs su dbye ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18343: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga po nyid
NK078(tshu)001:18344: re re la bye brag lnga lnga ste nyi shu
NK078(tshu)001:18345: rtsa lngar ldan zhing snang ba'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:18346: rigsa thams cad kyi bdag po yang dag par rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:18347: pa'i sangsa rgyas drug pa kun tu bzang po zhes
NK078(tshu)001:18348: pa de'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:18349: mtshan nyid gsum gyi tha ma ni 'bras bu de'i
NK078(tshu)001:18350: tha ma mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i skabs su bag
NK078(tshu)001:18351: la nyal gyi sgrib pa bcom pas phyogs zhen tha
NK078(tshu)001:18352: dag bral ba'i phyir sangs la /
NK078(tshu)001:18353: rang byung gi ye shes kyis 'gro 'ong med par
NK078(tshu)001:18354: shes bya'i chos kun la khyab pas na rgyas zhes
NK078(tshu)001:18355: bya'o // thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:18356: 'ong med par shes bya kun la khyab pas na
NK078(tshu)001:18357: rgyas pa'i phyir sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18358: chos nyid snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang byung
NK078(tshu)001:18359: gi ye shes ni ma bcos par lhun gyis grub
NK078(tshu)001:18361: ci bzhin pa de'i ngang nyid du dgongs pa 'gro
NK078(tshu)001:18362: 'ong med par nar son par gshegs pas na de
NK078(tshu)001:18363: bzhin gshegs pa zhes kyang bya /
NK078(tshu)001:18364: de bzhin du chos nyid la spros pa'i zug rngu med pas bde ba chen po'i ngang nyid du /
NK078(tshu)001:18365: rtsol rtog gi zug rngu kun dang brala te /
NK078(tshu)001:18366: bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir na bde bar gshegs pa zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18367: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang khams gsum gyi sems
NK078(tshu)001:18368: can thams cad gnyis su med par sems nyid la
NK078(tshu)001:18369: nar son pas 'khor 'das thams cad la dbang bsgyur
NK078(tshu)001:18370: bas dbang phyug chen po drug pa nyid longs spyod
NK078(tshu)001:18371: chen po'i skur bzhugs pas na dbang phyug chen po
NK078(tshu)001:18372: zhes bya'o // gsang ba'i bdag po ye shes dang
NK078(tshu)001:18373: yul dbyings gnyis 'adu 'bral med pa'am gsang ba'i dbang
NK078(tshu)001:18374: po rdo rje dang pad+ma gnyis 'du 'bral med par
NK078(tshu)001:18375: kha sbyor gyi bde ba la longs spyod pas gsang
NK078(tshu)001:18377: 'khor 'das kyi dngosa po gnyis kyi longs spyod la
NK078(tshu)001:18378: bstar la mi 'dzin pas bde ba chen por longs
NK078(tshu)001:18379: spyod pas na longs spyod ces bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18380: de dag ni drug pa kun tu bzang po'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs so //
NK078(tshu)001:18381: gnyis pa ma 'dras rnam grangs kyi ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:18383: dang po nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18385: lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa spyi'i gzugs
NK078(tshu)001:18386: can rigs thams cad kyi bdag po de nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18387: yon tan gyi cha las sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:18388: phrin las lnga po cha re re nas phyes te
NK078(tshu)001:18389: / nyi shu rtsa lnga brjod pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18391: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18402: dang po chos kyi sku dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18404: 'jig rten las 'das pa rnam par byang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18406: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos can ma lus pa
NK078(tshu)001:18407: kun chos nyid don dam pa dbyer med du gcig
NK078(tshu)001:18408: pa'i rgyal ba chos sku nyid yin pa'i phyir na
NK078(tshu)001:18409: / 'khor 'das sna tshogs pa'i chos su ma 'gag par kun rdzob tu snang ba'i dus nyid na /
NK078(tshu)001:18410: don dam la rang bzhin nam ngo bo rang rgyud du grub pa med pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:18411: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i don mngon du byed pa de nyid d+harma ni chos /
NK078(tshu)001:18412: k+aa ya ni sku ste snang stong gnyis su med pa'i chos skur gnas so //
NK078(tshu)001:18414: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK078(tshu)001:18415: snang ba nyid nas ngo bo med //
NK078(tshu)001:18416: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK078(tshu)001:18418: gnyis pa mngon par byang chub pa'i sku dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18420: 'khor 'das kyi chos thamsa cad rang rig par mngon sum du snang bas mngon par /
NK078(tshu)001:18421: de nyid la phyogs 'dzin gyi zhen pa'i mtha' kun dang bral bas byang /
NK078(tshu)001:18422: rang rig pa'i ye shes su kun chub pa'i phyir mngon par byang chub pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18423: rig pa de nyid rgyu rkyen dang byed pa po med par rang byung zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:18424: sgrib g.yogs med par rang gsal bas ye shes chen
NK078(tshu)001:18425: po ni sku bzhi po kun gyi gzhi byed cing
NK078(tshu)001:18426: gdul bya ji ltar 'dul ba ltar snang ba'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:18427: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ste sku bzhi po
NK078(tshu)001:18429: zhes pa ste rang sa'i che ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18432: tha ma 'dod pa'i khams kyi gnas kyi mtha' ma dmyal ba nas /
NK078(tshu)001:18433: yar mtha' yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18434: bar du dmyal ba la sogs pa ngan song gsum
NK078(tshu)001:18436: 'dod khams kyi lha mo'i 'dod yon gyi bde ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18437: gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18439: nyan rang gi 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18440: dgra bcom pa zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i bde ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18441: byang sems kyi btang snyoms dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18442: gsang sngags kyi bde chen dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18443: sogsa khongs nas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la
NK078(tshu)001:18444: yul yul can du zhen pa med par kun la
NK078(tshu)001:18445: rol pas longs spyod che ba ste longs spyod rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:18447: thams cad kyis ro myong yang bdag nyid chen po'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:18449: bzhi pa sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18451: rlung gi rta bdun la brten pa ni nyi ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18452: ri bong gzugs bris pa can zla ba nyid lha
NK078(tshu)001:18453: rnams kyi gzhal yas khang yin pa de las ma
NK078(tshu)001:18454: g.yos bzhin du / chu dwangs kun tu gzugs brnyan
NK078(tshu)001:18455: tha dad par snang ba ltar rgyal ba drug pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18456: sku'i ngo bo 'am dgongs par 'gro 'ong med par
NK078(tshu)001:18457: gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs la phyogs kun tu thub
NK078(tshu)001:18458: pa drug la sogs par snang nas don mdzad pa
NK078(tshu)001:18459: ni sprul sku'i mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18462: dpe ji ltar na 'dus ma byas kyi nam mkha' la skye ba dang 'jig pa med pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:18463: sprul sku la sogs 'dus byas mi rtag pa chos kun gyi dngos gzhir snang kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:18464: ngo bo rang la 'gyur ba med pas rtag pa
NK078(tshu)001:18465: chen por bzhugs pa de nyid snang stong gnyis med
NK078(tshu)001:18466: rdo rje'i sku mchog tu gyur pa de la skye
NK078(tshu)001:18467: 'jig med pa'o // de'i ni grangs kyi lnga pa
NK078(tshu)001:18468: dbyer med rdo rje'i sku nyid du le'u lag la
NK078(tshu)001:18469: sogs pa'i rgyud kun tu raba tu grags so //
NK078(tshu)001:18472: de ltar sku lnga pos so sor 'dul ba'i 'khor lnga bstan pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18473: chos sku'i 'khor ye shes lnga'i gzugs brnyan mchog gi
NK078(tshu)001:18474: rigs lngar shar bas ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshogs zhes
NK078(tshu)001:18475: bya ba dang / longs sku'i 'khor smin pa rgya ma tsho ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18476: shesa bya thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes la sgrib
NK078(tshu)001:18477: pa gyur pa sgrib pa'i mtha' ma shes sgrib cha
NK078(tshu)001:18479: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18480: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin rnams so //
NK078(tshu)001:18481: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i 'khor rgyal ba rgya mtsho ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18482: yo ga'i 'bras bu'i rgyal po rigs lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18483: u pa ya'i rigs bzhi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18485: pha rol tu phyin pa'i kun tu 'od kyi sangs
NK078(tshu)001:18486: rgyas la sogs pa'i rgyud mas sbyong ba theg pa
NK078(tshu)001:18488: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18489: sprul sku'i 'khor mos pa rgya mtsho ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18490: rgyu'i mos pa spyod pa'i tshogs sbyor ba dang rgyu'i
NK078(tshu)001:18491: sa dang po'am tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:18492: no // rdo rje sku'i 'khor ni dbyer med rdo
NK078(tshu)001:18493: rje'i tshogs kyi zhal mthong zhing gsung brda 'jal ba'i
NK078(tshu)001:18494: phyir lhun grub rig 'dzin ni rdo rje'i sku'i 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:18496: mdor na sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa des 'dul ba spyi'i 'khor ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18497: snyan cha lnga dang ldan pa'i sdud pa po gsang ba'i bdag po yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:18499: tshogs 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho las //
NK078(tshu)001:18500: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor lhan cig tu //
NK078(tshu)001:18501: ye shes lha mo la brten nas //
NK078(tshu)001:18502: ye shes chen po'i dbang bskur ba'i //
NK078(tshu)001:18506: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK078(tshu)001:18507: rang snang rgyal ba'i sems sogs dang //
NK078(tshu)001:18508: dang po sangs rgyas su rgyal ba //
NK078(tshu)001:18509: sems dpa' che dang 'jam pa che //
NK078(tshu)001:18511: gnyis pa gsung lnga la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:18513: dang po gsung lnga so so'i 'khor dang gsang bdag
NK078(tshu)001:18514: gis lhun grub tu brda 'jal tshul spyir bstan pa
NK078(tshu)001:18516: 'khor lnga po de dag la ston pa sku lnga
NK078(tshu)001:18517: po de'i dgongs pa gsungs lnga po bshad pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:18518: / sprul sku'i tshig tu brjod pas go ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18519: sku bzhi'i tshig tu ma brjod kyang brjod pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:18520: 'dra ba'i phyir don gyi gsung du nges pas ni
NK078(tshu)001:18521: / tshig dang yi ge ru brjod med par don go zhing brda 'jal bar byed pa'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:18527: sprul sku'i gsung tshig dang yi ge ru brjod pas ston pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18528: de yang 'gro drug gi gnas su rtsa ba drug po re re la yang /
NK078(tshu)001:18529: ring thung 'bring gi chas drug drug go //
NK078(tshu)001:18530: de re re la yan lag bcu bcu ste drug
NK078(tshu)001:18531: cu ba tshan pa drug la sum brgya dang drug
NK078(tshu)001:18532: cus / don go zhing brda 'jal bar byed pa sprul sku'i tshig gi gsung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18533: lnga po nyid kyi tshul gyis don gyi go ba de yang /
NK078(tshu)001:18534: sku lnga po so so rang rang gi 'khor lnga po de dag nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18535: spyi'i 'khor sdud pa po gsang bdag phyag na rdo
NK078(tshu)001:18536: rje dag gis gsung lnga lhun grub dus gcig tu
NK078(tshu)001:18537: thos nus pa'i snyan cha lnga dang ldan pa'i phyir
NK078(tshu)001:18538: gsung lnga lhun grub thos pas /
NK078(tshu)001:18539: sdud pa po'i tshig tshogs dang yi ger bkod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18540: tshe gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud sde kun
NK078(tshu)001:18541: gyi mgo la / sku bzhi'i gsungs pa la bshad ces pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18542: sprul sku'i gsung la thos zhes gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:18543: gong gi yi ge drug bcu ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18544: lha la sogs pa'i 'gro ba ris drug po la rim pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:18545: tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18548: ka la ping ka lta bu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18552: dbyangs ring mo 'bring nge ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18554: thung ba la sha ta pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18557: de gnyis 'dus pa las byung ba /
NK078(tshu)001:18558: cang ka te'u dang par ka te'u gnyis /
NK078(tshu)001:18560: dbyangs kyi yan lag bcu bcu dang ldan pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18564: mi mthun pa med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18567: gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18571: de ltar sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18572: gnyis pa gsung lnga so sor bshad pa de la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18574: dang po chos sku skye med don gyi gsungs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18577: skye med kyi don gnyis rang bzhin bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brela pa yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18578: 'khor gyi grib pa dag ste shes rab kyi dabnga po dwangs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:18579: dper na rgya mtsho rnyog ma dwangsa pa'i chu la
NK078(tshu)001:18580: nyi zla skar gsum gyi gzugs brnyan gsal bar 'char
NK078(tshu)001:18581: ba bzhin du / chos thams cad ma skyes shing skye ba med par brda sprod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:18582: chos sku skye med don gyi gsung mchog gis /
NK078(tshu)001:18583: sprul sku'i gsung ltar tshig tu smra brjod med par go bar byed pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18584: de yang chos sku'i dgongs pa skye med de /
NK078(tshu)001:18585: 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho'i blo la snang bar mdzad pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18586: gnyis pa mngon par byang chub pa'i gsung rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18588: rang riga pa'i ye shes de stong pa nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18589: ye shes la sogs pa ming lnga dang ldan pas
NK078(tshu)001:18590: / gong gi chos sku'i gsung de bzhin du rang
NK078(tshu)001:18591: bzhin 'brel ba'i rig pa byin rlabs kyis gsung gis
NK078(tshu)001:18592: brjod pa med par brjod bya'i don rang bzhin gsang
NK078(tshu)001:18593: ba'i snying po'i rgyud kyi don rnams kun /
NK078(tshu)001:18594: dper na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od kyis thams cad
NK078(tshu)001:18595: gsal bar byed pa lta bur 'khor gyi blo la
NK078(tshu)001:18597: gsum pa longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18599: dper na me long lta bur skyon sel bar byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18602: gzugs brnyan snang bar byed pa /
NK078(tshu)001:18606: mi ldan pa ma yin pa dang chos brgyad kyisa
NK078(tshu)001:18607: mtshon pa'i don dbang phyug chen po longs spyod rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:18608: pa'i sku de 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho'i tshogs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18609: mthong ba tsam gyis 'khor rgyu'i sa bcu'i byang chuba
NK078(tshu)001:18611: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18612: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi byang chub sems dpa' chen
NK078(tshu)001:18613: po rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyi rgyud la brda'i
NK078(tshu)001:18614: sgo nas gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa'i don snang
NK078(tshu)001:18615: bar byed do // bzhi pa sprul sku'i gsung tshangs pa dbyangs kyi tshig tu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18617: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las rnam par grol bar mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18618: thar pa'i gnas su bgrod pa lam gyi chos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18619: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa 'khor pa'i chos su snang ba'i sgra skad thams cad /
NK078(tshu)001:18620: sprul sku'i gsung gi rtsa ba tshangs pa'i dbyangs la
NK078(tshu)001:18621: sogs pa drug rigs drug gi yan lag 'du shes
NK078(tshu)001:18622: bskyed pa la sogs pa bcu bcu ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18623: sum brgya drug cu'i tshul gyis tshogs kun 'jig rten
NK078(tshu)001:18624: gyi mes po tshangs pa'i ngag ltar snyan cing yid
NK078(tshu)001:18625: du 'ong ba'i gsung gis gdul bya mos pa spyod
NK078(tshu)001:18626: pa'i sa pa las 'phro dang skal ba can rnams
NK078(tshu)001:18627: la / tshig dang sgra snang ba rang rang gi sha'i rna bas dngos su thos pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18628: lnga pa rdo rje'i gsung grags stong dbyer med du'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18630: gdul bya rnams rang rang so so'i ji ltar don go ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18631: 'dul bar snang ba'i 'khor la rdo rje'i gsung rnams dper na brag gi ngos la sgra'i bskyed pa'i /
NK078(tshu)001:18633: brag gis smra ba med pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:18634: don grags stong dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18635: ston pas gsung pa med par 'khor la snang bas na /
NK078(tshu)001:18636: dbyer med kyi gsung de yang gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18637: sgra thos par byed pa'ang rdo rje'i gsung de nyid brda 'jal ba'i mthu gzugs snang stong dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18638: sgra grags stong du shar ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18639: gsum pa thugs la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18641: dang po stong pa nyid kyi ye shes bde ba chen po'i thug dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18643: 'khor 'das kyi dngosa po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK078(tshu)001:18644: phyi nang snod bcud la sogs bye brag gis dbye
NK078(tshu)001:18645: ba yan lag dang bcas pa'i chos rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:18646: rang rig pa byang chub sems kyi bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:18647: snang ba ma spang bas rnam pa kun ldan gyi
NK078(tshu)001:18648: stong pa chen po'i don mngon du byas pa'i ye
NK078(tshu)001:18649: shes kyis dngos por snang bas zug rngu ma spangs
NK078(tshu)001:18650: bas ldan bzhin du rang rgyud du mi dmigs pas
NK078(tshu)001:18651: bral ba'i don de ka la bde ba chen po
NK078(tshu)001:18653: de yang dper na nam mkha' stong zhing go skabs
NK078(tshu)001:18654: 'byed pa lta bura shes bya'i chos thams cad ye
NK078(tshu)001:18655: nas sgrib g.yogs med par gsal la ngo bos stong
NK078(tshu)001:18656: pas na stong pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK078(tshu)001:18657: gnyis pa me long lta bu'i ye shes rnam par mi rtog mchog gi don dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18659: chos rnams spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid dbyer med
NK078(tshu)001:18660: pa'i chos rnams kun yul dang yul can du rtog
NK078(tshu)001:18661: pa med par / dper na me long dwangs par bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan gsal ba bzhin /
NK078(tshu)001:18662: mngon sum bzhi po kun gyi mchog rang rig pas mngon sum du rtog pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:18663: de ka la rnam pa mi rtog pa mchog gi thugs zhes bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18664: gsum pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes mnyam pa chen po mchog gi thugs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18666: dper na 'byung ba chen po lnga gang la yang /
NK078(tshu)001:18667: bzang ngan dang skyon yon thams cad mnyam pa lta bur /
NK078(tshu)001:18668: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la tha dad bzang
NK078(tshu)001:18669: ngan gyi skyon gang yang mi 'byed cing blang dor
NK078(tshu)001:18670: med par mnyam pa nyid kyis mkhyen cing /
NK078(tshu)001:18671: dus thams cad du dgongs pa chos nyid mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:18672: nyid kyi ngang las dgongs pa mi g.yo ba de
NK078(tshu)001:18673: ni mi g.yo ba'i thugs sam /
NK078(tshu)001:18674: mnyam pa chen po mchog gi thugs ces bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18675: bzhi pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes 'gro ba sgrol ba'i dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18677: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis su mi 'byed pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18678: thugs rje chen pos 'dul byed kyi ston pa dang
NK078(tshu)001:18679: / gdul bya gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid gcig par 'brel ba yod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18680: sangs rgyas de nyid kyi thugs ni mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings las /
NK078(tshu)001:18681: gdul bya rnams mi gzhan par mkhyen pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:18682: lam pa ltar gdul bya'i don bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18683: byed pa'i rtsol ba med par phrin las rnam pa
NK078(tshu)001:18684: bzhi yis 'gro ba rnams 'khor ba las sgrol bar
NK078(tshu)001:18685: byed pa'i thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:18686: / 'gro ba sgrol ba'i thugs rje yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18687: lnga pa so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes mi phyed rdo rje'i thugs so //
NK078(tshu)001:18689: yul chos nyid spros bral dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18690: chos can sems kyi 'dzin pa thams cad kun /
NK078(tshu)001:18691: tha dad kyi 'dzin pa dang bral bas chos can rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18692: chos nyid spyi'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18693: dbyer med dus gcig tu rig pa la gsal ba'i dpe ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18694: dper na nam mkha' la 'ja' tshon snang ba ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:18695: rang spyi gang yang gsal stong dbyer med du ma 'dres par gsal ba de ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18696: don rtogs pa'i ye shes sam thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs sam /
NK078(tshu)001:18697: rang spyi'i gsal stong dbyer med mi phyed pa rdo rje'i thugs mchog go //
NK078(tshu)001:18699: rgyas par ni spyi mdo'i le'u sum cu so bzhi par blta bar bya'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18700: 'o na chos sku'i sku gsung thugs gsum ka dbyer
NK078(tshu)001:18701: med du mthun par bshad pas na khyad med dam
NK078(tshu)001:18702: zhe na / ngo bo la khyad med kyang mtshon tshul la khyad yod de /
NK078(tshu)001:18703: de yang don dbyer med kyi rten byed pa'i cha nas sku dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18704: de nyid brda 'phrod pa'i cha nas gsung dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18705: de'i ngo bo zab pa'i cha nas thugs su phye ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18706: bzhi pa yon tan la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18708: dang zhing khams yon tan can dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18710: gnas phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos 'das pa ma lus /
NK078(tshu)001:18712: ma 'ongs pa lus pa med pa rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:18713: rang rgyud du grub pa med par rig pa rang snang ba nyid kyi phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:18714: semsa nyid kyi ngo bo yid bzhin nor bu rin
NK078(tshu)001:18715: po che lta bu ji ltar bsam pa ltar snang
NK078(tshu)001:18716: ba'i yon tan mang ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18717: sprin phung tsam gyi tshogsa kyis phyogsa bcu'i 'jig rten
NK078(tshu)001:18718: gyi khams ma lus pa thams cad sangs rgyas kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18719: zhing khams rnam par dag par snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18720: gnyis pa gzhal yas khang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18722: 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan thams cad 'bad pa
NK078(tshu)001:18723: med par lhun gyis grub cing rdzogs pa'i rig pa
NK078(tshu)001:18724: snang ba'i rten gzhal yas khang ni gnas kyi ngo
NK078(tshu)001:18726: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:18727: dang brala ba'i rang rig pa nyid la brten pa
NK078(tshu)001:18728: lha dang / rten can gzhal yas khang dang gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:18729: su med par de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi bzhugs
NK078(tshu)001:18730: gnas yin te gnas kyi rang bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18732: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK078(tshu)001:18733: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:18737: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa gang yang ma spang
NK078(tshu)001:18738: bar rang rig pa'i ye shes su lhun gyis rdzogs
NK078(tshu)001:18739: pa'i phyir / sna tshogs kyi snang ba ma 'gags pa de ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18740: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor chen pa'i rgyan yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18744: rta babs la sogs pa sna tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po mdzes pa'i rgyan du byas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18747: sangs rgyas kyi thugs ye shes lnga po nyid kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18748: rang bzhin la sgrib gsum gyis ma sgrib par 'od
NK078(tshu)001:18749: gsal ba'i phyir / dkar bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18754: shel lam dngul gyi mdog lta bu dang drug po
NK078(tshu)001:18755: re re la yang bye ba phrag drug cu drug
NK078(tshu)001:18756: cu ste sna tshogs pa'i 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro
NK078(tshu)001:18757: ba'i snang bas khyab cing rang bzhin gsal bar byed
NK078(tshu)001:18758: pa'o // lnga gdan khri yon tan can no //
NK078(tshu)001:18764: phrin las bzhi la sogs pa 'bras bu'i chos kun lhun gyis grub cing rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:18765: gdan sems can lnga'i bye brag rang snang ba'o zhes pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:18766: yang na seng ge la sogs pa lnga dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18767: rin po che'i khri rkang pad+ma nyi ma zla ba'i gdan lnga yi bye brag tu rang snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18768: 'dir yon tan lnga yi skabs su lnga po re re la'ang yon tan lnga lnga ldan nam /
NK078(tshu)001:18769: thams cad la yon tan lnga las med /
NK078(tshu)001:18770: dang po ltar na 'bras bu'i chos nyer lnga min
NK078(tshu)001:18771: par thal yon tan nyid la yang nyer lnga 'dug
NK078(tshu)001:18772: pa'i phyir ro // yang bye brag tu chos sku la yon tan ldan nam mi ldan /
NK078(tshu)001:18773: mi ldan na chos sku la yon tan med par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:18775: gzhal yas khang dang rgyan dang gdan 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:18776: gnyis pa ltar na sku lnga dang yon tan lnga
NK078(tshu)001:18777: grangs sprad pa'i 'thad pa med pa la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:18778: skyon du ma 'ong ngo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:18779: rang gis 'dod pa ni sku lnga yon tan lnga
NK078(tshu)001:18780: las med pa min te re re la'ang lnga lnga
NK078(tshu)001:18781: ldan no // 'o na nyer lnga'i grangs med snyam na /
NK078(tshu)001:18782: rigs kyi spyi bsdus pa la nyer lnga'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18783: de yang sku lnga sogs ma 'dres yongs rdzogs yin pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:18784: yon tan lnga yang ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18785: lnga pa phrin las la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18787: dang po gdul bya ngos bzung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18789: gdul bya ma lus pa 'dul ba'i phrin las kyi
NK078(tshu)001:18790: bya ba tha dad pa mang por snang ba yang
NK078(tshu)001:18792: 'dul bya ma zhi ba dang khro ba dang mi mos pa dang tshe bsod nams nyams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18793: gnyis pa 'dul thabs las bzhi gang 'tshams su don
NK078(tshu)001:18794: mdzad cing las bzhi re re la'ang bye brag lnga
NK078(tshu)001:18795: lngar lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18797: bzhi yod pa'i phyir gdul thabs zhi rgyas dbang drag
NK078(tshu)001:18798: rnam pa bzhi'i rol pa ste spyod pa rnams kyis
NK078(tshu)001:18799: zhi ba'i gdul bya zhi ba'i phrin las kyis gdug
NK078(tshu)001:18800: sems zhi bar byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18801: drag po'i phrin las kyis gdul bya ma rung ba bsgral ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18802: dbang gi phrin las kyis gdul bya mos shing dbang du bya ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18803: rgyas pa'i phrin las kyis gdul bya tshe dbang bsod nams longs spyod rgyas par bya ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18804: de ltar gang la gang 'tshams pa ltar snang nas gdul bya rnams 'dul bar mdzad de /
NK078(tshu)001:18805: phrin las rnam pa bzhi yi bye brag tha dad pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18806: phrin las bzhi po re re la'ang zhi rgyas dbang
NK078(tshu)001:18807: drag lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga ste
NK078(tshu)001:18808: / de yang zhi ba'i zhi ba /
NK078(tshu)001:18812: zhi ba'i lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18813: de bzhin du rgyas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18816: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las la yang lnga lnga'i tshul gyis gdul bya'i ngo la snang ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:18817: gsum pa 'dul byed rigs lngar snang ba phyogs chad du med par bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18819: phrin las bzhi po de la zhi ba'i phrin las de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18820: rgyas pa rin chen rigs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18822: drag po rdo rje'i rigs te rigs bzhi'i cha 'dzin par byed pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18823: lnga pa las kyi rigsa la phrin las lnga ka lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18824: de ltar rigs rnam pa bzhi yis gdug bya 'dul bar mdzad pa de yang /
NK078(tshu)001:18825: zhi rgyas dbang drag gis phyogsa kyis gdul bya 'dul ba'i cha nas brjod pa yin gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:18826: rigs phyogs gcig tu chad pa ma yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:18827: rigs lnga re res kyang kun 'dul ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18828: 'dir sku lnga bo re re la phrin las lnga lnga ldan nam /
NK078(tshu)001:18829: spyir lnga las med thams cad la lnga las med na /
NK078(tshu)001:18830: sku re re la phrin las re re grangs sprad dam /
NK078(tshu)001:18831: 'on te phrin las med pa'i sku yang yod dam /
NK078(tshu)001:18832: grongs sprod na ji ltar sprod de 'thad pa med do //
NK078(tshu)001:18833: re re la phrin las lnga lnga tshang na /
NK078(tshu)001:18834: chos sku de gzugs skur thal /
NK078(tshu)001:18835: phrin las kyis gzhan don byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:18836: sku la sogs pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs yin pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:18837: phrin las lnga yang ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18838: yang las bzhi gcig gam tha dad /
NK078(tshu)001:18839: gcig na las bzhir phye ba don med cing /
NK078(tshu)001:18840: zhi bas mi 'dul ba la dbang drag dgos par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:18843: gdul bya'i bya ba tha dad pa /
NK078(tshu)001:18846: lhun grub don med du thal /
NK078(tshu)001:18847: las bzhi ris su chad par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:18849: gdul bya 'dul bas 'dod do ce na /
NK078(tshu)001:18850: rnam bzhis bye brag ces pa'i sho lo ka gcig gis gsal zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:18851: gdul bya'i ngos nas tha dad /
NK078(tshu)001:18852: rgyal ba'i ngos nas gcig pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18853: gnyis pa 'bras bu thob nas dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:18855: dang po mthar lam pa las khyad du dpag pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18856: 'bras bu drug pa ni theg 'og gi 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:18857: las dpag tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18859: mthar lam man chad de ltar lam gyi rgyud rim par sbyang ba'i mtha' ma la /
NK078(tshu)001:18860: rgyal tshab skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa thob ste sangs rgyas tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:18861: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gdul bya'i
NK078(tshu)001:18862: snang ngor rigs lnga po'i cha tsam re 'dzin par
NK078(tshu)001:18863: byed kyang / rigs lnga rkyang bkar de dag las ciga shos te /
NK078(tshu)001:18864: sku lnga lhun grub kyi rgyal ba drug pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18865: sangs rgyas kun gyi ngo boo'i spyi gzugs nyid du bzhugs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18866: yang na kho bo'i bla mas 'di ltar du gsungs te /
NK078(tshu)001:18867: sgom lam man chad de ltar lam rim par sbyong
NK078(tshu)001:18868: ba'i mtha' ma lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi sku lnga'i
NK078(tshu)001:18869: rgyal tshab kyi skyes bu byed pa des rdo rje'i
NK078(tshu)001:18870: sems dpa' la sogs pa'i rigs lnga cha re'i rigs
NK078(tshu)001:18871: chung dang bcas pa'i lhun grub kyi rig pa 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:18872: par byed kyang / de la dgar bas na cig shos te /
NK078(tshu)001:18873: 'bras bu sku lnga lhun grub rgyal ba drug pa
NK078(tshu)001:18874: ni rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kun gyi ngo bo spyi
NK078(tshu)001:18875: gzugs can nyid du bzhugs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18876: 'o na dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas su bshad pa ci zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:18877: snga ma 'das pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18878: phyi ma ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18879: da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas su gsung pa de
NK078(tshu)001:18880: dag gdul bya drang ba'i don ched tsam du smos
NK078(tshu)001:18881: pa'am / yang na snga ma dbu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18882: phyi ma phyi rgyud kyi 'dod pa'i sangs rgyas ni drang ba'i don tsam yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:18883: nges don du sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa'i rgyal ba
NK078(tshu)001:18884: drug pa'i dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul ni gcig dang tha
NK078(tshu)001:18885: dad las grol bas tshig tu smra zhing blos bsam
NK078(tshu)001:18886: pa dang ngag gi brjod pa'i mtha' las 'das par
NK078(tshu)001:18887: bzhugs pa'o // gnyis pa bye brag rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18888: gzhan lugs 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18889: rang lugs rnam par bzhag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18890: de la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18893: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18895: de'i don phyogs gcig tsam brjod par bya ba gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:18896: gdul bya drang ba'i don du snga ma dbu ma dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18897: phyi ma phyi rgyud kyi sangs rgyas zhes pa'i don
NK078(tshu)001:18898: ni 'di lta ste gnyis pa rgyas pa de la
NK078(tshu)001:18900: dang po rgyud gcig par 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18902: dbu ma pas don dam gyi bden pa spros bral
NK078(tshu)001:18903: stong pa gcig pu mthar phyin nas chos sku thob
NK078(tshu)001:18905: de nyid mthar thug gi 'bras bu ma yin pa'i phyir na /
NK078(tshu)001:18906: dper na snga ma'i chu la phyi ma'i chu blugs dza gcig tu thim pa ltar /
NK078(tshu)001:18907: don dam dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad stong par rgyud gcig pa kho nar grub pa med pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18908: gnyis pa rgyud tha dad par 'dod pa dgag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18910: dbu ma las dgar ba'i cig shos ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18911: sems tsam dang sngags kyi phyi rgyud kyi kun rdzob
NK078(tshu)001:18912: kyi bden pa mthar phyin pa'i gzugs sku gcig pur
NK078(tshu)001:18914: de nyid ni mthar thug gi 'bras bu ma yin par brjod pas na /
NK078(tshu)001:18915: shing gi me dpung bzhin du dgongs pa'i rgyud la
NK078(tshu)001:18916: sbyang ba'i ye shes so so tha dad kyi cha
NK078(tshu)001:18917: dang rigs su grub pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:18918: rigs tha dad las grol ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18919: gnyis pa rang lugs la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:18921: dang po bden pa gnyis dbyer med la dbang bsgyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18923: 'dir ma h+aa'i gzhi don bden pa gnyis med rtogs pa'i don la rang dbang du bsgyur ba ni /
NK078(tshu)001:18925: gzhan don gzugs sku kun rdzob kyi bya ba gnyis su 'dzin pa med de /
NK078(tshu)001:18926: de bas na bden gnyis so sora grub pa med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:18927: gnyis pa de mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu thob tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:18929: gzhi gnyis med kyi don de nar son pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18932: stong ba don dam gyi mtha' rnams kyi phyogs su
NK078(tshu)001:18933: ma song bas mtha' kun dang brala la gang yang
NK078(tshu)001:18934: ma 'gags par snang ba mtha' kun dang ldan par
NK078(tshu)001:18935: / ye shes rang snang nyid zhen pa'i mtha' kun
NK078(tshu)001:18936: dang bral bar rang rig pa'i mngon sum du byas
NK078(tshu)001:18937: pa la 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa zhes
NK078(tshu)001:18938: ming du brjod kyis sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i ngo
NK078(tshu)001:18939: / bo ni / gcig dang tha dad 'di 'drar gnas pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18940: zhes smra zhing brjod par daka'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18941: gsum pa rtsod pa spang ba la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:18943: dang po bden gnyis tha dad kyi 'bras bu drangs don du bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18945: sems tsam dang sngags phyi rgyud kyi dus gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:18946: sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo gcig pa la sbyangs pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18947: ye shes kyi rtsal tha dad pas rgyud gcig tu
NK078(tshu)001:18949: dper na shing gi me dpung gcig la shing so
NK078(tshu)001:18950: so'i me tha dad pa ltara du brjod pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:18951: / tha dad la mos pa'i gdul bya kun drang ba'i don tsam du yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:18952: de nyid nges don gyi sangs rgyas min no //
NK078(tshu)001:18953: dbu ma pas dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams chu la
NK078(tshu)001:18954: chu thim pa ltar du dgongs pa rgyud gcig par
NK078(tshu)001:18955: 'dod pa yang gong gi don de dang 'dra'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18956: gnyis pa bden gnyis lhun grub kyi 'bras bu nges don du bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18958: de ltar gcig dang tha dad du 'dod pa ni drang ba'i don yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:18959: 'o na nges pa'i don ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:18960: 'dir bden pa gnyis su med par gnas pa'i tshul
NK078(tshu)001:18961: gyis gong gi rgyud 'dres ma phyogs rer 'dod pa
NK078(tshu)001:18962: rnams la skyon brjod pa yin pas /
NK078(tshu)001:18964: gzung 'dzin gnyis su 'dzin pa ngang gis dag pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:18965: gnyis med rang byung ye shes de nyid de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:18966: gshegs pa sangs rgyas kun gyi bzhugs gnas yin par
NK078(tshu)001:18967: / tan+t+ra ste rgyas pa'i rgyud nyid las /
NK078(tshu)001:18968: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK078(tshu)001:18969: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:18971: gnyis 'dzin gyi rtogs pa'i zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK078(tshu)001:18972: de'i don mngon sum du byas pas gshegs pa ste /
NK078(tshu)001:18973: de'ang mtha' gnyis gang la'ang mi gnas par mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:18974: chen po'i ngang nyid du spyod yul dang bral bas
NK078(tshu)001:18975: byon zhes rgyud le'u lag las gsung shing tshig tu
NK078(tshu)001:18976: brjod pa'ang / shes bya'i chos kun don dam dang
NK078(tshu)001:18977: kun rdzob dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi bden pa
NK078(tshu)001:18978: gsum pa yin pa'i phyir yang dag par nges par
NK078(tshu)001:18979: na rgyal ba rnams dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid yin
NK078(tshu)001:18980: brjod pa'ang / te / rgyud 'dres te gcig pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18981: ma 'dres te tha dad pa'i tha snyad dang brala ba'i tshul du gnas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18982: de ltar na sangs rgyas thams cad dgongs pa rgyud
NK078(tshu)001:18983: kyi bzhugs tshul gyi dgag sgrub kyi gtan tshigs la
NK078(tshu)001:18984: gnyis / gzhan lugs dgag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18987: dbu ma pas sangs rgyas thams cad stong par gcig par 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:18988: sems tsam dang sngags phyi pa'i ma 'dres te tha dad par 'dod pa dgag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18990: 'dod pa dgod pa dang de dgag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:18991: dang po dbu ma pas dus gsum sangs rgyas thams
NK078(tshu)001:18992: cad kyi dgongs pa stong nyid du rgyud gcig par
NK078(tshu)001:18993: 'dod pa ste / dper na chu la chu thim pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:18994: mar la mar bzhags pa bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:18996: bdag cag ji ltar sangs rgyas pa //
NK078(tshu)001:18997: de lta kho nar sangs rgyas pas //
NK078(tshu)001:18998: dper na mar dang mar nyid kyi //
NK078(tshu)001:18999: nying khu mtshungs par 'gyur ba bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:19002: 'di ni spros dang bral ba rnams la snang bar 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19004: gnyis pa de dgag pa la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19005: rgyu rkyen gyis bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu med par 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19006: 'bras bu sangs rgyas chad par 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19007: mdo sngags kyi 'bras bu khyad med du 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19009: theg pa'i 'bras bu rnams la mtho dman med par 'gyur ba'i skyon no //
NK078(tshu)001:19011: lam gyi dus su lha bsgom pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19012: gzugs sogs lam du khyer ba don med du 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19013: rgyu rtog tshogs zhe gnyis gnas su gyur pas 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:19014: bu sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa
NK078(tshu)001:19016: rgyu rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas su gyur pas 'bras bu ye shes lnga mi thob par 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:19017: mthar thug stong pa phyogs gcig las med pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:19019: de rnams rgyud rnams ji ltar ba //
NK078(tshu)001:19020: so so rnal 'byor tha dad pas //
NK078(tshu)001:19021: bsgrub pas de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK078(tshu)001:19022: rgyud dag lhun grub rgyal ba rnams //
NK078(tshu)001:19026: de phyir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK078(tshu)001:19027: ye shes rgyu ni ma 'dres te //
NK078(tshu)001:19029: gcig la mthun snang sgra mi 'jug /ces pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19031: 'on te thams cad gcig zhe na //
NK078(tshu)001:19035: tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogs pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19038: ye shes lnga yang rang byung gis //
NK078(tshu)001:19039: cha lngas btag cing gzhan na med //
NK078(tshu)001:19040: de phyir gcig mthar ltung ba med //
NK078(tshu)001:19043: rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa stong pa phyogs gcig pa yin par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:19046: gnyis med sems su mngon byas pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19047: bden gnyis dbyer med rdo rje'i sku //
NK078(tshu)001:19048: chu yi zla ba lta bu la //
NK078(tshu)001:19049: rang bzhin kun dang tha mi dad //
NK078(tshu)001:19051: gzhan yang ci yang med pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19054: mu stegs rgyang 'phen pa dang khyad med par 'gyur te /
NK078(tshu)001:19055: snang ba spang ba'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:19057: gal te snga phyi gcig 'gro na //
