NK078(tshu)001:19058: stong pa'i mur thim rig pas 'gal //
NK078(tshu)001:19059: snang ba spang ba'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19060: mtha' la thug par the tshom med //
NK078(tshu)001:19063: nyan rang lhag med dang dbu sems dang sngags phyi
NK078(tshu)001:19064: nang gi sangs rgyas la dgongs pa khyad med du
NK078(tshu)001:19065: thal / dgongs rgyud gcig pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:19066: 'dod na khyad par yod pas bsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:19068: so so'i grub mtha'i khyad par yang //
NK078(tshu)001:19070: so sor bsgrub phyir gcig par 'gal //
NK078(tshu)001:19071: gal te rgyal ba'ang rang rgyud 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19074: grangs rdzogs ngo bo byin brlabs las //
NK078(tshu)001:19075: snang dang don byed che chung gis //
NK078(tshu)001:19076: dpags pas ngo bo nyid kyis gsal //
NK078(tshu)001:19077: de tshul sa gzhi'i rgyal ba bdag /rgyud gcig 'dres dang grol smra ba //
NK078(tshu)001:19078: 'dir drang tsam yin bshad yin phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:19079: rgyud kyi khyad par bsam las 'das //
NK078(tshu)001:19082: 'og ma'i 'bras bu nas gong ma'i 'bras bur 'jug pa med par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:19083: sangs rgyas rnams dgongs rgyud gcig pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:19086: thabs chen theg pa'i bsti gnas yin //
NK078(tshu)001:19089: lam gyi rtsol bas ngal ba rnam //
NK078(tshu)001:19090: brod pa bskyed phyir kun tu 'ong //
NK078(tshu)001:19091: rdor 'dzin stug po dkod par bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:19093: rang sa thob las ngo bo dang //
NK078(tshu)001:19094: gcig par smra ba mun sprul pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19096: gzhan yang mdo dgongs 'dus kyi nang du le'u lnga
NK078(tshu)001:19097: 'bras bu la 'jug pa dang gsang snying le'u drug
NK078(tshu)001:19098: pa las spar khab mkhan pos 'bras 'jug ltar bshad
NK078(tshu)001:19099: pa dang / lam chung la sogs pa rnams kyi nang du bshad pas spang daka'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19100: gnyis pa dgongs rgyud tha dad du 'dod pa dgag pa la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:19101: gzhan gyi 'dod pa dgod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19104: 'bras bu dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams sangs rgyas tsam du mtshungs kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:19105: lam gyi sbyangs pa'i rtsal tha dad pa'i dbang gis dgongs pa'i rgyud rang mtshan ma 'dres te /
NK078(tshu)001:19106: dper na shing du ma'i me bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:19107: gnyis pa de dgag pa la kun khyab gsum las /
NK078(tshu)001:19108: dang po lung tshad ma ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19110: nam mkha' kun khyab rgyal ba dang //
NK078(tshu)001:19111: nyag gcig snang ba'i rgyal ba gnyis //
NK078(tshu)001:19112: gdul bya'i dbang gis tha dad las //
NK078(tshu)001:19113: sku dang gsung thugs gcig las med //
NK078(tshu)001:19116: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs rgyud ji bzhin du //
NK078(tshu)001:19117: rang gi mtshan nyid ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:19119: gnyis pa man ngag tshad mas bsgrub pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19121: 'on te de ltar mi gcig na'ang //
NK078(tshu)001:19122: rang rig rang byung mngon byas la //
NK078(tshu)001:19123: snga phyi'i sangs rgyas bla dwags btags //
NK078(tshu)001:19124: rang byung rang la shar bar zad //
NK078(tshu)001:19125: rang byung nyid dang rgyud med par //
NK078(tshu)001:19126: so so tha dad gang gis rung //
NK078(tshu)001:19129: spyan drangs byon dang mi byon 'byung //
NK078(tshu)001:19130: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19131: dngos po rnams kyi de nyid na //
NK078(tshu)001:19132: de la gnyis pa yod par 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19133: de phyir gzhi yi don dang 'gal //
NK078(tshu)001:19134: mi gcig gtan tshig rgyas pa med //
NK078(tshu)001:19137: rgyal ba kun dang dus gsum chos //
NK078(tshu)001:19138: bdag phyir kun gyi spyi gzugs can //
NK078(tshu)001:19139: chos gnyis yod pa gang gis rung //
NK078(tshu)001:19140: yod na bdag nyid chen po rdzun //
NK078(tshu)001:19143: cig shos bden par ma yin pas //
NK078(tshu)001:19144: so so tha dad cha rigs med //
NK078(tshu)001:19146: ngo bo gcig la rgyud 'dres min //
NK078(tshu)001:19147: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19148: drang ba tsam ste de nyid min //
NK078(tshu)001:19150: gsum pa rig pas dgag pa la lnga ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19151: gzhi la bzang ngan tha dad can du yod par thal ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19152: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes mi gcig par 'gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19153: gdul bya thams cad mthun snang gcig par 'gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19154: don res mos su byed par 'gyur ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19155: lha spyan drangs pa la byon mi byon yod par 'gyur ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19157: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba gzhi gnas lugs kyi don la dgongs pa gcig yin nam min /
NK078(tshu)001:19158: yin na dgongs rgyud tha dad du 'dod pa dang 'gal /
NK078(tshu)001:19159: min na dgongs pa gang yin /
NK078(tshu)001:19160: yin kyang dgongs rgyud tha dad na /
NK078(tshu)001:19161: gzhi bzang ngan can du thal te /
NK078(tshu)001:19162: gzhi mngon du byas pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dgongs rgyud tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:19164: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19165: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na //
NK078(tshu)001:19166: de la gnyis pa yod par 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19167: de phyir gzhi yi don dang 'gal //
NK078(tshu)001:19170: 'bras bu ye shes kyi dus su rang byung ngam /
NK078(tshu)001:19171: ji lta ba mkhyen pa mi gcig par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:19174: rang byung ye shes nyag gcig la //
NK078(tshu)001:19175: gdul bya'i mos dang bsam dbang gis //
NK078(tshu)001:19176: khyad par bye brag lnga sogs snang //
NK078(tshu)001:19177: rigs rgyu don la gcig tu gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:19180: 'on te de ltar mi gcig na //
NK078(tshu)001:19181: rang rig rang byung mngon byas la //
NK078(tshu)001:19182: snga phyi'i sangs rgyas bla dwags tsam //
NK078(tshu)001:19183: rang byung rang la shar bar zad //
NK078(tshu)001:19184: rang byung rig dang rgyud med par //
NK078(tshu)001:19185: so so ma 'dres gang gis rung //
NK078(tshu)001:19187: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19188: drang ba tsam ste de nyid min //
NK078(tshu)001:19191: dgongs pa tha dad na sprul pa yang tha dad pas /
NK078(tshu)001:19192: sprul sku byang chub sems dpa' la snang ba de
NK078(tshu)001:19193: gdul bya thams cad la mthun par snang bar thal
NK078(tshu)001:19194: te / sprul pa gcig la du mar snang ba med /
NK078(tshu)001:19197: nyi zer nyi ma'i shing me bzhin //
NK078(tshu)001:19198: ngo bo gcig la ye shes rgyud //
NK078(tshu)001:19199: so so yin na sprul pa yang //
NK078(tshu)001:19200: gdul bya gcig la mthun snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19201: sems dpa' che dang gcig par 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19204: rgyal bas sems can gyi don byed pa'i tshe bgo
NK078(tshu)001:19205: basha'i tshul gyis res mos su byed par thal te
NK078(tshu)001:19206: / don byed mkhan tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK078(tshu)001:19208: phyogs med lhun grub tu bshad pa dang 'gal te /
NK078(tshu)001:19210: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK078(tshu)001:19211: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK078(tshu)001:19212: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:19213: skad cig yud la lhun grub ho //
NK078(tshu)001:19216: rgyud tha dad na skal ldan rnams kyis zhi ba'i lha spyan drangs pa'i tshe /
NK078(tshu)001:19217: zhi ba'i lha byon la khro bo'i lha mi byon
NK078(tshu)001:19218: par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon du ma yod
NK078(tshu)001:19219: de / dper na mgron po bos ma bos bzhin no //
NK078(tshu)001:19221: spyan drangs byon dang mi byon 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19222: gzhi don lung rig kun dang 'gal //
NK078(tshu)001:19226: shes bya'i gshis la don dam dang kun rdzob dbyer med pas /
NK078(tshu)001:19227: de nyid mngon du byas pa mthar phyin pa'i sangs
NK078(tshu)001:19228: rgyas kun gyi spyi yi gzugs can thob pa ni
NK078(tshu)001:19229: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas zhes bya bar
NK078(tshu)001:19230: ming 'dogs te / de yang dgongs pa gcig dang
NK078(tshu)001:19231: du ma'i mtha' las grol ba'i tshul du bzhugs te
NK078(tshu)001:19232: ming 'dogs te / / dper na rdul gcig gi
NK078(tshu)001:19233: steng na rdul snyed kyi sangs rgyas ma 'dres pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19235: gcig pa'i mtha' las grol la /
NK078(tshu)001:19236: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dgongs pa mnyam pa
NK078(tshu)001:19237: nyid gcig las ma g.yos par bzhugs pas du ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:19240: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK078(tshu)001:19241: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:19244: mnyam pa gsum pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:19246: tha snyad bral ba'i tshul du gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:19253: mtsho nyid rlabs ltar thams cad kun //
NK078(tshu)001:19254: gdod nas rang byung ye shes gcig /ye shes de
NK078(tshu)001:19255: nyid 'di 'drar dka' //mtha' brjod ma lus der snang
NK078(tshu)001:19256: phyir // du ma nyid du gcig pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19257: du mar rgya chad yod gyur na //
NK078(tshu)001:19258: rang byung rang snang bden mi 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19261: rtag par yang zungs shig /mi rtag par yang zungs
NK078(tshu)001:19262: shig /yod par yang zungs shig /med par yang zungs
NK078(tshu)001:19263: shig /gcig par yang zungs shig /tha dad par yang
NK078(tshu)001:19264: zungs shig /tha dad kyi ngo bo las grol bar
NK078(tshu)001:19266: spar khab kyi nang du 'bras bu'i skabs thams cad la yang de ltar gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:19267: de ltar rgyud gcig par 'dod pa ni rten med kyis don byed par 'dod pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:19268: ma 'dres par 'dod pa ni rten can gyis don byed par 'dod pa yin cing /
NK078(tshu)001:19269: rang lugs ni dbyer med ngo bo nyid kyis don byed par 'dod pa'i lugs so //
NK078(tshu)001:19270: gsum pa 'bras bu'i khyad par la gsum te /
NK078(tshu)001:19272: dang po ming grangs kyi khyad par du dbye na bsam yas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19274: gsang ba'i theg pa thun mong min pa'i sku lnga
NK078(tshu)001:19275: lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa de'i ming
NK078(tshu)001:19277: gong ltar bde bar gshegs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19278: de bzhin gshegs pa dang bcoma ldan 'das dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19279: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19280: dgyes pa chen po zhes brjod pa la sogsa pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19281: ming gi rnam grangs mtha' yas pa zhig yod kyang
NK078(tshu)001:19282: gnyis pa 'dir bsdus te bstan pa de la gnyis
NK078(tshu)001:19284: dang po mdor bstan pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19287: ngo bo'i tshul dang khyad par gsum yod pas grangsa kyis phye bas ngo bo'i khyad par /
NK078(tshu)001:19289: ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par tsam zhig brjod na /
NK078(tshu)001:19290: 'dir mdor bsdus te brjod pa'i theg pa so so'i
NK078(tshu)001:19291: 'bras bu'i khyad par gyi don khung du chub par
NK078(tshu)001:19293: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19295: dang po 'bras bu'i ngo bo'i khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19297: ma h+aa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo ni sku gsung thugs
NK078(tshu)001:19298: yon tan phrin las lnga dang de re re la
NK078(tshu)001:19299: 'ang lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lngar lhun gyis
NK078(tshu)001:19300: grub pa'i drug pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19301: 'og ma dbu ma kri yog gis rgyal ba sku
NK078(tshu)001:19302: gsum rdzogs par 'dod pas so so'i grub mtha' rang
NK078(tshu)001:19303: sa'i sangs rgyas dang ma h+aa'i sangs rgyas gnyis la
NK078(tshu)001:19304: / grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19305: dbu ma pas kun tu 'od chos sku gcig phu dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19306: kri yas rigs gsum dang yo gas rigs lnga /
NK078(tshu)001:19307: ma h+aas ni nyer lnga lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19308: ngo bo 'dus byas ma byas kyi khyad par ni gzugs sku ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19309: dbu ma pas gzugs sku gdul bya'i ngor snang tsam du 'dod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19311: yo gas rnam snang brgya byin lha'i bla ma yang skye 'jig yod pas 'dus byas yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:19312: ma h+aa'i drug pa spyi gzugs can ni 'dus ma byas kyi gzugs sku'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19313: byin rlabs las mngon du snang ba dang mi snang ba'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19314: gsum pos ni rang sa rang sa'i 'bras bu'i sa las mi drong la /
NK078(tshu)001:19315: ma h+aas ni yi ge 'khor lo'i sa drong bar snang ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19316: don byed rgya che chung gi khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19317: dbu mas nyan rang man chad /
NK078(tshu)001:19318: kri yas dbu ma man chad /
NK078(tshu)001:19319: yo gas u pa ya man chad /
NK078(tshu)001:19320: ma h+aa yo ga man chad la lugs 'byung ldog gi sgo nas don byed pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19321: de ltar khyad par bzhi las dpag pa'i don gyis na /
NK078(tshu)001:19322: 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo nyid kyi khyad par yod par gsal lo //
NK078(tshu)001:19323: gnyis pa 'bras bu thob nas dgongs pa'i rgyud kyi bzhugs tshul gyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19325: sangs rgyas de dag gi dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul ni dbu ma /
NK078(tshu)001:19327: yo ga /ma h+aa dang rang sa'i 'bras bu bzhi'i
NK078(tshu)001:19328: rgyal ba kun tu 'od rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin
NK078(tshu)001:19330: sku lnga lhun grub dang bzhi po de dag gi khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19331: dbu mas rgyud gcig tu 'dres par 'dod pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19332: phyi rgyud kyis de las grol te tha dad par smra ba rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:19333: ma h+aa'i sa 'dir drang ba'i thabs tsam du bstan
NK078(tshu)001:19334: pa yin la ma h+aa ni gong du bshad pa
NK078(tshu)001:19336: de bas na dgongs pa rgyud kyi bzhugs tshul gyi
NK078(tshu)001:19337: khyad par ni blos bsam pa'i tshad las 'das pa'o
NK078(tshu)001:19338: // gsum pa 'bras bu'i ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19339: bde gshegs de bzhin gshegs pa'i khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19340: rgyal ba bcom ldan 'das kyi khyad par gtan tshig dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19341: dgyes pa longs spyod kyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19342: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu'i khyad par ro //
NK078(tshu)001:19344: thun mong gi theg pa'i bder gshegs de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19345: de las ma h+aa'i bde gshegs de bzhin nyid du gshegs pas dpag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19347: grol lam gyi bde gshegs de bzhin nyid du gshegs tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19348: thabs lam gyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19349: sh+aakya thub pa gshegs tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:19352: dang po byang chub sems dpa'i gshegs tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19354: 'bras bu'i ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par ni nyan rang la ltos na theg chen /
NK078(tshu)001:19355: gsang sngags la ltos na lta spyod dman pa byang
NK078(tshu)001:19356: chub sems dpa' theg pa bas rgyu thun mong gi
NK078(tshu)001:19357: tshogs gnyis bsags pa'i stobs kyis 'bras bu kun tu
NK078(tshu)001:19358: 'od kyi sa la bde bar gshegs shing /
NK078(tshu)001:19359: don dam skye ba med pa 'bras bu chos nyid
NK078(tshu)001:19360: stong pa de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gshegs pa
NK078(tshu)001:19361: de yang / dus bskal pa grangs med gsum gyi
NK078(tshu)001:19362: dbang du lam bsgrod pa'i phyir du dus der snga
NK078(tshu)001:19363: ma bzhin du thun mong gi tshogs gnyis bsags pa
NK078(tshu)001:19364: de yang / la brten nas / gnas lugs chos
NK078(tshu)001:19365: nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gshegas pa nyid
NK078(tshu)001:19366: de yang / la brten nas / dang / gnyis pa bya ba'i lugs kyi gshegs tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:19368: gsang sngags phyi rgyud kyi theg pa la'ang /
NK078(tshu)001:19369: khrus dang gtsang sbra'i bya ba byed pa kri ya'i lugs kyi shes rab lta ba rtogs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19370: 'bras bu 'grub pa'i yan lag cho ga bcu gcig
NK078(tshu)001:19371: gi lha bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin gsal
NK078(tshu)001:19372: zhing / sngags bzlas pa'i grangs rdzogs par byas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:19373: de yang 'bras bu rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK078(tshu)001:19374: ye nas sangs rgyas pa de la lam du byas
NK078(tshu)001:19375: pas dgongs pa bde bar gshegs pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:19376: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sar rang sems dag
NK078(tshu)001:19377: pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma dang bral ba'i de bzhin
NK078(tshu)001:19378: du mngon du gyur pas gshegs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19379: gnyis pa thams lam gyi gshegs tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:19381: dang po mtshan nyid kyi lugs kyi gshegs tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19383: grol lam du gshegs pa la dgar bas yang na thabs lam dbang gis gshegs pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19384: dbang gnas gang du bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19385: spyi'i gnas rgya gar gyi yul bya rgod phung po'i
NK078(tshu)001:19386: ri 'adba la sogs kyi bye brag tu bsod nams
NK078(tshu)001:19387: dang las skal ldan pa'i gnas dgon phug bye ma
NK078(tshu)001:19388: 'dab sna zhes bya ba de ru bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19390: dgra bcom stong dang lnga brgya 'dus nas bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19392: dge slong 'di ni bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal mthong gi 'khor te /
NK078(tshu)001:19393: zhes bden pa'i tshig gis bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19395: bram ze la bza' rgan mo'i bu dge slong sa ri zhes bya ba la bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19396: dgos ched ci'i phyir bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19397: rgyal tshab tu dbyung ba'i phyir bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19398: rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19399: tshig dang yi ge la brten dbang bskur ba ji bzhin nam /
NK078(tshu)001:19400: zhes dge slong sa ri la dbang bskur bas dgra bcom thob pa ci bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:19401: da lta lam pa la yang dbang bskur bas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19402: dper na 'jig rten na che ge mo la dbang bskur byas pas dbang thob pa lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19403: de yang snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:19404: bya rgod phung po'i 'dab log tu //
NK078(tshu)001:19405: dgon phug bye ma 'dab sna ru //
NK078(tshu)001:19406: dngos por lta ba'i rigs can te //
NK078(tshu)001:19407: bram ze la bza' rgan mo'i bu //
NK078(tshu)001:19408: dge slong s+aa ri zhes bya ba //
NK078(tshu)001:19409: rang gi sdug bsngal zag pa zad //
NK078(tshu)001:19410: rgyal tshab skyes bu'i sa 'dzin zer //
NK078(tshu)001:19411: dgra bcom lnga brgya stong gcig 'dus //
NK078(tshu)001:19412: skyes bu chen por dbang bskur ro //
NK078(tshu)001:19414: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang du /
NK078(tshu)001:19416: byang chub sems dpa' blo ldan gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:19417: 'dul ba'i sdom pa dam mnos te //
NK078(tshu)001:19418: bden gnyis rtogs pa'i lam brten te //
NK078(tshu)001:19419: sems can rgyud kyi mtshan rtogs nas //
NK078(tshu)001:19420: zhi gnas 'brel ba'i gnas drug sbyor //
NK078(tshu)001:19421: lhag mthong gsal bas skabs gsum bkod //
NK078(tshu)001:19422: zhi gnas brten pa'i gnas rnyed pas //
NK078(tshu)001:19424: stong pa nam mkha' de nyid bya //
NK078(tshu)001:19425: zla ba gcig gis brten gyur nas //
NK078(tshu)001:19426: de nyid stong par brten par bya //
NK078(tshu)001:19427: de nyid stoong pa'i klong chen las //
NK078(tshu)001:19428: char chen dbugs chen 'byin pa yis //
NK078(tshu)001:19429: bskal ba du ma gnas pa'ang srid //
NK078(tshu)001:19430: smon lam stobs drag myur du 'grub //
NK078(tshu)001:19431: sku byin ldan pas phyag brkyang nas //
NK078(tshu)001:19432: phyag gi gdugs kyis bkab nas ni //
NK078(tshu)001:19433: zhi gnas brten pa'i dbyings nas bslang //
NK078(tshu)001:19434: mtshan ma'i thabs kyis brten byas te //
NK078(tshu)001:19435: mtshon pa sku yi rgya ldan byas //
NK078(tshu)001:19436: bde gshegs zhing khams kun tu bsgrag /rdo rje bum pa na bza' dang //
NK078(tshu)001:19437: rang rtags phyag rgyas dbang bskur te //
NK078(tshu)001:19438: rig pa mchog gi dbang rnams bskur //
NK078(tshu)001:19439: 'dod pas mos pa'i tshig yin pas //
NK078(tshu)001:19440: nga rgyal mtshan ma'i bde ba thob //
NK078(tshu)001:19441: de yang bcos sla'i dbang gis bde gshegs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19443: gnyis pa kri ya'i lugs kyi gshegs tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:19446: spyi'i gnas wa ra na se'i bye brag sme khrod
NK078(tshu)001:19447: brtsegs pa mi gtsang ba'i dri ma med cing bsil
NK078(tshu)001:19450: dam pa kri ya'i rigs can si rtu sra ba /
NK078(tshu)001:19451: bram ze khyim bdag /ku ku ra tsa gsum la bskur //
NK078(tshu)001:19453: gtsang ma phyag na rdo rjes bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19454: rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19455: rdo rje rgya gram la sogs pa lha'i mngon rtags brgyad dam dgus bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19456: dgos ched ci'i phyir bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19457: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa la dgod pa'i ched du dbang bskur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:19458: 'bras bu rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob
NK078(tshu)001:19459: pa'i tshul ji bzhina du rjes 'jug rnams kyang de
NK078(tshu)001:19460: bzhin mthun no // de yang rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:19461: ba ra na se'i bsil khang du //
NK078(tshu)001:19462: gtsang ma lag na rdo rje yis //
NK078(tshu)001:19463: lag mthil gtsang ma'i dris byug la //
NK078(tshu)001:19464: rigs gsum stobs kyis dkyil 'khor bris //
NK078(tshu)001:19465: dam pa gsum la nges par brten //
NK078(tshu)001:19466: 'phrul gyi me long dgu bkram ste //
NK078(tshu)001:19467: dmigs pas dngos po'i rtog pa sbyong //
NK078(tshu)001:19468: lha yi mngon rtags lag tu gtad //
NK078(tshu)001:19469: gtsang ma'i sa la nges bkod de //
NK078(tshu)001:19470: de yang bcos ma'i sbyor ba yin //
NK078(tshu)001:19472: gsum pa sh+aaka thub gshegs tshul la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:19474: dang po theg pa gsum gyi 'dod pa'i thub pa gshegs tshul dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19476: sngon byung du sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang po yang /
NK078(tshu)001:19477: gong gi thun mong gi lam gyi gshegs tshul de ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:19480: rdo rje 'chang gi sa la gshegs pa'am /
NK078(tshu)001:19482: bya ba kri ya'i rgyud dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19483: gnyis ka spyod pa u pa ya'i rgyud la sogs
NK078(tshu)001:19484: pa rang rang so so'i gzhung las ji ltar grags
NK078(tshu)001:19485: pa bzhin du gshegs pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:19486: gnyis pa yo ga'i gzhung ltar gshegs tshul lo //
NK078(tshu)001:19488: rnal 'byor yo ga'i gzhung gi dbang gang la bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19489: rgyal bu don grub de nyid la /
NK078(tshu)001:19491: chu bo ne ra dza na'i 'grama logas su bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19492: dus nam gyi tshe bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19495: 'bras nyag ma re re gsol ba'i dka' thub kyi dka' ba sbyod pa'i tshe bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19497: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sprul pa'i sku rnams dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19498: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rigs lngas bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19499: rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19500: rin chen sna bdun la brten nas bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19501: tshul ji ltar du bskur na stong pa nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19505: sku yongs rdzogs dang mngon par byang chub pa dang rnam pa lnga'i stobs kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK078(tshu)001:19506: dgos ched ni 'di ltar du snang ba'i 'og min
NK078(tshu)001:19507: stug po bkod pa'i gnas nyid du rang bzhin gyi
NK078(tshu)001:19508: don 'grub ste / de'i sgra don grub pa'i tshul ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19509: sprul pa'i lus kyis bka' thub mdzad pa'i khog pa nas /
NK078(tshu)001:19510: sems nyid ye shes lngar rtogs pa'i rang gzugs la
NK078(tshu)001:19511: longs sku rnam par snang mdzad kyi lugs su gshegs
NK078(tshu)001:19513: ri rab kyi rtse mor rin po che'i khang bzang
NK078(tshu)001:19514: brtsegs par yo ga dum bu bzhi pa'i chos kyi
NK078(tshu)001:19515: 'khor lo sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la
NK078(tshu)001:19516: bskor nas don mdzad pa de /
NK078(tshu)001:19517: de yang ma h+aa la ltos na 'khor gyi rtog pa la snang ba'i gzugas sku yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:19518: de yang rna rgyud rdo rje zam pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:19519: rin chen lhun sdug brtsigs pa'i khang //
NK078(tshu)001:19520: ri bo 'bar ba'i rtse mo la //
NK078(tshu)001:19521: dpal byung phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK078(tshu)001:19522: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK078(tshu)001:19524: dam pa lnga la mngon du bstan //
NK078(tshu)001:19525: lha brag rdo rje'i rdzong phug tu //
NK078(tshu)001:19526: gtsang ma'i rig 'dzin gral du bkod //
NK078(tshu)001:19528: gnyis pa ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid gshegs lugs dpag pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19530: dang po thabs lam dang grol lam gnyis med kyi sgo nas gshegs lugs dpag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19532: ma h+aa rang gi bde gshegs de bzhin nyid du gshegs lugs gang zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:19533: thams lam dang shes rab grol lam gnyis med mnyam
NK078(tshu)001:19534: pa nyid kyi don nyams su blangs ba'i sgo nas
NK078(tshu)001:19535: snying po byang chub kyi 'gro 'ong gi rtog pa
NK078(tshu)001:19536: med par bde bar gshegas te /
NK078(tshu)001:19537: gzhi gnas lugs ci bzhin pa 'khor 'das lhun grub
NK078(tshu)001:19538: mnyam pa nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du nar
NK078(tshu)001:19540: 'og ma'i bde gshegs de bzhin gshegs pa pas dgongs
NK078(tshu)001:19541: pa'i bzhugs tshul dang ngo bo dang rnam grangs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:19542: khyad par dang gsum gyi che ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19543: gnyis pa sh+aaka thub gshegs lugs dpag pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19545: de yang dbang gnas gang du bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19546: chu bo ne ra dza na'i 'gram du /
NK078(tshu)001:19547: gang la bskur na rgyal bu don grub dka' thub kyi lus can de la /
NK078(tshu)001:19549: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad dbyar gyi sprin phung bzhin du 'dusa pa'i cha lugs ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19550: gsang ba'i ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rnams kyis bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19552: srod la rtog pa nub pa'i tshe gsang dbang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19553: tho rengsa ye shes skye ba'i dus nyid du shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur /
NK078(tshu)001:19554: rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK078(tshu)001:19555: ston pa yab yum gyi nyi zla byang sems lce
NK078(tshu)001:19556: thog tu bzhag pa khar bza' ba'i dabnga rdzas byin
NK078(tshu)001:19558: rol pa'i ka ra ste sbyor thabs kyi bstan chos
NK078(tshu)001:19559: bstan te sbyor du bcug pa'i thig le lugs su
NK078(tshu)001:19560: song ba'i yas bab kyi dga' ba bzhi la shes
NK078(tshu)001:19561: rab ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19562: thig le de nyid lugs su bzlog pa las mas
NK078(tshu)001:19563: brtan gyi dga' ba bzhi la shin tu brtan pa
NK078(tshu)001:19564: bde ba chen po rdzogs pa'i dbang thob pas gzhi
NK078(tshu)001:19565: don ji lta ba de bzhina du 'bras bu mngon
NK078(tshu)001:19567: rjes 'jug rnams kyang de bzhin du gshegs pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19568: de yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK078(tshu)001:19569: thabs dang lam gyi khyad par gyis //
NK078(tshu)001:19570: kun dga' rdo rje 'chang chen nyid //
NK078(tshu)001:19571: gtsang ma'i rigs dag spang pa yi //
NK078(tshu)001:19572: 'og min gnas mchog chen po der //
NK078(tshu)001:19573: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:19574: skal med skye bo 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:19575: sprul pa po de 'dir sangs rgyas //
NK078(tshu)001:19576: sangs rgyas kun gyi bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK078(tshu)001:19577: gtsang ma'i rigs dag rnam spang ba //
NK078(tshu)001:19578: 'dzin rten las kyi mthar thug pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19580: phyogs bcur rgya yongs ma chad pa'i //
NK078(tshu)001:19581: yon tan khyad par dpag pas na //
NK078(tshu)001:19582: gsang ba yum gyi b+ha ga la //
NK078(tshu)001:19583: bcu gsum sa yi dbang phyug ldan //
NK078(tshu)001:19584: rdo rje 'chang chen dpag med dang //
NK078(tshu)001:19585: til 'bru'i tshul du rab tu bzhugs //
NK078(tshu)001:19587: 'o na rgyal bu don 'grub 'di rgyu'i theg pas
NK078(tshu)001:19588: sprul sku sh+aakya thub tu sangs rgyas par 'dod la
NK078(tshu)001:19591: 'dir rdo rje 'chang chen du sangs rgyas par bshad pa 'di 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:19593: gdul bya'i ngo la rang rang gi bzhugs lugs ltar
NK078(tshu)001:19594: snang ba'i phyir theg pa thams cad kyis rang re'i
NK078(tshu)001:19595: sangs rgyas khor nar mthong nas nged kyi sangs rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:19597: de ni gdul bya'i snang ba'am drang don gyi sangs
NK078(tshu)001:19598: rgyas yin la nges don gyi sangs rgyas ni theg
NK078(tshu)001:19600: gsum pa des ni theg pa 'og ma las dpag tshul gtan tshigs dang bcas pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19602: gshegs lugs la khyad par yod pa de'i phyir thun
NK078(tshu)001:19603: mong gi theg pa byang sems kri yog rnam pa
NK078(tshu)001:19604: gsum dang ma h+aa dang bzhi las /
NK078(tshu)001:19605: byang ba bzhi'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19606: rgyu'i theg pas bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa mngon du byas tsam na /
NK078(tshu)001:19607: rnam par mi rtog pa'i rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:19608: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19609: shes bya sa bcu'i sgrib pa thams cad byang ba /
NK078(tshu)001:19610: kri yas rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19611: rig gsum stobs su byas pa'i rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis nyon mongs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19613: bcu gcig kun tu 'od man chad kyi sgrib pa byang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19614: yo gas stug po bkod pa'i sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19615: mtshan bcas dang mtshan ma med pa rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK078(tshu)001:19616: nyon mongs dang shes bya'i sgrib pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19617: u pa ya man chad kyi lta sgrib byang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19618: ma h+aa yo gas pad+ma spyan gyi sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19619: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin nam /
NK078(tshu)001:19620: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis nyon mongs dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19622: yo ga man chad kyi lta sgrib byang ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19624: rgyu'i kun tu 'od sku gsum gyi ngo bor chub /
NK078(tshu)001:19625: kri ya rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa rigs gsum gyi ngo bor chub /
NK078(tshu)001:19626: yo ga rigs lnga'i ngo bor chub /
NK078(tshu)001:19627: ma h+aa yo ga sku lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor chub pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19628: bde bar gshegs pa bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19629: rgyu'i theg pas bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19630: sa bcu pa man chad kyi nyon mongs rnam rtog gi zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK078(tshu)001:19631: bdag gzhan gyi don gyi phyir gshegs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19632: kri yas rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19633: kun tu 'od man chad kyi nyon mongs rnam rtog zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK078(tshu)001:19634: bdag gzhan gyi don phyir gshegs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19635: yo gas stug po bkod pa'i sa ma ngon du byas tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19636: kri ya man chad kyi nyon mongs rnam rtog zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK078(tshu)001:19637: bdag gzhan don phyir gshegs pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19638: ma h+aa yo gas pad+ma spyan gyi sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19639: yo ga man chad kyi nyon mongs rnam rtog gi
NK078(tshu)001:19640: zug rngu med pas bde bar bdag gzhan gyi don
NK078(tshu)001:19642: de bzhin gshegs pa bzhi'i khyad par ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19643: dbu mas don dam pa'i bden pa stong zhing spros pa dang bral ba de bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:19644: de'i don nar son pas gshegs /
NK078(tshu)001:19645: kri yas sems dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba de bzhin /
NK078(tshu)001:19646: yo gas chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba de bzhin /
NK078(tshu)001:19647: ma h+aa yo gas snang ba dang stong pa gnyis su med pas de bzhin /
NK078(tshu)001:19648: de dag gi don nar son pas gshegs pa dang brgyad do //
NK078(tshu)001:19652: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen sku gsung thugs yon
NK078(tshu)001:19653: tan phrin las nyer lnga'i grangsa rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi
NK078(tshu)001:19654: khyad par dang / 'bras bu'i ngo bo gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19655: byin rlabs dang rtsal la sogs pa'i yon tan gyis khyad par 'phags pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19656: gnyis pa rgyal ba bcom ldan 'das kyi khyad par gtan tshigs dang bcas pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19658: des na theg pa so so'i rgyal ba dang bcom ldan 'das la yang /
NK078(tshu)001:19659: theg pa thun mong gi dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19660: mchog ma h+aa'i bcom ldan 'das dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19661: lugs gnyis ni snga ma bzhina du yod pa yin /
NK078(tshu)001:19662: de dag gi don rgyas par bshad na theg pa
NK078(tshu)001:19663: bzhi so so'i thabs lam dang shes raba grol lam
NK078(tshu)001:19664: gnyis kyis rgyu'i theg pa'i kun tu 'od kyi skabs
NK078(tshu)001:19665: su rnam par mi rtog pa stobs su byas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19666: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19667: kri yas rigs gsum stobs su gyur pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19668: yo gas mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi stobs su dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19669: ma h+aa yo gas dbyer med stobs su byas pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19670: rdo rje lta bu'ii ting nge 'dzin bzhi rgyud la
NK078(tshu)001:19674: lha'i bu'i bdud dang bzhi nges par bcom zhing rang rang gi 'bras bu'i yon tan dang ldan te /
NK078(tshu)001:19675: rang rang gi sdug bsngal gyi mya ngan bzhi las 'das shing /
NK078(tshu)001:19676: yod med rtag chad kyi mtha' bzhi las 'das pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19677: de ltar theg pa gong 'og mi mthuna pa tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:19678: rang rang gi bzhung gi rang rang gi 'bras bu
NK078(tshu)001:19679: sangs rgyas thob pa de yang theg pa de dag
NK078(tshu)001:19680: rang rang gi rtogs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19681: rjes mthun gyi spyod pa dang nyams len ting nge
NK078(tshu)001:19682: 'dzin gyi lam rnams la gong 'og gi rim pa'am
NK078(tshu)001:19683: khyad par yod pa bzhin du /
NK078(tshu)001:19684: mthar thug gruba pa'i mtha'a 'bras bu sangs rgyas rnams
NK078(tshu)001:19685: la yang rim pa bzhin du khyad par yod pa
NK078(tshu)001:19686: ste / de'i rgyu mtshan ni lta ba mtho dman
NK078(tshu)001:19687: gyi rim pa'i chas 'og ma'i lta bas gong ma'i
NK078(tshu)001:19688: lta don la sgrib pas de bas na khyad phye
NK078(tshu)001:19689: ste / ba yin no // de yang bang mdzod las /
NK078(tshu)001:19691: gong ma ma mthong sgrib pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:19694: ro rnyed gser gyi rgyu 'bras sku //
NK078(tshu)001:19695: sku ru mnyam ste rgyu 'bras che //
NK078(tshu)001:19698: de bzhin theg pa che chung gi //
NK078(tshu)001:19699: rgyu 'bras lta ba phye ba yin //
NK078(tshu)001:19700: de ltar 'og ma kun brtag pas //
NK078(tshu)001:19701: 'bras bu'am kun brtag mthar phyin zad //
NK078(tshu)001:19702: gong ma gong ma de grol bas //
NK078(tshu)001:19705: sa dang lam la sogs pa yin //
NK078(tshu)001:19706: theg pa kun gyi 'bras bu ni //
NK078(tshu)001:19707: rang rang ltos pa'i mthar thug kyang //
NK078(tshu)001:19708: che mchog lhun grub mnyam dang bral //
NK078(tshu)001:19710: gsum pa dgyes pa longs spyod kyi khyad par dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19712: de ltar theg pa so so'i bcom ldan 'das la khyad par yod pa des na /
NK078(tshu)001:19713: dgyes pa chen po la yang khyad yod par bstan pa yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:19714: dgyes pa chen po'i longsa spyod kyi khyad par yang /
NK078(tshu)001:19715: mdo sde ste rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19717: rnal 'byor rgyud gyi yo ga gnyisa kyi rgyud gzhung
NK078(tshu)001:19718: so so las ji ltar gsungs pa bzhina tu longs
NK078(tshu)001:19720: gong gi ma h+aa'i dgyes pa chena po ni 'og ma'i yin tshod du gyur pa min no //
NK078(tshu)001:19721: bzhi pa 'bras bu'i khyad par la bzhi ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19723: dang po sangs rgyas pa'i khyad par bstan pa dngos dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19725: snga ma'i gtan tshigs de yi phyir theg pa gong
NK078(tshu)001:19726: 'og gi dgyes pa chen la rim pa yod pas
NK078(tshu)001:19727: / theg pa so so'i rang sa'i 'bras bu sangs
NK078(tshu)001:19728: rgyas rnams la khyad par gyi rim pa yod pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19729: / phyir na / ming gi rnam grangs sam yon
NK078(tshu)001:19730: tan gyi cha shas tsam gyis khyad par phye ba
NK078(tshu)001:19731: / phyir na / min tee / theg pa gong
NK078(tshu)001:19732: 'og gi 'bras bu ngo bo nyid kyisa mi 'dra
NK078(tshu)001:19734: 'og ma'i 'bras bu bas ma h+aa 'bras bu khyad par 'phags pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19735: gnyis pa thun mong gi sa gsum drang don du bstan pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19737: de yang theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu bshad pa la dgos ched ci yod ce na /
NK078(tshu)001:19738: theg pa 'og ma ba so so'i lam gyi rtsol
NK078(tshu)001:19739: bas shes rgyud ngal ba rnams 'bras bu la blo
NK078(tshu)001:19741: byang sems la kun tu 'od kyi sa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19742: kri ya la rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19743: yo ga la stug po bkod pa'i sa zhes bya bar bstan pa yin la /
NK078(tshu)001:19744: gsum pa mthar thug gi sa gsum yon tan gyi cha las btag pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19748: pad+ma spyan du gyur pa na //
NK078(tshu)001:19750: theg pa 'og ma'i 'bras bu'i mthar thug ma h+aa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19751: 'bras bu sa ni pad+ma spyan dang yi ge 'khor
NK078(tshu)001:19753: ye shes bla ma'i sa dang gsum ni bzang ngan
NK078(tshu)001:19754: dang mtho dman gyi khyad par med de yon tan
NK078(tshu)001:19757: sa yi khyad par bcu dang gsum //
NK078(tshu)001:19758: rgyu 'bras khyad par lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:19761: spyod yul bral bas ma chags phyir //
NK078(tshu)001:19762: chu skyes spyan gyi sa yang rdzogs //
NK078(tshu)001:19763: phung sogs rang bzhin lhar snang bas //
NK078(tshu)001:19764: mngon byas tshogs chen sa yang thob //
NK078(tshu)001:19765: de nyid rang bzhin 'od gsal bas //
NK078(tshu)001:19766: mngon gyur ye shes bla ma'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19768: 'o na ma h+aa'i mthar thug gi sa gsum la khyad par yod dam med /
NK078(tshu)001:19769: yod na mthar thug ma yin par thal /
NK078(tshu)001:19770: med na khyad yod par bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK078(tshu)001:19771: 'bras bu'i sa gsum rang gi ngo bo bzang ngan dang mtho dman gyi khyad med kyang /
NK078(tshu)001:19772: mtshon tshul dang byed las kyi dgos ched kyi yon
NK078(tshu)001:19773: tan ma 'dres pa'i cha nas bshad pas 'gal ba
NK078(tshu)001:19774: med do // bzhi pa sa gong 'og gi rim pa dpe'i sgo nas bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19776: theg pa la khyad par yod pa de'i phyir theg
NK078(tshu)001:19777: pa gong 'og gi so so'i 'bras bu'i khyad par
NK078(tshu)001:19778: skas kyi gdang bu lta bur mtho dman rim pa
NK078(tshu)001:19779: yod pa ste / de yang gdul bya 'dren pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19780: thabs la mkhas pa nang pa ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK078(tshu)001:19782: mthar thug gi 'bras bu dngos su thob par byed
NK078(tshu)001:19783: pa 'di la dngos su 'jug ma nus pa rnams
NK078(tshu)001:19784: / thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pa la gzhan
NK078(tshu)001:19785: pa yis thun mong lam stegs kyi theg pa'i thabsa
NK078(tshu)001:19786: la brten nas gang mos su 'jug bcug cing /
NK078(tshu)001:19787: de nas theg pa 'og ma nas gong ma nyid du 'du shes bsgyur nas /
NK078(tshu)001:19788: mthar thug ma h+aa yo ga 'di yis 'bras bu 'grub par 'gyur la /
NK078(tshu)001:19789: thun mong gi theg pa rang gi lam gyi thabs
NK078(tshu)001:19790: sna tshogs kyi sgo nas theg pa rang sa'i 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:19792: theg 'og thun mong dang mchog gi theg pa'i 'bras
NK078(tshu)001:19793: bu gnyis ngo bo nyid gcig cing khyad med par
NK078(tshu)001:19794: smra ba'i gang zag rnams ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19795: ma h+aa'i don ma mthong ba'i mun sprul gyi blo can yin pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19796: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu la khyad par yod pa'i rgyun mtshan ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19797: gsang sngags bla med kyi rgyud gzhung zab mo thams cad nas ston la /
NK078(tshu)001:19798: de nyid kyi dgongs pa'i bcud phyungs pa'i man ngag gi bdag po /
NK078(tshu)001:19799: rgya gar gyi mkhas grub chen po /
NK078(tshu)001:19805: sgeg pa rdo rje la sogs pa'i rgya gzhung thams cad nas gsungs la /
NK078(tshu)001:19806: bod kyi so zur gnubs gsum nas gzung te dam
NK078(tshu)001:19807: pa yab sras la sogs pa'i bla ma rnams kyi
NK078(tshu)001:19808: dgongs pa mthun par gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:19809: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19812: lam lnga'i gzhi'i don ji lta ba mthar phyin pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19813: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa'i rnam
NK078(tshu)001:19814: bzhag bstan pa'i gzhung don rnams mtshams dang ris su
NK078(tshu)001:19815: gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyi na
NK078(tshu)001:19817: de'i rnam grangs dagu yod pa las /
NK078(tshu)001:19818: yas bgrang dgu pa'i don du gada'o ////spyi don gsum pa 'jug gi don la gnyis te /
NK078(tshu)001:19819: brtsam pa'i dge ba 'gro ba yongs la bsngo ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19820: snod ngan dang ma 'phrad par smon lam btab pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19823: dang po gang gi phyir brtsams pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19825: 'gro ba lam log pa ni mu stegs yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:19826: de la rtag lta bzhi ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19831: chad lta rgyang 'phen pa dang lnga yin pa zur byams pa seng ges gsungs so //
NK078(tshu)001:19834: ngan song gsum dang lnga tshan gnyis po'i sems can rnams /
NK078(tshu)001:19837: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sa la dkri ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir /
NK078(tshu)001:19838: gnyis pa gang brtsams pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19840: 'khor 'das tha dad du mi gnyis te gnyis su med par ston pa'i /
NK078(tshu)001:19843: rdzogs pa'i lam mchog rnam par bkod pa 'di ni sangs rgyas gsang ba bdag gis bgyis pa'i /
NK078(tshu)001:19844: gsum pa de ltar brtsams pa'i dge ba'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19846: sgo gsum ngal ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba gang yin
NK078(tshu)001:19847: pa des 'gro ba sems can kun kyang yang dag
NK078(tshu)001:19848: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sar sgrol bar shog
NK078(tshu)001:19849: cig ces bsngo ba yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:19850: gnyis pa snod ngan dang ma 'phrad cig pa la gsum ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19852: dang po snod ngan gyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19854: bla na med pa'i byang chub gtso bor mi gnyer
NK078(tshu)001:19855: bar brtsam na kha na ma tho zhor la byed
NK078(tshu)001:19856: cing 'jig rten tshe 'di'i khe dang grags pa ched
NK078(tshu)001:19857: du gnyer ba dang gsang sngags kyi bcud chen po'i
NK078(tshu)001:19858: man ngag dang lta sgom gsang mi thub nas snod
NK078(tshu)001:19860: man ngag zab mo gzhan la gzhog ngoms can gyi gang zag dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19861: gnyis pa snod ngan gyi dpe dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19863: sngon byung rgyal bu mu tig 'bebs zhes bya ba gad mo bzhad tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19864: kha nas mu tig mang po sha ra ra skyugs pa zhig yod pa la /
NK078(tshu)001:19865: rgyal po stobs bzang zhes bya ba zhig yod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:19866: mu tig 'dod pa'i ched du rgyal bu bos nas
NK078(tshu)001:19867: snang g.yel che ba zhig tu bzhag nas gad mo
NK078(tshu)001:19868: bsgug pas / rgyal po de'i btsun mo gtsug rgyan
NK078(tshu)001:19869: la sgeg mo zhes bya ba gcig 'khor rnams kyis
NK078(tshu)001:19870: rin po che'i khri la bzhag ste /
NK078(tshu)001:19871: rgyal pos rin po che'i sor gdub chung ngu brgyab pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19872: 'khor rnams kyi me tog gtor ba phog tsam na a na na zer zhing ngu la /
NK078(tshu)001:19873: bram ze skog nag ces bya ba zhig dang dus
NK078(tshu)001:19874: btab byas shing dus bcags pa las khos ber rgas
NK078(tshu)001:19875: brdung tsa na / he he zer ba zhig mthong ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19876: 'jag skyil ste bram ze'i drang srong me len sbur skyil zhes bya ba /
NK078(tshu)001:19877: de'i mchod gnas shig 'dug pa des /
NK078(tshu)001:19878: ngas ma byin pa len pa spang ba yin zer zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:19879: gzhan la me slang tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19880: chos gos la rdul 'byar ba bskyal du 'ong /
NK078(tshu)001:19881: phags su nor thob tshad rku ba zhig yod pas /
NK078(tshu)001:19882: mgar ba'i khyim na gser gyi sgrom bu zhig yod pa mthong nas /
NK078(tshu)001:19883: mkhar sil gyi gsham du gar spyin bskus nas /
NK078(tshu)001:19884: mgar ba'i khyim gyi gser gyi sgrom bu la /
NK078(tshu)001:19885: mkhar sil mi tshor bar btsugs te /
NK078(tshu)001:19886: sga sbur med par gser brkus pa dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19887: ne la bya lta bu'i ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19888: ne tso lta bu kha na gshog tshags yin te /
NK078(tshu)001:19889: ne co gcig gi kha na gshog pa'i sgro gtsug nas chu 'thung zhing 'dug pa mthong ba las /
NK078(tshu)001:19891: chu la srog chags 'dug pa shi'i dgos pa yin zer /
NK078(tshu)001:19892: mi mi 'dug pa'i tshe na srog chags mthong tshad btu zhing za ba mthong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:19894: kho mo ku ma ri'i a ma yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:19895: mos khyo la ma dga' nas /
NK078(tshu)001:19896: ngas skyes pa pho dang reg pa spang ba yin zhing /
NK078(tshu)001:19897: bu la nu ma blud tsa na /
NK078(tshu)001:19898: gos la bug pa phug nas blud /
NK078(tshu)001:19899: phags su skyes pa pho dang 'khrigs pa spyod pa mthong ngo //
NK078(tshu)001:19900: sogs kyi sgras dka' thub ral gri 'greng bsgom lta bu'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19901: der rgyal pos rgyal bu la /
NK078(tshu)001:19902: khyod rgod bro ba byung ste ma rgod pa yin byas pas /
NK078(tshu)001:19904: nga rgod bro ba ma byung /
NK078(tshu)001:19905: yi mug pa zhig byung gsungs /
NK078(tshu)001:19906: de ji ltar du yi mug gsungs pas /
NK078(tshu)001:19907: rgyal bus de'i don tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
NK078(tshu)001:19908: rgyal mo me tog 'thor bshum dang //
NK078(tshu)001:19909: drang srong me len sbur skyil dang //
NK078(tshu)001:19910: ne tso kha nas gshog thog nas //
NK078(tshu)001:19911: ku ma ra yi a ma sogs //
NK078(tshu)001:19912: mi dge bcu la 'chol nyog spyod //
NK078(tshu)001:19913: mu tig 'bebs las ma gtogs pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19914: bden par smra ba ngas ma mthong //
NK078(tshu)001:19915: ha ha nga ni rgod re bro //
NK078(tshu)001:19917: mu tig 'khyor ba gang tsam lhur gyis byung skad do //
NK078(tshu)001:19918: gsum pa snod ngan gyi dbye ba bstan pa'o //
NK078(tshu)001:19920: de lta bu'i gang zag gis /
NK078(tshu)001:19921: dam tshig dang sdom pa rnams tshul 'chos tsam du
NK078(tshu)001:19922: bsrung bar byed cing yang dag pa'i dam tshig la
NK078(tshu)001:19924: gasnga ba theg pa chen po'i gzhung zab mo'i don
NK078(tshu)001:19925: nyams su blang ba la shes rab gsum gyis bsran
NK078(tshu)001:19926: mi tshugs shing brtson 'grus chung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19927: gzhung dang man ngag sna mang du bsgrub cing don
NK078(tshu)001:19928: du gnyer bar byed pa la de dag gang la
NK078(tshu)001:19929: yang yid ches par dka' ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19930: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon nyid spyi bos gus par mi len cing bkur sti chung ba dang /
NK078(tshu)001:19931: bla ma dang mched lcam rnams la zhe nas skur
NK078(tshu)001:19932: ba 'debs shing sems can yongs la'ang gnod par byed
NK078(tshu)001:19933: pa'i gang zag de lta bu snod med pa rnams
NK078(tshu)001:19934: dang / man ngag zab mo 'di dang ma 'phrada par gyur cig /ces gsungs pa yin no //
NK078(tshu)001:19935: spyi don gsum pa brtsam pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK078(tshu)001:19936: chos 'di bsgyur ba spyi'i gnas ni mang yul /
NK078(tshu)001:19937: bye brag tu khri bab ces bya ba'i gnas su /
NK078(tshu)001:19938: zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku
NK078(tshu)001:19939: m+aa ra ste ye shes gzhon nu zhes bya bas
NK078(tshu)001:19942: bye brag tu brjod bya'i gtso bo ni lam rgyas
NK078(tshu)001:19943: par ston pas lam rnam par bkod pa zhes bya
NK078(tshu)001:19944: ba // mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub brnyes
NK078(tshu)001:19945: pa'i slob dpon mkhas pa chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK078(tshu)001:19946: bas mdzad pa tshegs chung la don che ba'i man
NK078(tshu)001:19947: ngag /rdzogs so zhes pa'i tshig don ma lus pa'i
NK078(tshu)001:19948: ba // tha tshig gam / gnas skabs re zhig
NK078(tshu)001:19949: bshad du ma mchis pas na rdzogs so ////rgyud lung
NK078(tshu)001:19950: man ngag brgyud pa'i chu gter las //
NK078(tshu)001:19951: blo gros klu yi dbang pos legs bzung zhing //
NK078(tshu)001:19952: thos bsam bsgom pa dag gis 'bad pa yis //
NK078(tshu)001:19953: man ngag rin chen nor bu chu dwangs rnyed //
NK078(tshu)001:19954: 'di yang gsang bdag sprul pa sgro phug pa //
NK078(tshu)001:19955: gzhung lugs mkhas pa'i dgongs pa ma nor bar //
NK078(tshu)001:19956: bla ma brgyud pa'i gsung sgros gtsor bzhag nas //
NK078(tshu)001:19957: rje yi ngo sprod man ngag 'di byas so //
NK078(tshu)001:19958: 'grel tika brtsams pa'i nus tshad ldan min pas //
NK078(tshu)001:19959: nyes pa gang mchis bdag gi skyon yin te //
NK078(tshu)001:19960: mkhas mchog rnams kyis bzod mdzod rjes zung rigs //
NK078(tshu)001:19961: legs pa gang mchis mkhas grub gong ma'i bzhed //
NK078(tshu)001:19962: sbyor ba lhag bsam dag pa'i chu dwangs kyis //
NK078(tshu)001:19963: dngos gzhi'i gzhung don mi shes rab rib dwangs //
NK078(tshu)001:19964: rjes kyi dge ba shes bya'i gzugs brnyan 'char //
NK078(tshu)001:19965: bdag gzhan gnyis chos don bzhi mthar phyin shog /sangs rgyas bstan pa rab dkar phu lung nas //
NK078(tshu)001:19966: gsang sngags rmad byung theg chen chu klung las //
NK078(tshu)001:19967: thos bsam sgom gsum rba rlabs chil chil lang //
NK078(tshu)001:19968: nyams myong rtogs pa'i gsung snyan lhang lhang sgrog /blo gros rna dbang ldan pa'i gang zag gis //
NK078(tshu)001:19969: de lta'i don la mi sems su zhig yod //
NK078(tshu)001:19970: dad brtson pra dz+ny+aa med pas thos mi 'gyur //
NK078(tshu)001:19971: 'on kyang kha che'i yul na gur gum r+ts+wa //
NK078(tshu)001:19972: ma la ya na tsan+da na nags //
NK078(tshu)001:19973: rgya mtsho'i 'gram na rin chen nor bu rdo //
NK078(tshu)001:19974: nye skyo rgyang na rin thang che //
NK078(tshu)001:19975: de phyir de dang de dag gis //
NK078(tshu)001:19976: rgyu mtshan dgos ched blang ba gces //
NK078(tshu)001:19977: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba stong phrag brgyad pa'i bcud bsdus pa /
NK078(tshu)001:19978: rgya gar gyi mkhas grub chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK078(tshu)001:19979: bas mdzad pa'i sgyu 'phrul man ngag lam gyi rim
NK078(tshu)001:19980: pa'i 'grel bshad nor bu chu dwangs zhes bya ba
NK078(tshu)001:19981: 'di nyid / bla ma brgyud pa mkhas btsun gong
NK078(tshu)001:19982: ma rnams kyis 'grel bshad gsung sgros tshad ma rnams
NK078(tshu)001:19983: 'di nyid / dang / khyad par du bdag la
NK078(tshu)001:19984: bka' drin che ba'i slob dpon mkhas grub chen po
NK078(tshu)001:19986: ga ga ke tu yab sras gnyis kyi zhal shes ngo sprod kyi man ngag la brten nas /
NK078(tshu)001:19987: mkhas btsun dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyis yang yang bskul ba'i ngor /
NK078(tshu)001:19988: sh+aakya'i dge slong nam mkha' dpal gyis me mo lug gi lo'i zla ba brgyad pa'i yar tshes la /
NK078(tshu)001:19989: kah thog rdo rje'i gdan ma g+ha d+ha gnyis pa
NK078(tshu)001:19990: chos gling dgon du sbyar ba re zhig rdzogs so
